NK028(sa)001:2: mdo dbang gi dpe tho la /
NK028(sa)001:4: mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi dbang gi sa bcad /
NK028(sa)001:5: dbang don sbrang rtsi'i chu rgyun /
NK028(sa)001:8: yang bla ma brgyud pa'i gsol 'debs /
NK028(sa)001:10: nyan thos dbang gi them skas //
NK028(sa)001:11: rang sangs rgyas kyi dbang gi them skas //
NK028(sa)001:12: byang chub sems dpa'i dbang gi them skas //
NK028(sa)001:13: kri ya'i dbang gi the ma skas //
NK028(sa)001:14: yo ga'i dbang gi them skas //
NK028(sa)001:15: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i dbang gi cho ga /
NK028(sa)001:16: sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i dbang gi cho ga /
NK028(sa)001:18: mdo dbang gi khro bo'i mngon rtogs /
NK028(sa)001:19: sems sde bco brgyad kyi dbang gi cho ga /
NK028(sa)001:20: dngos grub blangs pa'i cho ga rnams bzhugs //////
NK028(sa)001:23: lce la bdud rtsi bzhag ste slob dpon gyis //
NK028(sa)001:24: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK028(sa)001:25: byang chub sems dang rdo rje 'dzin //
NK028(sa)001:26: de bzhin bsgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK028(sa)001:27: de dag la ni snying ring na //
NK028(sa)001:28: rdo rje yak+sha gnod sbyin gyis //
NK028(sa)001:29: khyod kyi snying la bzhos te 'thung //
NK028(sa)001:30: snying la yang dag gnas pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:31: 'di ni sems can dmyal ba'i chu //
NK028(sa)001:32: i dan ti na ra kan /
NK028(sa)001:34: zhes mna' dgag cing dam sgrag go /
NK028(sa)001:35: tshigs su bcad pa de nyid kyi don yang bshad //
NK028(sa)001:36: dpal ldan sangs rgyas sku 'chang ba //
NK028(sa)001:37: rdo rje mi phyed sku dang ldan //
NK028(sa)001:38: de dag byin gyis rlabs nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:39: rdo rje sku yi dngos grub rtsol //
NK028(sa)001:40: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ka ya badz+ra swa b+ha wa at+ma ko ham /
NK028(sa)001:42: bdun pa dam tshig sbyin pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:44: a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:45: a la la ste mnyes par mdzod //
NK028(sa)001:46: a la la ste dam tshig bskongs //
NK028(sa)001:47: a la la ste dngos grub stsol //
NK028(sa)001:48: dpal ldan rdo rje sku 'chang ba //
NK028(sa)001:49: mi phyed rdo rje'i sku rang bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:50: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas ni //
NK028(sa)001:51: rdo rje'i sku ru mdzad du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:53: dbang phyug gi ban+d+hara bdud rtsi cung zad blugs la /
NK028(sa)001:54: +aahh+aum zhes brjod cing sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin yig 'bru gsum gsal bar bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:55: badz+ra a mri ta h+aum hri tha //
NK028(sa)001:56: zhes pa'i sngags lan gsum gyis bdud rtsir chur byin gyis rlabs nas /
NK028(sa)001:57: dbang phyug gi phyag g.yas pa rdo rje dang bcas pa'i srin lag gi bdud rtsi blangs la /
NK028(sa)001:58: slob ma rnams kyi dpral bar zhes brjod cing /
NK028(sa)001:59: thig le byas la +amo dkar po bsam /
NK028(sa)001:61: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad sku'i byin rlabs bsdus nas /
NK028(sa)001:62: dpral ba'i la thim par bsam la /
NK028(sa)001:63: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya badz+ra swa b+ha wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK028(sa)001:64: zhes brjod cing byin gyis rlabs pas /
NK028(sa)001:65: slob bus dam tshig thob par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:66: de bzhin du dpal rdo rje gsung 'chang ba //
NK028(sa)001:67: mi phyed rdo rje gsung rang bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:68: deng bdag byin gyis rlabs nas ni //
NK028(sa)001:69: rdo rje'i gsung du mdzad du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:71: slob bu'i mgrin par thig le byas pa'i +aa'i 'phro 'du dang /
NK028(sa)001:72: wa ka badz+ra'i sngags kyi gsung gi dam tshig thob par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:73: yang dpal ldan rdo rje'i thugs 'chang ba //
NK028(sa)001:74: mi phyed rdo rje'i thugs rang bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:75: deng bdag byin gyis rlabs nas ni //
NK028(sa)001:76: rdo rje'i thugs su mdzad du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:77: zhes gsol ba btab pas slob bu'i snying khar thig le byas pa /
NK028(sa)001:78: h+aum 'phro dang tsit+ta badz+ra'i sngags kyi thugs kyi dam tshig thob par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:79: brgyad pa dam tshig dbab pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:80: dbang phyug gi slob bu'i snying khar rdo rje bzhag la /
NK028(sa)001:81: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba 'di //
NK028(sa)001:82: dam nyams ma 'dres med pa la //
NK028(sa)001:83: nam yang smra bar ma byed cig /
NK028(sa)001:84: theg pa chen po ston byed pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:85: nga la brnyas dang smad mi rung //
NK028(sa)001:86: sku gsung thugs la rtag gnas shing //
NK028(sa)001:87: ma lus sems can don gyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:89: dgu pa chu nan bya ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:90: tsan dan dkar dmar sbyar ba'i chu la //
NK028(sa)001:91: cho ga gsum gyis rdo rje sems dpar bskyed cing //
NK028(sa)001:92: ye shes pa bcug pas bdud rtsir zhu bar bsam la /
NK028(sa)001:93: thog mar skyon gyi sgo nas chu nan bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:94: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK028(sa)001:95: dam tshig nyams na sreg par byed /
NK028(sa)001:96: rdo rje'i chu ni 'thung bar gyis /
NK028(sa)001:100: slob bu'i lce la lan gsum bzhag go //
NK028(sa)001:101: yon tan gyi sgo nas nan tan bya ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:102: 'di lta bas na bu khyod kyis //
NK028(sa)001:103: dam tshig 'di dag bsrung bar gyis //
NK028(sa)001:104: dam tshig bsrungs na dngos grub pas //
NK028(sa)001:105: rdo rje bdud rtsi chu 'thung zhig /
NK028(sa)001:106: badz+ra ush+tha ka tra h+aum phata ces brjod cing rdo
NK028(sa)001:107: rjes chu blangs la lan gsum slob bu'i lce la
NK028(sa)001:108: bzhag go / slob bu kun la chu nan zin rjes /
NK028(sa)001:110: de ltar bdud rtsi'i chu de lce la bzhag kyang /
NK028(sa)001:111: babs pa snying gi dkyil du babs nas /
NK028(sa)001:112: gal te dam tshig ma bsrungs na /
NK028(sa)001:113: chu de rdo rje gnod sbyin zhes bya ba /
NK028(sa)001:114: lcags kyi sdig pa mgo dgu par gyur nas /
NK028(sa)001:116: tshe thung zhing nad mang ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:117: tshe phyi ma dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal gyi nyams thag par 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:118: dam tshig bsrungs na chu de rdo rje sems dpar gyur nas /
NK028(sa)001:119: des rtag tu byin gyis rlobs cing /
NK028(sa)001:123: nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi dang gdon stong phrag brgyad cus mi tshugs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:124: phyi mar bla na med pa'i byang chub thob nas /
NK028(sa)001:125: sems can thams cad mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las
NK028(sa)001:126: 'das pa'i gnas su 'dren pa'i ded dpon byed par
NK028(sa)001:128: bcu pa dam bsgrags pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:129: dbang phyug gi phyag g.yas pa rdo rje dang bcas pa slob bu rnams kyi spyi bor bzhag la /
NK028(sa)001:130: thabs dang shes rab sems nyid kyi //
NK028(sa)001:131: rtag tu gos pa med bgyis la //
NK028(sa)001:133: gzhan yang stong khams thams cad na /
NK028(sa)001:134: shes rab dbyings dang 'dod yon gzhan //
NK028(sa)001:135: rab 'bring tha mas thams cad spyod //
NK028(sa)001:136: gzhan yang dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:137: skye bo gang zhig dam ma gnod //
NK028(sa)001:138: brtul shugs can gyi de grongs la //
NK028(sa)001:139: khrag chen snying la bstung bar bgyis //
NK028(sa)001:140: 'di la mi bya cung zad med //
NK028(sa)001:141: sems nyid theg par rab nges na //
NK028(sa)001:142: nyon mongs 'dod la kun spyod kyang //
NK028(sa)001:144: tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:145: bya dang mi bya cung zad med //
NK028(sa)001:147: spyi don gnyis pa dbang slob bu la bskur ba la gsum te /
NK028(sa)001:152: slob bu rnams kyis dbang phyug dang /
NK028(sa)001:153: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la phyag btsal nas /
NK028(sa)001:155: dpal ldan sangs rgyas kun bdag nyid //
NK028(sa)001:156: brtse bar dgongs te bdag la yang //
NK028(sa)001:157: dbang bskur bdud rtsi chen po nyid //
NK028(sa)001:158: de ring rab tu rtsal bar mdzod /
NK028(sa)001:159: ces gsol ba gdab par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:161: sangs rgyas dag ni thams cad kyis //
NK028(sa)001:162: gsang ba rdo rje gsum las byung //
NK028(sa)001:163: khams gsum kun gyi phyag byas pa //
NK028(sa)001:164: dbang bskur snang ba chen po sbyin //
NK028(sa)001:166: spos dang rol mo dang bcas pas //
NK028(sa)001:167: kun gyis dkyil 'khor la bskor zhing //
NK028(sa)001:168: dkyil 'khor kyi lha tshogs la phyogs bcu dus bzhis bstod nas //
NK028(sa)001:169: be ka kra ma yam gyi sngags dang /
NK028(sa)001:170: phyag rgyas gzhal yas lha dang bcas pa mdun nam mkhar btegs la /
NK028(sa)001:171: dbang phyug gi me tog dang bcas pas thal mo sbyar nas gsol ba gdab par bya te //
NK028(sa)001:172: ho phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:173: bdag rdo rje che ge mo la sogs pa'i slob bu 'di rnams la lha mi'i dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:174: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis bdag la mthu bstan du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:176: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis /
NK028(sa)001:177: lha dang mi yi dkyil 'khor du /
NK028(sa)001:178: rdo rje shugs kyis bsgral nas kyang /
NK028(sa)001:179: byin rlabs dam pa nod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:184: gsang ba gsang chen gsang mchog gang //
NK028(sa)001:185: gsang ba kun la gnyan par bya //
NK028(sa)001:186: gsang ba'i don nyid brtag pa las //
NK028(sa)001:187: gzhan du smra bar bya ba min //
NK028(sa)001:189: bskur gnas slob bu'i lag gtad nas /
NK028(sa)001:191: nyan shes kyi thig le la bstims pas /
NK028(sa)001:192: sngon chad bka' phyi nang gi chos thams cad la
NK028(sa)001:193: thogs pa med par nyan mi nus pa'i sgrib pa
NK028(sa)001:194: dag nas / da phyin chad nyan nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:196: rigs kyi bu 'di rnams la nyan pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:197: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka' phyi nang thams cad la
NK028(sa)001:198: thogs pa med par nyan nus pa'i dbang dam pa
NK028(sa)001:200: gnyis pa bsgom dbang la bsam rgyu ni /
NK028(sa)001:201: dbang phyug gi thugs ka nas b+h+rum chad de /
NK028(sa)001:202: slob bu rnams kyi snying gi 'dom rtsar 'phros pa las gzhal yas khang dbus 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK028(sa)001:204: yang dbang phyug gi thugs ka nas am zung lnga dang /
NK028(sa)001:206: h+aum h+aum h+aum bam h+aum ho bcu 'phros pa 'od du zhu ba las /
NK028(sa)001:207: phyag mtshan bcu de 'od du zhu ba las /
NK028(sa)001:209: dbus su rnam snang yab yum /
NK028(sa)001:216: rdo rje chags pa yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:217: sgo bzhir sgo ba yab yum bzhi sgom /
NK028(sa)001:223: mchod bstod 'od du zhu ba las //
NK028(sa)001:224: slob bu rnam snang du bskyed la /
NK028(sa)001:226: dus gsum rgyal ba'i sras chen po //
NK028(sa)001:227: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje zung //
NK028(sa)001:228: rgyal ba thams cad mnyes mchod la //
NK028(sa)001:229: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor /
NK028(sa)001:235: sngon chad lha dang mi rtog dbyer med bsgom mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:236: da bsgom nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:239: lha dang mi rtog pa thams cad la thogs pa
NK028(sa)001:240: med pa'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'i dbang dam pa
NK028(sa)001:242: gsum pa phrin las kyi dbang la bsam rgyu ni /
NK028(sa)001:243: dbang phyug gi thugs ka nas b+h+rum ljang khu slob bu'i lag pa gnyis su 'phros /
NK028(sa)001:244: dmigs pa gzhung bzhin bsgom la /
NK028(sa)001:246: khyod ni rdo rje las yin gyis //
NK028(sa)001:247: las rnams ma lus khyod kyis byos //
NK028(sa)001:249: khyod kyi dgongs pa byed pa yin //
NK028(sa)001:251: bskur gnas ni lag par rgya gram gtad la /
NK028(sa)001:252: bstim gnas ni lag pa gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa'i bskyod byed kyi thig le la bstim nas /
NK028(sa)001:253: sngon chad phrin las bzhis dbang du 'dul mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:254: da 'dul nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes bar bsgom la /
NK028(sa)001:256: phrin las bzhis dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:257: phrin las rnam pa bzhis srid pa gsum gyi sems
NK028(sa)001:258: can ma lus pa'i don ji ltar 'dul ba bzhin
NK028(sa)001:259: byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:260: bzhi pa 'chad dbang la bsam rgyu ni //
NK028(sa)001:263: gyi bdud rtsi bla med kyis //
NK028(sa)001:264: dad ldan skyes bu ngom pa byos //
NK028(sa)001:265: rab 'bring tha ma'i blo can la //
NK028(sa)001:266: 'thung par gsang bsgrag gzhan du min //
NK028(sa)001:271: phyag shing gsum la 'khor lo gdan du byas la /
NK028(sa)001:273: g.yon du phyag shing gtad la /
NK028(sa)001:274: bstim gnas ni lce la gnas pa smra byed reg shes kyi thig le la bstim zhing /
NK028(sa)001:275: sngon chad sems can gyi shes rgyud la chos kyi
NK028(sa)001:276: 'khor lo bskor mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas
NK028(sa)001:277: / da chos kyi 'khor lo rgyun mi chad par bskor nus pa'i nus /
NK028(sa)001:278: lnga pa rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang ni /
NK028(sa)001:280: phyogs bcu dus bzhi thams cad kyis //
NK028(sa)001:281: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje che //
NK028(sa)001:282: dkyil 'khor kun gyis byed pa po //
NK028(sa)001:283: dkyil 'khor kun gyi sbyin pa spyod //
NK028(sa)001:284: bskur gnas ni lag g.yon du /
NK028(sa)001:285: dbang phyug gi rdo rje dang dril bu snol la gtad de snying khar snol du bcug la /
NK028(sa)001:286: bstim gnas ni yan lag lnga'i reg shes kyi thig le la bstim pas /
NK028(sa)001:287: sngon chad slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhug cing /
NK028(sa)001:288: dbang bskur ba la sogs pa gzhan don bya bar mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:289: da dbang phyug chen por 'gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:290: bdag dang gzhan gyi don phun sum tshogs par spyod
NK028(sa)001:291: cing bsgrub nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par
NK028(sa)001:292: bsgom / bden pa ni rigs kyi bu /
NK028(sa)001:293: 'di rnams la rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:294: slob ma dkyil 'khor du bzhugs cing dbang bskur ba
NK028(sa)001:295: la sogs pa'i las thams cad byed pa'i rdo rje
NK028(sa)001:296: rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang dam pa thob
NK028(sa)001:297: par gyur cig / de dag ni nang nus pa'i dbang gi las kyi rim pa te /
NK028(sa)001:298: nang lus kyi dkyil 'khor du bskur ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:301: bdag don nus phrin las kyi dbang dang 'chad dbang thob bas gzhan don nus /
NK028(sa)001:302: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang thob pas /
NK028(sa)001:303: bdag gzhan thams cad kyi don phun sum tshogs pa nus pa'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:304: nus pa'i dbang zhes tha snyad du bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:305: nang nus pa'i dbang lnga pa rnams la bsdus pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:313: mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi dbang gi sa bcad bzhugs so //
NK028(sa)001:314: 'khor 'das yongs la khyab pa chos kyi sku //
NK028(sa)001:315: thugs rje 'gags pa med pa gzugs kyi sku //
NK028(sa)001:316: bdag gzhan don gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK028(sa)001:317: dpal ldan rdo rje sems la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:318: de la 'dir mdo sgyu sems kyis dbang la klad kyi don dang /
NK028(sa)001:321: dang po klad kyi don la gsum ste //
NK028(sa)001:322: tshig bzhis mtshan bstan pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:326: chos skyong rnams la tshig bcad re res mchod par brjod pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:327: tshigs bcad bzhis 'gag bsdus te bshad pa dam bca' ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:328: gnyis pa gzhung gi don la gsum ste /
NK028(sa)001:329: yid ches zhing khungs btsun par bya ba'i phyir bla ma brgyud pa'i lo rgyus dang /
NK028(sa)001:330: de las byung ba'i gdams ngag dngos dang /
NK028(sa)001:331: rtsis che bas gtad rgya bstan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:333: rgyud ma ha yo ga'i brgyud pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:334: lung a nu yo ga'i brgyud pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:335: man ngag rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i brgyud pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:336: gnyis pa de las byung ba'i gdams pa la gnyis te /
NK028(sa)001:337: smin byed dbang dang grol byed gdams pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:341: dang po sgrub pa la gnyis ste /
NK028(sa)001:342: phun sum tshogs pa drug gis gzhi gzung ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:343: bsnyen sgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang pa dang gnyis so //
NK028(sa)001:351: phun sum tshogs pa dang drug go /
NK028(sa)001:352: gnyis pa bsnyen sgrub la bzhi ste /
NK028(sa)001:357: gnyis pa dbang la gsum ste /
NK028(sa)001:362: sa gzhi spyi mtshan du brtag pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:372: gnas kyi ri brtag pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:373: gnyis pa rang mtshan du brtags pa la gnyis te /
NK028(sa)001:376: gsum pa sa bslang ba la gnyis ste //
NK028(sa)001:377: mngon pa mi la slong ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:378: mi mngon pa mi ma yin la slang ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:379: mi mngon pa la slang ba la gnyis te //
NK028(sa)001:380: bde bar gshegs pa la slang ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:381: sa'i lha mo la slang ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:382: bzhi pa dbang du bya ba phur bu gdab pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:383: lnga pa sbyangs pa la bzhi ste //
NK028(sa)001:384: las dang bya bas sbyong ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:386: sngags dang phyag rgyas sbyang ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:388: ting 'dzin gyis sbyang ba la gnyis te /
NK028(sa)001:391: drug pa byin gyis brlabs pa gar chams so //
NK028(sa)001:392: bdun pa bsrung ba la gsum ste //
NK028(sa)001:393: phyi mtshams dang nang mtshams dang /
NK028(sa)001:396: rgyal chen phyogs skyong gis phyi'i phyi mtshams bcad pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:397: phyi'i nang mtshams dam sri brdung zhing mnan pa bya ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:398: phyi'i gsang mtshams sgo byang gdags pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:399: gnyis pa nang mtshams la gsum ste /
NK028(sa)001:400: nang gi phyi mtshams khro bcu'i phur pa bgegs la gdab pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:401: nang gi nang mtshams mtshon cha 'chol bas mtshon cha'i gur phub pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:402: nang gi gsang mtshams khro bcu'i stang stabs kyis bgegs rigs zil gyis mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:403: gsum pa gsang ba'i mtshams la gsum te /
NK028(sa)001:404: gsang ba'i phyi mtshams bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:405: mi g.yo bas dam sri'i bar chad tshar bcad pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:406: gsang ba'i nang mtshams lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs kyis ye shes su bsgoms pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:408: gsang ba'i dam sri bdud rtsi'i bsang gtor gyis rdul phran bzhin brlag par byed pa'o //

NK028(sa)001:783: nam mkha'i dbyings dang mnyam pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:784: tshul bzhin byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK028(sa)001:785: gzhal yas gsal bar gyur par b+hee //
NK028(sa)001:786: h+aum h+aum b+hi sha badz+ra kro ta dza la ma ta phata ha la ha la h+aum phata //
NK028(sa)001:788: bud+d+ha sh+ri he ru ka bud+d+ha /
NK028(sa)001:789: kro ti shwa ri h+aum phata //
NK028(sa)001:794: a kra ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:796: a kra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:797: ma h+aa mu tra hri sha pra ta pe sh+ra
NK028(sa)001:798: kri ta a nu ta na dz+nya na badz+ra sarba
NK028(sa)001:800: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya ba
NK028(sa)001:801: ga tsit+ta tis badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko
NK028(sa)001:802: ham // de nas byin gyis rlabs so /
NK028(sa)001:803: e ma ho dbu'i yon tan /
NK028(sa)001:805: nyi shu rtsa gcig dbu ni sa rnams lhun gyis grub //
NK028(sa)001:806: sgrib sbyongs ye shes dbu ni khro chen stobs po che //
NK028(sa)001:807: dang po rab du dga' ba'i sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:808: skyon sel ye shes dbu ni khro chen khams gsum rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:809: gnyis pa dri ma med pa'i sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:810: bdud 'joms ye shes dbu ni khro chen bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK028(sa)001:811: gsum pa 'o da 'phros pa'i sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:812: rtog 'joms ye shes dbu ni khro chen 'dod pa'i rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:813: bzhi pa 'od byed pa'i sa mnan pa'o /
NK028(sa)001:814: gzir mnan ye shes dbu ni khro chen rta mchog dpal //
NK028(sa)001:815: lnga pa sbyangs dka' ba'i sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:816: rnam dag ye shes dbu ni khro chen mi g.yo mgon //
NK028(sa)001:817: drug pa mngon du gyur pa'i sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:818: thabs mkhas ye shes dbu ni khro chen gshin rje gshed //
NK028(sa)001:819: bdun pa ring du gyur pa'i sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:820: stobs ldan ye shes dbu ni khro chen dbyug sngon can //
NK028(sa)001:821: brgyad pa mi g.yo ba'i sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:822: mkhyen ldan ye shes dbu ni khro chen rnam par rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:823: dgu pa legs pa'i blo gros sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:824: brjid gnon ye shes dbu ni khro chen h+aum ka ra //
NK028(sa)001:825: bcu pa chos kyi sprin gyi sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:826: mngon shes dbu ni yag sha he ru ka /
NK028(sa)001:827: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:828: kun mkhyen ye shes dbu ni 'gu ya he ru ka /
NK028(sa)001:829: bcu gnyis legs pa'i blo gros sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:830: byams mgon ye shes dbu ni sa nu he ru ka //
NK028(sa)001:831: bcu gsum rdo rje 'chang gi sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:832: rngam brjid ye shes dbu ni rak+sha he ru ka //
NK028(sa)001:833: bcu gcig stug po bkod pa'i sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:834: sprul pa ye shes dbu ni karma he ru ka //
NK028(sa)001:835: bco lnga pad+ma can gyis sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:836: chags med ye shes dbu ni pad+ma he ru ka //
NK028(sa)001:837: bcu drug pa 'khor lo tshogs chen sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:838: yid bzhin dbu ni rat+na he ru ka //
NK028(sa)001:839: bcu bdun de ba ko shi'i sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:840: 'bar 'phro ye shes dbu ni bud+d+ha he ru ka //
NK028(sa)001:841: bco brgyad kun bzang dbye ba med pa'i sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:842: stobs ldan ye shes dbu ni badz+ra he ru ka //
NK028(sa)001:843: bcu dgu rdzogs pa bla ma'i sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:844: khyab brdal dbu ni che mchog nyid kyi dbu //
NK028(sa)001:845: nyi shu srid gsum ngang du rdzogs pa'i sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:846: 'ub chub ye shes dbu ni rta skad nam mkhar 'tsher //
NK028(sa)001:847: rtsa gcig ye shes bla ma'i sa mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:848: g.yas kyi dbu bdun zhal gdangs mche ba gtsigs pas /
NK028(sa)001:849: zhal gyis yon tan 'khor ba'i skye shi rtsad nas gcod par mdzad /
NK028(sa)001:850: g.yon gyis dbu bdun zhal gdangs mche gtsigs pas //
NK028(sa)001:851: 'khor ba'i nyon mongs du kha zad par byed //
NK028(sa)001:853: chos nyid klong du thams cad rngub par mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:854: g.yas kyi spyan bzlog nyi shu rtsa gcig gis //
NK028(sa)001:855: bdud dang bgegs rigs thams cad thal bar rlog /
NK028(sa)001:857: ngan song 'khor ba'i du kha chag mas 'debs //
NK028(sa)001:858: dbus kyi spyan mi 'gyur chos kyi dbyings su ye re gzigs //
NK028(sa)001:859: mche ba dkar po zangs yag gtsigs pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:860: 'khor ba'i chags sdang skye shi rtsad nas gcod //
NK028(sa)001:861: ral ba dmar po gyen du bardzesa pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:862: chos dbyings ye shes mthar thug 'gran zla med //
NK028(sa)001:863: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis phyag rgya'i yon tan phyag mtshan gsal gdab ni mngon sangs rgyas /
NK028(sa)001:864: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi dang po na /
NK028(sa)001:865: kun tu bzang po mnyam pa'i kun tu bzang po yab yum gsal gdab phyag rgya bsnams /
NK028(sa)001:866: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon re mos bsnams pa 'adre'o /
NK028(sa)001:868: rnam par rigs lnga yab yum gsal gdab snang mdzad gser gyi 'khor lo bsnams pa /
NK028(sa)001:869: g.yon gnyis nas sangs rgyas spyan ma gser gyi dril bu /
NK028(sa)001:871: rdo rje sems dpa' rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK028(sa)001:873: rdo rje dbyings phyug ma shel gyi dril bu /
NK028(sa)001:878: ma ma ki ni g.yu'i ril bu /
NK028(sa)001:880: snang ba mtha' yas pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad bsnams pa /
NK028(sa)001:885: don yod grub pa rdo rje rgya gram /
NK028(sa)001:887: dam tshig sgrol ma mthing ga dril bu /
NK028(sa)001:889: sa'i snying po rin chen myu gu sems dpa' sems ma /
NK028(sa)001:891: la se dkar mo me long rgya gram /
NK028(sa)001:893: nam mkha' snying po gcod byed ral gri /
NK028(sa)001:895: ma le sngon mo rin chen phreng ba /
NK028(sa)001:897: spyan ras gzigs dbang pad ma chags med /
NK028(sa)001:899: g+hir ti dmar mo sgra dbyangs pi wang bsnams pa /
NK028(sa)001:901: phyag na rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK028(sa)001:903: nit+ti ljang khu gar gyi cod pan /
NK028(sa)001:905: byams pa me tri klu shing g+hu he bsnams pa /
NK028(sa)001:907: lha mo d+hu pe ma ni spos med /
NK028(sa)001:909: sgrib pa sel ba sbos kyi gleg bam /
NK028(sa)001:911: lha mo pus pe ma ni me tog bsnams pa /
NK028(sa)001:913: kun tu bzang po rin chen snye ma /
NK028(sa)001:915: lha mo a lo ke ni mar me /
NK028(sa)001:916: g.yas pa bcu bzhi 'jam dpal gzhon nu me tog ud pa la /
NK028(sa)001:918: lha mo g+han d+he ma ni dri chab /
NK028(sa)001:920: ya man sgo ba yab yum gsal ta trid thod pa kha gdangs bsnams /
NK028(sa)001:921: g.yon gyi bco lnga na 'gugs byed gdong mo ni lcags kyu bsnams /
NK028(sa)001:923: big nan pradz+nya ta krid rdo rje rtse lnga /
NK028(sa)001:928: pad+ma ta krita thod pa sbrul dkris pa /
NK028(sa)001:930: sdom byed nyi zla ma ni lcags sgrogs /
NK028(sa)001:932: pra dz+ny+aa big nan ta krid rdo rje rgya gram /
NK028(sa)001:933: g.yon pa bco brgyad thal byed dril bu ma //
NK028(sa)001:934: dril bu ma g.yas kyi bcu dgu //
NK028(sa)001:935: lha dbang rgya byin sgra brnyan pi wam /
NK028(sa)001:936: lha min thags bzangs ris ni go cha g.yas kyi nyi shu /
NK028(sa)001:937: sh+aakya thub pa bseg shang par bu /
NK028(sa)001:942: kha 'bar ni rin chen sgrom bu /
NK028(sa)001:943: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi tha ma na //
NK028(sa)001:944: glang po can ni me chu bsil bsod snams //
NK028(sa)001:945: ting 'dzin zhabs brgyad bsgrad bas khro mo'i dbu brgyad bardzisa //
NK028(sa)001:946: zhabs brgyad g.yas kyi dang po bsgrad pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:947: thig le chen po'i ting 'dzin chen po dang //
NK028(sa)001:948: spang bral med par chos kyi dbyings su sbyor /
NK028(sa)001:951: klong du gyur pa'i chos kyi dbyings /
NK028(sa)001:953: g.yas kyi gsum pa rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK028(sa)001:954: skye shi med pa'i chos kyi dbyings /
NK028(sa)001:955: g.yas tha ma thams cad 'byung gnas ting nge 'dzin /
NK028(sa)001:956: zad pa med pa chos kyi dbyings /
NK028(sa)001:957: zhabs brgyad g.yon gyi dang po bsgrad pa yis /
NK028(sa)001:958: chags pa med pa'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK028(sa)001:959: ye nas dag pa'i chos kyi dbyings /
NK028(sa)001:960: g.yon gyi gnyis pa 'da' bar dka' ba'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK028(sa)001:961: mthong ba med pa'i g.yon gyi gsum pa /
NK028(sa)001:962: dmigs su med pa'i ting nge 'dzin chen po dang /
NK028(sa)001:963: rang bzhin med pa'i chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK028(sa)001:964: zhabs brgyad g.yon gyi tha ma bsgrad pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:965: skye shi med pa'i ting 'dzin chen po dang //
NK028(sa)001:966: 'du 'bral med pa'i chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK028(sa)001:967: dbu skra kham nag gyen du 'khyil ba 'di //
NK028(sa)001:968: srid pa gsum las rgyal ba yi brgyan //
NK028(sa)001:969: rta mgo ljang khu rta skad sgrog pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:970: snang srid thams cad dbang du bsdud pa'i rtags //
NK028(sa)001:971: smin mtshams khro gnyer glog ltar 'gyu ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:972: ma rig rmongs pa'i mun pa sel ba'i rtags /
NK028(sa)001:973: tshangs pa'i g.yang gzhi na bza' gsol ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:974: longs spyod rdzogs sku mngon du bstan pa'i rtags //
NK028(sa)001:975: sku mdog mthing nag 'jigs par bstan pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:976: chos kyi sku la 'gyur ba med pa'i rtags //
NK028(sa)001:977: sku smad stag gi sham thabs bsnams pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:978: sprul pa sku yi cir yang ston mdzad rtags /
NK028(sa)001:979: sku stod glang chen ko rlon gsol ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:980: theg pa rim dgu 'gro don mdzad pa'i rtags /
NK028(sa)001:981: zhing chen g.yang gzhi sku la gsol ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:982: thugs rje tshad med bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags /
NK028(sa)001:983: thod pa skam po sku la brgyan pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:984: dus gsum sangs rgyas bsnyen bkur mdzad pa'i rtags /
NK028(sa)001:985: sbrul nag stong gis gdeng gas brgyan pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:986: klu rgyal rigs bzhi dbang du 'dus pa'i rtags /
NK028(sa)001:987: khrag dang zhag gis thig les brgyan pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:988: ma mo mkha' 'gro dbang du 'dus pa'i rtags /
NK028(sa)001:989: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong nas ni /
NK028(sa)001:990: ye shes lnga'i 'od zer 'phro bas brgyan /
NK028(sa)001:991: rdo rje gshog pa nam mkhar gdengs pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:992: stong gsum 'jig rten zil gyis gnon pa'i rtags /
NK028(sa)001:993: 'bar ba chen po'i gar dgus 'gying ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:994: che btsan dpe byad kun la rgyal ba'i rtags /
NK028(sa)001:995: khro rgyal che mchog 'bar ba'i zhabs 'og nas /
NK028(sa)001:996: shin tu rngams pa'i khro mo rnam zhal ma /
NK028(sa)001:997: sku mdog du kha sna tshogs cir yang ston /
NK028(sa)001:998: dbu dgu phyag ni bco brgyad zhabs bzhi bsgrad /
NK028(sa)001:999: rnam thar dbu brgyad gyen du byung ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:1000: gsang ba'i thugs rje thabs dang shes rab ldan /
NK028(sa)001:1001: byang chub sems ni bdud rtsi ga bur dkyil /
NK028(sa)001:1002: 'jam dpal gzhon nu'i bdud rtsi pho brang dkyil /
NK028(sa)001:1003: rta mgrin yab yum bdud rtsi pho brang dkyil /
NK028(sa)001:1004: stong pa bco brgyad phyag gis mya ngan 'das /
NK028(sa)001:1005: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis /
NK028(sa)001:1006: ban+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba rdo rje 'khrug /
NK028(sa)001:1007: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yas kyi dang 'og na /
NK028(sa)001:1008: ke ri ban khro mo brgyad gsal dmar zhing gi dbyug tho 'phyar /
NK028(sa)001:1010: sing ha sing ha brgyad gsal kha ro seng ge'i mgo can /
NK028(sa)001:1012: tsi'u ri ser mo mda' gzhu bsnams pa /
NK028(sa)001:1014: bya kri gnas stag stag gi mgo can /
NK028(sa)001:1016: sbra mo dmar mo chu srin rgyal mtshan 'char /
NK028(sa)001:1018: sri la byi 'dag wa'i mgo can /
NK028(sa)001:1020: se byi za rdo rje rtse dgur phyar /
NK028(sa)001:1022: sho na dgra sta sbyang ku'i mgo can /
NK028(sa)001:1024: puk+ka dmar ser byi rgyu 'dren pa /
NK028(sa)001:1026: kri ta 'grin dmar bya rgod mgo /
NK028(sa)001:1028: karma dung dmar rdo rje dung khrag 'thung /
NK028(sa)001:1030: kang ka kang phrag dur bya'i mgo can /
NK028(sa)001:1032: sme sha 'thing nag byi snying za ba /
NK028(sa)001:1034: kha kha kha ro bya rog mgo can /
NK028(sa)001:1035: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yas kyi tha ma na /
NK028(sa)001:1036: tsan+d+ra ser skya chog lus 'brel ba bsnams pa /
NK028(sa)001:1037: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yon gyi tha ma na /
NK028(sa)001:1038: hu lu lcags kyu 'ug pa'i mgo can bsnams /
NK028(sa)001:1039: ting 'dzin zhabs bzhi bsgrad pas rig bzhi dbu nas rdzis /
NK028(sa)001:1040: zhabs bzhi g.yas kyi dang po bsgrad pa yis /
NK028(sa)001:1041: klong du gyur pa'i gsang ba b+ha ga dang /
NK028(sa)001:1042: bde ba chen po'i byang chub sems su sbyor /
NK028(sa)001:1043: g.yon dang po bsgrad pa yis /
NK028(sa)001:1044: zad stong med pa gsang ba'i b+ha ga yi /
NK028(sa)001:1045: thams cad 'byung ba'i byang chub sems su sbyor /
NK028(sa)001:1046: g.yas kyi tha ma bsgrad pa yis /
NK028(sa)001:1047: 'du 'bral med pa gsang ba'i ba ga dang /
NK028(sa)001:1048: skye shi med pa'i byang chub sems su sbyor /
NK028(sa)001:1049: zhabs bzhi g.yon gyi tha ma bsgrad pa yis /
NK028(sa)001:1050: gdod nas dag pa gsang ba'i ba ga dang /
NK028(sa)001:1051: rdo rje lta bu'i byang chub sems su sbyor /
NK028(sa)001:1052: khro mo rnam zhal 'bar ma'i zhabs 'og nas /
NK028(sa)001:1053: sku gdung 'bar ba'i bud+d+ha he ru ka yab yum bcu la sogs pa dpal chen yab yum bcu /
NK028(sa)001:1054: sngo nag smug nag dmar nag dang /
NK028(sa)001:1055: ljang nag zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bsgrad /
NK028(sa)001:1056: rdo rje 'khor yug dung chos gsang ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:1057: ral gri thong gshol dgra sta sna tshogs bsnams /
NK028(sa)001:1058: sbrul dang thod rlon glang chen ko rlon dang /
NK028(sa)001:1059: zhing chen g.yang gzhi stag gi sham thabs dang /
NK028(sa)001:1060: khrag dang zhags dang rak+ta'i thig les brgyan /
NK028(sa)001:1061: skal pa me ri 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs /
NK028(sa)001:1062: gnas yul khro mo bcu drug brjid pa'i mdangs kyi bzhugs /
NK028(sa)001:1063: phyag rgya khro mo bzhi ni sgo bzhi thub par bzhugs /
NK028(sa)001:1064: dbang phyug chen mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad ni /
NK028(sa)001:1065: rang rang bstan dang lag cha sna tshogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:1066: ci bgyis zhes nas chas de gnas /
NK028(sa)001:1067: de ltar dkyil 'khor gsal bkod pas /
NK028(sa)001:1068: snang srid thams cad 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal /
NK028(sa)001:1069: phyogs bcu rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor rgyas nas /
NK028(sa)001:1070: 'jigs byed chen po'i dkyil 'khor bzhugs so 'tshal /
NK028(sa)001:1071: skad cig gcig la bde gshegs skur ston ma /
NK028(sa)001:1072: byin rlabs mchog dang ldan par mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:1073: phyag rgya bzhis badz+ra a ku sha la sogs pa gsal bstim /
NK028(sa)001:1074: chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang /
NK028(sa)001:1075: sku dang ye shes dkyil 'khor rang snang ba //
NK028(sa)001:1076: snang srid thams cad yab yum sku la sogs /
NK028(sa)001:1077: che mchog yab yum rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:1078: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa'i sku //
NK028(sa)001:1079: khams gsum sems can thams cad 'dren pa'i dpal //
NK028(sa)001:1080: 'gro ba drug po kun gyis sgrib sbyong ba //
NK028(sa)001:1081: bdud rtsi rgyal po khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:1082: dug lnga 'bar ba sku lngar sbyor //
NK028(sa)001:1083: len pa med cing stong ba med //
NK028(sa)001:1084: rigs lnga dpal chen yab yum bcu //
NK028(sa)001:1085: sku gdung 'bar ba khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:1086: chu zla lta bur rtog bral zhing //
NK028(sa)001:1087: thams cad rtog pa'i yongs kyis spangs //
NK028(sa)001:1088: ke'u ri sing ha sgo ma'i tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:1089: bdud rtsi sbyor la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:1090: bdag tu 'dzin med rnam par dag /
NK028(sa)001:1091: bdud dang ngan song gsum las thar //
NK028(sa)001:1092: dbang phyug cha dang ging gi tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:1093: bdud rtsi bdud la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:1097: bde bar gshegs pa dam bca' //
NK028(sa)001:1098: kun bzang kyi pu tsa dbul //
NK028(sa)001:1099: pu tsa lnga lha mo bzhi 'bul dbul //
NK028(sa)001:1101: h+aum rang byung sman mchog che ba'i yon tan gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK028(sa)001:1102: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK028(sa)001:1103: gnyid de bde chen las byung ba //
NK028(sa)001:1104: byang chub sems ni rdo rje ste //
NK028(sa)001:1105: zas mchog tshe yi dri chen po //
NK028(sa)001:1106: sha chen mchod pa rin po che //
NK028(sa)001:1107: pad+ma me tog yang dag ldan //
NK028(sa)001:1108: rdo rje mchu de bdud rtsi mchog /
NK028(sa)001:1109: ga bur shel gyis spos phor dri //
NK028(sa)001:1110: rin chen me tog 'bar ba'i tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:1111: yon tan 'bum phrag yang pa'i bcud //
NK028(sa)001:1112: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK028(sa)001:1113: ye shes lnga rdzogs sgrub pa'i rdzas //
NK028(sa)001:1114: rgyud lnga sems can kun grol ba //
NK028(sa)001:1115: dug lnga sel ba'i thabs mchog ste //
NK028(sa)001:1116: thams cad bdud rtsi rnal 'byor che //
NK028(sa)001:1117: ma lus bsdus pa'i thig le che //
NK028(sa)001:1118: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:1119: gcig tu dpa' bo ro rnams dang //
NK028(sa)001:1120: gnyis su med par mnyam sbyor na //
NK028(sa)001:1121: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK028(sa)001:1122: rgyal ba rgya mtsho thams cad la //
NK028(sa)001:1123: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:1124: thugs rje rtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK028(sa)001:1125: yang sangs rgyas pa'i che mchog he ru ka /
NK028(sa)001:1126: sku dang ye shes dal nyid la rdzogs //
NK028(sa)001:1128: sgyu 'phrul dkyil 'khor ye shes snang ba yis //
NK028(sa)001:1129: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sangs rgyas rang snang ba //
NK028(sa)001:1131: 'jam dpal gzhon nu rta mgrin yab yum dang //
NK028(sa)001:1132: bdud rtsi srid 'dzin mnga' bdag la /
NK028(sa)001:1135: khro mo rnam zhal ke'u seng bcu drug dang //
NK028(sa)001:1136: yum chen mkha' mnyam klong gi dkyil 'khor la //
NK028(sa)001:1138: tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal chen he ru la //
NK028(sa)001:1139: sku gsung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor yab yum la //
NK028(sa)001:1140: sgo ma dbang phyug dam can ging gi tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:1141: dbang chen dkyil 'khor kun 'dus 'khor bcas la //
NK028(sa)001:1143: bsrung dang bskrad dang mtshams kyi las mdzad ma //
NK028(sa)001:1144: rang byung bdud 'dul khro bo bcu rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:1146: rdo rje slob dpon man chad mthun //
NK028(sa)001:1147: thugs kyi sid d+hi sid+hi blangs pa stsol ba 'di //
NK028(sa)001:1148: dngos po med la dngos grub blangs //
NK028(sa)001:1149: byang chub sems kyi sprin chen las //
NK028(sa)001:1150: de ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'grub /
NK028(sa)001:1151: a lan gsum ho pu ka /
NK028(sa)001:1155: bar 'dir dza h+aum bam ho su ra tos bla med bdud rtsi dbul gtor ma dbul //
NK028(sa)001:1156: ye nas gtor ma 'dod yon gyi gtor ma pu tsa rgyu nyid dag pa la //
NK028(sa)001:1157: nga dang bdag tu rtog pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:1158: khams gsum 'khor ba'i rgyu ru gyur //
NK028(sa)001:1159: khams gsum thams cad bsgral ba'i zhing //
NK028(sa)001:1160: a tsa la sa ma ya /
NK028(sa)001:1161: d+harma dar du swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK028(sa)001:1162: lus kun yongs su 'khyud pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:1163: rdo rje pad+ma lhan byas pas //
NK028(sa)001:1164: rang byung rnams kyi bde mchog sems //
NK028(sa)001:1165: phul bas myur du 'grub pa yin //
NK028(sa)001:1167: rgyu drug 'khor ba stong par bsgral slad du //
NK028(sa)001:1168: dus gsum rtsad gcad sha khrag rus pa'i tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:1169: gzung 'dzin rnam rtog kun dang bral ba yis //
NK028(sa)001:1170: mnyam pa chen po'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:1171: ma h+aa ma sa kha hi /
NK028(sa)001:1173: ma h+aa kem ni ri ti dza la kha hi //
NK028(sa)001:1174: lha mo rol mo kungs putsa gro gar glu'i tshig /
NK028(sa)001:1175: mdzes ldan sgyu ma'i gar dang tshangs pa'i dbyangs //
NK028(sa)001:1176: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor rnams la 'bul lags na //
NK028(sa)001:1177: kun tu bzang po'i mchod par bzhes su gsol /
NK028(sa)001:1179: ho spros pa smon lam gdab pa'i don la dgongs su gsol med pa'i dbyings /
NK028(sa)001:1181: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa'i rang byung /
NK028(sa)001:1182: rang snang gi dkyil 'khor chen po /
NK028(sa)001:1183: bcom ldan khro bo thams cad kyi che ba'i mchog /
NK028(sa)001:1184: che mchog he ru ka la /
NK028(sa)001:1185: khro mo rnam zhal ma dang /
NK028(sa)001:1186: sku gdung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor la sogs rnams //
NK028(sa)001:1187: mkhyen pa dang byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:1188: yab yum thabs shes gnyis su med las sprul pa'i sku /
NK028(sa)001:1189: phyag na bzhugs pa sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK028(sa)001:1190: dal gyi lha mo nyi shu dang bcas pa /
NK028(sa)001:1191: ye shes dang las la grub pa'i /
NK028(sa)001:1192: bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnams mkhyen pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:1193: ho rnal 'byor gyi mchod pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i tshul sbyar ba'i /
NK028(sa)001:1194: chos nyid la chos nyid byung stee /
NK028(sa)001:1195: 'phags pa kun tu bzang po'i mchod sprin bsam gyis mi khyab par sprul nas /
NK028(sa)001:1196: bdag nyid chen po 'khor dang bcas pa la /
NK028(sa)001:1197: dbang mi 'tshal ba'i slad du phud dang gtsang mar sbags te /
NK028(sa)001:1198: phul bas ye shes la ye shes rol /
NK028(sa)001:1199: chos nyid la chos nyid rol pa'i tshul gyis bzhes shing longs spyad du gsol lo //
NK028(sa)001:1200: bshags pa bskyed rdzogs dang man chad mthun //
NK028(sa)001:1201: mkhyen pa bskyed rdzogs dang mthun gsol ba 'dzab bsnyen gyi dgongs pa bstan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:1202: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor smad po che //
NK028(sa)001:1203: zla gam dkyil 'khor rin chen dbang //
NK028(sa)001:1204: shar gyis phyogs su kha bltas na //
NK028(sa)001:1206: mchod gang yid bzhin rin po che //
NK028(sa)001:1208: phar 'phros pas ni thugs dam bskul //
NK028(sa)001:1209: slar 'a dus pas ni dngos grub gsol //
NK028(sa)001:1210: 'di yang bsnyen po'i mchog yin ste //
NK028(sa)001:1211: nam yang nyams pa'i dus mtha' med //
NK028(sa)001:1212: dus gsum dbyings su spyor bar mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:1215: pu tsa byin gyis brlabs tshogs kyi byin rlabs pa mthun /
NK028(sa)001:1216: mchod pa dkyil 'khor spyir bstan pa //
NK028(sa)001:1217: spyan 'dren bskyed spyan mig med dam dbang phyug chen pos drangs //
NK028(sa)001:1218: gzugs ni gzugs kyi lha mo chung spyan la thim /
NK028(sa)001:1220: gzugs mdzes spros pas phyogs bcur spros //
NK028(sa)001:1221: shin tu sgegs pas gzi brjid 'bar //
NK028(sa)001:1222: sgra'i lha mo snyan la thim //
NK028(sa)001:1223: dri ni lag gnyis spos chen bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:1224: spos kyi sprin lding bdug pa 'phros /
NK028(sa)001:1225: kun tu tshim byed dri bsung 'bar //
NK028(sa)001:1226: dri'i lha mo shangs la thim /
NK028(sa)001:1227: ro ni lag gnyis rin chen gzhong //
NK028(sa)001:1228: kun tu sbyor bas bde ba ste //
NK028(sa)001:1229: reg bya'i lha mo sku la thim //
NK028(sa)001:1230: de nas tshogs gsum du gcad de /
NK028(sa)001:1231: dang po mchod pa bstod pa 'bul ste /
NK028(sa)001:1232: h+aum rdo rje tshe dang mgo sha'i tshogs la sogs //
NK028(sa)001:1233: smin pa a 'bras rgun 'brum pa na se //
NK028(sa)001:1234: na ri ge sar a ri ka la sogs //
NK028(sa)001:1235: tshe'i tshim byed sna tshogs rnams dang ni //
NK028(sa)001:1236: zla rdzogs la sogs yang dag ldan pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:1237: bdud rtsi'i mchog du sbyar ba yis //
NK028(sa)001:1238: rnam shing rol ste dgyes par dgongs nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:1239: dbang dang si ti bdag la gsal du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:1240: bar pa bshags pa bya ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:1241: h+aum ma rig 'khrul pas snang zhing 'gyod pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:1242: snyom las dbang gis yi dam lha bsangs shing /
NK028(sa)001:1243: bslu byed rkyen gyis slob dpon snying nas smad //
NK028(sa)001:1244: nga rgyal dregs pas mched dang lcam dral dkrugs //
NK028(sa)001:1245: lcam la 'phyar bas gsang tshig gzhan la spel //
NK028(sa)001:1246: ser snas bcings pas mchod pa lo zlar 'gyangs //
NK028(sa)001:1247: khrel mdzem spangs pa chen ba'i sto na smad //
NK028(sa)001:1248: drag shul chung pas log 'dre tshar ma chod //
NK028(sa)001:1249: dpal brtan chung pas phrin las zab mos sngangs //
NK028(sa)001:1250: mtshan ngan dri mas gsang ba'i pu tsa chag /
NK028(sa)001:1251: rngam pas thug thub phud dang lhag ma nyams //
NK028(sa)001:1252: mthong bsen barngana char blang dor gnyis su gyur //
NK028(sa)001:1253: bka' chad rnam grangs gyur pa ci mchis pa //
NK028(sa)001:1254: byang zhing dag par byin gyis brlab du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:1255: bdag cag mchod pa chag dang ma chag ste //
NK028(sa)001:1256: chag par mchis na longs spyod tshogs kyi bskang //
NK028(sa)001:1257: dam tshig nyams dang ma nyams ste //
NK028(sa)001:1259: rtsa ba yan lag 'gal ba 'khrul bar gyur pa ci mchis pa //
NK028(sa)001:1260: thams cad tshogs 'di la rten nas skongs par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:1263: rdo rje dam bcas ma lus dgongs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:1264: rgyal ba zhi khro'i rjes 'brangs mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:1265: mchod sprin bla med nam mkha'i mthas bslubs pa //
NK028(sa)001:1266: phul ba 'di bzhes bdag la skyabs mdzod cig /
NK028(sa)001:1267: dus ngan tha mar skye ba'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK028(sa)001:1268: rang rig mngon shes mthu dang mi ldan pas //
NK028(sa)001:1269: snod dang skal ba mi ldan slob ma btsud //
NK028(sa)001:1270: mi 'tshal ba la dbang bskur gsang ba bshad //
NK028(sa)001:1271: gsang sngags bcos skyin ngan pa'i rgyu bsag pa //
NK028(sa)001:1272: rjes su 'a brang pa khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK028(sa)001:1273: khyed ni rang rig mngon shes mthu dang ldan //
NK028(sa)001:1274: 'gro ba'i skyabs mgon ci phyir bskul ba bzhes //
NK028(sa)001:1275: thugs rje byams mgon ldan pa'igrogasa mdzod cig /
NK028(sa)001:1276: dad pas rang gi 'phags mchod khyed la mos //
NK028(sa)001:1277: rnal 'byor sku gsum ma thob bar du ni //
NK028(sa)001:1278: lus dang grib ma bzhin du 'grogs bya zhing //
NK028(sa)001:1279: rnam lnga mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK028(sa)001:1280: bdag gis bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK028(sa)001:1281: de nas brtan ma bskyang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:1282: bdud rtsi bde ba chen po'i zhal byang rdzogs so /
NK028(sa)001:1284: chos thams cad kyi de bzhin nyid stong pa /
NK028(sa)001:1285: chos nyid de yid kyi shes pas mngon sum du mthong de /
NK028(sa)001:1286: rtogs pa'i don la ma yengs par rtse gcig du
NK028(sa)001:1287: gnas pa de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ni
NK028(sa)001:1288: / shes bya dngos pos bsdus pa'i chos //
NK028(sa)001:1289: thams cad sgyu ma lta bur yid kyi shes pa mngon sum du mthong ste /
NK028(sa)001:1290: rtogs pa'i don la ma yengs par rtse gcig tu gnas pa kun tu snang //
NK028(sa)001:1292: kun rdzob sgyu ma gnyis dbyer med pa'i ngo bo
NK028(sa)001:1293: la sogs mngon gsum du mthong ba'i don la ma
NK028(sa)001:1295: rgyal ba bzhi ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la sogs kyi sku snang zhing stong //
NK028(sa)001:1296: stong zhing gsal ba mngon gsum du mthong ba'i don sgom pa phyag rgya spros byas te //
NK028(sa)001:1297: rim pa ltar rim kyis sgom pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:1298: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga'i dgongs pa yin //
NK028(sa)001:1299: ting nge 'dzin bzhi cig char du sgom pa //
NK028(sa)001:1300: lung a nu yo ga'i dgongs pa yin ste //
NK028(sa)001:1301: bzhi po rim gyi mi bskyed de //
NK028(sa)001:1302: dngas pa'i mtsho la gza' skar bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:1304: sems sgom rnam gsum dus gcig la rdzogs so //
NK028(sa)001:1305: de ni de bzhin nyid kyi ngang //
NK028(sa)001:1306: de ni rgyu'i rim pa ldan //
NK028(sa)001:1308: mdo'i dbang gi skabs 'a dir rim gyis mi bskyed pa cig char du bskyed do //
NK028(sa)001:1309: de yang thog mar gzhal yas khang bskyed pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:1310: e las chos 'byung gru gsum kha dog mthing nag rgya khyon tshad dpag du med pa //
NK028(sa)001:1311: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor sra zhing mkhregs pa kha dog dud kha dbyibs zla gam //
NK028(sa)001:1312: bam las chu'i dkyil 'khor dkar po zlum po //
NK028(sa)001:1313: lam las gser gyi sa gzhi zlum po //
NK028(sa)001:1314: sum las rin po che sna bzhi las grub pa'i ri'i rgyal po ri rab gru bzhi pa //
NK028(sa)001:1319: mtha' lcags ri dang bcas pa //
NK028(sa)001:1320: ram las me'i 'od zer phyed mar spros 'byung pa rnams cha snyoms //
NK028(sa)001:1322: me rlung 'bar ba'i ri rab kyi steng du me'i gur khang zlum po //
NK028(sa)001:1324: rdo rje'i gur khang mthing nag /
NK028(sa)001:1325: 'og rdo rje'i sa gzhi'i steng du //
NK028(sa)001:1326: sna tshogs rdo rje rgya gram //
NK028(sa)001:1333: zur la bang rim bzhi bzhi dang ldan pa //
NK028(sa)001:1335: b+h+rum b+h+yi sha b+h+yi shu d+he //
NK028(sa)001:1337: rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK028(sa)001:1350: ral gri ljang khus brgyan pa rtse gcig phyir ngam pa'i lding du //
NK028(sa)001:1351: rin po che'i pha gu ser po gnyis sna gcig non du yod pa //
NK028(sa)001:1352: pha gu'i nang ngos la 'dod snam dmar po //
NK028(sa)001:1354: rin po che'i ka thung bcu drug dang brag rtse bres pa //
NK028(sa)001:1355: ka thung bcu drug gi phrag du //
NK028(sa)001:1356: mchod pa'i lha mo bcu drug gis mchod rdzas du ma thog pa //
NK028(sa)001:1358: mdzes gdung dmar po gru bzhir phres pa'i phyi ngos la //
NK028(sa)001:1359: shar bu dkar po bsgrigs pa //
NK028(sa)001:1360: lha rnams kyi nang zur phyogs re gnyis gnyis ste brgyad du ka gdan ka gzhu dang bcas pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:1361: rdo rje ka ba brgyad gtsugs pa'i steng du //
NK028(sa)001:1362: rdo rje gdung ma bzhi zur du bres pa //
NK028(sa)001:1363: de'i steng na mdzes gdung gi thog tu bres pa'i
NK028(sa)001:1364: sna tsi pa tra'i kha nas mu tig dkar dmar
NK028(sa)001:1366: dra ba phyed pas brgyan pa /
NK028(sa)001:1367: d+r+wa ba la dril bu dang dril bu chen po'i sgra 'khrol ba //
NK028(sa)001:1368: de la rnga yab dang rnga yab chen po'i bsil yab 'phyo ba //
NK028(sa)001:1369: d+r+wa ba'i nang du nyi ma rangs pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:1370: zla ba phye pa'i dkar khung lding ba //
NK028(sa)001:1371: phyis thud nyer brgyad dang bcas pa'i steng du //
NK028(sa)001:1373: sa tshags nag leb dang bcas pa'i steng du //
NK028(sa)001:1374: rdo rje mthing nag gi mo gyo ring yug du song ba'i rtse mo phyed pa mar 'chang pa //
NK028(sa)001:1375: pho gyo ring yug du song ba'i rtse mo mchod rten yar bsgrigs pa //
NK028(sa)001:1376: mchod rten gyi nang phyogs mtshams brgyad du //
NK028(sa)001:1379: ba dan brgyad re yod pa //
NK028(sa)001:1380: de rnams kyi lha rnams kab pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:1381: de'i steng du phyi ka gdung gi kha la mdzes gdung gru bzhir bres pa //
NK028(sa)001:1382: nang bad khar rtsigs pa gru bzhi steng du //
NK028(sa)001:1384: gdung zlum gyi steng nas mdzes gdung gi thog tu //
NK028(sa)001:1385: phyam nyi shu rtsa bzhi bres pa'i kha la dra ba la sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:1386: rdo rje'i mo gyo sog gi gru chad bzhir kab pa'o /
NK028(sa)001:1387: de'i steng du phyi ka thung gi kha la mdzes gdung gru bzhir bres pa //
NK028(sa)001:1388: nang bad khar rtsigs pa zlum po'i ka thung gru bzhir bres pa //
NK028(sa)001:1389: de'i thog tu phyams nyi shu bres pa'i kha la d+r+wa ba la sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:1390: mo gyo sogs kyis rtsibs mchan bzhi kab pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:1391: de'i steng du phyi ka thung gi kha la /
NK028(sa)001:1392: mdzes gdung gru bzhi bres pa /
NK028(sa)001:1393: nang bad dkar rtsigs pa gru bzhi steng du //
NK028(sa)001:1394: gdung ma zlum por bres pa //
NK028(sa)001:1395: de'i steng phyams bcu drug bres pa'i kha la //
NK028(sa)001:1397: rdo rje mthing nag gi mo gyo la sogs kyis rtsibs bzhi gab pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:1398: de'i steng du bum gdan gru bzhi //
NK028(sa)001:1400: bre dang bre ske gru bzhi //
NK028(sa)001:1404: rdo rje tog dang bcas pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:1406: rin po che zur bzhi la byas pa //
NK028(sa)001:1410: sgo thog du bcu gcig rdo rje'i dra mig /
NK028(sa)001:1411: sgo khang nang gi rgyab dgu dang bcas pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:1412: sgo theb kyi phyi rgyab tu /
NK028(sa)001:1413: lte ba rta bab bang rim bzhi bzhi dang bcas
NK028(sa)001:1414: pa sgo khang gi phyi zur bzhi nas ka ba
NK028(sa)001:1415: ka rgyan / ka gdan ga gzhu thams cad rin po che las byas pa /
NK028(sa)001:1417: glang gur dang bcas pa'i rta babs bang rim bzhi bzhi pad+ma dang bcas pa la /
NK028(sa)001:1419: de'i steng du yu ba chos 'khor bcu gsum dang bcas pa'i gdugs //
NK028(sa)001:1420: rin po che'i tog chos 'khor g.yas g.yon du ri dwags gnyis gnyis dang bcas pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:1421: lte ba'i shing dpag bsam gyi shing la rin po che tshang tshing gis bres pa //
NK028(sa)001:1422: de dag gi bar bar du rin po che'i pha 'ong dang //
NK028(sa)001:1424: gser gyi sa gzhi'i steng du ne'u sing sngon po yi thang //
NK028(sa)001:1425: me tog ldom rdzings dkar po'i tshal dang bcas pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:1426: gzhal yas khang de'i nang gi dbus //
NK028(sa)001:1427: 'khor lo'i lte ba zlum po mthing kha //
NK028(sa)001:1430: de'i phyir rol mu khyud rdo rje'i ra ba //
NK028(sa)001:1433: lha snam sgo dang bcas pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:1434: dbus su rin po che'i khri dang gcig /
NK028(sa)001:1435: de seng ge brgyad kyis stegs pa dang gnyis //
NK028(sa)001:1436: rin po che dra bas khri kheb byas pa dang gsum //
NK028(sa)001:1437: de'i steng du pad+ma dang bzhi //
NK028(sa)001:1442: glang po che la sogs pa'i gdan drug rtsegs //
NK028(sa)001:1444: rta la sogs pa'i gdan drug rtsegs //
NK028(sa)001:1445: nub rtsibs la rma bya la sogs pa'i gdan drug rtsegs //
NK028(sa)001:1446: byang rtsibs la shang shang la sogs pa'i gdan drug rtsegs //
NK028(sa)001:1448: gru chad bzhi dang brgyad la /
NK028(sa)001:1450: pad nyi zla bzhi brtsegs lha rnams la pad zla drug /
NK028(sa)001:1451: sgo bzhi bdud bzhi steng na nyi bzhi'o //
NK028(sa)001:1452: de ni rten gzhal yas khang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:1453: brten pa lha bskyed pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:1454: dbus kyi gdan gyi steng du //
NK028(sa)001:1455: h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra tsit+ta h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:1457: kun tu bzang po mthing kha //
NK028(sa)001:1461: phyag dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu gdengs pa //
NK028(sa)001:1462: gnyis pa gnyis byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya thugs kar 'dzin pa //
NK028(sa)001:1463: tha ma gnyis mnyam bzhag mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:1464: zhabs gnyis rdo rje dkyil mo dkrung gis bzhugs pa //
NK028(sa)001:1466: badz+ra ba tra sa ma ya a //
NK028(sa)001:1467: zhes yum kun tu bzang mo sngon mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis thal mo sbyar ba //
NK028(sa)001:1468: zhabs dkyil dkrung can dar dang rin po che rgyan sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa //
NK028(sa)001:1469: h+aum badz+ra d+h+riga mum d+ha du shwa ri /
NK028(sa)001:1470: kun bzang yab yum gyi mdun du //
NK028(sa)001:1471: mi bskyod pa mthing kha zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK028(sa)001:1474: phyag dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dril du thugs kar bsnol ba //
NK028(sa)001:1475: g.yas 'og ma gnyis 'khor lo rin chen //
NK028(sa)001:1476: g.yon 'og ma gnyis pad+ma dang ral gri //
NK028(sa)001:1479: rnam par snang mdzad yab yum dkar po //
NK028(sa)001:1483: phyag dang po gnyis 'khor lo dang dril bu //
NK028(sa)001:1484: g.yas 'og ma gnyis rdo rje dang rin chen //
NK028(sa)001:1485: g.yon 'og ma gnyis pad dkar dang ral gri /
NK028(sa)001:1489: rin chen 'byung gnas ser po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK028(sa)001:1491: phyag dang po gnyis rin chen dang dril bu //
NK028(sa)001:1492: g.yas 'og ma gnyis rdo rje 'khor lo //
NK028(sa)001:1493: g.yon 'og ma gnyis pad+ma dang ral gri'o //
NK028(sa)001:1496: nub tu snang ba mtha' yas dmar po //
NK028(sa)001:1497: zhal gsum phyag drug zhal g.yas dkar g.yon mthing /
NK028(sa)001:1498: phyag dang po gnyis kyis pad+ma dang dril bu /
NK028(sa)001:1499: g.yas 'og ma gnyis rdo rje dang 'khor lo //
NK028(sa)001:1500: g.yon 'og ma gnyis na ral gri ha pradz+ny+aa d+h+rika /
NK028(sa)001:1502: byang du don yod grub pa ljang gu /
NK028(sa)001:1505: phyag dang po gnyis ral gri dang dril bu //
NK028(sa)001:1506: g.yas 'og ma gnyis rdo rje dang 'khor lo //
NK028(sa)001:1507: g.yon 'og ma gnyis rin po che dang pad+ma //
NK028(sa)001:1508: de ltar lnga po kun zhabs rdo rje dkyil dkrung gis bzhugs pa //
NK028(sa)001:1509: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa //
NK028(sa)001:1510: yum thams cad sku mdog yab dang 'a dra ba //
NK028(sa)001:1513: g.yon pas dril bu yab kyi snyan char 'khrol ba //
NK028(sa)001:1514: zhabs pad+ma'i dkyil dkrung gis bzhugs pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:1516: h+aum la se sa ma ya s+t+wam //
NK028(sa)001:1518: sa snying dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis //
NK028(sa)001:1519: g.yas pa rin po che'i myu gu //
NK028(sa)001:1521: la se dkar mo rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin pa //
NK028(sa)001:1522: tram a dkar pa sa ya /
NK028(sa)001:1523: tram ma le sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK028(sa)001:1524: lho nub tu nam mkha'i snying po ser po g.yas ral gri //
NK028(sa)001:1525: yum phreng ba ma ser mo g.yon dril bu //
NK028(sa)001:1526: hri ha h+aum pad+ma ba ta la //
NK028(sa)001:1528: nub byang du spyan ras gzigs dmar po pad+ma 'dzin pa //
NK028(sa)001:1529: girti dmar mo pi wang can //
NK028(sa)001:1530: dzam ku ru pa na hrih a nir ti ra ga ya mi //
NK028(sa)001:1531: byang shar du phyag na rdo rje ljang khu g.yas rdo rje //
NK028(sa)001:1532: girti ljang khu rdo rje dril bu can //
NK028(sa)001:1533: me da ri ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:1534: dza du pa pra be sha /
NK028(sa)001:1536: byams pa ser po klu shing bum pa //
NK028(sa)001:1537: bdug ma dkar mo spos khang bsnams pa //
NK028(sa)001:1538: thim ha sa ri pa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:1539: h+aum push+pe a be sha ya dza //
NK028(sa)001:1540: lho nub du sgrib sel ser po po ti bsnam pa //
NK028(sa)001:1541: me tog ma ser mo me tog bsnams pa //
NK028(sa)001:1542: h+aum sa ra tsa ya s+w+aa h+aa //
NK028(sa)001:1543: bam ti ba su ki ni /
NK028(sa)001:1544: nub byang gi gru chad la //
NK028(sa)001:1545: kun bzang dmar ljang rin chen snye ma 'dzin pa //
NK028(sa)001:1546: mar me ma ljang khu mar me 'dzin pa //
NK028(sa)001:1547: mum gnyis a ram ba ya s+w+aah+aa //
NK028(sa)001:1549: byang shar gyi gru chad la //
NK028(sa)001:1550: 'jam dpal dkar ljang ut+pala bsnams pa //
NK028(sa)001:1551: dri chab ma dkar ljang dri'i dung chos thogs pa //
NK028(sa)001:1552: sems dpa' yab yum de rnams ni //
NK028(sa)001:1553: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs gyis brgyan pa //
NK028(sa)001:1554: yab rnams ni yum la 'khyud pa //
NK028(sa)001:1555: yum rnams ni yab la 'khyud pa //
NK028(sa)001:1556: yab rnams sems dpa'i dkyil dkrung te zhabs g.yas pa cung zad gdan la 'bab //
NK028(sa)001:1557: yum rnams yab kyi sked la 'khri la ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:1560: lha'i thub pa dkar po pi wam bsnams pa //
NK028(sa)001:1562: lha min thub pa mthing kha ral gri bsnams pa //
NK028(sa)001:1564: mi'i thub pa ser po par sregs bsnams pa //
NK028(sa)001:1566: byol song thub pa ser po pu ti bsnams ba //
NK028(sa)001:1568: yi dwags thub pa ljang khu rin po che'i sgrom bu bsnams pa //
NK028(sa)001:1570: dmyal ba'i thub pa mthing kha me chu bsnams pa //
NK028(sa)001:1571: thub pa de rnams dge slong gi cha byad can bzhengs nas gnas pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:1573: badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:1574: shar sgor khro bo gshin rje gshed po r+n+ri mgo smug nag /
NK028(sa)001:1575: ro langs ma smug nag lcags kyu thogs pa //
NK028(sa)001:1576: pradz+nya ta kri ta h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:1577: rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:1578: lho sgor khro bo gzhan gyis mi thub pa ser po rdo rje bsnams pa /
NK028(sa)001:1579: yum mi pham ma zhags pa bsnams pa //
NK028(sa)001:1580: pad+ma ta kri ta h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:1581: pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:1582: nub sgor rta mgrin dmar por thod sbrul //
NK028(sa)001:1583: yum khro gnyer ma lcags sgrogs //
NK028(sa)001:1584: a big nan takri ta h+aum phata //
NK028(sa)001:1585: kar ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:1586: byang sgor bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang nag rgya gram bsnams pa //
NK028(sa)001:1587: ral gcig ma ljang nag dril bu bsnams pa //
NK028(sa)001:1588: khro bo yab yum de rnams dbu skra dmar ser dpal chas dang dur khrod chas kyis brgyan pa //
NK028(sa)001:1589: me dpung nang na bzhugs pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:1590: de ltar bskyed pa'i lha zhe gnyis po de la //
NK028(sa)001:1591: dbang bskur byin gyis rlabs snyan gsan dbab //
NK028(sa)001:1597: de nas 'dzab 'bul ba la gsum ste /
NK028(sa)001:1599: rtog pa'i gnas gsal gdab cing 'dzab bya ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:1601: dang po lha bskul ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:1602: kun bzang yab yum kyi sngags brjod pas gsal bar byas la //
NK028(sa)001:1603: rang gi snying kha nas 'od zer gtso bo'i thugs khar spros pas //
NK028(sa)001:1604: gtso bo kun bzang yab yum la phog pas //
NK028(sa)001:1605: rgyud mnyes gtso bo'i thugs ka 'od zer 'phros pas rang la phog /
NK028(sa)001:1606: rang gi snod ngan pa'i bag chags dang dri ma kun dag /
NK028(sa)001:1607: dbus kyi kun bzang zhal 'dzum pa dang bcas nas /
NK028(sa)001:1608: bdag la mchog thun mong gi dngos grub ster par bsam la //
NK028(sa)001:1609: h+aum rig pa gsung gi byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:1610: ljags kyi rtse la bkram nas ni //
NK028(sa)001:1611: du ma nyid du so sor go //
NK028(sa)001:1613: seng chen bsnol ba'i khri stengs nas //
NK028(sa)001:1614: rin chen nyi zla pad steng na //
NK028(sa)001:1615: e ma kun bzang rdo rje yid //
NK028(sa)001:1616: rig pa tshul snang sangs rgyas pas //
NK028(sa)001:1617: sangs rgyas thams cad bskyed pa'i yab //
NK028(sa)001:1619: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK028(sa)001:1620: dang po byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK028(sa)001:1621: bar pa rdo rje dril bu 'dzin //
NK028(sa)001:1622: tha ma mnyam bzhag ye shes 'phro //
NK028(sa)001:1623: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK028(sa)001:1624: phyi'i yul la sangs rgyas pa //
NK028(sa)001:1625: snang srid thams cad chos kyi dbyings //
NK028(sa)001:1626: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:1627: bya ba mo dang gnyis su med //
NK028(sa)001:1628: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyis //
NK028(sa)001:1629: yi dam lha la mchod par 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:1630: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK028(sa)001:1631: gnyis pa rtog pa'i gnas gsal gdab cing 'dzab bya ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:1632: h+aum yid chos rang rig ma skyes sam //
NK028(sa)001:1633: kun bzang yab yum rang bzhin ni //
NK028(sa)001:1634: ting 'dzin byed por dbang bskur nas //
NK028(sa)001:1635: ma lus kun gyis byed par shog /
NK028(sa)001:1636: h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra tsit+ta h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:1637: a a a badz+ra b+had tras man ta +aa /
NK028(sa)001:1639: h+aum byang chub sems mchog ye shes rdo rje'i thugs //
NK028(sa)001:1640: srid gsum dbang bsdu thams cad mkhyen pa'i dpal //
NK028(sa)001:1641: bsnyel ba mi mnga' 'gro ba'i skyabs mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:1642: kun bzang rdo rje yid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:1643: h+aum gdod nas ma byung ye shes chos kyi dbyings //
NK028(sa)001:1644: mi skye mi 'gags dngos po 'dzin dang bral //
NK028(sa)001:1645: 'byung byed thams cad skyed pas yum gyis tshul //
NK028(sa)001:1646: bzang mo bya ba mo la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:1647: mi bskyod pa gsum gyi lha bskul ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:1648: dbus kun bzang yab yum gyi mdun du sngags kyi mi bskyod pa yab yum bskyed pa la //
NK028(sa)001:1649: ting nge 'dzin gyi spro bsdu dang //
NK028(sa)001:1650: rig pa gsung gi byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:1651: ljags kyi rtse la bkram nas ni //
NK028(sa)001:1653: seng chen bsnol ba'i khri stengs na //
NK028(sa)001:1654: rin chen nyi zla pad stengs na /
NK028(sa)001:1655: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' gtso //
NK028(sa)001:1657: zhal gsum phyag kyang drug pa ste //
NK028(sa)001:1658: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus 'thing zhal //
NK028(sa)001:1659: g.yas pa gsum na bsnams pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:1660: rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NK028(sa)001:1661: g.yon pa gsum na bsnams pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:1663: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK028(sa)001:1664: kun tu bzang dang gnyis su med //
NK028(sa)001:1665: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyi //
NK028(sa)001:1666: yi dam lha la mchod pa 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:1667: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK028(sa)001:1669: rnam shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK028(sa)001:1670: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes par /
NK028(sa)001:1671: mi bskyod yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK028(sa)001:1672: ting 'dzin thugs su dbang bskur nas //
NK028(sa)001:1673: dngos grub las rnams mngon byed shog /
NK028(sa)001:1677: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK028(sa)001:1678: gzugs sku stong pa nyid kyi tshul 'dzin cing /
NK028(sa)001:1679: yon tan ye shes lnga ldan thugs chud pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:1680: rgyal mchog mi bskyod pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:1681: don dam gnyis med dbyings su gcig pa la //
NK028(sa)001:1682: rdo rje dbyings phyug yum gyis tshul 'dzin cing //
NK028(sa)001:1683: yon tan rnam rtog mi yi cha 'dzin ma //
NK028(sa)001:1684: rgyal yum kun tu bzang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:1685: gsum gyi dang po bskul ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:1686: shar rtsibs la rnam snang yab yum sngags kyis bskyed la spro bsdu dang /
NK028(sa)001:1687: shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK028(sa)001:1688: glang chen bsnol ba'i khri stengs na //
NK028(sa)001:1689: rin chen nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan //
NK028(sa)001:1690: bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad gtso //
NK028(sa)001:1692: zhal gsum phyag kyang drug pa ste //
NK028(sa)001:1693: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus dkar zhal //
NK028(sa)001:1694: g.yas pa gsum na bsnam pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:1695: 'khor lo rdo rje rin po che //
NK028(sa)001:1696: g.yon pa gsum na bsnams pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:1697: dril bu pad+ma rgya gram g.yon //
NK028(sa)001:1698: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK028(sa)001:1699: sangs rgyas spyan dang gnyis su med //
NK028(sa)001:1700: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyi //
NK028(sa)001:1701: yi dam lha la mchod pa 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:1702: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK028(sa)001:1704: gzugs phung pa yi ngo bo nyid //
NK028(sa)001:1705: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa //
NK028(sa)001:1706: snang mdzad yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK028(sa)001:1707: ting 'dzin sku ru bum par gsal //
NK028(sa)001:1708: dngos grub las rnams 'grub byed shog /
NK028(sa)001:1712: h+aum chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK028(sa)001:1713: gzugs sku me long lta bu'i tshul 'dzin cing //
NK028(sa)001:1714: yon tan chos kyi 'khor lo bskor mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:1715: rgyal mchog rnam snang mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:1716: don dam gnyis med dbyings su gcig pa la //
NK028(sa)001:1717: de bzhin dbyings phyug yum mchog tshul 'dzin cing //
NK028(sa)001:1718: yon tan yod med stong pa'i cha 'dzin pa //
NK028(sa)001:1719: rgyal yum sangs rgyas spyan la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:1721: rin 'byung yab yum sngags kyis bskyed la spro bsdu ni /
NK028(sa)001:1723: lho phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK028(sa)001:1724: rta mchog bsnol ba'i khri steng na //
NK028(sa)001:1725: rin chen nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan //
NK028(sa)001:1726: bcom ldan rin chen 'byung ldan gtso //
NK028(sa)001:1728: zhal gsum phyag kyang drug pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:1729: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus ser zhal //
NK028(sa)001:1730: g.yas pa gsum na bsnams pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:1731: rin chen rdo rje 'khor lo g.yas //
NK028(sa)001:1732: g.yon pa gsum na bsnams pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:1733: dril bu pad+ma rgya gram mo //
NK028(sa)001:1734: yum gyis dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK028(sa)001:1735: ma ma ki dang gnyis su med //
NK028(sa)001:1736: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyi //
NK028(sa)001:1737: yi dam lha la mchod par 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:1738: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK028(sa)001:1740: tshor ba chu'i ngo bo nyid //
NK028(sa)001:1741: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa //
NK028(sa)001:1742: 'byung ldan yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK028(sa)001:1743: ting 'dzin yon tan dbang bskur na //
NK028(sa)001:1744: dngos grub las rnams 'grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:1748: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK028(sa)001:1749: gzugs sku mnyam pa nyid kyi tshul 'dzin cing //
NK028(sa)001:1750: yon tan yid bzhin re ba bskong mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:1751: rgyal mchog rin chen 'byung ldan phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:1752: don dam gnyis med dbyings su gcig pa la //
NK028(sa)001:1753: rin chen dbyings phyug yum mchog tshul 'dzin cing //
NK028(sa)001:1754: yon tan nga dang bdag med cha 'dzin ma //
NK028(sa)001:1755: rgyal yum ma ma ki la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:1757: mtha' yas yab yum sngags kyi bskyed la //
NK028(sa)001:1758: ting nge 'dzin dang bcas pas bskul ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:1759: nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs na //
NK028(sa)001:1760: rma bya brgyad kyi khri steng na //
NK028(sa)001:1761: rin chen nyi zla pad+ma'i steng //
NK028(sa)001:1762: bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas ni //
NK028(sa)001:1764: zhal gsum phyag kyang drug pa ste //
NK028(sa)001:1765: g.yas dkar g.yon sngo dbus dmar zhal //
NK028(sa)001:1766: g.yas pa gsum na bsnams pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:1768: g.yon pa gsum na bsnams pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:1769: dril bu rin chen rgya gram g.yon //
NK028(sa)001:1770: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK028(sa)001:1771: na bza' dkar dang gnyis su med //
NK028(sa)001:1772: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyi //
NK028(sa)001:1773: yi dam lha la mchod pa 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:1774: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK028(sa)001:1776: 'du shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK028(sa)001:1777: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes par //
NK028(sa)001:1778: mtha' yas yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK028(sa)001:1779: ting 'dzin gsum du dbang bskur na //
NK028(sa)001:1780: dngos grub las rnams 'grub byed shog /
NK028(sa)001:1784: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK028(sa)001:1785: gzugs skus so sor rtog pa'i tshul 'dzin cing //
NK028(sa)001:1786: yon tan mtha' gnyis skyon gyis ma gos pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:1787: rgyal mchog snang ba mtha' yas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:1788: don dam gnyis med dbyings su gcig pa las //
NK028(sa)001:1789: pad+ma dbyings phyug yum mchog tshul 'dzin cing //
NK028(sa)001:1790: yon tan ci dang rang gi tshul 'dzin ma //
NK028(sa)001:1791: rgyal yum na bza' dkar la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:1793: don grub yab yum sngags kyis bskyed cing //
NK028(sa)001:1794: ting nge 'dzin dang bcas pas bskul ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:1795: h+aum byang phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs na /
NK028(sa)001:1796: shang shang bsnol ba'i khri steng na //
NK028(sa)001:1797: rin chen nyi zla pad+ma'i stengs na //
NK028(sa)001:1798: bcon ldan don yod grub pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:1800: zhal gsum phyag kyang drug pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:1801: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus ljang zhal //
NK028(sa)001:1802: ral gri rdo rje 'khor lo g.yas //
NK028(sa)001:1803: dril bu rin chen pad+ma g.yon //
NK028(sa)001:1804: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK028(sa)001:1805: dam tshig sgrol dang gnyis su med //
NK028(sa)001:1806: bdag gi yi dam lha yin gyi //
NK028(sa)001:1807: yi dam lha la mchod pa 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:1808: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK028(sa)001:1810: 'du byed rlung gi ngo bo nyid //
NK028(sa)001:1811: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa //
NK028(sa)001:1812: don 'grub yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK028(sa)001:1813: ting 'dzin phrin las dbang bskur na //
NK028(sa)001:1814: dngos grub las rnams 'grub byed shog /
NK028(sa)001:1818: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK028(sa)001:1819: gzugs sku bya ba grub pa'i tshul 'dzin cing //
NK028(sa)001:1820: yon tan phrin las sna tshogs ston mdzad pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:1821: rgyal mchog don yod grub la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:1822: don dam gnyis med dbyings su gcig pa la //

NK028(sa)001:2171: thabs kyis 'khor ba'i gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:2172: rdo rje lcags kyu ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:2173: lho sgor stobs po che yab yum sngags kyis bskyed la //
NK028(sa)001:2175: h+aum gzhal yas lho'i sgo khyud la //
NK028(sa)001:2176: nyi zla brag gi khri stengs na //
NK028(sa)001:2177: 'joms pa'i khro rgyal stobs chen dang //
NK028(sa)001:2178: 'ching pa'i lha mo zhags pa ma //
NK028(sa)001:2179: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:2180: lho phyogs gshin rje'i ga don rnams 'dul du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:2182: reg bya chad pa ma skyes pa //
NK028(sa)001:2183: stobs chen yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK028(sa)001:2185: gdul bya ma lus mthar byed shog /
NK028(sa)001:2186: h+aum big nan ta krita h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:2187: rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:2189: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK028(sa)001:2190: gshin rje 'dul phyir khro bo'i skur ston zhing //
NK028(sa)001:2191: thabs kyi 'chi bdag bdud rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:2192: khro rgyal stobs po che la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:2193: gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK028(sa)001:2194: 'gro ba 'dul phyir khro mor skur ston zhing //
NK028(sa)001:2195: thabs kyis bla med gnas su 'dren mdzad cing /
NK028(sa)001:2196: rdo rje zhags pa ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:2197: nub sgor rta mgrin yab yum basngagasa kyis bskyed la /
NK028(sa)001:2200: gzhal yas nub kyi sgo khyud la /
NK028(sa)001:2201: rdo rje brag gi khri stengs na /
NK028(sa)001:2202: nyi ma gsal ba'i gdan stengs na //
NK028(sa)001:2203: 'joms pa'i khro rgyal rta mgrin dang //
NK028(sa)001:2204: sdom byed lha mo lcags sgrogs gnyis //
NK028(sa)001:2205: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK028(sa)001:2206: nub phyogs klu yi gdon rnams 'dul du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:2209: reg byed dag ni ma skyes pa //
NK028(sa)001:2210: rta mgrin yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK028(sa)001:2212: gdul bya ma lus mthar byed shog /
NK028(sa)001:2213: h+aum pad+ma ta kri ta h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:2214: pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:2216: h+aum so sor rtog pa'i ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK028(sa)001:2217: klu chen 'dul phyir khro bo skur ston cing //
NK028(sa)001:2218: thabs kyi phung po'i bdud rnams 'joms mdzad pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:2219: khro rgyal rta mchog dpal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:2220: h+aum gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs las //
NK028(sa)001:2221: 'gro ba 'dul phyir rta mgrin rgyal por sbrul //
NK028(sa)001:2222: thabs kyis nyon mongs gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:2223: nyi zla lcags sgrogs ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:2224: byang gi sgor bdud rtsi 'khyil pa yab yum sngags kyis bskyed la //
NK028(sa)001:2227: h+aum gzhal yas byang gi sgo khyud la //
NK028(sa)001:2228: rdo rje brag gi khri stengs na //
NK028(sa)001:2229: nyi zla gsal ba'i gdan stengs na //
NK028(sa)001:2231: 'bebs pa'i lha mo dril bu la //
NK028(sa)001:2232: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:2233: byang phyogs gnod sbyin gdon tshogs 'dul du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:2235: reg 'dus bdag lta ma skyes pa //
NK028(sa)001:2236: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK028(sa)001:2238: gdul bya ma lus mthar byed shog /
NK028(sa)001:2239: h+aum pra dz+ny+aa ta krita h+aum phata //
NK028(sa)001:2240: kar ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:2243: h+aum bya ba grub pa'i ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK028(sa)001:2244: gnod sbyin 'dul phyir khro bo'i skur ston pa //
NK028(sa)001:2245: thabs kyis nyon mongs bdud rnams 'dul mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:2246: khro rgyal bdud rtsi 'khyil la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:2247: gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK028(sa)001:2248: 'gro ba 'dul phyir myos byed ma ru sprul //
NK028(sa)001:2249: thabs kyis 'gro ba ma lus don mdzad ma //
NK028(sa)001:2250: rdo rje dril bu ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:2252: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su ka dz+ny+aa na d+ha rma d+ha du a //
NK028(sa)001:2253: zhes phyir spros gser gyi sa gzhi brjod nas //
NK028(sa)001:2255: de nas chu bo dus bzhi bstod //
NK028(sa)001:2256: ye nas mnyam nyid kyi bshags ye shes rgyal po'i lnga tshig gis dngos grub bskul la //
NK028(sa)001:2258: tshogs chen 'dus pa zhi ba'i mngon rtogs so ha //
NK028(sa)001:2261: bla ma brgyud pa'i gsol 'debs tshig sdebs ma lags so //
NK028(sa)001:2264: sku lnga'i bdag nyid rgyal ba kun tu bzang //
NK028(sa)001:2265: 'chad pa'i skyes bu rgyal tshab rigs mchog lnga //
NK028(sa)001:2266: khams dang skye mched dag pa rigs gsum mgon //
NK028(sa)001:2267: sku gsum dbyer med gsum la gsol ba 'debs //
NK028(sa)001:2268: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang rnams kyis byin gyis rlobs //
NK028(sa)001:2269: rig 'dzin gtso bo lha dbang brgya byin dang //
NK028(sa)001:2270: dug 'joms bdud rtsir ldan pa'i klu rgyal 'jog /
NK028(sa)001:2271: dgos 'dod re skong gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong //
NK028(sa)001:2272: rgyal ba'i bka' rnams sdud mdzad lang ka'i bdag /
NK028(sa)001:2273: skal bar ldan pa'i dge bsnyen li tsa byi //
NK028(sa)001:2274: rigs can dra ma lnga la gsol ba 'debs //
NK028(sa)001:2275: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang rnams kyi byin gyis rlobs //
NK028(sa)001:2276: rdo rje theg pa 'i bka' babs rgyal po dza //
NK028(sa)001:2277: glegs bam dbang thob in+t+ra bo ti dang //
NK028(sa)001:2278: bde chen rol pa ku ku ra dza'i zhabs //
NK028(sa)001:2280: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang rnams kyi byin gyis rlobs //
NK028(sa)001:2281: 'byung bzhi dbang thob ro langs d+he wa dang //
NK028(sa)001:2282: yi dam lha dang mnyam sbyor pra chen ha //
NK028(sa)001:2283: gang 'dul sprul pa shakya seng ge'i zhabs //
NK028(sa)001:2284: sprul pa'i skye mchog gsum la gsol /
NK028(sa)001:2285: rig 'dzin rtsal rtul zhugs dbang phyug d+ha na rak+shi ta //
NK028(sa)001:2286: rnal 'byor dbang phyug s+thi ra ma ti dang //
NK028(sa)001:2287: grub pa'i dbang phyug ba de ba gsal mdzad zhabs //
NK028(sa)001:2288: rig 'dzin dbang phyug gsum la rig 'dzin rtsal mkhas grub rig 'dzin d+harma bo d+hi dang //
NK028(sa)001:2289: gnas lnga rig pa'i pan chen che btsan skyes //
NK028(sa)001:2290: sa gsum mtshungs med sangs rgyas ye shes zhabs //
NK028(sa)001:2291: lo pan skyes mchog gsum la gsol ba 'debs //
NK028(sa)001:2292: rig 'dzin rtsal mthu stobs mnga' bdag yon tan rgya mtsho dang //
NK028(sa)001:2293: bdud rtsi bcud 'dzin legs pa'i sgron ma bsru //
NK028(sa)001:2294: dngos grub mchog brnyees bsod nams sh+aakya'i zhabs //
NK028(sa)001:2295: gdams pa'i bcud 'dzin gsum la rig 'dzin rtsal he ru ka pa bde gshegs zur po che //
NK028(sa)001:2296: lta sgom rtse mo rgyal ba zur chung pa //
NK028(sa)001:2297: ka bzhi'i mchog gyur glan ston sh+aakya bzang //
NK028(sa)001:2298: bstan pa'i sgron me gsum la rig 'dzin rtsal bstan pa'i gtso bo gsang bdag sgro phug pa //
NK028(sa)001:2299: 'gro ba'i dpal mgon lha rje 'gar ston zung nge dang //
NK028(sa)001:2300: mkhas pa'i gtsug rgyan grogs ston rdo rje rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:2301: gsang sngags sdong po glan ston rdo rje 'od //
NK028(sa)001:2302: ston pa'i zhal rkyen gsum la rig 'dzin rtsal gzhan
NK028(sa)001:2303: gyi mdo dbang brgyud pa nang 'di gsum mi bzhugs
NK028(sa)001:2304: mkhyen brtse'i nus ldan 'gos ston rin po che //
NK028(sa)001:2306: sgrub pa mnga' mnyes sgro ston bsod nams grags //
NK028(sa)001:2307: 'gro ba'i mgon 'gyur gsum la rig 'dzin rtsal gdams pa'i bka' babs glan ston brtson 'grus seng //
NK028(sa)001:2308: byin brlabs rgyud 'dzin glan ston bsod nams rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:2309: blo gros nges ldan glan ston chos seng zhabs //
NK028(sa)001:2310: kun gyi gshin rje gsum la rig 'dzin rtsal 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal sel mdzad lha rje 'bum //
NK028(sa)001:2311: thugs rje'i mnga' bdag glan ston sangs rgyas dpal //
NK028(sa)001:2312: don gnyis mthar phyin glan ston bsod nams mgon //
NK028(sa)001:2313: rgyal ba'i gdung 'dzin gsum la rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang rnams kyi byin gyis rlobs //
NK028(sa)001:2314: rgyal bas lung bstan zur dbang byams pa seng //
NK028(sa)001:2315: mkhas pa'i mchog gyur bsam 'grub rdo rje dang //
NK028(sa)001:2316: mkhyen nyid mngon gyur zur dbang sh+aakya 'byung //
NK028(sa)001:2317: kun mkhyen lung thob gsum la rig 'dzin rtsal 'phags ma'i rnam sprul dpal gyi ye shes dang //
NK028(sa)001:2318: mkha' spyod btsun mo ma cig rin chen zur //
NK028(sa)001:2319: ye shes mkha' 'groo zur mo dge 'dun 'bum //
NK028(sa)001:2320: rgyal ba'i yum gyur gsum la rig rtsal 'gro don lhun grub zur dbang bshes gnyen dang //
NK028(sa)001:2321: mkhas shing grub pa'i bra bo chos 'bum pa //
NK028(sa)001:2322: sku gsum mngon gyur dkon mchog bzang po'i zhabs //
NK028(sa)001:2323: rnying ma'i 'gro mgon gsum la rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang mdo sgyu sems kyi bdag po kahthoga pa //
NK028(sa)001:2324: dgongs don mthar phyin rdo rje rnam par rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:2325: bslab gsum rnam dag dpal 'byor rgyal mtshan zhabs //
NK028(sa)001:2326: kun gyis gtsug rgyan gsum la gsol ba 'debs //
NK028(sa)001:2327: rig 'dzin rtsal rgyal ba'i 'phrin las sna tshogs rang grol dang //
NK028(sa)001:2329: chu bo bzhi rdzogs rtsa ba'i bla ma'i zhabs //
NK028(sa)001:2330: bka' drin mnyam med rnams la rig 'dzin rtsal bde chen dbyings nas sprul pa'i skur bstan nas //
NK028(sa)001:2331: bslab gsum rgyan gyi rab mdzes brjid pa'i sku //
NK028(sa)001:2332: rgyal ba'i 'phrin las 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:2333: sna tshogs rang grol zhabs la gsol rig 'dzin rtsal mdo dbang brgyud pa'i rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang rnams //
NK028(sa)001:2334: bdag la dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:2335: bdag gzhan ma lus smin grol 'god par shog /
NK028(sa)001:2336: bla ma sku khams bzang bar gsol /
NK028(sa)001:2339: bla ma dang 'bral ba med par byin gyis rlobs //
NK028(sa)001:2340: skyabs gnas dkon mchog gsam gyi byin rlabs dang //
NK028(sa)001:2341: dkar phyogs bde ba'i mthu dang nus pa yis /
NK028(sa)001:2342: rgyal ba'i bstan 'dzin sna tshogs rang grol gyi //
NK028(sa)001:2343: sku tshe bstan zhing 'phrin las rgyas gyur cig //
NK028(sa)001:2344: dang po phyi dbang gi chu bo las //
NK028(sa)001:2345: lha mi'i theg pa'i them skas bzhugs so ////
NK028(sa)001:2347: sgyu 'phrul dbang don rin chen skas ka'i gdang //
NK028(sa)001:2348: mdo yi dbang don khang bzang yang thog rgyas //
NK028(sa)001:2349: rdzogs chen dbang don mkha' la nyi 'od gsal //
NK028(sa)001:2350: 'dus pa'i dbang don 'dus pa'i pad tshal rgyas /
NK028(sa)001:2351: zhes bya de ni mtshan don bstan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:2352: brgyud pa'i bla ma byin rlabs ldan pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:2353: rtsa ba'i bla ma bka' drin chen po ste /
NK028(sa)001:2354: skyabs gnas dam pa bla ma dkon mchog la //
NK028(sa)001:2355: rang snang dang bas mi phyed phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:2356: sku lnga lhun grub rgyal ba rgya mtsho dang //
NK028(sa)001:2357: 'dus ma byas shing lhun gyis grub la sogs //
NK028(sa)001:2358: mkhyen dang brtse dang mdzad pa'i 'phrin las te //
NK028(sa)001:2359: skyabs gnas dam pa sangs rgyas dkon mchog la //
NK028(sa)001:2360: lus ngag yid gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:2361: gsung lnga lhun grub dam chos rgya mtsho dang //
NK028(sa)001:2362: bsam med gnyis med rtog med 'gog pa'i bden //
NK028(sa)001:2363: dag dang gsal dang gnyen po lam gyi bden //
NK028(sa)001:2364: bka' dang bstan bcos lung ste dam chos la //
NK028(sa)001:2365: tshig don thugs chud ngang nas bsgrub phyag 'tshal //
NK028(sa)001:2366: thugs lnga lhun grub rgyal sras rig 'dzin dang //
NK028(sa)001:2367: ji bzhin ji snyed nang gi rig pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:2368: ye shes gzigs pa dag pa grol ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:2369: 'phags tshogs dge 'dun dkon mchog thams cad la //
NK028(sa)001:2370: dag snang mos gus ngang nas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:2371: shugs byung lha mi nyan rang byang chub sems //
NK028(sa)001:2372: dngos bstan bya spyod rnal 'byor yo ga'i lha //
NK028(sa)001:2373: nang pa bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga dang //
NK028(sa)001:2374: a nu yo ga a ti yo ga yi //
