NK028(sa)001:2375: yi dam rgyud sde drug la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:2376: rdo rje mkha' 'gro la sogs rigs lnga'i yum //
NK028(sa)001:2377: ma ltar byams shing bsring ltar brtse ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:2378: gzungs ltar gdung zhing bran ltar myur ba yi //
NK028(sa)001:2379: ma rgyud mkha' 'gro rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:2380: dpal ldan lha mo legs ldan rgyud mgon dang //
NK028(sa)001:2381: rgyal chen rnam sras dam can mgar ba sogs //
NK028(sa)001:2382: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan phrin las kyi //
NK028(sa)001:2383: chos skyong rgya mtsho'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:2384: de ni mchod par brjod pa'i rim pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:2385: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po nas //
NK028(sa)001:2386: drin can rtsa ba'i bla ma yan chad du //
NK028(sa)001:2387: bum pa gcig nas ga cig byo lta bu ste //
NK028(sa)001:2388: bla ma rim pa'i gsung bzhin brtsam par bya //
NK028(sa)001:2389: lha mi la sogs theg pa drug po dang //
NK028(sa)001:2390: ma h+aa yo ga nang dbang chu bo dang //
NK028(sa)001:2391: a nu yo ga bsgrubs dbang chu bo dang //
NK028(sa)001:2392: rdzogs pa a ti gsang dbang man ngag rnams //
NK028(sa)001:2393: gsal la ma 'dres yongs rdzogs bri bar bya //
NK028(sa)001:2394: phun sum tshogs pa lnga yi gzhi gzung la //
NK028(sa)001:2395: sa chog nas gzung dkyil 'khor las rim bsnyen //
NK028(sa)001:2396: bsgrub tshad zhag grangs phyed ni nye bsnyen no /
NK028(sa)001:2397: phyed ni bsgrubs pa tha ma dngos grub len //
NK028(sa)001:2398: bsgrub pa chen po'i dgos don dam pa ste //
NK028(sa)001:2399: bsnyen bsgrub tshul bzhin legs par bshad par bya //
NK028(sa)001:2400: de ni bshad par dam bca' ba'i rim pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:2401: snyan ngags sdebs sbyor rim pa 'dir ma smos //
NK028(sa)001:2402: des klad kyi don de song nas gzhung gi don //
NK028(sa)001:2403: mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi dbang don sbrang rtsi'i chu
NK028(sa)001:2404: rgyun zhes bya ba nyams su len pa la spyi
NK028(sa)001:2405: don gsum ste / yid ches shing khungs btsun par
NK028(sa)001:2406: bya ba'i phyir bla ma brgyud pa'i lo rgyus bstan
NK028(sa)001:2407: don gsum ste / pa dang / de las byung ba'i gdams ngag dngos dang /
NK028(sa)001:2408: rtsis che bas gtad rgya bstan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:2409: dang po la gsum ste rgyud ma h+aa yo ga'i brgyud pa'i rim pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:2410: lung a nu yo ga'i brgyud pa'i rim pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2411: man ngag rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i brgyud pa'i rim pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:2419: tshom bu lnga pa ste drug /
NK028(sa)001:2420: khro bo la'ang de bzhin du drug ste bcu gnyis kyi dbang thob pa'i brgyud pa la //
NK028(sa)001:2421: dang po rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:2422: rgyal ba kun tu bzang pos /
NK028(sa)001:2425: 'joms byed khro bo'i 'khor dang bcas pa la dgongs te brgyud /
NK028(sa)001:2426: gnyis pa rig 'dzin rig pa'i brgyud pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:2427: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rjes /
NK028(sa)001:2428: dam pa'i rigs can dra ma lnga la rig pa nas rig par brgyud /
NK028(sa)001:2429: gsum pa gang zag snyan brgyud ni /
NK028(sa)001:2430: gsang bdag ku ku r+aa dz+aa /
NK028(sa)001:2434: khyi'i rgyal po ku ku r+aa dz+aa /
NK028(sa)001:2435: ro langs bde pa'i dngos grub /
NK028(sa)001:2437: za hor gyi rgyal po pra ha sti /
NK028(sa)001:2438: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba /
NK028(sa)001:2441: mkhas pa gtsug gye rnam gnyis /
NK028(sa)001:2444: khu lung yon tan rgya mtsho yab sras /
NK028(sa)001:2450: gsang bdag lha rje sgro phug pa'ang zer sh+aakya seng ge /
NK028(sa)001:2455: dpal ldan chos kyi seng ge /
NK028(sa)001:2463: des rtsa ba'i bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen chen po dkon mchog bzang po la gnang /
NK028(sa)001:2464: des dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa sbra rmog ston rdo rje rin chen dpal bzang po la gnang /
NK028(sa)001:2467: des bdag sna tshogs rang grol la dgyes bzhin gnang sbyin bzang po dang bcas nas dbang bka' /
NK028(sa)001:2471: rgyud kyi bka' dang bcas pa rnams legs par gnang //
NK028(sa)001:2472: gnyis pa lung a nu yo ga'i brgyud pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:2473: sku lnga'i bdag nyid kun tu bzang po //
NK028(sa)001:2474: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje /
NK028(sa)001:2477: khyi'i rgyal po ku ku ra dz+aa /
NK028(sa)001:2485: lo tsa ba che btsan skyes kyis /
NK028(sa)001:2486: snubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che /
NK028(sa)001:2493: yang khyeng bla ma sgro phug pa /
NK028(sa)001:2495: zung chung bas glan sh+aakya bzang po la /
NK028(sa)001:2497: srog ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan /
NK028(sa)001:2502: glan ston chos kyi seng ge //
NK028(sa)001:2510: des rtsa ba'i bla ma dkon mchog bzang po la /
NK028(sa)001:2511: rdo rje rin chen dpal bzang po la /
NK028(sa)001:2516: rgyud kyi bka' dang bcas pa rnams dgyes bzhin du gnang /
NK028(sa)001:2517: des grwa dar lung du bzhugs pa chos rje rdo rje rnam rgyal ba la gnang /
NK028(sa)001:2518: de nyid kyis grwa byams sdings pa chos rje dpal 'byor rgyal mtshan pa la gnang /
NK028(sa)001:2519: des bdag don grub legs pa dpal 'bar mched lcam
NK028(sa)001:2520: dang bcas pa la dgyes pa chen po dang bcas
NK028(sa)001:2522: gsum pa man ngag rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i brgyud pa'i rim pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:2526: mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa cig /
NK028(sa)001:2528: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po /
NK028(sa)001:2529: mkhas pa ye shes gzhon nu //
NK028(sa)001:2530: sog po dpal gyi ye shes /
NK028(sa)001:2531: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes /
NK028(sa)001:2532: gnubs chung yon tan yab sras /
NK028(sa)001:2533: mkhas pa myang chen sher mchog /
NK028(sa)001:2536: zur chung shes rab grag pa /
NK028(sa)001:2538: gsang bdag mda' tsha hor po /
NK028(sa)001:2540: mkhas pa lce ston yab sras /
NK028(sa)001:2542: chos rje bla skyabs rdo rje //
NK028(sa)001:2543: drin chen mkhas grub chen po mkha' 'gro dpal gyi ye shes /
NK028(sa)001:2544: ma cig drin chen zur mo /
NK028(sa)001:2548: bshes gnyen dkon mchog bzang po /
NK028(sa)001:2549: des rdo rje bzang po la dbang bka' /
NK028(sa)001:2553: rgyud kyi bka' dang bcas pa rnams dgyes bzhin du gnang /
NK028(sa)001:2554: des dge slong rdo rje rnam rgyal ba la gnang /
NK028(sa)001:2555: des byams sdings pa dpal 'byor rgyal mtshan pa la gnang /
NK028(sa)001:2556: des bdag don grub legs pa dpal 'bar la'o //
NK028(sa)001:2557: de ni mdor bsdus pa'i brgyud rim yin //
NK028(sa)001:2559: mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi lo rgyus chen mo rnams su shes par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:2560: gnyis pa de las byung ba'i gdams ngag la gnyis te /
NK028(sa)001:2561: smin byed kyi dbang bskur ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:2566: phun sum tshogs pa drug gis bsgrub pa'i gzhi gzung
NK028(sa)001:2567: ba dang bsnyen bsgrub gzhi bsgrub pa'i gzhung bsrang ba'o
NK028(sa)001:2569: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2574: sgrub pa po phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:2576: ston pa rdo rje rgyal po ste /
NK028(sa)001:2579: slob dpon mtshan nyid brtags pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:2580: ye shes snying po khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:2581: ces pa la sogs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2582: yang rnam par snang mdzad thig le dbang gi tan+t+ra las /
NK028(sa)001:2583: de dang mtshungs pa ldan pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2584: brtan zhing dul la blo gros ldan /
NK028(sa)001:2585: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2587: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs /
NK028(sa)001:2588: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK028(sa)001:2589: man ngag drod tshad brgyad 'chang ba /
NK028(sa)001:2590: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK028(sa)001:2592: slob dpon nyid dang dgongs pa khyad par med pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:2595: gzhung kun nas bshad pa'i las bzhi po gang du dgos pa'i skabs kyi mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:2596: gnyis pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:2599: sde dpung chen pos mi tshugs shing /
NK028(sa)001:2600: sa dang bar snang shis pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2601: lo rgyus rnam gnyis ldan pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2602: yid 'ong sa rtsal rgyas par bya /
NK028(sa)001:2605: zur brgyad la sogs rtse mngas dang /
NK028(sa)001:2606: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pas /
NK028(sa)001:2608: gnas kyi gzhi brtags pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2609: mtshams kyi dgra brtags pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2610: gnas kyi ri'am phyogs brtags pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:2611: de yang gtsug lag gi lha gzhi yod cing /
NK028(sa)001:2612: lha chos mi chos kyi bkra shis pa'i gnas btsal /
NK028(sa)001:2615: de yang khyad par du zhabs kyis bcag pas byin che ba'i gnas dang /
NK028(sa)001:2616: grub pa thob pa bkra shis pa'i gnas dang /
NK028(sa)001:2618: yid du 'thad cing rnal 'byor pa gtso 'khor dang
NK028(sa)001:2619: bcas pa nyams dga' ba'i gnas su sgrub pa po
NK028(sa)001:2620: rnams 'dus la / der khang pa gsum rim du byas te /
NK028(sa)001:2621: de nyid du steng brgyan dang //
NK028(sa)001:2623: gzhan yang mchod pa'i sprin sna tshogs kyis gtibs par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:2625: 'khor khang phyi nang bar ldan pa //
NK028(sa)001:2626: rin chen byug pas bsrungs ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:2627: rin chen spras pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK028(sa)001:2629: gsum pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:2631: ston pa mchod brtson rtogs pa gsal /
NK028(sa)001:2632: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pas skyon drug spangs
NK028(sa)001:2633: shing yon tan drug dang ldan pa'i 'khor kar+m+aa las
NK028(sa)001:2634: mkhan skad kyi gdangs che zhing /
NK028(sa)001:2635: las kyi 'khrigs la mkhas pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2640: rdul phyag skyes bu la sogs pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:2642: bsgrub dang bsgom la dga' ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:2644: bzhi pa yo byad phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:2645: yo byad dka' ba kun bsdus nas /
NK028(sa)001:2647: bkod pa sku'i rten tsak+ka li phyi nang gi dang /
NK028(sa)001:2648: lugs sku dang thod pa la sogs pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:2649: bris pa gsung gi rten yi ge dang /
NK028(sa)001:2650: thugs kyi rten phyag mtshan rdo rje 'khor lo la sogs pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:2656: de dag ni sgrub pa rdzas kyi yo byad do //
NK028(sa)001:2657: 'tsho ba zas kyi yo byad sha mar la sogs kun /
NK028(sa)001:2658: zhag grangs kyi lhag thang du bshams pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2659: mnyes pa'i lha'i yo byad ni /
NK028(sa)001:2661: thun mong gi lnga la sogs pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:2662: rkyen bzlog dgos pa'i yo byad ni /
NK028(sa)001:2663: dgra'i rkyen bzlog pa'i go mtshon dang /
NK028(sa)001:2664: bgegs bzlog pa'i phur bu dang /
NK028(sa)001:2666: gu gul la sogs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2667: nad bzlog pa'i sman pa sman dang bcas pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:2668: de rnams la'ang tha mal gyi rdzas kyi rnam par
NK028(sa)001:2669: skad cig kyang mi lta bar dngos grub chen po'i
NK028(sa)001:2672: gos rgyan bza' btung gsang ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:2673: sgrub pa'i yo byad lnga rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:2674: dal dung yo byad mchod pa'i rdzas /
NK028(sa)001:2675: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK028(sa)001:2676: lnga pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:2677: bsgrub pa zug pa'i dus dang /
NK028(sa)001:2679: smin par thob pa dbang du bsgrub pa'i dus so //
NK028(sa)001:2680: de dag kyang gong ma rnams 'dzom pa'i dus ste /
NK028(sa)001:2682: tshes grangs yar gyi brgyad la brtsam /
NK028(sa)001:2685: bsnyen pa rdzogs nas lhag pa'i sems skyes pa'i dus su dbang bskur ba yin ste /
NK028(sa)001:2687: dang po sems bskyed 'jug dus su //
NK028(sa)001:2688: rdzas kyi dbang bcu rdzogs par sbyin /
NK028(sa)001:2691: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK028(sa)001:2693: drug pa sgrub pa po phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:2694: ston pa dang 'khor gnyis la ngos gzung ngo /
NK028(sa)001:2697: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen po /
NK028(sa)001:2698: sgrub pa dang ni sgrub chen po /
NK028(sa)001:2701: bsnyen pa dang nye bsnyen dang /
NK028(sa)001:2705: smin pa'i dbang du nang rgyud lung man ngag gi lta ba rtogs /
NK028(sa)001:2711: de nas bsgrub pa'i zhag grangs kyi phyed tshun chad nye bsnyen /
NK028(sa)001:2713: nub tha ma dngos grub len pa bsgrub pa chen po ste zag med kyi rig 'dzin thob pa'o /
NK028(sa)001:2716: nub gnyis pa sta gon legs par tshar nas dkyil 'khor bri /
NK028(sa)001:2724: sgrub pa ji tsam byed kyi phyed tshun chad do //
NK028(sa)001:2726: bsgrub pa ji tsam byed kyi zhag grangs phyed phan chad do //
NK028(sa)001:2727: bzhi pa bsgrub pa chen po ni /
NK028(sa)001:2728: nub tha ma dngos grub len pa'i cho ga'o //
NK028(sa)001:2729: 'di dag gi chog 'grig ni bsgrub gzhung du shes par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:2732: sa gzhi mnyam dang tshad thig dang /
NK028(sa)001:2733: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2734: rab gnas sbyin bsreg 'jug pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2735: yon tan rnam bcu rgyas zhes bya /
NK028(sa)001:2738: dang po sa gzhi yongs su gzung /
NK028(sa)001:2739: gnyis pa sta gon la gnas te /
NK028(sa)001:2740: nub gsum pa la 'jug par bya /
NK028(sa)001:2742: sgyu dra ba'i le'u gnyis pa las /
NK028(sa)001:2743: dang po sa gzhi yongs su gzung /
NK028(sa)001:2744: gnyis pa sta gon gnas pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:2745: nub gsum pa ni 'jug pa yin /
NK028(sa)001:2747: gsum ste nub dang po sa chog dang /
NK028(sa)001:2748: nub gnyis pa sta gon dang /
NK028(sa)001:2752: gzhi dang rang mtshan blang dbang dang /
NK028(sa)001:2753: sbyang byin bsrungs dang bzung ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:2754: dang po nying lag nyid du bshad /
NK028(sa)001:2756: sa gzhi spyi mtshan du brtag pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2757: sa gzhi rang mtshan du brtags pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2759: sa dbang du bya ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:2761: sa byin gyis rlabs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2769: zur brgyad la sogs rtse mang dang /
NK028(sa)001:2770: chu bo bzhin du ma bo zhing /
NK028(sa)001:2771: mnyam zhing 'o kha'i chu ltar dngas /
NK028(sa)001:2772: nyi ma shin tu gnas pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:2773: nam mkha'i mtshan nyid shes par bya //
NK028(sa)001:2775: gnyis pa gnas kyi ri brtag pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:2777: mtho dang 'dud pa nub byang yin /
NK028(sa)001:2778: shar lho gzhol zhing 'jam pa la //
NK028(sa)001:2779: mtho sgros grogs 'od chu sna tshogs /
NK028(sa)001:2780: dkyil 'khor dbang drag mtshams brtags bya //
NK028(sa)001:2781: lhun sdug ri bo nag tshal ldan //
NK028(sa)001:2782: rab tu mnyam zhing snum gnag can //
NK028(sa)001:2783: chu bo dbang gi phyogs yin te //
NK028(sa)001:2784: cung zad kyis ni rlung nyung zhing //
NK028(sa)001:2785: me tog shing tshal bya skad brtag /
NK028(sa)001:2786: lo rgyus shis pa'ang mchog tu gsungs //
NK028(sa)001:2787: bdag nyid brtags shing nyams dga' dang //
NK028(sa)001:2788: bsam gtan dgra las ring gyur pa //
NK028(sa)001:2789: rang khyim la sogs de bzhin te //
NK028(sa)001:2790: nan tan nus mthu ldan phyiir yin //
NK028(sa)001:2791: mtshan nyid sbyong ba phyogs gsum ste //
NK028(sa)001:2793: gnyis pa rang mtshan du brtag pa la gnyis te /
NK028(sa)001:2797: thang ga sog le lta bu dang /
NK028(sa)001:2798: rma dang bo ba'i mtshan nyid dang //
NK028(sa)001:2799: tsha rgod zug rdo rus sbal dang //
NK028(sa)001:2800: gram pa thal ba shing sol dang //
NK028(sa)001:2801: gyo mo rus pa gseg la sogs //
NK028(sa)001:2802: nya gro d+ha dang p+aa la sha //
NK028(sa)001:2803: u dum wa ra a shwa r+tha //
NK028(sa)001:2804: a dzu na la sogs pa'i tshul //
NK028(sa)001:2805: 'dod pa ma yin sbyong spo bya //
NK028(sa)001:2808: bkra shis rtsa dang me tog shing //
NK028(sa)001:2809: snag dang kha dog ldan pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:2810: rtsigs ma rgyus par rab nyung zhing //
NK028(sa)001:2811: lhag par bsgyur ba mchog tu gsungs //
NK028(sa)001:2813: gsum pa sa slang ba la gnyis te /
NK028(sa)001:2814: mngon pa mi la slang ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:2815: mi mngon pa mi ma yin la slang ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:2818: blon po la sogs pa sa de'i bdag po la rin nam /
NK028(sa)001:2819: zhu ba phul la slangs shing /
NK028(sa)001:2821: gnyis pa mi mngon pa la slang ba la gnyis te //
NK028(sa)001:2822: bde bar gshegs pa la blang ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:2823: sa'i lha mo la slang ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:2826: ga bur dang tsan dan gyi chus chag chag btab ste /
NK028(sa)001:2827: de'i steng du zhi ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi tshom bu'am //
NK028(sa)001:2828: khro bo lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kyi tshom bu'am //
NK028(sa)001:2829: de gnyis sgrags pa'i nas tshoms sam //
NK028(sa)001:2830: man+dala la tshom bu nyer gcig pa gang rung bkod //
NK028(sa)001:2831: de'i phyi rol byang shar gyi mtshams su mtshams 'dzin gyi me tog shar du mchod yon /
NK028(sa)001:2837: byang du zhal zas rnams bsham mo //
NK028(sa)001:2838: de'i phyi rol shar lho mtshams su bla ma'i gtor ma /
NK028(sa)001:2839: byang shar du yi dam kyi gtor ma /
NK028(sa)001:2840: nub byang du mkha' 'gro'i gtor ma /
NK028(sa)001:2841: lho nub tu chos skyong gi gtor ma rnams bsham mo //
NK028(sa)001:2845: rak+ta rnams gzhan yang brten cha dang /
NK028(sa)001:2846: mchod pa ci 'byor ba rnams bshams la /
NK028(sa)001:2847: gtor ma chu dang chang gis bran no //
NK028(sa)001:2848: de nas dpon slob rnams chas gos dkar po dang ldan pas stan bde ba la 'dug la /
NK028(sa)001:2849: zhi ba'i las byang bsnyen pa tshogs mchod yan chad dam /
NK028(sa)001:2851: yang na rnal 'byor mchod lugs gzhung bsrang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:2853: +amo su war+na b+hu ma man+da la h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:2854: zhes brjod pas sa gzhi nyid gser gyi sa gzhir bsam mo //
NK028(sa)001:2855: gnyis pa sa'i lha mo la blang ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:2857: sa'i lha mo'i me tog gi tshom bu gcig bkod /
NK028(sa)001:2858: de'i mthar mchod pa sna lnga la sogs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:2860: gser skyems la sogs bsham pa la /
NK028(sa)001:2861: slob dpon chas su zhugs te /
NK028(sa)001:2862: rnam par mi rtog pa'i khyad par las /
NK028(sa)001:2863: big nan ta grid a mri ta kun+da li ha na ha na h+aum phatah ces brjod cing /
NK028(sa)001:2864: skad cig dran rdzogs su bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang
NK028(sa)001:2865: khu g.yas sna tshogs rdo rje rtse lnga pa 'phyar
NK028(sa)001:2866: ba / g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK028(sa)001:2867: khro bo'i brgyan dang ldan zhing /
NK028(sa)001:2868: yum g.yas pa yab la 'khyud pa /
NK028(sa)001:2869: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa bskyed do //
NK028(sa)001:2873: gser skyems sngags drug phyag rgya drug gis byin gyis brlab cing /
NK028(sa)001:2874: bdag bdud rtsi 'khyil par gsal ba'i thugs ka nas /
NK028(sa)001:2875: lam ser po lag pa'i steng du 'phros pas /
NK028(sa)001:2876: lam las skyes pa'i sa'i lha mo sangs rgyas spyan ma gser gtso ma lta bu /
NK028(sa)001:2878: phag gi khri la bzhugs pa /
NK028(sa)001:2879: phyag g.yas pa gser gyi bum pa rin po ches gang ba bsnams pa /
NK028(sa)001:2880: g.yon mchog sbyin gyi phyag rgya mdzad pa /
NK028(sa)001:2881: 'ja' tshon sna lnga'i 'od dang ldan par bsgoom //
NK028(sa)001:2882: de la tram tram tram tram tram ye shes lnga yis dbang bskur /
NK028(sa)001:2883: rnam snang gis gtso byas pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa lngas dbu brgyan /
NK028(sa)001:2884: +aahh+aum zhes sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab bo //
NK028(sa)001:2885: de nas se gol gdab cing /
NK028(sa)001:2886: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:2887: sa'i lha mo ye shes pa snyan gsan phab nas /
NK028(sa)001:2888: rdo rje gsor zhing dril bu dkrol la /
NK028(sa)001:2889: don dam gser gyi sa la mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:2890: rin chen mdzes pa'i pho brang yid 'ong gdal /
NK028(sa)001:2891: nyi zla skar ma dag gis rab brgyan te //
NK028(sa)001:2892: yid du 'ong ba'i pho brang dbus na bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:2893: mi rtog dbus kyi sa la mnga' mdzad de //
NK028(sa)001:2894: dbus kyi sa bdag lha mo sangs rgyas spyan //
NK028(sa)001:2895: sku mdog gatsa ma rin chen gser gyi mdog /
NK028(sa)001:2896: phyag g.yas rin chen gser gyi bum pa bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:2897: phyag g.yon mchog sbyin phyag rgya ston mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:2898: 'gro ba kun gyi mgon dang skyabs mdzad pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:2899: dbus kyi lha mo 'khor dang bcas pa rnams /
NK028(sa)001:2900: bdud rtsi mchod sbyin 'gron du spyan 'dren na //
NK028(sa)001:2901: byams dang brtse phyir gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:2902: e h+ya hi ba su d+ha ri ma h+aa ka ru ni ka tri sha ho //
NK028(sa)001:2905: zhes brjod cing lag pa gnyis mathe'u chung sbrel ba'i phyag rgyas /
NK028(sa)001:2906: sa'i lha mo ye shes pa rang bzhin gyi gnas nas byon par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:2907: dza h+aum bam hoh zhes pa'i sngags brjod cing /
NK028(sa)001:2908: dgugs gzhug cing bstims pa'i phyag rgyas sa'i lha mo dam tshig pa dang gcig tu gyur nas //
NK028(sa)001:2909: kun bzang ni bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK028(sa)001:2910: rgyal ba rgya mtsho ye shes kyis //
NK028(sa)001:2911: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas kyi //
NK028(sa)001:2912: spyod pa rgya mtsho rmad byung kun //
NK028(sa)001:2913: kun bzang mchod sbrin mchog tu rol //
NK028(sa)001:2914: sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo bi shwa mu khe b+h+ya /
NK028(sa)001:2915: sarba th+aa kham ut+ga te s+phar na i mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa zhabs bsil ni /
NK028(sa)001:2916: yang dag nyid du dag mod kyang //
NK028(sa)001:2917: 'jig rten srid zhu'i tshul gyis ni //
NK028(sa)001:2918: phyag dang zhabs ni bsil mdzod la //
NK028(sa)001:2919: 'di nyid du ni bzhugs du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:2921: phyi nang brtag cing +amo badz+ra l+aa s+ya h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:2923: badz+ra girti hri badz+ra nirti +aah phyi'o /
NK028(sa)001:2926: badz+ra a lo ke h+r+ai badz+ra gan+d+he a h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:2927: nags tshal bcud ni yid khar 'ong //
NK028(sa)001:2928: dri zhim rgyas pa lha yi rdzas //
NK028(sa)001:2929: sa yi lha mo 'khor bcas la //
NK028(sa)001:2930: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags kyis //
NK028(sa)001:2931: bzhes nas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK028(sa)001:2932: badz+ra d+hu pe p+au dza me g+ha sa mu tra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:2933: gtsang zhing gtsang mar skyes pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:2934: lha rdzas bzang po'i me tog 'di //
NK028(sa)001:2935: sa yi lha mo 'khor bcas la //
NK028(sa)001:2936: bdag gis dad pas 'bul lags kyi //
NK028(sa)001:2937: bzhes nas kun tu dgyes par mdzod //
NK028(sa)001:2938: badz+ra push+pe p+au tsa me g+ha sa mu tra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:2939: sdug bsngal 'joms shing bkra shis pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:2940: dge zhing mun sel mar me 'di //
NK028(sa)001:2941: sa yi lha mo 'khor bcas la /
NK028(sa)001:2942: bdag gi dad pas 'bul lags kyi //
NK028(sa)001:2943: bzhes nas kun tu dgyes par mdzod //
NK028(sa)001:2944: badz+ra a lo ke pu tsa me g+ha sa mu
NK028(sa)001:2945: tra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum s+w+aa h+aa
NK028(sa)001:2946: / gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yi //
NK028(sa)001:2947: lha rdzas bzang po'i dri chab 'di //
NK028(sa)001:2948: sa yi lha mo 'khor bcas la //
NK028(sa)001:2949: bdag gis bzhes nas bdag badz+ra gan+d+he p+au tsa me /
NK028(sa)001:2950: sman rnams bcud ldan yid khar 'ong //
NK028(sa)001:2951: sngags kyi zhal zas bshos 'di dag /
NK028(sa)001:2952: sa yi lha mo bdag gis thugs rjes dgongs la bzhes su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:2953: +amo a ha ra a ha ra sarba ba da
NK028(sa)001:2954: ra p+au tsi te s+w+aa h+aa b+aa ling ta kh+aa
NK028(sa)001:2955: hi / rol mo'i sgra sgrags cing //
NK028(sa)001:2956: 'og phyogs sa yi lha mo brtan ma 'bar //
NK028(sa)001:2957: sku gser phyag na gser gyi bum pa bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:2958: 'ja' tshon 'od ldan phag gi khri la bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:2959: de la phyag 'tshal bsnyen bskur mchod pa 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:2961: sa'i lha mo brtan ma 'khor dang bcas pa rnams la 'phrin las gsol ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:2962: sngon dam bcas pa'i 'phrin las kyis sa gzhi dge zhing bkra shis par byin gyis rlabs tu gsol /
NK028(sa)001:2963: phyogs skyong ba'i 'phrin las kyis 'og gi phyogs srungs du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:2964: rigs 'dul ba'i 'phrin las kyis sa bdag gi gdon 'khor dang bcas pa bzlog tu gsol lo //
NK028(sa)001:2966: zhes pa'i sngags brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas pas sngags kyi 'od zer gyis sa'i nyes skyon sbyangs nas /
NK028(sa)001:2967: dngos grub kyi sa gzhir gyur par bsam mo //
NK028(sa)001:2968: de nas 'khor gyi sa bdag spyan drang zhing mchod pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:2969: 'dzam gling spyir gnas mthu chen dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:2970: nam zla dus 'dzin dbyar dgun ston dpyid la //
NK028(sa)001:2971: rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs ston dpyid kun la 'tshe //
NK028(sa)001:2972: sa bdag gtsang kun tsang tshang 'khor bcas dang //
NK028(sa)001:2973: sa bdag hong pan dang ni the se dang //
NK028(sa)001:2974: be sna lag chen sa bdag gnyan tshogs rnams //
NK028(sa)001:2975: mchod sbyin gtor ma'i 'gron du spyan 'dren na //
NK028(sa)001:2976: byams thugs brtse phyir gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:2977: yul ris 'di yis sa la mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:2978: gangs ri g.ya' ri brag ri spangs ri dang //
NK028(sa)001:2979: bye ri la gnas sa bdag 'khor dang bcas //
NK028(sa)001:2980: klu chu klu rgyun rgya mtsho chu bran dang //
NK028(sa)001:2981: chu mig rdzing dang khron par gnas la sogs //
NK028(sa)001:2982: sa gzhi 'di na gnas pa 'khor dang bcas //
NK028(sa)001:2983: rigs dang kha dog mi mthun bzhugs so 'tshal //
NK028(sa)001:2984: mchod sbyin gtor ma'i mgron du spyan 'dren na //
NK028(sa)001:2985: bde gshegs bka' yi gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:2987: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la //
NK028(sa)001:2988: na ga tri yam am gu sha dza dzah zhes gtor ma'i 'gron spyan drangs nas /
NK028(sa)001:2989: gtor ma sngags drug phyag rgya drug gis byin gyis brlabs la /
NK028(sa)001:2991: rgyas par ba shams pa'i mchod spyin gtor ma la /
NK028(sa)001:2992: gser dngul la sogs rin chen sna lngas brgyan //
NK028(sa)001:2993: sa bdag 'khor dang bcas la mchod par 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:2994: nor dbyig srang mang grangs su bzhes su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:2995: rin chen 'bru sna ma lus zas kyi mchog /
NK028(sa)001:2996: ras rus lhu tshigs nyams chags bskang slad du //
NK028(sa)001:2997: chags med stong ldan sems kyis 'bul lags na //
NK028(sa)001:2998: bzhes nas lhu tshigs slud ni sobs par mdzod //
NK028(sa)001:2999: bu ram sbrang rtsi ka ra 'o ma mar //
NK028(sa)001:3000: dug gsum sems la zhugs pa'i nad rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:3001: khro gtum drag po'i sdug bsngal bsal slad du //
NK028(sa)001:3002: zhi dul mnyes des mchod par bzhes su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3003: na ga ge sar la sogs sman sna brgyad //
NK028(sa)001:3004: chags nyams nad 'grams gdug pa gsal ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:3005: sa bdag sku yi snyung rkyen sbyang pa'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:3006: dka' zhing dkon pa'i yul nas btsal bsags te //
NK028(sa)001:3007: dbang chen sa bdag 'khor dang bcas pa la //
NK028(sa)001:3008: nyes skyon god sobs don du 'bul lags na //
NK028(sa)001:3009: yun du skyid cing dge ba'i sems nyid kyis //
NK028(sa)001:3010: dam rdzas bdud rtsi gtor ma bzhes su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3011: de nas gser skyems bsngo ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:3012: h+aum lcags ri dngul ri gser gyi ri //
NK028(sa)001:3013: shel ri gangs ri khyud 'khor nas //
NK028(sa)001:3014: mi la nor gyi dbyig 'byung zhing //
NK028(sa)001:3015: chos zas gnas lugs spyod pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:3016: mthu chen lha yi sman la sogs //
NK028(sa)001:3017: sa bdag gnyan po 'khor bcas la //
NK028(sa)001:3018: kun sbyar dri yis sbyar ba'i 'bru yi skyems //
NK028(sa)001:3019: rin chen gser gyi sa le sbram gyis spras //
NK028(sa)001:3020: rgyud nas bshad pa'i shel lnga la sogs 'di //
NK028(sa)001:3021: sa bdag rgyal po 'khor dang bcas la 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:3023: lag pa gnyis rin chen sgrom bu'i phyag rgya bcas la //
NK028(sa)001:3024: na mahsarba ta tha ga te b+h+yo bi shwa mu khe b+h+ya /
NK028(sa)001:3025: sarba th+aa kham ut+ga te s+pha ra na hi mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:3027: gser skyems gtor ma sbrengs la //
NK028(sa)001:3028: 'dod pa'i yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pas //
NK028(sa)001:3029: so so'i rgyud tshims par bsam //
NK028(sa)001:3030: gser skyems lhag ma sa phyogs kun tu gtor zhing /
NK028(sa)001:3031: yul gyi gdon phra mo rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:3032: glo bur du lhags pa'i 'gron rnams tshim par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:3033: lag pa gnyis thal mo sbyar nas ngag tu /
NK028(sa)001:3035: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:3036: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:3037: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3038: bdag rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam dral rnams kyi bsod nams gyis stobs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3039: sngags dang ting nge 'dzin gyi mthus /
NK028(sa)001:3040: mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma rgya chen po 'di 'bul
NK028(sa)001:3041: ba'i gnas ni 'dzam bu'i gling du spyir gnas pa'i
NK028(sa)001:3042: sa bdag gi tshogs ma lus pa rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:3043: yul khams 'di na gnas pa'i sa bdag gnyan gyis tshogs rgyal po dang /
NK028(sa)001:3048: g.yog 'khor dang bcas pa rnams la 'bul lo //
NK028(sa)001:3050: de dag gi spyan lam du /
NK028(sa)001:3054: zhal zas gyi bye brag tu gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:3055: de la gnas kyi khyad par ni ri rab gling bzhi gling phran brgyad /
NK028(sa)001:3056: mtha' lcags ri mu khyud kyis bskor ba de na bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun dang //
NK028(sa)001:3057: me tog brtsegs pa'i lding khang dang //
NK028(sa)001:3058: rtsi thog rgyas pa'i ne'u seng dang //
NK028(sa)001:3059: tsan dan gyi skyed mos tshal dang /
NK028(sa)001:3060: dar tshon sna lnga'i lam dang /
NK028(sa)001:3065: gser gyi sa gzhi la rin po che zhun ma'i thig bkye ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:3066: gser gyis skud pas mig mngas ris su bris pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:3067: rin po che brgyad kyi gcal du bkram pa la sogs te //
NK028(sa)001:3068: rang gzhan gyi yid dang mthun pa'i gnas su gyur nas //
NK028(sa)001:3069: pho brang gzhan du bskyod par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:3073: dbang po lag pa la sogs pa sman sna tshogs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:3074: sa bdag 'od dang gzi mdangs su ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:3075: de nas mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bsngosa pas chud ma zos shing /
NK028(sa)001:3076: dmigs pa gzhan du ma gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:3077: sa bdag rnams dgyes rab kyi mchog mnyes rab kyi phul du phyin par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:3078: de ltar bsngosa ba sa sa bdag 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyis dbang po'i spyod yul du /
NK028(sa)001:3079: chos dang zang zing gi sbyin pa rnam pa gnyis po char bzhin du 'bab par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:3080: de ltar gyur bas zang zing gi sbyin pas ni dbang po tshim /
NK028(sa)001:3081: chos kyi sbyin pas shes pa'i rgyud grol nas //
NK028(sa)001:3082: sa bdag gi gdug rtsub kyi sems zhi ba chen por gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:3083: bdag cag gi bsgrub pa zab mo 'di la bgegs
NK028(sa)001:3084: dang bar chad kyi bsam sbyor skad cig tsam yang
NK028(sa)001:3086: sa phyogs 'dir bdag rdo rje slob dpon che ge mos //
NK028(sa)001:3087: mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid mdo
NK028(sa)001:3088: sgyu sems gsum gyi lag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil
NK028(sa)001:3089: 'khor chen po bzhengs su gsol bas /
NK028(sa)001:3090: zhag grangs sam pho brang gzhan du bskyod cig /
NK028(sa)001:3091: 'byung bo gang dag ri rab stengs gnas dang //
NK028(sa)001:3092: dga' ba'i tshal dang lha yi yul khams dang //
NK028(sa)001:3093: shar nub ri dang nyi zla'i khyim rnams dang //
NK028(sa)001:3094: ri bo kun la gang dag gnas pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:3095: rin chen gling na lhag par gang gnas dang //
NK028(sa)001:3096: chu bo kun dang chu yi mdo rnams dang //
NK028(sa)001:3097: mtsho dang rdzing bu lteng ka chu ngogs dang //
NK028(sa)001:3098: g.ya' chu bsil ma can na gang gnas dang //
NK028(sa)001:3099: grong dang phyugs lhas grong khyer stong pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:3100: khang stong dag dang lha yi khang pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:3101: gtsug lag khang dang mchod rten gnas rnams dang //
NK028(sa)001:3102: dka' thub gnas dang glang chen bres rnams dang //
NK028(sa)001:3103: rgyal po'i dkor khang dag na gang gnas dang //
NK028(sa)001:3104: lam srang sum mdo dang ni bzhi mdo dang //
NK028(sa)001:3105: gang dag lam po che dang shing gcig drung //
NK028(sa)001:3106: dur khrod chen po nag tshal chen po dang //
NK028(sa)001:3107: seng ge dred dang gcan gzan gnas rnams dang //
NK028(sa)001:3108: 'brog chen 'jigs su rung bar gang gnas dang //
NK028(sa)001:3109: gang dag gling mchog dag na gnas pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:3110: lhun po dur khrod dag na gnas pa rnams //
NK028(sa)001:3111: rab tu dgyes shing mgu bar gyur nas su //
NK028(sa)001:3112: 'phreng ba dri dang byug pa me tog dang //
NK028(sa)001:3113: bstod dang gtor ma mar me gus 'bul na //
NK028(sa)001:3114: 'di dag gsol zhing legs par bsnams nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:3115: bdag gi las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK028(sa)001:3116: de nas lha mo dge ba'i dpang du bzhag pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:3118: bcom ldan 'das che mchog he rus kas /
NK028(sa)001:3120: tshogs gnyis rdzogs te mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:3121: sa 'di'i steng du sangs rgyas pa lha mo khyod kyis mkhyen te dpang du gyur /
NK028(sa)001:3122: da lta bskal pa bzang po 'di nyid la /
NK028(sa)001:3123: ston pa sh+aakya thub pas bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs te /
NK028(sa)001:3124: srod la bdud bye ba dung phyur dang bcas pa brtul nas /
NK028(sa)001:3125: tho rangs rdo rje gdan la mngon par rdzogs par
NK028(sa)001:3126: sangs rgyas pa yang sa'i lha mo khyod kyis dpang
NK028(sa)001:3127: po mdzad de sangs rgyas pa de bzhin du /
NK028(sa)001:3128: de ring bdag rdo rje slob dpon chen pos //
NK028(sa)001:3129: slob ma che ge mo smin cing tshogs gnyis rdzogs par bya ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:3130: sems can thams cad kyang bla na med pa'i byang chub thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:3131: sa phyogs 'dir mdo sgyu sems gsum gyis lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyis dkyil 'khor bzhengs su gsol bas /
NK028(sa)001:3132: sa'i lha mos dge ba'i stong grogs dang dpang po mdzad du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3134: khur tshur kha gan kyal du byas pa'i mathe'u chung gnyis sbrel la /
NK028(sa)001:3135: 'dzub mo gnyis rtse sprad pa'i phyag rgyas 'debs pa'i tshul bya zhing /
NK028(sa)001:3136: b+he ka tra ma yam zhes brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:3137: sa'i lha mos mdun gyi nam mkha' btegs ste dpang por bzhugs so //
NK028(sa)001:3138: de nas sa'i bar chad bsal bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:3139: bgegs la bka' bsgo ba bya ba'i don du lag pa gnyis se gol gdab cing /
NK028(sa)001:3140: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes lan gsum gyis /
NK028(sa)001:3141: dkyil 'khor gyis lha tshogs thams cad mdun gyi nam mkha' la spyan drangs nas //
NK028(sa)001:3142: bdag bdud rtsi 'khyil par gsal ba de la /
NK028(sa)001:3143: h+aum bzhis byin bsdu bar bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:3145: mdun gyi nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i /
NK028(sa)001:3146: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs /
NK028(sa)001:3147: thams cad 'od zer gyi tshul du bsdu //
NK028(sa)001:3148: yang h+aum zhes brjod pas 'od zer de dag thams cad bdag la bsdu /
NK028(sa)001:3150: 'od zer gyis bdag gis lus ngag yid gsum gyis
NK028(sa)001:3151: sdig sgrib kyi bag chags thams cad ba mo la
NK028(sa)001:3152: nyi zer phog pa bzhin du sbyangs /
NK028(sa)001:3153: yang h+aum zhes brjod pas rang gi sems nyid dag
NK028(sa)001:3154: pa'i ngo bo yi ge h+aum mthing ga gsal ba'i
NK028(sa)001:3155: ngang la / sngags pa go rjes pa'i tshul du /
NK028(sa)001:3156: +amo badz+ra sh+ri he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:3157: zhes brjod pas skad cig gis bdag zhe sdang rdo
NK028(sa)001:3158: rje sku mdog mthing nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs zhal
NK028(sa)001:3159: bsgrad pa / mche ba brtsigs pa /
NK028(sa)001:3161: phyag g.yas rdo rje rtse dgu pa /
NK028(sa)001:3162: g.yon dril bu skur brten pa de'i rkang mthil dang thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du /
NK028(sa)001:3163: h+aum mthing nag 'bar ba re bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:3164: sa bdag rnams la bka' bsgo ste /
NK028(sa)001:3166: dril bu dkrol ba'i rjes la /
NK028(sa)001:3167: na mo dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:3168: mdo sgyu sems gsum kyi lha tshogs rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:3170: bdag rdo rje slob dpon chen pos slob ma che
NK028(sa)001:3171: ge mo la sogs pa sems can thams cad kyi
NK028(sa)001:3172: bla na med pa'i ye shes thob par bya ba'i
NK028(sa)001:3174: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi rgyal po mdo sgyu sems
NK028(sa)001:3175: gsum gyis dkyil 'khor chen po 'byung ba yin pas
NK028(sa)001:3176: / sa 'di la gnas pa'i sa bdag pho mo dang /
NK028(sa)001:3177: sa bdag gi 'khor pho mo dang /
NK028(sa)001:3182: de la sogs pa'i 'khor rigs ngan du gtogs pa thams cad /
NK028(sa)001:3183: bdag cag gi sgrub pa 'di la bgegs dang bar
NK028(sa)001:3184: chad ma byed par sgrub pa 'di ma thon gyi
NK028(sa)001:3185: bar du / gnas gzhan du dengs shig /
NK028(sa)001:3186: gang dag mi 'gro ba de dag ni /
NK028(sa)001:3187: dpal rdo rje h+aum zhes bya ba spyan rab tu 'bar bas /
NK028(sa)001:3188: mgo bo tshal pa brgya ru 'gas pa 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:3190: rol mo dang bcas pas gtor ma phyiir skyal /
NK028(sa)001:3191: rkang pa rdo rje 'gros gyis dbang ldan mtshams nas brtsams nas /
NK028(sa)001:3193: thugs ka dang rkang mthil gyis h+aum gis 'od zer
NK028(sa)001:3194: gyis steng 'og phyogs mtshams rdo rje gur du gyur
NK028(sa)001:3195: par bsam zhing / lag pa g.yas pa rdo rje bkan thabs su dkur g.yas su brten cing //
NK028(sa)001:3196: g.yon pa rkang zhabs dang bstun pa'i dril bu 'khrol bzhin pas /
NK028(sa)001:3197: rdo rje rgya gram gyi 'gros re tshar ba'i rjes su /
NK028(sa)001:3200: g+h+rih+na pa ya g+h+rih+na pa ya h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:3203: bid+ya r+aa dza ya h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:3205: rdo rje'i 'gros kyis sa phyogs kun 'khor ba'i rjes su /
NK028(sa)001:3206: yungs kar khro mo'i sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab par dmigs nas /
NK028(sa)001:3207: slar yang s+aum+b+ha ni'i sngags brjod cing /
NK028(sa)001:3209: sgra ring po dang bcas pa'i /
NK028(sa)001:3211: khro bo de dag slar 'dus nas /
NK028(sa)001:3212: steng 'og phyogs mtshams bsrung bar bsam /
NK028(sa)001:3214: bdag zhe sdang rdo rje dang /
NK028(sa)001:3215: khro bo rnams kyi spyan rab tu 'bar ba las /
NK028(sa)001:3216: bskal pa' me lta bu byung nas /
NK028(sa)001:3217: me'i gur du gyur par bsam mo //
NK028(sa)001:3218: de nas sa'i dbus su brjid bag dang ldan par 'dug la /
NK028(sa)001:3219: dbang phyug bdag zhe sdang rdo rje bsam gtan gyis /
NK028(sa)001:3220: lag pa g.yas pa'i 'theb chen dang /
NK028(sa)001:3221: 'theb chung gis rdo rje 'dzin bzhin pa'i tri shu la'i phyag rgya dang ldan pas /
NK028(sa)001:3223: skyobs pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyis /
NK028(sa)001:3224: spyod pa'i tshul dang thams cad ni /
NK028(sa)001:3225: sa dang pha rol phyin pa la //
NK028(sa)001:3226: lha mo khyod ni dpang du gyur //
NK028(sa)001:3227: ji ltar che mchog rdo rje yis //
NK028(sa)001:3228: dpung bzhi bdud kyi sde brtul nas //
NK028(sa)001:3229: rgyal srid chos kyi dpung gtsugs pa //
NK028(sa)001:3230: de bzhin du ni bdag gis kyang //
NK028(sa)001:3231: nges par bya phyir dkyil 'khor bri //
NK028(sa)001:3232: sa yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3233: rat+na pa shi sit+d+ha ku ru sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK028(sa)001:3234: zhes brjod cing tri shu la'i phyag rgya lan gsum sa la bsnun pas /
NK028(sa)001:3235: nam mkha' la dpang por bzhugs pa'i sa'i lha mo
NK028(sa)001:3236: 'od du zhu nas 'od sa gzhi la thim pas
NK028(sa)001:3237: / sa nyid rtags rin chen sna lnga'i phye ma
NK028(sa)001:3238: don ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gyur par bsam mo
NK028(sa)001:3239: / // bzhi pa dbang du bya ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:3240: sa gzhi dngos grub can de bar chad kyi dbang du mi btang pa'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:3241: zhe sdang rdo rje'i thugs ka'i h+aum las /
NK028(sa)001:3242: dbang gi khro bo sku mdog dmar po //
NK028(sa)001:3243: stod zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa /
NK028(sa)001:3244: smad phur pa'i dbal zla gam du 'dug pa /
NK028(sa)001:3245: phyag g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis pad+ma dang zhags pa ba snams /
NK028(sa)001:3246: tha ma gnyis dbang gi phur pa 'dril cing /
NK028(sa)001:3247: ngag tu pad+ma ki la ya dza phatah zhes phyung nas /
NK028(sa)001:3248: zangs sam shing dmar mo la byas pa'i phur pa dbal zla gam sa la bstim nas /
NK028(sa)001:3249: mdun du snod gtsang ma'i nang du 'bru'i phung po la gtsugs /
NK028(sa)001:3250: lag pa gnyis rdo rje'i phyag rgyas phur pa'i spyi bor btugs shing /
NK028(sa)001:3251: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku'i byin gyis rlabs par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:3253: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko ham /
NK028(sa)001:3255: de bzhin du phur pas mgrin par btugs la /
NK028(sa)001:3256: de bzhi na gshegs pa thams cad kyis gsung gis byin gyis rlabs par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:3258: sarba ta th+aa ga ta w+aa ga badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko ham /
NK028(sa)001:3260: de bzhin du phur pa'i thugs kar gtugs nas /
NK028(sa)001:3261: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin gyis brlabs par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:3262: sarba ta th+aa ga tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko ham /
NK028(sa)001:3264: de nas dbang gi phur pa byin rlabs dang ldan pa de /
NK028(sa)001:3265: bdag zhe sdang rdo rje'i bsam gtan gyis phyag gnyis kyis gril la ngag tu /
NK028(sa)001:3266: pad+ma ki li ki la ya sarba pa sham ma na ho /
NK028(sa)001:3269: sa gzhi dngos grub can de bdag gi dbang du
NK028(sa)001:3270: gyur pas sa yang bkra shis shing gzhan gyis bar
NK028(sa)001:3271: du mi gcod par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:3272: ngag tu pa sham ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:3274: lnga pa sa sbyong pa la /
NK028(sa)001:3275: sbyong pa las me sngags phyag rgya /
NK028(sa)001:3279: las dang bya bas sbyangs ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:3281: sngags phyag rgyas sbyang ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:3283: dang po las dang bya bas sbyang ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:3284: sngar dbang gi phur pa sa la btab pa de bton la /
NK028(sa)001:3286: bdag zhe sdang rdo rje'i thugs kar bstim zhing /
NK028(sa)001:3287: phur pa dben par bzhag go //
NK028(sa)001:3288: de nas lto 'phye'i lto ba las sa brkos te /
NK028(sa)001:3290: dkyil 'khor ji tsam rtsigs pa'i rgya dang dpang gi
NK028(sa)001:3291: tshad dam yang na zabs su chu'am rdo la thug
NK028(sa)001:3292: par brko ba yang gsungs so //
NK028(sa)001:3293: 'di'i skabs su sa bzang ngan brtags pas /
NK028(sa)001:3294: mi shis pa'i mtshan ma sna tshogs pa byung na gnas gzhan du spo ba'am /
NK028(sa)001:3295: sa ngan pa tsam la ni zhi ba'i sbyin bsreg gis sbyangs pa sa 'dag par gsungs so //
NK028(sa)001:3297: rdza'i bum pa longs ma spyad pa'i nang du /
NK028(sa)001:3301: a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du /
NK028(sa)001:3302: tram las bum gter rin po che'i mchod sdong du bsam la /
NK028(sa)001:3303: dgos 'dod thams cad 'byung bar mos pas /
NK028(sa)001:3304: g.yam pas kha bcad la bzhag go /
NK028(sa)001:3305: sa'i ro lnga la sogs pa bsal la /
NK028(sa)001:3306: sa phud kyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mchod cing /
NK028(sa)001:3307: sa brkos pa'i nang rnams la khyab par gtor ro //
NK028(sa)001:3308: de nas las mkhan rnams kyis dkyil 'khor brtsigs te //
NK028(sa)001:3309: sngar kyi ro lnga bsal ba'i sa rnams dang //
NK028(sa)001:3310: gzhan yang sa bzang po sna tshogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3311: zhing mu ma la sogs pa'i bkra shis pa'i sa rnams bsres la /
NK028(sa)001:3312: dri bzang po'i chus bran zhing /
NK028(sa)001:3314: 'chad par 'gyur ba'i skabs kyi rgyas bsdus gang byed du brtsigs la /
NK028(sa)001:3315: de yang me long gi ngos ltar 'jam zhing mthas par bya /
NK028(sa)001:3316: ba byug lngas mnyam par byug /
NK028(sa)001:3317: de nas go ma yengs nyi shu rtsa lnga btang ste /
NK028(sa)001:3321: gzhan sel phung po lnga rang dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:3322: don gnyer sku lnga ma brtsal bar thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:3329: de bzhin du dbang po lnga dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:3330: 'phrin las lnga thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:3334: ga bur dang spos lnga'i lde gus byug /
NK028(sa)001:3336: yon tan lnga thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:3337: rin po che lnga'i dod la /
NK028(sa)001:3342: g.yu dang lnga'i lde gus byug /
NK028(sa)001:3344: ye shes lnga thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:3349: mar te snying po lnga'i lde gus byug /
NK028(sa)001:3351: gsung lnga thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:3359: rigs lnga thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:3363: sha chen dang bdud rtsis lnga'i lde gus byug /
NK028(sa)001:3364: de ltar ba byug dang bcas pa'i go ma ye sum cu so lnga rims kyis sam /
NK028(sa)001:3365: cig car du byug par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:3366: gnyis pa mes sbyang ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:3367: sngon du sa rang gi mtshan nyid brtag pas /
NK028(sa)001:3368: sa'i mtshan nyid bzang po ma rnyed pa'am /
NK028(sa)001:3370: zhi ba'i sbyin bsreg gcig gam bdun /
NK028(sa)001:3371: brgya la sogs pas dag par gsungs pas /
NK028(sa)001:3373: cho ga ni zur du shes par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:3374: gsum pa sngags dang phyag rgyas sbyang ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:3376: badz+ra kro d+ha ha na ha na kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:3377: ces brjod cing rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i phyag rgya
NK028(sa)001:3378: kha shar du phyogs pas dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su
NK028(sa)001:3379: btugs pas / rdo rje las sngags kyis 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK028(sa)001:3381: ye shes rang rang gi sa gzhir mos par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:3382: bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyang ba la gnyis /
NK028(sa)001:3383: dang po mtshan ma med pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:3384: chos tha mas cad rang bzhin gyis ye nas rnam par dag pa ltar /
NK028(sa)001:3385: dmigs pa med pa'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom zhing /
NK028(sa)001:3386: lag pa thal mo khong stong du sbyar nas /
NK028(sa)001:3388: ma h+aa shu nya ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko ham /
NK028(sa)001:3390: sa dang sar 'dzin gyi rtog pa thams cad stong pa nyid kyis ye shes su sbyang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:3391: gnyis pa mtshan ma dang bcas pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyang ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:3392: sgra ring po dang bcas pa'i h+aum zhes brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:3393: bdag zhe sdang rdo rjer gsal ba'i thugs ka'i h+aum gsal btab /
NK028(sa)001:3395: e yam ram bam lam rnams rim pa bzhin du ngag tu 'ang brjod cing /
NK028(sa)001:3397: yi ge de dag rim kyis brtsegs par bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:3400: yi ge de dag gi 'od zer phyogs bcu mtha' yas par 'phros pas /
NK028(sa)001:3401: sems can thams cad gyi 'byung ba lnga dang /
NK028(sa)001:3402: ngar 'dzin gyi rtog pa mtha' dag sbyangs nas /
NK028(sa)001:3403: sam ha ra na h+aum zhes brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:3404: slar 'dus te 'og phyogs su e las nam mkha'i dkyil 'khor yangs zhing rgya che ba /
NK028(sa)001:3405: de'i steng du yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor gzhu'i dbyibs lta bu ba dan gyis mtshan pa /
NK028(sa)001:3406: de'i steng du ram las me'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum dmar po /
NK028(sa)001:3407: de'i steng du bam las chu'i dkyil 'khor zlum po dkar po /
NK028(sa)001:3408: de'i steng du lam las sa'i dkyil 'khor gru bzhi pa gser gyis mdog can de /
NK028(sa)001:3409: ye shes rang snang gi 'byung ba lngar bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:3410: de'i steng du bdag gi thugs ka'i h+aum las b+h+rum 'phros par bsam zhing /
NK028(sa)001:3411: ngag tu b+h+rum zhes brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:3412: b+h+rum de dkar po 'byung pa lnga'i dkyil 'khor la phog pas thams cad 'od du zhu bar bsams /
NK028(sa)001:3414: b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud d+he dz+ny+aa na badz+ra tsakra zhes brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:3415: 'od phung de ye shes rang snang gi gzhal yas
NK028(sa)001:3416: khang 'chad par 'gyur ba'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan dang
NK028(sa)001:3417: / lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ji lta bar gdan dang bcas par mos par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:3418: drug pa byin gyis rlabs pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:3419: dkyil 'khor sa stegs kyi dbus su /
NK028(sa)001:3422: mchod yon la sogs pa'i phyi mchod dang /
NK028(sa)001:3423: sman raka gtor gsum la sogs gong bzhin bshams /
NK028(sa)001:3424: de nas rdo rje slob dpon rgyas pa'i las su zhugs la /
NK028(sa)001:3425: lag pa gnyis rdo rje dril bu dang ldan pas /
NK028(sa)001:3426: dkyil 'khor gzhal yas khang du mos la /
NK028(sa)001:3427: rdo rje'i 'gros kyis bskor ba byas nas /
NK028(sa)001:3428: lte ba'i gdan thog tu phyin la /
NK028(sa)001:3429: bde bar 'dug cing zhal shar du gzigs la /
NK028(sa)001:3431: med na'ang ting nge 'dzin gyis bdag mi bskyod pa'am /
NK028(sa)001:3432: he ru ka yab yum du bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:3433: de'i sbyor mtshams nas byang sems 'phros pa las dkyil 'khor gyis lha rnams /
NK028(sa)001:3434: yan lag lhag pa'i lha dang bcas pa /
NK028(sa)001:3436: sbyor mtshams nas 'phros pa'i byang chub sems kyi 'od zer gyis /
NK028(sa)001:3437: dus gsum gyis sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs dam gyis rgyud bskul bar bsgom zhing /
NK028(sa)001:3438: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes pa se gol dang bcas pa lan gsum gyis snyan gsan dbab /
NK028(sa)001:3440: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang bcas pas lan gsum gyis /
NK028(sa)001:3441: mdun gyis nam mkha' la ye shes pa spyan drangs la phyi'i mchod pa kun bzang //
NK028(sa)001:3443: nang gi mchod pa sman rag gtor gsum /
NK028(sa)001:3444: gsang ba'i mchod pa ta na sbyor sgrol ga na 'bul lo //
NK028(sa)001:3445: de nas shar la sogs pa'i phyogs bzhir /
NK028(sa)001:3446: dung can ma la sogs yum bzhi 'am /
NK028(sa)001:3447: med na bsgom pa'ang rung ste /
NK028(sa)001:3448: spyan ma la sogs pa'i dam tshig gis yum bzhir bskyed la /
NK028(sa)001:3450: sku gsung thugs byin gyis rlabs /
NK028(sa)001:3451: ye shes kyi yum bzhi sa man dzah snyan gsan dbab /
NK028(sa)001:3454: phyogs kyi yum bzhi pos dkyil 'khor gyis byin rlabs bskul ba'i don du /
NK028(sa)001:3456: yum bzhi kun gyis dus gcig la'ang rung ste /
NK028(sa)001:3458: kun bzang bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK028(sa)001:3459: rgyal ba rgya mtsho ye shes kyi //
NK028(sa)001:3460: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas kyis //
NK028(sa)001:3461: spyod pa rgya mtsho rmad byung kun //
NK028(sa)001:3462: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK028(sa)001:3463: sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo bi shwa mu khe
NK028(sa)001:3464: b+h+ya sarba tha kham ut+ga te s+pha ra na i
NK028(sa)001:3465: mam ga ga na kham swah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:3467: yang dag nyid du dag mod kyang //
NK028(sa)001:3468: 'jig rten srid zhu'i tshul gyis ni //
NK028(sa)001:3469: phyag dang zhabs ni bsil mdzod la //
NK028(sa)001:3470: 'di nyid du ni bzhugs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3471: badz+ra bzhi bsnol l+aa s+ya h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:3481: rdo rje las rim ltar na //
NK028(sa)001:3482: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs shing //
NK028(sa)001:3483: rang rig mtha' da bus med pa dkyil //
NK028(sa)001:3485: dkyil 'khor snying po bshad du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3486: ces phyogs bzhi ka nas zhu /
NK028(sa)001:3489: sangs rgyas kun dang grong khyer nyid //
NK028(sa)001:3490: de ring shis par mdzad du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3491: thams cad bdag nyid dgongs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3494: shar nas zhi ba'i ye shes rang snang ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:3495: brgyan rnams kun gyis rab mdzes pa //
NK028(sa)001:3496: sangs rgyas kun gyis sku yi mchog /
NK028(sa)001:3497: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3499: lho nas kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol dang /
NK028(sa)001:3500: yon tan rin chen rgyas pa'i gtso /
NK028(sa)001:3501: ma lus kun gyi re ba ba skongs //
NK028(sa)001:3502: sangs rgyas kun gyis yon tan mchog /
NK028(sa)001:3503: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3506: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol dang //
NK028(sa)001:3507: rang bzhin dag pas gos pa med //
NK028(sa)001:3508: sangs rgyas kun gyis gsung gi mchog /
NK028(sa)001:3509: 'dod chags pha rol phyin pas brnyes //
NK028(sa)001:3510: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3513: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol dang //
NK028(sa)001:3514: bsam pa thams cad rab rdzogs pa /
NK028(sa)001:3515: thams cad sgrol ba'i ded dpon mchog /
NK028(sa)001:3516: sangs rgyas kun gyis 'phrin las mchog /
NK028(sa)001:3517: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3518: ces brjod cing lung gis bskul lo //
NK028(sa)001:3519: dbang phyug gis mdun gyi nam mkhar gzigs nas //
NK028(sa)001:3520: rdo rje dril bus 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis bskul ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:3521: phyogs bcu ma lus dus gsum gyis //
NK028(sa)001:3522: rgyal ba sras bcas dgongs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3523: ch+gee mo sogs don gyi phyir /
NK028(sa)001:3524: dkyil 'khor chen po bdag bgyid pas //
NK028(sa)001:3525: bdag cag rnams ni bsrungs ba'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:3526: sa 'di shis par byin rlabs par /
NK028(sa)001:3527: bde bar gshegs pas ma dzad du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3529: dbang phyug gdan las bzhengs la //
NK028(sa)001:3530: sngar bzhin h+aum bzhis bsdus la //
NK028(sa)001:3531: zhe sdang rdo rje'i nga rgyal gyis //
NK028(sa)001:3532: rdo rje 'dzin dang nyi ma dang //
NK028(sa)001:3533: chos dang rta mchog snang mdzad kyang //
NK028(sa)001:3534: bdag nyid chen po nga nyid yin //
NK028(sa)001:3535: thams cad bka' las deng ma 'da' //
NK028(sa)001:3538: shar phyogs su phyin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:3539: sngar gyi zhu pa po gnyis g.yas gnyis g.yon te //
NK028(sa)001:3540: slob dpon lnga legs par bsgrigs la /
NK028(sa)001:3544: g.yas brkyang gi stangs stabs lan gsum dang /
NK028(sa)001:3545: badz+ra sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:3547: sum b+ha ni sum+b+ha h+aum brjod /
NK028(sa)001:3548: de nas dpon slob lnga po rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i 'gros kyis lhor phyin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:3550: g.yon brkyang gi stangs stabs lan gsum dang /
NK028(sa)001:3551: rat+na sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:3555: de nas rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i 'gros kyis nub tu phyin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:3557: zlum po'i stangs stabs lan gsum dang /
NK028(sa)001:3558: pad+ma sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:3560: grih+na pa ya grih+na pa ya h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:3561: 'gying 'gros gyis byang du phyin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:3563: sa ga'i stangs stabs lan gsum dang /
NK028(sa)001:3564: kar+m+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:3566: a na ya ho b+ha ga wan bid+ya r+aa dza ya h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:3568: de nas dga' ba yongs sbyor gyis 'gros kyis shar du phyin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:3569: sgeg mo'i 'jol 'gros kyis dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' bskor /
NK028(sa)001:3570: rdo rje rgya gram 'gros kyis kyang /
NK028(sa)001:3572: sum+b+ha ni'i 'chams brdung gis kyang dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' bskor ro //
NK028(sa)001:3573: de nas ma mo nyi shu'i gar ni /
NK028(sa)001:3575: g.yas zhing dbyug nam mkha' la 'phyar ba /
NK028(sa)001:3576: g.yon b+han d+ha thugs kar bsnams pa'i phyag rgya dang /
NK028(sa)001:3577: rkang pa g.yas bskum g.yon brkyang gi stangs stabs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:3581: mda' gzhu 'gengs pa'i phyag rgya sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3584: g.yas chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan nam mkha' la 'phyar ba /
NK028(sa)001:3585: g.yon thod khrag thugs kar bsnams pa'i phyag rgya sogs //
NK028(sa)001:3588: g.yas rdo rje nam mkha' 'phyar zhing //
NK028(sa)001:3589: g.yon zhing za ba'i phyag rgya sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3590: badz+ra bet+ta li ha shar lhor phyag g.yon pas zhing bsnams shing //
NK028(sa)001:3591: g.yas pas de'i rgyu ma 'dren pa'i phyag rgya sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3594: g.yon thod khrag thugs kar bsnams shing //
NK028(sa)001:3595: g.yas rdo rje dkrug pa'i phyag rgya sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3596: +amo badz+ra g+hasma r+ai hah nub byang /
NK028(sa)001:3597: phyag gnyis kyis zhing bzung nas //
NK028(sa)001:3598: khas snying za ba'i phyag rgya sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3599: badz+ra sme sh+aa n+ai h+aa byang shar /
NK028(sa)001:3601: g.yon pas de'i mgo gcod pa'i phyag rgya dang /
NK028(sa)001:3602: +amo badz+ra tsan+d+ha l+ai h+aa yang shar du /
NK028(sa)001:3603: phyag g.yas g.yon gnyis rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i phyag rgya thugs kar bsnol ba sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3607: rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgya thugs khar bsnol ba'i sogs badz+ra bya g+h+ri mu kh+aa he /
NK028(sa)001:3609: phyag g.yas g.yon gnyis kyi zhing gi lpags pa bsnams nas /
NK028(sa)001:3610: lces de'i chu ser 'dag pa'i phyag rgya sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3611: badz+ra ga la mu kh+aa he /
NK028(sa)001:3613: phyag gnyis kyis zhing gi khog pa phral te /
NK028(sa)001:3614: nang gi glo snying la mig gis 'bur tshugs su lta ba'i phyag rgya sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3615: badz+ra shwa na mu kh+aa he /
NK028(sa)001:3617: phyag g.yas gri gug nam mkhar 'phyar ba /
NK028(sa)001:3618: g.yon thod khrag thugs kar bsnams pa'i phyag rgya sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3621: phyag gnyis kyis zhing phrag pa la khur ba'i phyag rgya sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3622: badz+ra kam ka mu kh+aa he /
NK028(sa)001:3624: g.yas pas gri nam mkhar g.yon b+han d+ha thugs kar bsnams pa'i phyag rgya sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3625: badz+ra kha ka mu kh+aa he /
NK028(sa)001:3627: phyag g.yas lcags kyu nam mkhar 'phyar ba /
NK028(sa)001:3628: g.yon thod khrag thugs kar bsnams pa'i phyag rgya sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3629: badz+ra hu lu mu kh+aa he /
NK028(sa)001:3631: phyag g.yas pas lcags kyu nam mkhar 'phyar ba /
NK028(sa)001:3632: g.yon thod khrag thugs kar bsnams pa'i phyag rgya sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3633: badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dza /
NK028(sa)001:3635: phyag gnyis kyis rgyu ma'i zhags pa 'dren pa'i phyag rgya dang /
NK028(sa)001:3636: badz+ra ba ra ha mu kh+aa he /
NK028(sa)001:3638: phyag gnyis kyis lcags sgrogs 'dzin pa'i phyag rgya dang /
NK028(sa)001:3640: byang sgor phyag g.yas rdo rje dang /
NK028(sa)001:3641: g.yon dril bu bsnams pa'i phyag rgya sogs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:3642: badz+ra b+hasmi ba la ya ba to ho //
NK028(sa)001:3644: gar nyi shu po 'di la tshigs bcad gnyis re 'dug kyang /
NK028(sa)001:3645: 'phral du ma gzigs de ltar gar 'chams kyi rim pa rnams byas pas /
NK028(sa)001:3646: gzhal yas khang gi sa gzhi de mi 'gyur zhing
NK028(sa)001:3647: brtan pa rdo rje'i rang bzhin du mos par bya'o
NK028(sa)001:3648: // bdun pa sa bsrungs ba la /
NK028(sa)001:3650: zhe sdang rdo rje'i tshul bzung la /
NK028(sa)001:3651: 'bar ba'i spyan sogs bshad bzhin bya /
NK028(sa)001:3658: rgyal chen phyogs skyong gis phyi'i phyi mtshams bcad pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:3659: phyi'i nang mtshams dam sri brdungs la mnan pa bya ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:3660: phyi'i gsang mtsham sgo byang gdags pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:3662: gnas khang gi phyi rol du song la /
NK028(sa)001:3663: phyogs bzhir rgyal po chen po bzhi'i tho che ba bzhi'i rtse la tsa ka li gzugs pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:3664: phyogs bcur phyogs skyong bcu'i tho chung ba bcu brtsigs
NK028(sa)001:3665: la phyogs skyong bcu'i tsaka li bcu dkar rtsi btang
NK028(sa)001:3666: la gzugs / shar gyi tho'i rtsar mchod pa sna lnga dang /
NK028(sa)001:3668: gtor ma gser skyems rnams bshams la /
NK028(sa)001:3669: bdag nyid kha shar du phyogs pas /
NK028(sa)001:3670: h+r+aih pad+ma ta kri ta badz+ra kro d+ha h+ya g+h+ri ba h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:3671: zhes rta mgrin du khrong gis bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:3672: swa b+h+aa wa bi shud d+he d+har+m+aa th+aa badz+ra sid d+hi h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:3673: zhes dri chab kyi tho bsang /
NK028(sa)001:3675: shu nya ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko ham //
NK028(sa)001:3677: a tsan+da ma n+da la h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:3679: de'i steng du h+aum dkar po cig bsam /
NK028(sa)001:3681: sam ha ra na h+aum gis spro bsdu byas pas 'od du zhu ba las pi wam du gyur /
NK028(sa)001:3682: de yang par sang gis 'od du zhu ba las /
NK028(sa)001:3683: ti ta ra dza ye s+w+aa h+aa zhes pas yul 'khor bsrung sku mdog dkar po /
NK028(sa)001:3684: phyag na dri za'i rgyud mngas bsnams pa /
NK028(sa)001:3685: sku la dung khrab dang dbu la dung rmog gsol ba bskyed pa /
NK028(sa)001:3686: ma h+aa a ta ri sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:3687: mi bskyod pa ma h+aa shu nya ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:3689: ma h+aa pra ta pra be sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra s+w+aa b+h+aa wa ad+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:3691: ma h+aa sa man+ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:3693: ma h+aa kri ta a nu ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:3694: don yod grub pas dbang bskur /
NK028(sa)001:3695: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:3696: sar+b+aa ta th+aa ga ta wa k+aa badz+ra swa b+ha wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:3697: sar+b+aa ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:3698: zhes pas sku gsung thugs byin gyis rlabs //
NK028(sa)001:3699: de nas ye shes kyi rgyal po snyan gsan dbab pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:3701: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis /
NK028(sa)001:3702: tshur gshegs rgyal po yul 'khor bsrungs /
NK028(sa)001:3703: btsun mo sras dang yul 'khor bcas /
NK028(sa)001:3704: 'dir byon mchod pa dam pa bzhes /
NK028(sa)001:3707: sarba d+h+ri ta ra ta ye g+han+d+ha ra a ti
NK028(sa)001:3708: pa ta ye h+aum dza zhes lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas
NK028(sa)001:3709: spyan drangs / dzahh+aum bam hoh stim de nas mchod /
NK028(sa)001:3710: a ha ra a ha ra sarba bi da ra p+au dza de /
NK028(sa)001:3711: na mah sa man+ta bud+d+ha nan ga ga na sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:3713: de nas me tog la sogs pa'i mchod par char bzhin du 'bab par dmigs la /
NK028(sa)001:3714: gtsang zhing gtsang mar skyes pa yis /
NK028(sa)001:3715: lha rdzas bzang po'i me tog 'di /
NK028(sa)001:3716: bdag gis dad pas 'bul lags kyis /
NK028(sa)001:3717: bzhes nas kunatu dgye par mdzod /
NK028(sa)001:3718: badz+ra push+pe p+au dza me g+ha sa mu tra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:3719: nags tshal bcud ldan yid khar 'ong /
NK028(sa)001:3720: dri zhim rgyas par lha yi rdzas /
NK028(sa)001:3721: bdag gis dad pas 'bul lags kyi //
NK028(sa)001:3722: bzhes nas kun tu dgyes par mdzod //
NK028(sa)001:3723: badz+ra d+h+au pe p+au dza me g+ha sa mu tra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:3724: sdug bsngal 'dres shing bkra shis pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:3725: dge zhing mun sel mar me 'di //
NK028(sa)001:3726: bdag gi dad pa bzhes nas kun tu dgyes bar mdzod //
NK028(sa)001:3727: badz+ra a lo ke p+au dza me gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yi //
NK028(sa)001:3728: lha rdzas bzang po'i dri chab 'di //
NK028(sa)001:3729: bdag gis bzhes nas kun tu badz+ra g+han+d+he p+au dza sman rnams bcud ldan yid khar 'ong //
NK028(sa)001:3730: sngags kyi zhal zas bshos 'di dag /
NK028(sa)001:3731: bdag gis dad pas 'bul lags kyis //
NK028(sa)001:3732: thugs rjes dgongs la bzhes su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3733: a ha ra a ha ra sarba bi da ra
NK028(sa)001:3734: p+au dzi te s+w+aa h+aa ba lim ta kh+aa hi
NK028(sa)001:3736: ri rgyal lhun po'i shar phyogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:3737: pho brang chen po spos ngad ldan //
NK028(sa)001:3738: zab cing rgya che gzigs pa po //
NK028(sa)001:3739: chos skyongs rgyal po yul 'khor bsrungs //
NK028(sa)001:3740: btsun mo sras dang blon por bcas //
NK028(sa)001:3741: 'khor g.yogs bye ba stongs ldan pas //
NK028(sa)001:3743: sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs nas //
NK028(sa)001:3744: gnas 'dir brtse phyir gshegs nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:3745: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK028(sa)001:3746: bdag cag re ba bsgrub du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3748: dam tshig phyag rgya bcas la /
NK028(sa)001:3749: d+h+ri ta ra ta ra ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:3750: sngon lcang lo tshan gyi pho brang du /
NK028(sa)001:3751: ston pa zhal bzhugs pa'i tshe chos kyi bstan tshogs chen po mdzad pa la thugs dgongs te /
NK028(sa)001:3752: mgon po mi 'gyur ba'i gdan la bzhugs nas /
NK028(sa)001:3753: phyi mtshams skyongs bar zhal gyis bzhes pa de bzhin du /
NK028(sa)001:3754: bdag gi gsang bsgrub gnyan po 'di ma thon gyi bar du /
NK028(sa)001:3755: phyi'i dgra bgegs nang du mi btang zhing /
NK028(sa)001:3756: nang gi dngos grub phyir mi btang ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:3757: dngos grub kyi sdong grogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3758: phyi mtshams bsrungs ba'i 'phrin las sngon kyi thugs dam las mi 'da' bar mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:3759: zhes brjod la 'phrin las nan du bcol nas /
NK028(sa)001:3760: ka ya wa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK028(sa)001:3761: zhes ji srid du rang gis bsam pa ma rdzogs bar du brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3762: de bzhin du lho phyogs kyi tho la yang /
NK028(sa)001:3764: zla ba'i gdan la h+aum ser po yongs su gyur pa las ral gri /
NK028(sa)001:3765: de 'phros 'dus pas sku rdzogs par bskyed de /
NK028(sa)001:3766: be ru ta ka ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:3767: zhes pas rgyal po 'phags skyes po sku mdog sngon po ral gri bsnams pa bskyed la /
NK028(sa)001:3768: +amo ma h+aa sa man+ta zhes pa la sogs pa thog mar byas pa'i sngags tshan lngas dbang bskur /
NK028(sa)001:3769: k+aa ya badz+ra la sogs pas byin gyis rlabs /
NK028(sa)001:3770: de nas snyan gsan dbab pa la sogs gong ma'i 'dres shes par bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:3771: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK028(sa)001:3772: tshur gshegs rgyal po 'phags skyes po //
NK028(sa)001:3773: btsun mo sras dang g.yog 'khor bcas //
NK028(sa)001:3774: 'dir byon mchod pa dam pa bzhes /
NK028(sa)001:3775: yam badz+ra am gu sha ya ar+sha ya sarba be
NK028(sa)001:3776: ru ta ka ye g+han+ta ra a ti pa ta
NK028(sa)001:3777: ye h+aum dzah zhes lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas spyan drangs
NK028(sa)001:3779: +amo a h+aa ra na a ha ra na sarba
NK028(sa)001:3780: bi da ra p+au dza de na ma sa man+ta
NK028(sa)001:3781: bud+d+ha nan ga ga na sa ma ye swa h+aa
NK028(sa)001:3784: de nas me tog la sogs gong gis 'dre /
NK028(sa)001:3785: h+aum ri rgyal lhun po'i lho phyogs nas /
NK028(sa)001:3787: zab cing rgya che gzigs pa po //
NK028(sa)001:3788: chos skyong rgyal po 'phags skyes ni //
NK028(sa)001:3789: btsun mo sras dang blon por bcas //
NK028(sa)001:3790: g.yog 'khor bye ba stong ldan la //
NK028(sa)001:3792: sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK028(sa)001:3793: gnas 'dir brtse phyir gshegs nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:3794: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK028(sa)001:3795: bdag cag re ba bsgrub du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:3797: dam tshig gi phyag rgya bstan la //
NK028(sa)001:3798: bee ru ta ka ye s+w+aa h+aa //
NK028(sa)001:3799: sngon lcang lo can gyi pho brang du //
NK028(sa)001:3800: ston pa zhal bzhugs pa'i tshe //
NK028(sa)001:3801: chos kyi bstan tshogs chen po mdzad pa thugs la dgongs te /
NK028(sa)001:3802: mgon po mi 'gyur ba'i gdan la bzhugs nas //
NK028(sa)001:3803: phyi mtshams skyong bar zhal gyis bzhes pa bzhin du //
NK028(sa)001:3804: bdag gi gsang sgrub gnyen po 'di ma thon gyi bar du //
NK028(sa)001:3805: phyi'i dgra bgegs nang du mi btang zhing //
NK028(sa)001:3806: nang gi dngos grub phyir mi btang ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:3807: dngos grub kyis sdong grogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3808: phyi mtshams bsrungs pa'i phrin las sngon gyis thugs dam las mi 'da' bar mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:3810: 'phrin las nan tan du bcol nas /
NK028(sa)001:3811: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK028(sa)001:3812: zhes ji srid rang gi bsam pa ma rdzogs bar du brtan par bzhugs su gsol /
NK028(sa)001:3813: de bzhin du nub phyogs kyi tho bsang sbyang byas la /
NK028(sa)001:3815: h+aum dmar po 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las mchod rten du gyur /
NK028(sa)001:3816: de 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK028(sa)001:3817: be ru bak+sha ye zhes pas rgyal po spyan mi bzang /
NK028(sa)001:3818: sku mdog dmar po mchod rten dang sbrul zhags bsnams pa bskyed la /
NK028(sa)001:3819: +amo pra ta be sha thog mar sbyar ba'i sngags tshan lngas dbang bskur //
NK028(sa)001:3820: sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs //
NK028(sa)001:3821: de nas ye shes pa snyan gsan dbab ste //
NK028(sa)001:3822: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK028(sa)001:3823: tshur gshegs rgyal po spyan mi bzang //
NK028(sa)001:3824: btsun mo sras dang g.yog 'khor bcas //
NK028(sa)001:3825: 'dir byon mchod pa dam pa bzhes /
NK028(sa)001:3826: yam badz+ra ang+gu sha ya a kar+sha ya sarba be
NK028(sa)001:3827: ru pak+sha ye gan+d+har+pa a d+hi pa ti ye h+aum
NK028(sa)001:3830: a ha ra na a ha ra na sarba bi
NK028(sa)001:3831: da ra p+au dza de na mah sa man+ta bud+d+ha
NK028(sa)001:3832: nan ga ga na sa ma ye swah+aa zhes pas
NK028(sa)001:3833: argam 'bul / me tog la sogs gong gi 'dre //
NK028(sa)001:3834: ri rgyal lhun po'i nub phyogs na //
NK028(sa)001:3835: pho brang chen po'i rgya mtsho'i gling //
NK028(sa)001:3836: zab cing rgya che gzigs pa po //
NK028(sa)001:3837: chos skyong chen po spyan mi bzang //
NK028(sa)001:3838: btsun mo sras dang blon por bcas //
NK028(sa)001:3839: g.yog 'khor bye ba stong ldan la //
NK028(sa)001:3841: sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK028(sa)001:3842: gnas 'dir brtse phyir gshegs nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:3843: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK028(sa)001:3844: bdag cag re ba bsgrub du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:3845: zhes 'phrin las bskul dam tshig gi phyag rgya bstan la /
NK028(sa)001:3846: be ru bak+sha ye s+w+aa h+aa sngon lcang lo can gyi pho brang du /
NK028(sa)001:3847: ston pa zhal bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK028(sa)001:3848: chos kyi bsta na tshogs chen po mdzad pa la thugs dgongs te /
NK028(sa)001:3849: mgon po mi 'gyur ba'i gdan la bzhugs nas /
NK028(sa)001:3850: phyi mtshams skyong bar zhal gyis bzhes pa de bzhin
NK028(sa)001:3851: du bdag gi gsang bsgrub gnyan po 'di ma thon
NK028(sa)001:3852: kyi bar / phyi'i da gra bgegs nang du mi btang zhing /
NK028(sa)001:3853: nang gi dngos grub phyir mi btang ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:3854: dngos grub gyis gtong grogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:3855: phyi mtshams bsrungs ba'i 'phrin las sngon gyi thugs dam las mi 'da' bar mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:3857: 'phrin las nan tan du bcol nas /
NK028(sa)001:3858: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK028(sa)001:3859: zhes ji srid bdag gi bsam pa ma rdzogs bar du brtan par bzhugs su gsol /
NK028(sa)001:3860: de bzhin du byang phyoogs kyi tho bsang sbyang byas la /
NK028(sa)001:3861: zla ba'i gdan la h+aum ljang khu 'phros pas rgyal mtshan du gyur /
NK028(sa)001:3863: bee sha wa na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:3864: zhes pas rgyal po rnam thos sras sku mdog dmar
NK028(sa)001:3865: ser rgyal mtshan dang ne'u le 'dzin pa bskyed la
NK028(sa)001:3867: thog mar byas pa'i sngags tshan lngas dbang bskur /
NK028(sa)001:3869: ye shes snyan gsan dbab ste //
NK028(sa)001:3870: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK028(sa)001:3871: tshur gshegs rgyal po rnam thos sras //
NK028(sa)001:3872: btsun mo sras dang g.yog 'khor bcas //
NK028(sa)001:3873: 'dir byon mchod pa dam pa bzhes /
NK028(sa)001:3874: yam badz+ra am gu sha ya a kar+sha ya sarba bee sh+ra ma na ye /
NK028(sa)001:3877: me tog la sogs gong gis 'dre //
NK028(sa)001:3878: ri rgyal lhun po'i byang phyogs su //
NK028(sa)001:3879: pho brang chen po lcang lo can //
NK028(sa)001:3880: zab cing rgyal chen gzigs 'phags po //
NK028(sa)001:3881: chos skyong rgyal po rnam thos sras //
NK028(sa)001:3882: btsun mo sras dang blon por bcas /
NK028(sa)001:3884: dam tshig gi phyag rgya bstan la /
NK028(sa)001:3885: bee sh+ra ba na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:3886: sngon lcang lo can gyi pho brang du /
NK028(sa)001:3888: de nas phyogs skyong gi steng //
NK028(sa)001:3889: phyogs skyong tho khang thog gam /
NK028(sa)001:3890: shar phyogs brgya byin gyi tho'i mdun du rtsigs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:3891: phyogs mtshams brgyad kyi tho dang /
NK028(sa)001:3893: nub kyi klu'i tho'i mdun du rtsigs pa rnams bsang sbyang byas la /
NK028(sa)001:3894: phyogs skyong rang rang gnas nas byon nas bzhugs par bsam zhing /
NK028(sa)001:3896: go rim bzhin gtor ma dang mchod pa sngags kyis phul la 'phrin las bcol te /
NK028(sa)001:3897: sngon lcang lo can gyi pho brang du zhes pa nas bstan par bzhugs su gsol /
NK028(sa)001:3899: gnyis pa phyi'i nang mtshams dam sri mnan pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:3900: ra sog gam gro shog la /
NK028(sa)001:3901: mtshal lam btsag gis dam sri'i gzugs rid pa skra 'dzings pa /
NK028(sa)001:3902: lag pas skra 'a bal zhing brang brdung ba bri //
NK028(sa)001:3903: yang ra sog la bgegs kyi sgo byang //
NK028(sa)001:3904: dam sri'i gzugs cig bris la /
NK028(sa)001:3907: 'doms su bsgrub pa la bar du gcod pa'i dam srid m+aa ra ya phata /
NK028(sa)001:3910: ling ka gnyis ka thod pa dum bu drug par bcug nas dgug 'dren stabs su byas pas chog /
NK028(sa)001:3911: las mkhan rnams dang bcas pas /
NK028(sa)001:3912: phur bu la sogs pa'i lag cha tshang bar byas la /
NK028(sa)001:3913: e ram gyis drag po'i dkyil bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:3914: ba hus sngags kyis lha las la gzud /
NK028(sa)001:3915: pho nya drug skor btang la sprul par spro /
NK028(sa)001:3923: phur pa byin gyis rlabs te /
NK028(sa)001:3924: ma s+aur+ya man+da la h+aum swa +aam h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:3925: a tsan+t+ra man+da la mum lam mam pam tam /
NK028(sa)001:3929: badz+ra ki li k+ai la ya phata dza ha na ha na dib ta tsakra hri /
NK028(sa)001:3931: badz+ra swa ta r+aa dza y+aa h+aum phata de nas g+ha ta'i sngags kyi phur pa gdab ste /
NK028(sa)001:3932: them pa'i phyir dong gru gsum brus la /
NK028(sa)001:3935: ro g.yam la rdo rje rgya gram bris pas kha bcad cing /
NK028(sa)001:3936: de'i steng du lam bris la /
NK028(sa)001:3937: gser gyis ri rab kyis mnan par bsam nas /
NK028(sa)001:3938: sas bsubs la steng du bro byas ste /
NK028(sa)001:3939: bro ra gru gsum rtse mo lhor bstan pa bcas la /
NK028(sa)001:3941: e b+h+rum gyis drag po'i dkyil 'khor bskyed la /
NK028(sa)001:3943: de'i nga rgyal dang ldan pas 'di brjod do //
NK028(sa)001:3945: khro rgyal chen po sum+b+ha ni /
NK028(sa)001:3946: sum+b+ha ni yi nga rgyal gyis /
NK028(sa)001:3947: ri rab chen po'i rked nas bskor /
NK028(sa)001:3948: rgya mtsho chen po'i stengs nas skems /
NK028(sa)001:3949: 'di la byang chub sems bskyed btang bar bya /
NK028(sa)001:3950: byang chub sems ni ma skyes bar /
NK028(sa)001:3951: nam yang btang bar mi bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:3954: g+h+rih+na pa ya grih+na pa ya h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:3957: bid+y+aa ra dza ya h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:3958: h+ao bcom ldan 'das sum b+ha ni dkyil 'khor dang
NK028(sa)001:3959: bcas pa rnams la 'phrin las su bcol ba ni
NK028(sa)001:3960: / 'dir mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi dkyil chen po bzhengs su gsol bas /
NK028(sa)001:3961: bar du gcod pa'i ya ma dam sri la sogs pa /
NK028(sa)001:3962: dgra bgegs gdug pa can thal ba'i rdul du brlag pa mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:3963: m+aa ra ya m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:3965: ji srid byang chub kyi sems ma skyes kyi bar
NK028(sa)001:3966: du ri rab kyi 'og tu mnan pa bsams la
NK028(sa)001:3967: / su tri sa m+aa ya s+t+wam zhes brjod cing /
NK028(sa)001:3968: de ni steng du lha'i pho brang btab la /
NK028(sa)001:3969: ho khro bo chen po 'khor dang bcas pa gsan cing dgongs su gsol /
NK028(sa)001:3970: mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs
NK028(sa)001:3971: rnams kyi sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub bsgrub pa'i
NK028(sa)001:3972: phyir / sgrub pa po bdag cag gi bsam pa yid bzhin du ma rdzogs kyi bar du /
NK028(sa)001:3973: sgrub pa la bar du gcod par byed pa'i ya
NK028(sa)001:3974: ma dam sri la sogs pa gdug pa'i dgra bgegs
NK028(sa)001:3975: thams cad 'dul zhing bsgral du gsol lo //
NK028(sa)001:3976: bsgrub pa'i dngos grub thams cad kyang yid bzhin du thob par mdzad du gsol lo //
NK028(sa)001:3977: gsum pa phyi'i gsang mtshams ni /
NK028(sa)001:3978: sgo byang gdags par bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:3979: bgegs kyi sgo byang ra sog la bris pa'i ling
NK028(sa)001:3980: ga de'i snying khar seng ldeng gi phur pa dar
NK028(sa)001:3982: g+ha ta'i sngags kyis btab pa de /
NK028(sa)001:3983: gshin rje'i gnas su bskrad par bsams la //
NK028(sa)001:3984: dam sri la 'di skad ces bka' bsgo ste /
NK028(sa)001:3986: rang bzhin dag pa'i ngo bo la //
NK028(sa)001:3987: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med de //
NK028(sa)001:3988: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtogs //
NK028(sa)001:3989: phyogs rtogs yang dag nyid ma rtogs //
NK028(sa)001:3990: sgrib pas sems can spangs ma btang //
NK028(sa)001:3991: sems kyi rtog pas bcings pa'am //
NK028(sa)001:3992: gzhi stong ci la'ang bar chad byed //
NK028(sa)001:3993: rang gi dam tshig rang la 'da' //
NK028(sa)001:3994: 'dzam bu gling gi lho phyogs na //
NK028(sa)001:3995: 'di nas dpag tshad brgyad khri na /
NK028(sa)001:3996: gshin rje'i rgyal po chos ston gyi //
NK028(sa)001:3997: khyod kyi chos bskal de ru nyon /
NK028(sa)001:3998: ma 'da' rang rang gnas su dengs //
NK028(sa)001:3999: sa ma ya ka wa tsi rak+sha rak+sha h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:4001: tshigs nas ji ltar byung ba bzhin bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:4002: ske la thag pa nag po brtags shing /
NK028(sa)001:4004: spyi rting log nas yongs par byas nas gdags so //
NK028(sa)001:4005: de nas ye shes lha'i sgo byang kyang ngam /
NK028(sa)001:4006: lug gi sog pa g.yon pa la /
NK028(sa)001:4007: khro bo gshin rje gshed kyi gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:4008: nyi zla'i gdan la gyad gyi dor stabs kyis bzhugs la /
NK028(sa)001:4009: sku mdog smug nag be con dang 'khor lo bsnams pa /
NK028(sa)001:4010: khro bo'i cha byad can bris la /
NK028(sa)001:4015: ya man+ta kri ta h+aum phatah ces pas ji ltar bris pa bzhin dam tshig pa bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:4016: dbang bskur byin brlabs bsdus pa bya /
NK028(sa)001:4018: ye shes kyi gshin rje gshed snyan gsan dbab /
NK028(sa)001:4021: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod nas /
NK028(sa)001:4022: sgo gong gi g.yon dngos su btags la /
NK028(sa)001:4024: sum cu rtsa gsum lha yi mdun sa ru //
NK028(sa)001:4025: bcom ldan chos rje lha yis bka' stsal pa //
NK028(sa)001:4026: lha srin sde brgyad 'byung po'i dpon rnams khyed //
NK028(sa)001:4027: bsgrub pa mchog la deng 'dir nges zhugs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:4028: bla med byang chub 'bras bu ma thob bar //
NK028(sa)001:4029: sgo 'di yan chad 'da' bar ma byed cig /
NK028(sa)001:4031: khro bo'i rgyal po gshin rje gshed la 'phrin las su bcol ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:4032: bdag cag la dngos grub kyi sdong grogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:4033: phyi mtshams bsrung zhing nang mtshams skyong ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:4034: khyad par du dkyil 'khor chen po'i de'i bya ba ma thon gyi bar du /
NK028(sa)001:4035: phyi'i dgra bgegs nang du mi btang zhing /
NK028(sa)001:4036: nang gi dngos grub phyir mi btang ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:4037: ya ma dam sri la sogs bar chad thams cad bsrungs du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:4040: dkyil 'khor mtha' mar dam can gyi spyi mtshams byas las 'dul ba yang rung ngo //
NK028(sa)001:4041: gnyis pa nang mtshams la gsum ste /
NK028(sa)001:4042: nang gi phyi mtshams khro bo bcu'i phur pa bgegs la gdab pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:4043: nang gi nang mtshams mtshon cha'i gur phub pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:4044: nang gi gsang mtshams khro bo bcu'i stangs stobs kyi bgegs rigs zil gyis mnan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:4046: lcags sam shing las byas pa'i phur pa dar mthing dmar gyi cod pan can bcu /
NK028(sa)001:4050: gu gul gyi dud pas bdug go //
NK028(sa)001:4051: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngang nas /
NK028(sa)001:4052: h+aum zhes brjod pas rang gi rig pa h+aum du gyur pa de /
NK028(sa)001:4053: par sang gi 'phro 'du rdo rje gyur /
NK028(sa)001:4054: de 'phros 'dus badz+ra d+h+riga ces brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:4055: zhe sdang rdo rje sku mdog sngon nag zhal g.yas dkar g.yon dmar /
NK028(sa)001:4064: zhal mche ba cung zad gtsigs pa /
NK028(sa)001:4065: zhi ma khro'i cha lugs can du bsam /
NK028(sa)001:4066: de'i thugs khar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du h+aum sngon po bsam mo //
NK028(sa)001:4067: de nas ma zhes brjod pas mdun du ma dmar po cig bton la /
NK028(sa)001:4068: ma sur+ya man+da la zhes brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:4070: yang thugs ka nas h+aum sngon po cig mdun gyi nyi ma'i steng du spros nas /
NK028(sa)001:4071: sh+ri h+aum ka ra badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:4073: mdun du khro chen h+aum ka ra sngon po zhal gcig phyag gnyis par bskyed la /
NK028(sa)001:4076: grih+na pa ya grih+na pa ya h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:4078: b+ha ga wan bid+y+aa ra dza ya h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:4080: zhe sdang rdo rje'i phyag mtshan /
NK028(sa)001:4081: rdo rje dril bu de h+aum ka ra la gtad pas /
NK028(sa)001:4082: tho ba dang lcags kyur gyur par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:4083: de'i thugs ka nas ma dang nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor dang slar yang h+aum spros la /
NK028(sa)001:4084: sh+r+ai d+aa ki r+aa dza badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha h+aum phata ces brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:4085: t+aa ki r+aa dza dmar ljang zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa bskyed la /
NK028(sa)001:4086: h+aum ka ras tho ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:4087: lcag kyu t+aa ki r+aa dza la gtad la /
NK028(sa)001:4088: sum+b+ha ni'i sngags kyis gdan thing shig ces bsgo /
NK028(sa)001:4089: de'i thugs ka nas ma bcu phyogs bcu'i hom khung bcu ni gnas khang gi phyi rol lam //
NK028(sa)001:4090: nang yang rung bar phyogs mtshams brgyad dang //
NK028(sa)001:4091: steng gi hom khung gi shar ngos sam /
NK028(sa)001:4092: yang na shar stod du dgod //
NK028(sa)001:4093: 'og phyogs kyi hom khung nub kyi hom khung gi nub bam //
NK028(sa)001:4094: yang na nub smad du dgod de //
NK028(sa)001:4095: che chung ni phur pa rnams dang mtshams pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:4096: ngag tu ma sur+ya man+dala ces lan bcu brjod pas //
NK028(sa)001:4097: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bcur gsal bar bsgoms la //
NK028(sa)001:4098: t+aa kis rdo rje 'gros kyis sum+b+ha ni'i sngags kyis //
NK028(sa)001:4099: dri za pho mo'i snying ga nas lcags kyus bzung /
NK028(sa)001:4100: tho bas nyal nyes su brdungs /
NK028(sa)001:4101: shar phyogs kyi hom khung la gnas pa'i nyi ma'i steng du byi chings su bsnol bar zhags /
NK028(sa)001:4102: de bzhin du lhor gshin rje pho mo /
NK028(sa)001:4110: 'og phyogs su sa bdag pho mo nyi ma'i steng du byi chings su bsnol lo //
NK028(sa)001:4111: de nas tho ba dang lcags kyu h+aum ka ra la gtad nas //
NK028(sa)001:4112: ta ki r+aa dza h+aum ka ra'i thugs khar thim /
NK028(sa)001:4113: des tho ba dang lcags kyu zhe sdang rdo rje la gtad nas //
NK028(sa)001:4114: h+aum gdan bting lags so bcom ldan khro rgyal gtso //
