NK028(sa)001:4115: zhe sdang rdo rje thugs kyi dkyi la 'khor nas //
NK028(sa)001:4116: khro po'i rgyal po snams phyung rol pa'i sku /
NK028(sa)001:4117: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gdan la yang dag bzhugs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:4119: h+aum ka ra nyid tshangs pa pho mo'i gdan la bzhugs pa bsgom mo //
NK028(sa)001:4120: de nas zhe sdang rdo rje'i thugs ka nas /
NK028(sa)001:4123: 'og gi nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i phyogs skyong gi gdan la dgod do //
NK028(sa)001:4124: sh+r+ai ya man ta krid ma h+aa kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:4127: dri za'i gdan la gnas pa'i /
NK028(sa)001:4128: h+aum de gshin rje gshed po sku mdog smug nag zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK028(sa)001:4129: sku smad phur pa'i dbal can du gyur /
NK028(sa)001:4130: de bzhin du lhor a pa ra tsit+ta'i sngags kyis dpal ldan ser nag bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:4131: nub tu ha ya gri was rta mgrin dmar nag /
NK028(sa)001:4132: byang du a mri ta kun+da lis /
NK028(sa)001:4134: shar lhor +aar+ya a tsa las mi g.yo ljang ser /
NK028(sa)001:4135: lho nub tu ni la dan+dasa dbyugs pa sngon po sngo skya /
NK028(sa)001:4136: nub byang du ta ka r+aa dzas ta ki r+aa dza dmar ljang /
NK028(sa)001:4137: byang shar du ma h+aa ba las stobs chen dud ka /
NK028(sa)001:4138: 'og phyogs su nyi ma dang sa bdag gis gdan la ka ma la kun+da li'i sngags kyis /
NK028(sa)001:4139: pad+ma 'khyil pa mthing nag bskyed de /
NK028(sa)001:4140: kun kyang zhal gsum phyag drug pa sku smad du phur pa zur gsum dbal dang bcas pa /
NK028(sa)001:4141: dur khrod chas kyis brgyan pa /
NK028(sa)001:4142: rang rtags kyi phyag mtshan bsnams pa //
NK028(sa)001:4143: dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar bar bskyed do //
NK028(sa)001:4145: khro bo'i rgyal po 'di dag gis /
NK028(sa)001:4146: bgegs rnams bkug nas rnam par 'jig /
NK028(sa)001:4147: blo ldan rab tu sbyor ba yis //
NK028(sa)001:4148: cho ga bzhin du phur pas gdab //
NK028(sa)001:4150: zhe sdang rdo rjes h+aum ka ra la gzigs te /
NK028(sa)001:4151: g+ha g+ha g+h+aa ta ya g+h+aa t+aa ya sarba dush+tana ma ra ya phata phata /
NK028(sa)001:4154: h+aum badz+ra ki li ki la ya /
NK028(sa)001:4155: badz+ra d+ha ro a dz+ny+aa pa ya ti ka ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra k+ai la ya h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:4157: tho ba dang lcags kyu gtad nas /
NK028(sa)001:4158: khyod kyi phur pa rnams phyogs bcu'i bgegs la thob cig /
NK028(sa)001:4160: slar yang h+aum ka ras bdud rtsi 'khyil pa la gzigs te /
NK028(sa)001:4162: tho ba dang lcags kyu gtad nas khyod bgegs mthar byed yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:4163: bgegs la khyod kyis phur pa gdab par rigs so //
NK028(sa)001:4164: zhes bka' bsgo bar bsam zhing /
NK028(sa)001:4165: bdud rtsi 'khyil pas kyang lag sor dang phur pa byin gyis rlabs nas /
NK028(sa)001:4167: sh+r+ai ya man ta krid badz+ra ma h+aa k+ai la ya kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:4169: dngos su lag pa g.yon pas phur pa bzungs //
NK028(sa)001:4170: g.yas pas phur pa'i mgor rdo rje sdigs la //
NK028(sa)001:4171: khro bo'i sku smad lcags kyi phur ba zur gsum pa /
NK028(sa)001:4172: mgar gyi sol mal nas bton pa lta bu des dri za pho mo thal gyis phyung nas /
NK028(sa)001:4173: 'og gi nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la phur pa'i rtse mo reg par bsam mo //
NK028(sa)001:4176: shar lho la sogs pa'i mtshams bzhi dang //
NK028(sa)001:4177: 'og rnams go rim bzhin g+ha ta'i sngags la /
NK028(sa)001:4178: rang rang gi sngags btags la phur pa rang rang gi phyogs skyongs rnams la btab par bsam mo //
NK028(sa)001:4179: de nas bdud rtsi 'khyil bas tho ba dang lcags
NK028(sa)001:4180: kyu h+aum chen la gtad nas bdud rtsi 'khyil pa
NK028(sa)001:4181: byang gi phyogs skyong gi gdan la bzhugs pa la
NK028(sa)001:4182: / h+aum chen gyis g+ha ta'i sngags kyis rjes la /
NK028(sa)001:4183: sh+r+ai big nan ta krita badz+ra ma h+aa ki la
NK028(sa)001:4184: ya kro d+ha h+aum phatah ces brjod pas byang gi
NK028(sa)001:4186: tho ba dang lcags kyu zhe sdang rdo rje'i phyag
NK028(sa)001:4187: tu gtad de h'u chen steng phyogs tshangs pa pho
NK028(sa)001:4188: mo'i gdan la bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK028(sa)001:4189: de la zhe sdang rdo rjes g+ha ta'i sngags kyi rjes la /
NK028(sa)001:4190: sh+r+ai h+aum ka ra badz+ra ma h+aa k+ai la ya kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:4191: ces brjod cing btab pa'i rjes su /
NK028(sa)001:4192: phur pa'i rang bzhin khro bo'i rgyal po rnams la ched du brjod pa'i sgo nas bstod pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:4194: phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi steng 'og bcu //
NK028(sa)001:4195: khro bo'i rgyal po bdud chen rnams //
NK028(sa)001:4196: kun kyang zhal gsum phyag drug ste //
NK028(sa)001:4197: ya mtshan che ba'i dbu brgyan can //
NK028(sa)001:4198: dbu skra khams nag ral pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:4200: spyan gsum glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:4201: mche ba zang yag 'bar ba rtsigs //
NK028(sa)001:4202: rkan sgra rtogs pas khams gsum 'khrug /
NK028(sa)001:4203: bdud tshogs rnams kyis zhabs la btugs //
NK028(sa)001:4204: mdzes pa'i lha mo mang po yis //
NK028(sa)001:4205: snyan pa'i glu dbyangs du mas bstod //
NK028(sa)001:4206: bcom ldan 'das kyi sprul pa ste //
NK028(sa)001:4207: yang sprul grangs med phyogs bcur 'phro //
NK028(sa)001:4209: lho phyogs gshin rje zhabs kyis gnon //
NK028(sa)001:4210: nub phyogs klu yi gdon rnams gzir //
NK028(sa)001:4211: byang phyogs gnod sbyin kun gyi bla //
NK028(sa)001:4212: mtshams kyi bgegs rnams zhi mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:4213: ya mtshan che la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK028(sa)001:4214: phyogs mtshams phur pas btab nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:4215: steng 'og yang dag byin gyis brlabs //
NK028(sa)001:4216: de nas ram zhes brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:4217: khro bo rnams kyi sku la me dpung 'bar te /
NK028(sa)001:4218: me'i gur du gyur pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:4219: de dag gi nang du sgrub pa po /
NK028(sa)001:4220: bag yangs su spyod par bsam mo //
NK028(sa)001:4221: gnyis pa nang gi mtshams mtshon cha 'chol pas /
NK028(sa)001:4222: mtshon cha'i gur phub pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:4223: dpon slob thams cad kyis phyag mtshan dang mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs la /
NK028(sa)001:4225: gu gul gyis dud pa sbyar la /
NK028(sa)001:4226: tshig ji lta ba bzhin du ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK028(sa)001:4229: khro bo'i sdang mig gis mtshon cha'i gur du bsam zhing /
NK028(sa)001:4230: h+aum nga yi dkyil 'khor bstan bya'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:4231: khro rgyal byin rlabs las byung pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:4232: mtshon cha rnam pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:4233: dkyil 'khor rim pa tshul bzhin bsrungs //
NK028(sa)001:4234: steng yang rdo rje'i bla res ste //
NK028(sa)001:4236: phyogs mtshams rdo rjes gtams pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:4237: rdo rje'i mtshams las ma 'da' cig /
NK028(sa)001:4238: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha h+aum phata badz+ra dz+wa la ram /
NK028(sa)001:4239: steng yang 'khor los bla res steng //
NK028(sa)001:4241: phyogs mtshams 'khor los gtams pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:4243: badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra h+aum phatah steng yang rin chen bla res steng //
NK028(sa)001:4245: phyogs 'tshams rin chen gtams pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:4246: rin chen mtshams las ma 'da' cig /
NK028(sa)001:4247: badz+ra tik+sh+na dz+wa la h+aum phatah steng yang pad+ma'i bla res steng //
NK028(sa)001:4249: phyogs mtshams pad+mas gtams pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:4251: badz+ra ka la ru pa h+aum phata steng yang ral gri'i bla res steng //
NK028(sa)001:4253: phyogs mtshams ral gris gtam pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:4254: ral gri'i mtshams las ma 'da' cig /
NK028(sa)001:4255: badz+ra kar+m+ma swa ta ha ha h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:4257: gsum pa nang gi gsang mtshams khro bo bcu gcig gi stangs stabs ni /
NK028(sa)001:4258: khro bo bcu gcig gang gi stangs stabs byas pa des /
NK028(sa)001:4259: rang rang gi sprul pas stong gsum drug /
NK028(sa)001:4261: slar khro bo'i phyogs gang yin pa gtams te bskal pa'i rlung gis kyang ma thar bar bsam la /
NK028(sa)001:4262: rkang pa g.yon pas 'chong zhing g.yas pa 'gying ba dang bcas pas pad bskor bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:4263: de dag gi phyag rgya ni /
NK028(sa)001:4264: lag pa thal sbyar gyen du bstan //
NK028(sa)001:4265: rkang pa ma thil sbyar thur du gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:4266: tshigs chen bzhi yang bcag par bya //
NK028(sa)001:4267: mgo yang mtshan ma snying por brtag /
NK028(sa)001:4268: rdo rje rtse gcig rtse dgu dang /
NK028(sa)001:4269: bcu gcig tu ni bsdams bsams te //
NK028(sa)001:4271: badz+ra sh+r+ai ri he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:4276: gom pa'i stobs kyis 'chong zhing gar bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:4277: de bzhin du h+aum ka ra la sogs pa'i khro
NK028(sa)001:4278: bo bcu ka la rang rang gi stangs stabs bcas
NK028(sa)001:4280: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum ka ra h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:4282: ces pa la sogs dang ru lu ru lu h+aum
NK028(sa)001:4283: zhes gom stobs kyis 'chong ba rnams kun la 'adre'o
NK028(sa)001:4284: // lag pa thal sbyar spyi bor bzhag /
NK028(sa)001:4285: rkang pa phral te brkyang brkyang bya //
NK028(sa)001:4286: h+aum ka ra yi phyag rgya yin //
NK028(sa)001:4287: rkang g.yon g.yas pa'i barla steng 'khyud //
NK028(sa)001:4288: lag gnyis thal mo sdeb pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:4289: rnam par rgyal ba'i phyag rgya yin //
NK028(sa)001:4290: mathe'u chung mthe bo'i mthil du mnan //
NK028(sa)001:4291: sor gsum gdengs te stabs byed pa //
NK028(sa)001:4292: dbyug pa sngon po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK028(sa)001:4293: rkang g.yon brkyang la lag pa g.yon //
NK028(sa)001:4294: dkur brten lag g.yas nam mkhar phyar //
NK028(sa)001:4295: 'di ni gshin rje gshed kyi rgya //
NK028(sa)001:4296: lag g.yas gri gug phyar 'dra la //
NK028(sa)001:4297: g.yon pas 'dzin pa ltar byed pa //
NK028(sa)001:4298: mi g.yo mgon po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK028(sa)001:4299: rta gdongs phyag rgya bcas nas ni //
NK028(sa)001:4301: 'di ni rta mchog dpal gyi rgya //
NK028(sa)001:4302: rkang pa g.yon pa nam mkhar phyar //
NK028(sa)001:4303: lag g.yas gdengs pa'i tshul byas pa //
NK028(sa)001:4304: gzhan gyis mi thub phyag rgya yin //
NK028(sa)001:4305: lag pa gnyis kyis skur brten pa //
NK028(sa)001:4306: rkang gnyis gshibs nas g.yas g.yon mchong //
NK028(sa)001:4307: de ni bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i rgya //
NK028(sa)001:4308: lag pa mkhrig ma thugs kar bsnol //
NK028(sa)001:4309: sdigs mdzub gnyis ni dpung par bsgreng //
NK028(sa)001:4310: khams gsum rnam rgyal phyag rgya yin //
NK028(sa)001:4311: rkang pa gom stabs g.yas g.yon na mchong //
NK028(sa)001:4312: lag pa g.yas g.yon thal mo sdeb /
NK028(sa)001:4313: 'di ni stobs po che yi rgya //
NK028(sa)001:4314: de ltar khro bo'i stangs stabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:4315: ting 'dzin sngags dang phyag rgyar bcas //
NK028(sa)001:4316: dkyil 'khor mtha' ma bskor ba yis //
NK028(sa)001:4317: bgegs kyi tshogs rnams brlag par byed //
NK028(sa)001:4318: gsum pa gsang ba'i mtshams la gsum ste //
NK028(sa)001:4319: gsang ba'i phyi mtshams bdud rtsi 'khyil pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:4320: mi g.yo bas dam sri'i bar chad tshar bcad pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:4321: gsang ba'i nang mtshams lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs kyi ye shes su bsgom pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:4322: gsang ba'i gsang mtshams gsang ba'i dam sri bdud rtsi'i
NK028(sa)001:4323: bsang gtor gyis rdul phran bzhin du brlag par byed
NK028(sa)001:4325: kun gyis langs la rdo rje thugs kar bzung la
NK028(sa)001:4326: mi rtog pa'i ngang las thugs kar h+aum bsams te
NK028(sa)001:4328: rdo rje rtse lnga pa cig du gyur /
NK028(sa)001:4330: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:4332: bdag nyid bdud rtsi 'khyil pa sku mdog ljang khu
NK028(sa)001:4333: rdo rje rtse gsum pa thogs pa gcig bskyed la
NK028(sa)001:4335: rnam 'joms yang snying yan chad brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:4336: rang 'dra'i sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'phros nas bgegs thams cad bskrad /
NK028(sa)001:4337: h+aum zhes brjod pas khro bo'i gur du gyur /
NK028(sa)001:4338: ram zhes brjod pas de las me 'bar nas me'i gur du gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:4339: bskal pa'i rlung gis kyang mi thar bar bsam mo //
NK028(sa)001:4340: yang mi rtog pa'i ngang las bsams la bee ro
NK028(sa)001:4341: tsa na a zhes brjod pas bdag nyid rnam par
NK028(sa)001:4342: snang mdzad dkar po g.yas sngo //
NK028(sa)001:4344: phyag g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis 'khor lo //
NK028(sa)001:4348: tha ma ral gri bsnams pa /
NK028(sa)001:4349: nyi zla pad ma'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK028(sa)001:4350: de'i thugs ka nas ma bton la /
NK028(sa)001:4351: ma s+aur+ya man+da la zhes nyi ma bsam /
NK028(sa)001:4353: dpral ba'i dbyings nas h+aum ljang gu gcig phyung la /
NK028(sa)001:4354: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:4356: mi g.yo mgon po sku mdog sngo skya g.yas dkar g.yon dmar ba /
NK028(sa)001:4357: phyag g.yas rdo rje ral gri mda' /
NK028(sa)001:4362: me rab tu 'bar ba la gnas par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:4364: me yi dkyil 'khor la gnas snang mdzad kyis /
NK028(sa)001:4365: zhabs drung dpral dbyes nas phyung mi g.yo bran //
NK028(sa)001:4366: bdud las rnam rgyal phyag drug mda' gzhu dang //
NK028(sa)001:4367: ral gri zhags bsnams rdo rje'i char 'bebs pa //
NK028(sa)001:4368: khro bo grangs las 'das pas ni bskor te //
NK028(sa)001:4369: bgegs rnams skrags mdzad h+aum gis sgras bkang nas //
NK028(sa)001:4370: 'jig rten gsum po gang bar rnam par 'jigs //
NK028(sa)001:4371: thams cad ma lus rdul du rlag par byos //
NK028(sa)001:4372: phatahna mahs man+ta b+hu te nan a tsa la tsan+da
NK028(sa)001:4373: ma h+aa ro sha na spo ta ya kham kham
NK028(sa)001:4375: ral gri'i phyag rgyas g.yas nas klad la bskor bas dgra bgegs bskrad //
NK028(sa)001:4376: g.yon nas bskor ba'i ral gri'i gur du gyur par bsgom mo //
NK028(sa)001:4377: gnyis pa gsang ba'i nang mtshams lus ngag yid gsum
NK028(sa)001:4378: sku gsung thugs kyi ye shes su bsgom pa ni
NK028(sa)001:4379: / lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs kyi ye shes su bsam la /
NK028(sa)001:4381: ma bcos thig le lhun 'jam ni //
NK028(sa)001:4383: sems nyid bde chen dag pa'i ngang //
NK028(sa)001:4384: bgegs zhes bya ba'i ming yang med //
NK028(sa)001:4385: de ltar gsal bar rab rtogs pas //
NK028(sa)001:4386: mtshams kyi dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub //
NK028(sa)001:4388: gsum pa gsang ba'i gsang mtshams gsang ba'i dam sri
NK028(sa)001:4389: bdud rtsi'i bsang gtor gyis rdul phran bzhin du brlag
NK028(sa)001:4391: de nas ma tram mnan pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:4392: bdag nyid byang shar du phyin la /
NK028(sa)001:4393: badz+ra he ru ka h+aum zhes brjod nas /
NK028(sa)001:4395: he ru kar bskyed la lcags kya'i phyag rgya bcas
NK028(sa)001:4396: nas kha ra tra ang+gu sha dzahdzahh+aum zhes lan gsum
NK028(sa)001:4397: brjod pas / skad cig gis mdun du 'ongs par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:4398: badz+ra gu h+ya tri sha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK028(sa)001:4399: ces lan gsum thod pa'i phyag rgya bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:4400: ma tram bya ba'i dam pa nas sdong grogs mdzod cig /
NK028(sa)001:4402: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka'i sngags brjod nas /
NK028(sa)001:4403: kha stong kha'i phyag rgya bcas nas rgyab pas /
NK028(sa)001:4406: rkang pa byang shar du bstan nas g.yon gyis g.yas nas mnan nas /
NK028(sa)001:4408: bdag gi zhabs g.yas pa'i mthe 'ong dza'i 'phro 'dus
NK028(sa)001:4409: lcags kyu bsams nas rkang pa g.yas bteg gi byas
NK028(sa)001:4410: la / gnas kyi sgo ces pa nas /
NK028(sa)001:4411: phye zhig ces pa yan chad brjod /
NK028(sa)001:4412: h+aum h+aum phata phata ma tram ka ru tra h+aum phatah sarba phye dang tsa bya /
NK028(sa)001:4414: zhes pas rkang pa phral bar bsam /
NK028(sa)001:4415: de nas ral gri'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK028(sa)001:4416: ka dar kha pra be sha phata ces brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:4418: de nas pri h+aum zhes brjod pas kho'i shes pa h+aum dkar po cig tu gyur nas /
NK028(sa)001:4419: de bdag gi thugs kar thim pas /
NK028(sa)001:4420: thugs ye shes dbyer med par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:4421: de ga b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud+d+he b+han+d+ha dz+ny+aa na ram zhes brjod pas khog pa nyid zla gam /
NK028(sa)001:4422: smug nag tu gyur pa las /
NK028(sa)001:4423: b+h+rum khang pra be sha phata /
NK028(sa)001:4424: ces pas sgo phye bar bsams nas //
NK028(sa)001:4425: nang du h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes brjod nas byin par bsams //
NK028(sa)001:4426: ha ha ham h+aum pa ra na sam ha ra na h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:4428: gzhal yas khang gi sgo bcad par bsam de ka'i
NK028(sa)001:4429: rjes la steng yang rdo rje'i tshig dbyangs dang bcas
NK028(sa)001:4430: pa brjod nas / badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha h+aum phata badz+ra badz+ra ram yam kham /
NK028(sa)001:4431: zhes phyag rgyas bskor bas steng 'og rdo rje'i gur du gyur nas /
NK028(sa)001:4432: bskal pa'i rlung gis kyang mi thar bar bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:4434: dam sri phur pa bzhin las mkhan gyis mnan /
NK028(sa)001:4435: brgyad pa sa bzung ba la /
NK028(sa)001:4436: cha rkyen bsdu zhing slob ma rnams //
NK028(sa)001:4437: nang du 'dus la gleng gzhi bshad //
NK028(sa)001:4438: 'gag brgyad bshad la thugs dam bskang //
NK028(sa)001:4442: slob ma rnams la gleng gzhi bshad pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:4443: gags brgyad bshad pa dang thugs dam bskang ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:4445: mchod pa'i cha rkyen phyi nang gsang ba'i rdzas khyad par can dang /
NK028(sa)001:4450: thugs rje'i rgyun thag phur bu dang /
NK028(sa)001:4454: do shal rdzas rnams bsdus te spyad /
NK028(sa)001:4456: de rnams gzhung las ji ltar byung ba bzhin bsham /
NK028(sa)001:4460: phyi nang gsang ba'i rdzas khyad par can rnams tshogs par bsag cing bsdu'o //
NK028(sa)001:4461: gnyis pa gleng gzhi bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK028(sa)001:4462: slob ma bsre ba'i cho ga dang /
NK028(sa)001:4464: sngon 'gro'i dbang thun mong du bstan pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:4466: dam ma bsres pa rnams bsre ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:4469: slob dpon dang slob ma gnyis kas sgrub pa po
NK028(sa)001:4470: rnams kyi thugs kar dam tshig gis sems dpa' rang
NK028(sa)001:4471: 'dra ba tshon gang ba gsal bar bskyed la /
NK028(sa)001:4472: dbang gi rgyal thebs kyis sngar gyis bdud rtsi byin
NK028(sa)001:4473: gyis rlabs pa de blangs te rdo rjes dkrug cing
NK028(sa)001:4474: / rang dang rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi lce la lan gsum bzhag ste /
NK028(sa)001:4475: slob dpon gyis ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK028(sa)001:4476: byang chub sems dang rdo rje 'dzin //
NK028(sa)001:4477: de bzhin bsgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK028(sa)001:4478: de dag la ni snying ring na /
NK028(sa)001:4479: rdo rje yak+sha gnod sbyin gyis //
NK028(sa)001:4480: khyod kyi snying la gzhos te 'thung //
NK028(sa)001:4481: snying la yang dag gnas pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:4482: 'di ni sems can dmyal ba'i chu //
NK028(sa)001:4483: i dan ti na ra kan /
NK028(sa)001:4485: zhes mna' dgag cing dam bsgrag go /
NK028(sa)001:4487: de nyid kyi don yang bshad do //
NK028(sa)001:4488: gnyis pa 'dres pa mnan pa la gsum ste /
NK028(sa)001:4489: dang po mnan pa dngos ni /
NK028(sa)001:4490: thod pa'i bdud rtsi bla mas dbu byas pa'i rnal
NK028(sa)001:4491: 'byor pa rnams kyis btang zhing g.yon du bskor te
NK028(sa)001:4492: mgrin gcig tu / dpal ldan sangs rgyas sku 'chang ba //
NK028(sa)001:4493: rdo rje mi phyed sku dang ldan //
NK028(sa)001:4494: de dag byin gyis ba rlabs nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:4495: rdo rje sku yi dngos grub stsol //
NK028(sa)001:4496: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ka ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:4498: de nas bzung ste mched lcam dral rnams dam nyams
NK028(sa)001:4499: su mi btub pas bsgrub pa po rnams kyang grong
NK028(sa)001:4502: lung pa mi ga cig pa la mi phyed pa'i dad pa brtan po dang ldan pas /
NK028(sa)001:4503: dam tshig gzhung bzhin du shes par brlab ste /
NK028(sa)001:4505: gnyis pa bla ma la gtang rag btang ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:4506: dkyil 'khor du bcug pa de'i me tog ci ltar 'byor ba phul la /
NK028(sa)001:4507: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje slob dpon dang //
NK028(sa)001:4508: dam tshig 'brel ba'i mched dang lcam dral gyis //
NK028(sa)001:4509: bsgrub tshogs rnam gsum gyis brlabs pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:4510: bka' drin rjes su dran phyir gtang rag 'bul /
NK028(sa)001:4512: gsum pa rdo rje theg pa'i gral du zhugs pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:4514: lhag pa'i lhar gsal bar byas la /
NK028(sa)001:4515: g.yas g.yon gyi rdo rje dril bu blangs te lan gsum du gsor zhing /
NK028(sa)001:4516: rtsa ba sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig dang /
NK028(sa)001:4517: bsnyen bsgrub rnam bzhis bsnyen cing bsgrub pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:4518: yi dam lha yi 'dza' bsnyen drang ba'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:4519: dam tshig rdo rje dril bu 'chang bar snang /
NK028(sa)001:4522: gnyis pa gleng bzhi dang sngon 'gro'i dbang thun mong du bstan pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:4523: tshoms bu dang mchod gtor ci rigs pa bsham zhing //
NK028(sa)001:4524: yi dam lha'i bsgom bzlas ci rigs par byas la //
NK028(sa)001:4525: dal 'byor rnyed dka' la sogs pa'i chos bshad dang //
NK028(sa)001:4526: skyabs 'gro dang sems bskyed sdom pa 'bog go /
NK028(sa)001:4527: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:4528: de la rnam par snang mdzad thig le dbang gi tan+t+ra'i nang nas /
NK028(sa)001:4530: dbang bcu drug gi gleng gzhi dang /
NK028(sa)001:4531: dbang gi go rim nyi tshe phyung nas bshad pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:4532: 'dod khams 'di na bram ze dung gi 'phreng ba gon pa rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa zhig la /
NK028(sa)001:4533: slob ma rgyal po'i phru gu zhig yod pas /
NK028(sa)001:4534: bram zes slob sbyong la sogs pa yon tan mang po bslabs pa las /
NK028(sa)001:4535: rgyal bu nga rgyal skyes te bsams pa /
NK028(sa)001:4536: 'di na nga'i gong na su yang bshes gnyen can med de /
NK028(sa)001:4537: gong du mi 'chor na bram ze 'di gong du mi btang snyam ste /
NK028(sa)001:4538: bram ze bos nas dgun chang mang du blud de gzi ru bcug nas myos pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:4540: lce lcags kyus drangs te spu gris bcad /
NK028(sa)001:4541: lus rus sbal gyi khrag gis byugs /
NK028(sa)001:4542: bud med mang po'i zhabs mas gril zhing mnan /
NK028(sa)001:4543: sgyid pa spu gris bregs te bzhag pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:4544: bram ze de myos pa sangs nas /
NK028(sa)001:4545: drung na su 'dug 'bod par bsams pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:4546: lce med pas smra ma shes /
NK028(sa)001:4547: bud med mang po'i zhabs mas bstums shing /
NK028(sa)001:4548: gril bas dran pa yang cher nyams /
NK028(sa)001:4553: lus rus sbal gyi khrag gis byug pas //
NK028(sa)001:4554: chu bur dang kom pos gang bar gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:4555: sdug bsngal zhing nyams thag nas bram zes bsams pa /
NK028(sa)001:4556: kha sang kho na 'di 'dra bar gyur pa tshe
NK028(sa)001:4557: rabs sngon gyis las kyi rnam par smin pa zhig
NK028(sa)001:4558: yin nam / 'on te gong du shor dog pa'i
NK028(sa)001:4559: phrag dog zhig gis 'di ltar byas sam snyam nas
NK028(sa)001:4561: rgyal bu slob mas gong du shor gyi dog nas
NK028(sa)001:4562: sdug bsngal rnam pa de dag byas par bram zes
NK028(sa)001:4563: mngon shes kyis rig nas bram zes dmod po bor
NK028(sa)001:4565: rgyal po'i phru gu khyod la ngas /
NK028(sa)001:4566: lo zla de snyed cig du slob sbyong byas pas nga la 'di 'dra ba'i las byed pa /
NK028(sa)001:4567: khyod kyang tshe lus 'di la lus la sha za mo stong gis tshang 'chas par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:4570: rkang pas 'gro mi nus par shog cig /
NK028(sa)001:4571: tshe 'phos nas kyang dmyal ba'i gnas su yun ring
NK028(sa)001:4572: du skyes nas ngan song gsum gyi gnas brgyud par
NK028(sa)001:4573: shog shig / tshe rabs grangs med par 'phags pa'i zhal nyi zer tsam yang mi mthong zhing /
NK028(sa)001:4574: byang chub kyi myu gu gtan skams par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:4575: ces dmod bor te bram ze 'das so //
NK028(sa)001:4576: de nas rgyal bu de rang gi nyes byas kyi rnam smin dang //
NK028(sa)001:4577: bram ze'i dmod pa bor ba 'dom nas /
NK028(sa)001:4578: tshe de nyid la lus la nad rnam pa drug gis phyi nang du thebs te /
NK028(sa)001:4579: sha za mo stong gi tshangs 'chas nas 'jib /
NK028(sa)001:4584: sems byang chub mya gu yang sngo skams su song la thug /
NK028(sa)001:4586: dmyal ba'i khams bcu drug kha rgyud nas /
NK028(sa)001:4587: ngan song gsum du rgyud de bskal pa grangs med
NK028(sa)001:4588: pa'i bar du 'phags pa'i zhal nyi zer tsam yang
NK028(sa)001:4590: de nas 'phos nas sems can gyi nang na lus
NK028(sa)001:4591: bsrul po gcer bu zhes bya bar skyes nas yang
NK028(sa)001:4592: / lus la nad rnam pa drug gis thebs te sdug bsngal ba la /
NK028(sa)001:4593: bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyis thugs rje'i
NK028(sa)001:4594: gzigs nas dpal phyag na rdo rje thugs ka nas
NK028(sa)001:4595: phyung / de nas dpal phyag na rdo rje mdun drang por 'dug ste 'di skad ces gsol to //
NK028(sa)001:4596: bcom ldan 'das sems can gyi nang na lus bsrul
NK028(sa)001:4597: po gcer bu pa du kha sna tshogs kyis nyen
NK028(sa)001:4599: rgyu dang rkyen ji lta bu zhes gsol ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:4600: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK028(sa)001:4601: sems can lus bsrul po gcer bu 'di ni sngon
NK028(sa)001:4602: bskal pa grangs med pa'i gong du rgyal po zhig
NK028(sa)001:4604: slob dpon bram ze zhig gi lus la rngan sna tshogs byas pa'i rnam smin dang //
NK028(sa)001:4605: bram ze'i dmod pa 'dom pa'i dbang gis //
NK028(sa)001:4606: de ltar byang chub kyi myu gu 'di skams la
NK028(sa)001:4607: thug lus kyi rgyu ni shin tu nyon mongs shing
NK028(sa)001:4608: du kha de las 'das nas dmyal khams kyi kha
NK028(sa)001:4609: brgyud de thar pa'i dus med par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:4610: de nas lag na rdo rjes bcom ldan 'das nyon
NK028(sa)001:4611: mongs pa'i sems can 'di thugs rjes gzung du gsol
NK028(sa)001:4612: zhes gsol to // bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK028(sa)001:4613: lag na rdo rje khyod song la /
NK028(sa)001:4614: khyod kyis sems can nyams thags de la /
NK028(sa)001:4615: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis byin gyis brlabs
NK028(sa)001:4616: kyi dbang dam pa thob par byed pa 'di rnams
NK028(sa)001:4617: kyis bsrungs la / du kha'i nad rnams bsal ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:4618: ngan song gsum dmyal khams su skye ba las slar bzlog par bya ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:4619: mtho ris gnas su skye bar 'gyur ba'i thabs /
NK028(sa)001:4620: dbang 'di dag bskur bar bya ba'i las 'a di dag byos shig /
NK028(sa)001:4622: lag na rdo rje rjes su yid rang nas slar bcom ldan 'das la gsol pa /
NK028(sa)001:4623: bcom ldan 'das dbang thams cad kyi rang bzhin bshad du gsol zhes zhus pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:4624: rgyal rigs btsun par skyes pa'i tshe /
NK028(sa)001:4625: rgyal srid 'bangs kyis phul ba'i tshe /
NK028(sa)001:4626: tshig btsan yul la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:4627: sa bdag rgyal por gnas pa bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:4628: bcom ldan byang chub spyod pa'i tshe //
NK028(sa)001:4629: bde gshegs lha klu 'khor bcas pa //
NK028(sa)001:4630: dbang bskur rdzas kyis mnga' gsol nas //
NK028(sa)001:4631: de nas byang chub mngon sangs rgyas //
NK028(sa)001:4632: de bzhin phyag rgyas gnas bsrungs te //
NK028(sa)001:4633: gsang dbang bum pas sdig pa bkrus //
NK028(sa)001:4634: 'phreng ba tshul khrims cod pan dang //
NK028(sa)001:4635: rnam lnga thur mas bag chags bsal //
NK028(sa)001:4636: me long 'khor lo'i steng btsugs te //
NK028(sa)001:4637: chos dung rdo rje rgya gram dang //
NK028(sa)001:4638: rin chen sna bdun dgos pa bskong //
NK028(sa)001:4639: ral gri shes rab seng ge sgra //
NK028(sa)001:4640: nyi zla thabs dang shes rab dang //
NK028(sa)001:4641: mda' gzhu zhi gnas lhag mthong dang //
NK028(sa)001:4642: 'bras bu bkra shis rdzas brgyad byin //
NK028(sa)001:4643: bden pa'i bka' brjod dam bdar nas //
NK028(sa)001:4644: ting 'dzin tshangs pa'i glu dbyangs dang //
NK028(sa)001:4645: rten 'brel rdzas rnams tshogs byas nas //
NK028(sa)001:4646: dbang mchog des ni dbang bskur ro zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:4656: rdo rje rgya gram gyi dbang dang /
NK028(sa)001:4657: rin chen sna bdun gyi dbang /
NK028(sa)001:4661: bkra shis rdzas brgyad kyi dbang dang bcu drug go /
NK028(sa)001:4662: dang po ni phyag rgya'i dbang ni /
NK028(sa)001:4663: de nas lag na rdo rjes rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par bzhugs so //
NK028(sa)001:4664: rigs lnga'i phyag rgya lag tu gtad nas ni //
NK028(sa)001:4665: skal ldan skyes bu khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:4666: sku gsung thugs kyi yon tan rab rdzogs te //
NK028(sa)001:4667: ye shes lnga ni myur du rtogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:4668: badz+ra mu tra a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK028(sa)001:4669: b+hud+d+ha mu tra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:4670: rat+na mu tra a b+hi shiny+tsa tram pad+ma mu tra a b+hi shiny+tsa hri /
NK028(sa)001:4671: kar+m+aa mu tra a b+hi shiny+tsa ah de bzhin gshegs
NK028(sa)001:4672: pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje rnam
NK028(sa)001:4673: par dag pa'i phyag rgyas bcings te /
NK028(sa)001:4674: sems can lus srul po de'i gnas lngar thug cing krad pas /
NK028(sa)001:4675: sha za ma stong yod pa byer ro //
NK028(sa)001:4676: rigs kyi rigs te rigs kyi gtso //
NK028(sa)001:4677: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:4678: gsang ba gsang chen gsang mchog gi /
NK028(sa)001:4679: bdag por khyod la dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:4681: 'du 'bral med pa byang chub sems kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:4682: byang chub kyi mya gu sngo skams su gyur pa de //
NK028(sa)001:4683: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po can du byin gyis brlabs so //
NK028(sa)001:4684: rin chen sna tshogs rgyu las byas //
NK028(sa)001:4685: kha dog sna dbyibs dang ldan pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:4686: shes rab yum gyi bum pa ste //
NK028(sa)001:4687: dbang mchog 'dis ni dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:4688: bud d+ha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:4689: badz+ra rat+na a b+hi pad+ma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:4691: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rje byin rlabs pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:4692: bdud rtsi bum pas dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:4693: lus mi bde ba rnams bkrus nas dag par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:4694: byang chub yan lag me tog 'thor //
NK028(sa)001:4695: khams gsum btsun mo'i bdag po ste //
NK028(sa)001:4696: bde gshegs mchod pa thob pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:4697: 'gro don byed par dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:4698: rat+na ma l+ya tram tram tram /
NK028(sa)001:4699: me tog 'phreng bas dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:4700: tshul khrims kyi 'phreng ba zhig ral yongs su rdzogs nas /
NK028(sa)001:4701: ngan song gsum du ltung ba las bzlog pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:4702: ye shes bdag nyid cod pan 'dis //
NK028(sa)001:4703: klu gdug gnod pas mi rdzi zhing //
NK028(sa)001:4704: 'khor ba'i nyes pas mi gos pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:4705: dbang mchog des ni dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:4706: badz+ra pa ta a b+hi yam pa na a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+ai /
NK028(sa)001:4707: cod pan gyis dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:4709: sbyor ba ngan pa'i bag chags dang bral bar gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:4710: de nas thur ma thogs te //
NK028(sa)001:4711: sngon gyi mig mkhan rgyal po yis //
NK028(sa)001:4712: mig ni rab rib bsal ba bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:4713: bu khyod ma rig thibs pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:4714: rab rib rgyal ba rnams kyis bsal //
NK028(sa)001:4715: zhes thur mas dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:4716: ma rig pa'i ling thog thibs po byang nas bsal bar gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:4717: de nas me long byin te //
NK028(sa)001:4718: chos rnams gzugs brnyan lta bu ste //
NK028(sa)001:4719: rten 'brel mthu las snang ba'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:4720: brjod med rang bzhin dag pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:4721: don dam chos nyid rtogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:4722: zhes me long gi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:4723: chos thams cad gzugs brnyan rten 'brel sgyu ma lta bur mthong ngo //
NK028(sa)001:4726: brjid pa'i gdan gyi 'bru bkod nas //
NK028(sa)001:4727: gzhan don 'di la phan pa'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:4728: rgyal bas 'khor lo bskor bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:4730: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang ldan te /
NK028(sa)001:4731: khams gsum gyi gnas thams cad du 'gro nus par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:4733: chos dung rgyas par bus nas ni /
NK028(sa)001:4734: lo ga'i sems can skal ldan la //
NK028(sa)001:4735: rna gsal sdig sbyangs chos thos pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:4736: skyobs pa mgon po tshangs skad sgrog /
NK028(sa)001:4737: zhes dung gi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:4738: tshangs pa'i sgra skad phun sum tshogs par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:4739: de nas rdo rje rgya gram spyi bor bzhag ste /
NK028(sa)001:4740: dgos pa'i sems can gnyis med la //
NK028(sa)001:4741: gtsug tu rgya gram dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:4742: rdo rje 'dzin pa rnams kyis kyang //
NK028(sa)001:4743: de la bsrung ba nyid du 'gyur //
NK028(sa)001:4744: zhes rgya gram gyis dbang bskur bas phyogs bcu nas sngags 'chang rnams kyis bsrungs bar gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:4745: de nas rin po che sna bdun nam mkha' la brgyud mar byung ste //
NK028(sa)001:4746: lha rdzas las byas lte ba shin tu zlum //
NK028(sa)001:4747: rtsibs stong ldan zhing mu khyud rab mnyam bzang //
NK028(sa)001:4748: sdang pa'i dgra las rnam par rgyal gyur pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:4749: 'khor lo rin chen dam pas dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:4751: 'khor lo rin po che'i rtsibs stong dang ldan pa zhig lag tu babs pas /
NK028(sa)001:4752: de ma thag tu 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po stong sdoms pa'i mthu dang ldan par gyur nas //
NK028(sa)001:4753: sangs rgyas kyi sa la nges par lung bstan to //
NK028(sa)001:4754: yan lag thams cad legs skyes pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:4755: rab gnas ri 'dra gang chen glang po che //
NK028(sa)001:4756: rgyal po la 'os mkha' la rab 'gro ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:4757: glang po rin chen dam pas dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:4758: ha sti rat+na a b+hi shiny+tsa mam /
NK028(sa)001:4759: zhes glang po che thal dkar 'dug pa yan lag bdun dang ldan pa zhig mdun du babs pas /
NK028(sa)001:4760: snas blangs te steng du bzhag pas /
NK028(sa)001:4761: 'gro ba rigs drug gi mthong thos pa'i gnas su
NK028(sa)001:4762: nges par 'degs nus pa'i thabs dang ldan pa zhig
NK028(sa)001:4763: tu gyur to // tho rangs dus su phyogs kun ma lus pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:4764: sa rnams bskor te slar yang ldog gyur pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:4765: rma bya'i mgrin pa'i spu ltar yid 'ong ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:4766: rta mchog rin chen dam pa dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:4767: tu ram ga a sho rat+na a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:4768: rta rin po che sprin gyi shugs 'chang gtsug na rin po che can zhig lag tu babs pas //
NK028(sa)001:4769: mi gnas pa'i dbyings su thogs pa med par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:4770: rin chen ngo bo lha rdzas beed+aur+ya //
NK028(sa)001:4771: kun tu dpag tshad tsam du snang byed cing //
NK028(sa)001:4772: dri med nyin mo ji bzhin mtshan de bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:4773: nor bu rin chen dam pas dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:4774: ma ni rat+na a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:4775: nor bu rin po che 'od 'bar gcig spyi bo'i gtsug tu babs pas /
NK028(sa)001:4776: phyi nang thams cad du mun pa sel te /
NK028(sa)001:4777: bsam pa yid bzhin du 'byung ba'i yon tan ldan par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:4778: 'gro dang ldog dang kun tu 'ong gyur pa //
NK028(sa)001:4779: ma lus bdud dpung 'joms par byed pa de //
NK028(sa)001:4780: dpal ldan 'byor pa'i dpung dang bcas pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:4781: dmag dpon rin chen dam pa dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:4782: kha ga rat+na a b+hi shiny+tsa mam //
NK028(sa)001:4783: dmag dpon rin po che lus la 'od 'bar ba /
NK028(sa)001:4784: phyag na mtshon cha thogs pa 'jigs pa zhig dpral bar babs pas /
NK028(sa)001:4785: phyogs bcu thams cad nas brdo zhing rgol ba rnams
NK028(sa)001:4786: shin tu zil gyis non cing dpa' bkong par gyur
NK028(sa)001:4787: to // gzugs mdzes lta na sdug cing tshul bzang ba /
NK028(sa)001:4788: lpags pa'i mdog legs 'jam zhing dri mchog ldan /
NK028(sa)001:4789: btsun mo rin chen dam pa dbang bskur ro wa ti rat+na a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:4790: btsun mo rin chen 'od 'bar ba chags pa'i spyan
NK028(sa)001:4791: gsum dang ldan pa zhig yan lag g.yon par babs
NK028(sa)001:4792: pas / de ma thag tu gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin du 'brel te /
NK028(sa)001:4793: bden pa ma nor ba'i don la chags pa mi
NK028(sa)001:4794: gtong ba byed pa'i gzugs dang ldan par gyur to
NK028(sa)001:4795: // gang yang rgyal bas mu tig mdangs ldan pas //
NK028(sa)001:4796: gser sogs mang po thub la phul ba ltar //
NK028(sa)001:4797: bzod ldan mtshungs pa'i khyim bdag nor ldan te //
NK028(sa)001:4798: blon po rin chen dam pas dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:4799: ma h+aa ta rat+na a b+hi shiny+tsa yam /
NK028(sa)001:4800: blon po rin po che 'od 'bar bas /
NK028(sa)001:4802: gzhan gyis ltar mi mngon pa zhig lag pa g.yas par babs pas /
NK028(sa)001:4803: blo dang brtson 'grus su ldan nas bde skyid 'tshams
NK028(sa)001:4804: pa bkod pa'i bshes gnyen dang ldan par gyur to
NK028(sa)001:4805: // de nas rin po che sna bdun lus la rdzogs par bsams pas /
NK028(sa)001:4806: phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor los bsgyur ba'i mchog sprin phung zhes bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:4807: dug gsum gcod pas 'khor ba stong /
NK028(sa)001:4809: bag chags ma lus kun dag pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:4810: shes rab ral gris dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:4812: ye shes ral gri lag tu byin nas dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:4813: dug gsum gzung 'dzin 'khrul pa rgyun bcad de /
NK028(sa)001:4814: bag chags thams cad byang zhing yang dag pa'i shes rab dang ldan par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:4815: brjid pa'i seng ge shin tu myur ba yi //
NK028(sa)001:4816: gzugs can cig ni lag tu byin pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:4817: gsung rab rgya mtsho kun gyis sgra sgrogs te //
NK028(sa)001:4818: log pa'i phyogs kun zil gyis gnon par shog /
NK028(sa)001:4819: badz+ra sing ha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:4820: brjid pa'i seng ge shin tu myur ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:4821: gzugs can cig lag tu byin nas dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:4822: gsung rab rgya mtsho'i sgras log pa'i phyogs zil gyis mnan nas /
NK028(sa)001:4823: skad cig ma gcig gis stong spyi phud kyi steng du mngon par sangs rgyas te /
NK028(sa)001:4825: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po zhes bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:4826: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi legs so legs so zhes bya bas bstod do //
NK028(sa)001:4827: steng phyogs mnga' mdzad thugs rjes nyi ltar bdal //
NK028(sa)001:4828: thugs rje mun sel thugs rje zla ba'i 'od //
NK028(sa)001:4829: stong gsum mun pa kun tu gsal nas ni //
NK028(sa)001:4830: sems can kun gyi snang ba bskyed par shog /
NK028(sa)001:4831: s+aur+ya tsan+ta a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:4832: nyi zla phyag tu gtad de dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:4833: de ma thag tu nyi mas skye 'gro ma lus
NK028(sa)001:4834: pa'i sems can gyis rgyud la ye shes kyi 'od
NK028(sa)001:4835: zer chen po mtha' med shar bas /
NK028(sa)001:4838: stong gsum gyi mun pa rnams dus gcig tu gsal nas /
NK028(sa)001:4839: dus dang rnam pa thams cad du bsil zhing snang bar gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:4840: des thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang chen po rdzogs par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:4841: thabs kyi gzhu 'di ye shes gsal //
NK028(sa)001:4842: shes rab mda' ni dbyings su myur //
NK028(sa)001:4843: zung du 'brel bas ye shes gsal //
NK028(sa)001:4844: dag pa'i rtse mor gnas par shog /
NK028(sa)001:4845: d+ha na sha ro a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:4846: mda' gzhu phyag tu phul te dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:4847: thabs dang shes rab dbyings dang ye shes zung du
NK028(sa)001:4848: 'brel ba'i ye shes dag pa'i rtse mo la gnas
NK028(sa)001:4849: par gyur to / de nas thams cad nas thams
NK028(sa)001:4850: cad du bkra shis par grub pa'i rdzas su gsungs
NK028(sa)001:4851: par gyur to / pa / ta th+aa rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:4852: bo d+hi sa t+wa rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:4857: gang zag dad pas bsams shing rig pa'i glang po dang /
NK028(sa)001:4858: mkhyen pa'i dpal la sogs te legs pa'i sbyin gnas su bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:4859: bkra shis kyi mnga' gsol nas /
NK028(sa)001:4860: 'gro ba gzhan la phan pa'i don du tshigs su bcad pas bstod pa /
NK028(sa)001:4861: de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa bskyed ba kye /
NK028(sa)001:4862: rdo rje bdag yongs gtan du ma btang zhig /
NK028(sa)001:4863: yungs kar dngos grub bgegs kyi sbyor ba rnams 'joms dang /
NK028(sa)001:4864: zho yis rgyal byed ting 'dzin bcud kyis 'tsho ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:4865: dur bas dge ba'i rtsa ba dpag med tshogs ldan dang /
NK028(sa)001:4866: li khris lha mo dbang du sdud pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:4867: me long gis ni chos rnams gzugs brnyan lta bur mngon rtogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:4868: dung gis lo ga gsum du grags pa thob pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:4869: gi wam dug gsum zhi byed chos srog 'tsho ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:4870: bil bas bla med byang chub thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:4872: yangs kar rdo rjes bgegs mchog 'dul /
NK028(sa)001:4873: bgegs rnams 'joms pa'i mthu stobs ldan /
NK028(sa)001:4874: dgra bgegs kun las rgyal ba yi //
NK028(sa)001:4875: byin brlabs chen po'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:4878: da ltar bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyis thub pa'i rdzas gsum byin gyis rlabs /
NK028(sa)001:4879: shis pa'i yangs kar phyag tu phul bas //
NK028(sa)001:4880: bgegs kyi rigs stong phrag brgyad bcu'i rtog pa rnams
NK028(sa)001:4881: kyi bsam sbyor ngan pa kun gcod par mdzad do
NK028(sa)001:4882: // zho ni kun gyi snying por gyur pas te //
NK028(sa)001:4883: snying po rnam dag byang chub sems rtogs shing //
NK028(sa)001:4884: yon tan kun gyi snying por gyur pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:4885: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir zhi bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:4886: bcom ldan 'das la khyim bdag bzang skyong gis zho
NK028(sa)001:4887: phyag tu phul bas kun gyi dbang po'i bcud yongs
NK028(sa)001:4888: su tshim par byed pa 'dod 'jo'i ba khyad par
NK028(sa)001:4889: can du byin gyis rlabs so //
NK028(sa)001:4890: dur bas tshe ni 'phel bas byed pa ste //
NK028(sa)001:4891: rdo rje tshe ni dbang grub pas //
NK028(sa)001:4892: skye shi'i sdug bsngal rgyun bcad de //
NK028(sa)001:4893: dur ba'i bkra shis des ni tshe brtan shog /
NK028(sa)001:4894: bcom ldan 'das la bram ze kun d+aa lis rtsa dur ba phul bas /
NK028(sa)001:4895: dur ba lo 'dab rgyas shing 'phel ba bzhin du /
NK028(sa)001:4896: sems can thams cad la bsod nams 'phel bar byin gyis rlabs so //
NK028(sa)001:4897: li khri dmar ba dbang gi rang bzhin te /
NK028(sa)001:4898: chos kun ma lus dbang du gyur pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:4899: chos kyi rgyal srid rab tu brtan gyur pa /
NK028(sa)001:4900: bkra shis des kyang rab tu brtan par shog /
NK028(sa)001:4901: bcom ldan 'das la sa'i lha mo brtan mas li khri phul bas /
NK028(sa)001:4902: li khri chags shing zhen pa bzhin du thugs rje
NK028(sa)001:4903: chen po'i dbang gis nyon mongs pa'i sems can mi
NK028(sa)001:4904: gtong bar thugs dam du bzhes so //
NK028(sa)001:4905: gi wam dug gsum 'joms pa'i sman yin te //
NK028(sa)001:4906: sman mchog chos nyid rab tu rtogs gyur cing //
NK028(sa)001:4907: nyon mongs zug rngu med par gyur pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:4908: bkra shis des kyang sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:4909: bcom ldan 'das la glang po che sa bsrungs gis bus /
NK028(sa)001:4910: gi wam phyag tu phul bas //
NK028(sa)001:4911: bdud rtsi sman gyi mchog tu gyur te //
NK028(sa)001:4912: nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i gnyen por byin gyis brlabs so //
NK028(sa)001:4913: dung gi chos kyi sgra chen sgrog pa'i tshul //
NK028(sa)001:4914: yon tan rgya mtsho bdag nyid mchog gyur nas //
NK028(sa)001:4915: rnam dag chos la tho ga med longs spyod pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:4916: bkra shis des ni tshigs la longs spyod shog /
NK028(sa)001:4917: bcom ldan 'das la lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis
NK028(sa)001:4918: dung g.yas su 'khyil ba bcu drug pa cig phyag
NK028(sa)001:4919: tu phul bas / sum cu rtsa gsum gyi gnas
NK028(sa)001:4920: yan chad nas lo ga so so'i rigs su tshangs
NK028(sa)001:4921: pa'i sgra skad phun sum tshogs pas chos sgra chen
NK028(sa)001:4922: po yongs su rdzogs par mdzad do //
NK028(sa)001:4923: me long ye shes chen po'i gzugs brnyan te //
NK028(sa)001:4924: ye shes rgya mtsho'i bdag nyid mchog gyur nas //
NK028(sa)001:4925: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pas //
NK028(sa)001:4926: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir sgrib pa dag gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:4927: bcom ldan 'das la sa'i lha mos gzugs brnyan bstan cing me long phul bas //
NK028(sa)001:4928: me long g.ya' dag pa la gzugs kyi dngos po snang la /
NK028(sa)001:4929: stong pa shin tu thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK028(sa)001:4930: kyi go 'phang rdzogs pa stong pa snang bar mdzad
NK028(sa)001:4931: do // bil pa rgyu rkyen 'bras bur bcas pa'i chos //
NK028(sa)001:4932: 'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i spyod pa kun //
NK028(sa)001:4933: byang chub snying po mchog tu gyur pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:4934: bkra shis des ni 'jig rten 'grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:4935: bcom ldan 'das la shing gi lha mo 'od 'chang gis /
NK028(sa)001:4936: shing bil pa phyag tu phul bas /
NK028(sa)001:4937: bil pa ji ltar smin pa rgyas pa gang bar gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:4938: mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa bde ba chen po'i dbyings su rdzogs par sangs rgyas so //
NK028(sa)001:4939: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi spyi dbang rnam
NK028(sa)001:4940: par snang mdzad thig le dbang gi rgyal po'i rgyud
NK028(sa)001:4941: las / phyi dbang bcu drug gi gleng gzhi'i le'u ste lnga pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:4942: de nas bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang pos skad cig yud tsam la /
NK028(sa)001:4943: nam mkha' gang nas gang du khyab pa thams cad
NK028(sa)001:4944: du dbang gi dkyil 'khor zhi khro'i lha lnga brgya
NK028(sa)001:4945: brgyad bcu rtsa gsum gyis gang bar mdzad nas /
NK028(sa)001:4946: sngar sangs rgyas pa mya ngan las 'das //
NK028(sa)001:4947: chos kyi sku la bzhugs pa rnams /
NK028(sa)001:4948: chos kyi sku las gzugs kyis skur bzhengs la 'gro ba'i don mdzod cig par dbang bskur te /
NK028(sa)001:4949: sangs rgyas kyi sku re re la yang lha lnga
NK028(sa)001:4950: bcu rtsa gsum gyis thams cad kyis ye nas sangs
NK028(sa)001:4954: thams cad kyis de bzhin du dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:4955: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa rnams ngo mtshar rmad du gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:4956: e ma ho bcom ldan 'das ngo mtshar ro snyam nas /
NK028(sa)001:4957: mgrin cig tu 'di skad ces gsol to //
NK028(sa)001:4958: bcom ldan 'das ta th+aa thams cad kyis zhi khro'i
NK028(sa)001:4959: lha sku phyag rgya chen po'i dbang de bdag cag
NK028(sa)001:4960: dang phyi rabs kyi rnal 'byor pa rnams la lung
NK028(sa)001:4961: bstan du gsol // kun tu bzang pos bka' stsal pa //
NK028(sa)001:4962: 'gro ba'i don du zhus pa legs so //
NK028(sa)001:4963: dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud 'di yang bskur thabs nyi shu rtsa gcig dang //
NK028(sa)001:4964: 'dren pa'i las byang bskur ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:4965: lta ba ye 'byam gyi dang gsum mo //
NK028(sa)001:4966: de la bskur thabs ni gong du bstan pa bzhin no //
NK028(sa)001:4967: 'dren pa'i las byang chen pos bskur ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:4970: byin brlabs slob dpon gyi dbang dang /
NK028(sa)001:4971: thob pa ming gi dbang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:4972: de la dang po phan pa lha'i dbang ni /
NK028(sa)001:4973: dkyil 'khor gyi dbyibs zla ba tshes brgyad pa la spro bsdu byas pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:4974: tshes bcu drug bar pa'i steng man+dala gyis dbyibs 'dom bzhi khru bzhi cha gang pa rtsigs /
NK028(sa)001:4975: de nas phyogs bzhir mda' ro bcal bar bang rim cig rtsigs /
NK028(sa)001:4976: de nas 'dom phyed bcal bar bang rim gcig rtsegs /
NK028(sa)001:4977: de'i steng du bang rim gcig rtsigs te /
NK028(sa)001:4978: bang rim gsum brtsegs su bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:4979: yang dkyil na mtha' ru thig skud drangs la /
NK028(sa)001:4980: gsum ltab tu byas la bang rim gsum par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:4981: bang rim dang po'i steng du zhi ba'i lha zhe gnyis bkod /
NK028(sa)001:4982: bar pa la khro bo'i lha bdun cu rtsa brgyad dgod /
NK028(sa)001:4987: zla gam kha sprod la dus gsum gyis rig 'dzin slob dpon bzhugs /
NK028(sa)001:4989: man+dala gyi rtsar phur pa'i lha zhe gnyis dgod /
NK028(sa)001:4992: zhi khro gzhan rnams gzhung bzhin no //
NK028(sa)001:4993: de nas ting nge 'dzin gsum bsgom ste /
NK028(sa)001:4994: gzhal yas khang du gsung yig 'bru gsum las /
NK028(sa)001:4996: sku phyag rgya rdzogs par bskyed nas /
NK028(sa)001:4997: ye shes kyi lha spyan drangs la mchod de /
NK028(sa)001:4999: slob ma dal du drangs te /
NK028(sa)001:5000: phan pa lha'i dbang zhi khro gnyis kyi dbang bskur ba'i 'phrin las ni /
NK028(sa)001:5001: sku phyag rgya chen por bris pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:5003: rang bzhin gnyis su med pas /
NK028(sa)001:5004: zhi ba'i lha rnams sku gsung thugs bris sgom byas te /
NK028(sa)001:5005: tsak+ka li'i rgyab yig kun 'dus dang /
NK028(sa)001:5006: rngam klog nas gsungs pa bzhin klog cing dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:5007: slob ma'i spyi bor bzhag cing lag tu gtad nas dbang bskur la 'di skad do //
NK028(sa)001:5008: de nas khro bo'i dkyil 'khor che mchog yab yum nas rim par bskur ba yang 'di skad do //
NK028(sa)001:5009: de nas 'gro ba 'dul ba'i dkyil 'khor thugs rje
NK028(sa)001:5010: sprul pa'i 'khor rnams kyi dbang bskur ba 'di skad
NK028(sa)001:5011: do // de nas byin rlabs slob dpon gyi dbang ni //
NK028(sa)001:5012: dus gsum gyi rdo rje slob dpon gyis mtshan dang //
NK028(sa)001:5013: gsang mtshan du bcas pas dbang bskur te //
NK028(sa)001:5014: de yang dam tshig dbang gi slob dpon dang //
NK028(sa)001:5015: shes rab brgyud kyis slob dpon dang /
NK028(sa)001:5016: gnang ba 'bras bu'i slob dpon gyi rim pas bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:5017: thob pa ming gi dbang ni /
NK028(sa)001:5018: phal cher lha mang po bsgom mi nus pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:5019: lha mang po la mi mos pa la mang pos bskur kyang mi thob mi chags pas /
NK028(sa)001:5021: gang dag rgya cher ba cig la'ang /
NK028(sa)001:5023: gang yang mi spong ba la ming gis thams cad rdzogs par mi bskur du mi rung ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:5024: 'di dag gi go rim slob dpon gyis shes par byas la /
NK028(sa)001:5025: snod kyi rim pa dang sbyar ba las /
NK028(sa)001:5028: ngo dkar bya ba ni ma yin no /
NK028(sa)001:5029: ta th+aa thams cad kyi spyi dbang rnam par snang
NK028(sa)001:5030: mdzad kyi thig le dbang bskur ba rgyal po'i rgyud
NK028(sa)001:5031: las / rnal 'byor chen po rnams la 'dren pa'i
NK028(sa)001:5032: las byang chen pos dbang bskur ba'i le'u ste drug
NK028(sa)001:5033: las / pa'o // de nas rnal 'byor ba blo
NK028(sa)001:5034: rab 'bring med par yongs la bskur ba ni bskur
NK028(sa)001:5044: bdud rtsi ra sa ya na dang /
NK028(sa)001:5051: de la dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:5052: dbu rgyan thod pa'i gzhal yas khang lngar gyur pa'i
NK028(sa)001:5053: nang du he ra ka lnga bsams la 'di skad
NK028(sa)001:5054: do // sangs rgyas kun gyi rat+na che /
NK028(sa)001:5055: dpag tu med par 'od dang ldan //
NK028(sa)001:5056: rigs mchog phyag rgya lngar ldan pas /
NK028(sa)001:5057: khams gsum bdag por dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:5058: badz+ra rat+na mu gu tra tram tram tram /
NK028(sa)001:5059: khro bo'i dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:5060: dregs pa bdud dang srin po 'dul ba'i dbang chen po thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:5061: cod pan gyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:5062: slob ma de 'khor dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK028(sa)001:5063: chos la mnga' brnyes shing gdug pa can thams cad
NK028(sa)001:5064: 'dul ba dang / chos kyi rgyal po byed par
NK028(sa)001:5065: rgyal ba tshe dpag tu med par bsgoms la 'di
NK028(sa)001:5066: 'dul ba dang / skad do // cod pan mi 'gyur mnga' brnyes pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:5067: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po'i dbang //
NK028(sa)001:5068: khams gsum kun gyis dbang phyug che //
NK028(sa)001:5069: chos kyi rgyal po'i dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:5070: d+har+m+ma ra dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:5071: cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:5072: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po la mnga' brnyes nas //
NK028(sa)001:5073: chos kyi 'khor lo yongs su bskor bar gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:5074: ban d+has dbang bskur ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:5075: snod bcud chos kyi sku dang ldan par bsgoms la 'di skad do //
NK028(sa)001:5076: mtshan ma'i rtog bral b+han+d+ha'i rdzas /
NK028(sa)001:5077: mchog ni sngon gyi skyes mchog sgrub pa'i rdzas yin te //
NK028(sa)001:5078: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:5079: snod bcud chos kyi sku dang ldan par shog /
NK028(sa)001:5080: d+har+m+ma ra ka ya sha ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:5081: b+han d+has dbang bskur bas snod bcud chos kyi sku dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:5082: byang chub sems kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:5083: skye med byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ni /
NK028(sa)001:5084: dkar la dag pa gnyis med byang chub sems /
NK028(sa)001:5085: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:5086: rdo rje rigs kyi sid+d+hi thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:5087: a ta ri sha at+ma ko & ho //
NK028(sa)001:5088: byang chub sems kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:5089: me long lta bu'i ye shes dang ldan te rdo rje rigs kyi sid+d+hi thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:5090: dri chen gyi dbang bskur ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:5091: dri chen bdud rtsi chen po'i rang bzhin te //
NK028(sa)001:5092: rnam rtog dug sel bdud rtsi bdag nyid kyis //
NK028(sa)001:5093: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:5094: ta th+aa rigs kyi sid+d+hi thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:5095: ma h+aa shu nya ta at+ma ko & ho //
NK028(sa)001:5096: dri chen gyi dbang bskur bas stong pa nyid kyi
NK028(sa)001:5097: ye shes dang ldan te ta th+aa'i sid+hi thob par
NK028(sa)001:5098: gyur cig / mam sa'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:5099: ma rig khams gsum 'khor ba'i sems can rnams //
NK028(sa)001:5100: gnas nas sgrol mdzad rdzas mchog sha chen 'dis //
NK028(sa)001:5101: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:5102: rat+na rigs kyi sid+d+hi thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:5104: sha chen gyi dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:5105: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dang ldan te //
NK028(sa)001:5106: rat+na rigs kyi sid+d+hi thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:5108: gsang ba'i dbang gi rdzas mchog rak+ta 'di //
NK028(sa)001:5109: chags med bde bar spyad pas dmar la dngas //
NK028(sa)001:5110: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:5111: pad+ma rigs kyi sid+d+hi thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:5112: pra ta pra be sha at+ma ko & ho //
NK028(sa)001:5114: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang ldan te //
NK028(sa)001:5115: pad+ma rigs kyi sid+d+hi thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:5116: dri chu dbang bskur ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:5117: rang byung dag pas las kyi rigs kyi rdzas //
NK028(sa)001:5118: phyi nang gsos gyur bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin 'dis //
NK028(sa)001:5119: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:5120: las kyi rigs kyi sid+d+hi thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:5121: kri ta a nu ta at+ma ko & ham //
NK028(sa)001:5123: bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes dang ldan te /
NK028(sa)001:5124: las kyi rigs kyi sid+d+hi thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:5125: rdo rje dril bu dbang bskur ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:5126: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med pa //
NK028(sa)001:5127: thugs mchog rtogs pa rin chen brgyan //
NK028(sa)001:5128: rdo rje dril bu dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:5129: thabs dang shes rab dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:5130: badz+ra g+han+da ri sha s+w+aa h+aa //
NK028(sa)001:5131: rdo rje dril bus dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:5132: sku dang ye shes su ldan pa'i chos la longs spyod par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:5133: phur bu dbang bskur ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:5134: dpal chen yab yum thugs ka nas //
NK028(sa)001:5135: mthar byed bgegs rnams tshar gcod mtshon char ldan //
NK028(sa)001:5136: rdo rje ki la ya yi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:5137: log 'dren dgra bgegs tshogs rnams 'joms par shog /
NK028(sa)001:5138: badz+ra ki li ki li ya a b+hi sha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:5140: ya ma dam sri bar chad sgrol ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:5141: bdud rtsi ra sa ya na dbang bskur ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:5142: thams cad sman yin bdud rtsi mchog /
NK028(sa)001:5143: rgyal ba kun gyis bsgrub pa'i lam //
NK028(sa)001:5144: ra sa ya nas dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:5145: bdud rtsi bcud dang phrad par shog /
NK028(sa)001:5146: sarba a mri sha ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:5147: bdud rtsi a mri ta'i dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:5148: skye shi med pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:5150: 'phreng ba mya ngan 'das pa'i chos la spyod //
NK028(sa)001:5151: 'gro kun yang dag chos kyi don la 'jug /
NK028(sa)001:5152: me tog 'phreng ba la sogs dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:5153: gzungs dang ting 'dzin ldan pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:5154: rat+na ma la a b+hi shiny+tsa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:5155: me tog 'phreng ba dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:5156: gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:5157: yungs kar gyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:5158: yungs kar rgyal po'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:5159: bar gcod bgegs kyi tshogs 'joms grub rdzas ni /
NK028(sa)001:5160: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:5161: bar gcod bgegs rnams rdul du brlag par shog /
NK028(sa)001:5163: yungs dkar gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:5164: sprul pa 'gyed pa dang dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:5165: mar me gyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:5166: dpal chen yab yum gsang ba'i thugs bsdus pas //
NK028(sa)001:5167: skye med dbyings nas ye shes mar me gsal //
NK028(sa)001:5168: kun gzhi gnas gyur spyan gyi ye shes 'di //
NK028(sa)001:5169: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:5170: badz+ra dz+ny+aa na a lo ke shwa ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:5171: me mar gyi dbang bskur bas dpal chen po'i ye
NK028(sa)001:5172: shes kyi sku la ma skyes pa chos kyi dbyings
NK028(sa)001:5174: ma 'gags pa me long lta bu'i ye shes dang //
NK028(sa)001:5175: kun la khyab pa mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dang //
NK028(sa)001:5176: ma 'dres pa so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang //
NK028(sa)001:5177: mthar phyin pas bya ba nan tan gyis ye shes dang //
NK028(sa)001:5178: ma g.yos pa stong pa chen po'i ye shes dang //
NK028(sa)001:5179: klong du gyur pas 'da' ka thugs kyi ye shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:5180: bdag nyid chen po'i ngang du gyur pas dbyings su sgrol ba'i ye shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:5181: bde ba chen po la gnyis su med par sbyangs pa'i ye shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:5182: ye shes dgu dang ldan pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:5183: rnga chung gi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:5184: shes rab gsang ba'i sgra sgrogs rnga mchog 'di //
NK028(sa)001:5185: khams gsum ma lus kun la chos sgra sgrogs //
NK028(sa)001:5186: nga rgyal drag shul bdud tshogs rnam 'joms pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:5187: phyag mtshan 'di yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:5188: pradz+ny+aa tsa ma rak+sha ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:5189: rnga chung gi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:5190: chos sku skye ba med pa'i sgra sgrogs pas /
NK028(sa)001:5191: bdud dang srin po zil gyis mnan te /
NK028(sa)001:5192: ma mo dang d+aak+ki dbang du bsdud pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:5193: ta th+aa thams cad kyi spyi dbang /
NK028(sa)001:5194: rnam par snang mdzad thig le dbang bskur ba rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK028(sa)001:5195: 'dren pa'i las byang chung ngu'i le'u ste bdun pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:5196: de nas rnal 'byor pas man ngag nges pa'i don
NK028(sa)001:5197: la mkhas shing ye shes lhun gyis grub pa'i rang
NK028(sa)001:5198: bzhin du gyur pa rnams ni /
NK028(sa)001:5199: rigs pa'i rgyal po rang dbang du gyur pas dbang bskur kyang mi dgos /
NK028(sa)001:5202: lha'i rgyal po de rgyud dul phan 'dogs /
NK028(sa)001:5203: gser 'gyur ni gser du ma rtags kyang gser du snang zhing //
NK028(sa)001:5204: gser gzhan pas brgyad cu sde yis dpags la /
NK028(sa)001:5205: gser srang gcig gis zangs srang stong la reg kyang /
NK028(sa)001:5207: bdag nyid chen po byang chub sems kyi dbang du gyur na /
NK028(sa)001:5209: thams cad ye nas byang chub sems kyi sangs rgyas su dbang bskur zhing /
NK028(sa)001:5210: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par lhun gyis grub pas /
NK028(sa)001:5211: rgyu 'bras kyi chos thams cad dbyer med par mdzad /
NK028(sa)001:5212: sangs rgyas dang sems can zhes bya ba med par dbang bskur na /
NK028(sa)001:5213: yid bzhin gyis nor bu rin po che la ji ltar dgos 'dod 'byung ba dang 'dra bar /
NK028(sa)001:5214: ye nas yangs pa chen po'i klong la gang yang mi dog cing /
NK028(sa)001:5215: kun tu bzang po la ci yang mi rtog pas /
NK028(sa)001:5216: lta ba ye 'byams kyi dbang bskur ba'i phyir 'di skad gsungs so //
NK028(sa)001:5217: chos rnams thams cad nam mkha'i khams //
NK028(sa)001:5218: dang po mtshan ma kun las 'das //
NK028(sa)001:5219: nam mkha' bzhin du ye gnas la //
NK028(sa)001:5220: de la mkhas pas bcos su med //
NK028(sa)001:5221: de bzhin sems kyi rnam pa kun //
NK028(sa)001:5222: de bzhin nyid du bcos las 'das //
NK028(sa)001:5223: 'di ltar ye nas yin rtogs na //
NK028(sa)001:5224: dbang rnams bskur yang yong mi dgos //
NK028(sa)001:5225: stong gsum ma bcos chos nyid klong //
NK028(sa)001:5226: srid gsum ye nas rnam par dag /
NK028(sa)001:5227: khams gsum phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs //
NK028(sa)001:5228: dug gsum bdud rtsi byang chub sems //
NK028(sa)001:5229: lus ngag yid gsum ye shes lha //
NK028(sa)001:5230: thams cad skyon med yon tan dag /
NK028(sa)001:5231: bde ba che las gzhan med pas //
NK028(sa)001:5232: dbang rnams thams cad ma bskur rtogs //
NK028(sa)001:5233: sangs rgyas sems can thams cad dang //
NK028(sa)001:5234: rgyu dang 'bras bu la sogs pa //
NK028(sa)001:5235: gnyis su med par ye shes pas //
NK028(sa)001:5236: byang chub sems su dbang bskur yin //
NK028(sa)001:5237: ming dang tshig dang yi ge dang //
NK028(sa)001:5238: theg pa'i bye brag thams cad kyang //
NK028(sa)001:5239: don dam gcig tu sus shes pa //
NK028(sa)001:5240: byang chub sems kyi dbang thob yin //
NK028(sa)001:5241: las dang las chen la sogs pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:5242: rtsol bsgrub bya ba ci byas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:5243: byang chub don la rtsal med pas //
NK028(sa)001:5244: sangs rgyas rnams kyis ma rtsal bshad //
NK028(sa)001:5245: nyon mongs las dang du kha dang //
NK028(sa)001:5246: 'dzin rtog mtshan ma'i las rnams kyang //
NK028(sa)001:5247: pad+ma chus mi chags pa bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:5248: byang chub sems la gos pa med //
NK028(sa)001:5249: dbang dang dam tshig thams cad dang //
NK028(sa)001:5250: de bzhin 'phrin las bya ba kun //
NK028(sa)001:5251: byas na skyon med legs pa'i lam //
NK028(sa)001:5252: ma byas na yang byang chub sems //
NK028(sa)001:5253: phyi nyid nang la nang nyid phyi //
NK028(sa)001:5254: snang ba thams cad rang rig 'char //
NK028(sa)001:5255: brjod pas tshig dang yi ge med //
NK028(sa)001:5257: de bzhin ma bcos byang chub sems //
NK028(sa)001:5258: ma rtsal bzhag pas gdod nas dag /
NK028(sa)001:5259: 'gyur ba med pas lhun gyis grub //
NK028(sa)001:5262: ta th+aa thams cad kyi spyi dbang //
NK028(sa)001:5263: rnam par snang mdzad thig le dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK028(sa)001:5264: lta ba ye 'byams kyi dbang gi le'u ste brgyad pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:5265: de nas dam tshig nyams pa med pa'i dbang ni /
NK028(sa)001:5266: thams cad rang gi dbang yin par shes shing /
NK028(sa)001:5267: ye nas kun tu bzang por sangs rgyas pa la /
NK028(sa)001:5268: phyogs ris dang che chung sgro bskur med par lung bstan par rtogs pa las /
NK028(sa)001:5269: dam tshig la yang nyams pa med la /
NK028(sa)001:5270: dbang la yang thob pa med do //
NK028(sa)001:5271: spyod pa ma spangs lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang ni /
NK028(sa)001:5272: ci byas ci spyad 'dre ldog spyir gtsug gar 'dres kyang //
NK028(sa)001:5273: snying po byang chub sems las ma gtogs pa gang du yang 'gyur ba med pas /
NK028(sa)001:5274: nam mkha' mtshan gyis ma zhen pa bzhin du spyod
NK028(sa)001:5275: pa ci spyad pa sangs rgyas kyi mdzad spyod lhun
NK028(sa)001:5276: gyis grub la dbang yang thob bo //
NK028(sa)001:5277: bsgrub pa mthar phyin pa'i dbang ni /
NK028(sa)001:5278: skyon dang yon tan bde ba dang sdug bsngal gnyis med pas /
NK028(sa)001:5279: gcig gis brgyan du gcig gyur pas /
NK028(sa)001:5280: ci byas pa chud mi zos par 'khor ba nyid
NK028(sa)001:5281: mya ngan las 'das pa chen por lhun gyis grub
NK028(sa)001:5282: pas / the tshom med par yid ches pas /
NK028(sa)001:5283: bsgrub pa mthar ma phyin pa yang med la /
NK028(sa)001:5284: dbang ma thob pa yang med do //
NK028(sa)001:5285: 'phrin las bya rtsol med pa'i dbang ni /
NK028(sa)001:5286: ye nas sems sangs rgyas min na sol ba dang 'dra la /
NK028(sa)001:5287: ye nas sangs rgyas yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:5289: yin pa'i don la ma yengs ma chags pas /
NK028(sa)001:5290: sangs rgyas nyid yin pas yin pa'i don la ma yengs shing /
NK028(sa)001:5293: 'pho 'gyur med pa yin pas de la ma yengs shig /
NK028(sa)001:5294: 'dzin rtog gi skyon thams cad ma skyes pa'i klong du shes pas /
NK028(sa)001:5297: yon tan yang che bas ma yengs shig /
NK028(sa)001:5298: des na 'phrin las rtsol du med la //
NK028(sa)001:5299: dbang yang ma thob pa med do //
NK028(sa)001:5300: dbang yang sangs rgyas kyi dbang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:5301: yod ni rang gi sems la yod //
NK028(sa)001:5302: thob ni slob dpon la dam tshig ma nyams na slob dpon la thob bo //
NK028(sa)001:5303: mthar ni ma yengs na byin par 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:5304: 'grub ni ci yang ma bcos ma slad pas 'grub bo //
NK028(sa)001:5305: don thams cad dgongs pa nyag cig tu gtugs so //
NK028(sa)001:5306: ta th+aa thams cad kyi phyi dbang /
NK028(sa)001:5307: rnam par snang mdzad thig le dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK028(sa)001:5308: yongs su grub pa dbang gi le'u ste dgu pa'o ////
NK028(sa)001:5309: de nas kun tu bzang po'i thugs kyis klong nas bka' stsal pa /
NK028(sa)001:5310: ji ltar bka' mthun yid bcug kyang //
NK028(sa)001:5311: snying gi slob mar ma gyur cing //
NK028(sa)001:5312: gsang ba'i don dang ma ldan na //
NK028(sa)001:5313: dbang gi don 'di ma smra cig /
NK028(sa)001:5314: ma smras na ni gzi che la //
NK028(sa)001:5315: gsang mi thub la bstan byas na //
NK028(sa)001:5316: des ni gsang sngags zong du 'tshong //
NK028(sa)001:5317: sangs rgyas thams cad sku bslus so //
NK028(sa)001:5318: rdzogs pa chen po la sdig med kyang /
NK028(sa)001:5319: gsang mi thub pa'i gang zag ste //
NK028(sa)001:5320: sangs rgyas ma yin bdud yin pas //
NK028(sa)001:5321: de bsten sdig pa nang nas che //
NK028(sa)001:5322: khams gsum sems can bsad pa bas //
NK028(sa)001:5323: gsang sgrogs sdig pa'i char mi phod //
NK028(sa)001:5325: nyes byas nyams pa brjod las 'das //
NK028(sa)001:5326: ji lta ji snyed gsang zhing gsungs //
NK028(sa)001:5327: de bzhin bstan kyang nyan mi byed //
NK028(sa)001:5328: 'dod pas rdzas skyon phyir khrid pas //
NK028(sa)001:5329: slob dpon bka' bcog dam tshig med //
NK028(sa)001:5330: lo ga 'di na snying rje med //
NK028(sa)001:5331: de 'dra snod min gzhan du skrod //
NK028(sa)001:5332: sngags kyi theg pa la sogs pa //
NK028(sa)001:5333: bskal pa brgyar yang ma bsnyen cig /
NK028(sa)001:5334: gsang med gol zhing nyams pa med //
NK028(sa)001:5335: kun tu bzang po'i lung la med //
NK028(sa)001:5336: de bas rnal 'byor snying po des //
NK028(sa)001:5337: gsang ba la ni skyon med do //
NK028(sa)001:5338: dang po slob dpon pha bzhin byos //
NK028(sa)001:5339: bar du dbang dang dam tshig nos //
NK028(sa)001:5340: tha mar man ngag gter bzhin chos //
NK028(sa)001:5342: yang gsang nges pa'i don chen 'di //
NK028(sa)001:5343: gang gis bcangs pa sangs rgyas nyid //
NK028(sa)001:5344: kun tu bzang po skyon med pas //
NK028(sa)001:5345: 'gal zhing gsol bar ma gsungs so //
NK028(sa)001:5346: ta th+aa thams cad kyi spyi dbang //
NK028(sa)001:5347: rnam par snang mdzad thig le dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK028(sa)001:5348: kun tu bzang po thugs kyi gdams ngag gi le'u ste bcu pa'o ////
NK028(sa)001:5349: rgyu bde ba gsal mdzad kyis theg pa 'dus pa'i
NK028(sa)001:5350: mdo dbang la drug gsum bco brgyad du sdebs pa
NK028(sa)001:5351: las / dang por gdab pa'i dbang le'u drug bskal pa dum bu'i rgyud du ston pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:5352: theg pa 'dus pa'i mdo dbang rdzogs so //
NK028(sa)001:5353: de dag ni phyi dbang chen po'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK028(sa)001:5354: 'dren pa'i las byang che le dang //
NK028(sa)001:5355: 'dren pa'i las byang chung le dang //
NK028(sa)001:5356: yongs su grub pa'i dbang le dang //
NK028(sa)001:5357: lta ba ye 'byams dbang le dang //
NK028(sa)001:5358: kun bzang thugs kyi gdams ngag le dang /
NK028(sa)001:5359: rnam pa drug tu las gnyer gtad //
NK028(sa)001:5360: bar du dgos pa'i bsgrubs thabs drug /
NK028(sa)001:5361: dbang don bsdus dang dbang don rgyas //
NK028(sa)001:5362: rgya cher byed dang man ngag gsang //
NK028(sa)001:5363: las tho rab gnas bshags pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:5364: gsang sngags byung tshul gleng gzhi dang //
NK028(sa)001:5365: drug gis bsgrub pa'i don rnam bshad //
NK028(sa)001:5366: rgyun du dgos pa'i lag len drug /
NK028(sa)001:5367: sbyin bsreg lhag chog dkyil 'khor thig /
NK028(sa)001:5368: phyi nang gnyis kyi tsak+ka li //
NK028(sa)001:5369: rgyud khungs gtad rgya'i gleng gzhi drug /
NK028(sa)001:5370: drug gsum bco brgyad yi ge 'dis //
NK028(sa)001:5371: sangs rgyas ye shes bdag gis brnyed //
NK028(sa)001:5372: snod ldan rnams dang phrad par shog /
NK028(sa)001:5374: dbang chog rin chen 'khor lo las //
NK028(sa)001:5375: dang po bum dbang gleng gzhi nas //
NK028(sa)001:5376: yang dag brtsams te bdag gis bshad /
NK028(sa)001:5379: de ltar dpal ldan 'dus sogs pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:5380: rgyud rgyal kun las grags pa rnams //
NK028(sa)001:5381: gleng gzhi zhes su rnam par bshad //
NK028(sa)001:5383: ston pa 'das nas lo nyeer brgyad lon pa'i dus su /
NK028(sa)001:5384: rgyal po dza'i khang thog tu po ti dang glegs bam gyi char babs pa'i lo rgyus //
NK028(sa)001:5385: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa ji ltar byung ba'i tshul //
NK028(sa)001:5386: gdul bya la grags lugs kyi gleng gzhi bshad pas /
NK028(sa)001:5387: skal ldan rjes 'jug gis tshogs rnams yid ches te /
NK028(sa)001:5388: dkyil 'khor chen po'i 'di'i don ji ltar rtogs pa rnams dang 'brel ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:5389: yang 'khor los bsgyur rgyal rgyud byung ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:5390: spyi bor dbang bskur gleng gzhi yin /
NK028(sa)001:5391: re re la yang gleng gzhi dag /
NK028(sa)001:5392: rgyud rnams kun las rgyas par bshad /
NK028(sa)001:5394: gnas phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:5395: ston bka' 'khor phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:5396: yo byad phun gsum tshogs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:5397: dus phun sum tshogs pa dang lnga ni gong du zur tsam song ngo //
NK028(sa)001:5398: gsum pa bgegs brgyad bshad pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:5399: dper na chu rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag cing dngas pa la /
NK028(sa)001:5400: glo bur gyis bsnyogs mas bsnyogs nas /
NK028(sa)001:5402: 'byung chen gtos kyi nam mkha' rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa la /
NK028(sa)001:5403: glo bur gyis sprin dang khu rlangs kyis sgribs nas mi gsal ba bzhin /
NK028(sa)001:5404: chos nyid rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag cing gsal ba la /
NK028(sa)001:5405: glo bur gyi rnam par rtog pa'am /
NK028(sa)001:5406: bag chags sprin lta bur 'byung nas sgribs pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK028(sa)001:5407: sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos grub dang //
NK028(sa)001:5408: byin brlabs dbang chog 'byung ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:5409: dper na rgya mtsho dngas pa la //
NK028(sa)001:5410: nyi zla'i gzugs brnyan 'byung ba yang //
NK028(sa)001:5411: snyog ma chu yi gegs gyur bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:5412: byin rlabs dbang mchog 'byung ba'i gegs //
NK028(sa)001:5413: rnam pa brgyad du 'byung bar bshad //
NK028(sa)001:5416: sngon byung ston pa slob dpon la //
NK028(sa)001:5417: bka' gcog brnyas pa byed pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:5418: dbang dang dngos grub dam pa'i bgegs //
NK028(sa)001:5420: bla ma ni sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa'i sku //
NK028(sa)001:5421: dngos grub 'byung ba'i rtsa ba lags pas //
NK028(sa)001:5422: bka' gcog pa dang brnyas pa spangs bar bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:5423: bla med rdo rje 'gro ba'i spun /
NK028(sa)001:5424: 'khu ldog gdung ba'i sems med na /
NK028(sa)001:5425: dbang dang dngos grub bgegs gnyis pa //
NK028(sa)001:5426: zhes pa mched la brtse ba dang gdung ba'i sems cher bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:5427: byang chub lam la 'du 'bral med cing /
NK028(sa)001:5428: thar par 'dren pa'i lha spong ba /
NK028(sa)001:5429: dngos grub 'byung ba'i gegs gsum pa /
NK028(sa)001:5430: zhes pas don dam byang chub sems dang /
NK028(sa)001:5431: kun rdzob byang chub sems ma spong zhig /
NK028(sa)001:5432: de'i rtags yi dam lha dang nam yang 'bral bar ma byed cig /
NK028(sa)001:5433: snying rje'i yul gyur sems can la /
NK028(sa)001:5434: thag par gcod pa bgegs bzhi pa /
NK028(sa)001:5435: zhes pas khams gsum gyis sems can thams cad la snying rje'i thag pa ma bcad cig /
NK028(sa)001:5436: gsang sngags gsang ba'i lta spyod rnams /
NK028(sa)001:5437: yongs la byin pa lnga pa'i gegs /
NK028(sa)001:5439: snod kyis ma smin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:5440: zab pas ma smin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:5441: chos kyis ma smin pa la sogs pa snod du mi rung pa'i /
NK028(sa)001:5442: gang zag rnams la gsang sngags zab mo'i don ma bstan cig /
NK028(sa)001:5443: thar lam ston la bdud med cing //
NK028(sa)001:5444: ser snas bcings pa drug pa'i gegs /
NK028(sa)001:5446: dbang bskur ba'i bla ma la mos gus kyis dbang chags pa'i rten /
NK028(sa)001:5447: yon dbul ba la ser sna ma byed cig /
NK028(sa)001:5448: gzu lum dbang med las la spyod //
NK028(sa)001:5449: dngos grub 'byung ba'i gegs bdun pa /
NK028(sa)001:5451: bla ma'i bka' ma thob cing dbang ma bskur bar /
NK028(sa)001:5452: gsang sngags zab mo'i don la gzu lum dang ras chod ma byed cig /
NK028(sa)001:5453: 'dod pa'i khe grags lhur byed cing //
NK028(sa)001:5454: gsang ba'i dam tshig spong ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:5455: 'di ni brgyad pa'i bgegs su bstan /
NK028(sa)001:5457: 'dod pa dang khe grags lhur ma len par /
NK028(sa)001:5458: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig rin po che gser dang 'dra ba ma spongs zhing //
NK028(sa)001:5459: nyams pa 'di dag sus spongs ba //
NK028(sa)001:5460: dngos grub dbang gi snod du bshad //
NK028(sa)001:5461: 'di ltar khyed kyi rab brtan na //
NK028(sa)001:5462: bu khyod nang par 'dri byed pa //
NK028(sa)001:5463: dkyil 'khor drung du legs par nyol //
NK028(sa)001:5465: gegs brgyad bsal bar byed pa'i pra khrid //
NK028(sa)001:5466: snyan brgyud yi ge med pa'i gdams pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:5467: bzhi pa thugs dam bskang pa la gnyis te dang po /
NK028(sa)001:5468: phyi 'jig rten pa 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskangs pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:5469: dar phyar rol mo'i sgra sbyar la byin gyis brlabs te /
NK028(sa)001:5471: khyad par du gnas po gzhi bdag la /
NK028(sa)001:5472: gser skyems dang gtor ma byin la gnas po zhu /
NK028(sa)001:5473: gtsang rigs kyi mgon po bdun bcu rtsa gnyis la cha gsum btang la /
NK028(sa)001:5476: gzhan gyi lha 'dre thams cad la phud gtor byin la bsgrub pa chen po 'di dbu bzung nas /
NK028(sa)001:5477: mjug ma thon gyi bar la bar chad kyi sbyor pa zhi bar gyur cig par bka' bsgo /
NK028(sa)001:5478: khyad par du mgon po dang lha mo la gtong grogs kyis gcig par bka' bsgo /
NK028(sa)001:5479: dkon mchog gsum la gsol ba drag tu gdab /
NK028(sa)001:5480: gnyis pa nang gi thugs dam bskang ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:5481: cha gsum gyis dri chab khyer la /
NK028(sa)001:5484: mdos kyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs la phyi cha mthun sprul
NK028(sa)001:5485: pa'i ma mo gzhung gzhin mchod la bar chad bsrungs
NK028(sa)001:5487: nang ting nge 'dzin gyis bskyed pa'i ma mo yig
NK028(sa)001:5488: 'bru'i sgo nas ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed
NK028(sa)001:5489: la / ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs bstim
NK028(sa)001:5490: la mchod bstod 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab
NK028(sa)001:5491: la / / gsang ba thig le'i ma mo gsang ba'i tsan+t+ra li'i man ngag gis rtsa rlung gcun /
NK028(sa)001:5492: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i ma mo mkha' klong gnyis med du la zla'o //
NK028(sa)001:5493: spyi don gnyis pa nub gnyis pa sta gon la /
NK028(sa)001:5495: sa gzhi mnyam dang ces gsungs pas gnyis te /
NK028(sa)001:5496: bka' bkod kyi rim pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:5497: cho ga la 'jug pa'i rim pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:5500: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su ba byung lnga dang /
NK028(sa)001:5501: 'og ma yengs sum cu'i chag chag gdab /
NK028(sa)001:5502: lha'i bzhugs gnas mi 'chug pa'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:5503: thig ci rigs par gdab la /
NK028(sa)001:5504: mkhar yor gyi nang du phud la a mri ta dang /
NK028(sa)001:5511: snyug ma'i mgo srin bal lam dar dkar gyis pir byas la dri'i nang du bcug cing /
NK028(sa)001:5512: thig le lha gtso bo rnams kyi bzhugs gnas su gru bzhi bya /
NK028(sa)001:5513: 'khor rnams kyi bzhugs gnas su zlum po /
NK028(sa)001:5514: khro bo rnams kyi bzhugs gnas su gru gsum byas la /
NK028(sa)001:5515: thig le rnams kyi nang du nas kyi tshom bu re re bkod de /
NK028(sa)001:5521: badz+ra tsit+ta h+aum a a a /
NK028(sa)001:5522: badz+ra b+ha tra sa man+ta a /
NK028(sa)001:5523: dbus su kun bzung yab yum gyi tshom bu bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5524: a kra ma h+aa kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5525: ma ta ma h+aa krod+ha shwa ri h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5526: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5527: ces brjod la de'i mdun du bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5534: zhes mi bskyod pa yab yum gyi tshom bu bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5537: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5538: badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5539: de'i mdun du badz+ra he ru ka yab yum bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5549: rigs bzhi yab yum gyi tshom bu bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5552: ham la s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK028(sa)001:5554: tram ma le sa ma ya ho /
NK028(sa)001:5555: h+r+aihha ho pad+ma ba da ma /
NK028(sa)001:5557: dz+ram ku ru p+aa ni h+r+ai /
NK028(sa)001:5558: a nirti r+aa ga ya mi /
NK028(sa)001:5559: nang gi sems dpa' yab yum bzhi bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5561: mee d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa dzah d+hu pa pra be sha ya /
NK028(sa)001:5562: th+l+him ni pa ra b+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:5563: h+aum pash+pe a be sha ya /
NK028(sa)001:5564: h+aum sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:5565: bam d+ai pa su khi ni /
NK028(sa)001:5566: m+aum shi a ram ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:5568: phyi'i lha snams la sems dpa' yab yum bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5570: mu ne h+aum trum s+w+aa h+aa mu ne sum s+w+aa
NK028(sa)001:5571: h+aa mu ne bram swa h+aa ma ne k+sham s+w+aa
NK028(sa)001:5572: h+aa ma ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:5576: badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:5577: pradz+ny+aa na ta krita h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:5578: rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri dz+wa
NK028(sa)001:5579: la ni h+aum phata pad+mana ta krita h+aum phata pad+ma
NK028(sa)001:5580: d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri dz+wa la
NK028(sa)001:5581: ni h+aum phata / b+hig+nana ta krita h+aum phata kar+m+ma
NK028(sa)001:5582: d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri dz+wa la
NK028(sa)001:5583: ni h+aum phata / ni h+aum phata / sgo ba yab yum bzhi bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5584: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad kyi shar gyi rtsibs bzhi la /
NK028(sa)001:5585: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK028(sa)001:5586: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK028(sa)001:5587: pad+ma kro d+hi shwa ri he ru ka /
NK028(sa)001:5588: pad+ma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK028(sa)001:5590: kar+m+ma kro d+hi shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK028(sa)001:5591: he ru ka yab yum bzhi bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:5593: ma h+aa rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+ta
NK028(sa)001:5594: sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa
NK028(sa)001:5595: h+aum phatah ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5596: bi shi ka h+aum phata s+w+aa h+aa e sha ra sid+h+ri na ma s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:5597: ma h+aa yak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK028(sa)001:5598: ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da
NK028(sa)001:5599: ha pa tsa h+aum phatah ma h+aa yak+sha kro d+hi
NK028(sa)001:5600: shwa ri h+aum phatah bi she ka s+w+aa h+aah e
NK028(sa)001:5601: sha ra sid+d+hi na ma hih ma h+aa ka ya
NK028(sa)001:5603: ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tata ka ha na da ha
NK028(sa)001:5604: pa tsa h+aum phatah ma h+aa gu h+ya kro d+hi
NK028(sa)001:5605: shwa ri dz+ai la ni h+aum phatah bi she ka
NK028(sa)001:5606: s+w+aa h+aa / e ka sha ra sid+d+ha na ma /
NK028(sa)001:5608: ma ga la sa ti h+aumh he ru ka bzhi bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:5615: badz+ra p+auk+ka si hah badz+ra gasma r+ai hah badz+ra sma
NK028(sa)001:5616: sh+aa n+ai hah badz+ra tsan+da l+ai hah zhes gnas kyi
NK028(sa)001:5618: 'khyams dang po'i phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad sgo bzhi dang bcu gnyis la /
NK028(sa)001:5621: badz+ra sh+ri ga la mu kh+ai he /
NK028(sa)001:5622: badz+ra shwa na mu kh+ai he /
NK028(sa)001:5624: badz+ra kam ka mu kh+ai he /
NK028(sa)001:5626: badz+ra hu lu mu khi he /
NK028(sa)001:5627: yul gyi lha mo brgyad dang sgo bzhi dang bcu gnyis su /
NK028(sa)001:5628: badz+ra a pra ti ta +aar+ya ni tsa tur ta ra phata /
NK028(sa)001:5630: badz+ra kha kha mu kha sha ra ya y+aa na ma h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5631: sh+ri badz+ra ra ga sa ma yo na ma h+aum //
NK028(sa)001:5632: sh+r+ai badz+ra kha to kha pra la ya y+aa na ma h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5633: badz+ra gan+d+ha pra dza la ya y+aa na ma h+aumh spor mo brgyad /
NK028(sa)001:5634: gsang yum bzhi dang bcu gnyis bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5635: bar khyams gsum par shar du bdun /
NK028(sa)001:5638: byang du bdun gyi gnas su /
NK028(sa)001:5639: b+h+yo badz+ra me na r+aa k+sha si /
