NK028(sa)001:5656: badz+ra ma h+aa ma ra na /
NK028(sa)001:5666: zhes dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5671: byang du brgyad de so gnyis kyi gnas su /
NK028(sa)001:5672: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5673: kro d+ha kro ti shwa ri h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5674: badz+ra ma h+aa he ma ba ti h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5675: badz+ra ku m+aa ra pri ye h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5680: ma h+aa a mri tod pa t+ai h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5683: ma h+aa ra ma mi h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5684: ma h+aa mri ti ka pa la has te ta ki h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5686: pri ta pu ta dan+ta ri h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5694: dza du ma ya bas h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5695: ta ki bi ka te h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5697: ka li pra be sha h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5703: badz+ra sa b+han a ki h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5704: zhes mkha' 'gro ma sum cu so gnyis bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5705: bar khyams lnga par shar lho nub gsum du gnyis gnyis //
NK028(sa)001:5707: sgo bzhi ste bcu gcig gis gnas su ma ma
NK028(sa)001:5708: d+ha du 'di cig gcig gis sngags 'phral ma gzigs
NK028(sa)001:5709: h+aum bdun dang / badz+ra dun ting b+h+yoo /
NK028(sa)001:5710: zhes ma bdun sring bzhi bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5711: khyams drug pa la shar nub tu bzhi bcu zhe bzhi /
NK028(sa)001:5714: ging ka ra ha ha ru lu b+h+yo /
NK028(sa)001:5716: ging pho dgu ging mo dgu ste bco brgyad bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5717: de'i phyir mis khyams bdun pa la /
NK028(sa)001:5721: byang du bco lnga ste drug cu'i gnas su kro d+ha kro d+hi h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:5723: steng gi khro bo khro mo drug cu bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5728: byang du drug cu'i gnas su //
NK028(sa)001:5729: shar du rba na rba na a gu sha dzahdzah /
NK028(sa)001:5730: lhor ha la ha la pa sha h+aum //
NK028(sa)001:5731: nub tu gardza gardza s+pho ta bam //
NK028(sa)001:5732: byang du pa tsa pa tsa g+han+d+ha ho /
NK028(sa)001:5733: zhes pho nya drug bcu pa tshan bzhi bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5738: byang du bco lnga ste drug bcu'i gnas su /
NK028(sa)001:5740: drug cu brjod la 'og phyogs kyi ma ma mo drug bcu bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5744: pad+ma man+dala zhes dri'i thig le bya /
NK028(sa)001:5745: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ram zhes rgyud lung
NK028(sa)001:5746: man ngag gi bla ma rig 'dzin gyi tshom bu
NK028(sa)001:5748: de ltar 'dus pa mdo tshom bu thon nas //
NK028(sa)001:5749: rdzogs chen sems sde'i tshom bu la /
NK028(sa)001:5750: dkyil 'khor dbus su rkang gsum gyi thog tu shing leb kyi gdan nam /
NK028(sa)001:5751: ka to ra sas bkang pa'i steng du /
NK028(sa)001:5752: dri bzang gi thig le dang //
NK028(sa)001:5753: a bco brgyad brjod la dbus su tshom bu gnyis //
NK028(sa)001:5754: de'i phyi rol du bcu drug ste bco brgyad bkod //
NK028(sa)001:5755: de nas mdo'i dkyil 'khor gyi byang shar du /
NK028(sa)001:5756: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshom bu bzhi
NK028(sa)001:5757: bcu rtsa gnyis sngags dang bcas pa gong dang mthun
NK028(sa)001:5758: no // byang du khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshom bu la /
NK028(sa)001:5759: sngags gong dang mthun pa la lnga bcu rtsa brgyad bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5760: zhi khro 'di gnyis la rgyas par spro na zhi
NK028(sa)001:5761: ba'i dkyil 'khor bsdus pa la lha bco brgyad kyi
NK028(sa)001:5762: tshom bu / 'bring po la bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis gong gi de kho'o //
NK028(sa)001:5763: rgyas pa la brgyad cu rtsa gnyis kyi tshom bu bkod //
NK028(sa)001:5764: tshom bu gcig pa la lha bco brgyad kyi tshom bu bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5765: tshom bu gsum pa la lha bzhi bcu zhe drug gi tshom bu bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5766: tshom bu lnga pa la lha bdun cu bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5767: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsdus pa la lha lnga bcu
NK028(sa)001:5768: rtsa brgyad kyi tshom bu bkod de gong gi de
NK028(sa)001:5769: ka yin / 'bring po la drug cu rtsa brgyad kyi tshom bu bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5770: rgyas pa la brgya bco brgyad kyi tshom bu bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5771: tshom bu gcig pa la bdun cu rtsa brgyad kyi tshom bu /
NK028(sa)001:5772: gsum pa la dgu bcu rtsa brgyad kyi tshom bu /
NK028(sa)001:5773: lnga pa la brgya bco brgyad kyi tshom bu bkod do //
NK028(sa)001:5774: lho nub du byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor la dbus su thub pa /
NK028(sa)001:5778: byang gi pad 'dab la spyan ras gzigs kyi tshom bu ste lnga /
NK028(sa)001:5780: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi tshom bu bcu /
NK028(sa)001:5781: nub byang du yo ga'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK028(sa)001:5782: dbus su rnam par snang mdzad la gsang yum bzhi ste /
NK028(sa)001:5786: las kyi sems ma dang lnga'i tshom bu bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5787: shar gyi gtso bo mi ba skyod pa /
NK028(sa)001:5788: phyogs bzhir rigs chung gi sems dpa' ste /
NK028(sa)001:5792: rdo rje legs pa ste tshom bu lnga bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5797: rdo rje gzhad pa ste lnga bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5798: nub snang ba mtha' yas la /
NK028(sa)001:5802: rdo rje smra ba ste lnga bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5803: byang don yod grub pa la /
NK028(sa)001:5807: rdo rje khu tshur ste lnga bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5823: nub tu kri ya'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK028(sa)001:5824: dbus su phyag na rdo rje ste /
NK028(sa)001:5827: 'jam dbyangs ste tshom bu gsum bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5828: de'i phyi rol du zur bzhir gtum po lha bzhi /
NK028(sa)001:5831: khro bo bcu'i tshom bu bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5832: lhor rang rgyal gyi dkyil 'khor la /
NK028(sa)001:5833: dbus su thub pa la pad 'dab bcu gnyis la /
NK028(sa)001:5838: shar lhor nyan thos kyi dkyil 'khor la /
NK028(sa)001:5839: dbus su thub pa de'i phyi rol phyogs bzhir 'khor rnam bzhi /
NK028(sa)001:5840: de'i phyi'i rol nyan thos bcu drug ste nyi shu rtsa gcig bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5842: shar du lha mi'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK028(sa)001:5845: de'i phyi rol gleng gzhi gling phran brgyad dang bcu gnyis la /
NK028(sa)001:5847: pho nya mngag gzhugs dang bcas pa la sogs bcu gnyis te bcu bdun gyi tshom bu bkod /
NK028(sa)001:5848: gong gi tshom bu de rnams la dri'i thig le dang /
NK028(sa)001:5849: s+aur+ya tsan+da sogs dang rang rang gi sngags rnams brjod dgos so //
NK028(sa)001:5850: de nas bum pa bkod pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:5851: rin po che la sogs pa'i bum pa rgyas par na lha grangs dang mnyam pa dgos shing /
NK028(sa)001:5853: bum pa ci rigs pa bsags la /
NK028(sa)001:5855: gu gul gyis bdug pa la /
NK028(sa)001:5857: nang du bum sman nyi shu rtsa lnga dang chu blugs /
NK028(sa)001:5858: ras sam dar gyis mgul chings bcings /
NK028(sa)001:5860: dung chos dang gzungs thag rdo rje dang bcas pa yang bzhag /
NK028(sa)001:5861: de yang rdzogs chen sems sde'i dbang la dgos pa'i
NK028(sa)001:5862: bum pa bco brgyad la a bco brgyad bris la
NK028(sa)001:5863: / tshom bu bco brgyad kyi steng ngam phyi rol du bkod do //
NK028(sa)001:5864: 'dus pa mdo dbang la dgos pa'i bum pa lnga la rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan bris pa /
NK028(sa)001:5865: rgya gram bris pa'i las bum dang bcas pa ji ltar 'os par bsham /
NK028(sa)001:5866: sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i dbang rgyas bsdus la /
NK028(sa)001:5867: dgos pa'i bum pa yang gang bder bsham /
NK028(sa)001:5870: byang chub sems dpa'i dbang dang /
NK028(sa)001:5873: lha mi'i dbang dang drug gi bum pa yang re re bsham mo /
NK028(sa)001:5874: ka pa la bkod pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:5875: mdo dbang dang sgyu 'phrul zhi ba la bum pa bkod cing /
NK028(sa)001:5876: khro bo'i bum pa la ka p+aa la bkod dgos te //
NK028(sa)001:5877: ka pa la'i nang du mgo ma yang sum cu'i bum rdzas blugs la /
NK028(sa)001:5878: mdo dbang la dgos pa'i ka p+aa la lnga /
NK028(sa)001:5879: rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan bris la /
NK028(sa)001:5880: sgyu 'phrul khro bo la dgos pa'i ka pa la lnga ste bcu bum pa bcu'i thog tu bsham /
NK028(sa)001:5881: de'i steng du me long sin d+hu ras byugs pa bcus bkab /
NK028(sa)001:5882: de bcu'i steng du dar dmar po kha bcus dgab /
NK028(sa)001:5883: de bcu'i steng du rdo rje bcu bzhag go /
NK028(sa)001:5885: mchod rdzas la dgos pa'i ka p+aa la rnams kyang ji ltar 'os pa bsham mo /
NK028(sa)001:5886: rdo rje dril bu la sogs phyag chad dang /
NK028(sa)001:5887: rol cha rnams kyang gang der bsham mo //
NK028(sa)001:5888: snod lnga'i nang du tshon rtsi lnga byug la /
NK028(sa)001:5893: ljang khu la ha bris la gang bder bzhag go /
NK028(sa)001:5894: snod lnga'i nang du ye shes kyi thig skud sngon po /
NK028(sa)001:5897: dmar po ljang khu dang lnga bzhag pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:5898: snod gsum gyi nang du las kyi thig dkar po dang /
NK028(sa)001:5900: sngon po dang gsum bzhag la gang bder bsham mo //
NK028(sa)001:5901: de nas mchod pa bshams pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:5902: dkyil 'khor gyi byang shar du 'tshams 'dzin gyi me tog /
NK028(sa)001:5909: byang du zhal zas rnams bsham /
NK028(sa)001:5910: gzhan yang gong gi bum pa la sogs gang bshams
NK028(sa)001:5911: rnams la mchod pa brgyad po chu re res bskor
NK028(sa)001:5912: / gzhan yang 'byor na lha grangs dang mnyam pa'i mchod pa cha re re 'am /
NK028(sa)001:5914: de nas gtor ma bshams pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:5915: shar lhor bla ma'i gtor ma //
NK028(sa)001:5916: shar du yi dam gyi gtor ma /
NK028(sa)001:5921: byang shar du mkha' 'gro'i gtor ma /
NK028(sa)001:5926: lhor tshogs kyi gtor ma rnams la zas sna'i tshogs kyis bskor ba bsham /
NK028(sa)001:5927: gtor ma de rnams chab dang chang gis bran no /
NK028(sa)001:5928: de'i phyi rol du mda' brgyad dar sna dang bcas pa /
NK028(sa)001:5929: ral gri brgyad me long dang bcas pa /
NK028(sa)001:5930: phur pa brgyad cod pan dang bcas pa gzugs la /
NK028(sa)001:5931: tshon skud kyi dra bas sbrel /
NK028(sa)001:5933: mtha' dkris rgyab tu dkar gtor cha bzhi bsham /
NK028(sa)001:5934: ka ba'i rgyan la sogs pa bar snang gi brgyan dang /
NK028(sa)001:5935: gdugs dang bla res la sogs gnam gyi brgyan rnams bsham mo //
NK028(sa)001:5936: dbang rdzas kyi rim pa la /
NK028(sa)001:5959: dril bu la sogs nang dbang gi rdzas rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:5960: zab dbang gi rdzas phyag rgya ma mtshan dang ldan pa lo bcu gnyis ma /
NK028(sa)001:5963: 'tsho ba zas kyi yo byad la sogs gang dgos bsog /
NK028(sa)001:5964: sbyin sreg la dgos pa'i cha rkyen rnams kyang gang bder bsham mo //
NK028(sa)001:5965: gnyis pa cho ga la 'jug pa bcu gcig ste /
NK028(sa)001:5969: ka p+aa la sta gon dang /
NK028(sa)001:5970: rdo rje dril bu la sogs pa sta gon dang /
NK028(sa)001:5977: dang po bdag bskyed slob dpon sta gon ni //
NK028(sa)001:5978: byang chub kyi sems kun tu bzang po la na mo /
NK028(sa)001:5979: sngags kyi zhi khro rnam pa gnyis /
NK028(sa)001:5980: rnal 'byor pa rgan po rnams kyi don du rgyud lung du bsgyur te bsgrub sla bar mdzad pa /
NK028(sa)001:5981: de yang lus la lha bkod de yid kyis gsal btab nas /
NK028(sa)001:5982: na mo h+aum gis gzi byin bskyed ces 'byung ngo //
NK028(sa)001:5983: de la dang po p+au dza ci 'byor pa bsham pa 'ung nas /
NK028(sa)001:5984: sgo gsum gyi bsdus pa'i dngos po cir snang yang /
NK028(sa)001:5985: ma bcos par sems nyid stong pa nyid du gsal ba las /
NK028(sa)001:5986: zhe sdang rdo rje dran nas /
NK028(sa)001:5987: las kyi phyogs bcur nyi ma'i steng phyogs bskyong bcu mnan la /
NK028(sa)001:5988: de'i steng du bdag skad cig gis zhe sdang rdo rjer gsal ba'i thugs ka'i h+aum las /
NK028(sa)001:5989: badz+ra kro d+ha ki la ya h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:5991: ya man+ta krita ma h+aa kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:5992: ces pa la sogs pas khro bo bcu bkod de /
NK028(sa)001:5993: smad lcags kyi phur pa zur gsum la thal phyung nas brtan par bzhugs gsol /
NK028(sa)001:5994: h+aum gang zag sha yi phung po cir snang yang /
NK028(sa)001:5995: yi dam lha ru bsgom pa'i byin brlabs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:5996: bdag nyid sems can yin pa'i don rtogs nas /
NK028(sa)001:5997: sangs rgyas sa gsum lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:5998: phyogs mtshams steng 'og dngos po cir snang yang /
NK028(sa)001:5999: khro bo yab yam sgom pa'i byin brlabs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:6000: phyogs bcur gnas pa'i bgegs rnams kun bsgral nas /
NK028(sa)001:6001: sid+d+hi bar gcod ming yang med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6002: na mo h+aum 'ung nas h+aum gi 'od kyis rgyal
NK028(sa)001:6003: ba kun bsdus la phyag bya bsngo dang sems bskyed
NK028(sa)001:6004: do // h+aum sgrib pa rnam gnyis dngos po cir snang yang /
NK028(sa)001:6005: yid kyi dngos su gshegs pa'i byin brlabs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:6006: sgrib pa ye nas rtogs pa'i don rtogs nas /
NK028(sa)001:6007: ye shes rnam gnyis mngon du gsal bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:6009: 'ung nas phung po la che mchog bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:6010: kha la rta mgrin yab yam bskyed la /
NK028(sa)001:6011: badz+ra a mri ta +aah h+aum h+r+aih tha /
NK028(sa)001:6015: de la rim par babs pas rta mgrin gyi rol
NK028(sa)001:6016: pa'i byang chub sems bdud rtsi 'khyil pas gsang gtor
NK028(sa)001:6017: bya'o // 'ung nas gtor ma dang rak+ta brlabs pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:6018: h+aum bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams cir snang yang /
NK028(sa)001:6019: bdud rtsi sman mchog bsgrubs shing brtson pa'i mthus /
NK028(sa)001:6020: yun du rlags lta'i gnod pa kun bsal nas /
NK028(sa)001:6021: skye shi med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6024: brgyad khri bzhi stong gdon rnams cir snang yang /
NK028(sa)001:6025: tshogs dang gtor mas mchod pa'i byin brlabs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:6026: 'phral du skabs 'tshol gnod pa kun bsal nas /
NK028(sa)001:6027: 'pho 'gyur med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6030: thun mong rdzas kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6031: mchod pa byin gyis rlabs pa'i nus mthu yis //
NK028(sa)001:6032: 'dod pa'i yon tan mngon du rdzogs gyur nas //
NK028(sa)001:6033: dus gsum bde gshegs ma lus mchod par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6035: 'ung nas sems dang dbugs khrag sha rus mgo bo kun //
NK028(sa)001:6036: dur khrod kyi dkyil 'khor du shes par byas la /
NK028(sa)001:6037: b+h+rum bi sha bi shud+d+he dz+ny+aa na tsakra ces pas
NK028(sa)001:6038: 'byung ba dang bcas pa gzhal yas khang du gsal
NK028(sa)001:6039: du ti nan rat+na tsa s+aur+ya tsan+t+ra man+dala /
NK028(sa)001:6040: zhes so so'i gdan kun bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:6041: 'ung nas so so'i sngags brjod pa'am yid la dran
NK028(sa)001:6042: pa tsam gyis lha rnams yan lag gi lha dang
NK028(sa)001:6043: bcas pa gdan la gsal lo //
NK028(sa)001:6044: yang na snying la rigs lnga //
NK028(sa)001:6045: g.yas pa rnam shes kyi sems dpa' //
NK028(sa)001:6046: g.yon pa dbang po'i sems dpa' /
NK028(sa)001:6047: spyi bo la sogs par thub pa drug mdun rgyab tu bya byed yab yam du gsal lo //
NK028(sa)001:6048: de dag re re bskyed cing gsal gdab pa /
NK028(sa)001:6050: snod kyi lo ka 'byung pa cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6051: gzhal yas dbang chen bsgoms pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6052: chos nyid mtha' dbus med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6053: 'og min gnas su lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6055: 'gro ba'i lus ngag yid gsum cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6056: yongs rdzogs ting 'dzin bsgoms pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6057: cho ga rnam pa gsum gyi don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6058: sku gsung thugs su lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6060: h+aum phung po lnga dang 'byung lnga cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6061: rigs lnga yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6062: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6063: thabs shes 'bral med lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6064: na mo h+aum rnam shes dbang po'i yul du cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6065: sems dpa' sems mar bsgoms pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6066: thams cad lha dang lha mo'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6067: zhing dang spyod yul yongs dag lhun grub shog /
NK028(sa)001:6069: yid dang chos kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6070: kun bzang yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6071: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6072: chos sku 'gyur med lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6074: 'gro ba rigs drug dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6075: thub pa drug tu bsgoms pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6076: rang rig spyir yang sprul pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6077: sangs rgyas mdzad pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6079: yan lag bzhi yi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6080: sgo ba yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6081: bar gcod gdug pa ma lus kun bsal nas /
NK028(sa)001:6082: 'phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6084: 'ung nas sa man dza dang e h+ya his spyan drangs sngags bzhis bstim /
NK028(sa)001:6086: h+aum sangs rgyas sems can dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6087: bde gshegs spyan drangs stims pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6088: ye nas sangs rgyas yin pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6089: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6092: nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags dang /
NK028(sa)001:6093: a ha ra zhes zhabs bsil lha mo bzhi sngags rgyas dbul /
NK028(sa)001:6094: h+aum lha dang bdag dang gzhan du cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6095: dkyil 'khor lha mo mchod pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6096: 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6097: dngos grub rnam gsum lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6099: 'ung nas sngags dang ma h+aa pany+tsa amri ta h+aum zhes sman dbul 'bru gsum blangs sngags bya /
NK028(sa)001:6100: h+aum bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams cir bdud rtsi
NK028(sa)001:6101: sman mchog mchod pa'i yun du glags lta'i gnod pa
NK028(sa)001:6102: kun bral nas // skye 'chi med par lhun gyis grub par na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:6103: 'ung nas ma h+aa ba ling ta kh+ai hi /
NK028(sa)001:6106: stong phrag brgyad cu'i bgegs rnams cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6107: tshogs dang gtor mas mchod pa'i byin 'phral du skabs 'tshol gnod pa kun bral nas //
NK028(sa)001:6108: 'gyur ba med par lhun na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:6110: h+aum chags sdang rnam gnyis dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6111: tan gan rnam gnyis phul ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6112: nyon mongs dug gsum btsad nas dag gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:6113: bdag gzhan don gnyis lhun na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:6114: 'ung nas ma h+aa p+au dza ho //
NK028(sa)001:6116: h+aum yul dang dbang po dngos po cir 'dod yon
NK028(sa)001:6117: rnam lnga mchod pa'i yul sems gnyis su med pa'i
NK028(sa)001:6118: don rtogs nas // spyod yul ma lus yongs su dag par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6120: 'ung nas smon lam bsdus la gdab /
NK028(sa)001:6122: 'ung nas sku ci gsal du byas la so so'i 'dzab bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:6124: rgyu dang 'bras rtsol bsnyen bsgrub rdzogs pa'i 'dzab bsnyen 'phul ba'i mthus /
NK028(sa)001:6125: thams cad kun tu bzang po'i don 'bras bu rnam gsum lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6128: zhi ba'i 'dren pa'i las byang chung le'o //
NK028(sa)001:6129: sh+ri he ru ka la na mo //
NK028(sa)001:6130: khro bo'i lung la rang gi sgo gsum sems nyid
NK028(sa)001:6131: rang byung ye shes ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs
NK028(sa)001:6133: sems dang dbug khrag sha rus drod rnams ye shes
NK028(sa)001:6134: kyi dur khrod kyi ngo bo la sngags brjod pas
NK028(sa)001:6136: b+h+rum bi sha b+hi shud d+he ban d+ha dz+ny+aa na
NK028(sa)001:6137: tsakra zhes pas gzhal yas khang rtsibs brgyad par gsol
NK028(sa)001:6143: sha rus ban+d+ha'i dngos po cir snang yang /
NK028(sa)001:6144: 'bar ba'i gzhal yas sgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:6145: rdzas su snang ba'i bag chags kun sbyangs nas /
NK028(sa)001:6146: gnas mchog bkra shis lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6148: 'ung nas tsit+ta dgu'i bcud h+aum mthing ga dgu las he ru ka dgur bskyed do //
NK028(sa)001:6150: ru tra rnam gsum dngos po cir he ru dgu
NK028(sa)001:6151: ru bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs bdud dang srin po'i bar
NK028(sa)001:6153: ye shes dgu ru lhun na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:6154: sa dgu las yum dgu 'khril bar bskyed de /
NK028(sa)001:6156: khams gsum sa dgu'i dngos po cir yum chen dgu ru bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6157: ma bdun sring mo'i bar chad kun bsgral nas //
NK028(sa)001:6158: ma chen dgu ru lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6160: rnam shes brgyad la ha brgyad brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:6162: h+aum rnam shes brgyad kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6163: ma mo brgyad du sgoms pa'i byin rlabs mngon par rtogs pa'i bag chags kun byang nas //
NK028(sa)001:6164: ye shes chen po brgyad du gsal bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:6166: dur khrod brgyad la he brgyad brjod pas //
NK028(sa)001:6167: phra men yul ma brgyad du gsal lo //
NK028(sa)001:6168: h+aum dur khrod brgyad kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6169: phra men brgyad du sgoms pa'i byin /
NK028(sa)001:6170: dam tshig nyams dang dgra bgegs kun bsgral nas //
NK028(sa)001:6171: rnal 'byor bar chad ming yang med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6174: skye rgas na 'chi'i du kha cir sgo ma bzhi
NK028(sa)001:6175: ru sgom pa'i byin bar du gcod pa'i bdud bzhi
NK028(sa)001:6176: kun bcom nas // skye gnas rnam bzhi'i ming yang med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6178: lus kyi phyogs mtshams la ri brgyad brjod de spor mar gsal lo //
NK028(sa)001:6179: h+aum phyogs mtshams brgyad kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6180: spor ma brgyad du bsgoms pa'i /
NK028(sa)001:6181: lha srin sde brgyad bar chad kun bsgral nas //
NK028(sa)001:6182: lo ga bar chad ming yang med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6184: dngas ma bzhi'i bam ram yam kham brjod pas gsang ba'i yum bzhir bskyed de /
NK028(sa)001:6186: 'byung bzhi'i dngas ma cir snang gsang ba yum bzhir bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs gyis //
NK028(sa)001:6187: bem por lta ba'i dngos po kun gsal nas //
NK028(sa)001:6188: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6191: so sum cu rtsa gnyis la /
NK028(sa)001:6193: dbang phyug ma dang d+aak+ki mar gsal lo //
NK028(sa)001:6194: h+aum so dang sgal tshigs dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6195: dbang phyug dak+ki bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6196: lo zla mi mthun gnod pa kun bsal nas //
NK028(sa)001:6197: bar chad bdud kyi du kha med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6199: rtsa dang sha khrag la ma brjod pas //
NK028(sa)001:6200: ma mo dang sring bzhir gsal lo //
NK028(sa)001:6201: h+aum rtsa dang sha khrag dngos po ma dang sring
NK028(sa)001:6202: mor sgoms pa'i tshe srog gnod pa'i bar chad kun
NK028(sa)001:6203: bsal nas // nyin mtshan rtag tu thams cad bsrungs bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:6205: dbu rtsibs ha la ging gsal lo //
NK028(sa)001:6206: h+aum gnod cing bsam sbyor ngan pa cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6207: ging chen bco brgyad ba sgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6208: ki kang gshed bzhi'i gnod pa kun rnam par rtog pa'i bar gcod med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6210: rus pa la h+aum h+aum brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:6211: khro bo khro mo drug cu gsal lo //
NK028(sa)001:6212: h+aum kem rus tshogs kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6213: khro bo khro mor bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:6214: khams gsum gdug pa ma lus kun bsgral nas //
NK028(sa)001:6215: drag po'i 'phrin las lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6217: rtsa gsum brgya la h+aum sum brgya brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:6218: pho nya gsum brgya drug cu gsal lo //
NK028(sa)001:6219: h+aum rtsa dang bcud kyi dngos po cir pho nya
NK028(sa)001:6220: sum brgya drug cu bsgoms pa'i dgra dang bgegs kyi
NK028(sa)001:6222: bdag dang gzhan don lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6224: skra dang bas spu la rig 'dzin gsal lo //
NK028(sa)001:6225: h+aum skra dang ba spu dngos po cir /
NK028(sa)001:6227: rdo rje 'chang gral rim par gnon mdzad nas //
NK028(sa)001:6228: gzung 'dzin log rtog ming yang med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6230: 'ung nas e h+ya hi sh+r+ai he ru ka e a ra li hring /
NK028(sa)001:6235: sngags dang tshogs la spyi ltar bya /
NK028(sa)001:6236: phyag rgya bzhis stims bstan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:6237: h+aum sangs rgyas sems can dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6238: bde gshegs spyan drangs bstim pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6239: ye nas sangs rgyas yin pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6240: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6242: 'ung nas nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags dang //
NK028(sa)001:6243: a ha zhes zhabs bsil dang /
NK028(sa)001:6244: lha mo bzhi'i sngags dang phyag rgyas dbul /
NK028(sa)001:6245: h+aum lha dang bdag dang gzhan du cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6246: dkyil 'khor lha la mchod pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6247: 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6248: dngos grub rnam gsum lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6250: 'ung nas sngags dang ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ti h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:6253: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK028(sa)001:6254: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK028(sa)001:6255: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK028(sa)001:6256: ye shes lnga rdzogs bsgrubs pa'i rdzas //
NK028(sa)001:6257: rgyud lnga sems can kun grol ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:6258: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK028(sa)001:6259: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK028(sa)001:6260: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen gyis //
NK028(sa)001:6261: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskangs pa'i mchog /
NK028(sa)001:6262: ces che ba'i yon tan bsams la //
NK028(sa)001:6263: thog mar rtsa ba'i bla ma dang sgyu 'phrul gyi bla ma rnams kyi mtshan dngos su brjod la //
NK028(sa)001:6264: bdud rtsi g.yon pa'i theb srin gyis blangs la smin mtshams su gtor /
NK028(sa)001:6265: 'di ni sngon gyis dam tshig che /
NK028(sa)001:6266: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK028(sa)001:6267: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskul ba'i mchog /
NK028(sa)001:6268: sku gsung thugs kyis ngang nyid 'di //
NK028(sa)001:6269: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lag na //
NK028(sa)001:6270: thugs rjes dgongs nas bzhengs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:6271: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK028(sa)001:6272: 'phrul gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:6273: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa argam pra tits+tsha ho //
NK028(sa)001:6274: sh+ri bin kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK028(sa)001:6275: h+aum tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal chen he ru ka /
NK028(sa)001:6276: 'bar ba'i rgyal po khrag 'thung lnga rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:6277: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:6278: thugs rjes che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK028(sa)001:6279: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK028(sa)001:6280: dpal chen sku la gnyis med lhun sbyor ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:6281: kro d+hi shwa ri la sogs yum chen lnga rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:6282: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:6283: thugs rjes che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK028(sa)001:6284: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK028(sa)001:6285: mthing ga mchog rnams rdo rje gsang ba'i yum //
NK028(sa)001:6286: ke ri la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:6287: rnam dag bdud rtsi thugs rje che dgongs dbang ma
NK028(sa)001:6288: h+aa pany+tsa a mri rdo rje mchog brnyan za byed
NK028(sa)001:6289: mche gshogs can // sing ha la sogs phra men brgyad rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:6290: rnam dag thugs rje ma h+aa sarba sgo bzhi rab rngam rdo rje gdong mo'i tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:6291: rta gdong la sogs sgo ma bzhi rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:6292: rnam dag thugs rje ma h+aa sarba /
NK028(sa)001:6293: khams gsum ma lus sgrol ba'i las mdzad ma //
NK028(sa)001:6294: phyogs mtshams skyongs pa'i spor ma brgyad rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:6295: rnam dag thugs rje ma h+aa dpal chen sku la gnyis med dgyes par 'khril //
NK028(sa)001:6296: ye shes thugs kyi dgyes sde bzhi rnams la /
NK028(sa)001:6297: rnam thugs rje ma h+aa 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po'i mtha' bsrungs pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:6298: dam can dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad la //
NK028(sa)001:6299: rnam dag thugs rje ma h+aa 'phrin las ma lus sgrub byed pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:6300: nam mkhar 'gro ba so gnyis la /
NK028(sa)001:6301: rnam dag thugs rje ma h+aa ma mo chen po bdun rnams dang //
NK028(sa)001:6302: sring mo chen mo bzhi rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:6306: zhing bcu gtan nas len mdzad pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:6307: rdo rje ka tar ging chen bco brgyad la //
NK028(sa)001:6308: khams gsum gdug pa ma lus 'dul ba yi //
NK028(sa)001:6309: khro bo khro mo rol ba'i tshogs rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:6312: dgra bgegs ma lus 'gugs pa'i las byed pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:6313: mgyogs 'gro pho nya sum brgya drug cu la //
NK028(sa)001:6317: rdo rje 'chang gral rim par sa non pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:6318: rnal 'byor dbang phyug rig 'dzin tshogs rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:6322: lce yi rdo rje dam tshig la //
NK028(sa)001:6323: rdo rje can gyi h+aum bsgoms te //
NK028(sa)001:6324: bdud rtsi lnga las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK028(sa)001:6325: myang nas dngos grub gsum thob 'gyur //
NK028(sa)001:6332: sh+ri he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK028(sa)001:6333: i d+han d+h+au ba pash+pa di pam gan+d+he ba ling ta pra tits+tsha ho //
NK028(sa)001:6334: sh+ri ba na kha kha kha h+ai kh+aa hi /
NK028(sa)001:6337: ri rab chen po'i gling bzhi la //
NK028(sa)001:6338: gnas pa'i sems can ma lus kun //
NK028(sa)001:6339: ye shes me chen sgom byas te //
NK028(sa)001:6340: thams cad ma lus bsreg par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:6341: srid gsum bsreg pa'i me yin te //
NK028(sa)001:6342: yid kyi ye shes me ru 'bar //
NK028(sa)001:6345: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:6346: pad+mo la ni rdo rje zhugs //
NK028(sa)001:6347: 'khril ba'i mchod sbyin rnam sbyor bas //
NK028(sa)001:6348: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:6351: a nu ra ga ya mi /
NK028(sa)001:6352: a nu ra ga ya ho //
NK028(sa)001:6354: bza' dang bca' ba btung dang bsgo //
NK028(sa)001:6355: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni //
NK028(sa)001:6357: chos nyid la yang chos nyid thim //
NK028(sa)001:6360: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra a be sha ya /
NK028(sa)001:6364: sh+r+ai b+han d+ha kha ram kh+aa h+ai /
NK028(sa)001:6365: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6366: bdud rtsi sman gyis mchod pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6367: 'phra la dang skabs tshol gnod pa kun bsal nas //
NK028(sa)001:6368: skye shi med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6370: stong phrag brgyad cu'i bgegs rnams cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6371: dam rdzas gtor ma phul ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6372: yun du glags lta gnod pa kun zhi nas //
NK028(sa)001:6373: 'pho 'gyur med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6375: chags sdang rnam gnyis dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6376: khams gsum khrag mtsho phul ba'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6377: nyon mongs sems su gsal ba'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6378: sems nyid g.yo ba med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6380: ho phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i ta tha'i bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal he ru ka la sogs /
NK028(sa)001:6381: he ru ka dgu klong 'bar ba khro bo khro
NK028(sa)001:6382: mo bsam gyis mi khyab pa gsan cing dgongs su
NK028(sa)001:6383: gsol / bdag cag gis rnal 'byor gyi p+au dza
NK028(sa)001:6384: dam pa rigs pa'i khyad par phyi nang gsang ba
NK028(sa)001:6385: gsum gyi tshul du phul bas /
NK028(sa)001:6386: sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud du mnyes pa chen pos khyab par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:6387: de'i byin rlabs kyis mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams
NK028(sa)001:6388: cad rdo rje 'chang gi gral thob par gyur cig
NK028(sa)001:6389: / bdag cag gi dam tshig nyams pa thams cad bskongs par gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:6390: dngos grub kyi snod du gyur nas yi ge 'khor
NK028(sa)001:6391: lo tshogs chen gyi sa la mngon par sangs rgyas
NK028(sa)001:6392: te / 'khor ba ka dag par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:6393: a la la hoh bdag cag dam tshig 'di la zhes pa brjod /
NK028(sa)001:6394: khams gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal bar byas la 'dzab bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:6395: khro bo'i lha la mang nyung ma nges te /
NK028(sa)001:6397: gu h+ye dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:6399: rgyu 'bras rtsol ba'i sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6400: bsnyen bsgrub rnam bzhi 'dzab bsnyen byas pa'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:6401: thams cad kun tu bzang po'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6402: dngos grub rnam gsum lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6404: zhes pa bcu gsum par gsal lo //
NK028(sa)001:6409: bdag mchod kun mnyes thams cad 'grangs //
NK028(sa)001:6410: kun la phan pa'i sman yin te //
NK028(sa)001:6411: rnal 'byor bdag nyid chen po yis //
NK028(sa)001:6412: thams cad bza' zhing brgyan par bya //
NK028(sa)001:6415: 'dod yon lnga yi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6416: tshogs kyi mchod pa byas pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6417: mtha' la zhen pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas //
NK028(sa)001:6418: bde ba chen po'i longs spyod rdzogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6420: lhag ma'i steng du gtor ma kun blugs la /
NK028(sa)001:6423: kha chus gdab pa kun mthun /
NK028(sa)001:6424: de nas so so nas mchod de las bcol /
NK028(sa)001:6426: lo skegs zla skegs gnod pa cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6427: dak+ki dbang phyug lhag phud mchod pa'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:6428: mo ngan rmi ngan gnod pa kun bsal nas //
NK028(sa)001:6429: bar chad rkyen gyis sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6431: 'jig rten srin mo 'gro drug cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6432: gtor ma bri bkrol med par bsngosa pa'i byin brlabs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:6433: 'jig rten srin mo 'gro drug kun tshim nas //
NK028(sa)001:6434: zhing bcu bsgral zhing 'gro don rdzogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6436: dal lha kun 'od du zhu nas thig ler gyur //
NK028(sa)001:6437: thig le bla na med pa'i he ru kar gsal //
NK028(sa)001:6438: gzung 'dzin rnam gnyis dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6439: lha dang gzhal yas bsgrub pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6440: rtag chad gnyis su snang ba'i mtha' bsal nas //
NK028(sa)001:6441: snang srid chos kyis sku ru rdzogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6443: de nas rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:6444: rnam dag lus kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6445: spyod yul rgyun gyi ting 'dzin byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6446: bdag nyid yi dam lha ru gyur nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:6447: 'gro don ma lus rdzogs par byed par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6449: lung gi zhi khro'i las byang chung ba rdzogs so //
NK028(sa)001:6450: gnyis pa mdun bskyed dkyil 'khor sta gon ni /
NK028(sa)001:6451: na mo badz+ra sa t+wa ya /
NK028(sa)001:6452: lung gi zhi khro'i las byang la /
NK028(sa)001:6453: thog mar 'phrin las kyi dbu 'dren ni //
NK028(sa)001:6455: gdod nas ma skyes rnam dag chos kyi sku //
NK028(sa)001:6456: chos nyid byang chub sems dbyer med kyang //
NK028(sa)001:6457: srid pa srog gis bsdus pa'i 'jig rten pa //
NK028(sa)001:6458: log rtog dngos por gol ba'i rkyen gyis su //
NK028(sa)001:6459: nyon mongs brgyad khri bzhi stong rang las byung //
NK028(sa)001:6460: sdug bsngal gsum dang brgyad kyis gzir ba rnams //
NK028(sa)001:6461: rgyu 'bras theg pa gzhan gyis mi 'dul ste //
NK028(sa)001:6462: gsang ba'i gsang ba chen po'i dus la bab /
NK028(sa)001:6464: h+aum srid pa phyi nang snod bcud thams cad ni //
NK028(sa)001:6465: snyigs ma lnga yi skye 'gro ma lus kun //
NK028(sa)001:6466: thams cad sangs rgyas nyid kyi rang bzhin pas //
NK028(sa)001:6467: thabs la mkhas pas 'di la brtag cing bsgom //
NK028(sa)001:6469: mchod pa bshams nas stong pa las /
NK028(sa)001:6470: skad cig zhe sdang rdo rje bskyed de /
NK028(sa)001:6471: nying 'khor bcu gnyis sam bi shwa badz+ra sprul pas /
NK028(sa)001:6473: khro bcu bkod pa'i phur pas btab la /
NK028(sa)001:6474: lung rim par bsgom pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:6477: steng 'og phyogs mtshams dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6478: khro bcu yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6479: phyogs bcur gnas pa'i bgegs rnams kun bsal nas //
NK028(sa)001:6480: dngos grub bar chad ming yang med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6484: ye nas mnyam pa nyid kyi bshags rjes su //
NK028(sa)001:6485: sgrib pa rnam gnyis dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6486: yid kyi mngon du bshags pa'i byin brlabs kyi /
NK028(sa)001:6487: sgrib pa ye nas dag pa'i don rtogs nas /
NK028(sa)001:6488: sems nyid rang bzhin med pa'i don rtogs shog /
NK028(sa)001:6491: mthu dang bral ba'i sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6492: bde gshegs byin phob gsal bar rdzogs pa'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:6493: rgyal ba'i sku ru lhun gyis grub nas kyang /
NK028(sa)001:6494: thams cad byin brlabs mthu nyid 'grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6496: p+au dza gzhung bzhin byin gyis brlabs te //
NK028(sa)001:6498: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6499: bdud rtsi sman mchog bsgrubs cing mchod pa'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:6500: yun du glags lta'i gnod pa kun bsal nas /
NK028(sa)001:6501: skye 'chi med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6504: brgyad khri bzhi stong gdon rnams cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6505: tshogs dang gtor mas mchod pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6506: 'phral du skabs 'tshol gnod pa kun bsal nas /
NK028(sa)001:6507: 'pho 'gyur med pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6509: thun mong rdzas kyi dngos po p+au dza byin gyis brlabs pa'i nus mthu yis //
NK028(sa)001:6510: 'dod pa'i yon tan yongs su rdzogs gyur nas //
NK028(sa)001:6511: dus gsum bde gshegs ma lus mchod par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6514: gnam sa ri brag dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6515: de bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:6516: chos nyid stong pa nyid du don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6517: spros pa med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6519: ma rtogs sems can sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6520: kun tu snang gis ting 'dzin bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:6521: chos nyid skye ba med par don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6522: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6525: ma rig sems nyid dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6526: rgyu yi ting nge 'dzin ni bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:6527: chos nyid byang chub sems kyi don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6528: rang byung ye shes lhun na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:6529: stong pa las zhi dkyil 'khor rten bcas bskyed la //
NK028(sa)001:6530: h+aum snod kyi 'jig rten 'byung ba cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6531: gzhal yas dbang chen bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6532: chos nyid mtha' dbus med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6533: 'og min gnas su lhun na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:6534: rang ye shes su gsal ba las sngags kyis bskyed la /
NK028(sa)001:6535: h+aum phung po lnga dang 'byung lnga cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6536: rigs lnga yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK028(sa)001:6537: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6538: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6541: dbang po rnam shes yul dus cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6542: sems dpa' sems ma bsgoms pa'i byin kyis rlabs //
NK028(sa)001:6543: thams cad lha dang lha mo'i don /
NK028(sa)001:6544: rgyal ba'i sras su lhun gyis /
NK028(sa)001:6548: yid dang chos kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6549: kun bzang yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin /
NK028(sa)001:6550: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6551: chos sku 'gyur med lhun na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:6552: 'gro ba rigs drug dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6553: thub pa drug du bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6554: rol pa cir yang snang ba'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6555: sangs rgyas mdzad pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6557: rang ye shes su gsal bas //
NK028(sa)001:6558: sgo ba sngags kyis bskyed de /
NK028(sa)001:6559: h+aum yan lag bzhi po dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6560: sgo ba yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6561: yab yum 'du 'bral med pa'i don 'phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:6562: shu nya sogs sngags brjod la //
NK028(sa)001:6563: h+aum lus ngag yid gsum dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6564: dbang bskur byin gyis rlabs pa'i nyon mongs dngos po ma lus kun byang nas //
NK028(sa)001:6565: sku dang ye shes lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6567: zhi ba la sa ma y+aa dz+aah dang e h+ya hi /
NK028(sa)001:6570: sangs rgyas sems can dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6571: bde gshegs spyan drangs bstim pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6572: ye nas gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6573: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6578: h+aum bdag dang gzhan du dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6579: dkyil 'khor lha la phyag 'tshal byin rlabs gyis //
NK028(sa)001:6580: ye nas 'dres pa chen po'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6581: gnyis su med par lhun gyis /
NK028(sa)001:6583: bde bar gshegs so brjod la //
NK028(sa)001:6584: h+aum 'gro drug sems can sdug bsngal cir dam bca' rnam gsum byas pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6585: ma spangs mtha' ru phyin pa'i don rtogs bdag gzhan
NK028(sa)001:6586: don gnyis lhun gyis gzung 'dzin rnam rtog dngos po
NK028(sa)001:6587: phyag rgya'i p+au dza phul ba'i byin phyag rgya rnam
NK028(sa)001:6588: bzhi lhun gyis grub nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:6589: thams cad phyag rgya chen por lhun grub shog /
NK028(sa)001:6591: h+aum phyi nang gsang ba'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6592: kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa phul ba yis //
NK028(sa)001:6593: dngos po thams cad mchod par gyur nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:6594: spyod yul thams cad yongs su dag par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6596: bdag dang gzhan gyis dngos p+au dza rnam lnga phul
NK028(sa)001:6597: ba'i byin thams cad 'gags pa med pa'i don 'khor
NK028(sa)001:6598: gsum yongs su dag par lhun grub shog /
NK028(sa)001:6600: rang byung la sogs brjod nas /
NK028(sa)001:6602: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6603: bdud rtsi sman mchod phul ba'i byin dug lnga bdud
NK028(sa)001:6604: rtsir 'gyur ba'i don skye shi med par lhun gyis
NK028(sa)001:6605: na mo h+aum / ba ling 'bul tshigs brjod de //
NK028(sa)001:6607: stong phrag drug cu'i bgegs rnams cir dam rdzas gtor
NK028(sa)001:6608: ma phul ba'i byin yun du glags lta'i gnod med
NK028(sa)001:6609: don rtogs nas // 'pho 'gyur med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6611: lhag pa ting nge'i p+au dza brjod de /
NK028(sa)001:6612: sems kyi rtogs pa dngos por cir lhag pa'i ting 'dzin mchod pa'i byin /
NK028(sa)001:6613: dngos po yo byad lnga ru grub nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:6614: rig pa'i cir snang lnga ru lhun grub shog /
NK028(sa)001:6616: sbyor sgrol p+au dza brjod de //
NK028(sa)001:6618: chags sdang rnam gnyis dngos po cir snang yang /
NK028(sa)001:6619: ta g+han rnam gnyis mchod pa'i byin spyod yul yongs su dag po'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6620: bdag gzhan don gnyis lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6623: yul dang dbang po'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6624: 'dod yon lnga yi mchod pa phul ba'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:6625: yul sems gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6626: spyod yul ma lus yongs su dag par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6629: nyon mongs sdug bsngal dngos por cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6630: glu snyan rol mo phul ba'i byin /
NK028(sa)001:6631: thams cad theg pa chen po'i sgrar gyur nas //
NK028(sa)001:6632: gsang sngags don nyid lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6635: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i ta th+aa thams cad kyi bdag
NK028(sa)001:6636: nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la
NK028(sa)001:6637: sogs pa rigs lnga rgyal ba rgya mtsho 'khor bsam
NK028(sa)001:6638: gyis mi khyab pa dang bcas pa thams cad gsan
NK028(sa)001:6640: bdag cag gis rnal 'byor gyi mchod yon dam pa
NK028(sa)001:6641: rig pa'i khyad par phyi nang gsang ba'i tshul gyis
NK028(sa)001:6642: sbyar te phul bas sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud mnyes
NK028(sa)001:6643: pa chen pos khyab par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:6644: de'i byin rlabs kyis mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad rdo rje 'chang gi gral thob par cig /
NK028(sa)001:6645: bdag cag gi dam tshig nyams pa bskongs te dngos
NK028(sa)001:6646: grub kyi snod dam par gyur nas 'khor lo tshogs
NK028(sa)001:6647: chen gyi sar mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas
NK028(sa)001:6648: 'khor ba ka nas dag par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:6650: bdag cag dam tshig 'di zhes pa brjod /
NK028(sa)001:6652: yid la bsam pa'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6653: smon lam mngon du btab pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6654: yid la ci bsam thams cad don grub nas //
NK028(sa)001:6655: 'gro don ma lus lhun gyis khams gsum lha'i dal du gsal bar byas la 'dzab bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:6656: rgyu 'bras rtsol ba'i dngos po bsnyen bsgrub rnam bzhi 'dzab bsnyen byas pa'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:6657: thams cad kun tu bzang po'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6658: dngos grub rnam gsum lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6663: mi rtog pa las sha rus rang rig tu gsal ba las //
NK028(sa)001:6664: b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud+d+he ban d+ha dz+ny+aa na tsakra b+h+rum /
NK028(sa)001:6666: ma h+aa ru tra b+ai ti ra b+ai /
NK028(sa)001:6669: dur khrod rdzas kyis dngos por cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6670: 'bar ba'i gzhal yas bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6671: rdzas su lta ba'i rtog pa kun bsal nas //
NK028(sa)001:6672: gnas mchog rab 'byams lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6675: ru tra rnam gsum dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6676: he ru ka ru bsgoms pa'i byin bdud dang srin po bar chad kun bsgral nas //
NK028(sa)001:6677: ye shes dgu ru lhun na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:6679: khams gsum dgu'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6680: yum chen dgu ru sgoms pa'i ma bdun sring mo'i bar chad kun thig le dgu ru lhun gyis /
NK028(sa)001:6683: rnam shes brgyad kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6684: ke'u ri brgyad du bsgoms pa'i yul lha mngon par rtog pa kun bcom nas //
NK028(sa)001:6685: rnam par rtog med lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6688: dur khrod brgyad kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6689: 'phra men brgyad du bsgoms pa'i mtshan mar snang ba'i dngos po kun bral nas //
NK028(sa)001:6690: rnam par rtog pa'i bag chags med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6693: chu so bzhi yi dngos po sgo ba bzhi ru
NK028(sa)001:6694: bsgoms tshad med bzhi ru rdzogs pa'i don rtogs nas
NK028(sa)001:6695: // 'phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6697: phyogs mtshams brgyad kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6698: spor ma brgyad du bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyiis //
NK028(sa)001:6699: lha srin sde brgyad bar chad kun 'jig rten bar chad ming yang med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6702: 'byung ba bzhi yi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6703: gsang ba'i yum bzhi bsgoms pa'i byin chos nyid dngas snyigs 'byed pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6704: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6707: chu sgal tshigs rnams kyi dngos po dbang phyag nyer
NK028(sa)001:6708: brgyad rnam par rtog pa'i bar chad kun bsal nas
NK028(sa)001:6709: / bar chad rkyen gyis sdug bsngal med par na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:6710: h+aum so dang rus pa'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6711: dak+ki swo gnyis bsgoms pa'i bar du gcod pa ma lus kun bsgral nas //
NK028(sa)001:6712: bsgrub pa'i bar du gcod pa'i ming yang med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6715: sha khrag rtsa yi dngos por cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6716: ma dang sring mo bsgoms pa'i /
NK028(sa)001:6717: tshe srog gnod pa'i bar chad kun bsal nas //
NK028(sa)001:6718: nyin mtshan rtag tu thams cad skyobs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6721: gu rtsibs bco brgyad dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6722: ging chen bco brgyad bsgral ba'i zhing bcu ma lus kun bsgral nas /
NK028(sa)001:6723: sangs rgyas zhing khams yongs su dag par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6726: rus mgo tshogs kyis dngos po cir khro bo khro mor bsgoms pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6727: khams gsum gdug pa ma lus kun bsgral nas //
NK028(sa)001:6728: sangs rgyas 'phrin las lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6730: rtsa bran mang po dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6731: pho nya sum brgya drug cu bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:6732: dam tshig nyams dang dgra bgegs kun bsgral nas //
NK028(sa)001:6733: gnod pa'i bar chad ming yang med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6736: skra dang ba spu dngos por cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6737: rnal 'byor rig 'dzin bsgoms pa'i byin brlab kyi //
NK028(sa)001:6738: rdo rje 'chang gral rim par non mdzad nas //
NK028(sa)001:6739: gzung 'dzin log rtogs ming yang med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6743: e a ra li hri tri /
NK028(sa)001:6744: sa ma ya s+t+wmo dza h+aum bam ho //
NK028(sa)001:6745: e a ra li hrim hrim /
NK028(sa)001:6747: sangs rgyas sems can bdag gzhan dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6748: bde gshegs spyan drangs stims pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6749: ye nas gnyis su med pa'i don gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6755: sangs rgyas sems can bdag gzhan cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6756: bde gshegs lha la phyag 'tshal byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6757: ye nas 'dren pa chen po'i don rtogs nas /
NK028(sa)001:6758: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6760: bde bar gshegs so brjod la /
NK028(sa)001:6762: 'gro drug sems can sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6763: dam bca' rnam gsum byas pa'i byin rlabs ma spangs
NK028(sa)001:6764: mtha' ru phyin pa'i don bdag gzhan gnyis don lhun
NK028(sa)001:6766: h+aum gzung 'dzin rnam rtog dngos po cir phyag rgya'i
NK028(sa)001:6767: p+au dza phul ba'i byin phyag rgya rnam bzhi lhun
NK028(sa)001:6769: thams cad phyag rgya rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub nas kyang /
NK028(sa)001:6770: thams cad phyag rgya chen po lhun grub shog /
NK028(sa)001:6773: phyi nang gsang ba'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6774: kun tu bzang po'i mchod par phul pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:6775: dngos po thams cad mchod par gyur nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:6776: spyod yul thams cad yongs su dag par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6778: h+aum de nas sman gyi mchod pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:6779: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK028(sa)001:6780: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK028(sa)001:6781: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK028(sa)001:6782: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK028(sa)001:6783: rgyud lnga sems can kun sgrol ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:6784: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK028(sa)001:6785: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK028(sa)001:6786: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen gyis //
NK028(sa)001:6787: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskul ba'i mchog /
NK028(sa)001:6788: ces che ba'i yon tan bsams la //
NK028(sa)001:6789: thog mar rtsa ba'i bla ma dang sgyu 'phrul gyi bla ma rnams kyi mtshan dngos su brjod la /
NK028(sa)001:6790: bdud rtsi g.yon pa'i 'theb srin gyis blangs la /
NK028(sa)001:6792: 'di ni sngon gyis dam tshig che //
NK028(sa)001:6793: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6794: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskul ba'i mchog /
NK028(sa)001:6795: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang nyid 'di //
NK028(sa)001:6796: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK028(sa)001:6797: thugs rjes dgongs nas bzhengs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:6798: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK028(sa)001:6799: 'bul gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:6800: sar+b+aa ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa argam pra tits+tsha ho //
NK028(sa)001:6801: sh+r+ai pany+tsa kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK028(sa)001:6803: tshogs rjes tshogs bdag dpal chen he ru ka //
NK028(sa)001:6804: 'bar ba'i rgyal po khrag 'thung lnga rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:6805: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:6806: thugs rje brtser dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK028(sa)001:6807: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK028(sa)001:6808: dpal chen sku la gnyis med lhun sbyor ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:6809: kro d+hi shwa ri la sogs yum chen lnga rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:6810: rnam dag thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang /
NK028(sa)001:6812: mthing ga mchod rnams rdo rje gsang ba'i yum //
NK028(sa)001:6813: ke'u ri la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:6814: rnam dag bdud rtsi thugs rje ma h+aa pany+tsa rdo rje mgo brnyan za byed mche gshog can //
NK028(sa)001:6815: sing ha la sogs phra men brgyad rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:6816: rnam dag thugs rje ma h+aa sgo bzhi rab sdom rdo rje gdong mo'i tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:6817: rta gdong la sogs sgo ma bzhi rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:6818: rnam dag thugs rje ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK028(sa)001:6819: srin mo'i cha lugs shin tu 'jigs par ston //
NK028(sa)001:6820: phyogs mtshams 'dzin pa'i spor ma brgyad rnams la rnam
NK028(sa)001:6821: dag thugs rje ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta dpal
NK028(sa)001:6822: chen sku la 'du 'bral med pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:6823: ye shes thugs kyi dgyes sde bzhi rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:6824: rnam thugs rje ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta la 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po'i mtha' bsrungs ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:6825: dam can dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad la //
NK028(sa)001:6826: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam thugs rjes ma h+aa pany+tsa
NK028(sa)001:6827: a 'phrin las ma lus myur du 'grub byed pa'i
NK028(sa)001:6828: // rdo rje dak+ki sum cu rtsa gnyis la //
NK028(sa)001:6829: rnam dag thugs rje ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta la ma mo chen mo bdun rnams dang //
NK028(sa)001:6830: sring mo chen mo bzhi rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:6831: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam pa thugs rjes che dgongs
NK028(sa)001:6832: dbang ma h+aa pany+tsa zhing bcu ma lus brten nas
NK028(sa)001:6833: 'dren byed pa'i // rdo rje ka tar ging chen bco brgyad la //
NK028(sa)001:6834: rnam dag thugs rje ma h+aa khams gsum gdug pa ma lus 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:6835: khro bo khro mo rol pa'i tshogs rnams la /
NK028(sa)001:6836: rnam dag thugs ma h+aa pany+tsa ye shes rol pa'i phyag rgya cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6837: mgyogs ma pho nya sum brgya drug cu la //
NK028(sa)001:6838: rnam dag bdud rtsi thugs rjes che dgongs dbang ma
NK028(sa)001:6839: h+aa rdo rje 'chang gral rim par sa gnon pa'i
NK028(sa)001:6840: // rnal 'byor dbang phyug rig 'dzin tshogs rnams la /
NK028(sa)001:6841: rnam dag thugs rje ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK028(sa)001:6842: lce yi rdo rje dam tshig la //
NK028(sa)001:6843: rdo rje can gyis h+aum bsgoms te //
NK028(sa)001:6844: bdud rtsi lnga las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK028(sa)001:6845: myang nas dngos grub gsum thob 'gyur /
NK028(sa)001:6851: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6852: bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6853: 'phral dang skabs tshol gnod pa kun bsal nas //
NK028(sa)001:6854: skye shi med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6857: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK028(sa)001:6866: sh+ri ban kha kha kha h+ai kha hi /
NK028(sa)001:6867: stong phrag brgyad cu'i bgegs rnams cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6868: dam rdzas gtor ma phul ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6869: yun du glags lta'i gnod pa kun zhi nas //
NK028(sa)001:6870: 'pho 'gyur med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6873: ri rab chen po'i gling bzhi la //
NK028(sa)001:6874: gnas pa'i sems can ma lus kun //
NK028(sa)001:6875: ye shes me chen bsgom byas te //
NK028(sa)001:6876: thams cad ma lus bsregs par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:6877: srid gsum bsreg pa'i me yin te //
NK028(sa)001:6878: yid kyi ye shes me ru 'bar //
NK028(sa)001:6881: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:6882: pad+mo la ni rdo rje zhugs //
NK028(sa)001:6883: 'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor bas //
NK028(sa)001:6884: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:6887: a nu ra ga ya mi /
NK028(sa)001:6888: a nu ra ga ya ho /
NK028(sa)001:6890: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo /
NK028(sa)001:6891: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni /
NK028(sa)001:6893: chos nyid la yang chos nyid rol //
NK028(sa)001:6896: sh+ri he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra a be sha ya /
NK028(sa)001:6900: sh+r+ai b+han+d+ha kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK028(sa)001:6901: chags sdang rnam gnyis dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6902: khams gsum khrag mtsho phul ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6903: nyon mongs sems su gsal ba'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6904: sems nyid dbye ba med par lhun grub shog /
NK028(sa)001:6906: ho phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK028(sa)001:6907: cad kyi bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal che mchog
NK028(sa)001:6908: he ru ka la sogs pa /
NK028(sa)001:6909: he ru ka dgu klong 'bar ba /
NK028(sa)001:6910: 'khor khro bo khro mo bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:6911: bdag cag gis rnal 'byor gyis mchod yon dam pa rig pa'i khyad par /
NK028(sa)001:6912: phyi nang gsang ba gsum du phul bas /
NK028(sa)001:6913: sku gsung thugs kyis rgyud mnyes pa chen pos khyab par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:6914: de'i byin rlabs kyis mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams
NK028(sa)001:6915: cad rdo rje 'chang gi gral thob par gyur cig
NK028(sa)001:6916: / bdag gis dam tshig nyams pa thams cad bskongs te dngos grub kyi snod du gyur nas /
NK028(sa)001:6917: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sar mngon par sangs rgyas nas /
NK028(sa)001:6918: 'khor ba ka dag par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:6920: bdag cag dam tshig 'di la ces brjod /
NK028(sa)001:6921: khams gsam lha'i dal du byas la 'dzab bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:6922: khro bo lha mang nyung ma nges te /
NK028(sa)001:6923: gang la mos pa la bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:6924: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa s+au kha h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:6926: rgyu 'bras rtsol ba'i sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6927: bsnyen bsgrub rnam bzhi'i 'dzab bsnyen byas pa'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:6928: thams cad kun tu bzang po'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6929: dngos grub rnam gsum lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6931: 'dod yon lnga yi dngos po cir snang yang /
NK028(sa)001:6932: tshogs kyi mchod pa byas pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6933: mtha' la zhen pa'i btung ba kun bral nas //
NK028(sa)001:6934: bde ba chen po'i longs spyod rdzogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6936: lo zur zla gegs gdon la cir mkha' 'gro dbang phyug lhag phud mchod pa'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:6937: mo ngan rmi ngan gnod pa kun bsal nas //
NK028(sa)001:6938: bar chod rkyen gyi sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6940: 'jig rten srin mo 'gro drug cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6941: gtor ma dbri bkol med par bsngosa pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:6942: 'jig rten srin mo 'gro drug kun tshims nas //
NK028(sa)001:6943: zhing bcu sgrol zhing 'gro don rdzogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6945: gzung 'dzin rnam gnyis dngos po cir lha dang gzhal yas bsdus pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6946: rtag chad gnyis su snang ba'i mtha' bral nas //
NK028(sa)001:6947: snang srid chos kyis sku ru rtogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6949: rnam rtog lus kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6950: spyod lam rgyun gyis ting 'dzin byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6951: bdag nyid yi dam lha ru gyur nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:6952: 'gro don ma lus rdzogs par byed par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6955: rgyud kyis lha bskyed lung gis gsal btab te /
NK028(sa)001:6956: na mo h+aum gis gzi byin bskyed nas ni /
NK028(sa)001:6957: rdzogs pa chen po'i klong du la bzlas nas //
NK028(sa)001:6958: bskyed rdzogs rnam gsum don nyid rdzogs par gyur //
NK028(sa)001:6959: skyes bu blo rtsal can gyis spyod yul te //
NK028(sa)001:6960: thun mong min par kun bzang nyid kyis gsungs //
NK028(sa)001:6961: lung gi zhi khro'i las byang chen mo rdzogs so //
NK028(sa)001:6962: tshogs las khro chung dang mthun no //
NK028(sa)001:6963: gsum pa zhi ba'i bum pa sta gon ni /
NK028(sa)001:6965: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho sarba d+har+m+aa swa ba shu d+ho ham /
NK028(sa)001:6967: gnam sa ri brag dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6968: de bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin bsgom pa'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:6969: chos nyid stong pa nyid du don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6970: spros pa med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6973: ma rtogs sems can sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6974: kun tu snang ba'i ting 'dzin bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:6975: chos nyid skye ba med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6976: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6978: ma rig sems nyid dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6979: rgyu 'bras ting nge 'dzin ni bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:6980: chos nyid byang chub sems kyi don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:6981: rang byung ye shes lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:6983: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+rum las /
NK028(sa)001:6986: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor cha drug rdzogs par bskyed de /
NK028(sa)001:6987: de yang dbus kyi bum par /
NK028(sa)001:6988: rnam snang gis gtso byas pa'i bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK028(sa)001:6989: shar du mi bskyod gyis gtso byas pa'i bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK028(sa)001:6990: lhor rin chen 'byung ldan gyis gtso byas pa'i bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK028(sa)001:6991: nub tu snang mthas gtso byas pa'i bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK028(sa)001:6992: byang du don yod grub pas gtso byas pa'i bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK028(sa)001:6993: las bum gyi nang du don yod grub pa dang
NK028(sa)001:6994: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa dbyer med pas gtso byas pa'i
NK028(sa)001:6995: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rten gzhal yas khang dang bcas
NK028(sa)001:6997: snod kyi 'jig rten 'byung ba cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:6998: gzhal yas khang chen bsgom pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:6999: chos nyid mtha' dbus med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:7000: 'og min gnas su lhan gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7001: h+aum phung po lnga dang 'byung lnga cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7002: rigs lnga yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7003: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:7004: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7006: h+aum dbang po rnam shes yul dus cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7007: sems dpa' sems ma bsgoms pa'i thams cad lha dang
NK028(sa)001:7008: lha mo'i don rgyal ba'i sras su lhun gyis grub
NK028(sa)001:7011: yid dang chos kyis dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7012: kun bzang yab yum bsgoms dbyings dang ye shes gnyis
NK028(sa)001:7013: med don chos sku 'gyur med lhun na mo h+aum
NK028(sa)001:7014: / 'gro ba rigs drug dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7015: thub pa drug tu bsgoms pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7016: rol pa cir yang snang ba'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:7017: sangs rgyas mdzad pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7019: h+aum yan lag bzhi yi dngos po sgo ba yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7020: yab yum 'du 'bral med pa'i don 'phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7022: h+aum lus ngag yid gsum dngos po cir dbang bskur
NK028(sa)001:7023: byin gyis brlabs pa'i byin nyon mongs dngos po ma
NK028(sa)001:7025: sku dang ye shes lhun gyis 'grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7028: sangs rgyas sems can dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7029: bde gshegs spyan drangs stim pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7030: ye nas gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:7031: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7033: h+aum bdag dang gzhan du dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7034: dkyil 'khor lha la phyag 'tshal byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7035: ye nas 'dres pa chen po'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:7036: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7038: h+aum 'gro drug sems can sdug bsngal cir snang yang /
NK028(sa)001:7039: dam bca' rnam gsum byas pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7040: ma spangs mtha' ru phyin pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:7041: bdag gzhan gnyis don lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7044: gzung 'dzin rnam rtog dngos po phyag rgya'i p+au dza
NK028(sa)001:7045: phul ba'i byin phyag rgya rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub
NK028(sa)001:7046: nas kyang // thams cad phyag rgya chen por lhun grub shog /
NK028(sa)001:7048: h+aum phyi nang gsang ba'i dngos po kun tu bzang
NK028(sa)001:7049: po'i mchod pa phul ba'i byin dngos po thams cad
NK028(sa)001:7051: spyod yul thams cad yongs su dag par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7054: bdag dang gzhan gyis dngos po cir p+au dza rnam
NK028(sa)001:7055: lnga phul ba'i byin thams cad 'gag pa med pa'i
NK028(sa)001:7056: don rtogs nas // 'khor gsum yongs su dag par lhun grub shog /
NK028(sa)001:7058: h+aum bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams cir snang bdud
NK028(sa)001:7059: rtsi sman mchod phul ba'i byin dug lnga bdud rtsir
NK028(sa)001:7060: 'gyur ba'i don skye shi med par lhun gyis grub
NK028(sa)001:7062: stong phrag brgyad cu'i bgegs rnams cir dam rdzas gtor
NK028(sa)001:7063: ma phul ba'i byin yun du glags lta'i gnod med
NK028(sa)001:7064: don rtogs nas // 'pho 'gyur med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7066: h+aum sems kyi gtor ma dngos por cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7067: lhag pa'i ting 'dzin mchod pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7068: dngos po yo byad lnga ru grub nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:7069: rigs pa cir snang lha ru lhun grub shog /
NK028(sa)001:7072: chags sdang rnam gnyis dngos po cir ta g+han rnam
NK028(sa)001:7073: gnyis mchod pa'i byin spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i
NK028(sa)001:7074: don rtogs nas / bdag gzhan don gnyis lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7077: yul dang dbang po'i dngos po cir 'dod yon lnga yi mchod pa phul ba'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:7078: yul sems gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:7079: spyod yul ma lus yongs su dag par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7082: nyon mongs sdug bsngal dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7083: glu snyan rol mo phul ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7084: thams cad theg pa chen po'i sgrar gyur nas //
NK028(sa)001:7085: gsang sngags don gnyis lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7087: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi /
NK028(sa)001:7088: ye shes da lar thig le che /
NK028(sa)001:7089: bsod nams da la sku yi tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:7090: snang stong thig le kun rdzogs ho //
NK028(sa)001:7091: rdo rje bsod nams thig le che //
NK028(sa)001:7092: rdo rje ye shes da lar ldan //
NK028(sa)001:7093: rdo rje sgra can mtha' yas pa //
NK028(sa)001:7094: rdo rje rgyal po dkyil 'khor che ho //
NK028(sa)001:7095: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK028(sa)001:7096: yon tan phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK028(sa)001:7097: ye nas lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang //
NK028(sa)001:7098: 'dus pa'i rdzogs chen thig le che //
NK028(sa)001:7100: mi dmigs sgyu 'phrul mnyam pa'i dbyings //
NK028(sa)001:7101: mtha' yas kun tu sna tshogs 'phro //
NK028(sa)001:7102: mtha' yas kun tu lhun gyis thim //
NK028(sa)001:7103: sna tshogs sku gsung thugs chen ho //
NK028(sa)001:7104: phyogs bcu'i 'jigs rten brdul snyed du /
NK028(sa)001:7105: rgyal ba'i don rnams rdul phran snyed //
NK028(sa)001:7106: sprul pa'i rdul phran bsam yas kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7107: skad gcig nyid la lhun gyis grub ho //
NK028(sa)001:7108: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK028(sa)001:7109: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK028(sa)001:7110: sku gsung thugs kyis kun tu khyab //
NK028(sa)001:7111: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che ho //
NK028(sa)001:7112: h+aum yid la bsam pa'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7113: smon lam sngon du btab pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7114: yid la ci bsams thams cad don grub nas //
NK028(sa)001:7115: 'gro don ma lus lhun gyis na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7117: bum pa rnams kyis mdun du dung chos kyi nang du 'bru bcud kyi phud blugs la //
NK028(sa)001:7119: khar rdo rje a mri ta btab /
NK028(sa)001:7120: khar rdo rje bzhag gzungs thag phyag g.yon gyis 'dzin /
NK028(sa)001:7122: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta mah+aa su ka h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7123: la sogs zhi ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi snying po bzlas shing ting nge 'dzin no //
NK028(sa)001:7124: rang gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK028(sa)001:7125: gzungs thag la brgyud nas song /
NK028(sa)001:7126: rdo rje'i lte ba la zhi ba'i lha tshogs sgoms pa la phog /
NK028(sa)001:7127: de la 'od zer 'phros dung chos kyi nang du
NK028(sa)001:7128: zhi ba'i lha tshogs sgoms pa la phog de la
NK028(sa)001:7129: 'od zer 'phros / bum pa'i nang gi lha yab rnams kyi zhal du thim /
NK028(sa)001:7131: glad pa dung khang gi nang du song //
NK028(sa)001:7132: sgal tshigs kyi rta la brgyud //
NK028(sa)001:7133: srog bdag pa'i lam nas phyung //
NK028(sa)001:7134: rdo rje yum gyi mkhar bab /
NK028(sa)001:7136: yum gyi srog dag pa'i lam du zhugs //
NK028(sa)001:7137: sgal tshigs kyi rta la brgyud //
NK028(sa)001:7138: yum gyis zhal nas yab kyi zhal du zhugs //
NK028(sa)001:7139: yab kyi zhal nas sngar bzhin yum gyis mkhar bab /
NK028(sa)001:7140: sbyor mtshams nas bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun byung nas bum pa gang bar bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:7141: tab te tab te ma h+aa tab te ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:7143: bdud rtsi thigs gsum re bum pa drug gi nang
NK028(sa)001:7144: du blug pas lha tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa thams
NK028(sa)001:7146: bum pa rnams ltems kyis gang bar bsams pas /
NK028(sa)001:7147: dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK028(sa)001:7148: rdo rje rigs kyis yon tan rdzogs par bsam mo
NK028(sa)001:7149: // bzhi pa khro bo'i bum pa ka pa la sta gon ni /
NK028(sa)001:7151: swa b+ha wa shud+d+ha h+aum gnam sa ri brag dngos po cir snang yang /
NK028(sa)001:7152: de bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin bsgoms pa'i mthus /
NK028(sa)001:7153: chos nyid stong pa nyid du don rtogs nas /
NK028(sa)001:7154: spros pa med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7156: h+aum ma rtogs sems can sdug bsngal cir snang yang /
NK028(sa)001:7157: kun tu snang gi ting 'dzin bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:7158: chos nyid skye ba med pa'i gnyis su med pa lhun gyis 'grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7160: ma rig sems nyid dngos po rgyu yi ting nge chos nyid byang chub sems kyi don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:7161: rang byung ye shes lhun na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7164: b+h+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he b+han+d+ha dz+ny+aa na tsakra b+h+r+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7165: rigs lnga'i ka p+aa la lnga'i nang du khro bo'i lha lnga brgya rtsa rig 'dzin dang bcas /
NK028(sa)001:7166: pa cha lnga rigs lnga gtso byas pa'i bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:7167: ma h+aa ru ta nam ti ra ham /
NK028(sa)001:7170: dur khrod rdzas kyis dngos po 'bar ba'i gzhal yas
NK028(sa)001:7171: bsgoms rdzas su lta ba'i rtogs pa kun bsal nas
NK028(sa)001:7172: // gnas mchog rab 'byams lhun gyis grub na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7174: ru tra rnam gsum dngos he ru ka ru bsgoms pa'i /
NK028(sa)001:7175: bdud dang srin po'i bar chad kun bsgral nas //
NK028(sa)001:7176: ye shes dgu ru lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7178: h+aum khams gsum sa dgu'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7179: yum chen dgu ru bsgoms pa'i ma bdud srin mo'i
NK028(sa)001:7180: bar chad kun bsgral thig le dgu ru lhun na
NK028(sa)001:7182: rnam shes brgyad kyi dngos po cir ke'u brgyad du
NK028(sa)001:7183: bsgom pa'i byin yul la mngon par rtog pa kun
NK028(sa)001:7184: bcom nas // rnam pa rtog med lhun gyis grub na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7185: h+aum dur khrod brgyad kyi dngos po cir phra men brgyad du bsgom pa'i byin /
NK028(sa)001:7186: mtshan mar lta ba'i dngos po kun bral nas //
NK028(sa)001:7187: rnam par rtog pa'i bag chags med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7188: chu bo bzhi yi dngos po cir yang snang //
NK028(sa)001:7189: sgo ba bzhi ru bsgoms tshad med bzhi ru rdzogs pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:7190: phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7192: phyogs mtshams brgyad kyis dngos por cir spor ma brgyad
NK028(sa)001:7193: du bsgoms lha srin sde brgyad bar chad kun bsgral
NK028(sa)001:7194: nas // 'jig rten bar chad ming yang med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7197: 'byung ba bzhi yi gsang ba'i yum bzhi bsgoms chos nyid dwangs snyigs 'byed pa'i don /
NK028(sa)001:7198: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7201: sgal tshigs rnams kyi dngos po dbang phyug nyer brgyad
NK028(sa)001:7202: bsgoms rnam par rtog pa'i bar chad kun bsgral nas
NK028(sa)001:7203: // bar chad rkyen dang sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7205: h+aum so dang rus pa'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7206: d+aak+ki so gnyis bsgoms pa'i bar chad gcod pa ma lus kun bsgral nas //
NK028(sa)001:7207: bsgrub pa'i bar du gcod pa med pa shog /
NK028(sa)001:7209: h+aum sha khrag rus pa'i dngos po cir ma dang
NK028(sa)001:7210: sring mor bsgoms pa'i tshe srog gnod pa'i bar chad
NK028(sa)001:7211: kun bsal nyin mtshan rtag tu thams cad skyob par
NK028(sa)001:7214: gung rtsibs bco brgyad dngos po cir ging chen bco brgyad bsgoms pa'i byin /
NK028(sa)001:7215: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu ma lus kun bsgral nas //
NK028(sa)001:7216: sangs rgyas zhing khams yongs su dag par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7219: rus mgo tshogs kyi dngos po ci snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7220: khro bo khro mor bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7221: khams gsum gdug pa ma lus kun bsgral nas //
NK028(sa)001:7222: sangs rgyas 'phrin las lhun gyis 'grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7225: rtsa bran mang po'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7226: pho nya sum brgya drug bcu bsgoms pa'i mthus /
NK028(sa)001:7227: dam tshig nyams dang dgra bgegs kun bsgral nas /
NK028(sa)001:7228: gnod pa'i bar chad ming yang med par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7230: skra dang ba spu dngos po cir snang yang /
NK028(sa)001:7231: rnal 'byor rig 'dzin bsgoms pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7232: rdo rje 'chang gral rims par non mdzad nas //
NK028(sa)001:7233: gzung 'dzin log rtog ming yang med pa shog /
NK028(sa)001:7235: de nas ye shes lngas dbang bskur //
NK028(sa)001:7236: sku gsung thugs byin gyis rlabs /
NK028(sa)001:7239: e h+ya he sh+ri he ru ka e a ra li hrim /
NK028(sa)001:7242: zhes spyan drangs dzahh+aum bam ho //
NK028(sa)001:7243: e a ra la hrim hrim /
NK028(sa)001:7244: zhes gnyis su med par stim /
NK028(sa)001:7245: ka ya wa ka tsit+tasa brtan par bzhugs su gsol /
NK028(sa)001:7247: sangs rgyas sems can dngos po cir bde gshegs spyan drangs stims pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7248: ye nas gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:7249: gnyis su med pa'i lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7253: h+aum sangs rgyas sems can bdag gzhan cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7254: bde gshegs lha la phyag 'tshal byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7255: ye nas 'dres pa chen po'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:7256: gnyis su med pa'i lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7258: h+aum 'gro drug sems can sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7259: dam bca' rnam gsum byas pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7260: ma yengs mtha' ru phyin pa'i don bdag gzhan gnyis don lhun gyis na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7261: h+aum gzung 'dzin rnam rtog dngos po cir phyag rgya'i p+au dza phul ba'i /
NK028(sa)001:7262: phyag rgya rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:7263: thams cad phyag rgya chen por lhun grub shog /
NK028(sa)001:7265: h+aum phyi nang gsang ba'i dngos po cir kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa phul ba yis //
NK028(sa)001:7266: dngos po thams cad mchod pa gyur nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:7267: spyod yul thams cad yongs su dag par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7270: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7271: bdud rtsi sman gyis mchod pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7272: 'phral dang skabs tshol gnod pa kun bsal nas //
NK028(sa)001:7273: skye shi med par lhun gyis na mo h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7275: stong phrag brgyad bcu'i bgegs rnams cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7276: dam rdzas gtor ma phul ba'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7277: yun du glags lta'i gnod pa kun zhi nas //
NK028(sa)001:7278: 'pho 'gyur med par lhun gyis grub pa shog /
NK028(sa)001:7280: chags sdang rnam gnyis dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7281: khams gsum khrag mtsho phul ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7282: nyon mongs sems su gsal ba'i don rtog shog /
NK028(sa)001:7283: sems nyid dbye ba med par lhun grub shog /
NK028(sa)001:7287: gtum chen dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar //
NK028(sa)001:7289: khro gnyer glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:7290: mche ba zangs yag za byed che ho //
NK028(sa)001:7291: h+aum rngam pa'i nga ro 'brug stong ldir //
NK028(sa)001:7292: thugs chen ri rab 'bum snyil skad //
NK028(sa)001:7293: a a ha le gad rgyangs che //
NK028(sa)001:7294: bshug pa'i mthor rlung gi yid chen no //
NK028(sa)001:7296: khro bo shes rab 'od po che //
NK028(sa)001:7297: ye shes dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal //
NK028(sa)001:7299: sna tshogs ye shes thig le che ho //
NK028(sa)001:7300: h+aum khros pa'i rgyal po sprin chen po //
NK028(sa)001:7303: sna tshogs khros pa'i thig le che ho //
NK028(sa)001:7305: bdud kun gyi ni bdud chen po //
NK028(sa)001:7306: bdud kyi bdud sde bdud rnams 'joms //
NK028(sa)001:7308: 'jigs byed chen po thig le che ho //
NK028(sa)001:7310: rdo rje brag chen bsra ba po //
NK028(sa)001:7311: rdo rje chu bo bsdud chen po //
NK028(sa)001:7312: rdo rje me ste kun 'bar che //
NK028(sa)001:7313: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che ho //
NK028(sa)001:7316: yid la bsam pa'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK028(sa)001:7317: smon lam mngon du btab pa'i byin brlabs kyi //
NK028(sa)001:7318: yid la ci bsams thams cad don grub nas //
NK028(sa)001:7319: 'gro don ma lus lhun grub gyis par shog /
NK028(sa)001:7321: bsnyen pa ni ka p+aa la rnams kyis mdun du /
NK028(sa)001:7322: ka p+aa la cig gi nang du 'bru bcud kyi phud blug la /
NK028(sa)001:7327: a khra ma h+aa kro d+ha sh+ri he ru ka ka ta mah+aa kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:7328: badz+ra sh+ri he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7330: bud+d+ha kro d+hi sho ri h+aum //
NK028(sa)001:7332: rat+na kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7334: pad+ma kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7336: karma kro d+hi shwi ri h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7337: ma h+aa rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK028(sa)001:7339: ta ka ha da ha pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:7340: ma h+aa yak+sha kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:7341: ma h+aa sa nu sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa
NK028(sa)001:7342: tsa b+ha sarba dush+tana da ka ha na da ha
NK028(sa)001:7344: ma h+aa sa nu kro d+hi shwa ri dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:7345: gu h+ya sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsab+ha sarba
NK028(sa)001:7346: dush+tana ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK028(sa)001:7347: phata / gu h+ya kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7358: steng phyogs khro bo drug cu pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu /
NK028(sa)001:7360: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang rnams rim pas rtsa sngags bzlas shing //
NK028(sa)001:7362: rang gi thugs kha nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK028(sa)001:7363: gzungs thag la brgyud nas song //
NK028(sa)001:7365: khro bo'i lha tshogs bsgoms pa la phog /
NK028(sa)001:7367: ka p+aa la'i nang du khro bo'i lha tshogs sgoms pa la phog /
NK028(sa)001:7369: ka pa li'i lha yab rnams kyi zhal du thim //
NK028(sa)001:7371: glad pa dung khang gi nang du song /
NK028(sa)001:7372: sgal tshigs kyi rta la brgyud /
NK028(sa)001:7373: srog bdag pa'i lam nas byung /
NK028(sa)001:7374: rdo rje nas yum gyi mkhar bab /
NK028(sa)001:7376: yum gyis srog dag pa'i lam du zhugs /
NK028(sa)001:7377: sgal tshigs kyi rta la brgyud //
NK028(sa)001:7378: yum gyi zhal nas yab kyi zhal du zhugs yab kyi zhal nas sngar bzhin yum gyi mkhar bab /
NK028(sa)001:7379: sbyor mtshams nas bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun byung nas ka p+aa la gang bar bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:7380: tab te tab te ma h+aa tab te ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:7381: ka p+aa la nas bdud rtsi thigs gsum re ka
NK028(sa)001:7382: p+aa la lnga'i nang du blugs pas lha tshogs 'khor
NK028(sa)001:7383: dang bcas pa thams cad bdud rtsir gyur te ka
NK028(sa)001:7384: pa la rnams ltems kyis gang bar bsams pas /
NK028(sa)001:7385: dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi /
NK028(sa)001:7386: rdo rje rigs kyi yon tan rdzogs par bsam mo //
NK028(sa)001:7387: lnga pa rdo rje dril bu sta gon ni /
NK028(sa)001:7388: de nas rdo rje dril bu rab gnas ni /
NK028(sa)001:7389: rdo rje khro zhal can la sogs pa du yod dang /
NK028(sa)001:7390: dril bu tshangs pa'i gsung zhal dang ldan pa mdun du bzhag la //
NK028(sa)001:7391: gsang sbyang stong pa nyid kyi ngang las rdo rje'i lte ba la che mchog rdzogs tshul du bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:7392: yar gyi rwa lnga la rigs lnga zhi khro gnyis gang rung bar dpa' bo 'bru lnga'i sngags bsam /
NK028(sa)001:7393: h+aum lnga la yab bskyed mar gyi rwa lnga la mum lam mam pyam tam lnga'i /
NK028(sa)001:7395: rtse dgu yin na mtshams gyis rwa bzhi la lung gi he ru ka bzhi bskyed //
NK028(sa)001:7396: yar gyi pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad la sems dpa' brgyad /
NK028(sa)001:7397: mar gyi brgyad la yum bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:7398: khro zhal bzhi la sgo ma bzhi dang gsang yum bzhi /
NK028(sa)001:7399: ril pa la dbang gang byed pa'i lha rnams rdzogs par bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:7400: de nas dril bu'i lte ba la /
NK028(sa)001:7401: khro mo rnams zhal ma zhal la yum chen mo shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa /
NK028(sa)001:7402: rwa lnga la rigs lnga gang rung /
NK028(sa)001:7403: mar gyi pad+ma'i phyogs bzhi dbus dang lngar yum lnga //
NK028(sa)001:7404: mtshams bzhir gsang yum bzhi dang /
NK028(sa)001:7405: gong ras brgyad la khro mo brgyad /
NK028(sa)001:7406: mtha' ma'i rdo rje'i rwa ba la khro mo nyi shu bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:7407: dril bu'i lce la khro mo gar bsgyur ma bskyed //
NK028(sa)001:7408: rtse dgu yin na mtshams kyi rwa bzhi la las bzhi'i snying po bskyed des /
NK028(sa)001:7409: de dag sngags bsam ting nge 'dzin gyis gsal bar bskyed la ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
