NK028(sa)001:7410: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs /
NK028(sa)001:7415: kun bzang nas bstod pa yan chad kyis mchod de /
NK028(sa)001:7416: h+aum zhes brjod pas lha rnams rang rang gi nas
NK028(sa)001:7417: 'od du zhu nas rdo rje dril bu la thim
NK028(sa)001:7418: pas rdo rje dril bur gyur pa las sngags //
NK028(sa)001:7419: badz+ra d+ha ka dz+ny+aa la ha na badz+ra pa tsa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7420: gan+d+ha pa sha d+har+m+ma d+ha ra h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7422: rdo rje la 'bras bu'i chos thams cad rdzogs nas 'gro don mdzad par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:7423: dril bu'i sgra stong pa nyid kyi ngang las chos sgra sgrogs par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:7424: rdo rje dril bu lag tu bzung nas 'gro ba'i don la bskul te //
NK028(sa)001:7426: rdo rje dril bu rig pa 'dzin /
NK028(sa)001:7427: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:7429: chos la de bzhin dbang bsgyur shog /
NK028(sa)001:7430: ces brjod nas rdo rje gsor bas khams gsum zil gyis mnan /
NK028(sa)001:7431: dril bu bsil bas khams gsum dbang du bsdus par bsgom mo //
NK028(sa)001:7433: dung dang cha lang la sogs pa'i phyag cha rnams
NK028(sa)001:7434: yi ge 'bru gsum la sogs pas byin rlabs ci
NK028(sa)001:7435: rigs par bya'o // drug pa thig skud sta gon ni /
NK028(sa)001:7436: ye shes kyi thig skud stong pa nyid kyi ngang las /
NK028(sa)001:7440: zhes gdan lnga bsam de dag gi steng du thugs ka nas h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7442: zhes yig 'bru dgod yang dam tshig gi thig la /
NK028(sa)001:7444: zhes gdan gsum bsam +aahh+aum zhes 'bru gsum dgod /
NK028(sa)001:7445: de nas yang rang gi thugs ka nas 'od zer phyogs kun tu 'phros nas /
NK028(sa)001:7446: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dza /
NK028(sa)001:7448: e h+ya hi lan gsum brjod nas /
NK028(sa)001:7449: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa rnams
NK028(sa)001:7450: mdun gyi nam mkha' la spyan drangs te brtan pa
NK028(sa)001:7452: phyag na phyogs bcu dus yan gyi bstod cing /
NK028(sa)001:7455: mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid /
NK028(sa)001:7456: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bazhinagashegasa pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol lo //
NK028(sa)001:7457: bdag rdo rje slob dpon gyis slob ma 'di rnams
NK028(sa)001:7458: kyi don du mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi dkyil 'khor
NK028(sa)001:7459: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las bkod pa mi
NK028(sa)001:7460: bzad pa rgyan gyis 'khor lo gsang ba bas kyang
NK028(sa)001:7461: ches yang gsang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor lhag pa gzugs
NK028(sa)001:7462: brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du thig 'debs pas /
NK028(sa)001:7463: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis bdag la mthu bstan du gsol lo //
NK028(sa)001:7464: byin gyis brlabs du gsol lo //
NK028(sa)001:7465: rdo rje ye shes kyi thig gsal du gsol lo //
NK028(sa)001:7466: badz+ra ti ga na tish+tha gu h+ya sa ma ya
NK028(sa)001:7467: dz+ny+aa na a gu sha dza dzah zhes lan gsum
NK028(sa)001:7468: brjod pas / mdun gyi de bzhin gshegs pa rnams
NK028(sa)001:7469: kyi sbyor ba byang chub kyi sems kyi chu rgyun
NK028(sa)001:7470: kyang ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun du kha dog lngar
NK028(sa)001:7471: gsal bar babs nas thig lnga po la thim par
NK028(sa)001:7472: brjod pas / bsam / sku gsung thugs kyi gnas
NK028(sa)001:7473: gsum nas 'od dkar dmar mthing gsum 'phros nas dam
NK028(sa)001:7474: tshig gi thig la thim pas /
NK028(sa)001:7475: thig dngos po nyid sku gsung thugs su gyur par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:7476: de nas slob dpon shar du bltas //
NK028(sa)001:7477: slob bu nub du bltas thig sna yum la gtad la dbyangs dang bcas pas /
NK028(sa)001:7478: yi ge h+aum zhes bya ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:7479: rdo rje rigs kyi rang bzhin te /
NK028(sa)001:7480: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis /
NK028(sa)001:7481: zhe sdang dngos po sbyang ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:7482: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:7483: ma h+aa shu nya ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:7484: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes thig sngo sbreng gis gyur par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:7485: de nas yi ge zhes bya ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:7486: de bzhin rigs kyi rang bzhin te //
NK028(sa)001:7487: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7488: gti mug dngos po sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:7489: byin brlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:7490: a da sh+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:7491: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi ngo bo thig dkar breng gis gyur par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:7492: yi ge swa zhes bya ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:7493: rin chen rigs kyi rang bzhin te /
NK028(sa)001:7494: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis /
NK028(sa)001:7495: nga rgyal dngos po sbyang ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:7496: byin brlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:7497: ma h+aa sa man+ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa
NK028(sa)001:7498: at+ma mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi ngo bo
NK028(sa)001:7499: thig ser breng gis gyur par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:7501: pad+ma rigs kyi rang bzhin te /
NK028(sa)001:7502: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyis /
NK028(sa)001:7503: 'dod chags dngos po sbyangs pa'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:7504: byin brlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:7505: pra ta pra be sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma /
NK028(sa)001:7506: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo thig dmar breng gis gyur par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:7507: yi ge h+aahzhesa bya ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:7508: las kyi rigs kyi rang bzhin te //
NK028(sa)001:7509: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7510: phrag dog dngos po sbyangs pa'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:7511: byin brlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:7512: ma h+aa kro ti a nu ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:7513: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo thig ljang breng gis gyur pas bsam //
NK028(sa)001:7514: de nas thig rnams cig tu bsgoms la //
NK028(sa)001:7515: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK028(sa)001:7516: mdo sgyu sems gsum dkyil 'khor du //
NK028(sa)001:7517: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi 'phro 'du las //
NK028(sa)001:7518: rdo rje ye shes thig chen 'di btab pas //
NK028(sa)001:7519: pho brang dkyil 'khor ji bzhin lhun gyis grub /
NK028(sa)001:7521: thig skud rnams phyogs cig tu bsgrims nas ye shes
NK028(sa)001:7522: lnga'am sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las nyi shu
NK028(sa)001:7523: rtsa lnga'i ngo bor gyur par bsam mo //
NK028(sa)001:7524: de nas dam tshig gi thig lag du thogs la
NK028(sa)001:7525: +aahh+aum zhes sku gsung thugs kyi byin phab ste thig
NK028(sa)001:7527: yi ge zhes bya ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:7528: bde gshegs sku yi rang bzhin te //
NK028(sa)001:7529: lus kyi dngos po sbyangs pa'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:7530: byin brlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:7531: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:7533: sku'i ngo bo thig dkar breng gis gyur par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:7534: yi ge a zhes bya ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:7535: ngag gi dngos po sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:7536: byin rlabs dam par mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:7537: sarba ta th+aa ga ta wak+ka badz+ra sam b+ha wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:7539: gsung gi ngo bo thig dmar brengs kyis gyur par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:7540: yi ge h+aum zhes bya ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:7541: bde gshegs thugs kyi rang bzhin te //
NK028(sa)001:7542: yid kyi dngos po sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:7543: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:7544: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:7546: thugs kyi ngo bo thig sngo brengs kyis gyur par bsam //
NK028(sa)001:7547: de nas thig gsum po phyogs cig tu bsgrims la //
NK028(sa)001:7548: mu mtha' g.yo 'gul med pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:7549: rnal 'byoor mnyam nyid thod rgal du //
NK028(sa)001:7550: khro gtum rngam pa'i las mdzad pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:7551: gnas mdzad gzhal yas bri bar bya //
NK028(sa)001:7552: ahh+aum badz+ra dz+ny+aa na na ma tri kra ma h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7553: zhes brjod pas thig re re la'ang gsum gsum dgu phrugs dang ldan par bsam la /
NK028(sa)001:7555: glu ye shes yan chad thung lugs su gcogs na bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:7556: bdun pa tshon sta gon ni /
NK028(sa)001:7560: s+aur+ya tsan+t+ra rat+na pad+ma e man+da la /
NK028(sa)001:7562: cho ga gsum gyis lhar bskyed de la dbang bskur /
NK028(sa)001:7566: kun bzang nas bstod pa'i bar du byas la gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:7568: kun mkhyen ye shes dag pa la /
NK028(sa)001:7569: dug lnga bsgribs pas ma mthong pas /
NK028(sa)001:7570: mtshon cing dag par byas pa'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:7571: byin brlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:7573: na zhes brjod pas spung zhing /
NK028(sa)001:7574: gong gi rigs lnga 'od du zhu ba las ye
NK028(sa)001:7575: shes re re 'ang lnga lnga dang ldan par bsam
NK028(sa)001:7576: mo // brgyad pa dbang rdzas sta gon ni /
NK028(sa)001:7577: phan dbang bcu'i dbang rdzas dbu rgyan rin chen 'byung ldan gyis rab gnas byed //
NK028(sa)001:7578: cod pan rdo rje sems dpa' //
NK028(sa)001:7582: phyag rgya lha rang rang gis /
NK028(sa)001:7584: bum pa rigs rang rang gis /
NK028(sa)001:7586: snying po lnga rigs lngar bskyed la /
NK028(sa)001:7590: ka b+aa la rin chen 'byung gis /
NK028(sa)001:7591: 'phreng ba yi dam rang rang gis /
NK028(sa)001:7596: rdo rje dril bu kun bzang yab yum du bskyed la rab gnas byed do //
NK028(sa)001:7597: bu mo lo nyi shu ma la khrus gsum bya /
NK028(sa)001:7598: brgyan gsum btags chos gsum bshad pa gsang dbang gi dbang rdzas /
NK028(sa)001:7599: bcu drug ma shes rab ye shes kyi /
NK028(sa)001:7600: bcu gnyis ma dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang rdzas so //
NK028(sa)001:7601: gzhan bsrungs bskud dang po shing ku sha skyor chu
NK028(sa)001:7602: phur bu la sogs pa dbang rdzas la ji ltar
NK028(sa)001:7603: dgos pa rnams yi ge 'bru gsum la sogs pa
NK028(sa)001:7604: ci rigs pas byin gyis brlabs cing rab gnas bya'o
NK028(sa)001:7605: // dgu pa yo byad sta gon ni /
NK028(sa)001:7606: sngar bsogs pa'i yo byad ma lus pa thams cad la spyir byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:7607: ram yam kham gyis rdzas kyis dngos po dang mtshan ma sbyangs pa las /
NK028(sa)001:7609: sam ha ra na h+aum zhes brjod /
NK028(sa)001:7611: tram rat+na tree lok+sha man+da la h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:7612: zhes brjod pas yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po
NK028(sa)001:7613: che mi bzad pa'i gter dang ldan pa rin po
NK028(sa)001:7614: che'i rtse mo la +aahh+aum gsum gyis 'od 'phros pas
NK028(sa)001:7615: phyi nang gsang ba'i longs spyod bsam gyis mi khyab
NK028(sa)001:7617: bye brag tu brlabs pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:7618: yo byad de rnams tshogs gsum du bcad la /
NK028(sa)001:7619: tshogs gcig bam ser po'i 'phro 'du las dpa' bo 'bru lngar bskyed la tshogs dang mchod pa bya //
NK028(sa)001:7620: tshogs gcig dal dang ma'i 'phro 'du las gtor ma
NK028(sa)001:7621: byin gyis brlabs pa bzhin du 'dod yon du brlabs
NK028(sa)001:7622: la sgrub pa po rnams rol /
NK028(sa)001:7623: tshogs gcig nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags kyis mang zhing
NK028(sa)001:7624: rgya che bar byin gyis brlabs la mchod 'gron dgye
NK028(sa)001:7625: bcogs na brtags pa drug gis byin gyis brlabs /
NK028(sa)001:7627: mched rdo rje'i spun rnams lha dang lha mo'i rang bzhin du byin gyis brlabs te /
NK028(sa)001:7628: de dag gi yo byad sta gon zhes bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:7629: bcu pa slob ma sta gon ni /
NK028(sa)001:7630: don nyi shu rtsa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK028(sa)001:7631: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi lhor man+dala bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:7632: de la chags chags gdab pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:7633: pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes mtshon du byas la so shing la sogs pa'i rdzas bsham /
NK028(sa)001:7634: las mkhan gyis thun mong dang khyad par gyi mchod
NK028(sa)001:7635: pa bshams la phrin las thung lugs su mtshams nas
NK028(sa)001:7636: 'dzab dang bstod pa yan chad bya /
NK028(sa)001:7637: de'i bar la slob bu khrus bya /
NK028(sa)001:7638: gos sar ba gyon la bla ma'i g.yas phyogs su
NK028(sa)001:7639: gral rims su 'dug la bla ma la zhu ba
NK028(sa)001:7640: ni / slob bu rnams kyi thal mo sbyar la dang la bzod par gsol ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:7641: ho mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid /
NK028(sa)001:7642: mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rgyal
NK028(sa)001:7643: ba rgya mtsho zhing gi rdul snyed dang bcas pa
NK028(sa)001:7644: rnams gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:7645: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba rnams 'khor ba las nges par phyung nas /
NK028(sa)001:7646: 'gro ba sems can rnams kyi don bgyi ba'i slad du /
NK028(sa)001:7647: byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed nas bslab pa mthar phyin par 'tshal bas /
NK028(sa)001:7648: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis zhal bstan cing
NK028(sa)001:7649: byin gyis brlabs pa dang dbang bskur du gsol lo
NK028(sa)001:7651: khyad par gyi sems bskyed phog pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:7654: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang /
NK028(sa)001:7658: 'jig 'jug byang chub kyis sems bskyed do //
NK028(sa)001:7659: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK028(sa)001:7660: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK028(sa)001:7661: gnas pa med pa thams cad gnas /
NK028(sa)001:7662: gnas pa nyid na'ang gnas pa med //
NK028(sa)001:7664: gnas pa byang chub kyi sems bskyed do //
NK028(sa)001:7665: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos /
NK028(sa)001:7666: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang /
NK028(sa)001:7667: dmigs pa med la thams cad dmigs /
NK028(sa)001:7668: dmigs pa nyid na'ang dmigs pa med /
NK028(sa)001:7669: ces smon pa byang chub kyi sems bskyed do //
NK028(sa)001:7670: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK028(sa)001:7671: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK028(sa)001:7674: ces mthar phyin pa byang chub kyi sems bskyed do //
NK028(sa)001:7676: slob dpon snying rje'i dbang gi sems dang ldan pas //
NK028(sa)001:7678: e ma bde gshegs snying po las //
NK028(sa)001:7679: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK028(sa)001:7680: sna tshogs lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK028(sa)001:7681: gnas dang sdug bsngal la sogs pa //
NK028(sa)001:7682: bdag dang bdag gir so sor 'dzin //
NK028(sa)001:7683: sus kyang ma bcings bcing med de //
NK028(sa)001:7684: bcing par bya la yod ma yin //
NK028(sa)001:7685: bcing med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:7686: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK028(sa)001:7687: khyed la rab tu bstan par bya //
NK028(sa)001:7690: de nas brod pa bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:7693: dkyil 'khor don dang yon tan rnams //
NK028(sa)001:7694: gsal bya rab tu brod pa bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:7696: 'dir gsang ba mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi dkyil 'khor la don bzhi ste /
NK028(sa)001:7698: nges tshig dgos ched rnams grangs so //
NK028(sa)001:7699: ngo bo ni gtso 'khor tshogs pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:7702: gtso bo ni dkyil 'khor la 'khor gyis bskor ba'i phyir ro //
NK028(sa)001:7703: dkyil 'khor bye brag gi nges tshig ni /
NK028(sa)001:7704: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor gyi nges tshig rgyas pa'i don gsum pa las /
NK028(sa)001:7705: 'das pa rtag tu dkyil 'khor yin te //
NK028(sa)001:7706: lo ga sna tshogs 'khor du gsungs /
NK028(sa)001:7708: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin dang /
NK028(sa)001:7711: tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dang bzhi'i nges tshig ni //
NK028(sa)001:7713: rdo rje sems dpa' dkyil 'khor yin te //
NK028(sa)001:7714: rang bzhin lha dang lha mo'i 'khor zhes so //
NK028(sa)001:7715: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor kyi nges tshig ni //
NK028(sa)001:7716: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK028(sa)001:7720: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs par byed pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:7723: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dang //
NK028(sa)001:7725: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan /
NK028(sa)001:7727: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis /
NK028(sa)001:7728: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK028(sa)001:7729: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK028(sa)001:7730: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK028(sa)001:7731: chos nyid rang bzhin gyi spros pa dang bral ba la /
NK028(sa)001:7732: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rdzogs pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:7733: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor la zhi khro gnyis te /
NK028(sa)001:7734: de re re yang sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor lnga lnga'o //
NK028(sa)001:7736: don dam rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor las la g.yos
NK028(sa)001:7737: par kun rdzob snod bcud sna tshogs su rang snang
NK028(sa)001:7738: pa'o // lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ni las dang bya bas lhag pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:7739: de yang dbye na bzhi ste /
NK028(sa)001:7747: rang bzhin nyid kyi ngang la 'dris pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:7748: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ni //
NK028(sa)001:7749: bsgoms pa'i bya bas lhag pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:7750: zhi khro'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:7751: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK028(sa)001:7752: phyi nang gsang ba gsum ste /
NK028(sa)001:7755: gsang ba bde ba'i ye shes so //
NK028(sa)001:7756: tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK028(sa)001:7757: zhi ba la tshom bu gcig gsum pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:7758: khro bo la gcig gsum lnga pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi don bsdus pa tsam bshad pa'am /
NK028(sa)001:7759: rgyud gyi khog 'bubs nas bshad pa bzhin rgyas par yang rung ngo //
NK028(sa)001:7760: de nas slob ma rnams kyis gsol ba gdab par bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:7761: tshig rjes su don sems zhing /
NK028(sa)001:7762: rdo rje sems gtso khyod la 'dud //
NK028(sa)001:7763: thar lam chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK028(sa)001:7764: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang /
NK028(sa)001:7765: mgon po dpa' bo skyabs song ste //
NK028(sa)001:7766: theg chen khang par zhugs pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:7767: mkhyen rabs ye shes bdag la gsol //
NK028(sa)001:7768: zhes gsol ba btab pa'i slob bu rnams //
NK028(sa)001:7769: rdo rje slob dpon nam las slob kyis rdo rje phyed byin la /
NK028(sa)001:7770: bu 'dir shog cig ci bde ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:7771: las spyod rim par 'gro ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:7772: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje gzung //
NK028(sa)001:7773: rdzogs pa'i ye shes bde chen la //
NK028(sa)001:7774: dmigs pa med par gnas phyir du //
NK028(sa)001:7775: ser sna spangs pa'i dngas yid kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7776: stong zhing rang sems brtan par gzung //
NK028(sa)001:7777: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rdzogs dbang sbyin //
NK028(sa)001:7778: zhes gnas khang gi nang ngam //
NK028(sa)001:7779: dkyil 'khor gyi nye 'khor du drangs la /
NK028(sa)001:7780: de nas slob dpon rnams bde yangs su 'dug la lhar bskyed de /
NK028(sa)001:7781: de yang bgegs bskrad sgrib pa dral /
NK028(sa)001:7782: tshe la gsum gyis rdo rje sems dpa' bskyed de /
NK028(sa)001:7786: thog ma tshe mi yar bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:7788: dbang phyug gi thugs ka'i sa bon las yi ge b+h+rum re slob ma rnams kyi dpral bar 'phros /
NK028(sa)001:7789: b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud+d+he zhes brjod bas /
NK028(sa)001:7790: zla gam dmar po'i gzhal yas khang gnam sgo gcig pa /
NK028(sa)001:7792: de'i nang du h+aum zhes brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:7793: slob ma'i tshe'i dngos po thams cad h+aum la bsdu /
NK028(sa)001:7794: badz+ra h+aum ka ra h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:7796: h+aum ka ra sngon po tshe'i bum pa bsnams pa cig tu bsam /
NK028(sa)001:7797: zla gam gyi gnam sgom la /
NK028(sa)001:7798: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum phata //
NK028(sa)001:7800: khro bo mi g.yo ba ljang nag ral gri sdigs
NK028(sa)001:7801: 'dzub mdzad pa bskyed nas sgo bsrungs bar bsam nas
NK028(sa)001:7802: / yi dam gyi lha'i nga rgyal gyis /
NK028(sa)001:7803: bi shwa badz+ra gyis sngags kyis sprul pa spro /
NK028(sa)001:7804: bden pa brjod pa'i rjes la /
NK028(sa)001:7806: gnod cing 'tshe ba'i 'byung po thams cad 'dir ma gnas par dengs shig /
NK028(sa)001:7808: sum+b+ha ni sum+b+ha h+aum zhes lan gsum gyis bskrad do //
NK028(sa)001:7810: rdo rje slob dpon gyis lag g.yas kyi sor mo'i
NK028(sa)001:7811: bre kha lnga la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la gnas
NK028(sa)001:7813: g.yon gyi sor mo'i bre kha lnga la gnas pa'i dpa' mo 'bru lnga bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:7815: zhes dpa' bo dpa' mo sbyar //
NK028(sa)001:7817: badz+ra b+han+d+ha zhes phyag rgya bsdam /
NK028(sa)001:7818: bden pa brjod pa'i rjes la /
NK028(sa)001:7819: slob bu 'di rnams kyi rgyud la yod pa'i las kyi sgrib pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:7820: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:7822: lta ba'i dman pa'i sgrib pa /
NK028(sa)001:7823: chos kyis 'phongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:7824: bag chags ngan pa'i sgrib pa lwo nge sgrib pa'i
NK028(sa)001:7825: phung po ji snyed pa thams cad phyag rgya'i 'od
NK028(sa)001:7827: badz+ra ban+d+ha tra th+aa zhes pa'i sngags mang du brjod cing /
NK028(sa)001:7829: 'bru bcu rigs lnga yab yum du gyur pa sbyor
NK028(sa)001:7830: ba mdzad pas byang chub kyi sems su zhu ba'i
NK028(sa)001:7831: 'od zer gyis slob bu rnams kyi sgrib pa mtha'
NK028(sa)001:7832: dag bsregs shing // h+aum ka ra dang /
NK028(sa)001:7833: mi g.yo ba yang 'od du zhu nas slob bu rnams kyis rnam shes dang gcig tu gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:7834: dngul chu zhun ma lta bur gnas pa de /
NK028(sa)001:7835: cho ga gsum gyis rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog
NK028(sa)001:7836: dkar po brgyan cha lugs dang ldan par bskyed la
NK028(sa)001:7837: / shu nya ta la sogs pa'i sngags kyis dbang bskur /
NK028(sa)001:7838: gnas gsum du rdo rje gtug cing 'bru gsum brjod pas byin gyis brlabs par bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:7839: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya badz+ra la sogs pa brjod /
NK028(sa)001:7840: byin gyis brlabs pa'i rtags su /
NK028(sa)001:7841: dpral bar sku'i lha snang mdzad dkar po 'khor lo gyis mtshan pa 'dzin pa /
NK028(sa)001:7842: de bzhin du mgrin pa dang snying gar sku gsung thugs kyis lha 'adre'o //
NK028(sa)001:7843: rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgyas badz+ra ka ba tsi rak+sha rak+sha zhes rdo rje'i go khrab bkon /
NK028(sa)001:7844: rdo rje bsrungs pa'i phyag rgya dang /
NK028(sa)001:7845: trum gis khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin dang /
NK028(sa)001:7846: khro bo mi 'chi thal sbyor gnyis kyis lus gyi gnas drug bsrungs bar bsgoms mo //
NK028(sa)001:7847: de nas slob bu rnams kyi dngos grub kyis bltas brtags pa'i don du /
NK028(sa)001:7848: so shing sor bcu gnyis pa dri bzang po'i chus byug cing //
NK028(sa)001:7849: rtse mor me tog gi 'phreng ba bcings pa slob ma rnams la sbyin zhing //
NK028(sa)001:7850: de rnams kyis kyang rtse mos so rtsa bru /
NK028(sa)001:7852: sgrib pa dag pas bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:7853: badz+ri ma h+aa sa ma brti h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:7855: so shing gi rtse mo sos bzung nas /
NK028(sa)001:7856: mkha' dbyings phyag rgya'i dbus nas man+dala gyis steng du bud thabs kyis skyur bas /
NK028(sa)001:7859: mtshams bzhir na dngos grub dman pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:7860: de nas dri bzang po'i chu la /
NK028(sa)001:7861: badz+ra sa t+wa +aah zhes pas rdo rje sems dpa'
NK028(sa)001:7862: zhu ba'i chu ru byin gyis brlabs pa khyor bar
NK028(sa)001:7863: blugs la / sarba shwa d+ha na ye h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:7864: ces brjod pas 'thung du bzhug cing /
NK028(sa)001:7866: de nas rmi lam bar chad kyis mi tshugs par
NK028(sa)001:7867: bya ba'i don du bsrungs skud dmar po gsum bsgril
NK028(sa)001:7868: la / big+nana ta krita a mri ta ku n+da li ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:7870: mdud pa gsum byas la pho'i dpung pa g.yon dang /
NK028(sa)001:7874: srin lag gi dri chab bzhag ste /
NK028(sa)001:7875: bdud rtsi 'khyil pas mdud sgo bsrungs bar bsam mo //
NK028(sa)001:7876: de nas rmi lam brtag par bya ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:7877: ku sha'i chun bu gnyis gnyis /
NK028(sa)001:7880: stan dang sngas kyi don du byin la /
NK028(sa)001:7882: badz+ra ki li k+ai la ya h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:7883: phur pa sras mchog tu byin gyis brlabs la slob ma rnams la byin /
NK028(sa)001:7884: mched lcam rnams kyis phyag byas mes rtse gcig tu bzhag go /
NK028(sa)001:7885: de nas zab mo'i chos bshad pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:7886: 'jig rten du ni kun mkhyen dag /
NK028(sa)001:7887: u dum wa ra'i me tog bzhin /
NK028(sa)001:7888: brgya lam na ni re 'ga' zhig /
NK028(sa)001:7890: gsang sngags spyod pa'i tshul 'byung ba //
NK028(sa)001:7891: de bas kyang ni dkon pa ste //
NK028(sa)001:7892: zhes pas 'jig rten na yang dag pa'i sangs rgyas 'byung ba dkon te /
NK028(sa)001:7893: de nas 'byung bar dkon pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:7894: 'jig rten na sangs rgyas 'byung ba'i brtags su /
NK028(sa)001:7895: me tog u dum wa ra 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:7896: gang du 'byung na mtsho ma dros pa'i byang phyogs
NK028(sa)001:7897: ri nag po spun dgu 'das pa'i pha rol na
NK028(sa)001:7898: / me tog u dum wa ra'i tshal zhes bya ba /
NK028(sa)001:7899: me tog 'od dang ldan zhing kha dog gsal ba /
NK028(sa)001:7900: dris 'khor yug dpag tshad tsam du khyab cing /
NK028(sa)001:7901: 'khor ba thams cad kyi nad la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal sel bar nus pa yin /
NK028(sa)001:7902: tshad ni shing rta'i 'phang lo tsam ste /
NK028(sa)001:7903: sangs rgyas de rgyal rigs su 'byon na dkar po /
NK028(sa)001:7904: bram ze la 'byon na ser po //
NK028(sa)001:7905: de dag dga' ldan nas 'phos te /
NK028(sa)001:7906: yum gyi lhums su zhugs pa na me tog kha 'bus //
NK028(sa)001:7908: sangs rgyas pa na rab tu rgyas /
NK028(sa)001:7909: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang sbrang rtsi'i rgyun bab //
NK028(sa)001:7910: de'i tshe 'du byed btang ba na rab tu rnyid /
NK028(sa)001:7911: yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa na lo ma dang 'bras bu lhag par 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:7912: me tog de 'jig rten na 'khor los bsgyur ba 'byung ba'i dus na'ang mi 'byung na /
NK028(sa)001:7913: gzhan so so'i skye bo lta smos kyang ci dgos //
NK028(sa)001:7914: de bas kyang gsang sngags 'byung bar dkon te /
NK028(sa)001:7915: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyis ma gsungs /
NK028(sa)001:7916: ma 'ongs ba'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyis gsungs bar mi 'gyur /
NK028(sa)001:7917: da ltar kyi sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das 'di kho na'i smon lam las 'byung ba yin te /
NK028(sa)001:7918: de yang sngon byung du rgyal po a sho ka
NK028(sa)001:7919: zhes bya ba'i btsun mo la sras stong dus cig
NK028(sa)001:7921: bram ze bltas mkhan gyis bskal bzang 'di la sangs rgyas par lung bstan cing /
NK028(sa)001:7922: bum pa gcig gi nang du stong gi ming yig bcug nas mchod pa sna tshogs kyis mchod cing /
NK028(sa)001:7923: gang gis sangs rgyas snga brtags pas /
NK028(sa)001:7924: dang por byung ba dang bor sangs rgyas /
NK028(sa)001:7925: bar du byung ba bar du sangs rgyas /
NK028(sa)001:7926: tha mar byung ba tha mar sangs rgyas par lung bstan la /
NK028(sa)001:7927: rtsod ldan gyi dus su 'dul dka' bar dgongs te /
NK028(sa)001:7928: sangs rgyas gang gis kyang ming yig ma bzhed pa la thub pa nyid kyis blangs nas /
NK028(sa)001:7930: gsang sngags bla na med pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo
NK028(sa)001:7931: bskor bar gyur cig ces smon lam btab pa bzhin
NK028(sa)001:7932: du ste / bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa 'di nyid dang po byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:7933: bar du bskal pa grogs med pa gsum la tshogs bsags /
NK028(sa)001:7935: mthar mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi tshul du sangs rgyas /
NK028(sa)001:7936: de nas thog mar theg pa chung ngu la mos
NK028(sa)001:7937: pa'i gang zag la bka' dang po bden ba bzhi'i
NK028(sa)001:7939: bar du theg pa chen po la mos pa'i gang zag la /
NK028(sa)001:7940: bka' bar pa mtshan nyid med pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor /
NK028(sa)001:7941: mthar theg pa sna tshogs la mos pa'i gang zag la /
NK028(sa)001:7942: don dam pa nges pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ro /
NK028(sa)001:7943: bye brag tu yo ga la sogs theg pa drug pa'i dbang ni /
NK028(sa)001:7944: nyan thos kyi theg pa'i dbang chu bo ni ren dza rar bskur /
NK028(sa)001:7945: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'i dbang kun dga' ra bar bskur /
NK028(sa)001:7946: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa'i dbang bya rgod phung po'i ri'am rgyal po'i khab tu bskur /
NK028(sa)001:7947: kri ya'i dbang wa ra na sir bskur /
NK028(sa)001:7948: yo ga'i dbang me ri 'bar ba'i khar bskur te /
NK028(sa)001:7949: ma smin pa rnams smin par byas /
NK028(sa)001:7950: rnam par grol ba'i lam la bkod nas /
NK028(sa)001:7951: mya ngan las 'das par dgongs te /
NK028(sa)001:7952: 'khor 'dus pa rnams kyis nang na rdzu 'phrul cher brjod la bka' stsal pa /
NK028(sa)001:7953: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na nga'i slob ma ci yod pa bsdus shing gsungs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:7954: rdzu 'phrul can des thams cad bsdus pas 'dus par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:7955: de nas de dag rnams la bka' stsal pa /
NK028(sa)001:7956: kyee grogs po dag shes par gyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:7957: chos thams cad ni mi rtag pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:7958: 'byor ba thams cad ni mthar gud pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:7959: dngos po thams cad ni nges par 'jig pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:7960: gang zag gi srog gi dbang po la skye shi
NK028(sa)001:7961: yod pa'i phyir nga yongs su mya ngan las 'das
NK028(sa)001:7962: pas su dgra the tshom ma chod pa dag dris
NK028(sa)001:7963: shig ces bka' stsal ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:7965: 'dren pa'i theg pa rnam gsum la //
NK028(sa)001:7966: gang zag rim par bkod lags na //
NK028(sa)001:7967: mnyam pas blangs dor mi spyod cing //
NK028(sa)001:7968: byang chub ye nas mi tshol ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:7969: thabs mchog dpag gis mi langs ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:7970: nges ba'i theg pa yongs ma gsungs //
NK028(sa)001:7973: 'dren pa'i theg pa gsum bo dag /
NK028(sa)001:7974: nges par bcom ldan gsungs lags na //
NK028(sa)001:7975: rgyu 'bras lhun grub du spyod pa //
NK028(sa)001:7976: lhun grub theg pa cis ma gsungs //
NK028(sa)001:7977: zhus pa'i lan du bcom ldan gyis /
NK028(sa)001:7978: rgyu nas byung ba rgyu yi chos //
NK028(sa)001:7979: 'khor lo rab tu bskor byas nas //
NK028(sa)001:7980: 'bras bu'i theg pa nye lam zhig /
NK028(sa)001:7984: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK028(sa)001:7985: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis la //
NK028(sa)001:7986: 'dzam bu gling gi lho phyogs na /
NK028(sa)001:7987: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK028(sa)001:7988: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:7989: rgyal po dza zhes bya ba la //
NK028(sa)001:7990: thugs rje mthun pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:7991: gsang sngags 'byung bar lung bstan no //
NK028(sa)001:7992: de yang brgyud ma h+aa yo ga'i chos byung tshul ni /
NK028(sa)001:7993: za hor gyi rgyal khams zhes bya ba'i nye 'khor na /
NK028(sa)001:7994: ston pas zhabs kyis bcag pa'i sa /
NK028(sa)001:7995: phyag na rdo rje'i pho brang byang phyogs lcang lo can gyis gnas /
NK028(sa)001:7996: ri ma ya gnam lcags thog yod pa'i rtse mo zhes bya ba zhig yod de /
NK028(sa)001:7997: ri de yang rtse mo ri dwags kyi rgyal po seng ge 'khras par gyur ba /
NK028(sa)001:7998: 'dab shod ni gcan zan gyi rgyal po stag gis mkhreng bar gyur pa /
NK028(sa)001:7999: sman rtsa ba dang myu gu dang sdong po dang /
NK028(sa)001:8002: 'bras bu'i sman sna tshogs kyi shing skyes pa /
NK028(sa)001:8003: ngos la brag dkar po seng ge khyi tshugs su
NK028(sa)001:8004: gtad pa 'dra ba grangs dang grangs kyis yod pa
NK028(sa)001:8005: / de'i shar ngos na kri shang a su ra zhes bya ba'i gnod sbyin gyi phug yod de /
NK028(sa)001:8006: de yang sgo zla gam la ngo mtshar gyi ri mo rang byung /
NK028(sa)001:8007: phugs rin po che zur brgyad la nyi zla'i ri mo rang snang ba /
NK028(sa)001:8008: ri de'i spyi bo na bya ka lan ta ka zhes bya ba don gnyis par mi sgrogs ste /
NK028(sa)001:8009: gcig tu sgrogs par byed pa'i tshang bcas pa /
NK028(sa)001:8010: dgon gnas der gang zag las dang bskal bar ldan pa rnams kyi bsgrod cing phyin pa las /
NK028(sa)001:8011: las dang skal pa med pa rnams kyis sgrod cing phyin par mi nus pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:8012: de lta bu'i gnas khyad par can de shar phyogs
NK028(sa)001:8013: za hor gyi yul gyi a pa tra mu dz+ny+aa
NK028(sa)001:8014: na zhes pa rgyal po'i rigs can /
NK028(sa)001:8015: gsang sngags go ba'i skal pa dang ldan pa /
NK028(sa)001:8016: 'gug pa'i sgra dzahzhesa pa'i ming can de /
NK028(sa)001:8017: rten 'brel snying po la bsgrub pa byas kyang zer /
NK028(sa)001:8018: gsang sngags phyi rgyud la bsgrub pa mdzad cing bzhugs
NK028(sa)001:8019: pa'i rmi lam du gsang sngags mi yul 'byung ba'i
NK028(sa)001:8021: dang po ni ri de'i rtse mor dpal mor dpal phyag na rdo rje pho brang du byon nas /
NK028(sa)001:8022: sku'i khrun las 'od sngon po 'phros pas /
NK028(sa)001:8023: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad bsregs //
NK028(sa)001:8024: gsung gi sgra 'brug stong lta bur ldir /
NK028(sa)001:8025: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas 'od zer 'bar ba cig shar bas rgyal po'i nyid kyi thugs kar thim /
NK028(sa)001:8026: nyi ma'i 'od 'bar ba cig shar bas spyi bor thim /
NK028(sa)001:8027: zla ba'i 'od 'bar ba cig shar rgyal po'i rkang
NK028(sa)001:8028: mthil du thim nas snang srid kyi gtos thams cad
NK028(sa)001:8029: rgyal po'i lto ba na 'phyo ba cig rmis so
NK028(sa)001:8030: // gnyis pa ni sangs rgyas thams cad dang chos
NK028(sa)001:8031: kyi sgro gleng mdzad cing nyi zla la zhon te
NK028(sa)001:8032: gser gyi 'khor lo bskor nas srid pa gsum la
NK028(sa)001:8033: dbang bsgyur ba cig rmis so //
NK028(sa)001:8034: gsum pa ni nam mkha' la sprin gser gyi kha dog can 'thibs /
NK028(sa)001:8035: cho 'phrul gyi 'brug snyan par tshim par ni grags /
NK028(sa)001:8036: rin po che sna tshogs kyi rmugs pa ni 'thibs /
NK028(sa)001:8038: snang srid gsal ba'i glog ni 'gyus nas /
NK028(sa)001:8039: rin chen sna tshogs kyi char mngon par bab pa zhig rmis /
NK028(sa)001:8040: bzhi pa 'jig rten gyi gtos kun ni bsgyur /
NK028(sa)001:8041: rin po che sgron me 'bar ba shar bas snang srid kyi mun pa thams cad ni sangs /
NK028(sa)001:8042: bdud rtsi dang sman gyi chu rgyun byung bas 'gro ba thams cad kyi gcong snying ni sbyangs /
NK028(sa)001:8043: 'gro ba thams cad rdo rje rnal 'byor zhes pa'i sgra /
NK028(sa)001:8044: di ri ri sgrog pa zhig rmis so //
NK028(sa)001:8045: lnga pa ni sprin gyi dkyil nas nyi ma'i dkyil
NK028(sa)001:8046: 'khor la rin po che sna tshogs kyi 'od zer
NK028(sa)001:8047: can cig shar ba'i dkyil na /
NK028(sa)001:8048: rat+na smug po dpal be'u sgro mdog bcas pa phyi
NK028(sa)001:8049: nang med pa gsal ba'i nang nas gser gyi glegs
NK028(sa)001:8050: bam la beed+aur+ya zhun mas rang nan du bris pa'i
NK028(sa)001:8051: glegs bam mang po zhig gis bltams pa skar mda'
NK028(sa)001:8052: ltung ba bzhin du babs pa zhig rmis so //
NK028(sa)001:8053: drug pa ni yang glegs bam dang po ting 'dzin rnams la /
NK028(sa)001:8056: lha dang lha mo tshad med pa rnams yon tan gyi sgra sgrog cing p+au dza dbul te /
NK028(sa)001:8058: rol mo'i cha byad mang po 'don zhing bskor ba cig rmis so //
NK028(sa)001:8060: nam mkha'i sprin gseb nas lung bstan pa'i sgra byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:8061: las dang skal par rab ldan cing //
NK028(sa)001:8062: rgyal bas 'byung bar lung bstan pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:8063: bsod nams dra ba khyod sprul pas //
NK028(sa)001:8064: ji ltar lung bstan chen po bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:8065: de ltar dus 'dir mngon shar gyis //
NK028(sa)001:8066: 'khor ba'i snying po sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:8067: nga yi cho 'phrul byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:8068: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK028(sa)001:8069: bskal ldan khyod la bstan par bya /
NK028(sa)001:8070: ma la ya zhes bya ba'i ri /
NK028(sa)001:8071: dgon pa chen po'i gnas zhig na //
NK028(sa)001:8072: ye shes snying po can rnams kyi //
NK028(sa)001:8073: gsang bar nan gyis de la sems kyi me long gis //
NK028(sa)001:8074: mngon du gsal bar rtogs ma thag /
NK028(sa)001:8075: sangs rgyas sa la bskal pa mnyam //
NK028(sa)001:8076: bde ba can zhes bya ba'i ri //
NK028(sa)001:8077: 'od kyi rgyal po zhes bya'i ri //
NK028(sa)001:8078: kun rig bde ba chen por gyur //
NK028(sa)001:8079: rdo rje gsang chen gsang ba yi //
NK028(sa)001:8080: dam pa'i mdzod gsum rabs cig ni //
NK028(sa)001:8081: lha dang mi yi rig 'dzin la //
NK028(sa)001:8082: rim par brgyud de grags par 'gyur //
NK028(sa)001:8083: zhes lung bstan par rmis so //
NK028(sa)001:8084: de nas rgyal po gnyid sad nas rab tu dgyes te //
NK028(sa)001:8086: rmi lam du ji ltar byung ba'i tshul rnams bzlas nas /
NK028(sa)001:8087: rmi lam 'di dag dang sbyar na bdag las dang
NK028(sa)001:8088: skal bar ldan par nges so zhes gsung nas pho
NK028(sa)001:8089: brang gi yang thog tu phyin pas /
NK028(sa)001:8090: rmi lam du ji ltar byung ba dang mthun par
NK028(sa)001:8091: dpal phyag na rdo rje'i sku gzugs rin po che
NK028(sa)001:8092: las grub pa cig mthong nas //
NK028(sa)001:8093: rgyal po dgyes te bskor ba dang mchod pa dang byas nas tshig tu brjod pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:8094: sngon tshe gong nas bsgrubs pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:8095: las kyis mjal ba'i lha mchog 'di //
NK028(sa)001:8096: bskal pa brgyar yang mi gtong ngo //
NK028(sa)001:8097: e ma 'o ngo mtshar rmad kyis sku //
NK028(sa)001:8098: 'dren pa mchog gi dpal lags gang //
NK028(sa)001:8099: mos pas gzungs kyi lha mchog 'dzin /
NK028(sa)001:8100: zhes gsol nas yi dam lha ru bcas so //
NK028(sa)001:8101: de nas yang rgyal po'i thugs dgongs la rtags 'di dang yang ldan pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:8102: ri bo 'di yang dpal phyag na rdo rje'i rang bzhin du 'dug pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:8103: rig 'dzin mang po grub pa thob pa'i gnas yin pa gtam snying du thos pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:8104: rmi lam du mthun pa'i bltas rnams yang /
NK028(sa)001:8105: nam mkha' la mngon du snang ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:8106: gcan gzan gdug pa can rnams kyang //
NK028(sa)001:8107: dge ba dad pa'i tshul 'di dag ldan pas nges par bsgrub po gsungs nas /
NK028(sa)001:8108: gzungs brnyan de la brten nas zla ba bdun du bsgrubs pas /
NK028(sa)001:8109: rmi lam du ji ltar byung ba dang tshul mthun par glegs bam dang /
NK028(sa)001:8110: po ti mang po'i char mngon sum du babs nas /
NK028(sa)001:8111: yang phyag na rdo rje sku gzugs de nyid kyi mdun du rang byon nas /
NK028(sa)001:8112: der po ti rnams la rgyal po rab tu dga'
NK028(sa)001:8113: ba'i tshul gyis bltas pas tshig 'bru cig gi yang
NK028(sa)001:8114: brda ma mjal nas the tshom du gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:8116: sngar tshul la rtags 'di dang ldan na glegs bam
NK028(sa)001:8117: 'di rnams la zab mo gsang ba'i don cig yin
NK028(sa)001:8118: par nges na / bdag gis ma rtogs pa 'di ces nyes mnyam nas bshums so //
NK028(sa)001:8119: de nas yang cung zad cig nas the tshom gyi nyon mongs pa zhi ste /
NK028(sa)001:8120: de yang 'jig rten gyi khams na 'di dag brda' 'jal ba su zhig la yod ces bsgrags pas /
NK028(sa)001:8121: za hor gyi rgyal bo u pa r+aa dz+aa zhes
NK028(sa)001:8122: bya ba'i bshes gnyen can yod pa des shes pas
NK028(sa)001:8123: rigs so zhes thos nas pho nya rdzangs te lo
NK028(sa)001:8124: rgyus zhib tu gsol nas spyan drangs pas /
NK028(sa)001:8126: gal te bdag gis ma shes na der phyin pa
NK028(sa)001:8127: tshul ma yin par 'gyur gyi de dag glang po
NK028(sa)001:8128: che la khol las 'dir skyol zhig /
NK028(sa)001:8129: ces gsungs nas po ti de dag glang po che la bkal te bskyal bas /
NK028(sa)001:8131: tshig 'bru cig kyang ma shes nas /
NK028(sa)001:8132: 'di dag bdag gis spyod yul du ma gyur gyi /
NK028(sa)001:8133: rgyal po nyid kyi dgongs pa'i rtsal gyis dpag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:8135: rgyal po'i thugs dgongs la 'di dag kun gyis thun
NK028(sa)001:8136: mong min pa ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i don
NK028(sa)001:8138: sangs rgyas kyi chos thos pa'i gzhung las byung ba bzhin du tshogs bsogs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:8140: mchod pa rgya chen po byas nas brtags pas /
NK028(sa)001:8141: rdo rje sems dpa' bsgrub pa'i le'u brda' mjal bar gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:8142: de nas le'u de'i gzhung bzhin du bsgrubs pas /
NK028(sa)001:8143: rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal bstan nas rigs kyi bu dngos grub ci 'dod gsungs pas /
NK028(sa)001:8144: bdag ni po ti dang glegs bam 'di rnams kyi don rtogs par 'tshal lo zhes zhus pas /
NK028(sa)001:8146: rigs kyis bu rang gi rgyud sbyongs dang //
NK028(sa)001:8147: khyod kyi ston pa ni gsang ba'i bdag pos don ma lus pa bston par 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:8150: de nas yang rang gi rgyud sbyangs pas dpal phyag
NK028(sa)001:8151: na rdo rje mngon sum du byon nas de'i tshe
NK028(sa)001:8152: nyid kyis rdo rje nam mkha' la spar nas brtul
NK028(sa)001:8153: bzhugs mdzad de / h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:8155: rigs ma yin pa rigs min 'gyur //
NK028(sa)001:8156: skal ldan can gyi rigs su 'gyur //
NK028(sa)001:8157: thams cad rdo rje gsang ba gsor /
NK028(sa)001:8158: rak+sha kro d+ha tsit+ta dz+wa la ram zhes brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:8159: 'jig rten dregs pa can thams cad rdo khab len
NK028(sa)001:8160: la lcags 'du ba'i tshul gyis thams cad 'khor du
NK028(sa)001:8161: 'dus te de dag la rdo rje gsang ba'i ming
NK028(sa)001:8162: so sor btags nas grub pa lung gi gsang sgo
NK028(sa)001:8163: phye ste / dam pa'i mdzod gsum dang /
NK028(sa)001:8164: tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad la sogs pa rgyal po dza
NK028(sa)001:8165: dang dam pa'i rigs can lnga la sogs la bshad
NK028(sa)001:8166: de / de nas de'i rjes su tshom bu tshogs kyis bsgrubs pa la sogs byas pas /
NK028(sa)001:8167: rgya gar ba dang bod kyi gang zag mang po lhag med du sangs rgyas so //
NK028(sa)001:8168: de nas rgyal po dza'i in+t+ra po d+his gtso byas pas tshom bu tshogs bsgrubs pas /
NK028(sa)001:8169: 'bum phrag gcig dang bcas pa lhag med du chos kyi dbyings sangs rgyas kyi sar gshegs so //
NK028(sa)001:8170: de'i rjes su de bzhin du bsgrubs pas ku ku
NK028(sa)001:8171: r+aa dzas gtso byas pa'i khri dang bcas pa lhag
NK028(sa)001:8172: med du chos kyi dbyings su gshegs so //
NK028(sa)001:8173: de'i rjes su u pa ra dzas gtso byas pa'i
NK028(sa)001:8174: stong dang bcas pa lhag med du chos kyi dbyings
NK028(sa)001:8175: su gshegs so // de'i rjes su sras r+aa dza
NK028(sa)001:8176: has tis gtso byas pa'i tshom bu lnga brgya dang
NK028(sa)001:8177: bcas pa lhag med du chos kyi dbyings su gshegs
NK028(sa)001:8178: su gshegs so // so // de'i rjes su sras
NK028(sa)001:8179: mo mgo mas gtso byas pa'i sum brgya dang bcas
NK028(sa)001:8180: pa lhag med du chos kyi dbyings su gshegs so
NK028(sa)001:8181: su gshegs so // so // // gzhan yang rgya
NK028(sa)001:8182: gar na ma h+aa yo ga'i chos 'di nyams su
NK028(sa)001:8183: blangs pas lhag med du sangs rgyas pa la sogs
NK028(sa)001:8184: pa bsam gyis mi khyab cing gzhal las 'das so
NK028(sa)001:8185: su gshegs so // so // // // bod na'ang
NK028(sa)001:8186: yer pa'i brag la grub chen brgya rtsa brgyad lhag
NK028(sa)001:8187: med du gshegs pa la sogs pa bsams las 'das
NK028(sa)001:8189: de lta bu'i chos 'di yid ches shing khungs btsun
NK028(sa)001:8190: pa byin brlabs mchog dang ldan pa 'di'i sgor zhugs
NK028(sa)001:8192: shing / dbang thob na tshe gcig lus gcig la
NK028(sa)001:8193: sangs rgyas bar 'gyur ba'i phan yon yod pas /
NK028(sa)001:8194: blo gzengs bstod shes pa brod phyung mdzod cig /
NK028(sa)001:8195: lung a nu yo ga'i brgyud byung tshul ni /
NK028(sa)001:8196: de nas lo brgyad dang bcu gnyis 'das pa na /
NK028(sa)001:8197: dam pa'i rigs can sems dpa' chen po dag /
NK028(sa)001:8198: nang du yang dag par 'jog pa las langs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:8199: 'jig rten gyi ston pa nub par gyur pas rma ga chad par ngus so //
NK028(sa)001:8200: kun kyang rang rang gi rdzu 'phrul gyis lang ga'i
NK028(sa)001:8201: yul gyi grong brdal gyi mtsho gling ri ma la
NK028(sa)001:8202: ya'i gnam lcags yod pa'i rtse la rdzu 'phrul gyis
NK028(sa)001:8203: bya bas mngon par rab tu 'dus so //
NK028(sa)001:8204: yongs su 'dus nas 'dus pa de kun kyang mgrin
NK028(sa)001:8205: gcig tu shin tu nyams thag pa'i nga ros smre
NK028(sa)001:8206: sngags kyi gdung ba bton pa ni 'di lta ste
NK028(sa)001:8207: / kye ma'o kyi h+aud kye ma ho klong //
NK028(sa)001:8208: ston pa'i sgron me'i 'od nub na //
NK028(sa)001:8209: 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel //
NK028(sa)001:8210: zhes pa la sogs pa'i gdug tshig nyi shu rtsa
NK028(sa)001:8211: gsum gyis phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas la gsol ba btab
NK028(sa)001:8212: pas // srid gsum 'gro ba gnyen gcig po //
NK028(sa)001:8213: rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams kyis gsan //
NK028(sa)001:8214: snying rje'i bdag po de dag kun //
NK028(sa)001:8215: lcang lo can gyi pho brang du //
NK028(sa)001:8216: gsang ba'i bdag po'i gnas su 'dus //
NK028(sa)001:8217: bskul ba chen po'i 'di skad gsungs //
NK028(sa)001:8218: gsang ba po yi bdag po khyod //
NK028(sa)001:8219: sngon gyi cho ga yal lam ci //
NK028(sa)001:8220: 'jig rten sdug bsngal mi shes bsam //
NK028(sa)001:8221: snying rjes sa la babs nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:8222: 'jig rten sdug bsngal bsal bar rig /
NK028(sa)001:8223: gsang bdag rdo rje 'dzin pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:8224: thog ma tha ma med pa ru //
NK028(sa)001:8225: bskul ba'i dus ni gar byur par //
NK028(sa)001:8226: bdag kyang de bzhin cho 'phrul snang //
NK028(sa)001:8227: gdung ba bsal bar zhal gyis bzhes //
NK028(sa)001:8228: de nas gsang bdag phyag rdor ni //
NK028(sa)001:8229: drag shul can ni bya ba'i ri //
NK028(sa)001:8230: gnod sbyin 'du ba'i sa yin te //
NK028(sa)001:8231: chos 'dzin rigs kyis bsgrub gnas su //
NK028(sa)001:8232: thugs rje'i sa la mngon srol gshegs //
NK028(sa)001:8233: sa rnams yongs su g.yos 'gyur te //
NK028(sa)001:8234: de tshe dam pa'i rigs can rnams //
NK028(sa)001:8235: dga' ba dang bcas the tshom skyes //
NK028(sa)001:8236: spros pa chen pos dri ba dris //
NK028(sa)001:8237: e ma ngo mtshad rmad re che //
NK028(sa)001:8238: skyes bu chen po khyed su zhig /
NK028(sa)001:8239: gang nas byon te gang ltar byon //
NK028(sa)001:8240: gang la brten nas gang du byon //
NK028(sa)001:8241: don gyi phyed ka ci zhig dris //
NK028(sa)001:8243: nga ni cig kyang mi spyod de //
NK028(sa)001:8244: mi 'khrugs rdo rje sems dpa' yin //
NK028(sa)001:8245: snying rjes g.yo zhing bskyod pa na //
NK028(sa)001:8246: srid pa gsum gyi gnyen gcig po //
NK028(sa)001:8247: stong pa chen po nga yi yul //
NK028(sa)001:8248: rdo rje rigs chen nga yi gdung //
NK028(sa)001:8249: pha ni thabs mchog dpag tu med //
NK028(sa)001:8250: ma ni shes rab brjod las 'das //
NK028(sa)001:8251: thog ma tha ma med pa'i tshe //
NK028(sa)001:8253: nga ni thabs kyis gnyen pa mkhan //
NK028(sa)001:8254: 'khor ba'i chu bo mtha' med las //
NK028(sa)001:8255: srid gsum bsgral bar dam bcas kyis //
NK028(sa)001:8257: nga ni thabs kyi mig mkhan te //
NK028(sa)001:8258: 'jig rten longs pa dpag med rnams //
NK028(sa)001:8259: lig thog bsal bar dam bcas kyis //
NK028(sa)001:8261: nga ni thabs kyi sman pa ste //
NK028(sa)001:8262: grong khyer gsum gyi nad pa rnams //
NK028(sa)001:8263: gcong snying sbyang bar dam bcas kyis //
NK028(sa)001:8265: nga ni thabs kyi sa mkhan ste //
NK028(sa)001:8266: 'gro ba lam log lam gtor rnams //
NK028(sa)001:8267: ma nor khrid par dam bcas kyis //
NK028(sa)001:8269: nga ni thugs rje spyan ras mkhan //
NK028(sa)001:8271: thams cad skyabs par dam bcas kyis //
NK028(sa)001:8273: nga ni rdo rje rdzongs chen te //
NK028(sa)001:8274: 'khor ba'i g.yul chen dmag dpung las //
NK028(sa)001:8277: nga ni thabs kyi tshong dpon te //
NK028(sa)001:8278: 'dod pa rgya mtsho mi ngoms rnams //
NK028(sa)001:8279: gter chen sbyin par dam bcas kyis //
NK028(sa)001:8281: nga ni thabs kyi sgron ma ste //
NK028(sa)001:8282: mun nag smag rum 'khyams pa rnams //
NK028(sa)001:8283: mun nag bsal bar dam bcas kyis //
NK028(sa)001:8285: nga ni yid bzhin nor bu ste //
NK028(sa)001:8286: gang dag yid bzhin 'dod pa rnams //
NK028(sa)001:8287: yid bzhin bskyang bar dam bcas kyis //
NK028(sa)001:8289: nga ni bka' yi lde mig ste //
NK028(sa)001:8290: bka' sgroms tha ram gsang ba rnams //
NK028(sa)001:8291: rnam par 'byed par dam bcas kyis //
NK028(sa)001:8293: nga ni bka' yi 'grel pa ste //
NK028(sa)001:8294: gsung gi glegs bam zab mo rnams //
NK028(sa)001:8295: nges par dgrol bar dam bcas kyis //
NK028(sa)001:8298: sngon du byung bas rigs can rnams //
NK028(sa)001:8299: mchog tu dga' ba cher bskyes te //
NK028(sa)001:8300: dga' mgu rangs pa'i bsam pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:8301: lus btud gus sbyar spyan sngar 'dug /
NK028(sa)001:8302: gsang ba'i bdag po bka' stsal pa //
NK028(sa)001:8303: sems kyi dkyil 'khor de bzhin nyid //
NK028(sa)001:8304: nam mkha' bzhin tu nub pa med //
NK028(sa)001:8305: rang bzhin ye nas 'od gsal bas //
NK028(sa)001:8306: de la gang sgrib de nyid sel //
NK028(sa)001:8307: zhes pa la sogs sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs
NK028(sa)001:8308: pa 'dus pa'i mdo la sogs pa mdo snga ma
NK028(sa)001:8309: bdun dang / phyi ma bdun la sogs pa rnams gsungs pas /
NK028(sa)001:8312: gnod sbyin la skar mda' ltung //
NK028(sa)001:8313: srin po la blo gros thabs ldan /
NK028(sa)001:8314: mi la dge snyen li tsa byi dri ma med par grags pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:8315: dam pa'i rigs can lngas shes bya'i chos thams cad rang rig pa'i mngon sum du rtogs nas /
NK028(sa)001:8316: tshe gcig lus cig la sangs rgyas so //
NK028(sa)001:8318: bod kyi gang zag mang po smin cing grol te
NK028(sa)001:8319: lhag med du sangs rgyas pa la sogs bsam gyis
NK028(sa)001:8320: mi khyab pa'o // de lta bu'i chos zab mo
NK028(sa)001:8321: 'di dang mjal ba ni ngo mtshar shin tu che'o
NK028(sa)001:8322: snyam pa'i dga' spro chen po mdzad par zhu //
NK028(sa)001:8323: man ngag rdzogs pa chen po'i chos byung tshul ni /
NK028(sa)001:8324: lha yul du kun dga' snying po la rmi bltas rnam pa bzhi byung nas /
NK028(sa)001:8325: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas la gsol ba btab pas phyogs
NK028(sa)001:8326: bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis rdo rje sems dpa' bskul
NK028(sa)001:8327: / rdo rje sems dpa' gzugs med khams kyi lha mang po dang //
NK028(sa)001:8328: gzugs khams kyi lha mang po dang //
NK028(sa)001:8329: 'dod khams kyis lha mang po dang //
NK028(sa)001:8330: mi la sprul sku dga' rab rdo rje /
NK028(sa)001:8335: bee ro tsa na la sogs pa rnams la /
NK028(sa)001:8336: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bas /
NK028(sa)001:8337: rtogs grol thar pa dus mnyam du sangs rgyas so //
NK028(sa)001:8339: rgya gar dang bod kyi gang zag bsam gyis mi
NK028(sa)001:8340: khyab pa rnams tshe gcig lus gcig la sangs rgyas
NK028(sa)001:8341: pa la sogs gzhal las 'das so //
NK028(sa)001:8342: de lta bu'i chos dang phrad pa kun /
NK028(sa)001:8343: tshe rabs sngo na gyi bsod nams bsags pa'i mthu dang /
NK028(sa)001:8344: bla ma rin po che'i byin brlabs las byung ba yin pas //
NK028(sa)001:8345: dga' spro chen po mdzad par zhu //
NK028(sa)001:8346: de ni zab mo'i chos bshad pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:8347: bcu gcig pa sbyin bsreg sta gon ni /
NK028(sa)001:8348: slob ma kun gyi rmi lam ngan na drag po'i sbyin bsreg byed do //
NK028(sa)001:8349: cho ga zur na yod do //
NK028(sa)001:8350: gsum pa dngos gzhi la bzhi ste //
NK028(sa)001:8351: phyi dbang gi chu bo dang //
NK028(sa)001:8352: nang dbang gi chu bo dang /
NK028(sa)001:8353: bsgrub dbang gi chu bo dang /
NK028(sa)001:8356: yo ga la sogs pa theg pa drug la /
NK028(sa)001:8357: phyi dbang brgyud kyi chu bo bya /
NK028(sa)001:8362: rang sangs rgyas kyi dbang dang /
NK028(sa)001:8363: byang chub sems dpa'i dbang dang /
NK028(sa)001:8364: bya ba'i rgyud kyi dbang dang /
NK028(sa)001:8367: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:8372: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:8373: rab gnas sbyin bsreg ces gsung pas //
NK028(sa)001:8374: dkyil 'khor bri ba'i sa stegs la cha bzhi bsgo ste //
NK028(sa)001:8375: shar lho lha mi'i dkyil 'khor gyis tshad //
NK028(sa)001:8376: lho nub tu nyan thos kyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad
NK028(sa)001:8377: nub byang tu rang sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor tshad
NK028(sa)001:8378: // byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshad legs par gzhal la //
NK028(sa)001:8379: dri bzang gi chag chag gdab po //
NK028(sa)001:8380: thig skud tshad dang ldan pas //
NK028(sa)001:8381: shar nub tshangs thig drang por gdab //
NK028(sa)001:8382: tshangs phyed ci rigs lhag pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:8383: tshangs pa'i rtse nas nyis thig btsal //
NK028(sa)001:8384: de stengs tshangs thig gnyis pa gdab //
NK028(sa)001:8385: tshangs rtse bzhi nas zur bzhi ru //
NK028(sa)001:8386: bya rjes btsal nas zur thig gdab //
NK028(sa)001:8387: ji ltar rigs pa'i phyag len gyis //
NK028(sa)001:8388: cha chen nyi shu legs par gdabs //
NK028(sa)001:8389: de nas cha bran gdab pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:8390: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK028(sa)001:8391: gnyis pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK028(sa)001:8392: mchog rab steng du 'dab bzhi dang //
NK028(sa)001:8393: gsum pa bzhi pa dor byar bya //
NK028(sa)001:8394: gser ri bdun dang rol mtsho bdun //
NK028(sa)001:8395: gling bzhi gling phran 'khor yug sa //
NK028(sa)001:8396: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK028(sa)001:8397: rtsig pa 'dod snam pha gu yis //
NK028(sa)001:8398: drug pa phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK028(sa)001:8399: dra ba shar bu mda' yab yin //
NK028(sa)001:8400: bdun pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK028(sa)001:8401: glang gur rta babs bang rim bzhi //
NK028(sa)001:8402: brgyad pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK028(sa)001:8404: dgu pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK028(sa)001:8405: gdugs tog pad 'dab rdo rje rwa //
NK028(sa)001:8406: bcu pa me ri 'bar ba bri //
NK028(sa)001:8407: de nas mu khyud bskor ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:8408: cha chen gcig nas lte ba bskor //
NK028(sa)001:8409: cha chen gnyis nas 'dab bzhi bskor //
NK028(sa)001:8410: gdugs tog rtse nas pad+ma bskor //
NK028(sa)001:8411: phyi yi cha bran rdoo ra yin //
NK028(sa)001:8412: cha chen bcu pa me ri bskor //
NK028(sa)001:8413: de nas tshon gyis bri ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:8414: lte ba dkar po 'dab ma bzhi //
NK028(sa)001:8415: phyogs mdog mtshams bzhi mdzes mtshon no //
NK028(sa)001:8416: ri bo mchog rab shar phyogs dkar //
NK028(sa)001:8417: lho sngo nub dmar byang ser po /
NK028(sa)001:8418: ri bdun ser la mtsho bdun sngo //
NK028(sa)001:8419: lha rnams mchog rab kha dog la //
NK028(sa)001:8420: chu yi ri mo gsal bar bri //
NK028(sa)001:8421: de steng gling bzhi gling phran brgyad //
NK028(sa)001:8422: ci rigs mtshams pa legs par bri //
NK028(sa)001:8423: lcags ri sngon po rtsigs pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:8424: dkar po sngon po ser dmar ljang //
NK028(sa)001:8425: 'dod snam dmar la pha gu ser //
NK028(sa)001:8426: dra gdan gnag la dra ba phyed //
NK028(sa)001:8427: dmar dang dkar pos legs par bri //
NK028(sa)001:8428: shar gdan dmar la shar bu dkar //
NK028(sa)001:8429: mda' yab dkar po rtse bran gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:8430: mun pa nag po ka ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:8431: phyogs mdog ka brgyan de las bzlog /
NK028(sa)001:8432: rta babs pad+ma rtsigs par mtshungs //
NK028(sa)001:8433: chos 'khor ri dwags gser po byed //
NK028(sa)001:8434: gdugs sham dmar la gdugs tog dkar //
NK028(sa)001:8435: phyogs bzhi rdo rje phyogs tshon byed //
NK028(sa)001:8436: pad rdor me ri spyi dang mthun //
NK028(sa)001:8437: mngon rtogs bzhin du lha tshon ni //
NK028(sa)001:8438: sku gsung thugs kyi rnam pa dgod //
NK028(sa)001:8439: chad lhag bsal zhing zhal gsos mchod //
NK028(sa)001:8440: mchod yon la sogs phyi mchod dang //
NK028(sa)001:8441: gtor sogs bshams pa gong dang mthun //
NK028(sa)001:8442: de ni bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:8443: de nas rnam rgyal bum pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:8444: las bum chas dang ldan pa gang bder bsham /
NK028(sa)001:8445: dbang rdzas la ji ltar dgos pa'i sku'i rten tsa ka li la sogs pa yang bsham mo //
NK028(sa)001:8446: gsung rten bod kyi ka kha sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:8447: thugs rten mched lcam gyi grangs dang mnyam pa'i tsha tsha dkar po rnams dgod /
NK028(sa)001:8448: de nas dpon slob rnams gdan la bzhugs shing /
NK028(sa)001:8449: dkar gtor cha bzhi la chab bran nas sngags drug phyag rgya drug gis bsngo ba'am /
NK028(sa)001:8450: yang na dkar gtor cig bshams la chab kyis bran zhing //
NK028(sa)001:8452: badz+ra dz+wa la a na la ha na da ha pa tsa ma tha b+hany+dza ra na h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:8453: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ha sarba d+har+m+ma swa b+h+aa wa shud d+ho ham /
NK028(sa)001:8454: stong pa'i ngang las rin po che'i snod yangs zhing
NK028(sa)001:8455: rgya che ba'i nang du 'od du zhu ba las
NK028(sa)001:8456: byung ba'i lha rdzas las grub pa'i gtor ma dngas
NK028(sa)001:8458: zag pa med pa'i bde ba khyad par can bskyed par gyur /
NK028(sa)001:8459: a ka ro mu kham sarba d+harma nam ar+ya nud
NK028(sa)001:8460: pan+na t+wa ta b+hu m+ai pa ti sa pa ri
NK028(sa)001:8461: wa ra na ma sarba ta tha ga te b+h+yo
NK028(sa)001:8462: bi shwa mu khe b+h+ya sarba th+aa kham urga te
NK028(sa)001:8463: s+pha ra na hi mam ga ga na kham g+h+rih+na
NK028(sa)001:8464: da na ba lim te s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:8465: badz+ra argam pra tits+tsha ye swah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:8466: p+aa t+yam pra tits+tsha ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:8473: sa la rgyu ba'i lha kun dang //
NK028(sa)001:8474: gang yang sa la brten pa rnams //
NK028(sa)001:8475: sems can kun la dge don du //
NK028(sa)001:8476: byams pa'i sems su gnas par mdzod //
NK028(sa)001:8477: lha klu 'byung po mthu bo che //
NK028(sa)001:8478: dkar po'i phyogs la mngon par dga' ba rnams kyis /
NK028(sa)001:8479: dkyil 'khor gyi bya ba mthar phyin pa'i 'phrin las mdzod cig /
NK028(sa)001:8480: gang dag nag po'i phyogs su gyur pa /
NK028(sa)001:8481: dkyil 'khor lta bar ma dbang pa'i bgegs gang yin
NK028(sa)001:8482: pa de dag thams cad mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma
NK028(sa)001:8483: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga dang ldan pa 'dis tshims
NK028(sa)001:8484: par gyis la bdag gi bya ba ma grub kyi
NK028(sa)001:8485: bar du 'dir ma gnas par gzhan du song shig
NK028(sa)001:8486: / badz+ra yak+sha h+aum gis bgegs bskrad //
NK028(sa)001:8489: swa b+ha wa shud+d+ha stong pa'i ngang las /
NK028(sa)001:8490: las rin po che'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba'i
NK028(sa)001:8491: nang du +aahh+aum 'od du zhu ba las lha rdzas
NK028(sa)001:8492: las grub pa'i mchod yon zhabs bsil /
NK028(sa)001:8498: rol mo dngas shing thogs pa med pa nam mkha' dang mnyam pa gyur /
NK028(sa)001:8500: om p+aa t+yam pra tits+tsha ye swah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:8515: badz+ra d+har+m+ma hri d+aa ya san+to /
NK028(sa)001:8516: sha ni h+aum h+aum h+aum ho ho hoha kham s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:8517: bdag dang 'gro ba nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad dus 'di nas gzung ste /
NK028(sa)001:8518: byang chub ma thob kyi bar du /
NK028(sa)001:8519: bla ma la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK028(sa)001:8520: sangs rgyas la chos la dge 'dun la yi dam
NK028(sa)001:8521: dkyil 'khor kyi lha tshogs rnams la mkha' 'gro chos
NK028(sa)001:8522: skyong rnams la gsum la sogs brjod /
NK028(sa)001:8523: sems can thams cad kyi don du bdag sangs rgyas thob pa bya /
NK028(sa)001:8524: de'i ched du lha mi'i bsgom bzlas kyi rim pa
NK028(sa)001:8525: dbang dang bcas pa la 'jug sems can thams cad
NK028(sa)001:8526: bde ba dang bde ba'i rgyu dang ldan par gyur
NK028(sa)001:8527: cig / sdug bsngal dang sdug bsngal gyi rgyu dang bral bar gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:8528: sdug bsngal med pa'i bde ba dam pa dang mi 'bral bar gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:8529: nye ring chags sdang dang bral ba'i btang snyoms la gnas par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:8531: swa b+ha wa shud+d+ha sarba d+har+m+ma swa b+h+aa wa shud+ho&a ho //
NK028(sa)001:8532: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+aum las rin po che sna
NK028(sa)001:8533: tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas kyi khang pa gru
NK028(sa)001:8534: bzhi sgo bzhi / brgyan rta babs dang bcas pa'i dbus su ri'i rgyal po ri rab /
NK028(sa)001:8539: pad+ma 'dab bzhi phyogs mdog gi dbus su lte ba
NK028(sa)001:8540: cha bzhir gyur pa'i shar lhor bdag nyid rnam par
NK028(sa)001:8541: snang mdzad sku mdog dkar po byang chub mchog gi
NK028(sa)001:8543: lho nub tu sh+aakya thub pa ser po chos 'chad kyi phyag rgya mdzad pa /
NK028(sa)001:8544: nub byang du snang ba mtha' yas sku mdog dmar po mnyam bzhag gis phyag rgya mdzad pa /
NK028(sa)001:8545: byang shar du sman pa'i lha sngon g.yas mchog sbyin gyis a ru ra bsnams pa //
NK028(sa)001:8546: g.yon mnyam bzhag gi steng du bdud rtsis gang ba'i
NK028(sa)001:8547: lhung bzed bsnams pa bzhi ka'ang zhabs rdo rje'i dkyil
NK028(sa)001:8549: shar gyi pad 'dab la yul 'khor bsrungs dkar po pi wam bsnams pa /
NK028(sa)001:8550: lho'i pad 'dab la 'phags skyes po sngon po be con ral gri bsnams pa /
NK028(sa)001:8551: nub kyis pad 'dab la spyan mi bzang dmar smug /
NK028(sa)001:8552: mchod rten dang sbrul zhags bsnams pa /
NK028(sa)001:8553: byang gi pad 'dab la rnam thos sras ljang khu rgyal mtshan dang ne'u le 'dzin pa /
NK028(sa)001:8554: de'i phyi rol du gser gyi ri bdun rol pa'i
NK028(sa)001:8555: mtsho bdun la rang rang gi lha rnams mos pa
NK028(sa)001:8556: tsam bya / de'i phyi rol du gling bzhi gling
NK028(sa)001:8557: bran brgyad kyi shar lus 'phags por lha'i dbang po
NK028(sa)001:8558: brgya byin yab yum gling bran gnyis la /
NK028(sa)001:8559: mngag gzhug pho nya dang bcas pa //
NK028(sa)001:8560: lho 'dzam bu gling du tshangs pa yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:8561: gling bran gnyis la mngag gzhug /
NK028(sa)001:8563: nub ba glang spyod du lha khyab 'jug yab yum /
NK028(sa)001:8564: gling bran gnyis la pho nya mngag gzhugs dang bcas pa /
NK028(sa)001:8565: byang sgra mi snyan du lha dbang phyug chen po yab yum /
NK028(sa)001:8566: gling bran gnyis la pho nya mngag gzhug dang bcas pa bsgom /
NK028(sa)001:8567: gzhan yang stong gsum bye ba phrag brgya'i rten dang brten pa rnams mos pa tsam bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:8568: de la ye shes pa snyan gsan dbab //
NK028(sa)001:8570: phyag 'tshal mchod pa 'bul ba rnams ci rigs par bya /
NK028(sa)001:8572: snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i sku //
NK028(sa)001:8573: chos dbyings ye shes ngo bo nyid //
NK028(sa)001:8574: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:8575: phyag 'tshal rnam par snang mdzad la //
NK028(sa)001:8576: thabs mkhas thugs rje sh+aakya'i rigs 'khrungs shing //
NK028(sa)001:8577: gzhan gyis mi thub bdud kyi dpung rnams 'joms //
NK028(sa)001:8578: gser gyi lhun po lta bur brjid pa'i sku //
NK028(sa)001:8579: sh+aakya'i rgyal po khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK028(sa)001:8580: 'dod chags rdo rje chos kyi chu //
NK028(sa)001:8581: kun rtogs ye shes ngo bo nyid //
NK028(sa)001:8582: ting 'dzin chen po'i phyag rgya mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:8583: phyag 'tshal snang ba mtha' yas la //
NK028(sa)001:8584: thugs rjes kun la snyoms pa'i bcom ldan 'das //
NK028(sa)001:8585: mtshan tsam thos pas ngan 'gro'i sdug bsngal sel //
NK028(sa)001:8586: dug gsum nad sel sangs rgyas sman gyi bla /
NK028(sa)001:8587: beed+au r+ya yi 'od la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:8589: shar phyogs rgyal po yul 'khor bsrungs //
NK028(sa)001:8590: zhi ba'i 'phrin las mthar phyin sku mdog dkar //
NK028(sa)001:8591: thugs rje'i dbang gis 'gro don pi wam bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:8592: shar phyogs dri za'i tshogs 'dul phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK028(sa)001:8593: h+aum lho phyogs rgyal chen 'phags skyes po //
NK028(sa)001:8594: mngon spyod tshul gyis 'gro don sku mdog sngo //
NK028(sa)001:8595: dug gsum 'joms mdzad be con ral gri bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:8596: lho phyogs gshin rje tshogs 'dul phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK028(sa)001:8598: nub phyogs rgyal chen spyan mi bzang /
NK028(sa)001:8599: sku mdog dmar smug dbang ldan 'jigs pa'i sku //
NK028(sa)001:8600: bsod nams tshogs rdzogs rin chen sbrul zhags bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:8601: nub phyogs klu dbang tshogs 'dul phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK028(sa)001:8602: h+aum byang phyogs rgyal chen rnam thos sras //
NK028(sa)001:8603: che ba'i yon tan mthar phyin ljang khur ldan //
NK028(sa)001:8604: rin chen gter ldan be con ne'u le bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:8605: byang phyogs gnod sbyin tshogs 'dul phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK028(sa)001:8606: phyag byar 'os pa thams cad la //
NK028(sa)001:8607: zhing rdul kun gyi grangs snyed kyis //
NK028(sa)001:8608: lus bstud pa ni rnam kun tu //
NK028(sa)001:8609: mchog tu dad pas phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK028(sa)001:8614: sman bla'i snying po rnams ci rigs par bsnyen /
NK028(sa)001:8616: swa b+h+aa wa stong pa'i ngang las /
NK028(sa)001:8617: b+h+rum las rin po che'i bum pa mtshan nyid dang
NK028(sa)001:8618: ldan pa'i nang du b+h+rum las rin po che sna
NK028(sa)001:8619: tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang pa la sogs
NK028(sa)001:8620: bdag bskyed ltar bsnyen pa yan chad la bar skabs
NK028(sa)001:8623: swa b+h+aa wa stong pa'i ngang las /
NK028(sa)001:8624: b+h+rum las rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i
NK028(sa)001:8625: gzhal yas kyi khang pa sogs bdag bskyed ltar bsnyen
NK028(sa)001:8626: pa yan chad la bar skabs kyi 'don pa bsgyur
NK028(sa)001:8629: grub na sbyin bsreg kyang ci rigs par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:8630: gnyis pa 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa la /
NK028(sa)001:8633: yon tan rnam bcu rgyas shes bya /
NK028(sa)001:8635: slob dpon bdag nyid 'jug cing dbang len pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:8636: slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:8638: dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa dang dbang len pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:8648: dbang phyug gis snyim par me tog gi phreng ba thogs la //
NK028(sa)001:8649: dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgor gus pas 'dug ste /
NK028(sa)001:8650: dkyil 'khor de nyid 'og min gyis gnas rten dang brten par bcas pa dmigs la /
NK028(sa)001:8652: +aamh badz+ra sa ma ya +aamh h+aum badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:8653: swa badz+ra sa ma y+aa swa /
NK028(sa)001:8654: h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya h+aa //
NK028(sa)001:8655: zhes rig pa'i me tog dor bas //
NK028(sa)001:8656: sngags brjod pa'i go rim bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:8657: bdag dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:8658: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las dbyer med par bsams la //
NK028(sa)001:8659: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK028(sa)001:8660: yon tan 'phrin las rmad po che //
NK028(sa)001:8661: da lta nyid du mnyam sbyor bas //
NK028(sa)001:8662: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK028(sa)001:8664: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams 'od du zhu nas /
NK028(sa)001:8665: bdag dbang phyug la phog pas dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang dgongs pa tha mi dad par mos pas /
NK028(sa)001:8669: zhes brjod pas go rim bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:8670: ye shes rdo rje dam tshig gi dus la bab bo /
NK028(sa)001:8673: ces pas ste de ltar gnad nas bskul ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:8676: slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa ltar bcu drug gis 'jug go /
NK028(sa)001:8677: gnyis pa slob bu 'jug par gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:8678: rdo rje ye shes thob byed pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:8679: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis //
NK028(sa)001:8681: bdag gis slob ma bzhugs par bya //
NK028(sa)001:8682: zhes brjod cing snyim pa'i me tog dkyil 'khor gyi
NK028(sa)001:8683: lha la dor ba'i blo dor ba'i tshul byas pas
NK028(sa)001:8684: / de bzhin gshegs pa rnams zhal 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:8685: slob bu dkyil 'khor du chug cig /
NK028(sa)001:8686: dbang bco brgyad snod dang mtshams par bskur bar rigs so /
NK028(sa)001:8687: zhes snang ba thob par mos pas me tog 'phreng ba sbyi bor bcing ngo //
NK028(sa)001:8688: gnyis pa dbang len pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:8689: slob ma la dbang ji ltar bskur ba bzhin len par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:8690: gnyis pa slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba la gnyis te /
NK028(sa)001:8695: khrus dgab dri dang lus dbul dang //
NK028(sa)001:8696: bgegs bskrad lhar brlabs dam tshigs sbyin //
NK028(sa)001:8697: de nyid 'bog dang chu nan dang //
NK028(sa)001:8698: bsgrag dang rin chen dor ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:8699: lha dbab pa dang nan tan dang //
NK028(sa)001:8700: mig dbye dkyil 'khor bstan pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:8701: tshogs mchod yon dang nges pas bcu drug ste /
NK028(sa)001:8704: dri ba dang lus 'bul ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:8713: lha bsgoms pa la nan tan bya dang /
NK028(sa)001:8718: dang po ni las bum gyi khrus byed cing gos sar pa dang ldan par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:8719: gnyis pa mig dgab pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:8720: ma rig pa dang 'dod chags kyi dri mas /
NK028(sa)001:8721: gnyis med kyi ye shes bsgribs pa'i rtags su ras sam dar dmar pos mig dgab cing /
NK028(sa)001:8722: dar la sogs pa la byas pa'i me tog rin
NK028(sa)001:8723: po che'am 'bru'i 'phring ba can snyim par thogs la
NK028(sa)001:8724: // rdo rje sems gtso khyod la 'dud //
NK028(sa)001:8725: thar pa chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK028(sa)001:8726: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK028(sa)001:8727: mgon po dpa' bo skyabs song ste //
NK028(sa)001:8728: theg chen khang par zhugs pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:8729: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la stsol //
NK028(sa)001:8730: ces dkyil 'khor du chug par gsol ba lan gsum gdab po //
NK028(sa)001:8731: gsum pa dri ba byed pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:8732: dbang phyug gis bu khyod ci la dga' brjod /
NK028(sa)001:8733: slob bu rnams kyis bskal pa bzang po la bdag daga'o brjod do //
NK028(sa)001:8735: las mkhan gyis rdo rje'i phyed slob bu rnams kyi lag tu byin la //
NK028(sa)001:8736: bu khyod tshur shog ci bde ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:8737: las sbyod rim par 'gro ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:8738: sku gsung thugs kyis rdo rje gzungs //
NK028(sa)001:8739: rdzogs pa'i ye shes bde chen dang //
NK028(sa)001:8740: dmigs pa med par gnas phyir du //
NK028(sa)001:8741: ser sna spangs ba'i dang yid kyis //
NK028(sa)001:8742: stong zhing rang sems brtan par bzung //
NK028(sa)001:8743: mdo sgyu lha mi'i dkyil 'khor zer sems gsum rdzogs dbang byin //
NK028(sa)001:8744: ces dbang phyug gi mdun du slob bu rnams drang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:8746: slob ma rnam kyis thal mo sbyi bor sbyar la
NK028(sa)001:8747: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK028(sa)001:8748: yon tan 'phrin las kyis ye shes thob par bya
NK028(sa)001:8749: ba'i phyir / 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa rnams la lus 'bul bar bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:8750: sarba bud+d+ha p+au dzas+tha na ya arma nam nir+ya da y+aa mi //
NK028(sa)001:8752: yang thal mo smin mtshams su sbyar la sangs rgyas
NK028(sa)001:8753: thams cad kyi ye shes thob pa'i snod du rung
NK028(sa)001:8755: da ltar gyi sangs rgyas rnams la lus 'bul bar bagyi'o /
NK028(sa)001:8756: a tsar+ya p+au dzap+tha na ya arma nam nir+ya ta y+aa mi /
NK028(sa)001:8758: yang thal mo snying khar sbyar la /
NK028(sa)001:8759: sems can thams cad kyi don mi 'dor cing mthar phyin par bya ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:8760: ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad ma lus 'bul bar bagyi'o /
NK028(sa)001:8761: sa ga la sa ta p+au dzas+tha na ya at+ma nam nir+ya ta y+aa mi zhes phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:8762: lnga pa tshe mi yar bar bya ba'i phyir bgegs bskrad pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:8763: dbang phyug gi thugs ka'i sa bon las /
NK028(sa)001:8764: yi ge b+h+rum re slob ma rnams kyi byin bslabs 'phros /
NK028(sa)001:8765: b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud+d+he zhes brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:8766: zla gam dmar po'i gzhal yas khang gnam sgo cig pa sgo khyud can cig bsam /
NK028(sa)001:8767: de'i nang du h+aum zhes brjod pas /
NK028(sa)001:8768: slob ma'i tshe'i dngos po thams cad h+aum la bsdu //
NK028(sa)001:8769: badz+ra h+aum ka ra h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:8771: h+aum ka ra sngon po tshe'i bum pa bsnams pa cig tu bsam /
NK028(sa)001:8772: zla gam gyi gnam sgo la /
NK028(sa)001:8773: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:8775: khro bo mi g.yo ba ljang nag ral gri dang
NK028(sa)001:8776: sdigs 'dzub can bskyed nas sgo bsrungs bar bsams nas
NK028(sa)001:8777: / yi dam lha'i nga rgyal gyis /
NK028(sa)001:8780: bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+dala h+aumh phata
NK028(sa)001:8781: phatah ha la ha la h+aum phatah dz+wa la rwa
NK028(sa)001:8782: dz+wa la rwa dz+wa la ram /
NK028(sa)001:8783: khro bo'i tshogs dpag tu med pa spros pas /
NK028(sa)001:8784: slob bu rnams kyi lus ngag yid gsum la gnod
NK028(sa)001:8785: cing 'tshe bar byed pa'i gdon bgegs thams cad bskrad
NK028(sa)001:8786: par bsam la / na mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i
NK028(sa)001:8787: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK028(sa)001:8788: yon tan phrin las zhing khams zag pa med pa
NK028(sa)001:8789: zad mi shes pa brgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bden pa
NK028(sa)001:8790: par bsam la / dang / bden pa chen po'i
NK028(sa)001:8791: byin brlabs kyis 'dir 'dus pa'i slob bu rnams la
NK028(sa)001:8792: gnod cing 'tshe ba'i 'byung po thams cad 'dir ma
NK028(sa)001:8793: gnas par dengs shig byed cig /
NK028(sa)001:8795: drug pa lhar brlabs pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:8796: rdo rje slob dpon gyi lag pa g.yas kyi sor
NK028(sa)001:8797: mo'i bre kha lnga la gnas pa'i dpa' mo 'bru
NK028(sa)001:8798: lnga bsam la / su ra t+wa stam /
NK028(sa)001:8799: zhes dpa' bo dpa' mo sbyar /
NK028(sa)001:8801: badz+ra ban+d+ha zhes pas phyag rgya bsdam /
NK028(sa)001:8802: bden pa brjod pa'i rjes la /
NK028(sa)001:8803: slob bu 'di rnams kyi rgyud la yod pa'i las kyi sgrib pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:8804: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:8806: lta ba dman pa'i sgribs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:8807: chos kyi 'phongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:8808: bag chags ngan pa'i sgrib pa la sogs te /
NK028(sa)001:8809: sgrib pa'i phung po ji snyed pa thams cad /
NK028(sa)001:8810: phyag rgya'i 'od zer 'dis dral bar gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:8812: zhes pa'i sngags mang du brjod cing /
NK028(sa)001:8814: 'bru bcu rigs lnga yab yum du gyur pas sbyor
NK028(sa)001:8815: ba mdzad pas byang chub kyi sems su zhu pa'i
NK028(sa)001:8816: 'od zer gyis / slob bu rnams kyi sgrib pa mtha' dag bsregs shing /
NK028(sa)001:8820: slob bu rnams kyi rnam shes dang cig tu gyur
NK028(sa)001:8821: te dngul chu zhun ma lta bur gnas pa ste
NK028(sa)001:8822: / cho ga gsum gyis rnam snang sku mdog dkar
NK028(sa)001:8823: po rgyan dang cha lugs dang ldan pa bskyed la
NK028(sa)001:8824: / / ma h+aa shu nya ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:8826: ma h+aa a da ri sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK028(sa)001:8828: ma h+aa pra ta pra be sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK028(sa)001:8830: ma h+aa sa man+ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:8832: ma h+aa kri ta a nu ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&aham /
NK028(sa)001:8833: don yod grub pa rnams kyiis dbu brgyan /
NK028(sa)001:8834: gnas gsum du rdo rje gtug cing /
NK028(sa)001:8835: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK028(sa)001:8836: byin gyis brlabs pa'i rtags su dpral bar sku rdo
NK028(sa)001:8837: rje dkar po 'khor lo gyis mtshan pa 'dzin pa
NK028(sa)001:8838: / sarba ta th+aa ga ta wa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ho /
NK028(sa)001:8839: mgrin par gsung rdo rje dmar po +aamh gyiis mtshan pa 'dzin pa /
NK028(sa)001:8840: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko & ho /
NK028(sa)001:8841: snying khar thugs rdo rje sngon po rdo rje h+aum gis mtshan pa 'dzin pa /
NK028(sa)001:8842: rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgyas /
NK028(sa)001:8843: badz+ra ka wa tsi rak+sha rak+sha zhes rdo rje'i go khrab bkon /
NK028(sa)001:8844: rdoo rje bsrungs pa'i phyag rgya dang /
NK028(sa)001:8845: trum gyis khro bo'i rdo rje gnod sbyin dang /
NK028(sa)001:8846: khro bo mi 'chi thal sbyor gnyis kyis lus kyi gnas drug bsrungs par bsgom mo //
NK028(sa)001:8847: 'di nas gso sbyong sogs sbyin pas chog /
NK028(sa)001:8852: bcu pa gzhi'i tshabs su bsnyen gnas so //
NK028(sa)001:8853: pa dam tshig sbyin pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:8854: slob bu rnams kyis a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:8855: a la la ste mnyes par mdzod //
NK028(sa)001:8856: a la la ste dam tshig bskongs //
NK028(sa)001:8857: a la la ste dngos grub stsol //
NK028(sa)001:8858: dpal ldan rdo rje sku 'chang ba //
NK028(sa)001:8859: mi phyed rdo rje sku rang bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:8860: deng bdag byin gyis rlabs nas ni //
NK028(sa)001:8861: rdo rje'i sku ru mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:8863: dbang phyug gis ban+d+hara bdud rtsi cung zad blug la /
NK028(sa)001:8864: +aahh+aum zhes brjod cing sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin yig 'bru gsum gsal bar bsgoms la //
NK028(sa)001:8865: badz+ra a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK028(sa)001:8866: zhes pa'i sngags lan gsum gyis bdud rtsi'i chur byin gyis rlabs nas /
NK028(sa)001:8867: dbang phyug gi phyag g.yas pa rdo rje dang bcas pa'i srin lag gis bdud rtsi blangs la /
NK028(sa)001:8868: slob ma rnams kyi dpral bar zhes brjod cing //
NK028(sa)001:8869: thig le byas la dkar po bsam //
NK028(sa)001:8871: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku'i byin brlabs bsdus nas dpral ba'i la thim par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:8872: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya badz+ra swa b+ha wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK028(sa)001:8873: zhes brjod cing byin gyis rlabs pas /
NK028(sa)001:8874: slob bus dam tshig thob par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:8876: dpal ldan rdo rje gsung 'chang ba //
NK028(sa)001:8877: mi phyed rdo rje gsung rang bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:8878: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas ni //
NK028(sa)001:8879: rdo rje'i gsung du mdzad du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:8880: zhes gsol ba btab pa'i slob bu'i mgrin par thig le byas pa'i +aamhgi 'phro 'du dang /
NK028(sa)001:8881: wa ka badz+ra'i sngags kyis gsung gi dam tshig thob par bsam //
NK028(sa)001:8882: yang dpal ldan rdo rje'i thugs 'chang ba //
NK028(sa)001:8883: deng bdag byin gyis rlabs nas ni //
NK028(sa)001:8884: rdo rje thugs su mdzad du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:8885: zhes gsol ba btab pa'i slob bu'i snying gar thig
NK028(sa)001:8886: le byas pa h+aum 'phro 'du dang tsit+ta badz+ra'i sngagasakyi
NK028(sa)001:8887: thugs gyi dam tshig thob par bsam mo //
NK028(sa)001:8889: dbang phyug gis slob bu'i snying gar rdo rje bzhag la /
NK028(sa)001:8890: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba 'di //
NK028(sa)001:8891: dam nyams ma 'dres med pa la //
NK028(sa)001:8892: nam yang smra bar ma byed cig /
NK028(sa)001:8893: theg pa chen po ston byed pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:8894: nga la brnyas dang rmad mi rung //
NK028(sa)001:8895: sku gsung thugs la rtag gnas shing //
NK028(sa)001:8896: ma lus sems can don gyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:8898: dgu pa chu nan bya ba tsan+dana dkar dmar sbyar ba'i chu la /
NK028(sa)001:8899: cho ga gsum gyis rdo rje sems dpar bskyed cing /
NK028(sa)001:8900: ye shes pa bcug pas bdud rtsir zhu bar bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:8901: thog mar skyon gyi sgo nas chu nan bya ste //
NK028(sa)001:8902: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK028(sa)001:8903: dam tshig nyams na bsreg par byed //
NK028(sa)001:8906: zhes brjod cing rdo rje'i chu blangs la /
NK028(sa)001:8907: slob bu'i lce la lan gsum bzhag go /
NK028(sa)001:8908: yon tan gyi sgo nas nan tan bya ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:8909: 'di lta bas na bu khyod gyi //
NK028(sa)001:8910: dam tshig 'di dag bsrungs bar bgyis //
NK028(sa)001:8911: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub pas //
NK028(sa)001:8912: rdo rje bdud rtsi chu 'thung zhig /
NK028(sa)001:8913: badz+ra ush+tha ka ta h+aum th+aa /
NK028(sa)001:8916: lan gsum slob bu'i lce la bzhag go /
NK028(sa)001:8917: slob bu kun la chu nan zin rjes thog tu 'di skad brjod do //
NK028(sa)001:8918: de ltar bdud rtsi'i chu de lce la bzhag kyang /
NK028(sa)001:8919: bab pa snying gi dkyil du babs nas /
NK028(sa)001:8920: gal te dam tshig ma bsrungs na /
NK028(sa)001:8921: chu de rdo rje gnod sbyin zhes bya ba lcags gyi sdig pa mgo dgu par gyur nas /
NK028(sa)001:8923: tshe thung zhing nad mang ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:8924: tshe phyi ma dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal gyis nyams thag par 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:8925: dam tshig bsrungs na chu de rdo rje sems dpar gyur nas /
NK028(sa)001:8926: des rtag tu byin gyis rlobs zhing tshe 'dir yang /
NK028(sa)001:8929: nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi dang gdon stong phrag brgya bcus mi tshugs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:8930: phyi mar bla na med pa'i byang chub thob nas /
NK028(sa)001:8931: sems can thams cad mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i gnas su /
NK028(sa)001:8932: 'dren pa'i ded dpon byed par 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:8934: bcu pa dam bsgrag pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:8935: dbang phyug gis phyag g.yas pa rda rje dang bcas pa slob bu rnams kyi spyi bor bzhag la /
NK028(sa)001:8936: thabs dang shes rab sems nyid kyis //
NK028(sa)001:8937: rtag tu gos pa med bgyis la /
NK028(sa)001:8938: 'dod pa lnga yi yon tan spyod /
NK028(sa)001:8939: gzhan yang stong khams thams cad na //
NK028(sa)001:8940: shes rab dbyings dang 'dod yon gzhan //
NK028(sa)001:8941: rab 'bring tha mas thams cad sbyod //
NK028(sa)001:8942: gzhan yang dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:8943: skye bo gang zhig dam la gnod //
NK028(sa)001:8944: brtul zhugs can gyis de grongs la //
NK028(sa)001:8945: khrag chen snying la btung par gyis //
NK028(sa)001:8946: 'di la mi bya cung zad med //
NK028(sa)001:8947: sems nyid theg par rab nges na //
NK028(sa)001:8948: nyon mongs 'dod la kun spyod kyang //
NK028(sa)001:8949: pad ma la ni 'dam bzhin te //
NK028(sa)001:8950: tshul khrims sdom pa phun su tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:8951: bya dang mi bya cung zad med //
NK028(sa)001:8955: rang sangs rgyas kyi dbang dang /
NK028(sa)001:8956: byang chub sems dpa'i dbang rnams la dam tshig sbyin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:8958: chu nan bya ba dang dam tshig sgrags pa rnams mi dgos /
NK028(sa)001:8959: de'i tshab la gso sbyong dang bsnyen gnas kyi sdom pa /
NK028(sa)001:8963: sems bskyed kyi sdom pa rnams 'bog go /
NK028(sa)001:8964: bdun pa dam tshig sbyin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:8965: brgyad pa dam tshig dbog pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:8966: dgu pa chu nan bya ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:8967: bcu pa dam tshig bsgrags pa dang bzhi'i dod du bsnyen gnas kyis sdom pa 'bogs pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:8968: sems can thams cad kyi don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par bya /
NK028(sa)001:8969: de'i ched du bsnyen gnas kyi sdom pa zhus nas
NK028(sa)001:8970: nyams su len snyams pa'i thugs dgongs dang bcas pa'i
