NK028(sa)001:8971: sgo nas lad mo mdzod cig /
NK028(sa)001:8973: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyis ba dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK028(sa)001:8974: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du rkang gnyis rnams kyi mchog /
NK028(sa)001:8975: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK028(sa)001:8976: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK028(sa)001:8979: dge 'dun la bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK028(sa)001:8980: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du bsnyen gnas su btsun pas bzung du gsol lo //
NK028(sa)001:8982: tha ma la slob dpon gyis thabs yin no //
NK028(sa)001:8983: slob mas legs so zhes brjod do //
NK028(sa)001:8984: des bsdom pa thob nas bslab bya la bslab snyams pa'i mos pa bgyis la rjes bzlos mdzod /
NK028(sa)001:8986: ji ltar sngon gyis 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gi srog gcod pa spangs te /
NK028(sa)001:8987: srog gcod pa las slar log pa de bzhin du /
NK028(sa)001:8988: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang /
NK028(sa)001:8989: dus 'di nas bzung ste zla ba byung ngo cog
NK028(sa)001:8990: gi gnam stong la sogs la srog gcod pa spangs
NK028(sa)001:8991: te / srog gcod pa las slar bzlog bar bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:8992: yan lag dang po 'dis bdag 'a phags pa dgra
NK028(sa)001:8993: bcom pa de dag gi bslab pa la rjes su
NK028(sa)001:8994: bslab po // rjes su bsgrub bo //
NK028(sa)001:8996: gzhan yang 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gis ma byin par len pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:8997: mi tshangs ba spyod pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:9005: rgyan dang kha dog 'chang ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:9006: mal stan mthon po dang khri stan chen po dang //
NK028(sa)001:9007: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas spangs te //
NK028(sa)001:9008: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas las slar log pa de bzhin du //
NK028(sa)001:9009: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:9010: dus 'di nas bzung nas ji srid 'tsho'i bar du /
NK028(sa)001:9011: zla ba byung ngo cog gi gnam stong la ma byin par len pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:9012: mi tshangs pa spyod pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:9016: myos par 'gyur ba bag med pa'i gnas dang /
NK028(sa)001:9019: rol mo'i sgra dang 'phreng ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:9026: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas spongs te /
NK028(sa)001:9027: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas las zlog par bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:9029: bdag 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gi slab pa la rjes su bslab po //
NK028(sa)001:9031: slob dpon gyis thabs yin no //
NK028(sa)001:9032: slob mas legs so zhes brjod do //
NK028(sa)001:9033: gnam stong gi lha bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:9034: gnam stong bsrungs bas bskal pa stong gi bar du mu ge'i bskal pa la thar bar 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:9035: nya'i lha snang ba mtha' yas yin no /
NK028(sa)001:9036: nya bsrungs pas bskal pa nyi khri'i bar du nad kyi bskal pa las thar ro //
NK028(sa)001:9037: tshes brgyad kyi lha sman gyi lha beed+aur+ya 'od kyi rgyal po yin no //
NK028(sa)001:9038: tshes brgyad bsrungs pas bskal pa nyi khri'i bar du
NK028(sa)001:9039: mtshon gyi bskal pa las thar nas 'phrul dag'i gnas
NK028(sa)001:9040: su skye'o // gnam stong gi nyu le ma tshangs pa yin no //
NK028(sa)001:9043: mo mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:9044: nya'i nyu le ma tshangs pa yin no /
NK028(sa)001:9047: tshes brgyad kyi nyu le ma rgyal bu the'u tsha yin no //
NK028(sa)001:9050: b+he sha dze b+he sha dze ma h+aa b+he sha dza /
NK028(sa)001:9052: gso sbyong gi sdom pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:9053: gso sbyong gi sdom pa len snyam pa'i thugs bskyed dang ldan pa'i sgo nas lad mo mdzod /
NK028(sa)001:9054: ji ltar sngon gyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom
NK028(sa)001:9055: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rta cang
NK028(sa)001:9056: shes lta bu / glang po chen po bya ba byas shing /
NK028(sa)001:9059: rang gi don rjes su thob pa /
NK028(sa)001:9060: srid pa sbyor ba yongs su zad pa /
NK028(sa)001:9061: legs par rnam par grol ba'i bka' /
NK028(sa)001:9062: legs par rnam par grol ba'i thugs /
NK028(sa)001:9063: legs par rnam par grol ba'i shes rab can de
NK028(sa)001:9064: dag gis sems can thams cad kyi don gyi phyir
NK028(sa)001:9065: dang phan par bya ba'i phyiir dang /
NK028(sa)001:9066: grol bar bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK028(sa)001:9067: mu ge med par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK028(sa)001:9068: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos rnams yongs su rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK028(sa)001:9069: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang
NK028(sa)001:9070: chub tu nges par bya ba'i phyir du gso sbyong
NK028(sa)001:9071: nges par bya ba'i phyir du gso sbyong nges par
NK028(sa)001:9073: bdag ming 'di zhes bya ba dus 'di nas bzung
NK028(sa)001:9074: nas sang nyi ma ma shar bar du gso sbyong
NK028(sa)001:9075: gi sdom pa la nges par legs par gnas par
NK028(sa)001:9076: bgyi lags so // lan gsum brjod bslab bya mi
NK028(sa)001:9077: nyams par bsrungs snyam pa'i mos pa dang rjes bzlos
NK028(sa)001:9078: bgyi lags so // mdzod / deng nas srog gcod mi bya zhing /
NK028(sa)001:9079: gzhan gyi nor yang blang mi bya /
NK028(sa)001:9080: 'khrig pa'i chos kyang mi sbyad cing //
NK028(sa)001:9081: rdzun gyi tshig kyang mi smra'o //
NK028(sa)001:9082: skyon ni mang po nyer bstan pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:9083: chang ni yongs su spangs bar bya //
NK028(sa)001:9084: de bzhin dus ma yin pa'i zas //
NK028(sa)001:9085: dri dang 'phreng ba dang ni brgyan //
NK028(sa)001:9086: gar dang glu sogs spangs bar bya //
NK028(sa)001:9087: ji ltar dgra bcom rtag tu ni //
NK028(sa)001:9088: srog gcod la sogs mi byed pa //
NK028(sa)001:9089: de bzhin srog gcod la sogs mi byed pa //
NK028(sa)001:9090: de bzhin srog gcod la sogs spangs //
NK028(sa)001:9091: bla med byang chub thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9093: srid pa'i mtsho las sgrol bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:9094: byang chub sems dpa'i gso sbyong rang gis blang ba'i cho ga mdo las byung ba rdzogs so //
NK028(sa)001:9095: bcu gcig pa me tog dor ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:9096: rang rang gi me tog 'phreng ba rang gi yi dam dang 'brel ba brtag pa'i don du /
NK028(sa)001:9098: dbang phyug rigs thams cad kyi bdag por mos pas /
NK028(sa)001:9099: dbang phyug mngon par phyogs te //
NK028(sa)001:9100: me tog la sogs rin chen 'phreng /
NK028(sa)001:9101: sngon tshe ye shes bsnyen pa'i lha //
NK028(sa)001:9102: thugs rjes bzung bar dgongs nas kyang /
NK028(sa)001:9103: gang yin de la 'bab gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:9106: dbang phyug gis kyang phyag gnyis rdo rje dril bu dang ldan pas thugs kar dril bu dkrol zhing /
NK028(sa)001:9108: dril bu'i sgra la gtad pa la me tog gtor la //
NK028(sa)001:9109: yi dam gyi rigs ngos gzung ste /
NK028(sa)001:9110: dbu dang mtshams rnams de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs /
NK028(sa)001:9111: lag pa g.yas kyi cha rdo rje'i rigs g.yon gyi cha rin po che'i rigs //
NK028(sa)001:9112: rkang pa g.yas kyi cha las kyi sa rigs //
NK028(sa)001:9113: g.yon gyi cha pad+ma'i rigs yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:9114: rang gi rigs yid la ma rjed par bzung shig /
NK028(sa)001:9116: me tog 'phreng ba sbyi bor bcing ngo //
NK028(sa)001:9117: bcu gnyis pa lha dbab pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:9118: slob bu rnams kyis lus bde lugs su bsrang ste /
NK028(sa)001:9119: snying gi nang du chu nan gyi dus kyi lha gsal bar bsgoms zhing /
NK028(sa)001:9120: shes pa skad cig kyang ma yengs par gyis shig ces bgos la /
NK028(sa)001:9121: dbang phyug gis rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgyas /
NK028(sa)001:9122: h+aum badz+ra d+h+rig sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK028(sa)001:9124: rdo rje sems dpa' chos sku las gzugs skur bzhengs par bsam la /
NK028(sa)001:9125: las slob rnams kyis spos dang rol mo'i sgra sbyar zhing /
NK028(sa)001:9126: dbang phyug gis lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas /
NK028(sa)001:9127: badz+ra sa t+wa dz+ny+aa na sa t+wa e h+ya hi
NK028(sa)001:9128: b+ha ga wan ma h+aa ka ru ni ka tri
NK028(sa)001:9129: sha ho sa ma ya s+t+wam dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes
NK028(sa)001:9130: pa 'og min gyi gnas nas ye shes sems dpa'
NK028(sa)001:9131: rang bzhin gyi rdo rje sems dpa' slob bu rnams
NK028(sa)001:9132: kyi sbyi bor sbyan drangs la /
NK028(sa)001:9133: bden pa brjod pa'i rjes su yang dbang phyug gi phyag g.yas pa rdo rje dang bcas pa /
NK028(sa)001:9134: slob bu 'di'i tsit+ta'i dkyil 'khor du ye shes sems dpa'i rang bzhin du zhugs nas /
NK028(sa)001:9137: phyi ma bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi rgyur gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:9138: gal te dam tshig nyams na rdo rje gnod sbyin du gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:9139: srog rtsa'i khrag 'jib par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:9141: pra be sha phata kyis slob bu'i lus dbye /
NK028(sa)001:9143: snying gi dkyil du chu nan gyi chu dang /
NK028(sa)001:9144: gnyis su med par bstim par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:9145: bcu gsum pa lha bsgoms pa nan tan bya ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:9146: lha bsgoms pa dang 'bral du mi rung bar nan tan bya ba la /
NK028(sa)001:9147: thams cad legs par nyon la yid la zung shig /
NK028(sa)001:9149: lha sgom pa dang ma bral ba'i yon tan ni /
NK028(sa)001:9150: rang gi lus ngag yid gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs dang bskal ba mnyam pa'i ye shes thob cing /
NK028(sa)001:9151: 'dod pa'i don cig bsgrub kyang nye bar 'grub ste /
NK028(sa)001:9152: tshe gcig lus gcig la dngos grub ya mtshan chen
NK028(sa)001:9153: po sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par 'gyur te
NK028(sa)001:9154: / rtsa rgyud gsang ba snying po las //
NK028(sa)001:9155: bskal pa mnyam pa'i ye shes te //
NK028(sa)001:9156: nyer na nye bar 'byung ba yi //
NK028(sa)001:9157: ya mtshan chen po 'byung bar nges /
NK028(sa)001:9159: sgyu 'phrul man ngag lam rim las //
NK028(sa)001:9160: bdag nyid lha dang mnyam sbyor bas //
NK028(sa)001:9161: yon tan chung yang 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:9164: 'o na lha bsgom pa la phan yon chen po 'dug mod //
NK028(sa)001:9165: ma bsgom na skyon ci yod snyam na //
NK028(sa)001:9166: yi dam gyi lha spangs na /
NK028(sa)001:9167: dge ba gzhan spyad kyang don med par 'gyur zhing /
NK028(sa)001:9168: dad pa med pa'i stobs kyis dam tshig nyams na
NK028(sa)001:9169: kun tu nyon mongs pa ngan song gsum gyis sdug
NK028(sa)001:9171: bla na med pa'i byang chub thob pa'i lam nas gol nas rigs chad pa'i gnas su 'gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:9173: dam med nyams na phung par 'gyur /
NK028(sa)001:9174: zhes pa dang sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las kyi rim pa las //
NK028(sa)001:9175: lha spangs dge sbyad don med de //
NK028(sa)001:9176: gang zhig phyag rgya 'di spangs na //
NK028(sa)001:9177: nyon mongs ngan song gsum du skye //
NK028(sa)001:9179: bla med 'gro ba'i rgyun yang bcad //
NK028(sa)001:9180: rigs chad snying du gnas par 'gyur /
NK028(sa)001:9181: zhes gsungs pa'i don go bar bgyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:9183: bcu bzhi pa spyan dbye ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:9184: dbang phyug gi thugs ka nas /
NK028(sa)001:9185: 'od zer thur ma 'dra ba byung nas /
NK028(sa)001:9186: slob bu'i ma rig gi ling thog bsal bas rang
NK028(sa)001:9187: la gnas pa'i don dam dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs
NK028(sa)001:9188: rnams kyi zhal mthong bar bsam la /
NK028(sa)001:9189: de ring dad pa'i shugs kyis ni //
NK028(sa)001:9190: dkyil 'khor dam pa lta bar bya //
NK028(sa)001:9191: sangs rgyas gsung gi rigs su 'khrungs //
NK028(sa)001:9192: dngos grub mchog tu 'gyur bar bya /
NK028(sa)001:9193: badz+ra tsak+shu pra be sha phata /
NK028(sa)001:9194: ces pas mig dar bshus la /
NK028(sa)001:9195: dkyil 'khor la ltos shig ces brjod do //
NK028(sa)001:9196: bco lnga la dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:9197: 'o mdun 'di nas yod pa'i lha mi'i dkyil 'khor rten bstan pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:9198: phyi rol du me ri rdo ra pad bskor /
NK028(sa)001:9199: de'i nang du gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi rgyan rta babs dang bcas pa /
NK028(sa)001:9200: de'i nang du ri bo mchog rab /
NK028(sa)001:9204: gling bzhi gling phran brgyad mngon du mthong ba'i mos pa mdzod /
NK028(sa)001:9205: pad+ma'i lte ba'i dbus su rnam par snang mdzad /
NK028(sa)001:9210: rgyal po chen po sde bzhi /
NK028(sa)001:9211: gser ri dang rol mtsho la de'i 'khor gling bzhi gling phran bcu gnyis la /
NK028(sa)001:9212: lha dang mi bsam gyis mi khyab pa sku snang la rang bzhin med pa /
NK028(sa)001:9213: me long nang gi gzugs brnyan bzhin mngon sum du
NK028(sa)001:9214: mthong ba de khyed rang rnams kyi yi dam gyi
NK028(sa)001:9215: lha bskal yin ang snyam pa'i mos pa mdzod cig
NK028(sa)001:9216: / bcu drug pa tshogs mchod dang /
NK028(sa)001:9218: tshogs mchod rnams gzhung gzhan dang mthun par rgyas bsdus ci rigs par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:9220: de nas rigs kyi bu mchog des //
NK028(sa)001:9221: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK028(sa)001:9222: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK028(sa)001:9223: rab tu gces dang yid 'thad dbul //
NK028(sa)001:9224: dbang phyug longs spyod lngas mchod na //
NK028(sa)001:9225: dkyil 'khor thams cad mchod pa yin //
NK028(sa)001:9226: nye ba'i dkyil 'khor smos ci dgos //
NK028(sa)001:9227: nyes pa thams cad dag par 'gyur /
NK028(sa)001:9228: ces pa'i don khong du chud par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:9230: 'jug gi chos bcu drug po 'di rnams la tshig bcad dang sngags tsam gyis chog go /
NK028(sa)001:9231: de rnams kyis sa gzhi mnyam pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:9238: 'jug chos dang dgu po gong du song nas //
NK028(sa)001:9239: bcu pa dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa'i yon tan la //
NK028(sa)001:9240: yon tan rnam bcus rgyas shes bya /
NK028(sa)001:9243: bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK028(sa)001:9244: sdang dbyal gnyis sam yang na lnga /
NK028(sa)001:9245: byas te dad ldan rab zhugs nas /
NK028(sa)001:9249: dkyil 'khor thams cad du zhugs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK028(sa)001:9250: las dang po ba lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bzhugs pa yin kyang /
NK028(sa)001:9251: sngon 'og min du thar lam pa dang bskal pa mnyam pa'i yon tan dang /
NK028(sa)001:9252: lha mi'i dkyil 'khor 'di la mos ba tsam yang
NK028(sa)001:9253: skye ba sngon rol nas yi dam gyi lha bsnyen
NK028(sa)001:9254: pa'i stobs kyis / sangs rgyas thams cad kyi nye
NK028(sa)001:9255: ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur ba'i yon tan dang
NK028(sa)001:9256: pa'i stobs kyis / / dkyil 'khor 'dir shugs nas
NK028(sa)001:9257: dam tshig ma nyams na thun mong dang mchog gi
NK028(sa)001:9258: dngos grub thams cad thob par 'gyur ba'i yon tan
NK028(sa)001:9259: pa'i stobs kyis / / no // dang po ni sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las rim las //
NK028(sa)001:9260: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa bar legs zhugs pas //
NK028(sa)001:9261: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:9262: dkyil 'khor kun tu zhugs pa yin /
NK028(sa)001:9266: sdang 'byam gnyis sa ma yang na lnga //
NK028(sa)001:9267: byas te dad ldan rab zhugs nas //
NK028(sa)001:9269: sngon byas pa dang mnyam par 'gyur /
NK028(sa)001:9271: rtsa rgyud kyi le'u bcu gsum pa las /
NK028(sa)001:9272: gang zhig 'di la mos gyur pa //
NK028(sa)001:9273: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi //
NK028(sa)001:9274: phyogs dus kun nas thams cad dus //
NK028(sa)001:9275: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:9276: nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur /
NK028(sa)001:9278: bzhi pa ni rdo rje las rim las /
NK028(sa)001:9279: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rigs nges shing //
NK028(sa)001:9280: gdon rnams brlag cing ngan song sbyong //
NK028(sa)001:9281: longs spyod ku ba rnam pa gnyis //
NK028(sa)001:9282: ye shes spyan gyis bzhi ru nges //
NK028(sa)001:9283: de la sogs pa mtha' yas mchog /
NK028(sa)001:9285: spyi don gnyis pa dbang slob bu la bskur ba la gsum ste /
NK028(sa)001:9290: slob bu rnams kyis dbang phyug dang /
NK028(sa)001:9291: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la phyag btsal nas gus pa'i tshul gyis /
NK028(sa)001:9292: dpal ldan sangs rgyas kun ba dag nyid //
NK028(sa)001:9293: brtse bar dgongs te bdag la yang //
NK028(sa)001:9294: dbang bskur bdud rtsi chen po nyid /
NK028(sa)001:9295: de ring rab tu rtsal bar mdzod //
NK028(sa)001:9296: ces gsol ba gdab par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:9298: sangs rgyas dag ni thams cad kyis //
NK028(sa)001:9299: gsang ba rdo rje gsum las byung //
NK028(sa)001:9300: khams gsum kun gyis phyag byas pa //
NK028(sa)001:9301: dbang bskur gnang ba chen po sbyin /
NK028(sa)001:9303: spos dang rol mo dang bcas pas //
NK028(sa)001:9304: kun gyis dkyil 'khor la bskor zhing /
NK028(sa)001:9305: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs la phyogs bcu dus bzhis bstod nas /
NK028(sa)001:9306: be ka kra ma yam kyis sngags dang /
NK028(sa)001:9307: phyag rgyas gzhal yas khang lha dang bcas pa mdun gyi nam mkha' bteg la /
NK028(sa)001:9308: dbang phyug gis me tog dang bcas pas thal mo sbyar nas gsol ba gdab par bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:9309: sa ma dza'i sngags dang phyag rgyas /
NK028(sa)001:9310: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi mdun gyi nam mkha' la spyan drangs la /
NK028(sa)001:9311: ho phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK028(sa)001:9312: bdag rdo rje che ge mo la sogs pa'i slob bu 'di rnams la lha mi'i dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:9313: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis bdag la mthu bstan du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:9316: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis //
NK028(sa)001:9317: lha dang mi yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK028(sa)001:9318: rdo rje shugs kyis bsgral nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:9319: byin brlabs dam pa nod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:9320: zhes brjod cing dbang phyug dbu rgyan gon la /
NK028(sa)001:9321: dkyil 'khor gyi drung ngam steng du dbang khri la 'dug par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:9322: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gsum ste //
NK028(sa)001:9325: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:9327: bum pa snying po lnga yi dbang //
NK028(sa)001:9328: dbu brgyan cod pan 'phreng ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:9329: go cha rgyal mtshan gdugs bza' btung //
NK028(sa)001:9330: phyag rgya'i dbang ste rnam bcu bskur /
NK028(sa)001:9343: dang po bum pa'i dbang ni las rim las /
NK028(sa)001:9344: rgyu rkyen ngo bo 'bras bu dang //
NK028(sa)001:9345: rim las skyon yon brgyad ces bya /
NK028(sa)001:9347: bum pa'i dbang gi rgyu gnyis dang /
NK028(sa)001:9350: 'bras bu bum dbang gi nus pa dngos su bskyed pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:9351: rim pa thog mar dbang bskur ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:9358: nus pa gang bskyed drug dang //
NK028(sa)001:9359: bum dbang ma thob pa'i skyon dang //
NK028(sa)001:9360: bum dbang thob pa'i yon tan dang brgyad do //
NK028(sa)001:9361: dbang bco brgyad po kun la 'dis 'dres so //
NK028(sa)001:9363: bsams rgyud bum chu ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun du bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:9365: bum pa zlum po'i pho brang du //
NK028(sa)001:9366: snod bcud ma lus kun bsdus nas //
NK028(sa)001:9367: thig le chen por rgyas btab nas //
NK028(sa)001:9368: sems can thams cad sangs rgyas yin //
NK028(sa)001:9369: badz+ra ka la sha a b+hi shany+tsa h+aum //
NK028(sa)001:9370: b+hud+d+ha ka la sha a shiny+tsa /
NK028(sa)001:9371: rat+na ka la sha a b+hishiny+tsa tram /
NK028(sa)001:9372: pad+ma ka la sha a b+hi shiny+ts+aa h+r+aih kar+m+ma ka
NK028(sa)001:9373: la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah bskur gnas mgo'i gnas
NK028(sa)001:9374: lnga / bstim gnas rtsa gnas kyi thig le la /
NK028(sa)001:9375: sgrib pa phung lnga 'byung lnga nyon mongs lnga rang ka ma'i 'dzin pa dag /
NK028(sa)001:9376: nus pa ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun la longs spyod pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:9378: bum pa byang chub sems kyi chu rgyun gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:9379: phyi nang gi dri ma yongs su dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:9380: byang chub kyi sems ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:9381: dad pa snying po lnga'i dang po /
NK028(sa)001:9383: dbang phyug gi thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od 'phros //
NK028(sa)001:9384: slob bu'i spyi bor zla gdan la dkar po las //
NK028(sa)001:9385: 'khor lo gyis mtshan pa las sku rdo rje dkar
NK028(sa)001:9386: po 'khor lo dang dril bu bsnam pa bskyed pas
NK028(sa)001:9387: sku'i dbang thob par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:9389: bde gshegs sku yi ngo bo la //
NK028(sa)001:9390: mi shigs rdo rje rgyal ba'i gtso /
NK028(sa)001:9391: sngags dang phyag rgya ldan pa yi /
NK028(sa)001:9392: rdo rje sku yi gtso bor shog /
NK028(sa)001:9393: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya badz+ra swa b+ha wa at+ma ko&a ho //
NK028(sa)001:9395: stim gnas bdud rtsi dri chen gyi khams la bstim //
NK028(sa)001:9396: gnyis pa gsung gi dbang gi bsam rgyud ni //
NK028(sa)001:9397: dbang phyug gis thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od 'phros //
NK028(sa)001:9398: slob bu'i mgrin par pad gdan la /
NK028(sa)001:9400: pad+ma am gis mtshan pa las /
NK028(sa)001:9401: gsung rdo rje dmar mo pad+ma dang dril bu bsnams pa bskyed pas /
NK028(sa)001:9402: gsung gi dbang thob par bsam la /
NK028(sa)001:9404: +aamhbade gshegs gsung gi ngo bo las /
NK028(sa)001:9405: mi shigs rdo rje chos kyi dbyings /
NK028(sa)001:9406: sngags dang phyag rgya ldan pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:9407: rdo rje gsung gi gtso bor shog /
NK028(sa)001:9408: sarba ta th+aa ga ta wa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:9409: bskur gnas mgrin par bstim gnas khrag gi khams la bstim mo //
NK028(sa)001:9410: gsum pa thugs kyi dbang gi bsam rgyud //
NK028(sa)001:9411: dbug gi thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od 'phros /
NK028(sa)001:9412: slob bu'i thugs kar nyi gdan la h+aum sngon po las rdo rje h+aum gis mtshan pa las /
NK028(sa)001:9413: thugs rdo rje sngon po rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams pa bskyed pas /
NK028(sa)001:9414: thugs kyis dbang thob par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:9417: bde gshegs thugs kyi ngo bo las //
NK028(sa)001:9418: mi shigs rdo rje chos kyi dbyings //
NK028(sa)001:9419: sngags dang phyag rgya ldan pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:9420: rdo rje thugs kyi gtso bor shog /
NK028(sa)001:9421: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra /
NK028(sa)001:9423: stim gnas byang sems kyi khams la bstim //
NK028(sa)001:9424: bzhi pa yon tan gyi dbang gi bsam rgyud //
NK028(sa)001:9425: dbang phyug gis thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od 'phros /
NK028(sa)001:9426: slob bu'i lte bar rin chen zur brgyad la swa
NK028(sa)001:9427: ser po las rin po che swas mtshan pa las
NK028(sa)001:9428: mchod pa'i rdo rje ser po rin po che dang
NK028(sa)001:9429: dril bu thugs kar bsnol ba bskyed pas yon tan
NK028(sa)001:9431: sgrag tshig swa mi 'gyur ba yi /
NK028(sa)001:9432: zhing khams la ma skyes pa yi 'bras bu las //
NK028(sa)001:9433: ma bsags pa yis longs spyod 'byung //
NK028(sa)001:9434: cir yang 'gyur ba'i ye shes kyis //
NK028(sa)001:9435: rang dbang thabs kyis bsgyur bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:9436: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au dza badz+ra at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:9437: bskur gnas lte bar bstim gnas sha chen gyi khams la bstim /
NK028(sa)001:9438: lnga pa 'phrin las kyi dbang bsams rgyud /
NK028(sa)001:9439: dbang phyug gi thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od 'phros /
NK028(sa)001:9440: slob bu'i gsang gnas chos 'byung mthing nag la ha ljang gu las /
NK028(sa)001:9441: ral gri has mtshan pa las /
NK028(sa)001:9442: chags pa'i rdo rje ljang khu ral gri dang dril bu can bskyed pas /
NK028(sa)001:9443: 'phrin las kyi dbang thob par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:9446: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:9448: las dang dngos grub kun snang ba //
NK028(sa)001:9449: ma lus mnyam par sbyor bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:9450: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ra ga badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+mako &aham /
NK028(sa)001:9452: stims gnas dri chu'i khams la bstim //
NK028(sa)001:9453: sgrib pa sngar phan chad khams lnga las byung ba'i bdud rtsi lnga //
NK028(sa)001:9454: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las lngar ma dag pa dag /
NK028(sa)001:9455: nus pa de'i ngo bor dag pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:9456: na bden pa ni 'og ma rnams kyis bden pa shes pa'i skabs su 'adre'o /
NK028(sa)001:9457: mo phyoogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs dang /
NK028(sa)001:9459: zhing khams zad mi shes pa /
NK028(sa)001:9460: mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka' bden pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:9461: bden pa chen po'i byin gyi rlabs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:9462: rigs kyi bu 'di rnams la snying po lnga'i dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:9463: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung
NK028(sa)001:9464: dang thugs dang yon tan 'phrin las lnga'i dbang dam
NK028(sa)001:9466: gsum pa dbu brgyan gyi bsam rgyud ni /
NK028(sa)001:9467: rin chen 'byung ldan gyis rab gnas byas pa'i dbu brgyan dbang phyug gis thogs la /
NK028(sa)001:9468: rat+na mu gu tra a b+hi shiny+tsa tram tram tram tram tram /
NK028(sa)001:9469: zhes slob bu'i mgo la bkon pas rin po che'i khang bu lnga gdan dang bcas par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:9470: dbang phyug gi lag pa g.yas pa'i sor mo'i bre
NK028(sa)001:9471: ga la nyi ma la gnas pa'i dpa' bo 'bru
NK028(sa)001:9472: lnga dang sor mo g.yon pa'i bre kha lnga la
NK028(sa)001:9473: zla ba la gnas pa'i dpa' mo 'bru lnga bskyed
NK028(sa)001:9474: / rdo rje bsdams pa'i gung mo gnyis sbyar zhing
NK028(sa)001:9475: mi bskyod pa yab yum sbyor ba mdzad par bsams
NK028(sa)001:9476: / las / h+aum badz+ra d+h+rig mum da tu shwa ri a b+hi shany+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:9478: sbyor mtshams nas byang chub sems kyi chu rgyun mthing ga slob bu'i spyi bor thim pas /
NK028(sa)001:9479: gzhi don gyi kun gzhi stong pa nyid kyi ye shes su dag par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:9481: h+aum chos dbyings mnyam pa chen po las //
NK028(sa)001:9482: ye shes gsal ba rnam par dag /
NK028(sa)001:9483: chos kyi dbyings kyis ye shes kyis //
NK028(sa)001:9484: skye med chos la dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:9485: ma h+aa shu nya ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:9486: de bzhin du 'dzub mo gnyis sbyar ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:9487: dzi na dzig lam dwe shwa ra ti a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:9488: snang mdzad yab yum gyis sbyor mtshams nas byang chub sems kyi chu rgyun dkar po dpral bar thim /
NK028(sa)001:9489: sbyor ba don gyi kun gyi gzhi me long lta bu'i ye shes su dag par bsams la //
NK028(sa)001:9490: dag cing gsal ba'i rang bzhin te //
NK028(sa)001:9491: skyon med sems nyid rin po che //
NK028(sa)001:9492: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis //
NK028(sa)001:9493: srid pa gsum la dbang bsgyur shog /
NK028(sa)001:9494: ma h+aa a da ri sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK028(sa)001:9497: mam mo ha ra ti a b+hi shany+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:9498: rin 'byung yab yum gyi byang chub kyi sems gser mdog can rna ltag g.yas su thim pas /
NK028(sa)001:9499: nyon yid mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dag par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:9501: khams gsum re bskongs rgyal po de //
NK028(sa)001:9502: yid bzhin rin chen gter gyi mchog /
NK028(sa)001:9503: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis //
NK028(sa)001:9504: 'gro ba re bskongs rgyal por shog /
NK028(sa)001:9505: ma h+aa sa man+ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham //
NK028(sa)001:9507: a ro lig pam ra ga ra ti a b+hi
NK028(sa)001:9508: mtha' yas yab yum gyi byang chub sems byu ru'i
NK028(sa)001:9509: mdog can ltag par thim pas /
NK028(sa)001:9510: yid so sor rtog pa'i ye shes su dag par bsams la //
NK028(sa)001:9511: am nyes pa'i skyon bral dri ma med //
NK028(sa)001:9512: skye 'gag med pa'i dngos grub gter //
NK028(sa)001:9513: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK028(sa)001:9514: srid gsum nyes dmigs sel bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:9515: ma h+aa pra ta pra be sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa 'athe'u chung sbyar ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:9516: ha pra dz+ny+aa d+h+rig tam badz+ra ra ti ab+hi zhes
NK028(sa)001:9517: pa'i sngags kyis don grub yab yum gyi byang sems
NK028(sa)001:9518: ljang khu rna ltag g.yon du thim bas /
NK028(sa)001:9519: sgo lnga bya ba grub pa'i ye shes su dag par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:9521: dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor mthar phyin zhing //
NK028(sa)001:9522: grub pa las kyis bye brag las //
NK028(sa)001:9523: bya ba nan tan ye shes kyis //
NK028(sa)001:9524: skye 'gro dbyings su sgrol bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:9525: ma h+aa kri ta a nu ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko & ham /
NK028(sa)001:9526: bskur gnas mgo bo'i gnas lngar /
NK028(sa)001:9527: rigs lnga rang rang gi dam tshig gi phyag rgya btugs la /
NK028(sa)001:9528: bstim gnas rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad la rigs lnga yab yum bstim mo //
NK028(sa)001:9529: de ltar dbu brgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:9530: sngar phan chad rnam shes tshogs brgyad du 'khrul pa'i
NK028(sa)001:9531: sgrib pa dag nas de nyid ma spangs ye shes
NK028(sa)001:9532: lngar gsal ba'ii nus pa dngos su skyes par bsgoms
NK028(sa)001:9534: dbu brgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:9535: sems rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad ma spangs gnas
NK028(sa)001:9536: su dag nas ye shes lnga'i dbang dam pa thob
NK028(sa)001:9537: par gyur cig / bzhi pa cod pan gyi dbang gi bsam rgyud ni /
NK028(sa)001:9538: dar mthing dmar gyi cod pan rdor sems dang mtha' yas kyi rang bzhin can gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:9539: gdug pa can zil gyis gnon pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:9540: chos kyi rgyal srid la mnga' brnyes par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:9542: h+aum cod pan mi 'gyur dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9543: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po'i dbang //
NK028(sa)001:9544: khams gsum kun gyi dbang phyug che //
NK028(sa)001:9545: chos kyi rgyal por dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:9546: badz+ra ar+ya lam po ta ra a b+hi shany+tsa h+r+aim h+r+aim /
NK028(sa)001:9548: bskur gnas mgo la cod pan bcing /
NK028(sa)001:9549: bstims gnas rtsa ro rkyang gnyis la bstim sngar phan chad gdug pa can zil gyis mi non cing /
NK028(sa)001:9550: chos kyi rgyal srid la mi dbang pa'i sgrib pa dag nas //
NK028(sa)001:9551: da gdug pa can zil gyis non cing /
NK028(sa)001:9552: chos kyi rgyal srid la mnga' brnyes pa'i nus pa dngos skyes par bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:9554: cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:9555: dmar po g.yon nas gyen du 'phur bas /
NK028(sa)001:9556: srid gsum chos kyi rgyal srid chen po la dbang byed pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:9557: mthing ga g.yas nas thur du 'phyang bas khams gsum
NK028(sa)001:9558: gyi gdug pa can zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang dam
NK028(sa)001:9560: lnga pa 'phreng ba'i bsams brgyud ni /
NK028(sa)001:9562: ting 'dzin gyi dbang slob bus thob par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:9566: byang chub phyogs rnams shes rab rgyan //
NK028(sa)001:9567: mi 'jigs stobs dang dpe byad mtshan //
NK028(sa)001:9568: 'bras bu chos la dbang bskur ro /
NK028(sa)001:9569: rat+na m+aa le a b+hi shany+tsa tram tram /
NK028(sa)001:9571: bskur gnas mgo la rin po che'i 'phreng ba phra mig dang ldan pa bzhag la /
NK028(sa)001:9572: bstim gnas kun+d+hara ma'i thig le'i 'phreng ba la bstim mo //
NK028(sa)001:9573: sngan chad 'bras bu'i chos la mnga' mi brnyes pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:9574: da gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin gyis stobs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:9575: 'bras bu'i chos la mnga' brnyes pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:9579: gzungs kyi sgo lnga brgya dang /
NK028(sa)001:9580: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo 'bum phrag la sogs pa
NK028(sa)001:9581: 'bras bu'i chos thams cad la dbang bskur ba'i dbang
NK028(sa)001:9582: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:9583: drug pa go cha'i dbang gi bsams brgyud ni /
NK028(sa)001:9584: slob bu'i lus rdo rje'i go khrab kyis khyab pas bdud dpung gis mi tshugs bar bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:9586: h+aum mi shigs ye shes rdo rje 'dzin //
NK028(sa)001:9587: sangs rgyas kun gyi ya lad de //
NK028(sa)001:9588: khyab pa'i tshul gyis dra ba yin //
NK028(sa)001:9589: dbang mchog dam pa sbyin par bya //
NK028(sa)001:9590: badz+ra rak+sha a b+hi shany+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:9591: bskur gnas lus la go khrab bkon pas /
NK028(sa)001:9592: bstim gnas lus rtsa'i dra bas khyab pa la bstim mo //
NK028(sa)001:9593: sngar phan chad bdud dpung gis tshugs pa'i dri ma dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:9594: da bdud dpung la sogs pa phas kyi rgol bas mi tshugs pa'i nus pa thob par bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:9597: bdud kyi dpung tshogs la sogs pa /
NK028(sa)001:9598: phas kyi rgol ba thams cad kyis mi tshugs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:9599: bdun pa rgyal mtshan gyis dbang gi bsam rgyud ni /
NK028(sa)001:9600: slob bus bdud bzhi zil gyis gnon nus pa'i dbang thob par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:9603: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che /
NK028(sa)001:9604: log par blta ba zil gnon mtshan /
NK028(sa)001:9605: thams cad tshar gcod ye shes gsung /
NK028(sa)001:9606: yon tan mngon 'byung dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:9607: badz+ra ke d+hu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:9611: bstim gnas dbang po mchog la bstim mo //
NK028(sa)001:9612: sngar phan chad bdud bzhi zil gyis ma non pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:9613: bdud bzhi zil gyis gnon nus pa'i nus pa skyes par bsgom la /
NK028(sa)001:9615: rgyal mtshan gyi dbang bskur bas bdud bzhi dang mtha'
NK028(sa)001:9616: gnyis las rgyal ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK028(sa)001:9617: cig / brgyad pa gdugs kyi dbang gi bsam rgyud ni /
NK028(sa)001:9618: thugs rje'i skyabs kyis nyon mongs pa'i gdung pa bsil bar byed pa'i dbang thob par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:9621: gnyis med ye shes rtog bral ba //
NK028(sa)001:9622: rmongs sogs sems phyir rang bzhin stong //
NK028(sa)001:9624: thugs rjes skyobs par dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:9625: badz+ra tsha tra a b+hi shiny+tsah+aum /
NK028(sa)001:9627: bskur gnas mgo steng du gdugs phub la /
NK028(sa)001:9629: glad pa bde chen rtsa 'dab so gnyis la bstim pas /
NK028(sa)001:9630: nyon mongs pa'i tshad pas gdung ba'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:9631: bde ba chen po'i bsil dang ldan par nus pa dngos su skyes par bsgoms la bden pa /
NK028(sa)001:9633: bdag dang gzhan kyi shes pa'i rgyud la yod pa'i
NK028(sa)001:9634: nyon mongs pa thams cad kyi gdung ba bsil bar
NK028(sa)001:9635: byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:9636: dgu pa bza' btung gi dbang gi bsam rgyud ni /
NK028(sa)001:9637: slob bus 'dod yon chos nyid du spyod nus pa'i dbang thob par bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:9639: bza' dang bca' dang btung la sogs //
NK028(sa)001:9640: rang sems rnam dag brgyan gyi phyir //
NK028(sa)001:9641: gnyis med rol par dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9642: bdud rtsi yid bzhin sku 'grub shog /
NK028(sa)001:9643: badz+ra a li to h+aum a b+hi shany+tsah+aum /
NK028(sa)001:9645: bskur gnas ngag gi lam du bza' btung byin la /
NK028(sa)001:9646: bstim gnas lce la gnas pa'i ro 'bab ma la bstim pas /
NK028(sa)001:9647: sngon chad 'dod yon chos nyid du longs spyod mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:9648: da longs spyod chos nyid dag pa'i brgyan du rig nas /
NK028(sa)001:9649: 'dod yon la spyod pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:9651: rigs kyi bu bza' btung gi dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9652: 'dod yon rnam pa lnga chos nyid du rigs nas /
NK028(sa)001:9653: ma spangs par rol pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:9654: phyi phan pa'i dbang dgu po 'di rnams bsdus pa
NK028(sa)001:9655: la spro na tshig bcad dang sngags tsam gyis chog
NK028(sa)001:9656: go / bcu pa phyag rgya'i dbang la //
NK028(sa)001:9657: rnam snang gi dbang gi bsam brgyud /
NK028(sa)001:9658: slob bu rnam snang du bskyed la /
NK028(sa)001:9661: gnyis su med par thim par bsam la /
NK028(sa)001:9663: snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i sku //
NK028(sa)001:9664: chos dbyings ye shes ngo bo nyid //
NK028(sa)001:9665: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:9666: rnam par snang mdzad dbang bskur ro /
NK028(sa)001:9668: bskur gnas la sogs ci rigs pa bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:9669: slob bu sh+aaka thub tu bskyed la //
NK028(sa)001:9670: rang bzhin gyi gnas nas spyan drangs /
NK028(sa)001:9672: gang gi dang por byang chub thugs bskyed nas //
NK028(sa)001:9673: bsod nams ye shes tshogs ni rdzogs mdzad cing //
NK028(sa)001:9674: dus 'dir mdzad pa rgya chen 'gro don mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:9675: sh+aakya thub pa'i dbang bskur thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9678: slob bu snang mthar bskyed bstim /
NK028(sa)001:9680: 'dod chags rdo rje chos kyi chu //
NK028(sa)001:9681: kun rtogs ye shes ngo bo nyid //
NK028(sa)001:9682: ting 'dzin chen po'i phyag rgya mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:9683: snang ba mtha' yas dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:9687: bstim bsgrags tshig thugs rje kun la snyoms pa'i bcom ldan 'das //
NK028(sa)001:9688: mtshan tsam thos pas ngan 'gro'i sdug bsngal sel //
NK028(sa)001:9689: dug gsum nad sel sangs rgyas sman kyi bla //
NK028(sa)001:9690: sangs rgyas sman bla rgyal po'i dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:9693: slob bu yul 'khor bsrungs du bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:9695: h+aum shar phyogs rgyal po yul 'khor bsrungs //
NK028(sa)001:9696: zhi ba'i 'phrin las mthar phyin sku mdog dkar //
NK028(sa)001:9697: thugs rje'i dbang gis 'gro don pi wang bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:9698: shar phyogs yul 'khor bsrungs gi dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:9704: lho phyogs rgyal po 'phags skyes po //
NK028(sa)001:9705: mngon spyod tshul gyis 'gro don sku mdog sngo /
NK028(sa)001:9706: dug gsum 'joms mdzad be con ral gri bsnams /
NK028(sa)001:9707: lho phyogs 'phags skyes po yi dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:9709: slob bu spyan mi bzang du bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:9711: h+aum nub phyogs rgyal po mig mi bzang /
NK028(sa)001:9712: sku mdog dmar smug dbang ldan 'jigs pa'i sku //
NK028(sa)001:9713: bsod nams tshogs rdzogs rin chen sbrul zhags bsnams /
NK028(sa)001:9714: nub phyogs spyan mig bzang gi dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:9716: bskur gnas slob bu rnam thos sras su bskyed bstim /
NK028(sa)001:9718: byang phyogs rgyal chen rnam thos sras //
NK028(sa)001:9719: che ba'i yon tan mthar phyin ljang khur bstan //
NK028(sa)001:9720: rin chen gter ldan be con ne'u le bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:9721: byang phyogs rnam thos sras kyis dbang bskur ro /
NK028(sa)001:9723: bskur slob bu brgya byin du bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:9726: lha yi dbang po brgya byin dang /
NK028(sa)001:9727: lha chen de yi btsun mo dang //
NK028(sa)001:9728: mngag gzhugs dang ni pho nyar bcas //
NK028(sa)001:9729: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur ro /
NK028(sa)001:9731: bskur gnas slob bu tshangs par bskyed la //
NK028(sa)001:9732: bstim bsgrag mi mjed bdag po tshangs pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:9733: lha chen de yi btsun mo dang //
NK028(sa)001:9734: mngag gzhug dang ni pho nyar bcas //
NK028(sa)001:9735: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur ro //
NK028(sa)001:9738: bstim sgrag lha chen khyab 'jug chen po dang /
NK028(sa)001:9739: lha chen de yi btsun mo dang //
NK028(sa)001:9740: mngag gzhug dang ni pho nyar bcas /
NK028(sa)001:9741: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur ro /
NK028(sa)001:9742: a b+hi bskur gnas slob bu dbang phyug chen por bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:9743: bstim bsgrags lha chen dbang phyug chen po dang //
NK028(sa)001:9744: lha chen de yi btsun mngag gzhug skal ldan bu la dbang a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:9745: bskur rgya yig la sogs lnga bcu'i dbang bzhugs so //
NK028(sa)001:9746: ka yi dbyibs ni bing ka sogs /
NK028(sa)001:9747: bya ba mtshon pa'i yi ge ka //
NK028(sa)001:9748: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9749: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9751: kha yi dbyibs ni bu yi gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9752: khyab pa mtshon pa'i yi ge kha //
NK028(sa)001:9753: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9754: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9756: ga yi dbyibs ni bse yi dbyibs //
NK028(sa)001:9757: skye ba mtshon pa'i yi ge ga /
NK028(sa)001:9758: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9759: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9761: g+ha yi dbyibs ni bum pa'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9762: grol ba mtshon pa'i yi ge g+ha //
NK028(sa)001:9763: skal ldan bu la de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9765: nga yi dbyibs ni kang ka'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9766: 'dzin pa mtshan pa'i yi ge nga //
NK028(sa)001:9767: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9768: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9770: tsa ni tsa sha lta bu'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9771: sbyod pa mtshon ba'i yi ge tsa //
NK028(sa)001:9772: skal ldan de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9774: tsha yi dbyibs ni gdugs kyi gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9776: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9777: de yi a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:9778: dza yi dbyibs ni dra ba'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9779: mi gnas mtshon pa'i yi ge dza //
NK028(sa)001:9780: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:9782: dz+ha ni dra ba chen po'i gzugs dang //
NK028(sa)001:9783: dri ma mtshon pa'i yi ge dz+ha /
NK028(sa)001:9784: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9785: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9787: nya ni ba dan kha yi kha //
NK028(sa)001:9788: shes pa mtshon pa'i yi ge nya //
NK028(sa)001:9789: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9791: ta ni 'dzam bu ti pa'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9792: de nyid mtshon pa'i yi ge ta //
NK028(sa)001:9793: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9794: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9796: tha ni tha gu ra yi kha /
NK028(sa)001:9797: byed pa mtshon pa'i yi ge tha //
NK028(sa)001:9798: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9800: da ni mkha' 'gro ma yi kha //
NK028(sa)001:9801: nyer zhi mtshon pa'i yi ge da //
NK028(sa)001:9802: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9803: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9805: d+ha yi dbyibs ni dad pa'i kha //
NK028(sa)001:9806: chos mtshon pa yi yi ge d+ha //
NK028(sa)001:9807: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9809: na yi dbyibs ni to la'i kha //
NK028(sa)001:9810: ming mtshon pa yi yi ge na //
NK028(sa)001:9811: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9812: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9814: ta yi dbyibs ni dang ba bza' //
NK028(sa)001:9815: lam mtshon pa yi yi ge ta //
NK028(sa)001:9816: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9817: de yi dbang a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:9818: tha yi dbyibs ni pha wang gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9819: gnas pa mtshon pa yi ge tha //
NK028(sa)001:9820: skal ldan bu la de yi dbang a b+hi da yi dbyibs ni che ba'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9821: 'khrul pa mtshon pa'i yi ge da //
NK028(sa)001:9822: skal ldan bu la de yi dbang /
NK028(sa)001:9824: d+ha yi dbyibs ni gzhu yi gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9825: rang bzhin mtshon pa'i yi ge d+ha //
NK028(sa)001:9826: skal ldan bu la dbang de yi dbang a b+hi na yi dbyibs ni ma he'i kha //
NK028(sa)001:9827: yul mtshon pa yi yi ge na //
NK028(sa)001:9828: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9829: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9830: a b+hi pa yi dbyibs ni ri rab gzugs /
NK028(sa)001:9831: don mtshon pa yi yi ge pa //
NK028(sa)001:9832: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9833: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9835: pha yi dbyibs ni khrung bya'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9836: 'bras bu mtshon pa'i yi ge pha //
NK028(sa)001:9837: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:9838: de yi a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:9839: ba yi dbyibs ni 'dam bya'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9840: 'ching grol mtshon pa'i yi ge ba //
NK028(sa)001:9841: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9842: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9844: b+ha ni kha lag che yi gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9845: srid pa mtshon pa'i yi ge b+ha //
NK028(sa)001:9846: skal ldan bu de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9847: a b+hi ma ni spre'u slong ba'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9848: dran pa mtshon byed yi ge ma //
NK028(sa)001:9849: skal ldan de yi dbang a b+hi ya yi dbyibs ni nyi ma'i gzugs /
NK028(sa)001:9850: mi 'gyur mtshon pa'i yi ge ya //
NK028(sa)001:9851: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9852: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9854: ra ni ku tsi ta yi kha rdul tshon byed pa'i yi ge ra //
NK028(sa)001:9855: skal ldan de yi dbang a b+hi la ni bya rog sha 'then pa //
NK028(sa)001:9856: bcom pa mtshon pa'i yi ge la /
NK028(sa)001:9857: skal ldan bu a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:9858: wa ni ka ting ga yi kha //
NK028(sa)001:9859: rgyu rkyen mtshon pa'i yi ge wa //
NK028(sa)001:9860: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9861: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9863: sha yi dbyibs ni ri bong gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9864: zhi ba mtshon pa'i yi ge sha //
NK028(sa)001:9865: skal ldan bu de yi a b+hi sha ni shan+ta ha ka'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9866: shes pa mtshon byed pa yi ge sha /
NK028(sa)001:9867: skal ldan de yi a b+hi sa ni bram ze slong pa'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9868: rnam pa thams cad shes pa'i sa //
NK028(sa)001:9869: skal ldan de yi dbang a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:9870: ha yi dbyibs ni ha ra ka /
NK028(sa)001:9871: rgyud mtshon byed pa'i yi ge ha //
NK028(sa)001:9872: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:9873: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9875: k+sha yi dbyibs ni srin po'i kha /
NK028(sa)001:9876: thar zad k+sha yi dbyibs ni srin po'i kha /
NK028(sa)001:9877: thar zad mtshon byed yi ge k+shah skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9878: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9880: a ni seng ge glal ba'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9881: skye med mtshon pa'i yi ge a //
NK028(sa)001:9882: skal ldan bu la de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9884: a ni seng ge 'gying ba'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9885: bdag mtshon byed pa'i yi ge +aa //
NK028(sa)001:9886: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9887: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9889: i ni seng ge sgra 'byin gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9890: g.yengs pa mtshon pa'i yi ge i /
NK028(sa)001:9891: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9892: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9894: +ai ni lcags kyu bsnol bas brten pa'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9895: ri mtshon byed pa'i yi ge i //
NK028(sa)001:9896: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9897: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9899: u ni shin tu phun sum tshogs pa'i gzugs /
NK028(sa)001:9900: zhes pa mtshon byed yi ge u //
NK028(sa)001:9901: skal ldan bu la de yi dbang a b+hi u
NK028(sa)001:9902: ni 'od dpag med pa re ba drangs pa'i gzugs
NK028(sa)001:9903: / mun pa mtshon byed yi ge u //
NK028(sa)001:9904: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9905: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9907: ri ni lcags sgrogs skyo gas drangs pa'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9908: nga rgyal mtshon byed yi ge r+ai //
NK028(sa)001:9909: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9910: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9912: r+ai ni lcags sgrogs skyo gas drangs pa'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9913: lha min mtshon byed yi ge r+ai /
NK028(sa)001:9914: skal ldan bu la de yi dbang mchog a b+hi l+ai ni bya gag skyo gas drangs pa'i gzugs /
NK028(sa)001:9915: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9916: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9918: l+ai ni bya gag skyo gas drangs pa'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9919: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9920: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9921: a b+hi e ni a mo'i kha 'dra ba la //
NK028(sa)001:9922: gsung pa mtshon byed yi ge e //
NK028(sa)001:9923: skal ldan bu la de yi dbang mchog a b+hi
NK028(sa)001:9924: ee ni re ba rtsegs pa'i 'od dpag med pa'i
NK028(sa)001:9925: gzugs // mnar sems mtshon byed yi ge ee //
NK028(sa)001:9926: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9927: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9929: o ni 'od dpag thig le'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9930: 'jigs pa mtshon byed yi ge o /
NK028(sa)001:9931: skal ldan de yi dbang mchog thob par shog a b+hi shiny+tsah+aum //
NK028(sa)001:9932: +aoo ni gzhu brdungs pa yi gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9933: stong pa mtshon byed yi ge oo //
NK028(sa)001:9934: skal ldan bu yi de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9936: am ni drang srong tshul bstan gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9937: ngag mtshon byed pa'i yi ge am //
NK028(sa)001:9938: skal ldan bu la dbang skur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9939: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9941: ahni gdugs phub pa yi gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:9942: nus pa mtshon byed yi ge +aa //
NK028(sa)001:9943: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:9944: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:9946: des yan gyis rgya yig lnga bcu'i dbang song ngo //
NK028(sa)001:9947: bod kyi ka smad sum cu'i dbang bzhugs so //
NK028(sa)001:9948: ka ni gtsang byed sgrol ba'o zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:9949: khams gsum gyis sems can dbang byed cing /
NK028(sa)001:9950: nyon mongs pa las sgrol bar byed pa lags te /
NK028(sa)001:9951: de'i byin brlabs kyis chos kyis sku'i gsung gi gzugs brnyan du byung pa'i tshig gis gsung 'dis kyang /
NK028(sa)001:9952: sems can la dbang byed cing /
NK028(sa)001:9953: nyon mongs pa las sgrol ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:9954: kha ni khams gsum yongs gyi rgyun //
NK028(sa)001:9955: zhes 'byung ste khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyi brgyan du byung ba yin te /
NK028(sa)001:9957: don gyi gsung gi gzugs brnyan tshig gis gsung 'dis sems can gyis rgyan du gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:9958: 'khor ba las sgrol bar mdzad pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:9959: ga ni ma chags dag par mdzad ces 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:9960: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK028(sa)001:9961: ci la yang ma chags shing rnam par dag pa
NK028(sa)001:9962: yin pas / de'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:9964: ci la yang ma chags shing /
NK028(sa)001:9965: rnam par dag ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:9966: nga ni nga med nga las rgyal zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:9967: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po mnyam pa chen po'i ngang las ma g.yos shing /
NK028(sa)001:9968: mtshan ma las rgyal ba yin te /
NK028(sa)001:9970: chos kyi sku mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las ma g.yos shing /
NK028(sa)001:9971: mtshan ma las rgyal pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:9972: 'phrul gyi yi ge ka kha smad lnga ni /
NK028(sa)001:9973: rgyal ba rnams kyi gsung mchog dam pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:9974: rgyal ba'i gsung rabs rnams la phul ba yis /
NK028(sa)001:9975: yon bdag tshogs rnams mngon par sangs rgyas shog /
NK028(sa)001:9976: ca ni gnyis med don rtogs ces 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:9977: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK028(sa)001:9978: de ni mtshan ma dang mtshan ma med pa gnyis
NK028(sa)001:9979: su med pa'i don yin te /
NK028(sa)001:9981: chos sku'i mtshan ma dang mtshan ma med pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:9982: cha ni thabs dang shes rab bo zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:9983: dus gsum gyis chos sku bde pa chen po las
NK028(sa)001:9984: thabs dang shes rab kyi sprul ji snyed cig byung
NK028(sa)001:9985: nas / 'gro ba'i don byed pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:9987: chos kyi sku thabs dang shes rab gnyis kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:9988: ja ni ma gos dag par mdzad /
NK028(sa)001:9990: dus gsum gyis sku bde ba chen po de bag
NK028(sa)001:9991: chags kyi ma gos shing rnam par dag pa yin
NK028(sa)001:9992: te / de'i byin gyi brlabs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:9993: chos kyi sku bag chags kyis ma gos shing dag pa'i dbang dam pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:9994: nya ni chos nyid brdar sha gcod zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:9995: dus gsum du chos nyid rgya mtsho dang 'dra ba la /
NK028(sa)001:9996: rig pa'i ye shes dang 'dra bas brdar sha gcod pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:9997: de'i don gyis chos nyid rgya mtsho la /
NK028(sa)001:9998: rig pa'i ye shes dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:9999: 'phrul gyi yi ge ca cha smad lnga ni /
NK028(sa)001:10000: rgyal ba rnams kyi gsung mchog dam pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:10001: rgyal ba rnams kyi gsung rab rnams la phul ba yis /
NK028(sa)001:10002: yon bdag tshogs ni mngon par sangs rgyas shog /
NK028(sa)001:10003: ta ni mkhas pa'i 'od zer can zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:10004: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po de las /
NK028(sa)001:10005: thugs rje 'od zer byung ba yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10007: chos kyis thugs rje'i 'od zer 'byung ba dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10008: tha ni dkon mchog 'byung ba'i rgyu /
NK028(sa)001:10010: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po las /
NK028(sa)001:10011: dgongs pa zab mo'i ye shes 'byung ba yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10013: chos sku bde ba chen po'i dgongs pa zab mo'i
NK028(sa)001:10014: ye shes 'byung pa'i dbang dam pa dang ldan par
NK028(sa)001:10015: gyur cig / da ni rgyu 'bras gnyis su med pa zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:10016: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po
NK028(sa)001:10017: las rgyu'i chos dang 'bras bu'i chos gnyis su med
NK028(sa)001:10018: pa yin te / de'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:10019: chos kyi sdug bsngal gtan spangs ste /
NK028(sa)001:10020: ngang gis bde ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10021: d+ha ni bslu ba med pa'i sgo nas /
NK028(sa)001:10022: dri ma thams cad grol bar byed ces pa /
NK028(sa)001:10023: d+ha b+ha ra'i sgra la drangs nas rdzun dang bral ba ste /
NK028(sa)001:10024: sgyu ma lta bur thams cad grol ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10025: na ni sdug bsngal med ces 'byung ste //
NK028(sa)001:10026: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po las /
NK028(sa)001:10027: 'khor ba'i sdug bsdul med cing ngang gi bde ba yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10029: chos kyi sku sdug bsngal gtan spangs te ngang gis bde ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10030: 'phrul gyi yi ge ta tha smad lnga ni //
NK028(sa)001:10031: rgyal ba rnams kyi gsung mchog dam pa ste //
NK028(sa)001:10032: rgyal ba'i gsung rab rnams la phul ba yis //
NK028(sa)001:10033: yon bdag tshogs ni mngon par sangs rgyas shog /
NK028(sa)001:10034: pa ni thams cad bskyed par byed ces 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:10035: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po las rig pa'i ye shes bskyed pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10037: chos kyi sku 'di mthong ba tsam gyis /
NK028(sa)001:10038: gzhan rigs pa'i shes rab bskyed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10039: pha ni pha rol phyin la gnas zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:10040: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal thams cad kyi pha rol phyin cing /
NK028(sa)001:10041: mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10043: chos kyi sku bde ba chen po 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las pha rol tu phyin cing /
NK028(sa)001:10044: mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i dbang dam pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10045: ba ni bde ba chen po zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:10046: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po de ni /
NK028(sa)001:10047: dngos po mtshan ma thams cad las mnyam pa chen po'i ngang du bde ba yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10048: de yi byin gyis rlabs kyis /
NK028(sa)001:10049: chos sku dngos po dang mtshan ma thams cad las
NK028(sa)001:10050: mnyam pa chen po'i ngang du bde pa'i dbang dang
NK028(sa)001:10052: ma ni srid gsum yongs kyi ma zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:10053: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po de yang /
NK028(sa)001:10054: kun gyi gzhi mar gyur pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10056: chos kyi sku srid gsum yongs las rgyal zhing /
NK028(sa)001:10057: kun gyi gzhi ma gyur ba'i dbang dang ldan par
NK028(sa)001:10058: gyur cig 'phrul gyi yi ge pa pha smad lnga
NK028(sa)001:10059: ni / rgyal ba rnams kyi gsung mchog dam pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:10060: rgyal ba'i gsung rab rnams la phul ba yis /
NK028(sa)001:10061: yon bdag tshogs rnams mngon par sangs rgyas shog /
NK028(sa)001:10064: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po de ni /
NK028(sa)001:10065: sku dang ye shes dang stobs dang /
NK028(sa)001:10066: mi 'jigs pa la sogs ba'i 'du 'bral med pa'i gnas yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10067: de'i byin gyis brlabs kyi chos kyi sku dang ye
NK028(sa)001:10068: shes 'du 'bral med pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK028(sa)001:10069: cig / tsha ni don dam pa lus la rdzogs zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:10070: don dam pa chos kyi sku ni /
NK028(sa)001:10071: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i chos thams cad rdzogs pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10073: chos kyi sku'i rgyu dang 'bras bu rdzogs pa'i dbang dang ldan pa gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10074: dza ni 'bar ba'i yul gnas zhes 'byung ste //
NK028(sa)001:10075: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po de //
NK028(sa)001:10076: thugs rje'i 'od zer 'byung ba'i gnas yin te //
NK028(sa)001:10078: chos kyi sku thugs rje'i 'od zer 'byung ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10079: wa ni mya ngan thams cad 'dul zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:10080: dus gsum du chos sku bde ba chen po de
NK028(sa)001:10081: 'khor ba'i mya ngan thams cad 'dul ba yin te
NK028(sa)001:10083: chos kyi skus 'khor ba'i mya ngan thams cad 'dul ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10084: 'phrul gyi yi ge tsa tsha smad lnga ni /
NK028(sa)001:10085: rgyal ba rnams kyi gsung mchog dam pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:10086: rgyal ba'i gsung rabs rnams la phul ba yis /
NK028(sa)001:10087: yon bdag tshogs rnams mngon par sangs rgyas shog /
NK028(sa)001:10088: zha ni gzhal yas bde ba chen po zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:10089: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po zhes 'byung te /
NK028(sa)001:10090: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po de ni /
NK028(sa)001:10091: thams cad kyi gnas dang gzhal yas khang bde ba chen por gyur pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10093: gnas dang gzhal yas khang bde ba chen po'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10094: za ni skye ba med pa'i chos las 'phags zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:10095: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po de ni /
NK028(sa)001:10096: chos thams cad rgyu rkyen las ma skyes pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10098: chos nyid gsal ba'i ye shes kyis nyon mongs pa
NK028(sa)001:10099: ma rig pa'i mun pa sel ba'i dbang dang ldan
NK028(sa)001:10100: par gyur cig / 'a ni gom pa'i tshogs la brtson zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:10101: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po'i ngang du /
NK028(sa)001:10102: gsung gi tshogs rang bzhin med par sgra sgrogs pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10103: de'i byin gyis brlabs kyis chos kyi sku gsung gis
NK028(sa)001:10104: tshogs thams cad rang bzhin med par sgra sgrogs pa'i
NK028(sa)001:10105: dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10106: ya ni 'thor byed pho nya'i bdag /
NK028(sa)001:10108: dus gsum du chos kyi sku la bde bar chen
NK028(sa)001:10109: po de las gzugs sku rnam gnyis kyi pho nya
NK028(sa)001:10110: byung nas / 'gro ba sems can gyi don byed pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10111: de'i byin gyis brlabs kyis chos kyi sku las sprul pa'i sku byung nas /
NK028(sa)001:10112: 'gro ba'i sems can gyi don byed pa'i dbang dang
NK028(sa)001:10113: ldan 'phrul gyi yi ge zha za smad lnga ni
NK028(sa)001:10114: / rgyal ba rnams rgyal ba'i yon bdag ra ni
NK028(sa)001:10115: gcod par byed pa'i yul la dbang zhes 'byung ste
NK028(sa)001:10116: / // dus gsum du bde ba chen po chos kyi sku de ni //
NK028(sa)001:10117: ye shes bcad par bya ba'i yul yin te //
NK028(sa)001:10119: chos kyi sku ye shes spyod pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10120: la ni mnyam nyid sprul pa'i sku zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:10121: dus gsum du chos kyi sku mnyam pa nyid las
NK028(sa)001:10122: ye shes sprul pa'i sku byung nas sems can kyi
NK028(sa)001:10125: chos kyi sku mnyam pa nyid las //
NK028(sa)001:10126: ye shes sprul ba'i sku byung nas /
NK028(sa)001:10127: 'gro ba sems can gyi don byed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10128: sha ni snang byed mkha' la shar /
NK028(sa)001:10130: dus gsum du bde ba chen po chos kyi sku
NK028(sa)001:10131: mkha' las ye shes kyi bye brag ji snyed cig
NK028(sa)001:10132: shar nas / 'gro ba sems can gyi don byed pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10133: de'i byin brlabs kyi chos kyis sku la ye shes
NK028(sa)001:10134: kyi bye brag shar nas sems can gyi don byed
NK028(sa)001:10135: pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10136: sa ni 'khor ba'i rang bzhin ste /
NK028(sa)001:10138: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po de las /
NK028(sa)001:10139: 'khor lo la sogs sna tshogs 'byung nas 'gro ba sems can gyi don byed pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10141: thugs phyag mtshan sna tshogs byung nas 'gro ba sems
NK028(sa)001:10142: can gyi don byed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK028(sa)001:10143: cig / ha ni thabs mkhas dbyings nas byon zhes 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:10144: dus gsum du chos kyi sku bde ba chen po'i
NK028(sa)001:10145: dbyings nas thabs mkhas pa'i mdzad spyod bsam gyis mi
NK028(sa)001:10147: 'gro ba sems can gyi don mthar phyin pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10149: chos kyi skus 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10150: a ni skye med chos kyi dbyings zhes 'byung ste //
NK028(sa)001:10151: dus gsum du bde ba chen po chos kyi dbyings /
NK028(sa)001:10152: rgyu rkyen dang bral ba'i dbyings nas 'gro ba'i don ma 'gags par shar bas /
NK028(sa)001:10153: sems can gyi don mthar phyin pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10154: de'i byin gyis brlabs kyis chos kyi skus 'gro ba
NK028(sa)001:10155: sems can kyi don byed pa'i dbang dam pa dang
NK028(sa)001:10157: mgo ni ma nor lam yin te //
NK028(sa)001:10158: de yi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK028(sa)001:10159: tig ni shes rab ming du smra //
NK028(sa)001:10160: de yi dbang mchog khyod la sbyin //
NK028(sa)001:10161: shad ni thabs chen tshigs su gcod //
NK028(sa)001:10162: de yi dbang chog khyod la sbyin //
NK028(sa)001:10163: bskur gnas mago'am snying gar tsak+ka li rnams btug la /
NK028(sa)001:10164: bstim gnas lha tshogs rnams rang rang gi rtog tshogs la bstim /
NK028(sa)001:10165: rtog tshog rang dga' ma'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:10166: sku dang ye shes rang snang ba'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:10167: bden pa rigs kyi bu khyed rnams la phyag rgya'i dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:10168: rtog pa ma spangs gnas su dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:10169: sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo nyid mngon du gyur te
NK028(sa)001:10170: snang ba rnam par 'a byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK028(sa)001:10171: goms pa dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10172: de dag ni phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu'i las kyi rim ste //
NK028(sa)001:10173: phyi lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du bskur ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:10174: de yang phan dbang bcu po thob pas skye ba 'dir tshe ring ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:10175: bde ba phun sum tshogs pa thob pa la phan //
NK028(sa)001:10176: phyi mar mtho ris dang thar pa thob la phan pa'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:10177: phan pa'i dbang zhes tha snyad du byas pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:10178: gnyis pa nang nus pa'i dbang la lnga ste /
NK028(sa)001:10183: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams gyi dbang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:10184: dang po nyan dbang la bsam rgyud ni /
NK028(sa)001:10185: yang dbang phyug gi thugs ka nas b+h+rum ser po chad de /
NK028(sa)001:10186: slob bu rnams kyi rna ba gnyis kyi 'dom rtsar
NK028(sa)001:10187: 'phros pa las gzhal yas khang dbus 'khor lo rtsibs
NK028(sa)001:10189: yang dbang phyug gi thugs ka nas tram zung lnga dang /
NK028(sa)001:10190: h+aum dza h+aum h+aum h+aum bam h+aum ho /
NK028(sa)001:10191: bcu 'phros pa 'od du zhu ba las phyag mtshan bcu /
NK028(sa)001:10196: rdo rje rin chen yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:10197: lhor rdo rje gzi brjid yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:10198: nub tu rdo rje rgyal mtshan yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:10199: byang du rdo rje bzhad pa yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:10200: shar sgor gshin rje gshed yab yum /
NK028(sa)001:10201: lhor stobs po che yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:10202: nub tu rta mgrin yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:10203: byang du bdud rtsi 'khyil pa yab yum /
NK028(sa)001:10205: byin gyis brlabs snyan gsan dbab //
NK028(sa)001:10211: slob ma rin chen 'byung ldan du bskyed la /
NK028(sa)001:10212: bo ti ka pa li dang bcas pa rin 'byung gi rab gnas can bsnams la /
NK028(sa)001:10215: gsang ba gsang chen gsang mchog gang /
NK028(sa)001:10216: gsang ba kun la gnyan par bya //
NK028(sa)001:10217: gsang ba'i don nyid rtags pa las //
NK028(sa)001:10218: gzhan du smra bar bya ba min /
NK028(sa)001:10219: zhes brjod nas bskur gnas slob bu'i lag par gtad nas /
NK028(sa)001:10221: nyan shes kyi thig le la bstim pas /
NK028(sa)001:10222: sngon chad bka' phyi nang gi chos thams cad la
NK028(sa)001:10223: thogs pa med par nyan mi nus pa'i sgrib pa
NK028(sa)001:10224: dag nas / da phyin chad nyan nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsgoms la bden pa /
NK028(sa)001:10225: rigs kyi bu 'di rnams la nyan pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:10226: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka' phyi nang thams cad la
NK028(sa)001:10227: thogs pa med par nyan nus pa'i dbang dam pa
NK028(sa)001:10229: gnyis pa sgom dbang la bsam rgyud ni //
NK028(sa)001:10230: dbang phyug gi thugs ka nas b+h+rum chad de /
NK028(sa)001:10231: slob bu rnams kyi snying gi 'dom rtsar 'phros pa las gzhal yas khang /
NK028(sa)001:10234: yang dbang phyug gi thugs ka nas zung lnga dang /
NK028(sa)001:10238: bcu 'phros pa 'od du zhu ba las /
NK028(sa)001:10242: dbus su rnam snang yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:10243: shar rtsibs la rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:10244: lhor rdo rje rgyal po yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:10245: nub tu rdo rje chags pa yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:10246: byang du rdo rje legs pa yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:10247: sgo bzhir sgo ba yab yum bzhi bsgom /
NK028(sa)001:10252: mchod bstod 'od du zhu ba las /
NK028(sa)001:10253: slob bu rnam snang du bskyed la /
NK028(sa)001:10255: dus gsum rgyal ba'i sras chen po /
NK028(sa)001:10256: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje zung /
NK028(sa)001:10257: rgyal ba thams cad mnyes mchod pa /
NK028(sa)001:10258: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor /
NK028(sa)001:10260: bskur gnas ni lag par 'phreng ba gtad la /
NK028(sa)001:10261: bstims gnas ni snying gi rtsar /
NK028(sa)001:10262: dran byed rigs shes kyi thig le la bstim pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:10263: sngon chad lha dang mi rtog dbyer med bsgom mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:10264: da bsgom nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:10267: lha dang mi rtog pa thams cad la /
NK028(sa)001:10268: thogs pa med pa'i ting nge 'dzin sgoms pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10269: gsum pa 'phrin las kyi dbang la bsam rgyud ni //
NK028(sa)001:10270: dbang phyug gi thugs ka nas b+h+rum ljang khu //
NK028(sa)001:10271: slob bu'i lag pa gnyis kyi 'dom rtsar 'phros pa las /
NK028(sa)001:10275: yang dbang phyug gi thugs ka nas ha zung lnga dang /
NK028(sa)001:10284: dbus su don grub yab yum /
NK028(sa)001:10285: shar rtsibs la rdo rje las yab yum /
NK028(sa)001:10286: lhor rdo rje bsrungs pa yab yum /
NK028(sa)001:10287: nub tu rdo rje gnod sbyin yab yum /
NK028(sa)001:10288: byang du rdo rje khu tshur yab yum /
NK028(sa)001:10289: sgo bzhir sgo ba yab yum bzhi bskyed /
NK028(sa)001:10290: de la dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs /
NK028(sa)001:10296: slob ma don grub yab yum du bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:10298: khyod ni rdo rje las yin gyis //
NK028(sa)001:10299: las rnams ma lus khyod kyis byos //
NK028(sa)001:10301: khyod kyi dgos pa byed pa yin /
NK028(sa)001:10304: lag par rgya gram gtad la /
NK028(sa)001:10305: bstim gnas ni lag par gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa'i bskyod byed kyi thig le la bstim nas /
NK028(sa)001:10306: sngon chad 'phrin las bzhis dbang du 'dul mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:10307: da 'dul nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:10309: 'phrin las rnam pa bzhis srid pa gsum gyi sems
NK028(sa)001:10310: can ma lus pa'i don ji ltar 'dul ba bzhin
NK028(sa)001:10311: byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10312: bzhi pa 'chad dbang bsam brgyud ni /
NK028(sa)001:10313: dbang phyug gi thugs ka nas slob bu'i lce stengs su b+h+rum 'phros pa las /
NK028(sa)001:10317: yang dbang phyug gi thugs ka nas h+r+aih zung lnga dang /
NK028(sa)001:10322: bcu 'phros pa 'od du zhu ba la /
NK028(sa)001:10326: dbus su snang mtha' yab yum /
NK028(sa)001:10327: shar rtsibs la rdo rje chos yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:10328: lhor rdo rje rnon po yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:10329: nub tu rdo rje rgyu yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:10330: byang du rdo rje smra ba yab yum //
NK028(sa)001:10331: sgo bzhir sgo ba yab yum zung bzhi bskyed //
NK028(sa)001:10332: de la dbang bskur byin gyis rlabs //
NK028(sa)001:10333: ye shes pa dbab snyan gsan dbab /
NK028(sa)001:10337: 'od du zhu ba las slob ma snang ba mtha' yas su gyur bar bsam /
NK028(sa)001:10339: gyis bdud rtsi bla med kyis //
NK028(sa)001:10340: dad ldan skyes bu ngoms par byos //
NK028(sa)001:10341: rab 'bring tha ma'i blo can la //
NK028(sa)001:10342: mthun par gsang bsgrags gzhan du min /
NK028(sa)001:10347: phyag shing gsum la 'khor lo gdan du byos la /
NK028(sa)001:10349: g.yon du phyag shing gtad la /
NK028(sa)001:10350: bstim gnas ni lce la gnas pa smra /
NK028(sa)001:10351: byed reg shes kyi thig le la bstim zhing /
NK028(sa)001:10352: sngon chad sems can gyi shes rgyud la chos kyi
NK028(sa)001:10353: 'khor lo bskor mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas
NK028(sa)001:10354: / da chos kyi 'khor lo rgyun mi 'chad par bskor nus pa dngos su bskyed par bsgoms shing /
NK028(sa)001:10357: sems can thams cad kyi shes pa'i rgyud la theg
NK028(sa)001:10358: pa mtha' dag gi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i
NK028(sa)001:10359: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:10360: lnga pa rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams gyis dbang la bsam rgyud ni /
NK028(sa)001:10361: dbang phyug gi thugs ka nas /
NK028(sa)001:10362: b+h+rum cha lnga 'phros te slob bu'i mgo lag pa g.yas g.yon /
NK028(sa)001:10363: rkang mthil g.yas g.yon rnams su 'phros pas /
NK028(sa)001:10364: gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa cha lnga bskyed la /
NK028(sa)001:10365: mgor zung lnga lag pa g.yas su h+aum lnga /
NK028(sa)001:10367: rkang pa g.yon la am zung lnga /
NK028(sa)001:10373: sog pa g.yas sogs sprag sog pa g.yon /
NK028(sa)001:10376: gshang lam rnams su h+aum zung re re bkod la /
NK028(sa)001:10378: lha bcu rang rang gi phyag mtshan du gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:10380: mgo la rnam snang yab yum sogs bcu /
NK028(sa)001:10381: lag pa g.yas su rdor sems yab yum la sogs pa bcu /
NK028(sa)001:10382: lag pa g.yon du rin 'byung yab yum la sogs
NK028(sa)001:10383: bcu rkang ba g.yon du snang mtha' yab yum la
NK028(sa)001:10384: sogs pa bcu / rkang pa g.yas su don grub yab yum la sogs bcu /
NK028(sa)001:10385: spyi gtsug tu h+aum ka ra yab yum /
NK028(sa)001:10386: snying gar rnam par rgyal ba yab yum /
NK028(sa)001:10387: nu ma g.yas la dbyug sngon yab yum /
NK028(sa)001:10388: dpung mgo g.yas la gshin rje gshed mthing yab yum /
NK028(sa)001:10389: sog steng g.yas par mi g.yo mgon po ljang dmar //
NK028(sa)001:10390: sog dprag tu rta mgrin dmar po //
NK028(sa)001:10391: sog steng g.yon du gzhan gyis mi chod sngon po /
NK028(sa)001:10392: dpung mgo g.yon du bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang khu /
NK028(sa)001:10393: nu ma g.yon par khams gsum rnam rgyal ser po /
NK028(sa)001:10394: gshang mkhar stobs po che dud ka yab yum rnams bskyed cing /
NK028(sa)001:10395: de ltar lha bdun cu po la dbang bskur byin gyis rlabs //
NK028(sa)001:10401: slob ma kun tu bzang por bsam mo //
NK028(sa)001:10403: phyogs bcu dus bzhi thams cad kyis //
NK028(sa)001:10404: sku gsung thugs kyis rdo rje che //
NK028(sa)001:10405: dkyil 'khor kun gyi byed pa po //
NK028(sa)001:10406: dkyil 'khor kun gyi sbyin pa spyod /
NK028(sa)001:10408: lag pa g.yas g.yon du dbang phyug gi rdo rje
NK028(sa)001:10409: dang dril bu bsnol la gtad de snying khar bsnol
NK028(sa)001:10410: du bcug la / bstim gnas ni yan lag lnga'i reg shes kyi thig le la bstim pas /
NK028(sa)001:10411: sngon chad slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhug cing dbang
NK028(sa)001:10412: bskur ba la sogs pa gzhan don bya bar mi
NK028(sa)001:10413: nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:10414: da dbang pyug chen por gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:10415: bdag dang gzhan gyi don phun sum tshogs par spyod
NK028(sa)001:10416: cing bsgrub nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par
NK028(sa)001:10418: rigs kyi bu 'di rnams la rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:10419: slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhug cing dbang bskur ba
NK028(sa)001:10420: la sogs pa'i las thams cad byed pa'i rdo rje
NK028(sa)001:10421: rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang dam pa thob
NK028(sa)001:10422: par gyur cig / de dag ni nang nus pa'i dbang gi las kyi rim pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:10423: nang lus kyi dkyil 'khor bskur ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:10424: de yang nyan dbang dang bsgom dbang thob pas bdag don nus /
NK028(sa)001:10425: 'phrin las kyi dbang dang 'chad dbang thob pas gzhan don nus //
NK028(sa)001:10426: rdo rje rgyal bo bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang thob pas //
NK028(sa)001:10427: bdag gzhan thams cad kyi don phun sum tshogs pa nus pa'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:10428: nus pa'i dbang zhes tha snyad du bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:10429: nang nus pa'i dbang lnga pa rnams ma basngusa pa la spro na tshigs bcad dang //
NK028(sa)001:10431: gsum pa gsang ba zab mo'i dbang la /
NK028(sa)001:10432: rtsa brgyud le'u bcu pa las //
NK028(sa)001:10433: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya las //
NK028(sa)001:10434: bde ba'i 'bru tshogs gsol ba'i rgyun //
NK028(sa)001:10435: rdo rje'i lam nas pad+mora bskyil /
NK028(sa)001:10438: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang dang //
NK028(sa)001:10439: dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:10442: mi bskyod yab yum rol pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:10443: bde ba gsal zhing mi dmigs pa //
NK028(sa)001:10444: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya yis /
NK028(sa)001:10445: rdo rje ye shes h+aum tshogs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:10447: yungs dkar tshan tsam rdo rje sems /
NK028(sa)001:10448: rtse nas rtse ru phyin pa yis /
NK028(sa)001:10449: rang bzhin chos khams dkyil 'khor gyi /
NK028(sa)001:10450: sa bon zung gsum gnyis dang bcas /
NK028(sa)001:10451: gnas ngan len pa kun sbyangs ste /
NK028(sa)001:10452: dmigs med sems kyi ye shes lnga /
NK028(sa)001:10453: gsal ba'i sa bon tshig pa bzhin /
NK028(sa)001:10454: mi skye thabs kyi dbugs phyung pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:10456: gnyis pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ni /
NK028(sa)001:10458: de las gzhan yang bshad bya ba /
NK028(sa)001:10459: rjes su 'jug pa'i phyag rgya nyid /
NK028(sa)001:10460: zil ba'i thig le sngon lam bzhin /
NK028(sa)001:10461: bcu drug phyed phyed thig le gcig /
NK028(sa)001:10462: phan tshun bgod pa'i stobs kyis bstim /
NK028(sa)001:10463: bde ba gnyis pa'i ngo bo nyid /
NK028(sa)001:10464: gsum pa'i ye shes dkyil 'khor du /
NK028(sa)001:10465: gsal bar shar bas gyur pa'i sgra /
NK028(sa)001:10468: gsum pa dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang ni /
NK028(sa)001:10470: de las gzhan yang bshad bya ba //
NK028(sa)001:10471: rdo rje nyi ma thabs kyi rgya /
NK028(sa)001:10472: phung po khams tshogs dang lngan pa //
NK028(sa)001:10473: de zla bsil byed shes rab dngos //
NK028(sa)001:10474: dus gcig ro mnyam thig le che //
NK028(sa)001:10475: sum bcu rtsa gnyis mtshan rdzogs shing //
NK028(sa)001:10476: zla ba'i ye shes lnga bcu drug //
NK028(sa)001:10477: dpe la rdzogs pa dpag tu med //
NK028(sa)001:10478: sems shes mngon par shes dang ldan //
NK028(sa)001:10480: gnas nas log pa thim pa'i sgras //
NK028(sa)001:10481: mtha' gnyis ma gos pad+ma'i spyan //
NK028(sa)001:10482: sprul pa'i gnas nas skye ba yis //
NK028(sa)001:10483: bzhi bcu lnga sogs mtha' yas kun //
NK028(sa)001:10484: rang bzhin nyid las rang gsal bas //
NK028(sa)001:10485: bcu gsum yi ge 'khor lo brjod /
NK028(sa)001:10487: de dag gi cho ga'i las rim ni /
NK028(sa)001:10488: slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang ba'i dbang gi gal por gsungs pas 'dir ma bris so //
NK028(sa)001:10489: de dag ni gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gi las kyi rim pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:10490: gsang ba dang shes rab ye shes ni b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK028(sa)001:10491: dbyer med bde ba chen po ni sems kyi dkyil 'khor du bskur ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:10492: de yang gsang dbang thob nas /
NK028(sa)001:10493: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga la longs spyod pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:10494: steng sgo 'khor lo'i man ngag bsgom pa gsang dbang /
NK028(sa)001:10495: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob nas las kyi phyag rgya brten pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:10496: 'og sgo khams gsum bsrung 'khor gyi man ngag bsgom pa gsang /
NK028(sa)001:10497: dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang thob nas /
NK028(sa)001:10498: kun rdzob tu snod bcud sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK028(sa)001:10499: don dam dkor bdun ngo bo nyid kyi skur lhun gyis grub pa las ma g.yos par rtogs shing /
NK028(sa)001:10500: rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen po mngon du gyur pa'i don gsang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:10501: de yang thog ma gnyis ni /
NK028(sa)001:10503: dbang rdzas nyi zla byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK028(sa)001:10505: ba dang be'u bya dang byi'u /
NK028(sa)001:10506: bung ba dang me tog gi tshul dang //
NK028(sa)001:10507: nyams len ka ra ni'i bstan bcos brgyad dam /
NK028(sa)001:10508: drug bcu rtsa bzhi la sogs pa rnams ni /
NK028(sa)001:10509: 'jig rten pa rnams kyis bzhad gad kyis gnas su 'gyur ba'i phyir dang /
NK028(sa)001:10510: phyi ma blo chung ba rnams la rang gsang thabs kyis chod nas /
NK028(sa)001:10511: rang la gnas pa'i don de bstan kyang mi go /
NK028(sa)001:10513: yon tan brjod kyang brod pa'i blo mi skye pa'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:10514: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang zhes tha snyad du byas pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:10515: bdun pa dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni //
NK028(sa)001:10516: rtsa rgyud kyi le'u bcu pa las //
NK028(sa)001:10517: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK028(sa)001:10518: dbang rnams thob par ma byas na //
NK028(sa)001:10519: nyan pa la sogs brtsom pa rnams //
NK028(sa)001:10520: 'bras bu med cing brlag par gyur //
NK028(sa)001:10522: brgyad pa dbang thob pa'i phan yon ni /
NK028(sa)001:10524: dus 'di phan chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK028(sa)001:10525: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:10526: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:10527: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur /
NK028(sa)001:10529: gong gi gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum po de /
NK028(sa)001:10530: yo ga la sogs pa'i dbang drug po la dngos su mi bskur /
NK028(sa)001:10531: shugs la dod zur tsam bskur /
NK028(sa)001:10532: gong gi 'jug chog bco brgyad la dam tshig sbyin pa dam tshig 'bogs pa /
NK028(sa)001:10535: dam bsgrag pa bzhi ma gtogs pa'i bcu bzhi dang /
NK028(sa)001:10536: phyii phan pa'i dbang bcu la phyag rgya ma gtogs ba'i dgu dang /
NK028(sa)001:10537: nang nus pa'i dbang lnga po rnams yo ga la
NK028(sa)001:10538: sogs pa'i theg pa drug po kun la 'gres so
NK028(sa)001:10539: // bar skabs tshig kha bsgyur gong du bshad pa'i
NK028(sa)001:10540: dbang de rnams sgyu 'phrul gyi dbang dang mtshungs par
NK028(sa)001:10541: // snang snyam na / yo ga la sogs theg pa drug po'i dbang //
NK028(sa)001:10542: me long g.ya' dag pa dang 'dra ba la /
NK028(sa)001:10543: sgyu 'phrul gyis dang gzugs brnyan dang 'dra ba shar
NK028(sa)001:10544: ba yin pas 'gal ba med cing shin tu 'thad
NK028(sa)001:10545: do // lha mi'i dbang gi skabs 'dir //
NK028(sa)001:10546: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum gyi dod ni //
NK028(sa)001:10548: theg pa'i lam khyer lha mi'i theg pa //
NK028(sa)001:10549: lha lam khyer rnam par snang mdzad la sogs //
NK028(sa)001:10550: snying po lam khyer na mo b+ha ga wa ti sarba durga ti sogs /
NK028(sa)001:10552: gong du bshad pa'i gnas ni /
NK028(sa)001:10553: chu bo ne ran dza na'i 'gram du'o //
NK028(sa)001:10554: gang gis bshad pa'i ston pa ni sh+aakya thub pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:10555: gang la bshad pa'i 'khor ni byang chub sems dpa' don grub /
NK028(sa)001:10556: gang bshad pa'i theg pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:10557: lha mi'i theg pa'i dbang dgos pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:10558: 'jig rten pa'i bya ba la mkhas pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK028(sa)001:10560: gang gis gang la ci phyir gang dgos pa /
NK028(sa)001:10561: 'di ni lha mi theg pa'i 'gag drug yin /
NK028(sa)001:10564: dge bcu dag la gtsor byed pas /
NK028(sa)001:10569: rang gi spyi bor zla ba nya gang ba gcig bsgom /
NK028(sa)001:10570: de'i steng du sh+aakya thub pa 'du 'bral med par bsgom /
NK028(sa)001:10571: bya ba dang spyod pa ci byed kyang spyi bo'i sh+aakya thub pas bka' bsgo nas byed pas /
NK028(sa)001:10572: sh+aakya thub pa'i gsung las 'da' ba med pa ni mi dge ba'i sel med pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:10573: de nas ye shes ngang bsgom chung sngun gyis thad kar gzigs shig /
NK028(sa)001:10574: dbang don chen po skas gdang las lha mi'i theg pa'i skabs so //
NK028(sa)001:10575: 'di ni 'khrul snang btsad gcod nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud las gsungs so //
NK028(sa)001:10576: gsum pa rjes ni yon dang man+dala phul la /
NK028(sa)001:10579: tshogs dang dga' ston rgya chen po bya /
NK028(sa)001:10580: glu gar dang rtsed 'jo'i nyams bskyang /
NK028(sa)001:10588: dang po phyi dbang gi chu bo las /
NK028(sa)001:10589: nyan thos kyi dbang gi them skas bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:10590: gnyis pa nyan thos kyi dbang la gnyis ste //
NK028(sa)001:10591: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:10596: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:10597: rab gnas sbyin sregs dang zhes pas /
NK028(sa)001:10598: tshad dang ldan pa'i sa stegs la sa dri bzang chu yis chag chag gdab /
NK028(sa)001:10599: byin brlabs ldan pa'i thig skud kyis thig brgyad gong bzhin legs par gdab pa /
NK028(sa)001:10600: thig gi rgyal po 'khor lo la /
NK028(sa)001:10602: de nas cha phran gdab pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:10603: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma gdab /
NK028(sa)001:10604: gnyis pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab /
NK028(sa)001:10606: sgo sogs rta babs 'khor gdugs yin /
NK028(sa)001:10607: gsum pa bzhi pa dor bar bya /
NK028(sa)001:10609: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab /
NK028(sa)001:10612: bdun pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab /
