NK028(sa)001:10613: brgyad pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab /
NK028(sa)001:10614: dgu pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab /
NK028(sa)001:10615: bcu pa me ri dor bar bya /
NK028(sa)001:10616: de nas mu khyud bskor ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:10617: cha bran bzhi nas lte ba skor /
NK028(sa)001:10618: cha phran lnga nas mu khyud phyi /
NK028(sa)001:10619: cha bran dgu nas 'dab bzhi bskor //
NK028(sa)001:10620: bcu nas de yi mu khyud phyi //
NK028(sa)001:10621: bcu bzhir pad 'dab bcu drug bskor /
NK028(sa)001:10622: bco lnga de yi mu khyud phyi //
NK028(sa)001:10623: mda' g.yab tshangs thig phrag so nas //
NK028(sa)001:10624: g.yas g.yon phyogs su cha gnyis dor //
NK028(sa)001:10625: de nas spangs su cha gcig dor //
NK028(sa)001:10626: de nas cha phran gcig nas bskor //
NK028(sa)001:10627: mda' yab tshangs thig 'phrad so nas //
NK028(sa)001:10628: spangs su cha phran gnyis dor la //
NK028(sa)001:10629: gnyis nas bskor ba glang gur yin //
NK028(sa)001:10630: glang gur 'og ma bskor sa nas //
NK028(sa)001:10631: cha phran drug drug lan gsum bskor //
NK028(sa)001:10632: chu srin kha yi rdor rwa yin //
NK028(sa)001:10633: mda' yab zur thig phrad so nas /
NK028(sa)001:10634: pad 'dab rdo ra me ri la //
NK028(sa)001:10635: ci rigs mtshams pa bskor bar bya /
NK028(sa)001:10636: de nas tshon gyi rim pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:10637: dbus kyi lte ba gser po bya /
NK028(sa)001:10638: 'dab bzhi phyogs tshon mtshams bzhi mdzes //
NK028(sa)001:10639: bcu drug mdzes tshon mu khyud rnams //
NK028(sa)001:10640: ci ltar rigs pa bri bar bya //
NK028(sa)001:10641: sgo sogs phan chad spyi dang mthun //
NK028(sa)001:10642: de nas rnam pa dgod pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:10643: lha grangs mnyam pa'i tshom bu dang //
NK028(sa)001:10644: sku brten dbus su sh+aaka thub dang //
NK028(sa)001:10646: bcu drug 'dab la mchog bcu drug /
NK028(sa)001:10647: gsung rten rten la glegs bam bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:10648: thugs rten rdo rje dril bu dgod //
NK028(sa)001:10649: chad lhag bsal zhing zhal gsol mchod /
NK028(sa)001:10650: mchod yon la sogs phyi mchod dang /
NK028(sa)001:10651: gtor ma bshams pa la sogs dang /
NK028(sa)001:10652: bum sogs bshams pa gong dang mthun /
NK028(sa)001:10653: de ni bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:10654: de nas rab gnas kyi dod ni /
NK028(sa)001:10655: dpon slob rnams gdan la bzhugs shing /
NK028(sa)001:10656: sngon 'gro gtor ma cha bzhi'am cha gcig bshams la /
NK028(sa)001:10657: byin gyis brlabs la bsngo shing mtshams bcad pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:10658: mchod pas byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:10659: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed gong bzhin sngon du song nas /
NK028(sa)001:10661: swa wa b+ha stong pa'i ngang las /
NK028(sa)001:10662: b+h+rum las rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas gyi khang pa /
NK028(sa)001:10665: brgyan rta babs dang bcas pa'i dbus su /
NK028(sa)001:10666: pad+ma 'dab bzhi lte ba gser po shar gyi pad 'dab dkar po /
NK028(sa)001:10667: lho ser nub dmar byang ljang /
NK028(sa)001:10669: de'i phyi rol pad 'dab bcu drug gi phyogs bzhi
NK028(sa)001:10670: phyogs mdog mtshams bzhi rnams mdzes mtshon mu khyud mu
NK028(sa)001:10671: tig gi 'phreng bas bskor ba'i dbus su pad+ma dang
NK028(sa)001:10672: zla ba'i gdan la bdag gi bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya
NK028(sa)001:10673: thub pa sku mdog ser po /
NK028(sa)001:10674: g.yas sa gnon g.yon mnyam mazhaga /
NK028(sa)001:10676: chos gos ngur smrig sku la gsol ba /
NK028(sa)001:10677: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK028(sa)001:10678: dpe byas bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan par bsgoms /
NK028(sa)001:10679: bden pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i shar gyi pad 'dab la dge slong pho //
NK028(sa)001:10680: lho'i pad 'dab la dge slong mo //
NK028(sa)001:10681: nub kyi pad 'dab la dge tshul pho //
NK028(sa)001:10682: byang gi pad 'dab la dge tshul mo //
NK028(sa)001:10683: chos gos dang sham thabs can //
NK028(sa)001:10684: lhung bzed dang mkhar sil 'dzin pa //
NK028(sa)001:10685: zhabs dge sbyong gi bzhugs stangs so //
NK028(sa)001:10686: de'i phyi rol du pad 'dab bcu drug gi /
NK028(sa)001:10688: shar nas rim pa bzhin du /
NK028(sa)001:10713: kun dga' bo bsil yab 'dzin pa bzhi /
NK028(sa)001:10716: rin po che'i rkyal bu 'dzin gang po rin po che'i 'bar 'dzin 'od bsil yab 'dzin /
NK028(sa)001:10719: thams cad kyang sku mdog sna tshogs pa yang /
NK028(sa)001:10720: phyag na po ti dang lhung bzed dang mkhar sil 'dzin pa chos gos ngur smrig gyon pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:10721: lha tshogs de rnams la rang bzhin gyi gnas nas /
NK028(sa)001:10722: ye shes pa snyan gsan dbab /
NK028(sa)001:10725: mchod pa 'bul ba rnams ci rigs pa bya /
NK028(sa)001:10727: thabs mkhas thugs rje sh+aakya'i rigs 'khrungs shing /
NK028(sa)001:10729: sdug bsngal bden pa nyer len phung po dang //
NK028(sa)001:10730: kun 'byung bden pa las dang nyon mongs dang //
NK028(sa)001:10731: 'gog pa'i bden pa sdug bsngal zhi ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:10732: lam gyi bden pa gang zag bdag med la //
NK028(sa)001:10733: 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras spangs shing 'das pa bsgrub pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:10734: dge slong pho mo'i dge tshul pho mo la //
NK028(sa)001:10735: phyag 'tshal mchod 'bul gus pas bstod par bgyi //
NK028(sa)001:10736: ston pa'i rtags 'chang nyan thos tshul //
NK028(sa)001:10737: lhung bzed mkha' sil po ti bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:10738: bslabs sbyangs yon tan kun ldan pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:10739: nyan thos rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK028(sa)001:10740: bsnyen pa ni mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:10741: zhes ci rigs par bsnyen no //
NK028(sa)001:10743: swa b+h+aa wa bi stong pa'i ngang las /
NK028(sa)001:10744: b+h+rum las rin po che'i bum pa mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i nang du /
NK028(sa)001:10745: rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas
NK028(sa)001:10746: khang pa la sogs bdag bskyed ltar bsnyen pa yan
NK028(sa)001:10747: chad la bar skabs kyi 'don pa bsgyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:10749: swa b+ha wa stong pa'i ngang las b+h+rum las rin
NK028(sa)001:10750: po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang
NK028(sa)001:10751: pa sogs bdag bskyed ltar bsnyen pa yan chad la
NK028(sa)001:10752: bar skabs kyi 'don pa kha bsgyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:10754: bum pa dang dkyil 'khor la sogs la rab gnas byed /
NK028(sa)001:10755: grub na sbyin bsreg kyang ci rigs par bya'o /
NK028(sa)001:10756: gnyis pa 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa la gnyis ste /
NK028(sa)001:10757: slob dpon bdag nyid 'jug cing dbang len pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:10758: slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:10760: dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa dang dbang len pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:10764: dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod gsol dang /
NK028(sa)001:10766: 'jug pa dang bzod par gsol pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:10769: rgyas par 'jug tshul gong dang mthun no /
NK028(sa)001:10770: gnyis pa slob ma 'jug par gsol ba gdab pa ni gong dang mthun no //
NK028(sa)001:10771: gnyis pa dbang len pa ni gong dang mthun no /
NK028(sa)001:10772: gnyis pa slob ma 'jug cing dbang bskur ba la gnyis te /
NK028(sa)001:10773: dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba'o /
NK028(sa)001:10778: khrus dgab dri dang lus 'bul dang /
NK028(sa)001:10779: bgegs bskrad lhar brlabs dam tshig sbyin /
NK028(sa)001:10780: de nyid dbab dang chu nan dang /
NK028(sa)001:10781: bsgrag dang rin chen dor ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:10782: lha dbab pa dang nan tan dang /
NK028(sa)001:10783: mig dbye dkyil 'khor bstan pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:10784: tshogs mchod yon dang zhes pas /
NK028(sa)001:10788: ci la dga' dri ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:10789: dus gsum gyis sangs rgyas la lus 'bul ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:10792: drug pa gong dang mtshungs la //
NK028(sa)001:10798: dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa dbog pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:10799: dge tshul gyi sdom pa dbog pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:10800: dge slong gi sdom pa dbog pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:10801: thams cad mkhyen pa la phyag 'tshal lo /
NK028(sa)001:10803: bla ma rnams la gus btud de //
NK028(sa)001:10804: las kyi cho ga bsal byed pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:10805: gdam ngag cung zad dgod bar bya /
NK028(sa)001:10807: khyed rang rnams rtsog rtsog por sdod cig /
NK028(sa)001:10808: khyed rnams sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la 'jug par
NK028(sa)001:10809: 'dod pa la 'gal rkyen bar chad med pa cig
NK028(sa)001:10810: dgos / bar chad yod dam med dris pas shes //
NK028(sa)001:10811: dri rgyu 'ga' zhig yod yin pa la yin //
NK028(sa)001:10812: ma yin pa la ma yin zhes lan thob cig /
NK028(sa)001:10813: khyod mu stegs can ma yin nam //
NK028(sa)001:10814: lo bco lnga ma lon pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10815: lo bco lnga lon pa bya rog bskrod mi nus pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10816: bya rog bskrod nus pa lo bdun ma lon pa ma yin nam //
NK028(sa)001:10817: bran la sogs pa ma yin nam //
NK028(sa)001:10818: bu lon chags pa ma yin nam //
NK028(sa)001:10819: pha mas ma gnang ba ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10820: pha mas ma gnang ba yul thag mi ring ba ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10822: dge slong ma sun phyung ba ma yin nam //
NK028(sa)001:10823: rku thabs su gnas pa ma yin nam //
NK028(sa)001:10824: tha dad du gnas pa ma yin nam //
NK028(sa)001:10825: gnas par mi bya ba ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10830: mu stegs can zhugs pa ma yin nam //
NK028(sa)001:10831: ma bsad pa ma yin nam //
NK028(sa)001:10832: pha gsad pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10833: dgra bcom pa bsad pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10834: dge 'dun gyi dbyen byas pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10835: de bzhin gshegs pa la ngan sems kyi khrag phyung ba ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10836: pham par gyur pa'i ltung ba bzhi po dag las
NK028(sa)001:10837: ltung ba gang yang rung ba byung ba ma yin
NK028(sa)001:10838: nam / rgyu las bzlog pa'i chad pa khas mi lan pa gnas nas phyung ba ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10839: lag brdum la sogs ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10840: skra ser la sogs pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10841: sen mo cig pa la sogs pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10842: rgyal pos bkrabs pa la sogs pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10843: rgyal pos ma gnang ba ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10844: rgyal po ma gnang ba yul thag mi ring ba ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10845: chom rkun bar grags pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10846: phung khrol ba ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10850: mi ma yin ba'i 'gro ba ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10851: byang sgra mi snyan pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10852: mtshan lan gsum du gyur pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10853: skyes pa 'dra ba'i bud med ma ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10854: sdig sdig lta bu'i mtshan nyid can ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10855: gling gzhan nas skyes pa'i tshul byad mi 'dra ba ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:10857: ma yin zer na khyod sdom pa skye ba'i snod du rung bar 'dug pas /
NK028(sa)001:10859: nged la yang phyag gsum 'tshol bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:10860: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:10861: ri bo la babs kyi 'dzegs pa dang 'dra bas
NK028(sa)001:10862: rim pa nas slob dgos snga ma bsrung mi nus
NK028(sa)001:10863: pa la / phyi ma bstan kyang /
NK028(sa)001:10864: gang ma yog pa la do sbyin pa dang 'dra bas /
NK028(sa)001:10865: thog ma nyid du dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa ster bar byed /
NK028(sa)001:10866: 'di yang 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs bsams pas 'khor ba las yid dbyung /
NK028(sa)001:10867: thar pa'i phan yon bsams pas mya ngan las 'das
NK028(sa)001:10868: pa 'dod dungs pa gcig la brten nas skye bas
NK028(sa)001:10869: / 'khor ba 'di gang du skyes kyang bde ba med /
NK028(sa)001:10870: sdug bsngal las thar ba sangs rgyas yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:10871: sems can thams cad kyi don du /
NK028(sa)001:10872: sangs rgyas thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:10873: dge bsnyen kyi sdom pa blang snyam pa cig dgos /
NK028(sa)001:10874: dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa de yang skyabs su 'gro ba la brten nas skye ba yin te /
NK028(sa)001:10875: slob dpon zla ba grags pa'i zhal nas /
NK028(sa)001:10876: gang zhig gsum la skyabs 'gro ba /
NK028(sa)001:10877: de ni sdom brgyad rtsa ba yin zhes gsungs pa yin /
NK028(sa)001:10878: sangs rgyas lam la bsgrub pa'i ded dpon /
NK028(sa)001:10880: dge 'dun lam bsgrub pa'i zla grogs su gzung nas /
NK028(sa)001:10881: dkon mchog gsum la blo bkal /
NK028(sa)001:10882: skyabs 'gros thog grangs pa'i khas len lan gsum byas pas /
NK028(sa)001:10883: sdom pa skye ba yin pas rjes zlos gyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:10885: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas gzung ste /
NK028(sa)001:10888: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK028(sa)001:10889: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK028(sa)001:10893: bdag ji srid 'tsho'i bar du dge bsnyen du btsun pas gzung du gsol lo //
NK028(sa)001:10895: tshig gsum pa la slob dpon gyis shes bye brag tu brjod bar bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:10896: de'i rjes la khyod kyis dge bsnyen sdom pa thob pa yin /
NK028(sa)001:10897: slob dpon gyis thob pa yin no dang /
NK028(sa)001:10898: dge bsnyen kyis legs so zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:10899: de'i rjes la khyod kyis dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa thob pa yin /
NK028(sa)001:10900: thob pa tsam gyis mi chog bsrungs dgos /
NK028(sa)001:10901: bsrung bya shes pa'i phyir bslab bya brjod pa yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:10902: sngon 'phags pa dgra bcom pa rnams kyis ji ltar
NK028(sa)001:10903: bsrungs pa bzhin du bdag gis kyang bsrungs snyam pa
NK028(sa)001:10904: bgyis la nga'i rjes zlos gyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:10906: ji ltar 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gis
NK028(sa)001:10907: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du srog gcod pa spangs te
NK028(sa)001:10908: / srog gcod pa las slar log pa de bzhin du /
NK028(sa)001:10909: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang /
NK028(sa)001:10911: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du srog gcod pa spangs ste /
NK028(sa)001:10912: srog gcod pa las slar log par bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:10913: yan lag dang po 'dis bdag 'phags pa dgra bcom
NK028(sa)001:10914: pa de dag gi slob pa la rjes su slob
NK028(sa)001:10917: gzhan yang ji ltar 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gis /
NK028(sa)001:10919: ma byin pa len pa nga da /
NK028(sa)001:10920: 'dod pa log par g.yem pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:10925: bag med pa'i gnas spangs ste /
NK028(sa)001:10928: bag med pa'i gnas las slar log pa de bzhin du /
NK028(sa)001:10929: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang dus 'di nas gzung ste /
NK028(sa)001:10931: ma byin bar len pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:10932: 'dod pas log par g.yem pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:10937: bag med pa'i gnas spangs te /
NK028(sa)001:10938: bag med pa'i gnas las slar log par bagyi'o /
NK028(sa)001:10939: yan lag lnga pa 'dis bdag 'phags pa dgra bcom pa /
NK028(sa)001:10940: de dag gi slab pa la rjes su bslab po /
NK028(sa)001:10943: slob dpon gyis thabs yin no //
NK028(sa)001:10944: dge bsnyen gyi legs so zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:10945: de ni dge bsnyen gyi cho ga 'o //
NK028(sa)001:10946: de nas mkhan pos dge slong grogs dan byed pa cig la /
NK028(sa)001:10948: tshe dang ldan pa 'di rab tu 'byin ba'i dge 'dun la zhu ba phul ci bya /
NK028(sa)001:10949: dge slong des tshe dang ldan pa 'di'i bar chad dag par gda' 'am 'dri /
NK028(sa)001:10950: bar chad dag par gad'i zer na /
NK028(sa)001:10951: dge 'dun la phyag gsum 'tshal du bcug la /
NK028(sa)001:10952: bsgrub bya'i rgyab du phyin la 'greng ste 'dud ba dang bcas pas /
NK028(sa)001:10953: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams dgongs su gsol /
NK028(sa)001:10954: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyis ba la mkhan po 'di zhes bgyi ba /
NK028(sa)001:10956: khyim pa gos dkar po can skra dang kha spu ma bregs pa las /
NK028(sa)001:10957: legs par gsungs pa'i chos 'dul ba la rab tu 'byung bar 'tshal te /
NK028(sa)001:10958: ming 'di zhes bgyi ba ni rab tu /
NK028(sa)001:10959: 'byung bar 'tshal zhing skra dang kha spu bregs nas gos ngur smrig dag bgos te /
NK028(sa)001:10960: yang dag pa kho nar dad pas khyim nas khyim med par /
NK028(sa)001:10961: mkhan po ming 'di zhes bgyi ba la rab tu 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:10962: de yang bar chad kyi chos rnams yongs su dag go /
NK028(sa)001:10965: dge 'du thams cad kyis gal te yongs su dag na 'o zhes brjod do //
NK028(sa)001:10966: de ni rab tu byung ba zhu ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:10967: de'i rjes la mkhan po la phyag du bzhugs la /
NK028(sa)001:10968: mkhan pos khyodaraba tu 'byung bar byed pa la rang zhugs byas pas mi chog /
NK028(sa)001:10969: rab tu 'byung bar byed pa la mkhan po gcig dgos /
NK028(sa)001:10975: zhes pa'i rkyen gsum byin pas /
NK028(sa)001:10976: u ba d+ha ya bya ba /
NK028(sa)001:10979: mkhan po bya ba yin pas gang zag 'di bdag la blo gtod par 'dug pas /
NK028(sa)001:10980: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas la dgod par bya'o /
NK028(sa)001:10981: snyam pa'i thugs rjes 'dzin par zhu ba yin /
NK028(sa)001:10984: nye bar sbyor ba'i don gyis mkhan po bya ba yin /
NK028(sa)001:10985: sngar sdom pa dang mi ldan pa las sdom pa
NK028(sa)001:10986: rim pa bzhin 'bogs par zhu zhes gsol ba 'debs
NK028(sa)001:10987: pa yin / u pa ha ra na zhes pa
NK028(sa)001:10988: 'di nye bar lung 'bogs pa'i don gyis mkhan po
NK028(sa)001:10990: sdom pa thob pa'i rjes la dgag bsgrub snang gsum
NK028(sa)001:10991: gyis sa mtshams mi shes pas thams cad bslab par
NK028(sa)001:10992: zhu zhes gsol ba 'debs pa yin yang rnam pa
NK028(sa)001:10993: bcu gcig tu na srid pa don du gnyer ba'i
NK028(sa)001:10994: yid / phrag dog nas thar pa 'dod pa la
NK028(sa)001:10995: blo khrid pas na mkhan po bya ba yin gsung
NK028(sa)001:10996: yid / / sngar dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa 'bogs pa'i slob dpon la yin mod kyis /
NK028(sa)001:10997: da rab tu byung pa'i mkhan po zhu bar gsol ba gdab snyam du bsoms la /
NK028(sa)001:11001: slob dpon la mkhan por gsol gyis slob dpon bgyis bdag gi mkhan po mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11002: slob dpon mkhan pos bdag tu dbyung bar bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:11003: de bzhin du lan gnyis lan gsum du bzlas /
NK028(sa)001:11004: tshig gsum pa la mkhan po mkhan pos bdag rab tu dbyung ba bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:11006: mkhan pos thabs yin no zhes pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:11007: rten gyis legs so zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11008: de ni mkhan por gsol ba gdab pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:11009: de'i rjes la grogs byed pa des gtsug phud 'breg pa la spro ba /
NK028(sa)001:11010: dris la spro na breg par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11012: de nas mkhan pos gos ngur smrig sbyin par bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:11013: dang po mkhan po'i zhabs la spyi bos gtugs pa'i phyag gsum 'tshal du bcug nas mdun du bzhag /
NK028(sa)001:11014: bla gos lag tu gtad la /
NK028(sa)001:11015: 'di stod du rgyun du gyon pa'i chos gos bla
NK028(sa)001:11016: gos bya ba khyim pa dang mu stegs can las
NK028(sa)001:11017: brtags bsrungs / stod gcer pa mngon pa rlung nyi ma'i tsha grang mi bzod pa las skyobs /
NK028(sa)001:11018: dge sbyong gi dran pa gso bar byed pa'i stod g.yogs su sangs rgyas kyis gnang bas /
NK028(sa)001:11019: khyod kyis kyang gos 'di lta bu cig brten nas
NK028(sa)001:11020: sangs rgyas thob par byed dgos pas tshags gyis shig
NK028(sa)001:11021: / de nas mthong gos gtad la 'di smad du
NK028(sa)001:11022: gyon pa'i chos gos mthong gos bya ba smad gcer
NK028(sa)001:11023: bur mngon pa dang ngo tsha ba'i gnas las skyobs
NK028(sa)001:11024: / / khyim pa dang mu stegs can las rtags bsrungs /
NK028(sa)001:11025: dge sbyong gi dran pa gso bar byed pa'i chos gos smad g.yogs su sangs rgyas kyis gnang /
NK028(sa)001:11026: khyed kyis kyang gos 'di lta bu gcig la brten
NK028(sa)001:11027: nas sangs rgyas thob par byed dgos bas gos 'di
NK028(sa)001:11028: tshags gyis shig / de nas yang lhung bzed gtad la /
NK028(sa)001:11029: 'di lhung bzed bya ba bsod snyoms la 'gro tsa na /
NK028(sa)001:11030: khyim pa'i kham phor mu stegs kyi slong phor dang
NK028(sa)001:11031: mi nor bar bya ba'i ched du gnod brgyad kyis
NK028(sa)001:11032: rtags bsrungs byed du sangs rgyas kyi snang bas 'di
NK028(sa)001:11033: zas kyi 'gengs par byed pa bzhin du /
NK028(sa)001:11034: rang nyid yon tan gyis phyug bar byed dgos pa'i
NK028(sa)001:11035: rtags bud+hasa gnang bas lhung bzed cig kyang tshags gyis
NK028(sa)001:11036: shig / de nas 'ding ba gtad la /
NK028(sa)001:11037: 'di gding ba bya ba khyim pa'i dkar po gang zag gi khra bo //
NK028(sa)001:11038: dge 'dun gyi gnas mal la longs sbyod pa na /
NK028(sa)001:11039: 'dings pa'i gding ba cig kyang tshags gyis shig bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11040: 'di chu tshags bya ba chu srog chags dgos pa byung na 'dis tshogs la longs spyod cig /
NK028(sa)001:11041: de nas mkhan pos gos bgon par thar pa'i rgyal mtshan brtan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:11042: tshangs par spyod pa'i tshe yi mthar thug par spyod par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:11043: ngo tsha dang khrel yod kyis gos gyon par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:11045: de'i skabs su mtshan ma tshor bar brtags par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11046: de'i rjes la rab tu byung ba nye bar bsgrubs pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:11048: dang po ston pa sangs rgyas la phyag 'tshal du bcug /
NK028(sa)001:11049: de nas rang la phyag 'tshal du bcug la /
NK028(sa)001:11050: mkhan pos 'di skad brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11051: khyed rab tu byung bar bya snyam pa de legs par ces shes zhes na /
NK028(sa)001:11052: khyim na gnas pa sdug bsngal mang /
NK028(sa)001:11053: yod pa 'tsho skyong gi sdug bsngal /
NK028(sa)001:11054: med pa btsal gyis mi rnyed pa'i sdug bsngal yod /
NK028(sa)001:11055: dga' bo rab tu byung ba'i mdo las kyang /
NK028(sa)001:11056: khyim pa rnams ni me bos na /
NK028(sa)001:11058: mi gtsang pa'i 'dam rdzab tu phyin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:11059: khri mun du chud pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:11060: lcags sgrog gis bcings pa dang 'dra bar gsungs /
NK028(sa)001:11061: rab tu byung ba rnams ni bsil khang dang /
NK028(sa)001:11062: gtsang pa dang bde par rang dbang thob pa dang 'dra bar gsungs /
NK028(sa)001:11063: gzhan yang dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad rab
NK028(sa)001:11064: tu byung ba la brten nas sangs rgyas par gsungs
NK028(sa)001:11065: te / de ltar yang zla ba sgron me las /
NK028(sa)001:11066: gang dag khyim na gnas par byed bzhin du /
NK028(sa)001:11067: byang chub dam pa mchog 'di thob pa yi /
NK028(sa)001:11068: sangs rgyas sngon chad gang yang ma byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:11069: phyin chad na yang mi 'byung gnas pa med /
NK028(sa)001:11071: 'phags pa nyan rang gi yon tan thams cad kyang
NK028(sa)001:11072: rab tu byung ba la brten nas thob pas na
NK028(sa)001:11073: blo na skye lugs legs pa cig skyes pa yin
NK028(sa)001:11074: pas na / skabs 'dir ming cha lugs bsam pa lha dang gzhi spo ba yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:11075: de yang khyim pa'i ming bzhag nas /
NK028(sa)001:11077: khyim pa'i cha lugs bzhag nas /
NK028(sa)001:11080: gos ngur smrig gyon pa rtags so //
NK028(sa)001:11081: tshe 'di don du gnyer ba'i blo de btang nas
NK028(sa)001:11082: phyi ma don du gnyer dgos pas bsam pa spo
NK028(sa)001:11083: / sngar gyi 'jig rten gyi pho lha la sogs spangs ste /
NK028(sa)001:11084: dkon mchog gsum la lhar 'dzin pas spo /
NK028(sa)001:11085: 'o na de ltar spos nas gang gi rjes su rab tu 'byung na /
NK028(sa)001:11089: de rnams mtshan gyi rnam grangs yin /
NK028(sa)001:11090: sh+aakya thub pa kho na'i rjes su rab tu 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:11091: 'byung lugs khyim pa'i rtags cha lugs la sogs pa spangs /
NK028(sa)001:11092: rab tu byung ba'i cha lugs su bsgyur nas skyabs
NK028(sa)001:11093: 'gros thog grangs pa'i khas len lan gsum byas pas
NK028(sa)001:11094: / sdom pa skye ba yin pas nga'i rjes su lad mo gyis shig mkhan po dgongs su gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11095: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas gzung ste /
NK028(sa)001:11098: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK028(sa)001:11099: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK028(sa)001:11103: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa
NK028(sa)001:11104: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa
NK028(sa)001:11107: gtso bo de sa rab tu byung ba'i rjes su bdag rab tu 'byung ste /
NK028(sa)001:11109: rab tu byung pa'i rtags yang dag par rab tu len to //
NK028(sa)001:11110: zhes de bzhin du lan gnyis lan gsum du bzlas /
NK028(sa)001:11111: mkhan pos thabs yin no dang /
NK028(sa)001:11114: de ni mkhan po la rab tu byung pa'i cho ga'o //
NK028(sa)001:11115: de'i rjes la mkhan po des /
NK028(sa)001:11118: tshe dang ldan pa 'di bar chad med par gada'am dri /
NK028(sa)001:11119: mkhan pos bar chad dag par gda' zer na /
NK028(sa)001:11120: slob dpon gyi khyod dge tshul gyis sdom pa la
NK028(sa)001:11121: 'gal rkyen bar chad spangs shing mthun rkyen tshang ba
NK028(sa)001:11122: zhig dgos / bar chad mkhan pos dris /
NK028(sa)001:11123: khyed rang gis med par lan gdab pas bar chad med pa yin /
NK028(sa)001:11124: des kyang mi chog mthun pa'i rkyen lnga tshang ba
NK028(sa)001:11125: gcig dgos de la yul mthun pa'i rkyen bstan pa
NK028(sa)001:11126: 'di'i bdag po sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa yin pas
NK028(sa)001:11127: de'i sku rab tu gnas pa dang ldan pa gcig
NK028(sa)001:11128: spangs po'i tshul du dgos na /
NK028(sa)001:11129: sangs rgyas dngos dang khyad par med par bzhugs pa yin /
NK028(sa)001:11130: chos la lung dang rtogs pa'i chos gnyis las lung
NK028(sa)001:11131: gi chos la gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis kyi
NK028(sa)001:11132: rten du gyur pa spo ti dang glegs bam bzhugs
NK028(sa)001:11133: / rtogs pa'i chos mkhan po slob dpon sam g+ha
NK028(sa)001:11134: dang bcas pa'i chos rgyud la ci rigs su bzhugs
NK028(sa)001:11135: / / dge tshul gyi sdom pa mkhan slob la brten nas skye yang /
NK028(sa)001:11136: ngo tsha khrel yod skye ba'i rten du dad pa'i dge 'dun yang bzhugs /
NK028(sa)001:11137: mkhan po btsun pa bstan pa'i yan lag tu bsnyen
NK028(sa)001:11138: par rdzogs nas lo bcu bar ma chad bar bslabs
NK028(sa)001:11139: shing / mkhas shing phan thogs kyi yan lag tu lnga tshan nyi shu rtsa gcig las /
NK028(sa)001:11140: gang yang rung ba dang ldan pa gcig dgos na tshangs /
NK028(sa)001:11141: slob dpon dge slong gi sdom pa rnam dag dang
NK028(sa)001:11142: ldan pa dge tshul gyi cho ga brda sprod pa
NK028(sa)001:11143: la mkhas pa gcig dgos na tshangs /
NK028(sa)001:11144: gnyis pa rtags mthun pa'i rkyen la /
NK028(sa)001:11146: skra dang kha sbu breg shing khrus byas pa gcig dgos na tshangs /
NK028(sa)001:11147: gos kyi rtags bla gos thang gos 'ding ba chu
NK028(sa)001:11148: tshags dang bcas pa mkhan pos gsung gis gnang ba
NK028(sa)001:11149: dang bcas pa dgos na tshang /
NK028(sa)001:11150: gsum pa rgyud snod du rung ba mthun pa'i rkyen
NK028(sa)001:11151: la byang sgra mi snyan pa la sdom pa mi
NK028(sa)001:11152: skye bas gling gsum du skyes pa gcig dgos ste
NK028(sa)001:11154: ma ning bcu bzhi la sdom pa mi skye /
NK028(sa)001:11155: bud med kyi cho ga'i skabs ma yin pas skyes pa'i dbang po dang ldan pa dgos na tshang /
NK028(sa)001:11156: dngos po'am nad pa'i sgo nas lus nar son pa dgos /
NK028(sa)001:11157: dngos po nar son pa skyes nas lo bdun lon pa /
NK028(sa)001:11158: bsams pa nar son pa dge tshul gyi spangs bya spongs /
NK028(sa)001:11159: gnyen po brten pa'i mthu dang ldan pa ci dgos na tshangs /
NK028(sa)001:11160: skyabs 'gro thun mong pas thog drangs dge bsnyen rab
NK028(sa)001:11161: tu byung ba bar ma gsum dang bcas pa ci
NK028(sa)001:11162: dgos na tshangs / bzhi pa bsam pa mthun pa'i rkyen la blang bya /
NK028(sa)001:11163: nges par 'byung ba'i tshul khrims yin pas de thob par byed pa la /
NK028(sa)001:11164: mya ngan las 'das pa'i bsam pa brtan po dang ldan pa gcig /
NK028(sa)001:11165: bsam pa thag pa nas len par 'dod pa dang gnyis /
NK028(sa)001:11166: dngos gzhi'i dus na thob par shes pa'i nus pa dang ldan pa dang gsum /
NK028(sa)001:11167: nges pa lnga dang bral ba bzhi dang ldan dgos /
NK028(sa)001:11168: de la dang po mya ngan dang /
NK028(sa)001:11170: mya ngan 'khor ba'i ming gi rnam grangs yin /
NK028(sa)001:11171: 'khor ba gang du skyes kyang bde ba med /
NK028(sa)001:11172: dmyal ba la tsha grang gi sdug bsngal /
NK028(sa)001:11173: yi dwags la bkres skom gyi sdug bsngal /
NK028(sa)001:11174: dud 'gro rnams la bkol spyod dang gcig la gcig za ba'i sdug bsngal /
NK028(sa)001:11175: lha ma yin rnams la 'thab cing rtsod ba'i sdug bsngal /
NK028(sa)001:11176: lha rnams la ltung ba dang 'chi bltas kyi sdug bsngal /
NK028(sa)001:11177: mi rnams la skye rga na 'chi sdug bsngal la sogs dpag tu med pa yod /
NK028(sa)001:11178: sdug bsngal de rnams las thar nas /
NK028(sa)001:11179: gtan gyi bde ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par byed dgos /
NK028(sa)001:11180: de yang rang gcig pus thob pas mi chog 'khor
NK028(sa)001:11181: ba na gnas pa'i sems can 'di rnams thams cad
NK028(sa)001:11182: sangs rgyas kyi sa la dgod dgos /
NK028(sa)001:11183: bud+d+ha de yang rgyu med pa las mi 'byung /
NK028(sa)001:11184: rgyu nor sa dang ma tshang pa las mi 'byung
NK028(sa)001:11185: rgyu tshang la ma nor ba lam bslab pa gsum
NK028(sa)001:11186: yin / de ltar yang khrims ni rgyu dang mi rgyu kun gyis sa bzhin du //
NK028(sa)001:11187: yon tan kun gyi gzhi brten legs par thub pas gsungs /
NK028(sa)001:11188: zhes gsungs pas des na sems can gyi bud+d+ha thob par bya /
NK028(sa)001:11190: dge tshul gyi sdom pa blangs la ma shi'i bar
NK028(sa)001:11191: du bsrungs snyam pa gcig la mya ngan las 'das
NK028(sa)001:11192: pa thob par 'dod pa'i bsam pa brtan po zer
NK028(sa)001:11193: ba yin pas sngar nas de bzhin yod nas yod
NK028(sa)001:11194: / med na de bzhin skye dgos pa yin //
NK028(sa)001:11195: ku re dang bzhad gad la sdom pa mi skye bas //
NK028(sa)001:11196: bsam pa thag pas len 'dod pa gcig dgos te tshang /
NK028(sa)001:11197: dngos gzhi'i dus na thob par shes pa'i nus ldan ni /
NK028(sa)001:11198: cho ga brjod pa gsum gyi tha ma la skyes par shes pa la zer te tshang /
NK028(sa)001:11199: nges pa lnga dang bral ba cig dgos /
NK028(sa)001:11201: yul nges pa tshe nges pa /
NK028(sa)001:11204: yan lag nges pa dang lnga yin /
NK028(sa)001:11205: de rnams bsdu bar song na dus da nas ma shi 'i bar du /
NK028(sa)001:11206: dge tshul la mi rung pa thams cad spangs /
NK028(sa)001:11207: rung ba thams cad bsgrub snyam pa gcig la /
NK028(sa)001:11208: nges pa lnga bral tshang ba yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:11209: bsam pa de bzhin mdzod cig /
NK028(sa)001:11210: lnga pa cho ga mthun pa'i rkyen la sbyor dngos rjes gsum las /
NK028(sa)001:11212: dngos gzhi skyabs su 'gro ba la rten nas skye ba yin te /
NK028(sa)001:11213: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun gsum /
NK028(sa)001:11214: thar pa 'dod pa rnams kyi skyabs /
NK028(sa)001:11215: skyabs de dag la brten nas ni /
NK028(sa)001:11216: sdug bsngal kun las grol bar 'gyur /
NK028(sa)001:11218: dkon mchog la blo bkal nas skyabs 'gros thog grangs
NK028(sa)001:11219: ba'i khas len lan gsum byas pas sdom pa skye
NK028(sa)001:11220: ba yin pas / nga'i rjes su lad mo gyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:11222: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas gzung ste /
NK028(sa)001:11223: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du rkang gnyis rnams kyi mchog /
NK028(sa)001:11224: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK028(sa)001:11225: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK028(sa)001:11229: bdag ji srid 'tsho'i bar du dge tshul du btsun pas gzung du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11230: de bzhin du lan gnyis lan gsum du bzlas /
NK028(sa)001:11231: tshig gsum pa slob dpon gyis rjes brjod par bya'o /
NK028(sa)001:11232: slob dpon gyis thabs yin no //
NK028(sa)001:11233: dge tshul gyis legs so zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11234: des khyod kyi rgyud la dge tshul gyi sdom pa skyes pa yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:11235: da 'jug gi cho ga la thob pa'i /
NK028(sa)001:11237: slob pa brjod pa gnyis su yod //
NK028(sa)001:11238: dus sgo'i dbang du byas na //
NK028(sa)001:11239: mdo nas phra ba'i rim pa nas gsungs kyang //
NK028(sa)001:11240: khyod kyi rgyud la bde bar bya ba'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:11241: rags ba'i rim pa nas brjod na //
NK028(sa)001:11242: dus rtsis kyi phyi mo lo yin //
NK028(sa)001:11244: dus tshigs bzhi'i dbang du byas pa'i dgun gyi dus
NK028(sa)001:11245: zla ba ngos 'dzin dgun zla ra ba'i yar ngo'i
NK028(sa)001:11246: tshes gcig gi nyin mo thun snga dro'i dus skyes
NK028(sa)001:11247: bu gnyis dang / rkang pa gcig la khyod kyi rgyud la sdom pa thob pa yin /
NK028(sa)001:11248: de yan chad du sdom pa blangs pa rnams khyod
NK028(sa)001:11249: pas rgan pas phyag dang bsnyen bskur yar la stobs
NK028(sa)001:11250: / gral gong du bzhugs su chug /
NK028(sa)001:11251: da phyis sdom pa len pa rnams khyod pas slob pa /
NK028(sa)001:11252: gzhon pas gral 'og du bzhag pas chog /
NK028(sa)001:11253: phyag dang bsnyen bskur stobs pa byung na dang du long /
NK028(sa)001:11254: rang dang mnyam pa su snga ba gong du bzhag pas chog /
NK028(sa)001:11255: de ltar byas pas dgos pa rang bzhin kyi bslab pa la gus pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:11256: dge 'dun tshogs pa byed ba'i dus su gral la da long du mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:11257: 'jig rten pa'i chos dge ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:11258: mthun pa la sogs ba'i dgos pa yod pas de yang lag len la thob cig /
NK028(sa)001:11259: de'i rjes la slob dpon des 'jug gis cho ga
NK028(sa)001:11260: la gnyis yod pa'i de gcig yin gnyis pa sdom
NK028(sa)001:11261: pa thob pas mi chog bsrungs dgos /
NK028(sa)001:11263: bsrungs bya shes par bya ba'i phyir bslabs pa brjod pa yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:11264: sngon 'phags pa dgra bcom pa rnams kyis ji ltar khas blangs shing bsrung ba bzhin du /
NK028(sa)001:11265: bdag gis kyang khas blangs la bsrung snyams pa gyis la lad mo gyis shig byas la /
NK028(sa)001:11267: ji ltar 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gis
NK028(sa)001:11268: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du srog gcod pa spangs te
NK028(sa)001:11269: / srog gcod pa las slar log pa de bzhin
NK028(sa)001:11270: du bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang dus 'di
NK028(sa)001:11271: / nas gzung ste / ji srid 'tsho'i bar du /
NK028(sa)001:11273: srog gcod pa las slar log par bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:11274: yan lag dang po 'dis bdag 'phags pa dgra bcom
NK028(sa)001:11275: pa de dag gi bslab pa la rjes su slob
NK028(sa)001:11277: gzhan yang 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gi bslab pa la rjes su slob po /
NK028(sa)001:11280: gzhan yang ji ltar 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de
NK028(sa)001:11281: dag gis ji srid 'tsho'i bar du ma byin par
NK028(sa)001:11282: len pa dang / mi tshangs par spyod pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:11292: rgyan dang kha dog 'chang ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:11295: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas dang gser dngul len pa spangs te /
NK028(sa)001:11296: gser dngul len pa las slar log pa de bzhin du //
NK028(sa)001:11297: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:11300: ma byin par len pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:11301: mi tshangs bar spyod pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:11311: rgyan dang kha dog 'chang ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:11314: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas dang /
NK028(sa)001:11315: gser dngul len pa spangs te gser dngul len pa las /
NK028(sa)001:11317: yan lag bcu pa 'dis 'phags pa dgra bcom pa
NK028(sa)001:11318: de dag gi slab pa la rjes su slob po
NK028(sa)001:11321: slob dpon gyis thabs yin no //
NK028(sa)001:11322: dge tshul gyis legs so zhes brjod do //
NK028(sa)001:11323: de dag ni re zhig dge tshul gyi cho ga'o //
NK028(sa)001:11324: da ni bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i cho ga 'di ltar bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:11325: yul dbus dge slong bcu la sogs pa'i tshogs bsam /
NK028(sa)001:11326: mtha' 'a khob dag tu gzhan med na /
NK028(sa)001:11327: 'dul ba 'dzin pa dang lnga la sogs pa'i tshogs la'ang rung ste /
NK028(sa)001:11328: ltung ba bsdam bshags kyis 'dag par mi nus pa rnams byin gyis brlabs te /
NK028(sa)001:11329: dang por ston pa la phyag gsum 'tshal du bzhugs /
NK028(sa)001:11330: de nas bsgrub bya pha gu'i steng du r+ts+wa bting
NK028(sa)001:11331: ba la tsog tsog por 'dug du bcug ste thal
NK028(sa)001:11333: mkhan po byed pa des rnam sbyar gyon la bsgrub
NK028(sa)001:11334: bya'i rgyab tu 'greng te 'dud pa dang bcas pas
NK028(sa)001:11335: / dge bshes che ge mos tshe dang ldan pa /
NK028(sa)001:11336: ming 'di zhes bgyi ba'i las kyi slob dpon mdzad par zhu /
NK028(sa)001:11337: dge bshes che ge mos tshe dang ldan pa ming
NK028(sa)001:11338: 'di zhes bgyi ba'i gsang ste ston pa'i slob dpon
NK028(sa)001:11339: mdzad par zhu / dge bshes dge 'dun bzhugs rnams
NK028(sa)001:11340: kyis las kyi kha bskongs mdzad nas khong gi rgyud
NK028(sa)001:11341: la bsnyen pa rdzogs pa'i sdom pa rnam par dag
NK028(sa)001:11342: pa gnang ba zhu zhes gsol ba gdab bo //
NK028(sa)001:11343: de nas dge slong re re la phyag gsum gsum 'tshal du bcug la /
NK028(sa)001:11344: pha gu'i steng du tsog tsog bur 'dug tu bcug la /
NK028(sa)001:11345: thal mo sbyar ba bcug ste mkhan pos 'di skad brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11346: sangs rgyas kyis bstan pa la zhugs pa yongs su rdzogs par byed pa la /
NK028(sa)001:11347: sngon gyis gang zag rgyud dag pa /
NK028(sa)001:11348: tshogs rdzogs pa sngon gyi smon lam de ltar btab pa dag la /
NK028(sa)001:11349: dge slong tshur shog tshangs par spyod pa la legs
NK028(sa)001:11350: par spyod cig byas pa de tsam gyis dge slong
NK028(sa)001:11351: gi sdom pa thob pa byung nas gda' ste /
NK028(sa)001:11352: da ltar de tsam gyis sdom pa mi skye bas sdom pa len pa la /
NK028(sa)001:11353: mkhan slob dang bcas pa dgos te /
NK028(sa)001:11354: sangs rgyas kyi zhal nas da phyin chad mkhan po
NK028(sa)001:11355: dang bcas shing slob dpon dang bcas pa la bsnyen
NK028(sa)001:11358: khyed bsnyen par rdzogs par byed pa la mkhan po gcig dgos /
NK028(sa)001:11359: de yang u pa'i sgra las drangs nas nye ba yin /
NK028(sa)001:11363: zhes bya ba'i rkyen gsum byin bas /
NK028(sa)001:11365: nye bar 'dzin nye bar sbyor nye bar lung 'bog pa'i don gyis mkhan po bya ba yin bas /
NK028(sa)001:11366: bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i mkhan por gsol ba gdab snyam du bsams la /
NK028(sa)001:11367: rjes bzlos gyis shig byas la slob dpon dgongs su gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11369: slob dpon la mkhan por gsol gyis slob dpon gyis bdag gi mkhan po mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11370: slob dpon mkhan pos bdag bsnyen par rdzogs par bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:11371: de bzhin du lan gsum du bzlas /
NK028(sa)001:11372: tshig gsum pa la mkhan po mkhan pos bdag bsnyen par rdzogs par bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:11375: slob mas legs so zhes brjod do //
NK028(sa)001:11376: de ni mkhan pos gsol ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:11377: de'i rjes la mkhan po la phyag gsum 'tshal du bcug la /
NK028(sa)001:11378: chos gos gsum so sor btab la slob ma'i phrag
NK028(sa)001:11379: par bkal la gnyis ka bgreng ste 'dud pa dang
NK028(sa)001:11380: bcas pas snam sbyar gzung la /
NK028(sa)001:11381: 'di stod du gyon pa'i chos gos snam sbyar bya ba stod gcer bur mngon pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:11382: rlung nyi ma'i tsha grang las skyob par byed /
NK028(sa)001:11383: bsnyen par ma rdzogs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:11384: mu stegs can las rtags bsrungs /
NK028(sa)001:11385: dge sbyong gi dran pa gos pa'i snam sbyar du
NK028(sa)001:11386: sangs rgyas kyis gnang bas der byin gyis brlabs snyam
NK028(sa)001:11387: pa bgyis la nga'i rjes bzlos bgyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:11389: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba'i chos gos gyis lags
NK028(sa)001:11390: pa rung par sbyad par 'os pa 'di chos gos
NK028(sa)001:11391: rnam sbyar du byin gyis brlabs po /
NK028(sa)001:11392: lan gsum bzlas mkhan pos thabs yin no //
NK028(sa)001:11393: slob mas legs so zhes brjod /
NK028(sa)001:11394: de'i 'og tu bla gos nas bzung nas /
NK028(sa)001:11395: 'di stod du rgyun du gyon pa'i chos gos bla gos bya ba stod gcer bar mngon pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:11396: rlung nyi ma'i tsha grang mi bzod pa las skyobs /
NK028(sa)001:11397: khyim pa dang mu stegs can las brtags bsrungs pa'i thang gos su sangs rgyas kyis gnang /
NK028(sa)001:11398: der byin gyis brlab snyam bgyis la rjes bzlos gyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:11400: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba'i chos gos bgyis lags
NK028(sa)001:11401: pa rung bar spyad pa 'os pa 'di chos gos
NK028(sa)001:11402: thang gos su byin gyis brlabs po lan gsum bzlas
NK028(sa)001:11404: slob mas legs so zhes brjod /
NK028(sa)001:11405: dras shing drub pa med na rgyu la byin gyis brlabs par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11406: mkhan pos chos gos dkon te /
NK028(sa)001:11407: thar pa'i rgyal mtshan brtan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:11408: ngo tsha dang khrel yod kyi gos gyon par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:11409: tshangs par spyod pa'i tshe mthar phyin par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:11411: de'i skabs su grogs dan byed pa cig gis lhung bzed dge 'dun la bstan te /
NK028(sa)001:11412: lhung bzed byin gyis brlabs pa la yang phyag gsum byas la /
NK028(sa)001:11413: mkhan pos bsgrub bya'i lag pa g.yon du lhung bzed gtad la /
NK028(sa)001:11414: g.yas pas lhung bzed bkab la /
NK028(sa)001:11416: khyim pa'i kham phor mu stegs can gyi slong phor las rtags bsrungs byed du sangs rgyas kyis gnang /
NK028(sa)001:11417: 'di zas kyi ji ltar 'gengs pa bzhin du /
NK028(sa)001:11418: rang nyid yon tan gyi chos kyis phyug par byed dgos bya ba'i brdar gnang bas /
NK028(sa)001:11419: lhung bzed du byin gyis brlabs snyam pa gyis la rjes bzlos gyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:11421: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba'i lhung bzed zas la
NK028(sa)001:11422: spyad par 'os pa drang srong gi gnod 'di blang
NK028(sa)001:11423: ba'i snod du byin gyis brlab bo /
NK028(sa)001:11426: slob mas legs so zhes brjod /
NK028(sa)001:11427: de'i 'og tu gding ba dang chu tshags rim pa bzhin gtad la /
NK028(sa)001:11428: 'di ni gding ba bya ba khyim pa'i dkar po /
NK028(sa)001:11430: dge 'dun gyi gnas mal la longs spyod tsa na /
NK028(sa)001:11431: 'di lta bu cig gis skyabs nas longs spyod dgos pas /
NK028(sa)001:11432: gding ba cig kyang tshags bgyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:11434: chu srog chags dang bcas pa byung na 'dis btsags
NK028(sa)001:11435: nas longs spyod dgos pas chu chags cig kyang tshags
NK028(sa)001:11436: bgyis shig / skabs 'dir dge 'dun la phyag gsum 'tshal la /
NK028(sa)001:11437: de nas de thos ba'i nye bskor la bka' ltar
NK028(sa)001:11438: snang gi nyer bskor du 'greng ste 'dud pa dang
NK028(sa)001:11440: skabs 'dir ltung ba spyi'i byin brlabs dang gnas kyi blo mthun bya ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:11441: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams dgongs su gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11442: deng dge 'dun gyi bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i 'phrin las lags la /
NK028(sa)001:11443: bdag cag dge slong thams cad ni ltung ba dang bcas par gyur na /
NK028(sa)001:11444: gang gi 'dun bshags par bgyid pa bdag cag las dge slong 'ga' zhig nas gzhan du mchis ste /
NK028(sa)001:11445: dge slong gi mdun du ltung ba dag chos bzhin
NK028(sa)001:11446: du slar bgyid par spro ba su yang ma mchis
NK028(sa)001:11447: na / gal te dge 'dun gyis dus la bab
NK028(sa)001:11448: cing bzod na dge 'dun gyis gnang bar mdzod cig
NK028(sa)001:11449: na / dang / deng dge 'dun gyis ltung ba
NK028(sa)001:11450: de dag byin gyis brlabs ste bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i
NK028(sa)001:11452: slar yang ltung ba de dag chos bzhin du slar mdzad do //
NK028(sa)001:11455: gnas la blo mthun ni gnas kyi blo mthun gyi las la /
NK028(sa)001:11456: thugs gtad par zhu byas la /
NK028(sa)001:11457: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams dgongs su gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11458: gnas thams cad grub pa'am lag pa nang mtshams dang
NK028(sa)001:11459: phyi rol nye 'khor 'dom gang dang bcas pa 'di
NK028(sa)001:11460: dge 'dun gyis bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i gnas su blo
NK028(sa)001:11462: gal te dge 'dun gyi dus la bab cing bzod na /
NK028(sa)001:11463: dge 'dun gyis gnang bar mdzod cig dang /
NK028(sa)001:11464: dge 'dun gyis gnas thams cad grub pa 'am /
NK028(sa)001:11465: lags pa nang mtshams dang phyi rol nye 'khor 'dom
NK028(sa)001:11466: gang dang bcas pa 'di dge 'dun gyi bsnyen par
NK028(sa)001:11467: rdzogs pa'i gnas su blo mthun par mdzod /
NK028(sa)001:11470: brjod pa la thugs gtad bar zhu /
NK028(sa)001:11471: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams dgongs su gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11473: lag pa nang mtshams dang phyi rol nye 'khor 'dom
NK028(sa)001:11474: gang dang bcas pa 'di dge 'dun gyis bsnyen par
NK028(sa)001:11475: rdzogs pa'i gnas su blo mthun par bzhed na /
NK028(sa)001:11476: de'i slad du dge 'dun gyi gnas su grub pa'am /
NK028(sa)001:11477: lag pa nang mtshams dang phyi rol nye 'khor 'dom
NK028(sa)001:11478: gang dang bcas pa 'di dge 'dun gyi bsnyen par
NK028(sa)001:11479: rdzogs pa'i gnas su blo mthun bzhed na /
NK028(sa)001:11480: de'i slad du dge 'dun gyi gnas su grub pa'am /
NK028(sa)001:11481: lag par nang mtshams dang phyi rol nye 'khor 'dom
NK028(sa)001:11482: gang dang bcas pa 'di dge 'dun gyis bsnyen par
NK028(sa)001:11483: rdzogs pa'i gnas su blo mthun par mdzad na /
NK028(sa)001:11484: tshe dang ldan pa gang dag gnas thams cad grub pa 'am /
NK028(sa)001:11485: lags pa nang mtshams dang phyi rol nye 'khor 'dom
NK028(sa)001:11486: gang dang bcas pa 'di dge 'dun gyis bsnyen par
NK028(sa)001:11488: blo mthun mdzad pa bzod pa de dag ni cang ma gsungs shig /
NK028(sa)001:11489: gang dag mi bzod pa de dag ni gsungs shig /
NK028(sa)001:11490: dge 'dun gyis bzod cing gnang na /
NK028(sa)001:11491: dge 'dun gyi gnas thams cad grub pa'i /
NK028(sa)001:11492: lag pa nang mtshams dang phyi rol nye 'khor 'dom
NK028(sa)001:11493: gang dang bcas pa 'di dge 'dun gyis bsnyen par
NK028(sa)001:11494: rdzogs pa'i gnas su blo mthun par mdzad lags te
NK028(sa)001:11495: / 'di ltar cang mi gsung pa de de bzhin du 'dzin to //
NK028(sa)001:11497: de'i 'og tu slob dpon gyi dge slong las byed pas gsang te ston pa'i dge slong la /
NK028(sa)001:11498: mkhan po ming 'di zhes bgyi bas gsang ste ston
NK028(sa)001:11499: par gsol ba btab pa gang yin zhes dri bar
NK028(sa)001:11500: bya'o // gsang ste ston pa gang yin pa des bdag ming 'di zhes bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11502: de'i 'og tu dge slong las byed pas gsang ste ston pa'i dge slong la /
NK028(sa)001:11503: dge slong ming zhes bya ba khyod mkhan po ming 'di zhes bya bas /
NK028(sa)001:11504: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bya ba la
NK028(sa)001:11505: gsang ste ston par spro 'am zhes 'dri bar bya'o
NK028(sa)001:11506: // des spro'o zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11507: de'i 'og tu dge slong las byed pa gsang ste /
NK028(sa)001:11508: ston par bar chad dri ba'i phyir gsol ba 'ba' zhig gis las 'di ltar bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:11509: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11510: dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di /
NK028(sa)001:11511: mkhan po ming 'di zhes bgyi bas /
NK028(sa)001:11512: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba la /
NK028(sa)001:11513: gsang ste ston par spro na dge 'dun gyi dus la bab cing bzod na /
NK028(sa)001:11514: dge 'dun gyis snang bar mdzod cig dang /
NK028(sa)001:11515: dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di mkhan po ming 'di zhes bgyis bas /
NK028(sa)001:11516: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba la gsang ste ston to //
NK028(sa)001:11518: de nas gsang ste ston bas dkyil 'khor ba'i phyi rol du song te /
NK028(sa)001:11519: bsnyen par rdzogs par bya ba de dag la phyag 'tshal du bcug nas //
NK028(sa)001:11520: 'dun du tsog tsog por 'dug thal mo sbyar du bcug ste //
NK028(sa)001:11521: khyod bsnyen pa rdzogs par byed pa la //
NK028(sa)001:11522: bar chad med pa rgyu dag pa cig dgos /
NK028(sa)001:11523: bar chad yod med dris bas shes pa yin pa la yin //
NK028(sa)001:11524: ma yin pa la ma yin zhes len thob cig /
NK028(sa)001:11525: tshe dang ldan pa khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:11526: 'di ni khyod kyi bden pa'i dus //
NK028(sa)001:11527: 'di ni khyod kyi 'byung ba'i dus ste /
NK028(sa)001:11528: kho bos khyod la cung zad ci dri yis /
NK028(sa)001:11530: yin pa la yang yin zhes smos shis /
NK028(sa)001:11531: ma yin pa la ma yin zhes lan thob cig /
NK028(sa)001:11533: des skyes pa lags zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11534: skyes pa'i dbang po dang ldan nam //
NK028(sa)001:11535: des ldan zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11537: des lon zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11538: khyod kyi chos gos gsum pa lhung bzed tshang ngam //
NK028(sa)001:11539: des tshang zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11540: khyod kyi pha ma gson nam //
NK028(sa)001:11541: gal te gson zhes zer na //
NK028(sa)001:11542: khyod pha mas gnang ngam zhes dri bar bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11543: gal te shi zhes zer na /
NK028(sa)001:11547: rtsod pa can ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11549: rgyal pos krabs pa ma yin nam //
NK028(sa)001:11550: rgyal po la sdig pa ma yin nam //
NK028(sa)001:11551: rgyal po la gnod pa'i las byed pa ma yin nam //
NK028(sa)001:11552: khyod rgyal po la gnod pa'i las byas sam //
NK028(sa)001:11553: byed du bcug pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11554: choms rkun par grags pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11557: dge slong ma sun phyung pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11558: rku thabs su gnas pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11559: tha dad du gnas pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11560: gnas par mi bya ba ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11561: mu stegs can ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11562: mu stegs can zhugs pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11563: pha bsad pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11564: ma bsad pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11565: dgra bcom pa bsad pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11566: dge 'dun gyis dbyen byas pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11567: de bzhin gshegs pa la ngan sems kyi khrag byung ba ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11571: des ma lags shes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11572: khyod la la'i bu lon mang yang rung nyung yang rung /
NK028(sa)001:11573: cung zad chags pa med dam /
NK028(sa)001:11574: gal te bu lon chags so zhes zer na /
NK028(sa)001:11575: khyod bsnyen par rdzogs nas 'jal nus sam zhes dri bar bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11576: des nus zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11577: khyod sngon rab byung ba ma yin nam zhes dri bar bya /
NK028(sa)001:11579: ji ltar khyod da ltar rab tu byung pa yin zhes dri bar bya /
NK028(sa)001:11581: khyod kyi tshangs par spyod pa legs par spyad dam zhes dri bar bya /
NK028(sa)001:11582: des legs par spyad ces brjod do //
NK028(sa)001:11583: tshigs snga ma'i khyod kyi ming ci khyod kyi mkhan po'i ming ci /
NK028(sa)001:11584: des bdag gi ming 'di zhes bgyi ba lags /
NK028(sa)001:11585: don gyi slad du mtshan nas smos te /
NK028(sa)001:11586: bdag gi mkhan po'i ming 'di zhes bgyi ba lags zhes brjod /
NK028(sa)001:11587: tshe dang ldan pa khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:11588: mi rnams kyi lus kyi nad rnam pa 'di lta bu 'di dag 'byung ba 'a di lta ste /
NK028(sa)001:11621: yan lag du zug pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:11628: ngal ba dang lus tsha ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:11630: rus pa la zug pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:11631: lus kyi nad 'di lta bu 'di dag las gang yang rung ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:11632: 'di lta bu dag khyod kyi lus la med dam /
NK028(sa)001:11633: des ma mchis zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11634: ngas 'dir dris pa bzhin du las kyi slob dpon gyis kyang 'dri bas /
NK028(sa)001:11635: der lan btab pa bzhin du der thob cig /
NK028(sa)001:11636: nga 'bod du ma byung bar bsdod cig byas la /
NK028(sa)001:11637: dge 'dun gyi gral bzhugs nas 'greng ste 'dud pa dang bcas pas 'ong ba zhu ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:11638: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11639: bdag gi mkhan po ming 'di zhes bgyi bas tshe
NK028(sa)001:11640: dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba la bar
NK028(sa)001:11641: chad kyi chos rnams gsang ston gyis rjes su bstan
NK028(sa)001:11642: na / de yang bar chad kyi chos rnams yongs su dag go zhes kho na nyid mchi na /
NK028(sa)001:11644: thams cad kyi yongs su dag na'o zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11645: mi brjod na 'gal tshabs can du 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:11646: gnang ba dang nang du bos sgo yod na bcad
NK028(sa)001:11647: la rtsa'i steng nas phyag mtshan gsum po byed du
NK028(sa)001:11648: bzhug go / de nas pha gu'i steng du cig rtsog pur 'dug la thal mo sbyar te /
NK028(sa)001:11649: dge 'dun la bsnyen par rdzogs par gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:11650: las kyi slob dpon gyis gdam ngag cung zad gnang ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:11651: khyed bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i sdom pa len pa de /
NK028(sa)001:11652: yul gtso bo dge 'dun las skye ba yin te /
NK028(sa)001:11654: dge bdun las bsnyen par rdzogs par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11657: mtshan nyid tshangs mi mthun pa med pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:11658: chos gsum tshang ba cig dgos /
NK028(sa)001:11659: grangs tshangs pa la dbus dang mtha' 'khob kyi bye
NK028(sa)001:11660: brag gis bcu dang lnga yan chad tshang ba gcig
NK028(sa)001:11661: dgos yang tshang / mtshan nyid tshangs ba la kha
NK028(sa)001:11662: bskong gis chos rnams dang ldan pa dgos yang bslab
NK028(sa)001:11663: pa la gces spras su mdzad pa sha stag bzhugs
NK028(sa)001:11665: mi mthun pa med pa la ma lus pa dang
NK028(sa)001:11666: 'dus pa'i phyir bzlog pa med pa dgos na yang
NK028(sa)001:11667: tshang / de ltar chos gsum tshang ba'i dge 'dun la bsnyen par rdzogs par gsol ba gdab dgos /
NK028(sa)001:11668: gsol ba 'debs pa'i cho ga las /
NK028(sa)001:11669: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams kyis bdag bsnyen par rdzogs par mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11671: bdag rjes su gzung du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11672: bdag rjes su bstan du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:11673: bdag la thugs brtse bar mdzad du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:11674: zhes bya ba dang cho ga zur rnam pa lnga yod pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:11675: bdag bsnyen par rdzogs par mdzad du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:11676: zhes bya ba de byung tsa na rdzogs par ni /
NK028(sa)001:11677: gnod pa thams cad dang bral ba'i dngos po mya ngan las 'das pa la zer ba yin /
NK028(sa)001:11678: de la bsam pa dang sbyor ba gnyis kyis khad
NK028(sa)001:11679: nye ba'i dge slong gis sdom pa thob par mdzad
NK028(sa)001:11680: du gsol zhes gsol ba 'debs pa yin /
NK028(sa)001:11681: bdag drang du gsol zhes bya ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:11682: phyag rkyang ba'i tshul gyis bsam /
NK028(sa)001:11683: ma dag pa'i gnas nas dag pa'i gnas su drang du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11685: bdag rjes su gzung tu gsol zhes bya ba ni
NK028(sa)001:11686: bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i sdom pa dang mi ldan pa
NK028(sa)001:11687: las sdom pa dang ldan par gzung du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11689: bdag la rjes su bstan du gsol zhes bya ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:11690: thar ba'i lam bstan du gsol zhes gsol ba 'debs pa yin /
NK028(sa)001:11691: thugs brtse ba can dge 'dun btsun pa rnams kyis thugs brtse ba'i slad du bdag la /
NK028(sa)001:11692: thugs brtse bar mdzad du gsol zhes pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:11693: dge 'dun kun gyis kyang rnyed pa dang bkur sti
NK028(sa)001:11694: la ma gzigs par byams pas thugs rjes gzigs la
NK028(sa)001:11695: / bdag bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i sdom pa rnam par
NK028(sa)001:11696: dag pa zhig gnang par zhu zhes gsol ba 'debs
NK028(sa)001:11697: / pa yin / 'di yang dag par blangs pa
NK028(sa)001:11698: brda' las byung pa yin pas cho ga dag pa
NK028(sa)001:11699: / pa yin / dgos / bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba zhes pa de bas su la phob /
NK028(sa)001:11700: mkhan po ming 'di zhes pa bgyi bas /
NK028(sa)001:11702: dge 'dun las zhes bya ba'i skabs su sgra thon
NK028(sa)001:11703: pa zhig dgos gsol ba 'debs pa 'di med kha
NK028(sa)001:11704: med yin pas / dge 'dun kun gyis gsan dgos pas /
NK028(sa)001:11705: dge 'dun rnams bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i gsol ba 'debs pa'i las la thugs gtad par zhu /
NK028(sa)001:11706: khyed rang rnams dal bus nga'i rjes bzlos gyis shig byas la /
NK028(sa)001:11707: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11708: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba don gyi slad du mtshan nas smos te /
NK028(sa)001:11709: mkhan po ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dge 'dun las bsnyen par rdzogs par 'tshal ste /
NK028(sa)001:11710: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba don gyi slad du /
NK028(sa)001:11712: mkhan po ming 'di zhes bgyi bas /
NK028(sa)001:11713: dge 'dun las bsnyen par rdzogs par gsol na /
NK028(sa)001:11714: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams kyis bdag bsnyen par rdzogs par mdzad du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11715: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams kyi bdag drang du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11716: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams kyis bdag rjes su gzung du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11717: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gyis bdag rjes su bstan du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11718: thugs brtse ba can dge 'dun btsun pa rnams kyi
NK028(sa)001:11719: thugs ba rtse ba'i slad du bdag la thugs brtse
NK028(sa)001:11721: de bzhin du lan gsum bzlas /
NK028(sa)001:11722: des dge 'dun la bsnyen par rdzogs par gsol ba thebs pa yin /
NK028(sa)001:11723: khyed rang lad mo byed mi dgos /
NK028(sa)001:11724: dge 'dun nang du bar chad dri ba'i las la thugs gtad par zhu byas la /
NK028(sa)001:11725: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:11726: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di mkhan po /
NK028(sa)001:11727: ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dge 'dun las bsnyen par rdzogs par gsol nas /
NK028(sa)001:11728: gal te dge 'dun gyis bzod na /
NK028(sa)001:11729: dge 'dun gyis gnang ba ra mdzod cig dang /
NK028(sa)001:11730: bdag gis dge 'dun gyi nang du mkhan po ming 'di zhes bgyi bas /
NK028(sa)001:11731: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba la /
NK028(sa)001:11732: bar chad gyi chos rnams dri bar bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11734: de'i rjes la las kyi slob dpon la phyag 'tshal du bcug la /
NK028(sa)001:11736: khyed bsnyen par rdzogs par byed pa la /
NK028(sa)001:11737: 'gal rkyen bar chad med pa cig dgos /
NK028(sa)001:11738: bar chad yod med dris pas shes pa la /
NK028(sa)001:11739: gsang ste ston pa'i slob dpon gyis lkog du yang /
NK028(sa)001:11740: dris pa yin mod kyis bar chad glo bur ba yin pas 'phral du 'byung yang srid /
NK028(sa)001:11741: sngar ma dran pa dran pa yang srid /
NK028(sa)001:11742: dge 'dun thugs ches pa la sogs pa'i dgos pa du ma yod pas /
NK028(sa)001:11743: 'dir yang 'dri bar byed pa dngos po tshul dang /
NK028(sa)001:11745: tshe dang ldan pa khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:11746: 'di ni khyod kyi bden pa'i dus te /
NK028(sa)001:11747: kho bos khyod la cung zad cig dri yis /
NK028(sa)001:11749: yin pa la yin zhes smros shig /
NK028(sa)001:11750: ma yin pa la ma yin zhes lan thob cig khyod skyes pa yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11752: skyes pa'i dbang po dang ldan nam /
NK028(sa)001:11753: des ldan zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11756: khyod kyi chos gos gsum dang lhung bzed tshang ngam /
NK028(sa)001:11758: khyod kyi pha ma gson nam /
NK028(sa)001:11759: gal te gson zhes brjod na /
NK028(sa)001:11760: khyod pha mas gnang ngam zhes dri bar bya /
NK028(sa)001:11761: des gnang zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11762: gal te shi zhes zer na /
NK028(sa)001:11766: rtsod pa can ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11768: rgyal pos bkrabs pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11769: rgyal po la sdigs pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11770: rgyal po la gnod par byed pa'i las byas sam /
NK028(sa)001:11771: byed du bcug pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11772: chom rkun par grags pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11775: dge slong ma sun phyung pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11776: rku thabs su gnas pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11777: tha dad du gnas pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11778: gnas par mi bya ba ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11779: mu stegs can ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11780: mu stegs can zhugs pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11781: pha bsad pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11782: ma bsad pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11783: dgra bcom pa bsad pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11784: dge 'dun gyi dbyen byas pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11785: de bzhin gshegs pa la ngan sems kyi khrag phyung pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11789: des ma lags zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11790: khyod la la la'i bu lon mang yang rung nyung yang rung /
NK028(sa)001:11791: cung zad chags pa med dam zhes dri /
NK028(sa)001:11792: bu lon chags so zhes zer na /
NK028(sa)001:11793: bsnyen par rdzogs nas 'jal nus sam zhes dri bar bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11795: khyod sngon rab tu byung ba ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:11797: ji ltar da ltar khyod rab tu byung ba yin nam zhes dri /
NK028(sa)001:11799: khyod kyis tshangs pa spyod pa legs par spyod pa legs par spyad dam zhes dri /
NK028(sa)001:11800: des legs par spyod lags shes brjod /
NK028(sa)001:11802: des bdag gi ming 'di zhes bgyis ba lags /
NK028(sa)001:11803: khyod kyi mkhan po'i ming ci /
NK028(sa)001:11804: don gyis slad du mtshan nas smos te /
NK028(sa)001:11805: bdag gi mkhan po'i ming 'di zhes bgyi ba lags shes brjod /
NK028(sa)001:11806: 'di man chad khyed rang gi lus la yod med brtags nas lan phyogs gcig btab pas chog /
NK028(sa)001:11807: tshe dang ldan pa khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:11808: mi rnams kyi lus la nad kyi rnam pa 'di lta bu dag 'byung bas /
NK028(sa)001:11840: lhog pa dang yan lag zug pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:11843: mkhris nad dang gzhang 'brum dang skyug bro ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:11848: rus pa la zug pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:11849: lus gyi nad 'di lta bu 'di dag las gang yang rung ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:11850: 'di lta bu gzhan dag kyang khyod kyi lus la med dam de ma mchis shes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:11853: dngos gzhi'i chos ga la las kyi slob dpon gdam
NK028(sa)001:11854: ngag byas ste bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i sdom pa de
NK028(sa)001:11855: lung cig nas 'phros pa las mngon sum du gyur
NK028(sa)001:11856: pa bcu la brten nas skye par gsungs /
NK028(sa)001:11857: de yang tshig bcad du sdebs pa //
NK028(sa)001:11858: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun dang //
NK028(sa)001:11859: mkhan po slob dpon bsnyen rdzogs 'dod //
NK028(sa)001:11860: yo byad yongs su dag pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:11861: gsol dang las ni mngon sum zhes gsungs pas /
NK028(sa)001:11862: dang po sangs rgyas mngon sum du gyur pa /
NK028(sa)001:11863: bstan pa'i bdag po sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:11864: de'i sku rab tu gnas pa dang ldan pa cig bzhugs /
NK028(sa)001:11866: gnyis pa chos mngon sum du gyur pa lung dang rtogs pa'i chos yin te /
NK028(sa)001:11868: ston pa'i dam chos rnam gnyis ni /
NK028(sa)001:11869: lung dang rtogs pa'i bdag nyid do //
NK028(sa)001:11870: ces gsungs pas lung gi chos kyi rten po ti glegs bam yang bzhugs /
NK028(sa)001:11871: rtogs pa'i chos kyang mkhan slob dge 'dun dang bcas pa'i thugs rgyud la bzhugs pas tshang /
NK028(sa)001:11872: gsum pa dge 'dun mngon sum du gyur pa ni grangs tshang /
NK028(sa)001:11874: mi mthun pa med pa'i chos gsum bstan la /
NK028(sa)001:11875: gsol ba btab dgos na tshang /
NK028(sa)001:11876: bzhi pa mkhan po mngon sum du gyur pa btsun
NK028(sa)001:11877: pa bstan pa 'di yi yan lag tu bsnyen par
NK028(sa)001:11878: rdzogs pa'i sdom pa rnam par dag pas bar ma
NK028(sa)001:11879: chad par lo bcu lon pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:11880: mkhas shing phan 'dogs pa'i yan lag tu lnga mtshan du nye bar sbyor ba /
NK028(sa)001:11881: nyi shu rtsa gcig las gang yang rung ba bstan pas dgos na'ang tshang //
NK028(sa)001:11882: lnga pa slob dpon mngon sum du gyur pa la gnyis las //
NK028(sa)001:11883: gsang ste ston pa'i slob dpon de kha bskong par 'os pas /
NK028(sa)001:11884: 'gro ba ma yin pa bzhi dang bral ba /
NK028(sa)001:11885: lkog du bar chad dris nas nang du 'ong ba
NK028(sa)001:11886: zhu ba la mkhas par spro bar gyur pa cig
NK028(sa)001:11887: dgos na'ang tshang / las kyis slob dpon kha bskong
NK028(sa)001:11888: par 'os shing dge 'dun gyis dbus su las legs
NK028(sa)001:11889: par byed shes pa zhig dgos na'ang tshang /
NK028(sa)001:11890: drug pa bsnyen par rdzogs par 'dod pa mngon sum
NK028(sa)001:11891: du gyur pa khyed rang rnams la zer ba yin
NK028(sa)001:11892: / de la rten kyi cha dang bsam pa'i cha
NK028(sa)001:11893: gnyis las rten gyi cha la sgra mi snyan pa
NK028(sa)001:11894: / dang / mtshan nyams pa bcu bzhi dang /
NK028(sa)001:11895: mi ma yin pa'i 'gro ba la so sor thar pa'i sdom pa mi skye bas /
NK028(sa)001:11896: gling gsum gang rung gi mir skyes pa /
NK028(sa)001:11897: bud med kyi cho ga'i skabs ma yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:11898: skyes pa'i dbang po dang ldan pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:11899: dngos po'i bsam pa'i sgo nas lo nyi shu lon pa'am /
NK028(sa)001:11900: der shes pa yan chad dang ldan pa'am /
NK028(sa)001:11901: dge tshul gyis sdom pa yan chad rgyud la thob cing dgos na tshang /
NK028(sa)001:11902: gnyis pa bsam pa'i cha la blang bya nges 'byung gi tshul khrims yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:11903: mya ngan las 'das pa'i bsam pa brtan po dang ldan pas /
NK028(sa)001:11904: bsam pa thag pa nas len 'dod dang /
NK028(sa)001:11905: dngos gzhi'i dus na thabs shes kyi nus ldan dang /
NK028(sa)001:11906: nges pa lnga dang bral ba bzhi tshang dgos mya ngan khams gsum mam rigs drug yin /
NK028(sa)001:11907: de las 'das pa byang chub rnam pa gsum yin la /
NK028(sa)001:11908: mya ngan la rigs drug las so so'i sdug bsngal dar drag pas yun ring pa yod de /
NK028(sa)001:11910: sems can dmyal ba dmyal mes nyams //
NK028(sa)001:11911: yi dwags bkres shing bskoms pas nyams //
NK028(sa)001:11912: dud 'gro gcig la cig zas nyams //
NK028(sa)001:11913: lha dag bag med pa yi nyams //
NK028(sa)001:11914: mi dag yongs su 'tsho bas nyams //
NK028(sa)001:11915: 'khor ba khab kyi rtse tsam la //
NK028(sa)001:11916: bde ba nam yang yod ma yin /
NK028(sa)001:11918: bcom ldan 'das byams mgon gyi zhal nas kyang /
NK028(sa)001:11919: 'khor ba thog mtha' med pa 'dir skyee 'chi 'gro ba'i lam ni rnam pa lnga /
NK028(sa)001:11920: mi gtsang pa la dri zhim med bzhin du //
NK028(sa)001:11921: 'gro lnga dag na'ang bde ba med //
NK028(sa)001:11922: de'i sdug bsngal me mtshon dang //
NK028(sa)001:11923: kha ba rgya mtsho las sogs reg bskyed bzhin /
NK028(sa)001:11924: zhes gsungs pas khams gsum mam rigs drug pa 'di mya ngan nam sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin yin /
NK028(sa)001:11925: de las 'das pa byang chub rnam pa gsum yin /
NK028(sa)001:11927: mchog gam gtso bo rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:11929: sangs rgyas de yang rang gcig pu thob pas mi chog ste /
NK028(sa)001:11930: sems can thams cad rang gi pha ma byas pa
NK028(sa)001:11931: lan grangs kyang dpag tu med pa byas la byas
NK028(sa)001:11932: pa'i res la phan bde sna tshogs kyis phan btags
NK028(sa)001:11933: pa'i drin can sha stag yin te mdo las /
NK028(sa)001:11934: ma yi thug mtha' rgya shug tshil gu tsam //
NK028(sa)001:11935: ri bur bgrangs kyang sa yi lang mi 'gyur /
NK028(sa)001:11937: sems can gcig gis pha byas pa //
NK028(sa)001:11938: rta dang glang po skyon pa rnams //
NK028(sa)001:11939: stong gsum 'di yang snod du chung //
NK028(sa)001:11940: rkang 'gro gzhan yang de bzhin no //
NK028(sa)001:11942: drin can la drin can du shes pa la byas
NK028(sa)001:11943: pa shes pa zer de'i lan 'don pa la byas
NK028(sa)001:11944: pa gzo ba zer ba yin /
NK028(sa)001:11945: de gnyis yod na gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi phan bde mtha' dag 'byung ba yin te /
NK028(sa)001:11947: byas pa shes shing byas pa gzo //
NK028(sa)001:11948: byas pa chud zos mi byed pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:11949: mi la dpal mgon nyer bar gnas /
NK028(sa)001:11951: de la thabs gzhan gyis lan mi lon pas /
NK028(sa)001:11952: mya ngan las 'das pa'i bde pa la dgod dgos ste /
NK028(sa)001:11954: skye ba grangs med de dang der //
NK028(sa)001:11955: phan pa dpag med bsgrubs rnams la //
NK028(sa)001:11956: de la lan du phan 'dogs pa //
NK028(sa)001:11957: mya ngan 'das la gzhan ci yod /
NK028(sa)001:11959: da lta'i nus pa 'di tsam gyis sangs rgyas la 'god mi nus pas /
NK028(sa)001:11960: de'i ched du bdag gi dang por sangs rgyas thob par byed dgos /
NK028(sa)001:11961: sangs rgyas de rgyu med pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:11964: rgyu tshang la ma nor ba bslab pa gsum yin /
NK028(sa)001:11965: de la dngos kyi rgyu zag med kyi shes rab yin kyang /
NK028(sa)001:11966: de ting nge 'dzin la rag las /
NK028(sa)001:11967: de tshul khrims rnam par dag pa las skye ba yin te /
NK028(sa)001:11971: 'phags pa'i bden pa rnams rtogs par 'gyur /
NK028(sa)001:11973: khrims ni rgyu dang mi rgyu kun gyi sa bzhin du //
NK028(sa)001:11974: yon tan kun gyi gzhi rten lags par gsungs //
NK028(sa)001:11975: de la yang so so thar pa'i sdom pa rigs bdun nam brgyad las /
NK028(sa)001:11976: dge slong gi sdom pa mchog yin te /
NK028(sa)001:11978: so so'i thar pa rigs bdun du //
NK028(sa)001:11979: de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs pa las //
NK028(sa)001:11980: tshangs spyod dpal ni mchog yin te //
NK028(sa)001:11981: dge slong sdom pa dag tu bzhed /
NK028(sa)001:11983: mdor na sems can thams cad kyi don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par bya /
NK028(sa)001:11984: de'i ched du dge slong gi sdom pa rnam par
NK028(sa)001:11985: dag pa blangs la bsrungs snyam pa rgyun du 'byung
NK028(sa)001:11986: ba la / mya ngan las 'das pa thob 'dod pa'i bsam pa brtan po zer ba yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:11987: de skyed dgos pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:11988: bsam pa thag pa nas len 'dod dang dngos gzhi'i
NK028(sa)001:11989: dus na thabs shes kyi nus ldan dgos na yang
NK028(sa)001:11990: tshang / bzhi po nges pa lnga dang bral ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:11996: tshe nges par mi byed na thob bo /
NK028(sa)001:11999: dge slong la mi rung zer ba rnams spangs /
NK028(sa)001:12000: rung zer ba rnams bsgrubs pa la zer ba yin pas tshang /
NK028(sa)001:12001: mdor na de rnams kyis bsnyen par rdzogs par 'dod
NK028(sa)001:12002: mngon du gyur pa la ci dgos pa thams cad
NK028(sa)001:12003: tshang / bdun pa yo byad mngon gsum du gyur pa la ni /
NK028(sa)001:12004: chos gos dang lhung bzed mkhan pos byin gyis brlabs shing gnang ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:12005: 'ding ba chu tshags mkhan pos gsung gis gnang ba dang ldan pa dgos na yang tshang /
NK028(sa)001:12006: brgyad pa yongs su dag pa mngon sum du gyur
NK028(sa)001:12007: pa ni bar chad dang mi ldan pa dgos na
NK028(sa)001:12009: khyed rang gi med par lan btab pas tshang /
NK028(sa)001:12011: bcu pa las mngon sum du gyur pa /
NK028(sa)001:12012: da lta nyid du bsgrub pa yin /
NK028(sa)001:12013: de la gsol ba dang bzhi yod pa las /
NK028(sa)001:12015: brjod pa gsum pa'i ngo bo brjod pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12017: byed pa brjod pa de slad du /
NK028(sa)001:12018: dge 'dun gyi zhes bya ba 'byung ba'i tshe sdom
NK028(sa)001:12019: pa skye ba yin pas der skyes snyam pa byung
NK028(sa)001:12020: na'ang legs / ma byung pa dang der skye pa yin /
NK028(sa)001:12021: khyod rang rjes bzlos bya mi dgos /
NK028(sa)001:12022: dge slong dngos gzhi las thugs gtad par zhu /
NK028(sa)001:12023: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:12024: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di dge 'dun las bsnyen par rdzogs par 'tshal nas /
NK028(sa)001:12025: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di /
NK028(sa)001:12026: mkhan po ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dge 'dun las bsnyen par rdzogs par gsol ste /
NK028(sa)001:12028: skye pa'i dbang po dang yang ldan /
NK028(sa)001:12030: 'di'i chos gos gsum dang lhung bzed yang tshang /
NK028(sa)001:12031: bar chad kyi chos rnams kyang yongs su dag go /
NK028(sa)001:12032: zhes kho nar nyid mchi ste /
NK028(sa)001:12033: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di
NK028(sa)001:12034: mkhan po ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dge 'dun las
NK028(sa)001:12035: bsnyen par rdzogs par gsol na /
NK028(sa)001:12036: gal te dge 'dun gyis dus la bab cing bzod na /
NK028(sa)001:12037: dge 'dun gyi gnang bar mdzod cig dang /
NK028(sa)001:12038: dge 'dun gyis tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di /
NK028(sa)001:12039: mkhan po ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dge 'dun la bsnyen par rdzogs par mdzad do //
NK028(sa)001:12041: las brjod pa dang po la thugs gtad par zhu /
NK028(sa)001:12042: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK028(sa)001:12043: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba /
NK028(sa)001:12044: 'di mkhan po ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dge 'dun las bsnyen par rdzogs par 'tshal na /
NK028(sa)001:12045: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di
NK028(sa)001:12046: mkhan po ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dge 'dun las
NK028(sa)001:12047: bsnyen par rdzogs par gsol te /
NK028(sa)001:12049: skyes pa'i dbang po dang yang ldan /
NK028(sa)001:12053: bar chad kyi chos rnams kyang yongs su dag go zhes kho na nyid mchi ste /
NK028(sa)001:12054: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di mkhan po ming 'di zhes bgyi bas /
NK028(sa)001:12055: dge 'dun las bsnyen par rdzogs par gsol na /
NK028(sa)001:12056: de'i slad du dge 'dun gyis tshe dang ldan pa
NK028(sa)001:12057: ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di mkhan po ming 'di
NK028(sa)001:12058: zhes bgyi bas / dge 'dun las bsnyen par rdzogs par mdzad na /
NK028(sa)001:12059: tshe dang ldan pa gang dag tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:12060: mkhan po ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dge 'dun las
NK028(sa)001:12061: bsnyen par rdzogs par bzod pa de dag ni cang
NK028(sa)001:12062: ma gsungs shig / de bzhin du brjod pa gnyis pa la thugs gtad par zhu /
NK028(sa)001:12063: byas la brjod pa dang po'i mgo nas lan gsum tshar te gdabs nas bzlas /
NK028(sa)001:12064: las kyi 'jug bsdu la thugs bstad par zhu /
NK028(sa)001:12065: dge 'dun gyis bzod cing gnang nas /
NK028(sa)001:12066: dge 'dun gyis tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di /
NK028(sa)001:12067: mkhan po ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dge 'dun las bsnyen par rdzogs par mdzad lags te /
NK028(sa)001:12068: 'di ltar cang mi gsung ba de de bzhin du 'dzin to //
NK028(sa)001:12071: 'jug gi cho ga la gnyis las rdzogs pa'i dus sgo bya ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:12072: las kyi slob dpon las gzhan pa'i dge slong gcig gis /
NK028(sa)001:12073: lo gang la sdom pa thob pa'i lo dus /
NK028(sa)001:12074: rtsis zla ba tshes grangs nyin mtshan gyi cha grib
NK028(sa)001:12075: tshod rnams dge slong de dag la sgo bar bya
NK028(sa)001:12076: / dgos pa bsnyen bskur gyi gnas dang gnas ma
NK028(sa)001:12077: yin pa shes pa la sogs pa'i dgos pa yod
NK028(sa)001:12078: / / gnyis pa thob pa de mi nyams par
NK028(sa)001:12079: bya ba'i phyir gdam ngag brjod pa la slab bya
NK028(sa)001:12081: slob byed gnyen po brjod pa gnyis las //
NK028(sa)001:12082: bslab bya yul brjod pa la /
NK028(sa)001:12083: rang smin par bya ba'i chos brjod pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12084: cho ga rnam par dag pa'i sgo nas gzhan las shes 'gyur gyi brjod pa gnyis yin /
NK028(sa)001:12085: dang po rang smin pa'i chos la brten nas /
NK028(sa)001:12086: 'tsho ba rnam par dag pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12087: tshul khrims rnam par dag pa bsrungs pa dang rtogs
NK028(sa)001:12088: don lnga pa rnam par dag pa dang gsum las
NK028(sa)001:12089: / dang po brten pa 'tsho ba rnam par dag pa la dam ba ca' dgos pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:12090: khyod kyis deng phyin chad ji srid 'tsho'i bar du gos phyag dar khrod /
NK028(sa)001:12091: zas bsod snyoms sman brkus te bor ba /
NK028(sa)001:12092: gnas shing drung la rten nas dge slong bzang po cig byed dgos so //
NK028(sa)001:12093: zhes ston pa ni 'dir gda' tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di'i zhes bya pa khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:12094: bzhi po 'di dag ni bcom ldan 'das de bzhin
NK028(sa)001:12095: gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK028(sa)001:12096: sangs rgyas mkhyen cing gzigs pa des /
NK028(sa)001:12097: de ltar rab tu byung ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:12098: bsnyen par rdzogs pa dge slong gi gnas su gsungs te /
NK028(sa)001:12099: de la gnas na dge slong legs par gsungs pa'i chos 'dul ba la rab tu byung ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:12100: bsnyen par rdzogs pa dge slong gi dngos por 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:12101: des spyir brjod pa bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12102: bye brag tu brjod pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:12104: 'di lta ste gos kyi nang nas phyag dar khrod pa ni rung ba rnyed kyang sla ba ste /
NK028(sa)001:12105: de la gnas na dge slong legs par gsung pa'i chos 'dul ba la rab tu byung ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:12106: bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i dge slong gi dngos por 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:12107: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bya ba khyod
NK028(sa)001:12108: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du phyag dar khrod kyi gos
NK028(sa)001:12111: des 'dod pa bsod nams kyi mtha' spangs pa bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12112: da ngal zhing dub pa'i mtha' spangs pa bstan pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:12113: lhag par rnyed na dar ram /
NK028(sa)001:12122: yul ka shi ka'i ras phran nam /
NK028(sa)001:12132: gzhan yang gos rung ba gang /
NK028(sa)001:12133: dge 'dun nam gang zag las rnyed na de yang khyod kyi long la tshod zin par gyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:12134: ji ltar khyod gnas 'di lta bu la dam 'acha'am /
NK028(sa)001:12137: des gos phyag dar khrod pa la dam 'cha' ba bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12138: da zas bsod snyoms la dam 'cha' dgos so zhes /
NK028(sa)001:12140: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bya ba khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:12141: zas kyis nang nas bsod snyoms ni rung ba rnyed kyang bslab ste /
NK028(sa)001:12143: dge slong legs par gsungs pa'i chos 'dul pa las /
NK028(sa)001:12144: rab tu byung ba dang bsnyen par rdzogs pa dge slong gi dngos por 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:12145: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bya ba khyod
NK028(sa)001:12146: ji srid 'tsho'i bar bsod snyoms kyis zas kyis 'tsho
NK028(sa)001:12147: bar spro'am / des spro zhes brjod do //
NK028(sa)001:12148: des 'dod pa bsod snyoms kyi mtha' spangs pa bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12149: da ngal zhing dub pa'i mtha' spongs ston pa de /
NK028(sa)001:12150: lhag par rnyed na 'bras chan nam /
NK028(sa)001:12158: gral la bos pa'am spags pa'am /
NK028(sa)001:12159: gzhan yang zas rung ba gang dge 'dun nam /
NK028(sa)001:12161: de yang khyod kyis long la tshod zin par gyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:12162: ji ltar khyod gnas 'di lta bu la dam 'cha' 'am /
NK028(sa)001:12165: des zas bsod snyoms la dam 'cha' ba bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12166: da gnas shing drung la dam 'cha' dgos so zhes ston pa deng 'dir gda' /
NK028(sa)001:12167: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:12168: gnas mal gyi nang na shing drung gi rung pa rnyed kyang bslab te /
NK028(sa)001:12169: de la gnas na dge slong legs par gsungs pa'i
NK028(sa)001:12170: chos 'dul ba la rab tu byung ba dang bsnyen
NK028(sa)001:12171: par rdzogs pa dge slong gi dngos por 'gyur ro
NK028(sa)001:12172: // tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bya ba
NK028(sa)001:12173: khyod ji srid 'tsho'i bar du shing drung gi gnas
NK028(sa)001:12175: des spro zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12176: des 'dod pa bsod snyoms kyi mtha' spangs pa bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12177: da ngal zhing dub ba'i mtha' spong ba de 'dir gda' /
NK028(sa)001:12178: lhag par rnyed na khang pa 'am /
NK028(sa)001:12185: sgo khang gi steng gi bsil khang ngam /
NK028(sa)001:12186: khang steng gi yol khang ngam /
NK028(sa)001:12188: sa phug gam brag phug gam ri phug gam /
NK028(sa)001:12194: bya skyibs su ma byas pa'am /
NK028(sa)001:12195: gzhan yang gnas mal rung ba gang /
NK028(sa)001:12196: dge 'dun nam gang zag la rnyed na /
NK028(sa)001:12197: de yang khyod long la tshod zin par gyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:12198: ci ltar khyod gnas 'di lta bu dam 'cha' 'am /
NK028(sa)001:12199: des dam 'cha' 'o zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12200: des gnas shing drung la dam 'cha' ba bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12201: da sman bskus te bor ba la dam 'cha' 'o //
NK028(sa)001:12203: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bya ba khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:12204: sman gyi nang nas bskus te bor ba ni rung pa rnyed kyang sla ba ste /
NK028(sa)001:12205: de la gnas na dge slong legs par gsungs pa'i chos 'dul ba la rab tu byung ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:12206: bsnyen par rdzogs pa dge slong gi dngos por 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:12207: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bya ba khyod /
NK028(sa)001:12208: ci srid 'tsho'i bar du bskus te bor ba'i sman gyis 'tsho bar spro'am /
NK028(sa)001:12209: des spro zhes brjod par bya'o /
NK028(sa)001:12210: des 'dod pa bsod snyoms kyi mtha' spangs pa bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12211: da ngal zhing dub pa'i mtha' spong bar ston pa de 'dir gda' /
NK028(sa)001:12212: lhag par rnyed na zhun mar ram /
NK028(sa)001:12214: bu ram gyi sbu ba'am dus su rung ba'am /
NK028(sa)001:12223: gzhan yang sman rung ba gang dge 'dun nam /
NK028(sa)001:12224: gang zag las rnyed na de yang khyod kyi long la tshod zin par gyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:12225: ci ltar khyod gnas 'di lta bu la dam 'cha' ba'am /
NK028(sa)001:12228: 'tsho ba rnam dag 'cha' dgos par bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12229: da bsrungs bya tshul khrims rnam dag la dam 'cha' ba la /
NK028(sa)001:12230: mtshan nyid gnyen po dpe gsum yod pa las /
NK028(sa)001:12231: dang po mtshan nyid la dam 'cha' ba la /
NK028(sa)001:12232: spang bya'i bye brag ltung ba 'gyur ba'i chos bzhi spangs bar bya ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:12233: spyi'i gnyen po dge sbyong gi chos bzhi la bslab par bya ba gnyis las /
NK028(sa)001:12234: dang po spang bya'i bye brag ltung bar 'gyur ba'i chos bzhi spangs par bya ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:12235: da phyin chad khyed kyis ltung bar 'gyur ba'i chos
NK028(sa)001:12236: bzhi po 'di rnams ngo shes par byas nas de
NK028(sa)001:12237: rnams kyi rgyud la ma goms pa'i dge slong jo
NK028(sa)001:12238: bo bzang po cig byed dgos so zhes ston pa
NK028(sa)001:12239: ni 'dir gda' / tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:12240: bzhi po 'di dag ni bcom ldan 'das de bzhin
NK028(sa)001:12241: gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK028(sa)001:12242: sangs rgyas mkhyen cing gzigs pa des /
NK028(sa)001:12243: de ltar rab tu byung ba dang bsnyen par rdzogs
NK028(sa)001:12244: pa dge slong gi ltung bar 'gyur ba'i chos su
NK028(sa)001:12245: gsungs te / dge slong gis de dag byas nas
NK028(sa)001:12246: byas ma thag tu dge slong du mi rung bar
NK028(sa)001:12247: gsungs te / 'gyur / dge sbyong du mi rung bar 'gyur /
NK028(sa)001:12249: dge slong gi dngos po las nyams par 'gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:12250: de'i dge sbyong gi tshul phyir blang du med par 'gyur ro //
