NK028(sa)001:12251: 'di lta ste dper na shing ta la'i mgo bcad na sngon por 'gyur du mi rung la /
NK028(sa)001:12252: 'phel zhing rgyas pa dang yangs par 'gyur du mi rung pa bzhin no //
NK028(sa)001:12253: des spyir rdzogs pa bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12254: da bye brag du brjod pa bstan pa ni 'dir gda' /
NK028(sa)001:12260: 'dod pa la lhag par zhen par ni /
NK028(sa)001:12261: bcom ldan 'das kyi rnam grangs du mas smad do //
NK028(sa)001:12273: tshe dang ldan pa khyod deng phyin chad chags pa'i
NK028(sa)001:12274: sems kyis bud med gyi yul la mi gtad de
NK028(sa)001:12275: / mig gis blta bar yang mi bya na /
NK028(sa)001:12276: gnyis kyi gnyis sprad de mi tshangs par spyod pa
NK028(sa)001:12277: 'khrigs pa'i chos bsten pa lta smos kyang ci dgos
NK028(sa)001:12278: / tshe dang ldan pa bcom ldan 'das de bzhin
NK028(sa)001:12279: gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag pa rdzogs pa'i
NK028(sa)001:12280: sangs rgyas mkhyen cing gzigs pa des /
NK028(sa)001:12281: yang dge slong gang dge slong rnams dang lhan cig
NK028(sa)001:12282: bslabs pa mtshungs par 'gyur bas bslab pa ma phul
NK028(sa)001:12283: bslabs pa nyams par ma byas par mi tshangs par
NK028(sa)001:12284: spyod pa 'khrig pa'i chos bsten na //
NK028(sa)001:12285: tha na dud 'gro'i skye gnas su skyes pa dang lhan cig kyang rung ste /
NK028(sa)001:12286: dge slong de yang pham par gyur pa yin gyis gnas par mi bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12287: zhes bya ba 'di bka' stsal te /
NK028(sa)001:12288: dge slong gi gnas de lta bu byas na byas ma thag tu /
NK028(sa)001:12289: dge slong du mi rung bar 'gyur /
NK028(sa)001:12291: sh+aakya'i sras kyir mi rung dge slong gi dngos po las nyams par 'gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:12292: de'i dge slong gi tshul zhig par 'gyur zhing /
NK028(sa)001:12293: nyams pa bcom pa ltung pa pham par 'gyur ba ste /
NK028(sa)001:12294: de'i dge sbyong gi tshul phyir blang du med par 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:12295: 'di lta ste dper na shing ta la'i mgo bcad
NK028(sa)001:12296: na sngon por 'gyur du mi rung ba 'phel zhing
NK028(sa)001:12297: rgyas pa dang yangs par 'gyur du mi rung pa
NK028(sa)001:12298: bzhin no // deng phyin chad khyod spyad pa ma yin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12299: bya ba ma yin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12300: spyad pa ma yin pa spangs pa de la dran pa dang bag yod pas /
NK028(sa)001:12301: sems shin du bsrungs bar brtson par gyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:12302: ji ltar gnas 'di lta bu la mi spyod dam /
NK028(sa)001:12303: des mi spyod ces brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12304: des mi tshangs par spyod pa mtha' dang bcas pa
NK028(sa)001:12305: spongs dgos pa bstan nas da ma byin par len
NK028(sa)001:12306: pa mtha' dang bcas pa spongs dgos pa bstan nas
NK028(sa)001:12307: / da ma byin par len pa mtha' dang bcas pa spongs dgos pa ston pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:12308: 'dir gda' tshe dang ldan pa khyod nyon cig ma byin par len pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:12309: bcom ldan 'das kyis rnam grangs du mar smad do ma byin par len pa spangs pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:12314: tshe dang ldan pa khyod deng phyin chad rku sems
NK028(sa)001:12315: kyi gzhan gyi til gyi phub ma tsam yang ma
NK028(sa)001:12318: ma sha ka lnga las lhag par lta smos kyang ci dgos /
NK028(sa)001:12319: tshe dang ldan pa bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs
NK028(sa)001:12320: pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK028(sa)001:12321: rgyas mkhyen cing gzigs pa des yang dge slong gang
NK028(sa)001:12322: gzhan dag gi grong na 'dug pa 'am /
NK028(sa)001:12323: dgon pa na 'dug pa ma byin pa rku ba'i grangs su gtogs pa blangs na /
NK028(sa)001:12324: ci tsam ma byin par blangs pa de /
NK028(sa)001:12325: rgyal po'i blon po chen pos gzung nas /
NK028(sa)001:12327: kye mi khyod ni rkun ma'o /
NK028(sa)001:12330: rku'o zhes zer zhing gsod dam 'ching ngam /
NK028(sa)001:12332: dge slong de ltar ma byin par len na /
NK028(sa)001:12333: dge slong de yang pham par gyur pa yin gyis gnas par mi bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12334: zhes bya ba'i 'di bka' stsal te /
NK028(sa)001:12335: dge slong gi gnas de lta bu byas na byas
NK028(sa)001:12336: ma thag tu dge slong du mi rung bar 'gyur
NK028(sa)001:12337: / dge sbyong du mi rung bar 'gyur /
NK028(sa)001:12339: dge slong gi dngos po las nyams par 'gyur te //
NK028(sa)001:12340: de'i dge sbyong gi tshul zhig par 'gyur zhing /
NK028(sa)001:12341: nyams pa bcom pa ltung ba pham par 'gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:12342: de'i dge sbyong gi tshul phyir blang du med par 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:12343: 'di lta ste dper na shing ta la'i mgo bcad na sngon por 'gyur du mi rung la /
NK028(sa)001:12344: 'phel zhing rgyas pa dang yangs par 'gyur du mi rung pa bzhin no //
NK028(sa)001:12345: deng phyin chad khyod spyad pa ma yin pa dang bya ba ma yin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12346: spyad pa ma yin pa spang ba de la dran pa dang bag yod pas /
NK028(sa)001:12347: sems shin tu bsrungs pa la btson par bgyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:12348: ji ltar khyod gnas 'di lta bu la mi spyod dam des mi spyod ces brjod par bya /
NK028(sa)001:12349: des ma byin par len pa mtha' dang bcas pa spong dgos par bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12350: da srog gcod pa mtha' dang bcas pa spongs dgos /
NK028(sa)001:12351: dgos par ston pa de 'dir gda' /
NK028(sa)001:12352: tshe dang ldan pa khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:12353: srog gcod pa bcom ldan 'das kyi rnam grangs du ma smad do //
NK028(sa)001:12354: srog gcod pa spangs pa ni bstod do //
NK028(sa)001:12358: deng phyin chad tshe dang ldan pa khyod kyi bsams pa bzhin du /
NK028(sa)001:12359: srog chags grog sbur yan chad bsad par mi bya
NK028(sa)001:12360: na mi 'am mir chags pa lta smos kyang ci
NK028(sa)001:12361: dgos tshe dang ldan pa bcom ldan 'das de bzhin
NK028(sa)001:12362: gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK028(sa)001:12363: sangs rgyas mkhyen cing gzigs pa des /
NK028(sa)001:12364: yang dge slong gis mi'am mir chags pa la bsams
NK028(sa)001:12365: bzhin du rang gi lag bdar de srog bcad dam
NK028(sa)001:12367: de la mtshon thogs par gnyer gtad dam /
NK028(sa)001:12369: de la 'chi ba'i sngags pa brjod kyang rung te /
NK028(sa)001:12371: kyee mi khyod gson pas shi sla'o //
NK028(sa)001:12372: zhes zer zhing sems kyi 'dod pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12373: sems kyi kun tu rtog pa dag gis rnam grangs du mas de phyir 'jug gam /
NK028(sa)001:12374: de la 'chi ba'i basngagasa pa brjod de /
NK028(sa)001:12375: de yang rtsol ba des dus byas na /
NK028(sa)001:12376: dge slong de yang pham par gyur par yin gyis /
NK028(sa)001:12378: zhes bya ba bka' stsal ste /
NK028(sa)001:12379: dge slong gi gnas de lta bu byas na /
NK028(sa)001:12380: byas ma thag tu dge slong du mi rung par 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:12383: de'i dge sbyong gi dngos po las nyams par 'gyur te dge sbyong gi tshul zhig par 'gyur zhing /
NK028(sa)001:12384: nyams pa bcom pa ltung pa pham par 'gyur ba te //
NK028(sa)001:12385: de'i dge slong gi tshul phyir blang du med par 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:12388: shing ta la'i mgo bcad na sngon por 'gyur du
NK028(sa)001:12389: mi rung la 'phel zhing rgyas pa dang yangs par
NK028(sa)001:12390: 'gyur du mi rung ba bzhin no //
NK028(sa)001:12391: de'i phyin chad khyed spyad pa ma yin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12392: bya ba ma yin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12393: sbyad pa ma yin pa spangs ba de la dran
NK028(sa)001:12394: pa dang bag yod pas sems shin tu bsrungs ba
NK028(sa)001:12396: ji ltar khyod gnas 'di lta bu la mi spyod dam /
NK028(sa)001:12397: des mi spyod ces brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12398: des srog gcod pa mtha' dag dang bcas pa spongs dgos par bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12399: da brdzun du smra ba mtha' dang bcas pa spongs dgos par ston pa 'dir gda' /
NK028(sa)001:12400: tshe dang ldan pa khyod nyon cig brdzun du smra ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:12401: bcom ldan 'das kyis rnam grangs du ma smad do //
NK028(sa)001:12402: brdzun du smra ba spangs pa ni bstod do /
NK028(sa)001:12406: tshe dang ldan pa khyod deng phyin chad tha na bzhad gad bya par bsam te /
NK028(sa)001:12408: brdzun du smra bar yang mi bya na /
NK028(sa)001:12409: bsams bzhin du mi'i chos bla ma smra ba lta smos kyang ci dgos tshe dang ldan pa /
NK028(sa)001:12410: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa
NK028(sa)001:12411: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mkhyen cing gzigs
NK028(sa)001:12412: pa des / yang dge slong gang mngon par mi
NK028(sa)001:12413: shes shing yongs su mi shes la mi'i chos bla
NK028(sa)001:12414: ma mtha' dag dang 'phags pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12418: reg pa spyod pa med la /
NK028(sa)001:12420: 'di mthong ngo zhes khas che ba las /
NK028(sa)001:12421: de ltung ba byung ba rnam par dag par 'dod nas /
NK028(sa)001:12422: dus gzhan zhig ni dris kyang rung ma dris kyang rung /
NK028(sa)001:12423: 'di skad ces tshe dang ldan pa dag bdag gis ni mi shes par shes so //
NK028(sa)001:12425: ma mthong par mthong ngo zhes smras te //
NK028(sa)001:12426: bsog bsog brdzun du smras so //
NK028(sa)001:12427: zhes zer nas mngon pa'i nga rgyal ma gtogs te /
NK028(sa)001:12428: dge slong de yang pham par gyur pa yin gyis /
NK028(sa)001:12430: zhes bya ba 'di bka' stsal te /
NK028(sa)001:12438: gnod sbyin rnams dang nam 'kha' lding rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:12441: lto 'phye chen po rnams dang dri za rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:12443: sha za rnams dang grul bum rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:12446: dur khrod gyi sha za rnams kyi sgra thos so //
NK028(sa)001:12447: lha rnams kyi sgra thos so //
NK028(sa)001:12459: dur khrod kyi sha za rnams kyis kyang dag gi sgra thos so //
NK028(sa)001:12465: mi'am ci rnams dang lto 'phye chen po rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:12471: dur khrod kyi sha za rnams lta ba'i phyir 'agro'o //
NK028(sa)001:12477: mi'am ci rnams dang lto 'phye chen po rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:12483: dur khrod kyi sha za rnams lta ba'i phyir 'ong ngo /
NK028(sa)001:12484: lha rnams dang lhan gcig gtam 'dre bar bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12486: so sor kun dga' bar byed /
NK028(sa)001:12487: rtag tu yang lhan cig gnas par byed do //
NK028(sa)001:12488: klu rnams dang gnod sbyin rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:12498: dur khrod kyi sha za rnams blta ba'i phyir 'ong ngo /
NK028(sa)001:12499: lha rnams dang lhan gcig gtam 'dre bar bya'o /
NK028(sa)001:12501: so sor kun dga' bar byed /
NK028(sa)001:12502: rtag tu yang lhan cig gnas par byed do //
NK028(sa)001:12514: dur khrod kyi sha za rnams bdag dang lhan cig gtam 'dre bar byed /
NK028(sa)001:12516: so sor kun dga' bar byed /
NK028(sa)001:12517: rtag tu yang lhan cig gnas par byed do //
NK028(sa)001:12518: ma thob bzhin du bdag gis mi rtag pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12519: mi rtag pa la sdug bsngal ba'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12520: sdug bsngal ba la bdag med pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12521: zas la mi mthun pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12522: 'jig rten thams cad la mngon par mi dga' ba'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12525: 'dod chags dang bral ba'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12529: rnam par bsdos pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12530: rnam par gnag pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12531: rnam par bam pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12532: rnam par 'bus gzhig pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12533: rnam par zos pa'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12534: rnam par dmar ba'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12535: rnam par mthor ba'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12537: stong pa nyid du so sor rtogs pa'i 'du shes thob bo //
NK028(sa)001:12538: ma thob bzhin du bdag gi bsam gtan dang po dang /
NK028(sa)001:12546: nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched dang /
NK028(sa)001:12547: rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched dang /
NK028(sa)001:12548: ci yang med pa'i skye mched dang /
NK028(sa)001:12549: 'du shes med 'du shes med min kyi skye mched dang /
NK028(sa)001:12550: rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu dang /
NK028(sa)001:12551: lan cig phyir 'ong ba'i 'bras bu dang /
NK028(sa)001:12556: sems kyi rnam grangs dang sngon gyi gnas dang /
NK028(sa)001:12559: zag pa zad pa thob po //
NK028(sa)001:12560: bdag ni dgra bcom pa rnam par thar pa brgyad la bsam gtan pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12561: gnyis ka'i cha las rnam par grol ba yin no //
NK028(sa)001:12562: zhes bya ba te dge slong gi gnas 'di lta
NK028(sa)001:12563: bu byas na byas ma thag du dge slong mi
NK028(sa)001:12564: rung bar 'gyur / dge sbyong du mi rung /
NK028(sa)001:12565: sh+aakya'i sras kyir mi rung bar 'gyur /
NK028(sa)001:12566: dge slong gi dngos po las nyams par 'gyur te /
NK028(sa)001:12567: de'i dge sbyong gi tshul zhig par 'gyur zhing /
NK028(sa)001:12568: nyams pa bcom pa lta bu pham par 'gyur ba ste /
NK028(sa)001:12569: de dge sbyong gi tshul phyir blang du med par 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:12571: shing ta la'i mgo bcad na /
NK028(sa)001:12572: sngon por 'gyur du mi rung la /
NK028(sa)001:12573: 'phel zhing rgyas pa dang yangs par 'gyur du mi rung ba bzhin no /
NK028(sa)001:12574: de phyin chad khyod spyod pa ma yin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12575: bya ba ma yin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12576: spyod pa ma yin pa spangs pa de la dran pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12577: bag yod pas sems shin du bsrungs ba la brtson par gyis shig /
NK028(sa)001:12578: ji ltar khyod gnas 'di lta bu la mi spyod dam /
NK028(sa)001:12579: des mi spyod ces brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12580: des spang bya'i bye brag ltung bar 'gyur ba chos bzhi spang bar bya ba bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12581: da spyi'i gnyen po dge spyong du byed pa'i chos bzhi la bslab par bya ba ston pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:12582: deng phyin chad khyod kyis dge sbyong du byed pa'i
NK028(sa)001:12583: chos bzhi la gnas nas gzhan gnod pa byed pa'i
NK028(sa)001:12584: lan tsam yang byar med do zhes ston pa 'dir
NK028(sa)001:12585: gda' / tshe dang ldan pa khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:12587: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa
NK028(sa)001:12588: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mkhyen cing gzigs
NK028(sa)001:12589: pa des / de ltar rab tu byung ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:12590: bsnyen par rdzogs pa dge slong gi dge sbyong du byed pa'i chos su gsungs te /
NK028(sa)001:12592: tshe dang ldan pa khyod kyis da phyin chad gshe yang slar mi gshe bar bya ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:12593: khros kyang slar mi khro bar byed pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12594: brdeg kyang slar mi rdeg par bya ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:12595: mtshang brus kyang slar mtshang mi 'bru bar bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12596: ji ltar gnas 'di lta bu la spyod dam /
NK028(sa)001:12597: des spyod ces brjod par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12598: des dge sbyong gi chos bzhi la bslab par bya
NK028(sa)001:12599: ba de'i gong mas ltung bar 'gyur ba'i chos bzhi
NK028(sa)001:12600: spang par bya ba don gnyis po de mtshan nyid
NK028(sa)001:12602: da bsnyen pa la dam 'cha' ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:12603: khyod sngon legs par gsungs pa'i chos 'dul ba rab tu byung ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:12604: bsnyen par rdzogs pa dge slong gi sdom pa thob
NK028(sa)001:12605: na dga' snyam pa'i smon pa gang yin ba'i sdom
NK028(sa)001:12606: pa de mkhan po 'os pa la sogs pa rgyu
NK028(sa)001:12607: phun sum tshogs pa las grub cing /
NK028(sa)001:12608: rgyu de las byung ba'i 'bras bu sdom pa yang phun sum tshogs pa mchog tu gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:12610: tshe dang ldan pa khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:12611: khyod sngon legs par gsung pa'i chos 'dul ba la rab tu byung pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12612: bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i dge slong gis dngos po thob
NK028(sa)001:12613: kyang ci ma rung snyam du smon pa gang yin
NK028(sa)001:12614: pa de / de khyod mkhan po 'os ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:12618: bzhi las mi g.yo zhing bzhag par mi 'os pas rab tu byung zhing bsnyen par rdzogs so //
NK028(sa)001:12619: des bsnyen pa la dam 'cha' ba bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12620: gsum pa de la dam bca' ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:12622: nga gsar bu yin pas sdom pa bsrungs mi shes la bsrungs kyang mi dgos mnyam na /
NK028(sa)001:12623: 'jig rten na ma'i me long mi bya ba yin pas dge slong rgan po bzang po rnams /
NK028(sa)001:12624: ci ltar bdud dung ba bzhin du bsrungs dgos /
NK028(sa)001:12625: nga gsar bu yin pas de dang mi 'dra snyam na /
NK028(sa)001:12626: bsnyen par rdzogs nas lo brgya lon pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12627: de ring bsnyen pa rdzogs pa gnyis mnyam pa nyid gsum kyis mnyam ste /
NK028(sa)001:12628: rang bzhin gyi kha na ma tha ba spongs pa'i
NK028(sa)001:12629: tshul khrims su mnyam byas ba'i kha na ma thob
NK028(sa)001:12630: spong ba'i bslab par mnyam chos kyi longs spyod so
NK028(sa)001:12631: sor thar pa 'i mdo 'don pa nyid kyis mnyam
NK028(sa)001:12632: pas de bzhin du bsgrub dgos shes ston pa de
NK028(sa)001:12633: 'dir gda' / tshe dang ldan pa khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:12634: bsnyen par rdzogs nas lo brgya lon pa'i dge slong
NK028(sa)001:12635: gi slab bya de la de ring bsnyen par rdzogs
NK028(sa)001:12637: de ring bsnyen pa rdzogs pa'i dge slong gis bslab
NK028(sa)001:12638: pa gang la bslab par bya ba de la bsnyen
NK028(sa)001:12639: par rdzogs nas lo brgya lon pas kyang bslab po
NK028(sa)001:12640: / de ltar tshul khrims nyid kyis mnyam pa dang
NK028(sa)001:12641: bslab pa nyid kyis mnyam pa dang so so thar
NK028(sa)001:12642: ba'i mdo 'don pa nyid kyis mnyam pa de /
NK028(sa)001:12643: khyod kyi deng phyin chad bsgrub par bya yis /
NK028(sa)001:12645: des dpe de'i gong mas gnyen po de'i gong mas mtshan nyid don gsum po des /
NK028(sa)001:12646: bsrung bya tshul khrims rnam dag la dam 'cha' ba bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12647: da rtogs don lta ba rnam dag la dam 'cha' ba ston pa la /
NK028(sa)001:12648: lta ba'i gnas la gus pa skyed pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12649: lta ba dngos sbyangs pa gnyis las //
NK028(sa)001:12650: dang po lta ba'i gnas la gus pa bskyed pa la //
NK028(sa)001:12651: rkyen gtso bo mkhan po la gus pa skyed pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:12652: phal pa grogs la gus pa bskyed pa gnyis las //
NK028(sa)001:12653: dang po gtso bo mkhan po la gus pa bskyed pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:12654: khyod kyis mkhan po la pha'i 'du shes bskyed nas bsnyen bkur byed dgos la /
NK028(sa)001:12655: mkhan pos kyang khyod la bu'i 'du shes bzhag nas
NK028(sa)001:12656: nad g.yog byed dgos shes ston pa deng 'dir gda'
NK028(sa)001:12657: / deng phyin chad khyod kyis mkhan po la pha'i 'du shes nye bar bzhag par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12658: mkhan pos kyang khyod la bu'i 'du shes nye bar bzhag par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12659: khyod kyi mkhan po la ji srid 'tsho'i bar du bsnyen bskur bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12660: mkhan po kyang khyod shi 'am sos kyi bar nad g.yog bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12661: des rkyen gtso bo mkhan po la gus pa skyed pa bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12662: da phal pa grogs la gus pa bya ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:12663: tshangs par spyod pa grogs la rag las par gsungs pas /
NK028(sa)001:12664: grogs rgan gzhon 'bring gsum la lus ngag yid gsum
NK028(sa)001:12665: gyis gus par byed dgos shes ston pa de 'dir
NK028(sa)001:12666: gda' / deng phyin chad khyod kyis tshangs par mtshungs pa spyod pa rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:12669: gsar bu rnams la gus pa dang bcas pa dang zhes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12671: 'jigs pa dang bcas pa'i dbang du gyur pa'i gnas par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12672: des phal pa grogs la gus pa bskyed pa /
NK028(sa)001:12674: rkyen gtso bo mkhan po la gus pa ba skyed pa /
NK028(sa)001:12675: don gnyis pa des gnas la gus pa bskyed pa bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12676: da lta ba dngos sbyangs pa ston pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:12677: bsnyen par rdzogs nas dal bar bsdad mi chog /
NK028(sa)001:12678: thos bsam sgom gsum la 'bad rtsol chen po byed dgos ste /
NK028(sa)001:12680: tshul gnas thos dang bsam ldan pas /
NK028(sa)001:12681: sgom pa la ni rab tu sbyar //
NK028(sa)001:12683: sde snod gsum la mkhas par byas nas /
NK028(sa)001:12684: tshul khrims la sogs pa'i phung po gsum thob pa dang rtogs pa dang mngon du byed dgos //
NK028(sa)001:12686: deng phyin chad khyod kyi lung nod par bya //
NK028(sa)001:12687: bklag par bya kha don du bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12688: phung po la mkhas pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12690: skye mched la mkhas pa dang rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba la mkhas pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12691: gnas dang gnas ma yin pa la mkhas par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:12692: ma thob pa thob par bya ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:12693: ma rtogs pa rtogs par bya ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:12694: mngon sum du ma byas pa mngon du bya ba'i phyir khyod kyis /
NK028(sa)001:12696: des lta ba sbyangs pa dngos de'i gong mas lta ba'i gnas la gus pa bskyed pa /
NK028(sa)001:12697: don gnyis po des rtogs don lta ba rnam dag /
NK028(sa)001:12698: de'i gong mas bsrungs bya tshul khrims rnam dag de'i gong mas rten bsam 'tsho ba rnam dag /
NK028(sa)001:12699: don gsum po des rang smin par bya ba'i chos brjod pa brten nas /
NK028(sa)001:12700: da cho ga rnam par dag pa'i sgo nas gzhan la shes 'gyur gyi brjod pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:12701: 'di cho ga'i skabs yin pas bslab pa'i gzhi che long tsam las ma brjod pa yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:12702: rgyas par so sor thar pa'i mdo 'don pa'i tshe dang /
NK028(sa)001:12705: grogs rnams la nyon la shes par gyis shig ces ston pa de 'dir gda' /
NK028(sa)001:12706: 'di dag ni kho bos khyod la slob pa'i che long tsam zhig brjod par zad do //
NK028(sa)001:12707: gzhan dag ni zla ba phyed phyed cing so so
NK028(sa)001:12708: thar pa'i mdo 'don pa'i tshe thos par 'gyur ro
NK028(sa)001:12711: mkhan po dang mkhan po gcig pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:12716: 'grogs shes rnams kyang rgya cher ston par 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:12717: des cho ga rnam par dag pa'i sgo nas gzhan las shes 'gyur gyis brjod pa /
NK028(sa)001:12718: de'i gong mas rang smin par bya ba'i chos brjod pa /
NK028(sa)001:12719: don gnyis po des bslab bya yul brjod pa bstan nas /
NK028(sa)001:12720: da slob byed gnyen po brjod pa ston pa la /
NK028(sa)001:12721: gus pa la sbyor ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:12722: spong byed kyis gnyen po dang po gnyis las /
NK028(sa)001:12723: dang po la gus pa la sbyar ba ston ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:12724: bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i sdom pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:12725: shin du rnyed par dka' ba las /
NK028(sa)001:12727: mi khom pa'i gnas brgyad spangs shing /
NK028(sa)001:12728: 'byor ba'i chos bcu thob pa shin tu rnyed par dka' ba las //
NK028(sa)001:12729: rnyed cing thob pa yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:12730: ci skad bshad pa bzhin du sgrubs shig /
NK028(sa)001:12732: shes rab mchog gi bstan pa la //
NK028(sa)001:12733: khyod ni bsnyen par rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK028(sa)001:12734: dal dang 'byor pa rnyed dka' bas //
NK028(sa)001:12735: 'di dag ji ltar bzhin du bsgrubs //
NK028(sa)001:12736: mdzes pa rab tu dbyung ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:12737: yongs su dag pa bsnyen rdzogs par //
NK028(sa)001:12738: rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi rab mkhyen de //
NK028(sa)001:12739: bden pa'i mtshan gyis bka' brtsal to //
NK028(sa)001:12740: de gus pa la sbyar ba bstan nas //
NK028(sa)001:12741: da spong byed kyi gnyen po dngos ni //
NK028(sa)001:12742: dge slong dag gis bag yod par sgrubs shig /
NK028(sa)001:12744: de'i don dran shes bzhin bag yod kyis zin par bgyid la bslab pa legs par bsrungs shig /
NK028(sa)001:12746: tshe dang ldan pa khyod bsnyen par rdzogs zin gyis bag yod par sgrubs shig /
NK028(sa)001:12747: de ltar sbyor dngos mjug gsum gyis /
NK028(sa)001:12748: khyod kyi rgyud la bsnyen rdzogs kyi sdom pa bsrungs thabs dang bcas pa thob pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:12749: mi yi srid pa legs par thob //
NK028(sa)001:12750: de ring sangs rgyas rigs su skyes //
NK028(sa)001:12751: sangs rgyas sras su da gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:12752: ces pa de lta bu cig thob pa yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:12753: de mkhan slob dge 'dun dang bcas pa'i bka' drin las thob pa yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:12754: phyag gsum tshol la bka' drin che'o //
NK028(sa)001:12756: 'di dag ni bla ma'i gsung las byon pa lag
NK028(sa)001:12757: tu blang pa'i rim pa mdo tsam zhig brjod pa
NK028(sa)001:12758: yin rgyas par ni lung dang bstan chos las shes
NK028(sa)001:12759: par bya'o // lag len yid bzhin nor bu zhes
NK028(sa)001:12760: bya ba skal ldan rnams re ba skong par byed
NK028(sa)001:12761: par bya'o // pa 'dis ni / 'gro don lhun grub shog /
NK028(sa)001:12764: bcu gcig pa rin chen dor ba dang bcu gnyis pa lha dbab pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:12765: bcu gsum pa lha bsgom par nan tan du bya ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:12766: bcu bzhi pa mig dbye ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:12767: bzhi po gong dang mtshungs la //
NK028(sa)001:12768: bco lnga pa lha ngo bstan pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:12769: 'o mdun na yod pa'i nyan thos kyi dkyil 'khor brten dang rten pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:12770: phyi rol du me ri rdo rje'i rwa ba /
NK028(sa)001:12771: pad skor de yi nang du gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi /
NK028(sa)001:12772: rgyan rta babs dang bcas pa /
NK028(sa)001:12773: de'i nang du pad 'dab bcu drug /
NK028(sa)001:12774: de'i nang du pad 'dab bzhi'i lte ba dang bcas pa mngon sum du mthong ba'i mos pa mdzod /
NK028(sa)001:12775: pad+ma'i lte bar bcom ldan 'das rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa /
NK028(sa)001:12777: 'dab ma bcu drug la nyan thos chen po bcu drug bzhugs te /
NK028(sa)001:12778: de yang sku snang la rang bzhin med pa me
NK028(sa)001:12779: long nang gi gzugs brnyan bzhin mngon sum du mthong
NK028(sa)001:12780: ba de / khyed rang rnams kyi yi dam gyi lha skal yin snyam pa'i mos pa mdzod cig /
NK028(sa)001:12781: bcu drug pa tshogs mchod dang yon gong dang mtshungs so //
NK028(sa)001:12782: spyi don gnyis pa dbang bskur ba la gsum ste /
NK028(sa)001:12785: dang po ni gong dang mthun no //
NK028(sa)001:12786: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gsum ste //
NK028(sa)001:12789: gsang dbang zab mo'i dbang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:12790: dang po bum pa'i dbang dang //
NK028(sa)001:12799: dgu po gong dang mthun la //
NK028(sa)001:12800: bye brag tu bcu pa phyag rgya'i dbang la /
NK028(sa)001:12804: bstim gnas sgrib pa gang dag /
NK028(sa)001:12809: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus nas sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa'i
NK028(sa)001:12810: tshogs rnams byon nas khyed rang rnams la thim pas
NK028(sa)001:12811: khyed rang rnams kyi phung po khams skye mched dang
NK028(sa)001:12812: gnyis su med par bsgom mdzod /
NK028(sa)001:12814: dang por byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed nas /
NK028(sa)001:12815: bar du grangs med gsum la tshogs gnyis bsags /
NK028(sa)001:12816: tha mar mdzad pa bcu gnyis rdzogs sangs rgyas /
NK028(sa)001:12817: thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang bskur lhun grub shog /
NK028(sa)001:12820: bstim gnas phung po skye mched la bstim //
NK028(sa)001:12821: sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang skye /
NK028(sa)001:12822: phung po khams skye mched rang ka mar 'dzin pa'i dri ma dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:12823: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor lhun grub pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:12824: sangs rgyas thub pa'i dngos po 'khor dge slong pho //
NK028(sa)001:12825: sdug bsngal bden pa nyer len phung po dang //
NK028(sa)001:12826: kun 'byung bden pa las dang nyon mongs dang //
NK028(sa)001:12827: 'gog ba'i bden pa sdug bsngal zhi ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:12828: lam gyi bden pa gang zag bdag med dang //
NK028(sa)001:12829: 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras spangs shing 'das pa bsgrub pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:12830: phung po lhag bcas lhag med mya ngan las //
NK028(sa)001:12831: 'das nas dgra bcom sa la phyin par shog /
NK028(sa)001:12832: sarba sa ni sa tam a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:12834: rigs kyi bu khyod la bden pa bzhi'i dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:12835: 'phags pa dgra bcom pa'i sa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:12836: sangs rgyas thub pa'i dngos po 'khor dge slong mo //
NK028(sa)001:12837: sdug bsngal bden pa nyer len phung po dang //
NK028(sa)001:12838: kun 'byung bden pa las dang nyon mongs dang //
NK028(sa)001:12839: 'gog pa'i bden pa sdug bsngal zhi ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:12840: lam gyi bden pa gang zag bdag med la //
NK028(sa)001:12841: 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras spangs shing 'das pa bsgrub pa yis /
NK028(sa)001:12842: phung po lhag med mya ngan las //
NK028(sa)001:12843: 'das nas dgra bcom sa la phyin par shog /
NK028(sa)001:12844: sarba sa ni sa tam a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:12846: rigs kyi bu khyod la bden pa bzhi'i dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:12847: 'phags pa dgra bcom pa'i sa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:12848: sangs rgyas thub pa'i dngos slob dge tshul pho /
NK028(sa)001:12849: sdug bsngal bden pa nyer len phung po dang /
NK028(sa)001:12850: kun 'byung bden pa las dang nyon mongs dang /
NK028(sa)001:12851: 'gog pa'i bden pa sdug bsngal zhi ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:12852: lam gyi bden pa gang zag bdag med la /
NK028(sa)001:12853: 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras spangs shing 'das pa bsgrub pa yis /
NK028(sa)001:12854: phung po lhag bcas lhag med mya ngan las /
NK028(sa)001:12855: 'das nas dgra bcom sa la phyin par shog /
NK028(sa)001:12856: sarba sa ni sa tam a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:12857: bden pa 'dre rigs kyi bu khyod la bden pa bzhi'i dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:12858: 'phags pa dgra bcom pa'i sa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:12859: sangs rgyas thub pa'i dngos slob dge tshul mo //
NK028(sa)001:12860: sdug bsngal bden pa nyer len phung po dang //
NK028(sa)001:12861: kun 'byung bden pa las dang nyon mongs dang //
NK028(sa)001:12862: 'gog pa'i bden pa sdug bsngal zhi ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:12863: lam gyi bden pa gang zag bdag med la //
NK028(sa)001:12864: 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras spangs shing 'das pa bsgrub pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:12865: phung po lhag bcas lhag med mya ngan las //
NK028(sa)001:12866: 'das nas dgra bcom sa la phyin par shog /
NK028(sa)001:12867: sarba sa ni sa tam a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum //
NK028(sa)001:12869: rigs kyi bu khyod la bden pa bzhi'i dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:12870: 'phags pa dgra bcom pa'i sa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:12871: gcung dga' bo'i dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:12872: sh+aakya'i gcung gi dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:12873: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:12875: sgra gcan 'dzin gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:12876: bcom ldan sras kyi dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:12877: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:12879: sha ri bu yi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:12880: shes rab chen po'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:12881: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:12883: mo'u gal bu yi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:12884: rdzu 'phrul mchog gi dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:12885: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:12888: 'dri zhing lan lon dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:12889: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:12891: nye 'khor bu yi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:12893: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:12896: rdzu 'phrul spyan lnga dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:12897: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye swah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:12899: cang shes ko'u de nas dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:12900: ston par chos thob lnga ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:12901: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye swah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:12903: nye 'khor gzugs kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:12905: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye swah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:12907: rta thul gzugs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:12908: bdud tshogs dad pa skye ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:12909: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye swah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:12911: ba glang bdag gi dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:12913: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye swah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:12915: kun dga' bo'i gzugs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:12916: zhabs 'bring rtags mdzad dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:12917: mu ne a b+hi ming chen gzugs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:12918: shang gnyis skra breg dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:12919: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:12920: nor sbyin 'dzin gyi dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:12921: bslab pa la gus dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:12922: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne swah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:12924: tshe ldan gang pos dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:12925: sbyangs ba'i yon tan dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:12926: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye swah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:12928: 'od bsrungs gzugs kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:12929: zhal zla sku 'dres dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:12930: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye swah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:12935: sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang skyed phung po
NK028(sa)001:12936: khams skye mched rang dgar 'dzin pa'i dri ma dag
NK028(sa)001:12937: / bden rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:12938: gnyis pa nus pa'i dbang la lnga ste /
NK028(sa)001:12943: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byam gyis dbang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:12944: dbang de lnga'i cho ga yang gong dang mthun /
NK028(sa)001:12945: gsum pa gsang dbang zab mo'ii dbang la gsum te /
NK028(sa)001:12946: gsang dbang shes rab ye shes kyi dbang dang /
NK028(sa)001:12947: dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang de gsum gyis don ni /
NK028(sa)001:12948: lam khyer gsum po bshad la sgom du bzhugs /
NK028(sa)001:12949: de nas dbang mi nyams par bya ba'i phyir 'debs chung gcig bya na /
NK028(sa)001:12950: rang gi dpral bar rus pa'i thig le nyung dkar tsam cig bsgom /
NK028(sa)001:12951: de la shes pa gtad pas thig le de je
NK028(sa)001:12952: cher la snang srid thams cad keng rus kyi dal
NK028(sa)001:12953: du bsam / de yang yul rang rgyud pa la
NK028(sa)001:12954: bstan pa la bstan na chags sdang rmongs gsum skye
NK028(sa)001:12955: ste nyon mongs pa 'khor ba'i rgyu yin /
NK028(sa)001:12956: der 'bras bu sdug bsngal gyi bden pa nyams su myong pa yin te /
NK028(sa)001:12957: de'i gnyen por rus pa'i 'khor lo yul mi sdug pa bsgoms pas /
NK028(sa)001:12958: nyon mongs pa chags sdang mi skye /
NK028(sa)001:12959: kun 'byung gis nyon mongs pa brtsad bcad nas /
NK028(sa)001:12960: 'bras bu sdug bsngal rang bzhin gyis 'gogs pas de ka lam gyi bden pa yin gsung ngo //
NK028(sa)001:12961: theg pa lam khyer gyi dbang du byas na nyan thos gzung 'dzin /
NK028(sa)001:12962: don dam 'dod pa lta ba la sogs pa gong gis 'gres /
NK028(sa)001:12963: bsgom chen gyi 'dug tshul ni mi blo phal po sdug gtam gtong pa lta bu'o //
NK028(sa)001:12964: mi dge ba bcu dgra dang tsher ma bzhin du bltas na spongs /
NK028(sa)001:12965: dge bcu sman dang phan pa'i zas ltar len de yang nyan thos la 'du shes bcu ste //
NK028(sa)001:12966: srog gcod pa la btsan dug lta bu'i 'du shes dang //
NK028(sa)001:12967: nyon mongs pa la dug sbrul lta ba'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12968: kha zas la mtha' 'khob kyi rgan rgon lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12969: gos la smad dkris lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12970: rnyed pa dang bkur sti la rgya dang snyi lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12971: bla ma dang dkon mchog la nor bu rin po che lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12972: chos la lam lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12973: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la gser lta bu'i 'du shes dang //
NK028(sa)001:12974: tshul khrims la rgyan lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK028(sa)001:12975: chos nyid mngon du gyur pa la mun khung du
NK028(sa)001:12976: sgron me btegs pa lta bu'i 'du shes dang bcu'o
NK028(sa)001:12977: // de don ni dbang rdo rje zab pa las kyang bshad do //
NK028(sa)001:12978: nyan thos kyi gag drug ni gnas ba ra na si'i bsil khang du //
NK028(sa)001:12979: ston pa sh+aakya thub pa chen po yin //
NK028(sa)001:12980: 'khor mchog chen po brgyad la sogs pa la bden pa bzhis dbang bskur nas /
NK028(sa)001:12981: 'bras bu dgra bcom pa thob pa de dgos pa
NK028(sa)001:12982: mu stegs rtag chad rang rgyud du 'dod pa las
NK028(sa)001:12985: gang gi gang la gang du gang bstan pa //
NK028(sa)001:12986: ci yis phyir gyis dgos par bcas pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:12987: 'di ni nyan thos theg pa'i gag drug yin /
NK028(sa)001:12993: tshogs dang dga' ston rgya chen po bya //
NK028(sa)001:12994: glu gar dang rtse 'jo'i nyams skyangs /
NK028(sa)001:12998: gshegs gsol byas la dkyil 'khor bsdu //
NK028(sa)001:12999: des ni nyan thos kyi dbang gi thems skas rdzogs so //////
NK028(sa)001:13000: dang po phyi dbang gi chu bo las /
NK028(sa)001:13001: rang sangs rgyas kyi dbang gi them skas bzhugs so //
NK028(sa)001:13002: gsum pa rang sangs rgyas kyi dbang la gnyis ste /
NK028(sa)001:13003: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:13004: 'jug cing dbang bskur ba'i rim pa'o /
NK028(sa)001:13007: tshad dang ldan pa'i sa stegs la //
NK028(sa)001:13008: dri bzang chu yis chag chag gdab //
NK028(sa)001:13009: byin brlabs ldan pa'i thig skud kyis /
NK028(sa)001:13010: thig brgyad spyi dang 'dra ba la /
NK028(sa)001:13011: shwad d+ha ka ri'i thig rtsa bzhin /
NK028(sa)001:13012: lo ma thang gsum bskyed la bdag /
NK028(sa)001:13013: cha chen bcu drug byung ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:13014: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK028(sa)001:13015: gnyis pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab /
NK028(sa)001:13016: gsum pa bzhi pa dor bar bya //
NK028(sa)001:13017: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK028(sa)001:13018: drug pa phyed gda' phyi ma gdab //
NK028(sa)001:13019: bdun pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK028(sa)001:13020: brgyad pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab /
NK028(sa)001:13021: de nas mu khyud bskor ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:13022: cha phran drug nas lte ba bskor //
NK028(sa)001:13023: mdun nas de yi mu khyud phyi //
NK028(sa)001:13024: bcu bzhi'i so nas pad 'dab bskor //
NK028(sa)001:13025: bco lnga de yis mu khyud phyi //
NK028(sa)001:13026: glang gur rdo ra gong dang 'dra //
NK028(sa)001:13027: mda' yab zur thig phrad so nas //
NK028(sa)001:13028: pad 'dab rdo ra me ri la //
NK028(sa)001:13029: ci rigs 'tshams pas bskor bar bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:13030: byin brlabs ldan pa'i tshon rtsi yis //
NK028(sa)001:13031: mkhas pas re kha legs par bri /
NK028(sa)001:13032: lte ba dmar po yang na sngo /
NK028(sa)001:13033: pad 'dab bcu gnyis mdzes tshon byed //
NK028(sa)001:13034: gru chad rtsig sogs gong dang mthun //
NK028(sa)001:13035: de nas rnam pa bkod pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:13036: dbus su sh+aakya thub pa'i gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:13038: rang rgyal bcu gnyis tsaka li bkod //
NK028(sa)001:13039: gsung thugs rten ni nyan thos mtshungs //
NK028(sa)001:13040: chad lhag bsal zhing ga zhal gsol mchod //
NK028(sa)001:13041: mchod yon la sogs phyi mchod dang //
NK028(sa)001:13042: gtor ma bsham pa la sogs dang //
NK028(sa)001:13043: bum sogs bsham pa gong dang mtshungs //
NK028(sa)001:13044: de ni bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:13045: de nas rab gnas kyi dod ni //
NK028(sa)001:13046: dpon slob rnams gdan la bzhugs shing /
NK028(sa)001:13047: sngon 'gro gtor ma cha bzhi'am cha gcig bshams la //
NK028(sa)001:13048: byin gyis brlabs la bsngo zhing //
NK028(sa)001:13050: mchod pa byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:13051: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed rnams gong bzhin sngon du song nas /
NK028(sa)001:13055: b+h+r+aum las rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal med khang pa grub bzhi sgo bzhi /
NK028(sa)001:13056: rgyan rta babs dang bcas pa'i nang du /
NK028(sa)001:13057: pad+ma 'dab ma bcu gnyis kyi dbus su /
NK028(sa)001:13058: rin po che dang seng ge'i khri'i steng du pad+ma dang zla ba'i gdan la /
NK028(sa)001:13059: bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa sku mdog ser po /
NK028(sa)001:13061: g.yon mnyam bzhag chos gos ngur smrig sku la gsol ba /
NK028(sa)001:13062: zhabs rdo rje dkyil mo dkrung du bzhugs pa /
NK028(sa)001:13063: de'i phyi rol gyi pad 'dab bcu gnyis kyi shar
NK028(sa)001:13064: nas rim pa bzhin du gdung ba sel ba bsil
NK028(sa)001:13065: yab 'dzin pa // snang ba brtsegs pa rin po che'i mdzod 'dzin pa //
NK028(sa)001:13066: 'jigs pa med pa rdo rje 'dzin pa //
NK028(sa)001:13067: dpa' bo 'dul ba rdo rje 'dzin pa //
NK028(sa)001:13068: shes rab mgyogs chen zla tshes 'dzin pa //
NK028(sa)001:13069: ri bo'i rgyal po rin po che'i snye ma 'dzin pa //
NK028(sa)001:13070: smra ba sgra chen bsam gtan gyi phyag rgya mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:13071: bse ru lta bu mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:13073: rdzu 'phrul cher ston me 'bar ba bsnams pa /
NK028(sa)001:13074: seng ge'i sgra rdo rje 'dzin pa //
NK028(sa)001:13075: yid myur ba bsil yab 'dzin pa /
NK028(sa)001:13076: yang na thams cad kyang lhung bzed dang mkhar bsil 'dzin cing /
NK028(sa)001:13077: chos gos ngur smrig gyon te /
NK028(sa)001:13078: dbu'i gtsug gtor cung zad byas pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:13079: lha tshogs de rnams kyi spyi bor /
NK028(sa)001:13082: de las 'od zer 'phros rang bzhin gyis gnas nas ye shes pa snyan gsan dbab /
NK028(sa)001:13085: phyag 'tshal mchod pa 'bul ba rnams ci rigs par bya /
NK028(sa)001:13087: thabs mkhas thugs rje sh+aakya'i rigs khrungs shing /
NK028(sa)001:13089: rten 'brel don la rten gnas pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:13090: 'phags pa rang rgyal bcu gnyis ni /
NK028(sa)001:13091: 'byung dang ldog la rab zhugs pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:13092: rang rgyal rnams la phyag 'tshal so //
NK028(sa)001:13094: mu ne dang rten 'brel snying po ci rigs pas bsnyen no //
NK028(sa)001:13098: rin po che'i bum pa mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i nang du /
NK028(sa)001:13099: rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas
NK028(sa)001:13100: khang pa la sogs bdag skyed ltar bsnyen pa yan
NK028(sa)001:13101: chad la / bar skabs kyi 'don pa tshig kha bsgyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:13102: zhar la o rgyan la sogs pa'i dbang rdzas rnams kyang byin gyis brlabs so /
NK028(sa)001:13105: stong ba'i ngang las b+h+rum las rin po che sna
NK028(sa)001:13106: tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang pa sogs bdag
NK028(sa)001:13107: bskyed ltar bsnyen pa yan chad la bar skabs su
NK028(sa)001:13110: bum pa dang dkyil 'khor la sogs la rab gnas byed /
NK028(sa)001:13111: grub na sbyin bsreg kyang ci rigs bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:13112: gnyis pa 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa la gnyis te /
NK028(sa)001:13113: slob dpon bdag nyid 'jug cing dbang len pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:13114: slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:13115: dang po slob dpon 'jug cing dbang len pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:13116: gong gi nyan thos kyi dbang gi skabs dang mtshungs so //
NK028(sa)001:13117: gnyis pa slob ma 'jug pa dang dbang bskur ba la gnyis ste /
NK028(sa)001:13118: dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:13119: dang po la 'jug chos bcu bzhi po ni gong nyan thos kyi dbang gi skabs dang mthun la /
NK028(sa)001:13121: bco lnga pa dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:13122: 'o mdun 'di na yod pa'i rang sangs rgyas kyi dkyil rten dang brten pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:13126: de'i nang du gzhal yas kyi khang pa gru bzhi sgo bzhi /
NK028(sa)001:13127: rgyan rta babs dang bcas pa /
NK028(sa)001:13128: de'i nang pad+ma 'dab ma bcu gnyis ste /
NK028(sa)001:13129: lte ba dang bcas pa mngon sum du mthong ba'i mos pa mdzod /
NK028(sa)001:13130: pad+ma'i lte bar bcom ldan 'das rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa /
NK028(sa)001:13131: pad 'dab bcu gnyis la rang rgyal ba chen po bcu gnyis dang bcas pa /
NK028(sa)001:13132: sku snang la rang bzhin med pa me long nang
NK028(sa)001:13133: gi gzugs brnyan bzhin mngon sum du mthong ba de
NK028(sa)001:13134: / khyed rang rnams kyi yi dam gyi lha skal yin ang snyam pa'i mos pa mdzod cig /
NK028(sa)001:13135: spyi don gnyis pa dbang bskur ba la gsum ste //
NK028(sa)001:13138: dang po ni gong dang mthun no //
NK028(sa)001:13139: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gsum ste /
NK028(sa)001:13142: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:13143: dang po la bcu'i bum pa la sogs dgu po gong nyan thos kyi dbang dang mthun la /
NK028(sa)001:13144: bye brag tu bcu pa phyag rgya'i dbang la /
NK028(sa)001:13149: nus pa gang skye lnga'i dang po bsam brgyud ni //
NK028(sa)001:13150: 'og min dang bla ma'i thugs ka dang /
NK028(sa)001:13151: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus nas sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa'i tshogs rnams byon nas /
NK028(sa)001:13152: khyed rang rnams kyis phung po khams skye mched dang gnyis su med par bsgoms mdzod /
NK028(sa)001:13154: dang por byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed nas /
NK028(sa)001:13155: bar du grangs med gsum la tshogs gnyis bsags /
NK028(sa)001:13156: tha mar mdzad pa bcu gnyis rdzogs sangs rgyas /
NK028(sa)001:13157: thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang bskur lhun grub shog /
NK028(sa)001:13159: bskur gnas mgo bstim gnas phung po khams dang skye mched la bstim /
NK028(sa)001:13160: sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang skye smon lam dang bcas pa ci rigs pa bya /
NK028(sa)001:13163: nyon mongs sel bas gdung ba sel //
NK028(sa)001:13164: rang rgyal chen po bsil yab 'dzin //
NK028(sa)001:13165: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:13166: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13171: nyon mongs ba'i gdung ba sel nas /
NK028(sa)001:13172: nyon mongs pa zad pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:13173: mi skye ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13176: ting 'dzin sdang ba thob pas snang ba brtsegs //
NK028(sa)001:13177: rang rgyal chen po rin chen mdzod 'dzin pa //
NK028(sa)001:13178: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:13179: de yi dbang bskur dam pa mchog thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:13182: ting 'dzin la dbang ma thob ba'i dri ma dag nas //
NK028(sa)001:13183: ting 'dzin du ma la dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13187: rang rgyal chen po rdo rje 'dzin //
NK028(sa)001:13188: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:13189: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13192: sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang skye ni /
NK028(sa)001:13193: 'khor ba'i 'jig pa thams cad bral nas /
NK028(sa)001:13194: mi 'jig pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13198: rang rgyal chen po rdo rje 'dzin /
NK028(sa)001:13199: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:13200: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13203: sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang skye ni /
NK028(sa)001:13204: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las grol nas /
NK028(sa)001:13205: 'khor ba la ci mi mnyam ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13208: shes rab rtsal dang ldan pas shes rab mchog /
NK028(sa)001:13209: rang rgyal chen po zla tshes 'dzin //
NK028(sa)001:13210: skal ldan bu la dbang de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13213: sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang skye ni //
NK028(sa)001:13214: shes rab 'chal ba'i dri ma dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:13215: shes rab kyi rtsal dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13218: 'khor ba'i rlung gis mi bskyod ri yi rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:13219: rang rgyal chen po rin chen snye ma 'dzin skal ldan bu la de yis a b+hi /
NK028(sa)001:13221: sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang skye ni //
NK028(sa)001:13223: 'khor ba'i rlung gi mi skyod pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13226: gsung sgra ldan pa sgra chen po /
NK028(sa)001:13227: rang rgyal chen po bsam gtan phyag rgya mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:13228: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:13229: de yi dbang a b+hi bskur gnas bstim gnas 'dre /
NK028(sa)001:13232: gsung rab la rmongs pa'i dri ma dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:13233: gsung gi sgra chen po dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13236: ting 'dzin rtse gcig gyur pas bse ru 'dra //
NK028(sa)001:13237: rang rgyal chen po mnyam bzhag phyag rgya mdzad /
NK028(sa)001:13238: skal ldan de yis a b+hi bskur gnas bstim gnas 'dre /
NK028(sa)001:13240: nus pa ga nga skye ni /
NK028(sa)001:13241: rnam g.yeng gi dri ma dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:13242: ting nge 'dzin rtse gcig tu gnas pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13245: nyon mongs sel bas dug sel 'joms /
NK028(sa)001:13246: rang rgyal chen po dung 'dzin pa /
NK028(sa)001:13247: skal ldan de yis a bskur gnas bstim gnas 'dre //
NK028(sa)001:13248: sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang skye ni /
NK028(sa)001:13249: nyon mongs pa spangs mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:13250: nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba sel nus pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13253: sprul pa cho 'phrul ldan pas rdzu 'phrul che //
NK028(sa)001:13254: rang rgyal chen po me sgron bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:13255: skal ldan bu la de yis dbang a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:13259: sprul pa 'gyed mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:13260: rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13263: 'khor ba skrag mdzad seng ge'i sgra //
NK028(sa)001:13264: rang rgyal chen po cha lang 'dzin //
NK028(sa)001:13265: skal ldan de yis a b+hi bskur gnas bstim gnas 'dre /
NK028(sa)001:13268: chos kyi sgra sgrog mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:13269: chos kyi sgra 'jigs pa med pa seng ge'i sgra sgrogs pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13271: ting 'dzin myur bas yid myur ba //
NK028(sa)001:13272: rang rgyal chen po bsil yab 'dzin //
NK028(sa)001:13273: skal ldan bu de'i dbang a bskur gnas /
NK028(sa)001:13274: bstim sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang skye ni /
NK028(sa)001:13275: ting nge 'dzin myur du mi skye ba'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK028(sa)001:13276: ting nge 'dzin myur ba dang ldan ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13277: bse ru ltar dang ne tso lta bu'i sa //
NK028(sa)001:13278: 'bras bu la sogs phyi yi rten 'brel dang /
NK028(sa)001:13279: ma rig la sogs nang gi rten 'brel dang //
NK028(sa)001:13280: lugs 'byung 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras spangs byas shing /
NK028(sa)001:13281: lugs bzlog 'das pa'i rgyu 'bras bsgrub byas te //
NK028(sa)001:13282: 'jig rten cha drug nyan thos sa dang bdun //
NK028(sa)001:13283: 'das nas rang sangs rgyas kyi sa la phyin par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13284: mo ye d+har+m+ma he tu pra b+h+aa wa he tun+te sh+aan ta tha ga to h+ya ba data /
NK028(sa)001:13285: tesh+aany+tsa yo ni ro d+ha e wam b+aa d+ai ma h+aa sh+ra ma nahye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:13288: rigs kyi bu khyod la rten 'brel gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:13289: yid bzhin bde ba mchog gi sa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13291: ma rig rgan mo long ba 'dra //
NK028(sa)001:13293: ma rig stong pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:13298: 'du byed stong pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:13303: rnam shes stong pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:13306: ming gzugs gru la zhugs pa 'dra //
NK028(sa)001:13308: ming gzugs stong pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:13311: skye mched grong khyer stong pa 'dra //
NK028(sa)001:13313: skye mched stong pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:13318: reg pa stong pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:13321: tshor ba mig la mda' phog 'dra //
NK028(sa)001:13323: tshor ba stong ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:13328: sred pa stong pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:13331: len pa shing thog len pa 'dra //
NK028(sa)001:13333: len pa stong pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:13338: srid pa stong pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:13341: skyes pa bud med bu skye 'dras //
NK028(sa)001:13343: skye ba stong pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:13346: rga shi rgas dang shi ba 'dra //
NK028(sa)001:13348: rga shi stong ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:13350: lugs 'byung 'khor ba'i chos las grol nas /
NK028(sa)001:13351: lugs bzlog mya ngan las 'das pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13352: rgyas par spro na bcu gnyis po kun la ci rigs par sbyar /
NK028(sa)001:13353: gnyis pa nus pa'i dbang la lnga ste /
NK028(sa)001:13358: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:13359: dbang de lnga'i cho ga yang gong dang mthun no //
NK028(sa)001:13360: gsum pa gsang dbang zab mo'i dbang la gsum ste /
NK028(sa)001:13362: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang dang /
NK028(sa)001:13363: dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:13364: dbang de gsum gyi cho ga'i dod ni //
NK028(sa)001:13365: lam 'khyer la dbang gi lam khyer bum pa //
NK028(sa)001:13366: thub pa rang rgyal bcu gnyis //
NK028(sa)001:13367: rten 'brel bcu gnyis dang bcas pa bskur /
NK028(sa)001:13369: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa /
NK028(sa)001:13371: lta sgom spyod 'bras gong nyan thos kyi skabs su smos pa bzhiin /
NK028(sa)001:13373: nyan thos las khyad par 'phags tshul yang bshad do //
NK028(sa)001:13374: de nas yang dbang chags par byed pa'am /
NK028(sa)001:13375: gnas pa'i rten du 'debs chung cig byed na /
NK028(sa)001:13376: rang gi spyi bor thig le dmar po sran ma tsam cig bsgom /
NK028(sa)001:13377: de las mtho bar thig le dkar po sran ma tsam cig bsgom /
NK028(sa)001:13378: de nas thig le dmar po de la shes pa gtad pas /
NK028(sa)001:13379: je che je che snang srid thams cad dmar lam gyis song par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:13380: dmar po de chags ba'i rang bzhin lugs 'byung 'khor ba'i chos yin gsungs /
NK028(sa)001:13381: yang thig le dkar po de la sems gtad pas /
NK028(sa)001:13382: je che je che la snang srid thams cad dkar lam gyis song par bsam /
NK028(sa)001:13383: dkar po de lugs bzlog mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos yin gsungs //
NK028(sa)001:13385: spyi bo nas mar bab snying gi dkyil du thim pas //
NK028(sa)001:13386: rang gi sems dang dbyer med du 'dres pas /
NK028(sa)001:13387: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa thams cad
NK028(sa)001:13388: mnyam pa nyid du blos sgyur la bzhag gsungs so
NK028(sa)001:13390: gnas ri bo bya rkang can dbang rten cing 'brel par 'byung pa lugs 'byung /
NK028(sa)001:13391: 'khor ba dang lugs bzlog mya ngan las 'das pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:13392: dbyer med du rtogs pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK028(sa)001:13393: de min kun nyan thos dang 'dra /
NK028(sa)001:13395: sgom chen po ni thad kar blta'o //
NK028(sa)001:13396: de dag ni rang sangs rgyas gyi them skas so //
NK028(sa)001:13399: bsngo ba smon lam dang bkra shis brjod tshogs dang dga' ston rgya chen po bya //
NK028(sa)001:13400: glu gar dang rtse 'jo'i nyams bskyangs //
NK028(sa)001:13401: mchod bstod bsngo ba bzod gsol //
NK028(sa)001:13402: gshegs gsol byas la dkyil 'khor bsdu //
NK028(sa)001:13403: rang sangs rgyas kyi dbang rdzogs so ////
NK028(sa)001:13405: dang po phyi dbang gi chu bo las /
NK028(sa)001:13406: byang chub sems dpa'i dbang gi them skas bzhugs so //
NK028(sa)001:13407: bzhi pa byang chub sems dpa'i dbang la gnyis ste /
NK028(sa)001:13408: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:13411: tshad dang ldan pa'i sa stegs la //
NK028(sa)001:13412: dri bzang chu yi chag chag gdab //
NK028(sa)001:13413: byin brlabs ldan pa'i thig skud kyis //
NK028(sa)001:13414: thig brgyad gong bzhin legs par gdab //
NK028(sa)001:13415: de nas cha chen bcu drug la //
NK028(sa)001:13416: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma gdab /
NK028(sa)001:13417: gnyis pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK028(sa)001:13418: gsum pa bzhi pa dor bar bya //
NK028(sa)001:13419: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK028(sa)001:13420: drug pa phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK028(sa)001:13421: bdun pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK028(sa)001:13422: brgyad pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK028(sa)001:13423: de nas mu khyud bskor ba ni //
NK028(sa)001:13424: cha phran drug nas lte ba bskor //
NK028(sa)001:13425: bdun nas de'i mu khyud phyi //
NK028(sa)001:13427: bco lnga de'i mu khyud phyi //
NK028(sa)001:13428: glang gur rdo ra spyi dang mtshungs //
NK028(sa)001:13429: mda' yab zur thig 'phrad so nas //
NK028(sa)001:13430: pad 'dab rdo rwa me ri la //
NK028(sa)001:13431: ci rigs 'tshams pa bskor bar bya //
NK028(sa)001:13432: byin brlabs ldan pa'i mtshon rtsi yis //
NK028(sa)001:13433: mkhas pas re kha legs par bri //
NK028(sa)001:13434: dbus kyi lte ba ser por byed //
NK028(sa)001:13435: pad 'dab bzhi po phyogs mtshon byed //
NK028(sa)001:13436: pad 'dab bcu po mdzes tshon byed //
NK028(sa)001:13437: gru chad rtsigs sogs gong dang mthun //
NK028(sa)001:13438: de nas rnam pa dgod pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:13439: dbus su sh+aakya thub pa bkod //
NK028(sa)001:13440: pad 'dab bzhi la yum chen dang //
NK028(sa)001:13441: phyag na rdo rje sha ri'i bu //
NK028(sa)001:13442: spyan ras gzigs kyi sku bzhi dgod //
NK028(sa)001:13443: 'dab ma bcu la sangs rgyas bcu //
NK028(sa)001:13444: gsung thugs rten ni gang dang mtshungs //
NK028(sa)001:13445: chad lhag gsal zhing zhal gsol mchod //
NK028(sa)001:13446: mchod yon la sogs phyi mchod dang //
NK028(sa)001:13447: gtor ma bshams pa la sogs dang //
NK028(sa)001:13448: bum sogs bsham pa gong dang mthun //
NK028(sa)001:13449: der ni bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:13450: de nas rab gnas kyi don ni //
NK028(sa)001:13451: dpon slob rnams gdan la bzhugs shing /
NK028(sa)001:13452: sngon 'gro gtor ma cha bzhi'i cha cig bsham la //
NK028(sa)001:13453: byin gyis brlabs pa bsngo zhing /
NK028(sa)001:13455: mchod pa byin gyis brlabs pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:13456: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed rnams gong bzhin /
NK028(sa)001:13461: b+h+rum las rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang pa /
NK028(sa)001:13463: rgyan rta babs dang bcas pa'i nang du /
NK028(sa)001:13465: bcom ldan gser mdog chos 'chad g.yas //
NK028(sa)001:13466: g.yon pa mnyam bzhag phyag rgyar ldan //
NK028(sa)001:13467: rdo rje dkyil dkrung gtsug gtor bcas //
NK028(sa)001:13468: spyan yangs mthing kha mdzod spur ldan //
NK028(sa)001:13472: pad zla rgyas steng yum chen mo //
NK028(sa)001:13473: longs spyod brgyan lngan rdo rje dkyil //
NK028(sa)001:13474: gser mdog sku ni shin tu rgyas /
NK028(sa)001:13475: phyag bzhi'i dang po mnyam bzhag phyag /
NK028(sa)001:13477: g.yon pa po ti bsnams nas ni //
NK028(sa)001:13478: 'gro ba sems can don mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:13480: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan steng na //
NK028(sa)001:13481: phyag na rdo rje zhi ba'i zhal //
NK028(sa)001:13482: mthing kha g.yas na rdo rje 'dzin /
NK028(sa)001:13484: rin chen rgyan ldan sems dpa'i dkyil //
NK028(sa)001:13486: sha ri gser mdog dka' thub gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:13487: chos gos gsum ldan bsil byed bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:13488: pus gtsugs g.yon pa lhung bzed bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:13489: lus ngag yid gsum mnyam pa'i ngang //
NK028(sa)001:13491: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs nas //
NK028(sa)001:13492: spyan ras dkar po byang chub sems //
NK028(sa)001:13493: brgyan mdzes sems dpa'i dkyil dkrung bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:13494: g.yas na pad+ma mchod sbyin dang //
NK028(sa)001:13496: pad 'dab bcu yi shar phyogs kyi //
NK028(sa)001:13497: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:13498: bde gshegs dkon mchog 'byung gnas ni //
NK028(sa)001:13499: sku mdog shel ltar dkar ba la //
NK028(sa)001:13500: phyag g.yas rin chen mchod sbyin mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:13501: phyag g.yon lte ba'i thad dkar ni //
NK028(sa)001:13504: pad zla rgyas ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:13505: bde gshegs mya ngan med pa'i dpal //
NK028(sa)001:13506: sku mdog nam mkha'i mdog can la //
NK028(sa)001:13508: g.yon pa lte ba'i thad dkar ni //
NK028(sa)001:13509: 'gro la bstan pas nyon mongs sel //
NK028(sa)001:13511: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:13513: sku mdog gangs ri ltar dkar zhing //
NK028(sa)001:13514: g.yas pa mche ba brtsigs pa bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:13515: g.yon pa lte ba thad dkar ni //
NK028(sa)001:13518: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs na //
NK028(sa)001:13519: bde gshegs rgyal pa'i dbang po ni //
NK028(sa)001:13520: sku mdog in 'dra ni la'i mdog /
NK028(sa)001:13522: g.yon pa lte ba'i thad dkar ni //
NK028(sa)001:13523: 'gro la bstan pas mun pa sel //
NK028(sa)001:13525: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs na //
NK028(sa)001:13526: bde gshegs pad+ma dam pa'i dpal //
NK028(sa)001:13527: sku mdog dug ltar dkar ba'i mdog //
NK028(sa)001:13528: phyag g.yas pad+ma dmar po bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:13529: g.yon pa lte ba'i thad dkar ni //
NK028(sa)001:13532: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan steng na //
NK028(sa)001:13533: nyi ma snang ba dam pa'i dpal //
NK028(sa)001:13534: sku mdog mar gad dmar smug la /
NK028(sa)001:13535: phyag g.yas mun sel nyi ma bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:13536: g.yon pa sku la rten mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:13538: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:13539: sangs rgyas gdug chen pad+ma'i rtsal //
NK028(sa)001:13540: sku mdog in tra ni la'i mdog /
NK028(sa)001:13541: g.yas pa sna tshogs rdo rje 'dzin //
NK028(sa)001:13542: phyag g.yon lte ba'i thad dkar ni //
NK028(sa)001:13545: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:13546: ting 'dzin glang po dam pa'i dpal //
NK028(sa)001:13547: sku mdog gser ltar 'tsher ba la //
NK028(sa)001:13548: phyag g.yas chos 'chad phyag rgya ston //
NK028(sa)001:13549: g.yon pa chos gos 'dzin mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:13551: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:13552: dga' bar byed pa'i sangs rgyas ni //
NK028(sa)001:13553: sku mdog ud dpal sngon po'i mdangs //
NK028(sa)001:13554: phyag g.yas rin chen bum pa bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:13555: g.yon pa sku la rten mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:13557: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:13558: bde bshegs pad+ma dam pa'i dpa' //
NK028(sa)001:13559: sku mdog gser ltar 'tsher ba'i mdangs //
NK028(sa)001:13560: phyag g.yas pad+ma dmar po bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:13561: g.yon pa lte ba'i thad dkar ni //
NK028(sa)001:13562: mthil ni phyir bstan gdung pa sel //
NK028(sa)001:13563: de la ye shes snyan gsan dbab //
NK028(sa)001:13570: sgra 'jug pa yi rgyu mtshan gyi //
NK028(sa)001:13571: bsgyur ba bsnyen par byed pa po //
NK028(sa)001:13572: thub pa chen po'i dus 'dir lags //
NK028(sa)001:13573: skyes bu gtso bo gshegs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:13574: skyes bu cang mkhyen gshegs su gsol /
NK028(sa)001:13575: thub pa chen po gdugs tshod bab //
NK028(sa)001:13576: rkang gnyis gtso bo gshegs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:13577: rkang gnyis dam pa gshegs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:13578: rkang gnyis cang mkhyen gshegs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:13581: slob ma bum pa'i sgra 'dzin pa //
NK028(sa)001:13582: thub pa dam pa gshegs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:13583: 'phags pa'i bden ba'i gnas bcas te //
NK028(sa)001:13584: byams dang snying rje'i spyan mnga' zhing //
NK028(sa)001:13585: bdag med pa'i sgra sgrogs pa //
NK028(sa)001:13586: rgyal ba seng ge gshegs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:13587: khrims ni rtsa ba chung bas dran //
NK028(sa)001:13588: byung chub yan lag me tog brgyan //
NK028(sa)001:13589: rnam grol 'bras bu phun sum tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:13590: rgyal ba sdong pa gshegs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:13591: shes rab rgya chen zab pa po //
NK028(sa)001:13592: ting 'dzin chab ni btang ldan zhing //
NK028(sa)001:13593: rnal 'byor pa yi tshogs pas bltams //
NK028(sa)001:13594: ston pa rgya mtsho gshegs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:13595: thugs rjes dkyil 'khor dpal dang ldan //
NK028(sa)001:13596: shes rab 'od zer legs pas brgyan //
NK028(sa)001:13598: thub pa nyi ma gshegs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:13599: phas kyi rgol bas mi skyod cing //
NK028(sa)001:13600: rnal 'byor la sogs tshogs pa can //
NK028(sa)001:13601: slob dang mi slob ri dgas bltam //
NK028(sa)001:13602: thub pa ri bo gshegs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:13603: sangs rgyas nyan thos 'khor rnam dag /
NK028(sa)001:13605: bdag gi re ba bskong pa'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:13606: thams cad myur du gshegs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:13607: da lta phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten na //
NK028(sa)001:13608: rtag tu bzhugs pa'i rkang gnyis gtso //
NK028(sa)001:13609: thugs brtse thugs rje ldan pa'i thugs //
NK028(sa)001:13610: brtse bas bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:13611: mya ngan mi 'da' thugs rje yi //
NK028(sa)001:13612: nyon mongs mi spongs dgos pa med //
NK028(sa)001:13613: ma chags rang bzhin dag pa nas //
NK028(sa)001:13614: pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:13615: sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa'i gtso //
NK028(sa)001:13616: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK028(sa)001:13617: dkon mchog gsum gyi rtsa ba der //
NK028(sa)001:13618: bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13619: bdag sogs slob ma ma lus pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:13620: dug gsum nad kyi gdungs pa la //
NK028(sa)001:13621: dam chos bdud rtsis gso mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:13622: bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13623: rtag tu lha drug brten la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13624: dpal ldan dge slong khyed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13625: mkhas pa chen po khyed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13626: thugs ni thugs rje can la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13627: rnal 'byor dbang phyug can la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13628: rtag tu dbyings na bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13629: gzhan gyi sdug bsngal gyis gdungs sel la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13630: mar me mdzad pa ye shes zhabs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13631: ston pa bla med sangs rgyas rin po che //
NK028(sa)001:13632: skyobs pa bla med dam chos rin po rin po //
NK028(sa)001:13633: 'dren pa bla med dge 'dun rin po che //
NK028(sa)001:13634: bla med dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13635: gang dag gis ni chos ston pa //
NK028(sa)001:13636: sangs rgyas kun la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13637: gang la sangs rgyas gus mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:13638: chos la bdag ni phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13639: gang la phul ba'i don che ba //
NK028(sa)001:13641: dmigs med chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13642: cir yang sprul ba'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13643: rnam dag chos kyi dbyings la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13644: sgrub pa'i 'phags lam brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13645: bstan pa'i gdung rabs gus par phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13646: ngan 'gro rnams bzlog byang chub sems //
NK028(sa)001:13647: rnam dag dgra bcom dge la sogs //
NK028(sa)001:13648: rang sangs rgyas rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13649: ngan 'gro rnams ni bzlog bgyis cing //
NK028(sa)001:13650: mtho ris lam ni rab ston la //
NK028(sa)001:13651: rga shi med par 'dren mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:13652: byang chub sems la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13653: nyes pa kun la rnam grol zhing //
NK028(sa)001:13654: yon tan kun gyis rgyan pa po //
NK028(sa)001:13655: sems can kun gyi gnyen gcig po //
NK028(sa)001:13656: thams cad mkhyen la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13657: 'dul dka' mi zad sems ni khyed kyis 'dul //
NK028(sa)001:13658: g.yul ma dpa' bo g.yul gyi dpa' bo bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:13659: shin tu tshar bcad rang gi dbang du mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:13660: thugs 'dul mi snyems khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13661: yon tan rin chen mang po'i tshogs mnga' zhing //
NK028(sa)001:13662: mtshan rab ye shes yongs su dag pa'i sku //
NK028(sa)001:13663: gser gyis mdog can lha dang mi mchod pa //
NK028(sa)001:13664: bcom ldan lha'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13665: sems can rnams la brtse ba can //
NK028(sa)001:13666: 'phrad dang bral ba'i dgongs pa can //
NK028(sa)001:13668: phan bde dgongs pa can la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13669: lus can kun gyi khyod mthong na //
NK028(sa)001:13670: skyes bu mchog tu rtogs par 'tshal //
NK028(sa)001:13671: mthong ba tsam gyis dad gyur pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:13672: mdzad pa khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13673: bla med mi 'jigs sbyin pa khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13674: gzhan phan sems can gnyen rtsa khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13675: stobs bcu bden pa'i rtsal mnga' khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13676: gang tshe rkang gnyis gtso bo khyod bltams tshe //
NK028(sa)001:13677: sa chen 'di la gom pa bdun zhu nas //
NK028(sa)001:13678: nga ni 'jig rten 'di na mchog ces gsungs //
NK028(sa)001:13679: de tshe mkhas pa khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13680: gang tshe thub chen zhi ba'i grong bzhud de //
NK028(sa)001:13681: bzhugs kyang 'dzam bu'i grib mas ma btang zhing //
NK028(sa)001:13682: lha bu gzhon nu drug gis btud gyur pa /
NK028(sa)001:13683: de tshe mchod 'os khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13684: da yang 'di dang khyod la lan gsum du //
NK028(sa)001:13685: thub pa khyod kyi zhabs la mgos phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13686: thugs rje che mnga' lha yi mchod pa'i gtso //
NK028(sa)001:13687: khyod 'dra 'jig rten ma mchis lhag ci smos //
NK028(sa)001:13688: mtshan ni don 'grub lags zhes sngon brjod pa /
NK028(sa)001:13689: pha dang ma yi bsam ste btags pa lags //
NK028(sa)001:13690: khyod kyi bsam rdzogs bdud rtsi mnyes pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:13691: don grub lags par bdag gis da sdod 'tshal //
NK028(sa)001:13692: rnam dag sku lnga mchog tu gzugs bzang ba //
NK028(sa)001:13693: ye shes rgya mtsho gser gyi lhun po 'dra //
NK028(sa)001:13694: grags pa 'jig rten bkram nas lham me ba //
NK028(sa)001:13695: mgon po mchog khyod la ni skyabs su mchi //
NK028(sa)001:13696: rab tu lam stor rnam par mig zum la //
NK028(sa)001:13697: khyod ni 'jig rten sgron me nyi ma 'dra //
NK028(sa)001:13698: gzhan gyis mi thub srog chags rtsa lag cig /
NK028(sa)001:13699: ded dpon khyod nyid la ni skyabs su mchi //
NK028(sa)001:13700: shin tu tshogs pa ye shes 'byor ba'i mdzod //
NK028(sa)001:13701: nam mkha' rang bzhin bzod nas rnam grol thugs //
NK028(sa)001:13702: thugs rje'i bsam pa yid 'ong 'jam pa'i gsung //
NK028(sa)001:13703: don kun 'grub pa khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13704: 'khor ba'i dgon pa las ni khyod thar mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:13705: tshogs pa las ni rgyu dang 'bras bur ston //
NK028(sa)001:13706: byams pa las ni mchog gi go cha mkhyen //
NK028(sa)001:13707: thugs rje gnas pa'i skyabs su rab tu mchi /
NK028(sa)001:13708: sgyu ma mig sgyu chu zla 'dra ba yis //
NK028(sa)001:13709: srid pa las ni yul gyi gnas kyi chags //
NK028(sa)001:13710: mi shes nad sel 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon //
NK028(sa)001:13711: sman pa'i rgyal po khyod la skyabs su mchi //
NK028(sa)001:13712: chu bo bzhi dbus zam par gyur pa la //
NK028(sa)001:13713: nor bdun 'phags pa'i tshul gyis rab grol ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:13714: yang dag lam ston lo ka rtsa lags so //
NK028(sa)001:13715: thugs rje ldan pa khyod la 'di mchod do //
NK028(sa)001:13716: mtshan mchog ldan pa dri med zla ba'i zhal //
NK028(sa)001:13717: gser mdog 'dra ba khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13718: rdul bral khyod 'dra srid pa gsum ma mchis //
NK028(sa)001:13719: mnyam med mkhyen pa khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13720: rgyal ba'i dbu skra 'jam mdzes snum zhing bzang //
NK028(sa)001:13721: khyod kyi gtsug gtor 'di ni ri rgyal bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:13722: gtsug gtor mi mthong khyod dang mtshungs ma mchis //
NK028(sa)001:13723: thub pa khyod kyi smin mtshams mdzod spu mdzes //
NK028(sa)001:13724: kun la zla ba dung dkar dkar //
NK028(sa)001:13725: thugs rje gang gi 'gro ba 'di gzigs la //
NK028(sa)001:13726: spyan mchog bzang po ut+pala sngon po 'dra //
NK028(sa)001:13727: rgyal ba dri med spyan la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13728: ljags yangs srab la zangs kyi mdog 'dra ba //
NK028(sa)001:13729: de yis rang gi zhal gyis gdong yang kheb //
NK028(sa)001:13730: chos gsungs pas ni 'gro ba 'dul bar bgyid //
NK028(sa)001:13731: 'jam rtsub gsung ldan khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13732: tshems bzang shin tu brtan pa rdo rje 'dra //
NK028(sa)001:13733: bcu dang sum cu snyoms shing thags bzang pa //
NK028(sa)001:13734: 'dzum pa mdzad nas 'gro ba 'dul bar mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:13735: bden gtams mnyam pa khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13736: rgyal ba khyod kyi gzugs dang mtshungs ma mchis //
NK028(sa)001:13737: 'od kyi zhing brgyad dag dang snang bar bgyid //
NK028(sa)001:13738: 'jig rten na ni tshangs dbang skyong de dag /
NK028(sa)001:13739: bcom ldan khyod nyid 'od kyis zil du brlag /
NK028(sa)001:13741: byon pa mnyam med bcom ldan 'das //
NK028(sa)001:13742: glang po'i rgyal po rma bya seng ge'i stabs //
NK028(sa)001:13743: bcom ldan gnya' shing gang du gzigs shing gshegs //
NK028(sa)001:13744: sa dang ri dang ngam pa g.yo bar mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:13745: bcom ldan khyod sku mtshan gyi brgyan pa de //
NK028(sa)001:13746: khyod kyi lpags pa 'jam zhing gser mdog 'dra //
NK028(sa)001:13747: 'gro bas gzugs 'di lta bas ngoms mi 'gyur //
NK028(sa)001:13748: khyod ni mtshungs pa ma mchis gzugs dang ldan //
NK028(sa)001:13749: khyod sngon skal pa brgya nas bka' thub spyod //
NK028(sa)001:13750: khyod stong dul dang spyin pa kun la dgyes //
NK028(sa)001:13751: sems can kun la thugs brtse byams thugs ldan //
NK028(sa)001:13752: mchog tu thugs rje can la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13753: khyod ni spyin dang tshul khrims rtag tu dgyes //
NK028(sa)001:13754: khyod ni bzod dang brtson 'grus dgyes rab brtan //
NK028(sa)001:13755: khyod ni bsam gtan shes rab 'di gzigs mnga' //
NK028(sa)001:13756: mtshungs med ye shes lnga la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13757: khyod ni smra ba ngan pa'i tshogs can 'joms //
NK028(sa)001:13758: khyod ni seng ge lta bur 'khor du sgrog /
NK028(sa)001:13759: khyod ni sman pa'i rgyal po srid gsum sel //
NK028(sa)001:13760: mchog dbang mdzad pa khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13761: thub pa sku gsung thugs ni rnam par dag /
NK028(sa)001:13762: pad+ma chu ltar srid pa gsum ma bgos //
NK028(sa)001:13763: khyod ni tshangs dbyangs ka la ping ka'i skad /
NK028(sa)001:13764: srid gsum gsol gshegs khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13765: lha dang mi dang klus mchod bde bar gshegs //
NK028(sa)001:13766: yon tan kun gyi mthar phyin de bstod las //
NK028(sa)001:13767: bsod nams rgya chen gang bsgrubs gyur pa des //
NK028(sa)001:13768: 'gro ba sangs rgyas go 'phang thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13769: nyi ma lta bu ma rig mun pa sel //
NK028(sa)001:13770: zla ba lta bur nyon mongs gdungs pa sel //
NK028(sa)001:13771: dug gsum nad sel sangs rgyas sman gyi lha //
NK028(sa)001:13773: lha mi ston pa sman pa'i rgyal po ste //
NK028(sa)001:13774: bcom ldan 'jig rten gsum na skyob mdzad cing //
NK028(sa)001:13775: dug gsum nad dang 'dus pa'i nad sel ba //
NK028(sa)001:13777: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK028(sa)001:13778: gzugs sku 'ja' tshon bzhin du so sor gsal //
NK028(sa)001:13779: thabs dang shes rab mchog la mnga' mnyes pa //
NK028(sa)001:13780: rigs lnga bde bar gshegs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13781: 'jig rten gsum mgon yon tan pha rol phyin //
NK028(sa)001:13782: mtsho ltar dkar yangs mdzes pa'i sku dang ldan /
NK028(sa)001:13783: mnyam med de bzhin nyid kyi seng ge'i khri la bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:13784: bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad de la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK028(sa)001:13785: mdangs ldan nor bu mthon ka chen po ltar 'phro zhing //
NK028(sa)001:13786: 'od kyi phyogs rnams ma lus snang bar mdzad pa po //
NK028(sa)001:13787: 'jig rten gsum na rmad byung glang po'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:13788: snyems 'bras sangs rgyas mi bskyod de la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK028(sa)001:13789: rin chen dbang bskur 'byor ba 'gro don mdzad la mkhas //
NK028(sa)001:13790: bsod nams tshogs mnga' shin tu rdul rnams bral gyur zhing //
NK028(sa)001:13791: gser gyi rgya mtsho lta bu rta 'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:13792: thub pa rin chen 'byung ldan de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13793: rma bya'i rigs rnams rgya yi mdzes par snang mdzad cing //
NK028(sa)001:13794: 'od kyi phyogs bcur khyab pa sngon dga' pad+ma ni //
NK028(sa)001:13795: rang dag'i ngo bo lta bur rma bya'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:13796: thub pa 'od dpag med la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK028(sa)001:13797: dam chos 'od zer phyogs kyi mun pa sel mdzad cing //
NK028(sa)001:13798: 'od kyi nam mkha' snang ba'i cha kun rnam par 'gengs //
NK028(sa)001:13799: beedur+ya'i mtsho ltar mkha' lding gdan la bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:13800: sangs rgyas don yod grub pa de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13801: smra bsam brjod med shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK028(sa)001:13802: ma skyes mi 'gag nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK028(sa)001:13803: so so rang rig ye shes spyood yul ba //
NK028(sa)001:13804: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yum la phyag zhing khams thams cad gser gyi sa gzhi la //
NK028(sa)001:13805: me tog ku mu ta'i char rgyun 'bab //
NK028(sa)001:13806: yon tan rin chen mang pos bcal du bkram //
NK028(sa)001:13807: yum gyur dge ma khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13808: stong pa bco brgyad chos kyi sdong po la //
NK028(sa)001:13809: pha rol phyin bcu mdzes pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK028(sa)001:13810: tshad med bzhi'i lo 'dab rgyas pa la //
NK028(sa)001:13811: skye 'gags med pa'i 'bras bu so sor smin //
NK028(sa)001:13812: sa bcu chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13813: dam chos mdo sde 'dus ma byas //
NK028(sa)001:13814: dus gsum rgyal ba bskyed pa'i yum //
NK028(sa)001:13815: mdo sde 'dul ba mngon pa la //
NK028(sa)001:13816: lus dang ngag yid dang bas phyag bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:13817: phyag stong 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po stong /
NK028(sa)001:13818: spyan stong bskal pa bzang po'i sangs rgyas stong /
NK028(sa)001:13819: gang la ci 'dul de la der ston pa //
NK028(sa)001:13820: btsun pa spyan ras gzigs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13821: don dam dbyings nas skye ba gcig pa po /
NK028(sa)001:13822: khams gsum dag na btsun pa spyan ras gzigs /
NK028(sa)001:13823: zla ba nya 'dra dri ma med pa'i sku /
NK028(sa)001:13824: thugs rje rang bzhi na can la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13825: spyan ras gzigs dbang 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon //
NK028(sa)001:13826: 'das pa'i dus na mngon par sangs rgyas kyang /
NK028(sa)001:13827: thugs rje'i dbang gi sa bcu'i tshul ston pa /
NK028(sa)001:13828: thabs tshul dpag med rigs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13829: spyan ras gzigs dbang rgyal ba'i gtsug gtor can /
NK028(sa)001:13830: phyag gi 'thil nas thugs rje'i chu 'bebs pa //
NK028(sa)001:13831: yi dwags bskres bskom sdug bsngal sel mdzad pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:13832: btsun pa spyan ras gzigs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13833: 'jig rten gsum gyis dpag bsam shing //
NK028(sa)001:13835: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa chos kyi sku //
NK028(sa)001:13836: 'gro drug sems can rnams la spyan ras gzigs //
NK028(sa)001:13837: nam mkha' lta bur khyab pa'i bcu gcig zhal //
NK028(sa)001:13838: gzi brjid 'od dpag med la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13839: dpal gyis 'byung gnas 'jam dpal kun kyi dpal //
NK028(sa)001:13840: mtha' dag byams pas khyab pas 'jam pa'i dbyangs //
NK028(sa)001:13841: 'jam dang dpal du grags pas don dang ldan //
NK028(sa)001:13842: 'jam dpal yang dag dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13843: lcang lo can gyis gnas mchog dam pa na //
NK028(sa)001:13844: gsang sngags rigs sngags kun gyis bdag po ste //
NK028(sa)001:13845: log 'dren bgegs kyi tshogs rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:13846: bcom ldan rdo rje bsnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13847: rigs pa las kyi dbyings na skyes //
NK028(sa)001:13848: rtog med spros bral bde ba che //
NK028(sa)001:13849: rnam dag don dam byang chub sems //
NK028(sa)001:13850: sgrol ma chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13851: gzhon nu mtshan ldan mdzes pa'i sku /
NK028(sa)001:13852: kha dog mchog ldan brjid pa'i zhal //
NK028(sa)001:13853: ma mo dkyil 'khor dbyings na bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:13854: sgrol ma longs spyod sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13855: thugs kyi gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK028(sa)001:13856: sna tshogs phyag rgya'i gzugs 'phro zhing /
NK028(sa)001:13857: 'gro drug sems can sgrol mdzad yum //
NK028(sa)001:13858: sgrol ma sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13859: mi g.yo shes bya'i khro bo ni //
NK028(sa)001:13860: ral gri zhags pa legs par bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:13861: spyi bo'i zur phud g.yon du 'phyangs //
NK028(sa)001:13863: klu chen la sogs thams cad kyi //
NK028(sa)001:13864: rgyan rnams kun gyis rab tu brgyan //
NK028(sa)001:13865: byis ba'i gzugs can khro ba can //
NK028(sa)001:13866: rdo rje sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13867: skal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK028(sa)001:13868: dpa' bo'i stangs stabs brkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:13869: nyi zla 'bar ba'i spyan gyis gdangs mig gis //
NK028(sa)001:13870: bgegs dpung bskrags par mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13871: gdung ba'i ye shes rol pa ston mdzad cing //
NK028(sa)001:13872: sdig ba'i mtshon cha sna tshogs phyag na bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:13873: nyon mongs dug can gtan nas 'joms mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:13874: sbrul dug rgyan gyi brgyan la phyag la 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13875: ye shes zhi ba'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK028(sa)001:13876: sku'i cha lugs za byed rngam bstabs can //
NK028(sa)001:13877: gsung gis nga ro 'brug sgra lngir ba'i sgra //
NK028(sa)001:13878: ma lus dbang du sdud la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13879: 'jigs pa'i h+aum sgra nges par sgrogs mdzad cing //
NK028(sa)001:13880: bgegs dpung ma lus par ni bsregs mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:13881: dngos grub thams cad stsol bar mdzad pa'i lha //
NK028(sa)001:13882: khro chen mi g.yo mgon la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:13883: rgyal ba'i sku la nyon mongs mi mnga' yang //
NK028(sa)001:13884: sems can nyon mongs bag chags sbyang slad du //
NK028(sa)001:13885: sku gsung thugs la yon chab 'di phul bas /
NK028(sa)001:13886: khams gsum gnas pa'i bag chags dag gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13887: tshul khrims ldan pa'i spos mchog dam pa 'dis //
NK028(sa)001:13888: ting 'dzin sngags dang phyag rgyas byin brlabs te //
NK028(sa)001:13889: sangs rgyas zhing du spos dri ngad ldang pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:13890: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs rnams tshim gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13891: dkyil 'khor kun du rgyal ba mnyes mdzad pa'i /
NK028(sa)001:13892: kha dog dbyibs legs lha rdzas me tog 'di //
NK028(sa)001:13893: nam mkha' gang bar sems gyis dngos sprul te //
NK028(sa)001:13894: gzhal yas khang du sprin bzhin bstib gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13895: nyon mongs dug bsreg ma lus sel mdzad pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:13896: shes rab gzi ldan dpal gyi sgron me 'di //
