NK028(sa)001:13897: sprin med mkha' la nyi shar ji bzhin du //
NK028(sa)001:13898: 'od der snang bas phyogs bcur gsal gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13899: stong gsum kun tu dri mchog 'byung gyur pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:13900: spos dang tsan dan sbyar ba'i chu gtsang rgyal ba'i khrus //
NK028(sa)001:13901: ye shes sprin phug mkha' la char babs pas //
NK028(sa)001:13902: 'gro ba'i don du lha rdzas bdud rtsi shos //
NK028(sa)001:13903: dag cing gtsang mar sbyar te 'bul lags na //
NK028(sa)001:13904: ye shes thugs rje can gyi bzhes su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:13905: dril chen bsil snyan rnam grol tshangs ba'i dbyangs //
NK028(sa)001:13906: bsam dag ngag gi bstod de gus mchod nas //
NK028(sa)001:13907: sa bcu rim kyi bsgrod nas sangs rgyas par //
NK028(sa)001:13908: tshogs gnyis rdzogs nas chos kyi rgyal por shog /
NK028(sa)001:13909: yan lag brgyad ldan dri ma dag pa'i chus //
NK028(sa)001:13910: bkra shis sna tshogs 'o ma'i chu rgyun 'di //
NK028(sa)001:13911: rgyal ba'i drung du mchod yon 'di 'bul bas //
NK028(sa)001:13912: 'gro kun zhi zhing bkra shis phun sum tshogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13913: spos dang tsan dan la sogs spyar ba yis //
NK028(sa)001:13914: las kun dag pa'i chu gtsang dag pa 'di //
NK028(sa)001:13915: rgyal ba'i zhabs la zhabs bsil 'di phul bas //
NK028(sa)001:13916: 'gro kun glo bur dri ma dag par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13917: lhan cig skyes dang sbyar dang yongs gyur pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:13918: rab tu tshims ldan dge ba'i gdug spos 'di //
NK028(sa)001:13919: rgyal ba'i shangs la dri bsung 'di 'phul bas //
NK028(sa)001:13920: 'gro kun tshul khrims rnam par dag gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13921: chu skyes thang skyes yid las byung pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:13922: byang chub yan lag mdzes pa'i me tog 'di //
NK028(sa)001:13923: bsam gtan rang bzhin rgyal ba'i dbu la 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:13924: 'gro kun mtshan dang dpe byad yongs rdzogs shog /
NK028(sa)001:13925: dmar gsal mdzes la dngas zhing gsal ba yi //
NK028(sa)001:13926: mi shes mun pa gsal byed sgron me 'di //
NK028(sa)001:13927: smon lam rang bzhin rgyal ba'i spyan la 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:13928: 'gro kun spyan lnga rnam par dag gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:13929: tsan dan gur gum la sogs sbyar ba yis //
NK028(sa)001:13930: dri ngan rnams spangs dri zhim byug pa 'di //
NK028(sa)001:13931: thabs kyi rang bzhin rgyal ba thugs la 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:13932: 'gro kun zag med phung po lnga thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:13933: kha dog dri dang ro bcud ldan pa'i zas //
NK028(sa)001:13934: ro brgya ldan pa'i zas su byin brlabs te //
NK028(sa)001:13935: stobs kyis rang bzhin rgyal ba'i zhal du 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:13936: 'gro kun sred med bu'i stobs thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:13937: dril chen bsil snyan rnam grol tshangs pa'i dbyangs //
NK028(sa)001:13938: bsam dag ngag gi bstod de gus mchod nas //
NK028(sa)001:13939: sa bcu rims kyi bsgrod de sangs rgyas par //
NK028(sa)001:13940: tshogs gnyis rdzogs nas chos kyi rgyal por shog /
NK028(sa)001:13941: lus kyi las ni rnam gsum dang /
NK028(sa)001:13942: ngag gi rnam pa bzhi dag dang //
NK028(sa)001:13943: yid kyi rnam pa gsum po rnams //
NK028(sa)001:13944: de dag thams cad bdag bshags so //
NK028(sa)001:13945: bdag gis sdig pa'i las gang dag /
NK028(sa)001:13947: sangs rgyas spyan sngar mchis nas ni //
NK028(sa)001:13948: de dag thams cad bshags par bgyi /
NK028(sa)001:13949: sems kyi dbang du gyur pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:13950: bdag gi sdig pa ci bgyis pa //
NK028(sa)001:13951: sangs rgyas spyan sngar mchis nas bshags //
NK028(sa)001:13952: sangs rgyas sku gsum mnyes pa'i byin brlabs dang //
NK028(sa)001:13953: chos nyid mi 'gyur bden pa'i byin brlabs dang //
NK028(sa)001:13954: dge 'dun mi phyed 'dus pa'i byin brlabs dang //
NK028(sa)001:13955: rgyu rkyen rten 'brel tshogs pa'i nus mthu dang /
NK028(sa)001:13956: bdag gis dang ba'i smon lam btab pa'i mthus //
NK028(sa)001:13957: ji ltar bsams pa bzhin du 'grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13958: bdag gis deng 'dir sangs rgyas dang //
NK028(sa)001:13959: chos dang dge 'dun la mchod pas //
NK028(sa)001:13960: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun gsum //
NK028(sa)001:13961: rtag tu 'jig rten gnas par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13962: khyed la mchod pa'i bsod nams gyis //
NK028(sa)001:13963: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK028(sa)001:13964: khyod 'drar yun rings tshogs bsags te //
NK028(sa)001:13965: yon tan khyed dang mnyam par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13966: bdag gi 'di dang gzhan dag tu //
NK028(sa)001:13967: bsod nams gang dag gang bgyis pa //
NK028(sa)001:13968: bsod nams de yis mgon po khyod //
NK028(sa)001:13969: rtag tu bdag gi mthong par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13970: bdag cag 'di na 'chi 'pho skye ba na //
NK028(sa)001:13971: mi dge gzhan du dbang du mi 'gyur zhing //
NK028(sa)001:13972: tshe la nad kyi bar chad med pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:13973: skyes ma thag tu chos dang phrad par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13974: gang rten gang la brten bcas nas //
NK028(sa)001:13975: zag zad mchog la mchod gyur pa /
NK028(sa)001:13976: de 'dra ba yi grogs po dang //
NK028(sa)001:13977: rtag par rgyun du 'phrad par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13978: bsod nams 'di yis thams cad gzigs pa nyid //
NK028(sa)001:13979: thob nas nyes pa'i sgra rnams pham byas ste //
NK028(sa)001:13980: skye rgas na 'chi'i rba klong 'khrugs pa la //
NK028(sa)001:13981: srid pa'i mtsho las 'gro ba ma lus 'don par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13982: dge ba 'di yi skye bo kun /
NK028(sa)001:13983: bsod nams ye shes tshogs bsags te //
NK028(sa)001:13984: bsod nams ye shes las byung ba //
NK028(sa)001:13985: dam pa gnyis ni thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13986: phyag 'tshal ba dang mchod cing bshags pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:13987: rjes su yid rang bskul zhing gsol ba yi //
NK028(sa)001:13988: dge ba cung zad bdag gis ci bsags pa //
NK028(sa)001:13989: thams cad bdag gis byang chub phyir bsngo'o //
NK028(sa)001:13990: byang chub spyod pa bdag ni bdag spyod cing //
NK028(sa)001:13991: 'gro ba kun du skye ba dran par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13992: tshe rab kun tu 'chi 'pho skye ba na //
NK028(sa)001:13993: rtag tu bdag ni rab tu 'byung par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13994: rgyal ba kun gyi rjes su slob gyur te //
NK028(sa)001:13995: bzang po spyod pa yongs su rdzogs byed cing //
NK028(sa)001:13996: tshul khrims spyod pa dri med yongs dag par //
NK028(sa)001:13997: rtag tu ma nyams skyon med spyod par shog /
NK028(sa)001:13998: 'jam dpa' dpa' bo'i ji ltar mkhyen pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:13999: kun tu bzang po de yang de bzhin te //
NK028(sa)001:14000: de dag kun gyi rjes su bdag slob cing /
NK028(sa)001:14001: dge ba 'di dag thams cad rab tu ba sngo //
NK028(sa)001:14002: dus gsum gshegs pa rgyal ba thams cad kyi //
NK028(sa)001:14003: bsngo ba gang lags mchog tu sngags pa des //
NK028(sa)001:14004: bdag gi dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di kun yang //
NK028(sa)001:14005: bzang po spyod phyir rab tu bsngo bar bgyis //
NK028(sa)001:14006: bdag ni 'chi ba'i dus byed gyur pa na //
NK028(sa)001:14007: sgrib pa thams cad dag ni phyir gsal te //
NK028(sa)001:14008: mngon sum snang ba mtha' yas de mthong nas //
NK028(sa)001:14009: bde ba can gyis zhing der rab tu 'gro //
NK028(sa)001:14010: der song nas ni smon lam 'di dag kyang //
NK028(sa)001:14011: thams cad ma lus sngon du 'grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:14012: de dag ma lus bdag gis yongs su bskangs //
NK028(sa)001:14013: 'jig rten ji srid sems can phan par bgyi //
NK028(sa)001:14014: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor bzang zhing dga' ba der //
NK028(sa)001:14015: pad+mo dam pa bzhin du mdzes las skyes //
NK028(sa)001:14016: snang ba mtha' yas rgyal bas mngon sum du /
NK028(sa)001:14017: lung bstan pa yang bdag gis der thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:14018: der ni bdag gi lung bstan rab thob nas //
NK028(sa)001:14019: sprul pa mang po bye ba phrag brgya yi //
NK028(sa)001:14020: blo'i stobs kyi phyogs bcu rnams su yang //
NK028(sa)001:14021: sems can rnams la phan pa mang bgyid shog /
NK028(sa)001:14022: bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam btab pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:14023: dge ba cung zad bdag gis ci bsags pa /
NK028(sa)001:14024: des ni 'gro ba'i smon lam dge ba rnams /
NK028(sa)001:14025: skad cig gcig gis thams cad 'byor par shog /
NK028(sa)001:14026: gang yang bzang po spyod pa'i bsngo ba yis //
NK028(sa)001:14027: bsod nams dam pa mtha' yas thob pa des //
NK028(sa)001:14028: 'gro ba sdug bsngal chu bor bying ba rnams //
NK028(sa)001:14029: 'od dpag med ba'i gnas rab thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:14030: thugs rje chen po rkang gnyis mchog gyur pa //
NK028(sa)001:14031: sbyin pa'i pha rol phyin pa phun sum tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:14032: ji ltar bco ma ldan sbyin pa'i pha rol phyin //
NK028(sa)001:14033: bdag kyang ring por mi thog de bzhin shog /
NK028(sa)001:14034: thugs rje chen po rkang gnyis mchog gyur pa //
NK028(sa)001:14035: tshul khrims pha rol phyin pa phun sum tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:14036: ji ltar bcom ldan tshul khrims pha rol phyin //
NK028(sa)001:14037: bdag kyang ring por mi thogs de bzhin shog /
NK028(sa)001:14038: thugs rje chen po rkang gnyis mchog gyur pa //
NK028(sa)001:14039: bzod pa'i pha rol phyin pa /
NK028(sa)001:14040: ji ltar bcom ldan bzod pa'i pha rol phyin //
NK028(sa)001:14041: bdag kyang ring por mi thogs de bzhin shog /
NK028(sa)001:14042: thugs rje chen po rkang gnyis mchog gyur pa //
NK028(sa)001:14043: brtson 'grus pha rol phyin pa phun sum tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:14044: ji ltar bcom ldan brtson 'grus pha rol phyin //
NK028(sa)001:14045: bdag kyang ring por mi thog de bzhin shog /
NK028(sa)001:14046: thugs rje chen po rkang gnyis mchog gyur pa //
NK028(sa)001:14047: bsam gtan pha rol phyin pa phun sum tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:14048: ji ltar bcom ldan bsam bstan pha rol phyin //
NK028(sa)001:14049: bdag kyang ring por mi thogs de bzhin shog /
NK028(sa)001:14050: thugs rje chen po rkang gnyis mchog gyur pa //
NK028(sa)001:14051: shes rab pha rol phyin pa phun sum tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:14052: ji ltar bcom ldan ye shes pha rol phyin //
NK028(sa)001:14053: bdag kyang ring por mi thogs de bzhin shog /
NK028(sa)001:14054: thugs rje chen po rkang gnyis mchog gyur pa //
NK028(sa)001:14055: ye shes pha rol phyin pa phun sum tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:14056: ji ltar bcom ldan ye shes pha rol phyin //
NK028(sa)001:14057: bdag kyang ring por mi thogs de bzhin shog /
NK028(sa)001:14058: thugs rje chen po rkang gnyis mchog gyur pa //
NK028(sa)001:14059: chos sku pha rol phyin pa phun sum tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:14060: ji ltar bcom ldan chos sku pha rol phyin //
NK028(sa)001:14061: bdag kyang ring por mi thogs de bzhin shog /
NK028(sa)001:14062: thugs rje chen po rkang gnyis mchog gyur pa //
NK028(sa)001:14063: longs sku pha rol phyin pa phun sum tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:14064: ji ltar bcom ldan longs sku pha rol phyin //
NK028(sa)001:14065: bdag kyang ring por mi thogs de bzhin shog /
NK028(sa)001:14066: thugs rje chen po rkang gnyis mchog gyur pa //
NK028(sa)001:14067: sprul sku pha rol phyin pa phun sum tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:14068: ji ltar bcom ldan sprul sku pha rol phyin //
NK028(sa)001:14069: bdag kyang ring por mi thogs de bzhin shog /
NK028(sa)001:14070: nor gyi nor mchog dad pa'i nor //
NK028(sa)001:14072: dad pa'i nor 'di mdun na sdod //
NK028(sa)001:14073: nyi ma dang ni 'od zer bzhin //
NK028(sa)001:14074: de dag nyid dang lhan cig tu //
NK028(sa)001:14075: dad pa'i nor dang mi 'bral shog /
NK028(sa)001:14076: tshul khrims gtong pa thos pa'i nor //
NK028(sa)001:14077: ngo tsha khrel yod shes rab nor //
NK028(sa)001:14078: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK028(sa)001:14079: nor bu rin chen 'di phul pas //
NK028(sa)001:14080: bkres dang skom pa rgyun bcad nas //
NK028(sa)001:14081: 'byor pa phun sum tshogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:14082: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK028(sa)001:14083: btsun mo rin chen 'di phul bas //
NK028(sa)001:14084: chos nyid zab mo'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:14085: thabs dang shes rab mi 'bral shog /
NK028(sa)001:14086: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK028(sa)001:14087: blon po rin chen 'di phul bas //
NK028(sa)001:14088: phyi nang gsang ba'i don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:14089: yon tan thams cad rtogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:14090: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK028(sa)001:14091: glang po rin chen 'di phul bas //
NK028(sa)001:14092: ltas ngan rtags pa rab gsal ste //
NK028(sa)001:14094: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad la /
NK028(sa)001:14095: rta mchog rin chen 'di phul bas //
NK028(sa)001:14096: rdzu 'phrul mchog gi shugs thob nas //
NK028(sa)001:14097: sangs rgyas zhing du phyin par shog /
NK028(sa)001:14098: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK028(sa)001:14099: dmag dpon rin chen 'di phul bas //
NK028(sa)001:14100: phas kyi rgol ba tshar bcad nas /
NK028(sa)001:14101: snyems dang bral ba'i mchog thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:14102: shar phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i 'jig rten na //
NK028(sa)001:14103: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:14104: rdo rje rigs kyi 'khor dang skyid //
NK028(sa)001:14105: bdag kyang de'i skyid dang 'dra bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:14106: lho phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i 'jig rten na //
NK028(sa)001:14107: bcom ldan rin chen 'byung ldan bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:14108: rin chen rigs kyi 'khor dang skyid //
NK028(sa)001:14109: bdag kyang de'i skyid dang 'dra bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:14110: nub phyogs bde ba can gyi zhing khams na //
NK028(sa)001:14111: bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:14113: bdag kyang de'i skyid dang 'dra par shog /
NK028(sa)001:14114: byang phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i 'jig rten na //
NK028(sa)001:14115: bcom ldan don yod grub pa bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:14116: las kyi rigs kyi 'khor dang skyid //
NK028(sa)001:14117: bdag kyang de'i skyid dang 'dra bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:14118: dbus phyogs mngon par dga' ba'i 'jig rten na //
NK028(sa)001:14119: bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:14120: gsang ba gsum gyi 'khor dang skyid //
NK028(sa)001:14121: bdag kyang de'i skyid dang 'dra bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:14122: dad pa can gyi btang ba'i nor mi mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:14123: rgya mtsho che las bcus pa'i chu mi mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:14124: bdag cag slong ba'i bu ni ngoms par mdzod //
NK028(sa)001:14125: tshe ring skal ldan khyed la bsod snyoms 'debs /
NK028(sa)001:14126: slong na chung yang sbyin par bya //
NK028(sa)001:14127: snyan par smra zhing khro mi bya //
NK028(sa)001:14128: 'di gsum ldan pa'i gang zag ni /
NK028(sa)001:14129: lha ru skye ba'i rgyu yin no //
NK028(sa)001:14130: gang gi don du sbyin pa btang //
NK028(sa)001:14132: bde ba'i don du sbyin btang na //
NK028(sa)001:14133: de ni bde bar 'gyur ba yin //
NK028(sa)001:14134: sangs rgyas gtso la ston mchog mnga' ba //
NK028(sa)001:14135: che dgus mchod cing smon lam sprin tshogs 'dus //
NK028(sa)001:14136: gong mas mchog nyes ston pas char phab pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:14137: bkra shis dam pa des 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14138: skyobs pa'i chos la legs pa'i tshogs mnga' ba //
NK028(sa)001:14139: shin tu phan dang bde dang nges gsung pa //
NK028(sa)001:14140: 'khor ba rtag bde mya ngan med pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:14141: bkra shis dam pa deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14142: dge la mthu rtsal smad mnga' ba //
NK028(sa)001:14143: slab bzhi legs spyad btson pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK028(sa)001:14144: bdag gzhan don ched bsgrub pa'i lam bzhugs pa //
NK028(sa)001:14145: bkra shis dam pa deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14146: bsod nams ri bo bzhin du brten pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:14147: rgyud 'dzin nyi zla bzhin du gsal ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:14148: snyan pas nam mkha' bzhin du khyab pas te //
NK028(sa)001:14149: gsum po des kyang rtag tu bsrungs gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:14150: bgegs rigs stong phrag rgya bcu zhi ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:14151: mi mthun gnod pa'i rkyen dang bral ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:14152: 'dod pa bsgrubs cing phun sum tshogs gyur pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:14153: bzhi po des kyang rtag tu bsrungs gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:14154: lo brgya mtsho zhing ston brgya mthong ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:14155: tshe ring ba dang longs spyod 'phel ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:14156: theg pa mchog gis nges par 'byung 'gyur ba //
NK028(sa)001:14157: lnga po 'dis kyang rtag tu bsrungs gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:14158: sbyin pa gtang zhing tshul khrims bsrungs ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:14159: bzod pa sgom zhing brtson 'grus rtsom pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:14160: mnyam par 'jog cing shes rab bskyed pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:14161: drug po 'dis kyang rtag tu bsrungs gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:14162: rgya mtsho lta bur rgal dka' 'khor ba'i 'dam las rgal //
NK028(sa)001:14163: bsod nams ye shes bsags daka'i tshogs gnyis ma lus rdzogs //
NK028(sa)001:14164: 'gro ba kun gyi gnyen gcig gyur pa de bzhin gshegs //
NK028(sa)001:14165: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14166: skye 'gags med pa rtogs pa'i 'chi byed mtha' dag spangs //
NK028(sa)001:14167: ma rig mun pa sel mdzad stong nyid sgrol ma'i macha ga /
NK028(sa)001:14168: dmigs pa sna tshogs spangs pa las kyi bde 'grub chos //
NK028(sa)001:14169: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14170: rang don spangs shing rtag tu lhur len pa //
NK028(sa)001:14171: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la lta bas rgyang srings shing //
NK028(sa)001:14172: dad pa brtson 'grus lhur len grogs mchog byang chub sems //
NK028(sa)001:14173: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14174: rnying ma'i dus 'dir smon lam dbang gi sku sprul nas //
NK028(sa)001:14175: bdag cag lta bu'i gdul daka'i nyon mongs byas pa las //
NK028(sa)001:14176: sku dang gsung gis 'dren mdzad bcom ldan sh+aakya thub //
NK028(sa)001:14177: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14178: 'gro ba'i mig rgyu lta bu'i bcom ldan sh+aaka thub 'das //
NK028(sa)001:14179: sems can sdug bsngal skul ma skyabs pa lta bu yis //
NK028(sa)001:14180: don phyir pha rol phyin drug myur gshegs mi 'pham mgon //
NK028(sa)001:14181: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14182: 'das pa'i dus na sangs rgyas gyur kyang byang chub sems //
NK028(sa)001:14183: sdug bsngal ldan pa kun la ma ltar byams 'gyur zhing //
NK028(sa)001:14184: skyobs phyir dam bcas sa bcu'i tshul ston spyan ras gzigs //
NK028(sa)001:14185: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14186: mi shes dbang gis log rtog mtha' dag rab rgyas pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:14187: khams gsum 'khor ba'i zo chu'i rgyun ltar rab 'khor ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:14188: shes rab dmigs med bde ba'i gnas 'dir 'jam dpal lags //
NK028(sa)001:14189: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14190: 'dul ba'i dbang gi drag po'i khro bo'i skur ston pa //
NK028(sa)001:14191: khams gsum bdud rnams bde dang bcas pa zhi la dgod //
NK028(sa)001:14192: thugs rje mi g.yo phyag na rdo rje mthu stobs mchog /
NK028(sa)001:14193: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14194: rnam par snang mdzad ye shes dam pa mtsho chen ldan //
NK028(sa)001:14195: zla ba nya 'dra'i sku mnga' srid ba'i mthar phyin pa //
NK028(sa)001:14196: dgongs pa mtha' dag rdzogs pa'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK028(sa)001:14197: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14198: deng 'dir skyes dgu rnam par zhi byed shog /
NK028(sa)001:14199: mi 'khrugs rgyal po srid dang rnam sbyong pa //
NK028(sa)001:14200: mgon po yon tan kun gyi bkra shis pa //
NK028(sa)001:14201: dge mnyam bsam sems ldan pa'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK028(sa)001:14202: bkra shis des ni skyes dgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK028(sa)001:14203: sangs rgyas yon tan rgyan gyis brgyan mdzad cing //
NK028(sa)001:14204: yang dag bden pa'i 'byor ba sbyin mdzad mi bslu ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:14205: rin chen 'byung zhes bya ba'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK028(sa)001:14206: bkra shis des ni skyes dgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK028(sa)001:14207: bsam gtan ting 'dzin dam pa pha rol phyin pa'i gnas //
NK028(sa)001:14208: ye shes pad+ma'i steng bzhugs dpag med tshe ldan zhing //
NK028(sa)001:14209: tshe grangs med par byin gyis rlobs ba'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK028(sa)001:14210: bkra shis des ni skyes dgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK028(sa)001:14211: sems can don gyi las la thugs kyis sbyor mdzad cing /
NK028(sa)001:14212: 'gro ba kun gyi 'ching ba'i bcings las grol 'gyur ba //
NK028(sa)001:14213: thub mchog don yod grub pa'i gang lags pa //
NK028(sa)001:14214: bkra shis dam pa des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK028(sa)001:14215: de bzhin gshegs pa lnga'i bden pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:14216: bkra shis bde legs thams cad 'byung bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:14217: bcom ldan rnam par gzigs ni rgyal rigs gzi brjid can //
NK028(sa)001:14218: tshe lo brgyad khri'i dus na grong khyer gnyer ldan du //
NK028(sa)001:14219: pa ta la'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:14220: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pas deng 'dir bkra shis shog /
NK028(sa)001:14221: bde gshegs gtsug tor mnga' ba rgyal rigs rdzu 'phrul can //
NK028(sa)001:14222: tshe lo bdun khri'i dus na ka na'i grong khyer na //
NK028(sa)001:14223: pun ta ri ka'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:14224: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pa deng 'dir bkra shis shog /
NK028(sa)001:14225: rgyal ba thams cad skyob pa rgyal rigs blo gros can //
NK028(sa)001:14226: tshe lo drug khri'i dus na grong khyer gnyan yod du //
NK028(sa)001:14227: shing mchog pa la'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:14228: bkra shis phun tshogs pa deng 'dir bkra shis shog /
NK028(sa)001:14229: thub pa 'khor ba 'jig ni stobs ldan bram ze'i rigs //
NK028(sa)001:14230: tshe lo bzhi khri'i dus na grong khyer bde ldan du //
NK028(sa)001:14231: ri shi ma'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:14232: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pa deng 'dir bkra shis shog /
NK028(sa)001:14233: 'dren pa gser ldan bslab pa mchog ldan bram ze'i rigs //
NK028(sa)001:14234: tshe lo gsum khri'i dus na grong khyer mdzes ldan du //
NK028(sa)001:14235: u dum wa ra'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:14236: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pas deng 'dir bkra shis shog /
NK028(sa)001:14237: skyob pa 'od bsrungs rgyal rigs bla med yon tan can //
NK028(sa)001:14238: tshe lo nyi khri'i dus na ba ra na si ru /
NK028(sa)001:14239: nya gro d+ha'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:14240: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pa'i deng 'dir bkra shis shog /
NK028(sa)001:14241: 'gro mgon sh+aakya thub ni rgyal rigs brtson 'grus can //
NK028(sa)001:14242: tshe lo brgya pa'i dus na grong khyer ser skya ru //
NK028(sa)001:14243: a shwa ta'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:14244: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pas deng 'dir bkra shis shog /
NK028(sa)001:14245: dam pa tog dkar dga' ldan pho brang du //
NK028(sa)001:14246: mi pham mgon la rgyal tshab dbang bskur zhing //
NK028(sa)001:14247: 'dzam gling nyid du glang chen thal dkar gshegs //
NK028(sa)001:14248: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14249: rgyal po'i khab kyi grong khyer zas gtsang sras //
NK028(sa)001:14250: bud med g.yo sgyu spangs ba lha mdzes yum //
NK028(sa)001:14251: lhums nas zla bcur 'gro ldan sh+aakya rigs //
NK028(sa)001:14252: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14253: lum ra'i tshal ni nyams dga' glags sha'i shing //
NK028(sa)001:14254: yal ga nas bzung tshangs dang brgya sbyin 'du /
NK028(sa)001:14255: mkha' gshegs phyogs bcur pad+mo 'byung gyur pa /
NK028(sa)001:14256: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14257: gzhal yas khang mdzes drang srong mdun bzhag nas /
NK028(sa)001:14258: mtshan bltas shis par brjod cing ston pa 'byung gyur gang /
NK028(sa)001:14259: sh+aaka rigs bud med 'khor gyi kun du brgyan /
NK028(sa)001:14260: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14261: gzhon nu'i stobs kyi sgyu rtsal yig 'phongs bslab //
NK028(sa)001:14262: kun las mthar phyin lha mi kun las rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:14263: sh+aaka rigs 'jig rten gsal phyir btsun mo 'khor //
NK028(sa)001:14264: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14265: pho brang nas byung skye rgas na 'chi gzigs /
NK028(sa)001:14266: mi rnams smin mdzad lha yi mkha' la ni //
NK028(sa)001:14267: srid gsum rgyal phyir dbu skra mthon 'thing bregs /
NK028(sa)001:14268: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs /
NK028(sa)001:14269: lha yis rdzu 'phrul slangs nas ngur smrig phul //
NK028(sa)001:14270: ne ra dza rar thub pas dka' thub rdzogs //
NK028(sa)001:14271: bsam gtan nas bzhengs 'o thug bzhes //
NK028(sa)001:14272: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14273: pad+ma la sogs khyu mchog shing drung du //
NK028(sa)001:14274: skyil dkrung mi mchog bdud brtul nas //
NK028(sa)001:14275: tho rangs bdud rtsi 'chi med phun sum tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:14276: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14277: ba ra na sir chos kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK028(sa)001:14278: kun mkhyen lnga sde bzang la bden bzhi bstan //
NK028(sa)001:14279: lha mi mi min rnams kyang 'du gyur pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:14280: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK028(sa)001:14281: nga rgyal mu stegs ston pa drug btul pa //
NK028(sa)001:14282: glang chen rab myos rbad pas lhas sbyin btul //
NK028(sa)001:14283: drang srong spre rgyal lcang shes sbrang rtsi mchog /
NK028(sa)001:14284: bkra shis pad+mo gzhon nu lta bu sh+aakya'i rigs //
NK028(sa)001:14285: zas gtsang sras kyi rgyal rigs 'khor lo bsgyur //
NK028(sa)001:14286: sku bltams nas bzung mdzad pa ma lus rdzogs /
NK028(sa)001:14287: bkra shis byams ba'i stobs kyis 'gro ba ma lus sgrol //
NK028(sa)001:14288: sems can thams cad zhi ba'i lam la dgod //
NK028(sa)001:14289: grong khyer r+ts+wa mchog dam par dgongs pa rdzogs //
NK028(sa)001:14290: bkra shis gsang bdag thugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:14291: dkyil 'khor bri dang mchod pa bsham /
NK028(sa)001:14292: lha bskyed pa dang spyan drangs dang /
NK028(sa)001:14293: mchod pa 'bul rim pa rgyas par sbyar //
NK028(sa)001:14294: bstod pa don ni 'di lta ste /
NK028(sa)001:14295: pho brang dbus kyi gzhal yas su //
NK028(sa)001:14296: rnam dag pad+ma'i lte ba la //
NK028(sa)001:14297: mi 'jigs brgyad bsgom rin chen khri //
NK028(sa)001:14298: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:14299: thugs mchog rdo rje sems dpa' ni //
NK028(sa)001:14300: sku mdog sngon po nam mkha'i 'od //
NK028(sa)001:14301: sa gnon chen po'i phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14302: mtshan dang dpe byad brgyan spras la //
NK028(sa)001:14304: shar phyogs sangs rgyas dga' ba'i sbyan /
NK028(sa)001:14306: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK028(sa)001:14308: lho phyogs yongs su dgongs ba'i rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:14310: mchod sbyin chen po'i phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14312: nub phyogs gser gyi 'od zer ni //
NK028(sa)001:14314: ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14316: byang phyogs sangs rgyas 'od kyi dpal //
NK028(sa)001:14318: skyabs sbyin chen pa'i phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14320: shar lho zhi ba'i dbang po ni //
NK028(sa)001:14321: sku mdog sngo skya byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14323: lho nub sangs rgyas me long 'od //
NK028(sa)001:14325: skyabs sbyin chen po'i phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14327: nub byang sangs rgyas yid 'ong dbyangs //
NK028(sa)001:14329: ting nge 'dzin gya phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14331: byang shar sangs rgya me long 'od //
NK028(sa)001:14333: skyabs sbyin chen po'i phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14335: de dag ni pad ma 'dab brgyad lte ba bcas
NK028(sa)001:14336: pa'i dbus kyi lha tshogs rnams la bstod cing mchod
NK028(sa)001:14337: pa 'bul ba'i cho ga'i las rims so //
NK028(sa)001:14338: de nas 'di'i phyi rim la 'khor lo rtsibs drug tu byas pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:14339: byang shar gyi rtsibs drug tu byas pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:14340: thub pa chen po nyid kyi gtso byas pa'i gtso
NK028(sa)001:14341: 'khor dgu la mchod pa 'bul ba'i las rim ni
NK028(sa)001:14342: // h+aum 'khor lo rtsibs drug byang shar gyis //
NK028(sa)001:14343: dbus kyi pad+ma'i lte ba la //
NK028(sa)001:14344: rin chen khri rkang mi 'jigs brgyad //
NK028(sa)001:14345: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs su /
NK028(sa)001:14346: bcom ldan thub pa chen po ni //
NK028(sa)001:14347: sku mdog gtso mo gser gyi mdog /
NK028(sa)001:14348: phyag g.yas sa gnon chen po'i rgya //
NK028(sa)001:14349: g.yon pa mnyam bzhag ting 'dzin ldan //
NK028(sa)001:14351: shar na yum chen gser gyi mdog /
NK028(sa)001:14352: rdo rje skyil dkrung phyag bzhi yi //
NK028(sa)001:14353: dang po mnyam bzhag phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14355: g.yon pa glegs bam po ti bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:14357: shar lho mtshams na lha'i thub //
NK028(sa)001:14358: srid thub 'dzin zhes mtshan du grags //
NK028(sa)001:14359: 'thing kha go mtshon phyag na bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:14362: gser gyi mdog can mnyam bzhag rgya //
NK028(sa)001:14363: sangs rgyas 'gro la dam tshig ston //
NK028(sa)001:14365: lho nub mtshams na yid dwags thub //
NK028(sa)001:14366: rnam par snang byed mtshan du grags //
NK028(sa)001:14367: dmar nag phyag na sgrom bu bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:14369: nub na sha ra'i bu zhes pa /
NK028(sa)001:14370: sku mdog gser ldan dka' thub gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:14371: phyag na mkhar bsil lhung bzed bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:14373: nub byang mtshams na byol song thub //
NK028(sa)001:14374: rnam par non zhes mtshan du grags //
NK028(sa)001:14375: ser nag phyag na po ti bsnams /
NK028(sa)001:14377: byang gi phyogs na lha min thub //
NK028(sa)001:14378: rnam par rgyal zhes mtshan du grags //
NK028(sa)001:14381: byang shar mtshams na dmyal ba'i thub //
NK028(sa)001:14382: rnam par rgyal zhes mtshan du grags //
NK028(sa)001:14383: dud kha phyag na me chu bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:14385: de nas 'og gzhi 'khor lo rtsibs drug du yod pa'i dbang gis //
NK028(sa)001:14386: rtsibs shar lhor byang chub yang 'phrin las su brjod pa'i tshig 'di skad do //
NK028(sa)001:14387: h+aum shar lho'i 'khor lo rtsibs drug gi /
NK028(sa)001:14388: dbus kyi pad+ma'i lte ba la //
NK028(sa)001:14389: rin chen khri rkang glang chen brgyad //
NK028(sa)001:14390: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:14391: sku mchog rnam par snang mdzad ni //
NK028(sa)001:14392: sku mdog dkar po'i gangs ri'i mdog /
NK028(sa)001:14393: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14395: shar phyogs sangs rgyas zla 'od dpal //
NK028(sa)001:14397: sa gnon chen po'i phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14399: lho phyogs sangs rgyas nyi snying dpal //
NK028(sa)001:14400: sku mdog ser po gser gyi mdog /
NK028(sa)001:14401: mchod sbyin chen po'i phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14403: nub phyogs sangs rgyas spos kyi rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:14405: ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya ldan //
NK028(sa)001:14407: byang phyogs sangs rgyas mngon spro'i rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:14409: 'gro la skyabs sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14411: shar lho mtshams na rin chen rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:14413: sa non chen po'i phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14415: lho nub mtshams na 'od zer dpal //
NK028(sa)001:14417: 'gro la chos sbyin phyag rgya mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:14419: nub byang mtshams na dka' thub rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:14421: ting 'dzin mnyam bzhag phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14423: byang shar mtshams su gtsug tor snying //
NK028(sa)001:14425: 'gro la skyabs sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14427: lho phyogs rtsibs kyi drang po la /
NK028(sa)001:14428: rin 'byung gtso 'khor bskyed pa'i cho ga ni /
NK028(sa)001:14429: h+aum 'khor lo rtsibs drug lho phyogs kyi //
NK028(sa)001:14430: dbus kyi pad+ma'i lte ba la //
NK028(sa)001:14431: rin chen khri rkang rta mchog khri //
NK028(sa)001:14432: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:14433: yon tan rin chen 'byung gnas ni //
NK028(sa)001:14434: gtso mo gser gyis mdog dang ldan //
NK028(sa)001:14435: mchod sbyin chen po'i phyag rgya can /
NK028(sa)001:14438: sku mdog shel gyi mdog ltar dkar //
NK028(sa)001:14439: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14441: lho phyogs sangs rgyas bkod pa'i rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:14442: sku mdog ser po gzi brjid can //
NK028(sa)001:14443: sa gnon phyag rgyas bdud dpung 'joms //
NK028(sa)001:14445: nub phyogs sangs rgyas gser gyis gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:14446: sku mdog pad+ma ra ga la //
NK028(sa)001:14447: ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya ldan //
NK028(sa)001:14449: byang phyogs sangs rgyas dpal gyi rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:14450: sku mdog un tra ni la'i 'od //
NK028(sa)001:14451: 'gro ba skyabs sbyin phyag rgya mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:14453: shar lho sangs rgyas snang ba brtsegs //
NK028(sa)001:14454: sku mdog dkar gser mdangs dang ldan //
NK028(sa)001:14455: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:14457: lho nub sangs rgyas mya ngan med //
NK028(sa)001:14459: sa gnon chen po'i phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14460: de la phyag 'tshal nub byang sangs rgyas dga' ba'i dpal //
NK028(sa)001:14461: sku mdog dmar ljang 'od dang ldan //
NK028(sa)001:14462: ting 'dzin mnyam bzhag phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14464: byang shar sangs rgyas gzi brjid dpal //
NK028(sa)001:14465: sku mdog dkar ljang 'od dang ldan //
NK028(sa)001:14466: skyabs sbyin chen po'i phyag rgya mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:14468: de nas lho nub mtshams kyi rtsibs la //
NK028(sa)001:14469: yang thub pa chen po nyid kyis gtso byas ba'i //
NK028(sa)001:14470: lha tshogs dgu bskyed ba'i cho ga las rims ni /
NK028(sa)001:14471: h+aum 'khor lo rtsib drug lho nub kyi //
NK028(sa)001:14472: dbus kyi pad+ma'i lte ba la //
NK028(sa)001:14473: mi 'jigs brgyad bsnol rin chen khri //
NK028(sa)001:14474: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs na //
NK028(sa)001:14475: bcom ldan sh+aakya thub pa che //
NK028(sa)001:14476: gser gyis mdog can sangs rgyas gtso //
NK028(sa)001:14477: phyag g.yas sa gnon g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK028(sa)001:14479: shar phyogs sangs rgyas dri med sgra //
NK028(sa)001:14480: sku mdog gangs ri lta bu la //
NK028(sa)001:14481: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgyar ldan //
NK028(sa)001:14483: lho phyogs sangs rgyas dkon mchog sbrin //
NK028(sa)001:14484: sku mdog sngon po ut+pala mdog /
NK028(sa)001:14485: mchod sbyin chen po'i phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14487: nub phyogs yon tan 'byung gnas ni //
NK028(sa)001:14488: sku mdog dmar po byi ru'i mdog /
NK028(sa)001:14489: ting nge 'dzin gyis phyag rgya bcas //
NK028(sa)001:14491: byang phyogs sangs rgyas seng ge'i sgra //
NK028(sa)001:14493: 'gro la skyabs sbyin phyag rgya bcas //
NK028(sa)001:14495: shar lho mdzes pa'i me tog ni //
NK028(sa)001:14497: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya bcas //
NK028(sa)001:14499: lho nub sangs rgyas gzi brjid dpal //
NK028(sa)001:14500: sku mdog dmar ser 'od dang ldan //
NK028(sa)001:14501: mchod sbyin chen po phyag rgya bcas //
NK028(sa)001:14503: nub byang tsan dan dri med dpal //
NK028(sa)001:14504: sku mdog dmar ljang mdangs dang ldan //
NK028(sa)001:14505: ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya bcas //
NK028(sa)001:14507: byang shar sangs rgyas snying rje'i rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:14508: sku mdog dkar ljang 'od zer ldan //
NK028(sa)001:14509: 'gro la skyabs sbyin phyag rgya bcas //
NK028(sa)001:14511: de nas rtsibs drug gi nub byang gi rtsibs la //
NK028(sa)001:14512: 'khor lo drug du song ba'i stobs kyis snang ba
NK028(sa)001:14513: mtha' yas gtso 'khor dgod pa'i cho ga'i las rims
NK028(sa)001:14515: h+aum 'khor lo rtsibs drug nub byang gi //
NK028(sa)001:14516: dbus kyi pad+ma'i lte ba la //
NK028(sa)001:14517: rin chen khri rkang rma bya'i khri //
NK028(sa)001:14518: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:14519: gsung mchog snang ba mtha' yas ni //
NK028(sa)001:14520: sku mdog dmar po byi ru'i mdog /
NK028(sa)001:14521: mnyam bzhag ting 'dzin phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14523: shar phyogs sangs rgyas nges par gshegs //
NK028(sa)001:14524: sku mdog dung ltar dkar zhing mtsher //
NK028(sa)001:14525: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14527: lho phyogs sangs rgyas nges par gsungs //
NK028(sa)001:14528: sku mdog sngon po nam mkha'i 'od //
NK028(sa)001:14529: 'gro la chos sbyin phyag rgya ston //
NK028(sa)001:14530: de la phyag 'tshal mchod nub phyogs sangs rgyas rdal pa che //
NK028(sa)001:14531: sku mdog dmar po mdangs dang ldan //
NK028(sa)001:14532: sa gnon chen po'i phyag rgya mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:14534: byang phyogs sangs rgyas me tog dbyangs //
NK028(sa)001:14535: sku mdog ljang la 'od zer ldan //
NK028(sa)001:14536: skyabs sbyin chen po'i phyag rgya ston //
NK028(sa)001:14538: shar lho sangs rgyas grags pa'i dpal //
NK028(sa)001:14540: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya ston //
NK028(sa)001:14542: lho nub sangs rgyas sprul ba'i rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:14543: sku mdog pad+ma ra ga'i mdangs //
NK028(sa)001:14544: 'gro la chos kyi phyag rgya ston //
NK028(sa)001:14546: nub byang sgra dbyangs mi zad pa //
NK028(sa)001:14548: sa gnon chen po'i phyag rgya mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:14550: byang shar sangs rgyas sman pa'i rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:14552: 'gro la skyabs sbyin phyag rgya ston //
NK028(sa)001:14554: byang phyogs kyi rtsibs drang po la /
NK028(sa)001:14555: 'phrin las don yod grub pa gatsa /
NK028(sa)001:14556: 'khor bcas bskyed pa'i cho ga'i las rims ni /
NK028(sa)001:14557: h+aum 'khor lo rtsibs drug byang phyogs kyi //
NK028(sa)001:14558: dbus kyi pad+ma'i lte ba la //
NK028(sa)001:14559: rin chen khri rkang shang shang khri /
NK028(sa)001:14560: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:14561: 'phrin las don yod grub pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:14562: sku mdog in tra ni la'i mdog /
NK028(sa)001:14563: skyabs sbyin phyag rgyas las rnams 'grub //
NK028(sa)001:14565: shar phyogs dge ba'i bshes gnyen ni //
NK028(sa)001:14566: sku mdog dkar po dung gi mdog /
NK028(sa)001:14567: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya ston //
NK028(sa)001:14569: lho phyogs sangs rgyas ngan song sbyong //
NK028(sa)001:14570: sku mdog sngon po g.yu'i mdog /
NK028(sa)001:14571: chos sbyin phyag rgyas 'gro don mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:14573: nub phyogs kun gyis slob dpon ni //
NK028(sa)001:14575: ting nge 'dzin gyis phyag rgya ston //
NK028(sa)001:14577: byang phyogs sangs rgyas rnam par rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:14579: sa gnon phyag rgyas gdon bgegs 'joms //
NK028(sa)001:14581: shar lho me tog bkod pa'i rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:14582: sku mdog mdangs ldan ljang sngon 'od //
NK028(sa)001:14583: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgyas mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:14585: lho nub sangs rgyas thams cad snang //
NK028(sa)001:14586: sku mdog ljang zer 'od dang ldan //
NK028(sa)001:14587: 'gro la chos sbyin phyag rgyas mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:14589: nub byang sangs rgyas tsan dan dri //
NK028(sa)001:14591: ting 'dzin mnyam bzhag phyag rgya ldan //
NK028(sa)001:14593: byang shar sangs rgyas leng 'bum gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:14595: sa gnon chen pa'i phyag rgya can //
NK028(sa)001:14597: ces gsung pa de dag 'khor lo rtsibs drug gi
NK028(sa)001:14598: lha tshogs rnams la mchod pa 'bul ba'i las rims
NK028(sa)001:14599: so // de nas phyi rol du glo bur bzhi la //
NK028(sa)001:14601: gru chad bzhi la phyi'i sems ma bzhi bkod ba'i cho ga brjod pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:14602: sprul sku rnam dag dbye'i dkyil 'khor gyis //
NK028(sa)001:14603: shar lho nub byang phyogs bzhi la /
NK028(sa)001:14604: sgeg mo 'phreng thog dbyangs dang gar /
NK028(sa)001:14605: glo 'a bur bzhi la bzhugs nas kyang /
NK028(sa)001:14606: dgyes pa chen po'i mchod 'bul ma //
NK028(sa)001:14608: gru chad shar lho lho nub dang /
NK028(sa)001:14609: nub byang byang shar mtshams bzhi la //
NK028(sa)001:14610: bdug spos me tog mar me dri //
NK028(sa)001:14611: mnyes pa'i mchod pa chen po 'bul //
NK028(sa)001:14613: lha rnams la bskal bzang gi sems dpa' bcu drug gi mchod pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:14614: sprul ba'i dkyil 'khor lha rnams kyis //
NK028(sa)001:14615: bskal bzang sems dpa' bcu drug ni //
NK028(sa)001:14616: rang rang so so'i 'dul bskal las //
NK028(sa)001:14617: byang chub sems dpa'i mdzad spyod kyis //
NK028(sa)001:14620: sgo bzhi la sgo ma bzhi'i phyag rgya brjod pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:14621: sprul ba'i dkyil 'khor sgo bzhi la //
NK028(sa)001:14622: tshad med sgo ma bzhi po ni //
NK028(sa)001:14623: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril /
NK028(sa)001:14624: shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi bsrungs //
NK028(sa)001:14625: log lta'i gdug pa ma lus 'dul //
NK028(sa)001:14627: phyi rim 'dod yon snam bu la //
NK028(sa)001:14628: mdzes pa'i bkra shis lha mo brgyad //
NK028(sa)001:14629: rang rang so so'i phyag mtshan gyis //
NK028(sa)001:14630: dgos 'dod re ba thams cad skong /
NK028(sa)001:14632: sprul sku rnam dbye'i dkyil 'khor lha drangs go dgu ma //
NK028(sa)001:14633: byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor lugs gcig 'di yin no //
NK028(sa)001:14634: 'di byang chub sems dpa'i dbang bskur ba'i lha grangs rgyas par dbang bskur ba lags /
NK028(sa)001:14635: bsdus pa lha bco lnga ma lags so //
NK028(sa)001:14638: stong pa'i ngang las rin po che'i bum pa mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i nang du /
NK028(sa)001:14639: rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yang khang pa la sogs /
NK028(sa)001:14640: bdag bskyed ltar bsnyen pa yan chad la bar skabs kyi 'don pa tshig kha bsgyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:14641: zhar la dbu rgyan la sogs pa'i dbang rdzas rnams kyang byin gyis brlabs so //
NK028(sa)001:14643: swa b+ha wa stong pa'i ngang las b+h+rum las rin
NK028(sa)001:14644: chen sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang pa
NK028(sa)001:14645: sogs bdag bskyed ltar bsnyen pa yan chod la bar
NK028(sa)001:14646: skabs kyi 'don pa kha sgyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:14648: bum pa dang dkyil 'khor la sogs la rab gnas byed /
NK028(sa)001:14649: grub na sbyin bsregs kyang ci rigs par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:14650: gnyis pa 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa la gnyis ste //
NK028(sa)001:14651: slob dpon bdag nyid 'jug cing dbang len pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:14652: slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:14653: dang po slob dpon 'jug cing dbang len pa ni //
NK028(sa)001:14655: gnyis pa slob ma 'jug cing dbang bskur pa la gnyis te //
NK028(sa)001:14656: dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa dbang bskur ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:14663: drug po gong dang mthun la //
NK028(sa)001:14668: gzhi'i dod la sems bskyed kyi sdom pa dbog pa la gnyis ste //
NK028(sa)001:14670: dbu ma lugs kyi cho ga'o //
NK028(sa)001:14677: sam ba ra bi d+hi kra ma /
NK028(sa)001:14679: sems bskyed pa dang sdom pa'i cho ga'i rim pa //
NK028(sa)001:14680: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gzhon nu gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:14681: ngan song thams cad 'jigs pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:14682: sgrib pa thams cad las grol zhing //
NK028(sa)001:14683: rdzogs sangs rgyas go 'phang rtsol mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:14684: byang chub sems la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:14685: rdzogs sangs rgyas dang dam pa'i chos //
NK028(sa)001:14686: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs la'ang /
NK028(sa)001:14687: ji bzhin byang chub sems dpa' yis //
NK028(sa)001:14688: sdom pa'i rim pa bri bar bya /
NK028(sa)001:14689: de la dang po cho ga bzhin byang chub du
NK028(sa)001:14690: sems bskyed pa byas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' thams
NK028(sa)001:14691: cad kyi tshul khrims gyis bslab pa la legs par
NK028(sa)001:14692: bslab pa la legs par bslab par 'dod pas //
NK028(sa)001:14693: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa la gnas pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:14694: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa'i cho ga shes pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:14695: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa dbog pa'i sgo nas /
NK028(sa)001:14696: slob ma rjes su bzung bar nus pa'i dge ba'i
NK028(sa)001:14697: bshes gnyen la phyag byas te de'i rkang pa la
NK028(sa)001:14698: gtugs nas gsol ba btab pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:14699: slob dpon khyed la bdag byang chub sems dpa'i tshul
NK028(sa)001:14700: khrims gyi sdom pa yang dag par blang ba len
NK028(sa)001:14701: par 'tshal gyis / gnod pa ma mchis na bdag la thugs brtse ba'i slad du /
NK028(sa)001:14702: myur du gsan 'tshal ba rigs so //
NK028(sa)001:14703: zhes de ltar lan gsum gyi bar du gsol ba gdab par bya'o /
NK028(sa)001:14704: rigs kyi bu khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:14705: 'di ltar sems can ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:14706: ma grol ba rnams grol ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:14707: dbugs ma phyung ba rnams dbugs dbyung yongs su mya
NK028(sa)001:14708: ngan las ma 'das pa rnams yongs su mya ngan
NK028(sa)001:14710: sangs rgyas gyi gdung rgyun mi 'chad par 'dod dam /
NK028(sa)001:14711: de la khyed kyi sems bskyed pa brtan pa dang yi dam brtan par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:14712: gzhan dang 'gran pa'i phyed du ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:14713: gzhan gyis nan gyis len du bcug pa ma yin nam /
NK028(sa)001:14715: de'i 'og tu de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa'i lugs sku mdun du bzhag la //
NK028(sa)001:14716: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa la sogs pa //
NK028(sa)001:14717: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad na bzhugs
NK028(sa)001:14718: pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad
NK028(sa)001:14719: la // ci nus pa'i phyi'i mchod pa lngas mchod pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:14720: phyag byas la de ma thag tu dge ba'i bshes gnyen bstan mthon po la 'dug la /
NK028(sa)001:14721: ston pa'i 'du shes kyi phyag byas ste /
NK028(sa)001:14722: spus mo g.yas pa'i lha nga sa la btsug te 'am /
NK028(sa)001:14723: tsog pur 'dug ste thal mo sbyar nas /
NK028(sa)001:14724: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa 'di ltar bskul bar byas ste /
NK028(sa)001:14725: slob dpon gyi byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims gyi
NK028(sa)001:14726: sdom pa yang dag par blang ba la stsal du
NK028(sa)001:14727: gsol / zhes de ltar lan gsum dge ba'i bshes gnyen la bskul nas /
NK028(sa)001:14728: mi zad pa dpag tu med pa bla na med pa bsod nams kyi gter chen por gyur pa /
NK028(sa)001:14729: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi yon tan rin po che'i
NK028(sa)001:14730: 'byung gnas byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa yun mi
NK028(sa)001:14732: zhes sems rab tu dad par gyur pas cang mi smra par thal mo sbyar te 'dug par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:14733: de nas dge ba'i bshes gnyen 'dug pa'i 'greng bas /
NK028(sa)001:14734: de ltar 'dug pa'i byang chub sems dpa' de la //
NK028(sa)001:14735: 'di skad ces mi 'di zhes bya ba khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:14736: byang chub du smon lam btab pa'i /
NK028(sa)001:14737: byang chub sems dpa' yin nam zhes brjod pa na /
NK028(sa)001:14738: lan pa'i byang chub sems dpa' des kyang lags so zhes khas blang bar bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:14739: de nas dge bshes bshes gnyen des //
NK028(sa)001:14740: dus gsum gyi byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis bslab ba'i gzhi rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:14742: dge ba chos sdud pa'i tshul khrims dang sems cad
NK028(sa)001:14743: don byed pa'i tshul khrims dang mdor bsdu ba slob
NK028(sa)001:14744: ma la go bar bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:14745: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi bslab pa rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:14746: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi tshul khrims de dag /
NK028(sa)001:14747: ci bdag las len par 'dod dam zhes slob ma la dri bar bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:14748: des de ltar len par 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:14749: zhes khas len par gyur pa na /
NK028(sa)001:14750: byung chub sems dpa'i sdom pa sbyin par bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:14751: btsun pa'am tshe dang ldan pa'am rigs kyi bu 'di
NK028(sa)001:14752: zhes bya ba khyod bdag byang chub sems dpa' ming
NK028(sa)001:14754: 'das pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa'i gzhir gyur pa gang yin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:14755: tshul khrims gang yin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:14756: ma byon pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i gzhir gyur pa gang yin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:14757: tshul khrims gang yin pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:14758: da ltar phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa'am //
NK028(sa)001:14759: gzhi gyur pa gang yin pa //
NK028(sa)001:14760: tshul khrims gang yin pa'i bslab pa'i /
NK028(sa)001:14763: 'das pa'i byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi bslab par 'gyur pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:14764: ma byon pa'i byang chub sems dpa' thams cad slob par 'gyur pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:14765: da ltar bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' thams cad slob par mdzad pa'i gzhi rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:14767: dge ba chos bsdus pa'i tshul khrims dang /
NK028(sa)001:14768: sems can don byed pa'i tshul khrims len par 'dod dam /
NK028(sa)001:14769: len par byed pa nges par 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:14771: de ltar dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyis lan gsum gyi bar du brjod cing /
NK028(sa)001:14772: slob mas lan gsum gyis bar du len par 'tshal lo zhes khas blangs par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:14774: de nas sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:14775: mchod pa'i cho ga la sogs sngon du song bas /
NK028(sa)001:14776: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la 'di skad gsol ba gdab par bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:14777: ji ltar sngon gyi de gzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom
NK028(sa)001:14778: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams dang
NK028(sa)001:14779: / sa chen po la bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems
NK028(sa)001:14780: dpa' rnams kyis bla na med pa'i byang chub tu
NK028(sa)001:14782: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba yang byang chub tu
NK028(sa)001:14783: sems bskyed pa rin po che'i sbyin pas rjes su
NK028(sa)001:14784: bzung du gsol / zhes lan gsum gyis bar du brjod do /
NK028(sa)001:14785: de ltar gsol ba btab nas /
NK028(sa)001:14786: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:14789: snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du /
NK028(sa)001:14791: sangs rgyas bcom ldan rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK028(sa)001:14794: snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du /
NK028(sa)001:14795: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK028(sa)001:14796: zhi ba chos kyi mchog la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK028(sa)001:14799: snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du /
NK028(sa)001:14800: tshogs rnams kyi mchog 'phags pa phyir mi bzlog ba'i
NK028(sa)001:14801: byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun la skyabs su mchi'o
NK028(sa)001:14803: de ltar skyabs su 'gro ba khyad par can byas nas /
NK028(sa)001:14804: bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:14805: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad yid kyi dmigs te /
NK028(sa)001:14806: phyag 'tshal ba dang ci 'byor ba'i mchod pa la sogs byas la /
NK028(sa)001:14807: slob dpon mdun du byas te //
NK028(sa)001:14808: spus mo g.yas pa'i lha nga la btsugs te //
NK028(sa)001:14809: thal mo sbyar bas sems bskyed par bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:14810: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK028(sa)001:14812: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba'i skye ba 'di dang skye ba gzhan dag tu /
NK028(sa)001:14814: tshul khrims kyi rang bzhin dang /
NK028(sa)001:14815: sgom ba'i rang bzhin gyi dge ba'i rtsa ba bgyid pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:14817: rjes su yid rang ba'i dge ba'i rtsa ba des //
NK028(sa)001:14818: ji ltar sngon gyis de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom
NK028(sa)001:14819: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams dang
NK028(sa)001:14820: / sa chen po la rab tu bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis /
NK028(sa)001:14821: bla na med pa'i byang chub du thugs bskyed pa ltar /
NK028(sa)001:14822: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang /
NK028(sa)001:14823: sems can thams cad ma bsgral rnams bsgral bar bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK028(sa)001:14824: ma grol ba rnams grol bar bya ba'i phyir dang dbugs ma phyung rnams dbugs dbyung pa'i phyir dang /
NK028(sa)001:14825: yongs su mya ngan las ma 'das pa rnams yongs su mya ngan las 'da' bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:14827: snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du /
NK028(sa)001:14828: byang chub chen po'i sems bskyed par bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:14830: de ltar slob dpon med kyang /
NK028(sa)001:14831: bdag nyid byang chub du sems bskyed pa'i cho ga ni /
NK028(sa)001:14832: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa dang phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa yid la bsam ste /
NK028(sa)001:14833: phyag 'tshal ba dang mchod pa'i cho ga la sogs pa byas nas /
NK028(sa)001:14835: slob dpon zhes bya'i tshig spangs pa'i /
NK028(sa)001:14836: skyabs su 'gro ba la sogs ba'i go rims gong ma bzhin du bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:14837: de ltar sems bskyed pa'i gang zag gis byang chub kyis sems 'phel bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:14838: tha na nyin lan gsum mtshan gsum du //
NK028(sa)001:14839: sangs rgyas chos dang tshogs mchog la //
NK028(sa)001:14840: byang chub bar du skyabs su mchi /
NK028(sa)001:14841: bdag gis sbyin sogs byas ba'i 'di dag gis //
NK028(sa)001:14842: 'gro la phan phyir sangs rgyas 'grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:14843: ces byang chub tu sems bskyed par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:14844: byang chub kyi sems nyams par byed pa'i chos bzhi las bzlog par bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:14846: bla ma dang mchod par 'os pa bslu ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:14847: gzhan 'gyod pa med pa la 'gyod pa bskyed pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:14848: sems bskyed pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la zhe sdang
NK028(sa)001:14849: gi tshigs su bcad pa ma yin pa brjod pa
NK028(sa)001:14850: dang / sems can thams cad la g.yo dang sgyus spyod pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:14851: byang chub kyi sems nyams par mi byed pa'i chos bzhi la bslab par bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:14853: srog gi phyir yang bsams bzhin du rdzun mi smra ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:14854: sems can thams cad la lhag pa'i bsam pa rnam
NK028(sa)001:14855: par dag pas gnas par bya'i g.yo dang sgyu ma
NK028(sa)001:14856: yin pa dang / sems bskyed pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la ston pa'i 'du shes bskyed cing /
NK028(sa)001:14857: phyogs bcur yang dag pa'i yon tan brjod par bya ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:14858: sems can 'ga' zhig dge ba la dgod pa de dag /
NK028(sa)001:14859: bla na med pa'i byang chub la dgod kyi //
NK028(sa)001:14860: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas la ni ma yin no //
NK028(sa)001:14861: khyad par du mngon par shes pa myur du thob
NK028(sa)001:14862: par 'dod pa'i byang chub sems dpa' 'phags pa spyan
NK028(sa)001:14864: zhus pa'i chos bdun pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo las bslab par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:14865: byang chub du sems bskyed pa'i yon tan ni /
NK028(sa)001:14866: 'phags pa sdong po bkod pa'i mdo la sogs pa las shes par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:14867: gsum pa rjes ni de nas dge ba'i bshes gnyen des /
NK028(sa)001:14868: slob ma byang chub sems la sdom pa sbyin nas /
NK028(sa)001:14869: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la //
NK028(sa)001:14870: yan lag lngas phyag 'tshal ba sngon du 'gro bas thal mo sbyar te //
NK028(sa)001:14871: 'di skad ces lan gsum brjod par bya ste //
NK028(sa)001:14872: byang chub sems dpa' ming 'di zhes bya ba las /
NK028(sa)001:14873: byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims kyi sdom pa yang
NK028(sa)001:14874: dag par blang bar bya ba lan gsum gyi bar
NK028(sa)001:14875: yang dag par mnos lags te /
NK028(sa)001:14876: byang chub sems dpa' ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'dis /
NK028(sa)001:14877: byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims gyi sdom pa yang dag par blangs pa /
NK028(sa)001:14878: bdag ming 'di zhes bya spang du gyur par 'phags pa rnams lkog tu gyur kyang /
NK028(sa)001:14879: phyogs bcu'i 'jigs rten gyis khams mthas gtugs pa na /
NK028(sa)001:14880: chos thams cad lkog tu ma gyur ba'i thugs mnga' ba'i thams cad la mkhyen par gsol lo //
NK028(sa)001:14881: zhes lan gsum gyis bar du phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas
NK028(sa)001:14882: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la brjod de phyag
NK028(sa)001:14883: 'tshal nas / slob ma ldang bar bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:14884: langs la dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyis /
NK028(sa)001:14885: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa mnos pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la 'di ltar bslab par bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:14886: byang chub sems dpa' ming 'di zhes bya ba khyod nyon cig /
NK028(sa)001:14887: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa yang dag par blangs ba 'di //
NK028(sa)001:14888: dad pa med pa rnams kyis mdun du smra bar mi bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:14889: gang gi phyir dad pa med pa rnams la byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa rab tu bstan na /
NK028(sa)001:14890: dad pa med pa'i sems can de dag gis /
NK028(sa)001:14891: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa la gnas pas spongs par byed do //
NK028(sa)001:14892: ji srid byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa la gnas
NK028(sa)001:14893: pa'i bsod nams kyi phung po dang ldan par gyur
NK028(sa)001:14894: pa de srid du bsod nams ma yin pa dang
NK028(sa)001:14896: gang gis phyir byang chub sems dpa' sems can thams
NK028(sa)001:14897: cad kyi sdug bsngal thams cad las yongs su bsrungs
NK028(sa)001:14899: sdig pa las ldog cing mchog tu dge ba'i byang chub sems dpa' gsang bar bya ba yin no //
NK028(sa)001:14900: de nas dge ba'i bshes gnyen des /
NK028(sa)001:14901: byang chub sems dpa' de la 'di skad ces brjod par bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:14902: ming 'di zhes bya ba khyod nyon cig 'di ni chos nyid yin te /
NK028(sa)001:14903: gang gi tshe byang chub sems dpa' byang chub sems
NK028(sa)001:14904: dpa'i sdom pa yang dag par blangs ba'i las rdzogs
NK028(sa)001:14905: ma thag tu / phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK028(sa)001:14906: thams cad kyi sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'
NK028(sa)001:14907: rnams la 'di lta bu'i ltas 'byung bar 'gyur zhing
NK028(sa)001:14908: gang gi sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' de
NK028(sa)001:14909: dag gis 'di ltar sangs rgyas kyi zhing che ge
NK028(sa)001:14910: mo zhig na byang chub sems dpa' ming 'di zhes
NK028(sa)001:14911: ma thag tu / bya ba las / byang chub
NK028(sa)001:14912: sems dpa'i sdom pa yang dag bar blang ba mnos
NK028(sa)001:14913: so zhes yang dag par mkhyen par 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:14914: de nas sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de dag dang /
NK028(sa)001:14915: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyang /
NK028(sa)001:14916: chos la dgyes pas pha dang bu dang spun zla'i dgongs pa mdzad nas /
NK028(sa)001:14917: de ltar dgongs pa mdzad pas /
NK028(sa)001:14918: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs 'phel bar 'gyur ro //
NK028(sa)001:14919: de nas bslab ba'i gzhi pham pa'i gnas su gyur pa sdom pa 'jigs pa'i rgyu bstan cing /
NK028(sa)001:14920: nyes byas kyi ltung ba nyon mongs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:14921: nyon mongs pa can ma yin pa yang bstan par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:14922: dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi mdor bsdus pa byang chub sems dpa' sdom pa nyi shu pa /
NK028(sa)001:14923: byang chub sems dpa'i sa yi tshul khrims kyi le'u bshad par bya'o //
NK028(sa)001:14924: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa'i cho ga slob dpon
NK028(sa)001:14925: chen po dpal mar me mdzad ye shes kyi mdzad
NK028(sa)001:14926: pa rdzogs so // rgya gar gyi mkhan po d+hi pham ka ra sh+ri dz+ny+aa na dang /
NK028(sa)001:14927: lo tsa ba dge slong dge ba'i blo gros kyis bsgyur ro ////
NK028(sa)001:14928: gnyis pa sems bskyed dbu ma lugs ni /
NK028(sa)001:14933: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK028(sa)001:14934: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyis khams mtha' yas mu med
NK028(sa)001:14935: pa dag na bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa dgra
NK028(sa)001:14936: bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang
NK028(sa)001:14937: dam chos dang / byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun
NK028(sa)001:14938: chen po dang bcas pa thams cad la phyag 'tshal
NK028(sa)001:14939: dam chos dang / lo // sangs rgyas dang byang
NK028(sa)001:14940: chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol
NK028(sa)001:14941: dam chos dang / lo // / bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba /
NK028(sa)001:14942: thog ma dang tha ma ma mchis pa'i 'khor ba na 'khor ba'i tshe /
NK028(sa)001:14943: sangs rgyas dang chos dang dge 'dun dang /
NK028(sa)001:14944: pha ma dang sems can gzhan dag la /
NK028(sa)001:14945: sdig pa mi dge ba'i las bgyis pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:14947: bgyis pa la rjes su yi rang ba ci mchis
NK028(sa)001:14948: pa de dag thams cad dang gcig tu sdoms shing
NK028(sa)001:14949: bsdus te / sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi spyan sngar /
NK028(sa)001:14950: bla na med pa'i so sor bshags pas 'chags so /
NK028(sa)001:14952: slad chad kyang sdom par bgyid lags so //
NK028(sa)001:14955: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:14956: ji ltar sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i 'das
NK028(sa)001:14957: pa rnams kyis bsod nams kyis rjes su yi rang
NK028(sa)001:14958: ba na med pa thugs su chud pa de bzhin
NK028(sa)001:14959: du / bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba yang sangs rgyas dang /
NK028(sa)001:14960: byang chub sems dpa' dang rang sangs rgyas dang /
NK028(sa)001:14961: 'phags pa nyan thos thams cad dang 'gro ba ma
NK028(sa)001:14962: lus pa'i bsod nams thams cad la rjes su yid
NK028(sa)001:14963: rang ngo // de skad lan gsum bzlas so //
NK028(sa)001:14964: bsod rnams kyi rjes su yi rang ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:14965: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:14966: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas sangs rgyas kyi gdung rgyun mi 'chad par bgyi ba'i slad du /
NK028(sa)001:14968: byang chub gyi snying po gnas kyi bar du /
NK028(sa)001:14969: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rkang gnyis rnams kyi mchog la skyabs su mchi ste /
NK028(sa)001:14970: thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa /
NK028(sa)001:14973: 'jigs pa thams cad dang bral ba /
NK028(sa)001:14976: sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
NK028(sa)001:14978: chos kyi sku mnga' ba la skyabs su mchi'o /
NK028(sa)001:14979: chos 'dod chags dang bral ba'i mchog la skyabs su mchi ste /
NK028(sa)001:14980: bla na med pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa la mnga' ba /
NK028(sa)001:14982: so sor rang gi rig pa'i chos la skyabs su mchi 'o //
NK028(sa)001:14983: dge 'dun 'dul ba tshogs kyi mchog la skyabs su mchi ste /
NK028(sa)001:14984: phyogs bzhi'i 'phags pa phyir mi ldog pa'i byang chub
NK028(sa)001:14985: phyir mi ldog pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa'
NK028(sa)001:14986: chen po'i dge 'dun la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK028(sa)001:14987: de skad lan gsum byas la skyabs su 'agro'o //
NK028(sa)001:14988: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:14989: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di bzung ste /
NK028(sa)001:14990: byang chub kyi snying po la gnas kyi bar du
NK028(sa)001:14991: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la
NK028(sa)001:14992: dus ci lta ba dang stobs ci mchis pa bzhin
NK028(sa)001:14994: mgon po thugs rje dang ldan pa rnams bdag bzhes su gsol //
NK028(sa)001:14995: de skad lan gsum bzlas so //
NK028(sa)001:14997: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK028(sa)001:14998: sngon gyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de dag /
NK028(sa)001:14999: sngon byang chub sesama dpa'i spyad pa spyod pa'i tshe //
NK028(sa)001:15000: sems can thams cad sgral ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:15001: sems can thams cad sgrol ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:15002: sems can thams cad dbug 'byung pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:15003: sems can thams cad yongs su mya ngan las bzla ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:15004: sems can thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes la dgod
NK028(sa)001:15005: ba'i slad du ji ltar bla na med pa yang
NK028(sa)001:15006: dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu thugs bskyed pa
NK028(sa)001:15007: de bzhin du bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba yang
NK028(sa)001:15009: byang chub snying po la gnas kyi bar du //
NK028(sa)001:15010: sems can thams cad dgrol ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:15011: sems cad thams cad dbugs dbyung ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:15012: sems can thams cad yongs su mya ngan las 'da' ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:15013: sems can thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes la dgod pa'i slad du /
NK028(sa)001:15014: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu sems bskyed par bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:15015: ji ltar sngon gyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom
NK028(sa)001:15016: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang
NK028(sa)001:15017: chub sems dpa' de dag gis dngos po thams cad
NK028(sa)001:15018: dang bral ba'i phung po dang /
NK028(sa)001:15020: gzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i dngos po spangs pa /
NK028(sa)001:15021: chos bdag med par mnyam pa nyid kyis /
NK028(sa)001:15022: rang gi sems gdod ma nas ma skyes pa stong
NK028(sa)001:15023: pa nyid kyi byang chub du sems bskyed pa de
NK028(sa)001:15024: bzhin du / bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba yang /
NK028(sa)001:15026: snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du //
NK028(sa)001:15027: byang chub du sems bskyed par bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:15028: ji ltar sngon gyis de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom
NK028(sa)001:15029: pa yang par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de dag gis
NK028(sa)001:15030: / bdud dpung dang bcas pa mtha' dag 'pham par mdzad de /
NK028(sa)001:15031: nyid mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa de bzhin du /
NK028(sa)001:15033: bdud dpung dang bcas pa mtha' dag pham par bgyi ste //
NK028(sa)001:15034: bdag nyid mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:15035: ji ltar sngon gyis de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom
NK028(sa)001:15036: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de dag
NK028(sa)001:15037: gis nyid mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas /
NK028(sa)001:15038: chos kyi 'khor lo rab tu bskor ba de bzhin du /
NK028(sa)001:15039: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang /
NK028(sa)001:15040: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas ste /
NK028(sa)001:15041: chos kyi 'khor lo rab tu bskor bar bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:15042: ji ltar sngon gyis de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom
NK028(sa)001:15043: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de dag
NK028(sa)001:15044: gis nyid mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas tshogs
NK028(sa)001:15045: yongs su ba sdu ba de bzhin du /
NK028(sa)001:15046: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang /
NK028(sa)001:15047: bdag nyid mngon par sangs rgyas te /
NK028(sa)001:15048: tshogs yongs su bsdu par bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:15049: byang chub mchog gi sems ni bskyed par bgyi //
NK028(sa)001:15050: sems can ma lus bdag gis 'gron du gnyer //
NK028(sa)001:15051: byang chub spyod mchog yid 'ong spyad par bgyi //
NK028(sa)001:15052: 'gro la phan phyir sangs rgyas 'grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15053: de skad lan gsum bzlas so //
NK028(sa)001:15054: byang chub tu sems bskyed pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15055: bdag gi byang chub sems bskyed pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di dang /
NK028(sa)001:15056: gzhan yang bdag gi bsod nams cung zad bgyis pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:15058: dge ba thams cad pha ma la sogs pa /
NK028(sa)001:15059: sems can thams cad kyi don du bla na med
NK028(sa)001:15060: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu yongs
NK028(sa)001:15061: su bsngo 'o / bdag gi bsod nams 'di yi
NK028(sa)001:15062: pha ma la sogs pa sems can ma sgral ba
NK028(sa)001:15063: su bsngo 'o / rnams bsgral lo // ma grol ba rnams grol lo //
NK028(sa)001:15064: dbugs ma phyungs rnams dbugs dbyung ngo /
NK028(sa)001:15065: yongs su mya ngan las ma 'das pa rnams ni yongs su mya ngan las bazla'o //
NK028(sa)001:15066: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas ma rgyas pa rnams ni mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par bagyi'o //
NK028(sa)001:15067: skyabs ma mchis pa dang gnas ma mchis pa rnams dang /
NK028(sa)001:15068: dpung gnyen ma mchis pa'i 'jig rten pa la skyabs gnas dang dpung gnyen du gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15069: bsod nams 'di yis thams cad mkhyen pa nyid //
NK028(sa)001:15070: thob nas nyes pa'i dgra rnams pham byas te //
NK028(sa)001:15071: rga nad 'chi ba'i brlabs chen 'khrugs pa yi //
NK028(sa)001:15072: srid pa'i mtsho las 'gro ba 'don par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15073: gzhan yang bdag gis sbyin pa bsags pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:15077: bsam gtan la yid mnyam par 'jog pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:15078: shes rab rnam par spyod pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:15079: thabs la mkhas pa la bslab pa ci yang rung ste /
NK028(sa)001:15080: de dag thams cad sems can thams cad kyi don dang /
NK028(sa)001:15081: phan pa dang bde ba'i slad du /
NK028(sa)001:15082: bla na med bas yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub las brtsams te /
NK028(sa)001:15085: da ltar byung ba'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po snying rje chen po dang ldan pa /
NK028(sa)001:15086: lam chen po la yang dag par bzhugs pa /
NK028(sa)001:15087: sa chen po la gnas pa rnams kyi rjes su 'jug go /
NK028(sa)001:15089: bdag byang chub sems dpa' lags kyis byang chub sems dpa' lags par gzung du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:15090: sa dang chu dang me dang rlung dang //
NK028(sa)001:15091: rtsi dang nag kyi shing lta bur //
NK028(sa)001:15092: bdag ni sems can thams cad kyis //
NK028(sa)001:15094: mthong ba dang ni thos pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:15095: reg pa dang ni dran pas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:15096: bdag ni sems can thams cad kyi //
NK028(sa)001:15097: nad rnams gso bar bgyid gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15098: sems can thams cad bde gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15099: ngan 'gro thams cad rtag tu stong par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15100: byang chub sems dpa' gang dag su bzhugs pa //
NK028(sa)001:15101: de dag kun gyi smon lam 'grub gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15102: de dag lan gsum bzlas so //
NK028(sa)001:15103: bsod nams yongs su bsngo ba'o //
NK028(sa)001:15104: byang chub tu sems bskyed pa'i cho ga rdzogs so //
NK028(sa)001:15105: sa dang po'i bden pa gzigs pa /
NK028(sa)001:15106: slob dpon 'phags pa klu grub gyis zhal snga nas
NK028(sa)001:15107: mdzad pa'i byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i cho
NK028(sa)001:15108: ga rdzogs so // rgya gar gyi mkhan po su ran tra b+ho de dang /
NK028(sa)001:15109: zhus chen gyi lots+tsha ba ban+d+he ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o ////
NK028(sa)001:15110: bcu gcig pa me tog dor ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:15111: bcu gnyis pa lha dbab pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:15112: bcu gsum pa lha bsgom par nan tan bya ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:15113: bcu bzhi ba spyan dbye ba dang bzhi gang dang mthun la /
NK028(sa)001:15114: bye brag tu bco lnga pa dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:15115: 'o mdun 'di na yod pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dkyil 'khor rten dang brten pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:15116: phyi rol du me ri rdo rje ra ba /
NK028(sa)001:15117: pad skor de'i nang du gzhal yas kyi khang pa /
NK028(sa)001:15119: rgyan rta babs dang bcas pa /
NK028(sa)001:15120: de'i nang du pad+ma 'dab ma bcu /
NK028(sa)001:15121: de'i nang du pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa /
NK028(sa)001:15122: mngon sum du mthong ba'i mos pa mdzod //
NK028(sa)001:15123: pad+ma'i lte bar bcom ldan 'das dpal rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa /
NK028(sa)001:15124: shar gyi pad 'dab la yum chen mo //
NK028(sa)001:15126: nub du phyag na rdo rje //
NK028(sa)001:15128: de'i phyi rol pad ma 'dab bcu la /
NK028(sa)001:15129: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang bcu dang bcas pa /
NK028(sa)001:15130: sku snang la rang bzhin med pa me long nang
NK028(sa)001:15131: gi gzugs brnyan bzhin mngon sum du mthong ba de
NK028(sa)001:15132: / khyed rnams kyi yi dam gyi lha skal yin ang snyam ba'i mos pa mdzod cig /
NK028(sa)001:15133: bcu drug pa tshogs dang yon 'bul ba yang gong dang mtshungs so //
NK028(sa)001:15134: sbyi don gnyis pa dbang bskur ba la gsum ste /
NK028(sa)001:15138: dang po ni gong dang mthun no //
NK028(sa)001:15139: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gsum ste phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu dang /
NK028(sa)001:15140: nang nus pa'i dbang la lnga dang /
NK028(sa)001:15141: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang ngo /
NK028(sa)001:15143: bum pa la sogs dgu po gong nyan thos kyis dbang dang mtshungs la /
NK028(sa)001:15144: bye brag du phyag rgya'i dbang la /
NK028(sa)001:15145: bcom ldan gser mdog chos 'chad g.yas //
NK028(sa)001:15146: g.yon pa mnyam bzhag phyag rgya ldan //
NK028(sa)001:15147: rdo rje dkyil dkrung gtsug tor bcas //
NK028(sa)001:15148: spyan yangs 'thing kha mdzod spur ldan //
NK028(sa)001:15151: 'di yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK028(sa)001:15152: 'di yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15153: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:15155: shar phyogs pad ma'i 'dab ma na //
NK028(sa)001:15156: pad zla rgyas stengs yum chen mo //
NK028(sa)001:15157: longs spyod rdzogs ldan rdo rje dkyil //
NK028(sa)001:15158: gser mdog sku ni shin tu rgyas //
NK028(sa)001:15159: phyag bzhi'i dang po mnyam bzhag mdzad //
NK028(sa)001:15161: g.yon pa po ti bsnams nas ni //
NK028(sa)001:15162: 'gro ba sems can don mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:15163: 'di yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK028(sa)001:15164: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15165: d+hi pra wa me ya ni de pra dud pra me b+hi shud d+he b+h+ya /
NK028(sa)001:15166: d+harma d+har tu ba ga wan /
NK028(sa)001:15167: dza h+aum bam hoh a la la ho /
NK028(sa)001:15168: a pa ra pra ti dzim h+aum /
NK028(sa)001:15171: pad zla rgyas ba'i gdan stengs na //
NK028(sa)001:15172: phyag na rdo rje zhi ba'i zhal //
NK028(sa)001:15175: rin chen rgyan ldan sems dpa'i dkyil //
NK028(sa)001:15176: 'di yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK028(sa)001:15177: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15178: badz+ra tsan d+ha ma h+aa ro sha na h+aum phata /
NK028(sa)001:15180: nub phyogs pad ma'i 'dab ma na /
NK028(sa)001:15181: sha ri gser mdog dka' thub gzugs //
NK028(sa)001:15182: chos gos gsum ldan bsil byed bsnams /
NK028(sa)001:15183: spus gtsug g.yon pa lhung bzed bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:15184: lus ngag yid gsum mnyam pa'i ngang /
NK028(sa)001:15185: 'di yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK028(sa)001:15186: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15187: na mah sa man+tabud+d+ha nan b+ha ga wan /
NK028(sa)001:15188: bra b+ha ta th+aa ga ta b+hi sha ya sa b+ha wa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:15191: pad zla rgyas ba'i gdan stengs na //
NK028(sa)001:15192: spyan ras dkar po byang chub sems //
NK028(sa)001:15193: brgyan mdzes sems dpa' dkyil dkrung bzhugs //
NK028(sa)001:15194: g.yas na pad ma mchog sbyin dang //
NK028(sa)001:15195: g.yon pa'ang pad ma po ti 'dzin /
NK028(sa)001:15196: 'di yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK028(sa)001:15197: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15198: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a wa lo ki te ka ru nan ma ra ya badz+ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:15200: gzhal yas lha snams shar phyogs kyi //
NK028(sa)001:15201: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:15202: bde gshegs dkon mchog 'byung gnas ni //
NK028(sa)001:15203: sku mdog shel ltar dkar ba la /
NK028(sa)001:15204: phyag g.yas rin chen mchog sbyin mdzad /
NK028(sa)001:15205: phyag g.yon lte ba'i thad dkar ni /
NK028(sa)001:15207: 'di yi byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK028(sa)001:15208: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15209: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a yu pu ra ga ti swah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:15211: gzhal yas lha snams lho phyogs na //
NK028(sa)001:15212: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:15213: bde gshegs mya ngan med pa'i dpal //
NK028(sa)001:15214: sku mdog nam mkha'i mdog can la //
NK028(sa)001:15216: g.yon pa ltee ba'i thad dkar ni /
NK028(sa)001:15217: 'gro la bstan pas nyon mongs sel //
NK028(sa)001:15218: 'di yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK028(sa)001:15219: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15220: sarba ta th+aa ga ta rat+na a b+hi ya ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:15222: gzhal yas lha snams nub phyogs na //
NK028(sa)001:15223: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:15225: sku mdog gangs ri ltar dkar zhing //
NK028(sa)001:15226: g.yas pa mche ba rtsigs pa rnams //
NK028(sa)001:15227: g.yon pa lte ba'i thad dkar ni //
NK028(sa)001:15229: 'di yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK028(sa)001:15230: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15231: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tri ti sha ga pa ri bi sa ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:15233: gzhal yas lha snams byang phyogs na //
NK028(sa)001:15234: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs na //
NK028(sa)001:15235: bde gshegs rgyal ba'i dbang po ni //
NK028(sa)001:15236: sku mdog in tra ni la'i mdog /
NK028(sa)001:15237: g.yas pa pad ma dkar po 'dzin //
NK028(sa)001:15238: g.yon pa lte ba'i thad dkar ni //
NK028(sa)001:15239: 'gro la bstan ba'i mun pa sel /
NK028(sa)001:15240: 'di yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK028(sa)001:15241: de yis dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15242: sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+hi sha rat+na san ti s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:15244: gzhal yas snam bu'i shar lho na //
NK028(sa)001:15245: pad zla rgyas ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:15246: bde gshegs pad+mo dam pa'i dpal //
NK028(sa)001:15247: sku mdog dung ltar dkar ba'i mdangs //
NK028(sa)001:15248: phyag g.yas pad+ma dmar po rnams /
NK028(sa)001:15249: g.yon pa lte ba'i thad dkar ni //
NK028(sa)001:15251: 'di yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK028(sa)001:15252: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15253: sarba ta th+aa ga ta du du ma le ke ta do pa ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:15255: gzhal yas snam bu'i lho nub na /
NK028(sa)001:15256: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs na /
NK028(sa)001:15257: nyi ma snang ba dam pa'i dpal /
NK028(sa)001:15258: sku mdog mar gad dmar smug la //
NK028(sa)001:15259: phyag g.yas mun sel nyi ma bsnams /
NK028(sa)001:15260: phyag g.yon sku la rten mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:15261: 'di yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK028(sa)001:15262: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15263: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mug ri bam mug ti mar gad du sha ma ri s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:15265: gzhal yas bsnams bu'i nub byang na //
NK028(sa)001:15266: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs na //
NK028(sa)001:15267: sangs rgyas gdug chen dam pa'i dpal //
NK028(sa)001:15268: sku mdog in tra ni la'i mdog /
NK028(sa)001:15269: g.yas pa sna tshogs rdo rje 'dzin //
NK028(sa)001:15270: phyag g.yon lte ba'i thad dkar ni //
NK028(sa)001:15272: 'di yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK028(sa)001:15273: de yis byin gyis brlabs du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:15274: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15275: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sur+ya bi la ta s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:15277: gzhal yas bsnams bu'i byang shar na //
NK028(sa)001:15278: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs na //
NK028(sa)001:15279: sangs rgyas glang po dam pa'i dpal //
NK028(sa)001:15280: sku mdog gser ltar 'tsher ba la //
NK028(sa)001:15281: phyag g.yas chos 'chad phyag rgya ston //
NK028(sa)001:15282: g.yon pa chos gos 'dzin mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:15283: 'di yis byin gyis brlabs du gsol //
NK028(sa)001:15284: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15285: sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+ha ga b+ha te b+ha shi la sa b+ha wa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK028(sa)001:15287: gzhal yas bsnams bu'i shar stod na //
NK028(sa)001:15288: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:15289: dga' bar byed pa'i sangs rgyas ni //
NK028(sa)001:15290: sku mdog ud+pala sngon po'i mdangs //
NK028(sa)001:15291: phyag g.yas rin chen bum pa bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:15292: g.yon pa sku la rten mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:15293: 'di yis byin gyis de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15294: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ra ma ti ra badz+ra s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:15296: gzhal yas bsnams bu'i nub smad du //
NK028(sa)001:15297: pad zla rgyas pa'i gdan stengs su //
NK028(sa)001:15298: bde gshegs pad+ma dam pa'i dpal //
NK028(sa)001:15299: sku mdog gser ltar 'tsher ba'i mdangs //
NK028(sa)001:15300: phyag g.yas pad+ma dmar po bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:15301: g.yon pa lte ba'i thad dkar ni //
NK028(sa)001:15302: 'thil ni phyir bstan gdung pa sel //
NK028(sa)001:15303: 'di yis byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK028(sa)001:15304: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15305: sarba ta th+aa ga ta pad+ma b+ha la s+w+aah+aa /
NK028(sa)001:15307: byang chub sems dpa'i dbang dang /
NK028(sa)001:15309: yo ga'i dbang dang gsum la bkra shis kyi dbang
NK028(sa)001:15310: rgya rtsa brgyad yod pa la 'di byang chub sems
NK028(sa)001:15311: dpa'i dbang la nyi shu kri ya la /
NK028(sa)001:15312: nyi shu rtsa drug yo ga la drug bcu rtsa gnyis ste /
NK028(sa)001:15313: dang po byang chub sems dpa'i dbang la nyi shu ni /
NK028(sa)001:15314: sngon byang chub sems dpa' dam pa tog dkar po
NK028(sa)001:15315: de dga' ldan gyi gnas nas yum sgyu ma lha
NK028(sa)001:15316: mdzes kyi lhums su gshegs pa'i dus su /
NK028(sa)001:15317: dbu las rin po che'i srog zhu phud nas /
NK028(sa)001:15318: mi pham mgon po la chos kyi rgyal tshab du
NK028(sa)001:15319: lha rnams kyis ston pa mdzad par dbang bskur ro
NK028(sa)001:15320: / de dang rjes su mthun par rin po che cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15321: chos kyi rgyal tshab byed pa'i mthu dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15322: tog dkar dbu las rin chen cod pan bshus //
NK028(sa)001:15323: nyid kyi phyag gis kho bo'i dbu la bzhag /
NK028(sa)001:15324: mi pham mgon po chos kyi rgyal tshab rje /
NK028(sa)001:15325: chos kyi rgyal srid ched po byed par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15326: chos kyi dbyings nas 'byung gnas ga na bar //
NK028(sa)001:15327: sprul sku kun khyab yid bzhin 'byung ba'i gter //
NK028(sa)001:15328: dang por tshogs rdzogs yongs la mthar phyin pa'i //
NK028(sa)001:15329: 'di na bkra shis rdzogs pa'i dbang gi le'u ste dang po'o //
NK028(sa)001:15330: sngon byang chub sems dpa' dam pa tog dkar po
NK028(sa)001:15331: de yum sgyu ma lhum mdzes kyi lhums zhugs pa
NK028(sa)001:15332: dang / yum gyi phyag gis sems can thams cad la reg cing da bang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15334: na tsha'i sdug bsngal thams cad zhi bar gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:15335: de dang rjes su mthun par de yi dbang mchog dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15336: sgyu ma lhum mdzes lha yi lcam //
NK028(sa)001:15337: lha yi lus la rin chen mdzes //
NK028(sa)001:15338: nyon mongs sdug bsngal kun zhi zhing //
NK028(sa)001:15339: na tsha'i sdug bsngal kun zhi nas //
