NK028(sa)001:15340: na tsha'i sdug bsngal thar bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:15341: byin brlabs yum chen shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK028(sa)001:15342: kun la'ang byams snyoms thugs rje che ba'i ma //
NK028(sa)001:15343: gzhan la phan mdzad nyid don lhun gyis grub /
NK028(sa)001:15344: 'di ni lhun gyis grub ba'i bkra shis le'u gnyis pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15345: sngon byang chub sems dpa' dam pa tog dkar po de /
NK028(sa)001:15346: lum bi'i tshal du yum gyi lhum nas bltams pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:15347: seng ge'i phru gu zung cig gis bskor ba byas zhing dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:15348: sdo ba'i phyogs thams cad zil gyis non ba'i dbang dam pa thob bo //
NK028(sa)001:15349: de dang rjes su mthun par seng ge'i phru gu zung cig gi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15350: sdo ba'i phyogs thams cad zil gyis non pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15351: seng ge'i nga ro sgra can thogs med pas //
NK028(sa)001:15352: 'jigs pa med pa'i sgra chen bsgrags nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:15353: bar du gcod pa'i bdud kyi sde btul te //
NK028(sa)001:15354: sdo ba'i phyogs rnams zil gyis non par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15355: thams cad zil non cho 'phrul che ba'i lha //
NK028(sa)001:15356: yon tan kun tshangs gdug pa zil gyis non //
NK028(sa)001:15357: che ba'i mthu stobs khyad par kun las 'phags /
NK028(sa)001:15358: 'di ni che btsan mthu stobs bkra shis le'u gsum pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15359: sngon sgyu ma lhum mdzes kyis grong khyer ser skya na bzhugs pa la //
NK028(sa)001:15360: glang po che phru gu gnyis kyi snas byug cing dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:15361: 'jig rten 'degs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15363: theg pa bzhi yis don rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:15364: bye brag 'byed pa'i stobs rdzogs te //
NK028(sa)001:15365: stobs kyi pha rol phyin rdzogs shog /
NK028(sa)001:15366: mthu stobs phun sum ldan pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:15367: rin chen gser brgyan kun gyis brgyan //
NK028(sa)001:15368: dpe byad mtshan rdzogs glang po stobs //
NK028(sa)001:15369: 'di ni stobs bcu ldan pa'i bkra shis le'u bzhi pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15370: sngon byang chub sems dpa' dam pa tog dkar po de /
NK028(sa)001:15371: byang chub kyi rgyan tshal du yum gyis lhums nas bltams pa las /
NK028(sa)001:15372: tshangs pa dang brgya byin gyis blang nas /
NK028(sa)001:15373: na bza' ka ri ka gsol te dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15374: mkhyen pa'i bye brag la mkhas pa ma 'dres pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15375: de dang rjes su mthun par na bza' ka shi ras dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15376: mkhyen pa'i ye shes gsal zhing ma 'dres pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15377: nyon mongs skyon spangs ka shi ras //
NK028(sa)001:15378: legs pa'i yon tan kun rdzogs te //
NK028(sa)001:15379: nyes pa'i skyon las skyobs pa dang /
NK028(sa)001:15380: mkhyen pa'i bye brag gsal bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:15381: tshangs pa brgya byin bsod nams dag pa'i lha //
NK028(sa)001:15382: lha yi rgyal po blon po tshangs pa'i sku //
NK028(sa)001:15383: mngon shes lnga ldan chos nyid zhi ba'i bdag /
NK028(sa)001:15384: 'di ni yon tan bkra shis dbang gi bkra shis le'u lnga pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15385: sngon rgyal bu don grub pa de //
NK028(sa)001:15386: yum gyi lhum nas bltams nas //
NK028(sa)001:15388: rgyal po sh+aa kya rigs kun tshogs nas /
NK028(sa)001:15389: gzhon nu don 'grub tu ming btags nas dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15390: shes bya la ma rmongs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:15391: de dang rjes su mthun par slob ma 'di la ming gi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15392: shes bya la ye shes ma rmongs pa gzhon nu don 'grub du dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15393: rigs kyi bu khyod deng phan chad //
NK028(sa)001:15394: ming mchog grags pas dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:15395: gzhon nu don 'grub yin pa'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:15396: rgyal po don 'grub yin par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15397: rgyal rigs khrims gtsang mang po kun 'dus nas //
NK028(sa)001:15398: lha mi kun la dbang bskur rgyal por bskos //
NK028(sa)001:15399: kun las dpag pa'i rgyal dbang dam pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:15400: 'di ni kun gyi rgyal po'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u drug pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15401: sngon rgyal bu don thams cad grub pa de yig dpon kun gyis bshes gnyen la //
NK028(sa)001:15402: yi ge slob pa'i dus su tsan dan sbrul gyi shing la gser gyi yang mig btags nas //
NK028(sa)001:15403: rin chen sna tshogs kyi rgyan gyis brgyan nas /
NK028(sa)001:15404: yig ge slob pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15405: yig dpon gyis kyang ma thub la /
NK028(sa)001:15406: lha dang mi'i yi ge thams cad la mkhas pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:15407: de dang rjes su mthun par yig shing gis dbang bskur bas //
NK028(sa)001:15408: chos kyi sgra sgrogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15409: tsan dan sbrul gyi yig shing la //
NK028(sa)001:15410: rin chen gser gyi yang mig btags //
NK028(sa)001:15411: 'gro ba'i don byed yi ge'i mthu //
NK028(sa)001:15412: chos kyi sgra rnams sgrogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15413: chos nyid kun ston rdzu 'phrul yi ge'i mthu //
NK028(sa)001:15414: pha rol zil gnon chos nyid kun las rgyal //
NK028(sa)001:15415: 'di 'dra yon tan gzhan na med pa'i /
NK028(sa)001:15416: 'di ni yi ge tshogs rdzogs dbang gi bkra shis le'u bdun pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15417: sngon rgyal bu don thams cad grub pa la sru
NK028(sa)001:15418: mo ko ta mas rgyan gyis bye brag gis brgyan
NK028(sa)001:15420: sa dang rdo la byas pa'i bsam mno med pa
NK028(sa)001:15421: rnams phyag tshur 'tshal ba'i dbang thob par gyur to
NK028(sa)001:15422: // de dang rjes su mthun par rgyan gyi bye brag gis dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15423: 'gro ba thams cad shes pa dang ldan pa ra byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15424: mdzes pa'i rgyan rnams myur du btags nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:15425: legs pa'i yon tan kun tshang ye shes sku //
NK028(sa)001:15426: ma rig thar lam ma lus 'dren pa'i mchog /
NK028(sa)001:15427: rtogs pa'i ye shes mchog dang ldan par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15428: yon tan kun ldan sru mo mdzes pa'i brgyan //
NK028(sa)001:15429: legs pa kun rdzogs yon tan mthar phyin pa //
NK028(sa)001:15430: che ba'i yon tan gzhan phyir mi lang ste /
NK028(sa)001:15431: 'di ni legs pa kun rdzogs dbang gi bkra shis le'u brgyad pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15432: sngon rgyal bu don thams cad grub pa de bdud lhas sbyin dang rtsal 'gran pa'i dus su /
NK028(sa)001:15433: mes chen po seng ge 'gram gyis rnam rus gzhul zer dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15434: sgra'i bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab pa byung zhing /
NK028(sa)001:15435: bdud bsgyur brtsal gyis 'dul ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:15436: de dang rjes su mthun par /
NK028(sa)001:15437: slob ma rnams la rnam rus dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15438: snyan pa'i sgra sgrogs shing bdud dpung 'dul ba'i dbang 'phongs rtsal dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15439: snyan pa'i sgra sgrogs rna rus mchog /
NK028(sa)001:15440: 'gro ba kun gyis yid tshim zhing /
NK028(sa)001:15441: gnod pa'i bdud rnams bcom nas ni //
NK028(sa)001:15442: bdud rnams 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK028(sa)001:15443: thams cad kun 'dul mthu stobs phun sum tshogs //
NK028(sa)001:15444: rdzu 'phrul thabs kyi pha rol zil gyis non //
NK028(sa)001:15445: don dang mi 'gal gdug pa zhi mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:15446: 'di ni snam rus dbang gi le'u dgu pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15447: sngon rgyal bu don thams cad grub pa de la
NK028(sa)001:15448: drang srong skar ma la dga' bas 'dod 'jo ba'i
NK028(sa)001:15449: zho phyag tu phul de bkra shis pa de bzhin
NK028(sa)001:15450: du / slob ma rnams la 'dod 'jo ba'i zho lag tu sbyin pas bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15451: zho ni kun gyi snying por gyur pa na //
NK028(sa)001:15452: snying po rnam dag ye shes dag rtogs nas //
NK028(sa)001:15453: yon tan kun gyi dbyings su 'gyur ba yi //
NK028(sa)001:15454: bkra shis des kyang dug gsum zhi bar shog /
NK028(sa)001:15457: sngon rgyal bu don thams cad grub pa des 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal por bskos nas /
NK028(sa)001:15459: 'dzam bu gling bzhi la 'khor los bsgyur bar gyur nas /
NK028(sa)001:15460: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad mi rtag par mi rtag
NK028(sa)001:15461: par mkhyen pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to
NK028(sa)001:15462: // de dang rjes su mthun par shing rta la
NK028(sa)001:15463: sogs pa 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal por dbang bskur
NK028(sa)001:15464: // bas / 'dzam bu gling bzhi la dbang bsgyur
NK028(sa)001:15465: zhing skye shi mi rtag par mkhyen pa'i sdug bsngal
NK028(sa)001:15467: rgyal srid longs spyod dpal dang ldan pa'i mchog /
NK028(sa)001:15468: 'gro ba'i don mdzad 'khor los bsgyur ba'i lha /
NK028(sa)001:15469: lha mi yongs kyi spyod pa bsam mi khyab /
NK028(sa)001:15470: skye shi mi rtag pa las bzlog par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15471: rgyal srid longs spyod dpal dang ldan pa'i lha //
NK028(sa)001:15472: gling bzhi mtha' skor skye rgas na 'chi spongs //
NK028(sa)001:15473: 'khor ba'i skyon shes sdug bsngal sel mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:15474: 'di ni shing rta dbang gi bkra shis le'u bcu gcig pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15475: sngon rgyal po don thams cad grub pa de khab
NK028(sa)001:15476: nas khab med par rab tu byung ba'i dus su
NK028(sa)001:15477: / 'bangs mos can gyis chibs rin po che lnga ldan phyungs nas phul bas //
NK028(sa)001:15478: srod cig la dpag tshad brgyad khri stong 'das nas /
NK028(sa)001:15479: rab tu byung te nyon mongs las thar ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:15480: de dang rjes su mthun par phyibs 'dis dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15481: rab tu byung zhing nyon mongs pa las thar pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15482: gang yang thogs med brtson 'grus myur ba'i shugs /
NK028(sa)001:15483: tshangs pa brgya byin mthu chen che ba'i lha //
NK028(sa)001:15484: rgyal chen rigs bzhi 'degs pa'i stobs dang ldan /
NK028(sa)001:15485: thog med tshangs par spyod pa'i mthu ldan shog /
NK028(sa)001:15486: 'khor ba'i chos ni 'ching ba ltar gzigs pa //
NK028(sa)001:15487: 'khor ba'i nyes pa dgra rnams gzhom pa'i phyir /
NK028(sa)001:15488: 'dod pa'i rgyu spongs rnam rtog bor mdzad pa //
NK028(sa)001:15489: 'di ni phyibs kyi dbang gis bkra shis le'u bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15490: sngon rgyal bu don thams cad grub pa des /
NK028(sa)001:15491: rnam dag mchod rten gyis 'gram du khab nas khab med par rab tu byung ba las /
NK028(sa)001:15492: sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lha'i bu mdzes pa tog gis /
NK028(sa)001:15493: bshan ral gri phyag tu phul bas dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15494: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa'i dra ba gcod pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:15495: de dang rjes su mthun par bcom ldan 'das kyis
NK028(sa)001:15496: bshan ral gris dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i sgrib
NK028(sa)001:15497: pa'i dra ba gcod pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK028(sa)001:15498: gyur cig / nyon mongs dra ba gcod pa'i ral gri de //
NK028(sa)001:15499: mi shes nyon mongs rgyu rnams bcad nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:15500: bla med byang chub gnas su bgrod pa'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:15501: nyon mongs sgrib pa'i dra ba gcod par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15502: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus bcom nas kyang //
NK028(sa)001:15503: bde ba'i don rtogs nag khrod dben par gnas //
NK028(sa)001:15504: bdag don lhun grub gzhan don mthar phyin pas /
NK028(sa)001:15505: 'di ni tshul khrims dbang gi bkra shis le'u bcu gsum pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15506: sngon rgyal bu don thams cad grub pa de //
NK028(sa)001:15507: chu bo na ra dza na'i 'gram du bka' thub
NK028(sa)001:15508: rdzogs pa sum cu rtsa gsum gyis lha'i bu yid
NK028(sa)001:15509: bzhin 'byung bas / sreg shang dang bar bu phul bas /
NK028(sa)001:15510: 'gro ba'i don mthar phyin par rdzogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob po //
NK028(sa)001:15511: de dang rjes su mthun par bcom ldan 'das kyis sreg par kyis rdzas kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15512: bdag dang 'gro ba'i don mthar phyin par rdzogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15513: ser sna mdud pa grol phyir sreg shang bsnams /
NK028(sa)001:15514: chog shes bgang ba sla phyir par bu bsnams //
NK028(sa)001:15515: bsod nams tshogs rdzogs byang chub nyid kyi sku //
NK028(sa)001:15516: bdag dang gzhan don mthar phyin rdzogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15517: 'di ni don grub dbang gi bkra shis le'u bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15518: sngon bcom ldan 'das bsnyen par rdzogs pa la //
NK028(sa)001:15519: sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lha zhig gis na bza'
NK028(sa)001:15520: dur smrig gsol bas nyon mongs 'gro ba srid las
NK028(sa)001:15521: skyobs ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:15522: de dang rjes su mthun par /
NK028(sa)001:15523: bcom ldan 'das kyis na bza' ngur smrig gi rdzas
NK028(sa)001:15524: 'dis dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa 'khor ba las
NK028(sa)001:15525: skyobs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15526: ngan 'gro skyobs phyir na bza' chos gos gsol //
NK028(sa)001:15527: mi shes rmongs pa ma lus bsal ba dang //
NK028(sa)001:15528: bag chags skyon gyi dri mas ma gos pas //
NK028(sa)001:15529: 'bras bu byang chub gnas su 'grub par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15530: 'di ni nyon mongs bsal ba'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u bco lnga pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15531: sngon bcom ldan 'das ma ga ta ru //
NK028(sa)001:15532: bsod snyoms la gshegs pa la /
NK028(sa)001:15533: sbre'u'i rgyal po sbrang rtsi lhung bzed gang 'phul bas /
NK028(sa)001:15534: bkra shis pa'i rdzas mchog dam pa dang ldan par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:15535: de dang rjes su mthun par slob ma rnams la bkra shis pa'i rdzas 'di dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15536: 'bras bu phun sum tshogs pa'i mchog dang ldan pa'i bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15537: rgyal rigs sbre'u rgyal po yis //
NK028(sa)001:15538: sbrang rtsi phul ba'i bsod nams mchog /
NK028(sa)001:15539: thugs rjes mthun pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK028(sa)001:15540: bkra shis stobs mchog ldan par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15541: 'di ni bsod nams ma chog gi dbang gi bkra shis le'u bcu drug pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15542: sngon bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa chu bo na ra dza ra'i 'gram du /
NK028(sa)001:15543: dka' thub lo gsum mdzad lo gnyis 'bras sa le ljang pa nyag re gsol /
NK028(sa)001:15544: lo gcig chu thig pa re gsol lo gcig ci yang ma gsol na yang /
NK028(sa)001:15545: sbribs cing skyems pa mi mnga' /
NK028(sa)001:15546: mas grong khyer gyis bus bas kyang mtho tsam pa las /
NK028(sa)001:15547: nyid la tshor ba'i rgyu dum bu yang mi mnga' ste /
NK028(sa)001:15548: rgyu skam zhing rid pa la grong pa legs 'ong ma'i bu mo legs skyes mas /
NK028(sa)001:15549: 'bras chen mkhar gzhong gang phul bas /
NK028(sa)001:15550: sku gser gyi gtan pa phyis pa bzhin gyur nas //
NK028(sa)001:15551: mtshan dang dpe byad du ldan par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:15552: de dang rjes su mthun par slob ma rnams kyang
NK028(sa)001:15553: mtshan dang dpe byad du ldan pa'i dbang dam pa
NK028(sa)001:15555: nyon mongs med pa 'bras kyi mchog /
NK028(sa)001:15556: zhi ba'i ngang la rab tu gnas //
NK028(sa)001:15557: bsod nams thob phyir dngos po 'di //
NK028(sa)001:15558: mtshan dang dpe byad rdzogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15559: 'di zas mchog dbang gi bkra shis le'u bcu bdun pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15560: sngon bcom ldan 'das byang chub kyi shing drung du gshegs pa'i dus su /
NK028(sa)001:15561: rtsa mchog bkra shis mas rtsa rma bya'i mgrin pa 'dra ba phyag du phul bas /
NK028(sa)001:15562: bcom ldan 'das kyi gdan du bting pas bdud kyi
NK028(sa)001:15563: mi tshugs shing bkra shis pa'i rdzas su ldan par
NK028(sa)001:15564: gyur to // de dang rjes su mthun par dbang rdzas 'dis dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15565: bkra shis pa dang bar chad kyis mi tshugs pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15566: sngon gyi drang srong rnams kyis grub pa yis //
NK028(sa)001:15567: bkra shis rtsa mchog rma bya'i mgrin pa 'dra //
NK028(sa)001:15568: legs pa kun rdzogs nyes pa med pa de //
NK028(sa)001:15569: 'gro ba'i don du bkra shis rdzogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15570: 'di ni r+ts+wa mchog dbang gi bkra shis le'u bco brgyad pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15571: sngon bcom ldan 'das skyes bu gyad kyi nye 'khor na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK028(sa)001:15572: byang phyogs tshangs pa nye mgon dang /
NK028(sa)001:15573: legs skyabs kyi bu ram shing shun pa dang ma bral ba dang /
NK028(sa)001:15574: sbrang rtsi yon du phul bas /
NK028(sa)001:15575: shin tu bkra shis pa'i rdzas dam pa dang ldan par gyur to //
NK028(sa)001:15576: de dang rjes su mthun par slob ma rnams la bkra shis pa'i rdzas 'dis dbang bskur bas /
NK028(sa)001:15577: bkra shis skye 'chi med pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK028(sa)001:15578: thams cad kun gyi snying po yon mchog te //
NK028(sa)001:15579: dad pa skyes nas mchog gnas byas pa dang //
NK028(sa)001:15580: 'bras bu smon lam myur du thob pa'i phyir //
NK028(sa)001:15581: 'di dag bkra shis myur du rdzogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15582: 'di ni shes rab mthar phyin dbang gi bkra shis le'u bcu dgu pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15583: sngon bcom ldan 'das kyis mdzad pa bcu gnyis yongs su rdzogs par mdzad pa'i dus su /
NK028(sa)001:15584: dpal chen po gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo
NK028(sa)001:15585: rje la mchod rten gnyis kyi dbang bskur bar mdzad
NK028(sa)001:15586: pas shin tu bkra shis pa'i rdzas dam pa dang
NK028(sa)001:15588: de dang rjes su mthun par slob ma rnams la
NK028(sa)001:15589: bkra shis pa'i rdzas mchod rten gnyis kyi dbang bskur
NK028(sa)001:15590: bas / bkra shis myur du mngon par rdzogs par
NK028(sa)001:15591: sangs rgyas pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK028(sa)001:15592: bas / / yon tan mthar rdzogs sangs rgyas sa la gnas //
NK028(sa)001:15593: go 'phang bla med rgyal thabs spyod pa gcig /
NK028(sa)001:15594: 'gro don mthar phyin 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon //
NK028(sa)001:15595: mdzad pa mthar phyin bkra shis rdzogs par shog /
NK028(sa)001:15596: 'di ni mchod rten dbang gi le'u ste nyi shu pa'o //
NK028(sa)001:15597: gnyis pa nus pa'i dbang lnga ste /
NK028(sa)001:15602: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:15603: dbang de lnga'i cho ga yang gong dang mthun no //
NK028(sa)001:15604: gsum pa gsang ba zab mo'i dbang la gsum ste /
NK028(sa)001:15606: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang dang //
NK028(sa)001:15607: dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang ngo //
NK028(sa)001:15608: dbang de gsum gyi cho ga'i dod ni /
NK028(sa)001:15610: theg pa lam 'khyer byang chub sems dpa' /
NK028(sa)001:15611: lha yum chen mo la phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi skor bar bsam /
NK028(sa)001:15612: tsa ka li'i lha bco lnga /
NK028(sa)001:15613: snying po tad+ya th+aa ga te /
NK028(sa)001:15614: dbang mdzad pa nyi shu'i dbang /
NK028(sa)001:15615: gdams ngag ni bu gcig pa la mas brtse ba lta bu //
NK028(sa)001:15616: byams pa dang snying rje sgom pa'i sgo nas //
NK028(sa)001:15617: sems can thams cad khyab par bsgoms //
NK028(sa)001:15618: lta ba ni bdag med kyi don rtogs /
NK028(sa)001:15619: bsgom pa ni rnam par mi rtog pa bsgom spyod
NK028(sa)001:15620: pa pha rol tu phyin pa drugaldana bsgrub pa nyams
NK028(sa)001:15621: su blang / 'bras su bcu gcig kun tu 'od thob /
NK028(sa)001:15623: yul dpon yul tshis byed pa lta bu /
NK028(sa)001:15624: spyi don la dmigs pa kho na'o //
NK028(sa)001:15625: de la ye shes kyi ngang sgom gyi dbang du byas na /
NK028(sa)001:15626: de yang bden pa gnyis kyi don bsgom pa ste /
NK028(sa)001:15627: de nas kun rdzob kyi dbang du byas na /
NK028(sa)001:15628: dbang rdzas lag tu gtad nas /
NK028(sa)001:15629: ting nge 'dzin dang cho gas dbang bskur bya /
NK028(sa)001:15630: bskur byed bcas pa ye shes chen po'i mdzad pa nyi shu'i dbang de rang yin pas /
NK028(sa)001:15631: don dam pa na snying gi dkyil du thig le lcog sgo tsam cig sgom /
NK028(sa)001:15632: 'od kyi rnam pa kha dog du'ang ma nges pa cig bsgom /
NK028(sa)001:15633: de'ang thig le stong pa skye ba med pa /
NK028(sa)001:15635: thig le de la brtag pas kha dog gi rnam pa ma 'gags pa cir yang snang ba /
NK028(sa)001:15636: kha dog rnams la brtags pas /
NK028(sa)001:15637: phyogs gcig pas gang du'ang ma 'grub po //
NK028(sa)001:15638: de bzhin du kun rdzob du dbang rdzas dang dbang
NK028(sa)001:15639: bskur ba la sogs cir yang ma 'gags par shar
NK028(sa)001:15640: yang / don dam par na gang du yang ma
NK028(sa)001:15641: dmigs par chos nyid spros pa thams cad dang bral
NK028(sa)001:15642: zhing ci'i ngo bor ma grub par gnas pa yin
NK028(sa)001:15643: yang / no // de ltar spros pa thams cad
NK028(sa)001:15644: dang bral ba'i ngang la ma bcos par gnas pa
NK028(sa)001:15645: med pa'i tshul gyi gnas par bya'o gsungs so //
NK028(sa)001:15646: de'i rjes la rtags kun rdzob ma 'gag pa'i snang cha /
NK028(sa)001:15647: rang nyid yum chen mo shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin mar bsgoms la /
NK028(sa)001:15648: spyod pa rnam bzhi lha dang mi 'bral bar bya ba ni /
NK028(sa)001:15649: bden pa gnyis zung du 'ajugapa'i lam pa zhes bya ste /
NK028(sa)001:15650: ye shes kyis ngang bsgom chen mo'i thad dkar gzigs shig /
NK028(sa)001:15651: da ni byang chub sems dpa'i gnas drug bshad na /
NK028(sa)001:15652: gang du bskur ba'i gnas ni /
NK028(sa)001:15653: bya rgod phung po'i ri'i rgyal po' khab du bskur //
NK028(sa)001:15654: gang gis bskur ba'i ston pa ni /
NK028(sa)001:15655: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi skur /
NK028(sa)001:15657: byang chub sems dpa' rgyal ba don grub la sogs pa la bskur /
NK028(sa)001:15659: ye shes mdzad pa nyi shu'i dbang bskur /
NK028(sa)001:15660: ci'i phyir na dbang bskur na mdzad pa nyi shu yongs su rdzogs pa 'am /
NK028(sa)001:15661: mi lus lha ru bsgrub par bya ba'i phyir bskur /
NK028(sa)001:15662: dgos pa ni bdud kyi dpung 'joms nas chos kyi rgyal srid chen po 'jug pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK028(sa)001:15664: gang gis gang la gang du ci lta bar //
NK028(sa)001:15665: tshul dang dgos par bcas pa rnam drug gis //
NK028(sa)001:15666: 'di ni byang chub sems dpa'i 'gag drug yin zhes so //
NK028(sa)001:15670: 'di dag pha rol tu phyin pa'i dbang gi gdams pa te /
NK028(sa)001:15671: phal la ma mchis thugs kyi dkyil du phyung /
NK028(sa)001:15672: a ho sa ma ya stam /
NK028(sa)001:15673: nor bu byi dor byas na dgos pa 'byung //
NK028(sa)001:15674: rtsa cha rnams su byas na rgal can 'phags //
NK028(sa)001:15675: drang po'i thig gdab sgur po ras su 'gro //
NK028(sa)001:15676: sbal bu pad+ma'i drung na 'dam la spyod ces gsungs so //
NK028(sa)001:15679: bsngo ba smon lam dang bkra shis brjod /
NK028(sa)001:15680: tshogs dang dga' ston rgya chen bya /
NK028(sa)001:15688: gshegs gsol dang bkra shis brjod la /
NK028(sa)001:15690: de ni byang chub sems dpa'i dbang gi them skas rdzogs so ////
